            { 738206991, "Fort Adamant" },
            { 738206992, "レリック：サイラ１　ＬＶ２" },
            { 738206994, "タンタ・サイラを怒らせぬうちに早く行け" },
            { 738206995, "ロビアンと再会できるなんて……！　君には本当に感謝しているよ" },
            { 738206996, "タンタ・サイラ……きっとあの方はまた来る……" },
            { 738206997, "この悪魔め！　まだシパールにいたのか！？　早く出ていけ！" },
            { 738206998, "仮セリフ12" },
            { 738206999, "仮セリフ13" },
            { 738207000, "仮セリフ14" },
            { 738207001, "仮セリフ15" },
            { 738207002, "おお タンタよ……お労しい……" },
            { 738207003, "ここからは上層です　身だしなみにはお気を付けを……" },
            { 738207004, "バロウの樹は神聖なものです　気軽に触れてはなりません" },
            { 738207005, "タンタ・サイラ！　あなたのお導きなら私はどこまででもついていきます！" },
            { 738207006, "羊の相手ばっかりするのに飽きちゃったよ……" },
            { 738207007, "オーデンったらお父さんが帰ってきたのが嬉しくて張り切ってるみたいよ！" },
            { 738207008, "聞いたかい？　タンタ・サイラの兵は皆 体を強化されているとかいないとか……" },
            { 738207009, "おなか減ったー！　なんで僕たちが作ってるのに僕たちが全部食べれないの？" },
            { 738207010, "働かざる者食うべからず！　今日も働くわよ！" },
            { 738207011, "ロビアン・キーン……噂とはかなり違うただの爺さんに見えるけどな……" },
            { 738207012, "先の事件で多くの人々が亡くなりました……" },
            { 738207013, "我々では化け物たちには歯が立たない……　あんただけが頼りだ" },
            { 738207014, "下層の奴らは落ち着きがなくて下品だな" },
            { 738207015, "ごみ処理場？　そんなとこシパールにあったなんて知らなかった！" },
            { 738207016, "図書館では静かにお願いいたします" },
            { 738207017, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>正面は避けたほうがいい" },
            { 738207018, "なんで？　あたしが負けると思うの？" },
            { 738207019, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>俺はただより安全で血を流さなくていい方法を提案してるだけだ" },
            { 738207020, "それには賛成　なるべく怪我はしたくない　でもほかに方法がないかも" },
            { 738207021, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>裏に回ったらどうだ？" },
            { 738207022, "門が閉まってたら考えるよ" },
            { 738207023, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>……" },
            { 738207024, "この化け物たちって" },
            { 738207025, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>言っただろ　ブレイク化したプレイノストの住人だ" },
            { 738207026, "ブレイクから逃げられなかったんだね" },
            { 738207027, "やっと兵士のおでましだね" },
            { 738207028, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>城に近づいたからな　気を抜くなよ" },
            { 738207029, "ほら　城に登れたでしょ" },
            { 738207030, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>さあ　玉座を目指すぞ" },
            { 738207031, "<iconChapterSumVfxAlt>ここから入れそうだな" },
            { 738207032, "いよいよだね　慎重にいくよ" },
            { 738207033, "投げ縄！" },
            { 738207034, "ロープみたいなやつ！" },
            { 738207035, "出でよ！" },
            { 738207036, "やめろ" },
            { 738207037, "一体何をしようとしているんだ？" },
            { 738207038, "お前を操ろうと思って" },
            { 738207039, "俺を操る！？" },
            { 738207040, "俺はお前の玩具じゃないんだよ 間抜け！" },
            { 738207041, "ちょっと！" },
            { 738207042, "あたしはただこの状況をどう切り抜けるかかんがえているの！" },
            { 738207043, "色々こっちにも都合あるのよ" },
            { 738207044, "クソ野郎" },
            { 738207081, "Pilo's city tour" },
            { 738207082, "To Town Square" },
            { 738207083, "To Pasture" },
            { 738207084, "To Graveyard" },
            { 738207085, "To Find Gravestone" },
            { 738207086, "To Upper City" },
            { 738207087, "To Mausoreum" },
            { 738207088, "To Bar" },
            { 738207089, "魔石１（魔力強化Ｌｖ１）" },
            { 738207090, "魔石２（魔力強化Ｌｖ２）" },
            { 738207091, "魔石３（魔力強化Ｌｖ３）" },
            { 738207092, "魔石４（体力強化Ｌｖ１）" },
            { 738207093, "魔法の威力が少し上がる" },
            { 738207094, "魔法の威力が上がる" },
            { 738207095, "魔法の威力がかなり上がる" },
            { 738207096, "ＥＰが少し増える" },
            { 738207097, "Learn Magic (SP Needed: <Unknown1> / Current SP <Unknown30> )" },
            { 738207099, "So, you're Guild-bound, I hear?" },
            { 738207100, "Guess you hear a lot of things." },
            { 738207101, "That I do. There's not a lot happens in this town I don't come to know of eventually." },
            { 738207102, "Huh." },
            { 738207103, "No idea if he can be trusted, but we might as well see what he can tell us, wouldn't you say?" },
            { 738207104, "What should I ask him?" },
            { 738207149, "Pray, lend me your ears. I've a fine song to play you!" },
            { 738207150, "Listen to his song?" },
            { 738207151, "So you will hear my melody after all?" },
            { 738207180, "Hello there. Can I get you something?" },
            { 738207181, "I was sorry to hear about Olevia." },
            { 738207182, "Just can't believe Tanta Sila did what she did..." },
            { 738207183, "You be careful out there. She's not one to mess with lightly." },
            { 738207184, "None of the folks from Praenost look too happy." },
            { 738207185, "Can't blame them, really." },
            { 738207186, "Time was they couldn't sing their Tanta's praises loud enough." },
            { 738207187, "You sure you don't want another before you go?" },
            { 738207188, "No better friend than a drink, or so they say." },
            { 738207189, "Hello, Frey." },
            { 738207190, "I was just pondering the fleeting nature of life..." },
            { 738207191, "One moment, we are laughing together, not a care in the world... The next, we are naught but dust on the wind..." },
            { 738207192, "What good can come of love in such a time? Surely it can only end in tragedy?" },
            { 738207193, "I hate to say it, but you might be right." },
            { 738207194, "Some music, perhaps? Though I fear it will do precious little to lift the mood..." },
            { 738207195, "Listen to his song?" },
            { 738207196, "Sure." },
            { 738207197, "Not right now." },
            { 738207198, "Then allow me to perform \"The Horrible Terror of Praenost.\"" },
            { 738207199, "He really needs some help naming these..." },
            { 738207200, "Praenost is a harsh and unforgiving land." },
            { 738207201, "Not all who make the journey there are fortunate enough to escape a fiery fate." },
            { 738207202, "And for those they leave behind, naught remains but emptiness..." },
            { 738207203, "You would do well to take care if you plan on venturing there yourself." },
            { 738207204, "What a pity..." },
            { 738207205, "A change of heart, perhaps? I pray that it is so." },
            { 738207206, "Not exactly the most illuminating of ditties, was it?" },
            { 738207207, "That's the trouble with these arty types—very little in the way of practical advice." },
            { 738207208, "What do you mean? \"Praenost bad. Stay away.\" That was pretty much the message, right?" },
            { 738207209, "Those who plan to venture to Praenost would do well to take care..." },
            { 738207210, "You! You there!" },
            { 738207211, "It's about Sir Robian. I—" },
            { 738207212, "Actually, it's about everything. The city, too. We...we owe you our thanks." },
            { 738207213, "Had you not been here, who knows how many more would have suffered?" },
            { 738207214, "I...could have done more." },
            { 738207215, "Please. I know you are in pain. But you must not lose heart." },
            { 738207216, "The bard at the square—Wallace—do you know him?" },
            { 738207217, "He may be a frivolous, nonsensical sort of person...but his talent is undeniable." },
            { 738207218, "Perhaps a tune might do you good? Truly, his music has the power to soothe the soul." },
            { 738207219, "Wait. You're not telling me she's... Really? That foppish nonsense?" },
            { 738207228, "The dutiful swordmaiden and the foppish bard, eh? What a pair." },
            { 738207229, "Yeah, it's like the plot of a corny romance novel." },
            { 738207232, "So you are going to face Tanta Sila?" },
            { 738207233, "Remember, she is not to be trifled with." },
            { 738207234, "You're young Olevia's friend..." },
            { 738207235, "Eleph, this is the girl Olevia was talking about." },
            { 738207236, "Th-the amazing girl?" },
            { 738207237, "Oh, come on. I wouldn't go that far." },
            { 738207238, "Olevia used to look after my Eleph a lot, you know." },
            { 738207239, "But I never heard her talk about another grown-up like she did you." },
            { 738207240, "You must have been very special to her." },
            { 738207241, "You think so?" },
            { 738207242, "And she was special to you too, I imagine." },
            { 738207243, "She was..." },
            { 738207244, "I guess I felt kinda sorry for her." },
            { 738207245, "Just felt like she needed someone, you know?" },
            { 738207246, "She was special." },
            { 738207247, "She never knew her parents, you know." },
            { 738207248, "They left her at the dump when she was just a baby." },
            { 738207249, "What? You're kidding..." },
            { 738207250, "It's no wonder she found it so hard to trust adults. Felt safer fending for herself." },
            { 738207251, "I never knew..." },
            { 738207252, "Hah! She was forever stealing things. And she never listened to anyone." },
            { 738207253, "But then, I suppose that's what made her such a little character." },
            { 738207254, "Heh. And such a handful..." },
            { 738207255, "She was just doing what she needed to survive." },
            { 738207256, "Hmm... Something tells me you know a little bit about that yourself." },
            { 738207257, "Guess you could say that." },
            { 738207258, "We were even more alike than I realized..." },
            { 738207259, "Guess we only ever actually spoke a few times." },
            { 738207260, "But we just kinda...connected, you know?" },
            { 738207261, "Y-you remind me of her." },
            { 738207262, "She was strong. And you could trust her." },
            { 738207263, "And she was lonely." },
            { 738207264, "Huh." },
            { 738207265, "Tanta Sila was a mighty warrior." },
            { 738207267, "I'd watch yourself out there if I were you." },
            { 738207271, "I felt so powerless... There was nothing I could do to help her. Nothing." },
            { 738207272, "But I won't let anything happen to my son. I can't." },
            { 738207273, "Dad?" },
            { 738207289, "And who doesn't want to spend quality time with their pals?" },
            { 738207290, "So, Milia, are you Wallace's..." },
            { 738207291, "Girlfriend?" },
            { 738207292, "Admirer?" },
            { 738207293, "Fangirl?" },
            { 738207294, "N-no! Of course not! My feelings are not—" },
            { 738207295, "I-I mean of course I... Never mind!" },
            { 738207296, "N-no! I am nothing of the sort!" },
            { 738207297, "Fan...girl? Whatever do you mean?" },
            { 738207298, "That you like him so much, like, it totally drives you insane." },
            { 738207299, "It...truly seems so to you?" },
            { 738207300, "His music gives me a certain...courage, that's all." },
            { 738207301, "A sense that it may not be altogether foolish to hope for a brighter tomorrow." },
            { 738207302, "Wow. I guess I'll have to listen harder." },
            { 738207303, "You plan to face Tanta Sila, do you not?" },
            { 738207304, "Those of my line have long been her most faithful protectors." },
            { 738207305, "Though such a legacy is no longer one to speak of with pride..." },
            { 738207306, "Take care. She is not to be trifled with." },
            { 738207308, "Uh...you didn't think it might be an idea to close up shop when the Break rolled into town?" },
            { 738207309, "Are you joking? If we give up on this place, we give up on life!" },
            { 738207310, "A drink at the end of a hard day's all most of these people have to look forward to." },
            { 738207311, "Wonderful. So they're not only doomed, they're all hopeless drunks, to boot." },
            { 738207312, "You should have a little something yourself." },
            { 738207313, "Have a drink?" },
            { 738207314, "One for the road, is it?" },
            { 738207316, "Maybe not." },
            { 738207349, "Do not try to stop me, Frey! I have been pushed beyond my limit!" },
            { 738207350, "\"Nothing we can do\"? How could you!" },
            { 738207351, "Have you not seen how the people suffer?" },
            { 738207352, "Indeed I have. And though I wish it were otherwise, I am powerless to aid them." },
            { 738207353, "Perhaps a song might—" },
            { 738207354, "A pox on your music! Were I never to hear it again, it would be too soon!" },
            { 738207355, "M-Milia..." },
            { 738207356, "It gives me courage, it is true." },
            { 738207357, "But you have no right to tell me how to face the present." },
            { 738207358, "Especially when you cannot escape the past!" },
            { 738207359, "Forgive me, fair maiden, but I fear I cannot bring myself to play." },
            { 738207360, "Perhaps this will go some way to assuaging your disappointment..." },
            { 738207363, "Murderer! Murderer!!!" },
            { 738207364, "You killed my daddy!" },
            { 738207365, "I'll never forgive you! You killed him!" },
            { 738207366, "Eleph! Stop that at once!" },
            { 738207396, "Can't believe you're still keeping this place going." },
            { 738207397, "The town won't survive without it." },
            { 738207398, "Yeah, I get it, but—" },
            { 738207399, "Look, it's simple. None of us know when we're gonna die, right?" },
            { 738207400, "And what do you need to get you through the day in a world where that's true?" },
            { 738207401, "Believe me, you're asking the wrong person." },
            { 738207402, "Hope, that's what." },
            { 738207403, "That or a good, stiff drink. Suppose a miracle cure wouldn't go amiss, either..." },
            { 738207404, "Anyway, something to help you believe that tomorrow will be better than today." },
            { 738207405, "Robian, Auden, all of us—that's what we're looking for." },
            { 738207406, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738207407, "You noticed, eh? Yeah, it'll probably taste a little different from normal." },
            { 738207408, "We've run out of the old Avoalet spice, see." },
            { 738207409, "So I've given things a little Visorian twist instead." },
            { 738207410, "Not quite the quality you're used to, but good enough to keep this place going." },
            { 738207447, "Good to see things are the same as always around here." },
            { 738207448, "Yep. No news is good news." },
            { 738207449, "Had any more thoughts on how you like the city, by the way?" },
            { 738207450, "We were talking about that?" },
            { 738207451, "I...think so. But I could be wrong." },
            { 738207452, "Anyway, how've you been finding it?" },
            { 738207453, "Do I like being in Cipal?" },
            { 738207454, "Well, not exactly conclusive, but it'll have to do." },
            { 738207457, "Anyway, here. Little something for the savior of the city." },
            { 738207458, "Whoa. What's this?" },
            { 738207459, "A few spices grown right here in Cipal, and a dash of inspiration." },
            { 738207460, "Alright... It's good!" },
            { 738207461, "You like it?" },
            { 738207462, "Didn't want it to be too sweet, you know? Wanted it to have a little bite." },
            { 738207463, "What do you think? A new drink for a new Cipal." },
            { 738207464, "Hell yeah. Keep 'em coming!" },
            { 738207465, "Guess what I've called it? The Frey!" },
            { 738207466, "You're serious? Come on, you knew I'd hate that!" },
            { 738207478, "My post here is a vital one, standing as I do in close proximity to both the square and the courtyard." },
            { 738207479, "You take your work pretty seriously, huh?" },
            { 738207480, "But of course! It is no mere workaday job. It is my vocation, and my greatest pride." },
            { 738207481, "Speaking of which, we guards agreed that you should be presented with this." },
            { 738207482, "Although I fear such formal trappings are not much to your liking..." },
            { 738207483, "Yes, not exactly your style, is it?" },
            { 738207484, "I dunno... Gotta say, it's a cute look on me." },
            { 738207485, "I would prefer that you did not make light of it! But I must say, it suits you well." },
            { 738207486, "Oi! Milia! What are you doing? Get back to your post!" },
            { 738207487, "Right away! Well, until next time." },
            { 738207489, "Some music to brighten your day?" },
            { 738207490, "What song should I request?" },
            { 738207525, "You may rest easy at last!" },
            { 738207526, "The boy has laid down his knife, and shall not pick it up again!" },
            { 738207527, "Even he now sees that to take up arms against the savior of the city would be ill-advised indeed!" },
            { 738207528, "And in time, I am sure he will come to learn that to hate a hero such as yourself is pure foolishness." },
            { 738207529, "Give me the knife." },
            { 738207530, "I—sorry?" },
            { 738207531, "The boy's knife. Hand it over." },
            { 738207532, "But I cannot. I threw it away." },
            { 738207533, "Whatever can the matter be?" },
            { 738207573, "[Debug] Revive" },
            { 738207574, "[Skill Magic] Cure Flower" },
            { 738207575, "Create curative flowers to restore EP." },
            { 738207576, "You're Frey, aren't you?" },
            { 738207577, "I'm Pilo." },
            { 738207579, "I'm not a hero. Not now, never will be." },
            { 738207580, "Did you want something?" },
            { 738207581, "Um... Just wondering if there's...anything I can do?" },
            { 738207582, "I don't know, I could... Hey, I could show you around town! You haven't been here long, right?" },
            { 738207583, "A guided tour? What an excellent idea!" },
            { 738207584, "Certainly couldn't hurt to get the lay of the land." },
            { 738207585, "No. Thanks, but I'm not in the mood." },
            { 738207586, "Oh, don't say that!" },
            { 738207685, "Look, I'll be waiting for you, alright? When you're ready, just let me know!" },
