            { 738208969, "Wake up, princess." },
            { 738208970, "Don't call me princess." },
            { 738208971, "Fine, \"Alfre Holland.\"" },
            { 738208972, "Frey. It's just Frey." },
            { 738208973, "Whatever, \"Frey.\" My holiday started three hours ago, so step up." },
            { 738208975, "Keep walking." },
            { 738208976, "Hey!" },
            { 738208977, "Where do you think you're going?" },
            { 738208978, "Let's go." },
            { 738208979, "Move it." },
            { 738208980, "Gotcha workin' overtime, huh?" },
            { 738208981, "I haven't got all day." },
            { 738208982, "Eyes on the road!" },
            { 738208983, "You see those two officers standing there?" },
            { 738208984, "That's your spot." },
            { 738208985, "Wait. Aren't you gonna take these off?" },
            { 738208986, "Very funny." },
            { 738208987, "Hey, Loretta. Got holiday plans?" },
            { 738208988, "Having mi familia all over to our place." },
            { 738208989, "My condolences." },
            { 738208990, "How 'bout you, girl?" },
            { 738208992, "Hey, how's it going, Gino?" },
            { 738208993, "Oh... Again, kiddo?" },
            { 738208994, "Couldn't stay away from your handsome face." },
            { 738208995, "You lose weight?" },
            { 738208996, "Oh, yeah... Thanks for noticing!" },
            { 738208997, "Honorable Judge Maya Bird presiding in the case of the People of the State of New York vs. Alfre Holland." },
            { 738208998, "Defendant charged with attempted grand larceny." },
            { 738208999, "How do you plead?" },
            { 738209000, "Not guilty, Your Honor." },
            { 738209001, "I see you've waived your right to an attorney." },
            { 738209002, "Do you think that is wise?" },
            { 738209003, "Yeah, I can handle it." },
            { 738209004, "Pro se. It's Latin for \"I'm standing—\"" },
            { 738209005, "I know what \"pro se\" is." },
            { 738209006, "You okay with this, Gino?" },
            { 738209007, "I am, Your Honor." },
            { 738209008, "Arrogant for a girl with a file as thick as a tree trunk." },
            { 738209009, "It hasn't been easy! It's not like I've had—" },
            { 738209010, "Spare me your sob story." },
            { 738209011, "Officer, please remove her cuffs." },
            { 738209012, "Hey!" },
            { 738209013, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209014, "Okay, it's—it's fine. It's fine." },
            { 738209015, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209016, "Officer, leave the cuffs off." },
            { 738209017, "Clever trick." },
            { 738209018, "Thanks. One of my many gifts." },
            { 738209019, "You've had a nice run with misdemeanors. Years of petty theft." },
            { 738209020, "But now you've moved on to felonies: auto theft, breaking and entering..." },
            { 738209021, "Well, you know what they say." },
            { 738209022, "When you can turn your hobby into your occupation, you're living your best self." },
            { 738209023, "If you think this is your best life then you really are a lost cause." },
            { 738209024, "It's almost your twenty-first birthday. Maybe it's time you got your shit together?" },
            { 738209025, "It's not my fault. My mother left me outside—" },
            { 738209026, "Do you know how many times I've heard this story in my courtroom?" },
            { 738209027, "Take accountability for your actions." },
            { 738209028, "Has anyone else been left outside the Holland Tunnel?" },
            { 738209029, "Only a monster abandons their child the day they're born." },
            { 738209030, "You know, silver lining out of this whole thing..." },
            { 738209031, "After years in the foster system, you're mad." },
            { 738209032, "No, you know what? It was super fun getting tossed from home to home." },
            { 738209033, "In spite of everything, you finished high school. You're smart." },
            { 738209034, "But you'd rather take the easy way out. I get it." },
            { 738209035, "I mean, why should you give a damn about anybody else when nobody ever gave a damn about you?" },
            { 738209036, "Are you familiar with the \"persistent felony offender\" law?" },
            { 738209037, "Also known as the \"three strikes\" law?" },
            { 738209038, "W-wait, you can't do that, I never hurt anyone." },
            { 738209039, "Just yourself." },
            { 738209040, "You have two previous felony thefts." },
            { 738209041, "And with this new one, your grand total will be three." },
            { 738209042, "This could put you away for a very, very long time." },
            { 738209043, "You have so much—" },
            { 738209044, "Potential?" },
            { 738209045, "I can do so much more with my life?" },
            { 738209046, "I-I'm a smart girl with a bright future?" },
            { 738209047, "I was going to say you have so much anger and resentment in you, I'm not sure you'll ever amount to anything at all." },
            { 738209048, "Truth hurts." },
            { 738209049, "You think I don't know you? I was you." },
            { 738209050, "It was the end of the line for me, too." },
            { 738209051, "I did things I shouldn't have." },
            { 738209052, "But I turned it around. I found purpose." },
            { 738209053, "So..." },
            { 738209054, "In the holiday spirit, I'm going to give you an early present." },
            { 738209055, "Try not to piss it away." },
            { 738209056, "I'm going to release you under the condition you serve 120 hours of community service." },
            { 738209057, "Thanks. You won't regret it." },
            { 738209058, "I probably will." },
            { 738209059, "We clear?" },
            { 738209060, "Good. You're free to go." },
            { 738209061, "Frey. One more thing." },
            { 738209062, "Happy almost birthday." },
            { 738209063, "It's not too late to start using your gifts to help others." },
            { 738209065, "Shit, that was close." },
            { 738209066, "I gotta get out of this city while I still can." },
            { 738209068, "I need to go straight home." },
            { 738209070, "Don't wanna get myself in trouble again." },
            { 738209071, "I am so tired of living in this dump." },
            { 738209072, "Gotta get the hell outta here." },
            { 738209073, "Ugh, I hate the cold. Gotta get inside..." },
            { 738209074, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209075, "Hello." },
            { 738209076, "Goodbye." },
            { 738209077, "Oh, fuck..." },
            { 738209078, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209079, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209080, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209081, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209082, "Aw, Frey. Thought we wouldn't find you?" },
            { 738209083, "Hey, uh... Uh..." },
            { 738209084, "Lisa!" },
            { 738209085, "Lisa? Really? I thought she was Lisa." },
            { 738209086, "That's Chrissy!" },
            { 738209087, "Huh. Well, in my defense, you don't really look like a Lisa." },
            { 738209088, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209089, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209090, "Where is it?" },
            { 738209091, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209092, "I don't have it, alright? There were complications." },
            { 738209093, "Not like I wanted to get caught stealing the car, but...here we are." },
            { 738209094, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209095, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209096, "We don't like complications!" },
            { 738209097, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209098, "You're running out of chances." },
            { 738209099, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209100, "Get the fuck back here, Frey!" },
            { 738209101, "No turning back now." },
            { 738209102, "Need to get out of these back streets." },
            { 738209106, "Damn! Can't go this way." },
            { 738209107, "Maybe it's safer to go through the alley." },
            { 738209108, "Where the fuck are you, Frey?" },
            { 738209109, "Yeah, there's no point in running, you know!" },
            { 738209110, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209111, "Won't they just give up already?" },
            { 738209112, "I gotta find a way out of here." },
            { 738209113, "Almost there." },
            { 738209114, "Hopefully I'll lose them when I get out on the street." },
            { 738209115, "You really thought you could outrun us?" },
            { 738209116, "Shit!" },
            { 738209117, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209118, "Homer must be waiting for me." },
            { 738209119, "Better get inside before I freeze." },
            { 738209120, "I can't get in from here." },
            { 738209121, "Need to go up through the window like always." },
            { 738209122, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209123, "She doesn't like this, but it's all I have." },
            { 738209124, "I wonder where Homer's at." },
            { 738209125, "\"'Curiouser and curiouser!' cried Alice.\"" },
            { 738209126, "Wish I could find that rabbit hole and tumble away to wonderland..." },
            { 738209127, "My favorite kicks." },
            { 738209128, "I could stare at you guys all day." },
            { 738209129, "Bottle's half-empty." },
            { 738209130, "Or just...empty." },
            { 738209131, "Homer sure isn't pulling her weight with the chores." },
            { 738209132, "Do I need to do everything myself?" },
            { 738209133, "My ticket out." },
            { 738209134, "Finally I can start over. Took long enough, though..." },
            { 738209135, "Hey, Homer." },
            { 738209136, "I'm sorry I'm late, I know." },
            { 738209137, "You miss me?" },
            { 738209138, "Oh!" },
            { 738209139, "Well, thank you, but my birthday isn't for another few days." },
            { 738209140, "Tell you what, I...almost forgot." },
            { 738209141, "Been so busy recently." },
            { 738209142, "Oh, well, you know... Important things to do." },
            { 738209143, "Holding court, slaying dragons..." },
            { 738209144, "I'll let you in on a secret, but I'm a pretty big deal." },
            { 738209145, "Real big deal." },
            { 738209146, "Everybody needs me." },
            { 738209147, "We are getting out of this city, Homer." },
            { 738209148, "Away from the assholes, the garbage, the cops. I..." },
            { 738209149, "I got us just enough to get us started." },
            { 738209150, "Yeah. I promise we'll go somewhere that loves cats." },
            { 738209151, "Even ones like you." },
            { 738209152, "God...I just can't wait for clean air. Bright skies." },
            { 738209153, "No more chases, no more cops, no more fights..." },
            { 738209154, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209155, "Tomorrow. One more sleep, and we are out of here." },
            { 738209156, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209157, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209158, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209159, "Homer! Come on, baby!" },
            { 738209160, "No! No! No!!!" },
            { 738209161, "Homer! Holy shit!" },
            { 738209162, "Okay, we gotta get outta here. Now!" },
            { 738209163, "Door's no good!" },
            { 738209164, "Window it is." },
            { 738209166, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209167, "And finally..." },
            { 738209168, "The blaze that engulfed the abandoned building in the Hell's Kitchen district of Manhattan has been ruled as arson." },
            { 738209169, "Luckily, no one was harmed in the fire." },
            { 738209170, "The FDNY believe it was set by some local gang members." },
            { 738209171, "The suspects are still at large." },
            { 738209172, "Frey." },
            { 738209173, "What happened to you? You look like hell." },
            { 738209174, "Are you allergic?" },
            { 738209175, "What?" },
            { 738209176, "To cats. Are you allergic to cats?" },
            { 738209177, "No, I-I love cats, b—" },
            { 738209178, "Are you in trouble?" },
            { 738209179, "Good." },
            { 738209180, "She likes wet food—the flaky kind, not pâté." },
            { 738209181, "She needs a warm place to sleep. Maybe a lap every once in a while." },
            { 738209182, "And she needs a bath, but...good luck with that." },
            { 738209183, "What are you doing, Frey?" },
            { 738209184, "The right thing." },
            { 738209185, "Her name is Homer. Promise me you'll look after her." },
            { 738209186, "Promise!" },
            { 738209187, "Thank you." },
            { 738209188, "Now...I'm gonna mark my big birthday where it all began." },
            { 738209189, "Gotta find a bus to the Holland Tunnel." },
            { 738209191, "This isn't the right way." },
            { 738209192, "Are you doing this or not, Frey?" },
            { 738209193, "Need to get back to the avenue and find that bus." },
            { 738209195, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209196, "Full circle." },
            { 738209197, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209198, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209199, "Thanks, mom." },
            { 738209201, "Wonder what that is..." },
            { 738209202, "It's beautiful." },
            { 738209203, "Must be worth some serious cash." },
            { 738209204, "Who would leave it in a dump like this?" },
            { 738209205, "Well, finders keepers." },
            { 738209206, "I'll grab it, sell it, get Homer back, and then we're outta here." },
            { 738209207, "Nope, not getting in that way." },
            { 738209208, "Must be another way." },
            { 738209209, "Place is abandoned." },
            { 738209210, "Doesn't look like there's an alarm..." },
            { 738209211, "I mean...wow." },
            { 738209212, "Who says there's no such thing as second chances..." },
            { 738209213, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209214, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209215, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209216, "What. The actual. Fu—" },
            { 738209217, "Where am I?" },
            { 738209218, "What's happened to me?" },
            { 738209219, "Is that a...throne?" },
            { 738209220, "Damn, that is a serious draft..." },
            { 738209221, "What's going on outside?" },
            { 738209222, "Whoa." },
            { 738209223, "Where on earth is this?" },
            { 738209224, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209225, "Athia." },
            { 738209226, "Who's there?" },
            { 738209227, "And technically not \"Earth.\"" },
            { 738209228, "Where are you?" },
            { 738209229, "Right here! At the end of your arm." },
            { 738209230, "The thing that you so fruitlessly tried to remove." },
            { 738209231, "Oh, hello! Yes! Oh, perhaps you're smarter than you look." },
            { 738209232, "No." },
            { 738209233, "Yes." },
            { 738209234, "N-no!" },
            { 738209235, "Yes!" },
            { 738209236, "You—the one talking to me right now—are this..." },
            { 738209237, "Cuff?" },
            { 738209238, "\"Cuff\"? That's a bit reductive, isn't it, \"Cuff\"?" },
            { 738209239, "Pfft. Gauntlet, maybe. Vambrace..." },
            { 738209240, "Oh! Vambrace. Vaaambraaace." },
            { 738209241, "Yeah. No, it's definitely \"Vambrace.\"" },
            { 738209242, "No, no, no. This is batshit bananas." },
            { 738209243, "Argh! And yet it's the truth..." },
            { 738209244, "Stop! You're hurting...me! Owww!" },
            { 738209245, "Seriously?" },
            { 738209246, "No." },
            { 738209247, "But what you're doing is completely futile." },
            { 738209248, "How is this happening!?" },
            { 738209249, "Well, what were you doing before this was happening, hm?" },
            { 738209250, "I was—" },
            { 738209251, "Doesn't matter." },
            { 738209255, "Still here..." },
            { 738209256, "Whoever is doing this, stop!" },
            { 738209257, "This is one sick joke! I am outta here." },
            { 738209258, "You can't run away from me." },
            { 738209259, "I am literally attached to you." },
            { 738209260, "Why don't we settle down a bit and talk about ourselves?" },
            { 738209261, "Talk about our interests in life, perhaps?" },
            { 738209262, "I am not hearing this! This is all a bad dream!" },
            { 738209263, "Be careful not to trip on anything." },
            { 738209264, "You can also see things!?" },
            { 738209265, "This cannot be fucking real." },
            { 738209266, "Wake up. Wake up, girl." },
            { 738209267, "Come on, you're asleep or you jumped. You're dead." },
            { 738209268, "You jumped and you're dead and this is hell. This is what hell is." },
            { 738209269, "Or you've finally snapped. This is what crazy feels like." },
            { 738209270, "You're not asleep, you're not dead. Not crazy." },
            { 738209271, "Well, maybe crazy, but that's separate." },
            { 738209274, "Listen to me, Frey!" },
            { 738209275, "How the hell do you know my name?" },
            { 738209276, "We are bonded." },
            { 738209277, "\"Bonded\"? What do you mean, \"bonded\"?" },
            { 738209278, "Why is this happening?" },
            { 738209279, "This is...no! Unbond! Unbond now!" },
            { 738209280, "As you can see, you're stuck with me, and I with you." },
            { 738209281, "And only you can hear me." },
            { 738209282, "Stop! Stop talking! This is completely insane!" },
            { 738209284, "Frey, slow down. You need to listen to me." },
            { 738209285, "No, what I need is to figure out how to get back." },
            { 738209286, "I-I thought I wanted out. I was wrong. I was in a bad place..." },
            { 738209287, "Well, this place might be worse, depending on how you look at it..." },
            { 738209288, "What do you mean?" },
            { 738209289, "Quiet!" },
            { 738209290, "What?" },
            { 738209291, "Hide!" },
            { 738209292, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209293, "Is that a motherfucking dragon!?" },
            { 738209294, "Shh! Don't let it see you." },
            { 738209295, "You think?" },
            { 738209296, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209297, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209298, "Is it gone?" },
            { 738209299, "Yes, and we should leave this place as well." },
            { 738209300, "With that thing out there?" },
            { 738209301, "I don't think so." },
            { 738209302, "I'm sure the creature is far away by now. And besides..." },
            { 738209303, "What?" },
            { 738209304, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209336, "So this is Athia?" },
            { 738209337, "Junoon." },
            { 738209338, "Junoon? I thought you said—" },
            { 738209339, "Athia, big picture. Junoon, small picture. Junoon is part of Athia." },
            { 738209340, "I get it. Like New York City versus New York State." },
            { 738209341, "Exactly. I think." },
            { 738209342, "I have no idea what Newark is." },
            { 738209343, "No, not Newark. New York." },
            { 738209344, "Is there a difference?" },
            { 738209345, "About a million." },
            { 738209347, "Okay, so let me get this straight." },
            { 738209348, "I'm somewhere that's \"not what I would call 'Earth'\"..." },
            { 738209349, "I'm seeing freaking dragons, and...oh yeah, I'm talking to a fucking cuff!" },
            { 738209350, "Vambrace." },
            { 738209351, "Hey, Cuff." },
            { 738209352, "So, if we are \"bonding\"—" },
            { 738209353, "Correction: bonded." },
            { 738209354, "Whatever. If we are stuck with each other, then what's your deal?" },
            { 738209355, "My deal?" },
            { 738209356, "Who are you?" },
            { 738209357, "I am what you see." },
            { 738209358, "Lovely. And I suppose you'll tell me more if I answer your riddles three?" },
            { 738209360, "I don't follow." },
            { 738209361, "Never mind." },
            { 738209363, "Why were you rusting at that old shop anyway?" },
            { 738209364, "Good question. I've been wondering that myself." },
            { 738209365, "All I do know is that before I visited Earth, I was here in Athia." },
            { 738209366, "Wait, what?" },
            { 738209367, "That means it must be your fault I wound up here!" },
            { 738209368, "How dare you? It was nothing to do with me!" },
            { 738209369, "If you must know, I'm as keen to find out what brought us here as you are." },
            { 738209370, "So, have you always been...this?" },
            { 738209371, "This?" },
            { 738209372, "This. This...chatty bling." },
            { 738209373, "As I recall...no." },
            { 738209374, "What do you recall?" },
            { 738209375, "Hmmm. I traveled here." },
            { 738209376, "Athia was not my home. I, like you, am an outsider." },
            { 738209377, "When I arrived, there was a lot of turmoil between the Tantas." },
            { 738209378, "The who-whas?" },
            { 738209379, "The Tantas." },
            { 738209380, "They were four very powerful women who ruled Athia. Each with a special ability." },
            { 738209381, "Like, what...magic or something?" },
            { 738209382, "If by \"magic,\" you mean the ability to turn me into an inanimate object, then yes." },
            { 738209385, "What in all creation is that contraption?" },
            { 738209386, "It's a smartphone." },
            { 738209387, "It's for texting, calling, games, videos, taking selfies, and—" },
            { 738209388, "—which by the way, I am not gonna explain to you, so don't bother asking." },
            { 738209389, "I know what a selfie is." },
            { 738209390, "Really?" },
            { 738209391, "Not really." },
            { 738209392, "What else can that thing do?" },
            { 738209393, "Hey, look at you." },
            { 738209394, "I'd be careful..." },
            { 738209400, "Come on, don't be shy." },
            { 738209401, "Seriously, I wouldn't. Let's just keep moving." },
            { 738209402, "Why are you so freaked out by this fella?" },
            { 738209403, "Because it's not as it seems." },
            { 738209408, "You tell me that now? Shit!" },
            { 738209409, "What the—" },
            { 738209410, "Don't start panicking now!" },
            { 738209416, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209417, "Did I just do that?" },
            { 738209418, "Well, definitely with my assistance." },
            { 738209419, "I did not just do that." },
            { 738209420, "We did." },
            { 738209421, "I just moved shit with my mind." },
            { 738209422, "Perhaps our connection has somehow awoken some abilities—" },
            { 738209423, "I just moved shit...with my mind." },
            { 738209424, "I just keep hearing \"I,\" \"I,\" \"I.\"" },
            { 738209425, "I just moved shit. With my freaking mind! Ha ha!" },
            { 738209426, "Yeah, okay, that is something I do now. I do magic, talk to sentient cuffs, kill jacked-up beasts—you know what?" },
            { 738209427, "I'll probably fly next." },
            { 738209428, "Now you're just being ridiculous." },
            { 738209429, "Oh, that's too far? Good to know there's a line." },
            { 738209430, "If you could just master these new abilities—with my help of course—" },
            { 738209431, "Um, did you not just see me take out that gnarly beast?" },
            { 738209460, "Oh, fuck! What now?" },
            { 738209461, "Well, for starters, I think we should run." },
            { 738209462, "Too late for that!" },
            { 738209463, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209464, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209474, "That's not a good thing, is it?" },
            { 738209475, "Probably not..." },
            { 738209477, "Okay, this is awesome! I am catching some serious air!" },
            { 738209496, "What? How does that thing not even have a scratch!?" },
            { 738209497, "Do you think it's dead? The dragon?" },
            { 738209519, "Oh... Whoa, hey!" },
            { 738209520, "Hey! Over here!" },
            { 738209521, "...The hell?" },
            { 738209522, "Move, monster!" },
            { 738209523, "Hey! The fuck you calling \"monster\"!?" },
            { 738209524, "The monster speaks!" },
            { 738209525, "Yeah, of course I speak! And put your pointy stick away, asshole!" },
            { 738209526, "Move!" },
            { 738209527, "Alright! Moving..." },
            { 738209529, "Where are we now?" },
            { 738209530, "This is the city of Cipal." },
            { 738209531, "Why are they speaking English?" },
            { 738209532, "It's my experience that languages share commonalities across many dimensions." },
            { 738209533, "Okay... Any answer works for me, I guess." },
            { 738209534, "Quiet!" },
            { 738209535, "Keep moving, fiend!" },
            { 738209536, "Of course. Back in court." },
            { 738209537, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209538, "Easy!" },
            { 738209539, "Settle! Settle!" },
            { 738209540, "Who are you, child?" },
            { 738209541, "Who are you?" },
            { 738209543, "I would humble thyself and answer their questions." },
            { 738209544, "I got this. I'm used to repping \"thyself.\"" },
            { 738209545, "I don't think you comprehend the gravity of your situation." },
            { 738209546, "I've gotten myself out of much tougher scrapes than this, thank you very much." },
            { 738209547, "So why don't you shut your shiny mouth and let me do the talking?" },
            { 738209548, "Look at her! She speaks with invisible beings!" },
            { 738209549, "Is she in cahoots with demons?" },
            { 738209550, "What? No! And who uses \"cahoots\"?" },
            { 738209551, "I would like to hear the answer to Councilwoman Bellette's question, child." },
            { 738209552, "My name is Frey Holland." },
            { 738209553, "I do not know how I got here. I am exhausted, I am starving, and all I want is to go home." },
            { 738209554, "Her vestments are strange. Where is she from?" },
            { 738209555, "Hell's Kitchen." },
            { 738209556, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209557, "You see? She is hellspawn—how else could she survive in the Corruption?" },
            { 738209558, "Please... How did you emerge from the corruption of Junoon unscathed?" },
            { 738209559, "I wouldn't exactly say \"unscathed\"—" },
            { 738209560, "'Tis because she and the Corruption are one and the same!" },
            { 738209561, "We must execute her immediately!" },
            { 738209562, "Wait, what? No!" },
            { 738209563, "That's crazy! I don't even know how I got here!" },
            { 738209565, "Please, listen to me!" },
            { 738209566, "I believe we need her!" },
            { 738209567, "Who wishes to address the Council?" },
            { 738209568, "Great. Wound up right back in court..." },
            { 738209570, "I must be cursed or something." },
            { 738209571, "You really think they're gonna kill me?" },
            { 738209572, "I'm not sure..." },
            { 738209573, "Don't you move a muscle!" },
            { 738209574, "I said, keep still!" },
            { 738209575, "Move once more and you're in for it!" },
            { 738209576, "Both Auden Keen and Councilman Jennesh have made very compelling arguments." },
            { 738209577, "The Council is divided. Therefore, there shall be no blood spilled today." },
            { 738209578, "But..." },
            { 738209579, "Heed my warning, child—if you prove a threat, we will have no choice but to eliminate you." },
            { 738209580, "Take her to the Tower of Binnoi!" },
            { 738209581, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209582, "Please, Councilwoman Bellette, your ruling is too harsh!" },
            { 738209583, "The Council is adjourned!" },
            { 738209584, "She has done nothing wrong!" },
            { 738209585, "Wait, wha—Tower of Binnoi? What's a Tower of Binnoi?" },
            { 738209586, "I believe it's a prison." },
            { 738209587, "Please!" },
            { 738209588, "What? Oh hell no, I'm not getting locked up again!" },
            { 738209589, "Let me go! Let me go!" },
            { 738209590, "Don't touch me, asshole!" },
            { 738209591, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209592, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209593, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209594, "Get up." },
            { 738209595, "Get up." },
            { 738209596, "Get up." },
            { 738209597, "Get up, get up, GET UP!" },
            { 738209598, "Look. I am imprisoned a million miles from home in a Ren Faire nightmare. Just let me die in peace." },
            { 738209599, "If you die, I'm just a meaningless bauble that they bury you with." },
            { 738209600, "And I am fine with that. Just...leave me alone." },
            { 738209601, "Oh, and tell me how exactly this is my fault." },
            { 738209602, "Can we just not talk?" },
            { 738209603, "Fine. Fine by me. Suit yourself. I'd love a bit of silence." },
            { 738209604, "You know, I never thought I'd miss the Hell's Kitchen courthouse." },
            { 738209605, "It appears to be too high." },
            { 738209606, "Does it? Thanks." },
            { 738209607, "Shit. Of course it's locked." },
            { 738209608, "Dammit! This is going nowhere!" },
            { 738209609, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209610, "Did that piss bucket do something to annoy you?" },
            { 738209611, "No. You know what? You did!" },
            { 738209612, "Because of you, I'm not getting back to—" },
            { 738209613, "Newark?" },
            { 738209614, "New York! How hard is that to remember?" },
            { 738209615, "Oh, maybe as hard to remember as Vambrace?" },
            { 738209616, "If memory serves me right, you weren't exactly in the best of spirits when our paths first crossed." },
            { 738209617, "I'm not sure why you're so determined to return." },
            { 738209618, "You know what? I'm just gonna use magic to bust us out of here." },
            { 738209619, "It isn't advisable to use your abilities in front of them." },
            { 738209620, "Why not? They already think I'm in \"cahoots\" with demons!" },
            { 738209621, "But they will hang you for being a heretic." },
            { 738209622, "What, like a Salem situation?" },
            { 738209623, "Do you expect me to know what that means?" },
            { 738209624, "Look, we did it your way, and now we're gonna try it my way." },
            { 738209625, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209626, "Did I just do that?" },
            { 738209627, "Quick! Put this on." },
            { 738209628, "Who's there?" },
            { 738209629, "I will free you, but you have to put it on and do as I say." },
            { 738209630, "Okay, it's on." },
            { 738209631, "You..." },
            { 738209632, "You're the one who stood up for me in court." },
            { 738209633, "Why are you doing this?" },
            { 738209634, "Because I believe you. But we must hurry." },
            { 738209635, "How did you sneak past the guards?" },
            { 738209636, "I prepared a tincture of slumber baked into a pastry." },
            { 738209637, "Huh, looks can really be deceiving." },
            { 738209638, "Let's go! Before they wake." },
            { 738209639, "W-wait! Where are we going? What's your angle?" },
            { 738209640, "Angle?" },
            { 738209641, "She did defend you in court, and right now she seems to be your only option." },
            { 738209642, "Fair point." },
            { 738209643, "Alright, wherever we're going, there's gotta be food." },
            { 738209644, "As you can see, our land suffers." },
            { 738209645, "Everything that corruption touches—" },
            { 738209646, "It breaks. Yeah. I saw it up close." },
            { 738209647, "It's real fucked up in there." },
            { 738209648, "Uh...not pleasant." },
            { 738209649, "Indeed. Athia is all but lost." },
            { 738209650, "Where did the break-shit come from?" },
            { 738209651, "I'll tell you soon enough. We must keep moving." },
            { 738209652, "I would advise staying off the main thoroughfares." },
            { 738209653, "Less chance of being spotted." },
            { 738209654, "You know, we should stay off the main thoroughfares." },
            { 738209655, "Less chance of being spotted." },
            { 738209656, "Are you trying to get yourself captured again?" },
            { 738209657, "There are guards in that direction." },
            { 738209658, "Come this way." },
            { 738209659, "Fan out! She can't have got far!" },
            { 738209660, "It appears they've noticed that you're missing." },
            { 738209661, "Head for the shadows and keep moving." },
            { 738209662, "Stick to the shadows!" },
            { 738209663, "Great idea!" },
            { 738209664, "Why can't you be more like her? She likes all my ideas." },
            { 738209665, "Wow, nice digs. Some shmancy houses." },
            { 738209666, "This is where the nobility live." },
            { 738209667, "Ah yes, the \"Upper East Side.\"" },
            { 738209668, "Technically, we're in the north of the city." },
            { 738209669, "This way now. Follow me." },
            { 738209670, "Are you sure you don't need to follow that peasant girl?" },
            { 738209671, "What happened here?" },
            { 738209672, "After what you called the \"break-shit\"—" },
            { 738209673, "Let's just go with the Break." },
            { 738209674, "After the Break occurred, people fled their villages." },
            { 738209675, "Cipal is the last bastion." },
            { 738209676, "Nowhere left to go... A generation on the streets." },
            { 738209679, "You are safe now." },
            { 738209680, "Uh, thanks." },
            { 738209681, "We are close to where I live." },
            { 738209682, "Come, I have food." },
            { 738209685, "Bit of a half-hearted thank-you, I must say..." },
            { 738209686, "Nobody does anything nice without wanting something in return." },
            { 738209687, "I have trust issues." },
            { 738209688, "Hmm. Do you trust me?" },
            { 738209689, "What you and I have is an unholy alliance at best." },
            { 738209690, "I couldn't get rid of you even if I wanted to." },
            { 738209691, "She did just risk her own life to get you out of jail." },
            { 738209692, "Point taken." },
            { 738209693, "Plus, she promised me food." },
            { 738209694, "We can speak freely here." },
            { 738209695, "I am Auden Keen." },
            { 738209696, "Daughter of Robian and Calista Keen." },
            { 738209697, "Oh, uh...I'm Frey Holland." },
            { 738209698, "Daughter of...who the eff knows." },
            { 738209699, "I don't know how to respond..." },
            { 738209700, "It's okay." },
            { 738209701, "Boring story. I'm over it." },
            { 738209702, "Liar." },
            { 738209703, "My father was a notable Cognoscent." },
            { 738209704, "\"Cognizant\"?" },
            { 738209705, "Cognoscent." },
            { 738209706, "You say \"tomato,\" I say \"tomahto.\" Tomato. Tomahto." },
            { 738209708, "You are very strange, Frey." },
            { 738209709, "Cognoscents are Athia's most highly respected scholars." },
            { 738209710, "And my mother was a general." },
            { 738209711, "Oof. That is a lot to live up to." },
            { 738209712, "Wait, \"was\"?" },
            { 738209714, "I've been on my own almost my whole life." },
            { 738209715, "I know what that's like." },
            { 738209716, "So you must feel the same way—" },
            { 738209717, "That we got royally screwed?" },
            { 738209718, "That we must help others." },
            { 738209719, "Tomato, tomahto." },
            { 738209720, "This is my home." },
            { 738209721, "You live in a bar?" },
            { 738209722, "Above." },
            { 738209723, "I like you more and more." },
            { 738209724, "So, about that food?" },
            { 738209725, "You had this on you the whole time?" },
            { 738209726, "I needed you to follow me, Frey Holland, daughter of \"who the eff knows.\"" },
            { 738209727, "Hmm. Just Frey is fine, and...well played." },
            { 738209728, "Well, thanks for the jailbreak, lady—and the apple—but this is where we part ways." },
            { 738209729, "Please wait!" },
            { 738209730, "I need your help to save my homeland!" },
            { 738209731, "Ah, mystery solved!" },
            { 738209732, "That's not happening." },
            { 738209733, "The circle of bending light, the rushing sound!" },
            { 738209734, "That's what brought you here, yes?" },
            { 738209735, "You want to go back home, don't you?" },
            { 738209736, "I may be able to help you." },
            { 738209737, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209738, "I'll give you to the bottom of a drink." },
            { 738209739, "Nice. Looks like one of those medieval-themed bars." },
            { 738209752, "You new?" },
            { 738209753, "Tavernkeeper, your ale is the finest in all the land!" },
            { 738209754, "Those are some very strange clothes indeed, girl." },
            { 738209755, "Wait, isn't that..." },
            { 738209756, "A pint of your finest ale, my good sir." },
            { 738209757, "Oof, helluvah kick. You guys do not mess around." },
            { 738209758, "My father researched the phenomena known as the torana extensively." },
            { 738209759, "\"Torana\"?" },
            { 738209760, "The tunnel of light you traveled through." },
            { 738209761, "I believe his work holds the answers you need." },
            { 738209762, "In the Break, right?" },
            { 738209763, "It does not seem to have any effect on you." },
            { 738209764, "So they say." },
            { 738209765, "Many have tried to find what's outside the city, but..." },
            { 738209766, "They don't get far before..." },
            { 738209767, "Before what?" },
            { 738209768, "You are the only hope we have." },
            { 738209769, "You're special." },
            { 738209770, "Okay, you obviously don't know me." },
            { 738209771, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209772, "I want proof." },
            { 738209773, "And...thank you." },
            { 738209774, "I haven't said yes!" },
            { 738209781, "Do you believe her?" },
            { 738209782, "I suppose anything is possible." },
            { 738209783, "Some chance is better than no chance." },
            { 738209784, "I do not want to go back into that hellscape." },
            { 738209787, "Is this them? Your folks?" },
            { 738209788, "Yes. It was painted when we were at one of the Cognoscents' Guilds." },
            { 738209789, "Father was one of the Cognoscents of Junoon." },
            { 738209790, "He had the foresight to move his work to Praenost just before the Guild in Junoon fell to the Break." },
            { 738209791, "So your dad's notes are in Praenost?" },
            { 738209793, "But it wasn't long before he went back to finish his work." },
            { 738209794, "That was twenty years ago..." },
            { 738209795, "I never saw him again." },
            { 738209796, "And the Break eventually overtook everything outside the city..." },
            { 738209797, "Could you tell me about him?" },
            { 738209798, "He was a brilliant man, beloved by many." },
            { 738209799, "He was close to finding a way of slowing down the Break, maybe even reversing it." },
            { 738209800, "The people put their faith in him..." },
            { 738209801, "Believed that he would make the world how it used to be." },
            { 738209802, "I'm trying my hardest to continue his work, to keep hope alive." },
            { 738209807, "Here. These are his notes on the torana." },
            { 738209808, "Yeah. Yeah, this looks familiar." },
            { 738209809, "Quid pro quo. I get it." },
            { 738209810, "He kept his notes on the Break in red journals like this one." },
            { 738209811, "Okay, so I go and get the journals, bring them back, and then we're square?" },
            { 738209812, "That's the full extent of my savior-ing?" },
            { 738209813, "You wish me dead?" },
            { 738209814, "No, no! It's a phrase we have on Earth—forget it." },
            { 738209815, "I shall pretend those words were never uttered." },
            { 738209816, "Good. Okay, I'm in. Why not? It's not like I've got any better options." },
            { 738209817, "Oh, this is good news!" },
            { 738209818, "You are truly helping the people of Athia." },
            { 738209819, "Uh... Not why I'm doing it, but yeah, sure." },
            { 738209820, "If you're planning on heading into the Break, you'll need to get some rest." },
            { 738209821, "I'll go in the morning." },
            { 738209822, "You got anywhere I can crash?" },
            { 738209823, "\"Crash\"?" },
            { 738209824, "Crash. Uh, sleep." },
            { 738209825, "Oh, of course! Follow me." },
            { 738209833, "You can use this room whenever you like." },
            { 738209834, "And I'll prepare a change of clothes for you." },
            { 738209835, "Thanks. You're a lifesaver." },
            { 738209836, "What a fucking day. Still can't tell if any of this is real..." },
            { 738209837, "And yet it is. Now rest." },
            { 738209838, "Now you look like one of us!" },
            { 738209839, "But your shoes betray you." },
            { 738209840, "These have gotten me out of a lot of scrapes." },
            { 738209841, "Where I go, they go. The kicks stay." },
            { 738209842, "So it shall be. Here, you'll also need this." },
            { 738209843, "It's a map of Athia. It should aid you on your journey." },
            { 738209844, "Here—I've marked the Cognoscents' Guild." },
            { 738209845, "Perfect." },
            { 738209847, "Thank you again. Tanta's blessings." },
            { 738209848, "You too. Whatever that means." },
            { 738209849, "Maybe you should grab an apple?" },
            { 738209850, "An apple a day—" },
            { 738209851, "Will keep Frey's hunger at bay!" },
            { 738209852, "Such a poet." },
            { 738209853, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209854, "Dammit! I mean..." },
            { 738209855, "Well, that was a short trip." },
            { 738209856, "How the hell do you get out of this dump, anyway?" },
            { 738209857, "I know a way." },
            { 738209858, "You. You been following me, kid?" },
            { 738209859, "No. But I know how to help you." },
            { 738209860, "Really?" },
            { 738209861, "I know everything around here." },
            { 738209862, "Mm-hm? And what's that gonna cost me?" },
            { 738209863, "So you have been following me." },
            { 738209864, "You seem hungry." },
            { 738209865, "Don't you want to know my name?" },
            { 738209866, "Not really." },
            { 738209867, "It's Olevia. And you're Frey." },
            { 738209868, "Everyone's been talking about you." },
            { 738209869, "I guess I'm kinda famous around here." },
            { 738209870, "Does \"famous\" mean hunted by the guards?" },
            { 738209871, "I call it \"Finders Keepers.\"" },
            { 738209872, "Damn. Did you steal all this stuff?" },
            { 738209873, "Not all of it." },
            { 738209874, "You're growing on me, kid." },
            { 738209875, "Sometimes, people have no idea what they're throwing away." },
            { 738209876, "I often make new things out of the \"stuff.\"" },
            { 738209877, "Here! If you get hurt, this will help you heal." },
            { 738209878, "Alright! Nice. You'll have to give me the recipe." },
            { 738209879, "Of course. Let me teach you how." },
            { 738209880, "Try it!" },
            { 738209881, "People really do throw a lot of stuff away, huh?" },
            { 738209882, "Yes. A lot of useless rubbish." },
            { 738209883, "Hey, shorty. I got you something." },
            { 738209884, "That thing you said isn't worth crap?" },
            { 738209885, "No, not my cellphone—and thanks for not swiping that again." },
            { 738209886, "I don't steal from friends." },
            { 738209887, "Friends?" },
            { 738209888, "Cool." },
            { 738209889, "Well, as your friend, I got you this." },
            { 738209890, "Wow! What is that? Are you a Tanta?" },
            { 738209891, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738209892, "It's a penlight. And no, I am not a Tanta." },
            { 738209893, "What's the deal with those guys anyway?" },
            { 738209894, "They were the strongest and most powerful women in Athia." },
            { 738209895, "They all had gifts." },
            { 738209896, "And in the past, they used them to help protect the land." },
            { 738209897, "And one day, they will again." },
            { 738209898, "They'll come and save us." },
            { 738209899, "Uh...listen, kid." },
            { 738209900, "From personal experience, you've got to look out for yourself." },
            { 738209901, "People only really get \"saved\" in fairy tales." },
            { 738209902, "You're wrong. You'll see." },
            { 738209903, "Alright, well...I gotta split." },
            { 738209904, "Um, you said you knew the best way out of this place?" },
            { 738209905, "Well, if you climb over that wall there, that should help you get to where you want to be." },
            { 738209906, "Cool. Thanks." },
            { 738209907, "I'll, uh...see you when I see you." },
            { 738209908, "I'll keep the city safe while you're gone!" },
            { 738209909, "Sure. You do that." },
            { 738209914, "This time, let's try to steer clear of \"cute\" animals." },
            { 738209915, "Noted." },
            { 738209916, "And this time, let's try to be less petulant and annoying, alright?" },
            { 738209917, "I am hardly petulant and annoying." },
            { 738209918, "Agree to disagree." },
            { 738209919, "What the hell are these things?" },
            { 738209920, "Are they...people!?" },
            { 738209921, "I believe this is what happens when humans are affected by the Break." },
            { 738209922, "Then I can't kill them!" },
            { 738209923, "What choice do you have?" },
            { 738209924, "It's either them or you." },
            { 738209925, "So this is what Auden meant when she said people who come out here don't make it very far..." },
            { 738209926, "Explains why the people of Cipal prefer staying inside those walls of theirs." },
            { 738209927, "These...Breakzombies... They're everywhere." },
            { 738209928, "I'm sure they were nice people before, but come on!" },
            { 738209929, "Is that the Guild?" },
            { 738209930, "According to the map, it is, yes." },
            { 738209931, "Seems like the Athians are into tall buildings, huh?" },
            { 738209932, "It's said that the more towers a land has, the more prosperous it is." },
            { 738209933, "And the taller, the better." },
            { 738209934, "Guess that's one thing this place and home have in common." },
            { 738209935, "Although in this case, it might be more accurate to say \"the more prosperous it was\"..." },
            { 738209936, "Well, looks like this is the place." },
            { 738209937, "Seems like it's seen better days..." },
            { 738209938, "Well, you're not going to find what you're looking for out here." },
            { 738209939, "I know, I know." },
            { 738209940, "Great start." },
            { 738209941, "It's so dark in here." },
            { 738209944, "Damn, this place is full of books..." },
            { 738209945, "Great. Talk about a needle in a haystack!" },
            { 738209946, "How am I gonna find these damn journals?" },
            { 738209947, "He must have kept them somewhere safe. They contained his last great works, did they not?" },
            { 738209949, "Let's make our way upwards, shall we?" },
            { 738209950, "Whoa!" },
            { 738209951, "What the hell is that!?" },
            { 738209952, "It appears to be a person under that getup." },
            { 738209953, "No shit, Sherlock." },
            { 738209954, "You need to know who he is." },
            { 738209955, "Well, there's only one way to find out." },
            { 738209956, "Okay, Mister Axe Murderer, I'm gonna come towards you and take off your mask." },
            { 738209957, "You gonna be cool, or uncool?" },
            { 738209958, "RAAARGH!" },
            { 738209959, "Okay, it looks like we're going with uncool!" },
            { 738209960, "So...I'm gonna let you chill in my grass prison while I go and look for the journals." },
            { 738209961, "Auden did not say there were gonna be so many." },
            { 738209962, "Auden..." },
            { 738209963, "Auden?" },
            { 738209964, "My Auden?" },
            { 738209965, "Wait... Hold on..." },
            { 738209966, "Robian?" },
            { 738209967, "I am looking at a goddamn ghost." },
            { 738209968, "H-how are you alive? Everybody thinks you're dead." },
            { 738209969, "It's the hue of blue... And the bloomers too..." },
            { 738209970, "I don't understand. I thought you wrote about it in the red journals." },
            { 738209971, "They get inside, and..." },
            { 738209972, "Sometimes I can't...but I try...I have to." },
            { 738209973, "Looks like you're losing the battle with the Break, buddy." },
            { 738209974, "You look like you're winning. How?" },
            { 738209975, "I dunno." },
            { 738209976, "I am so far from home. I'm trying to get back..." },
            { 738209977, "I-I fell through a, um..." },
            { 738209978, "Voosh!" },
            { 738209979, "Yeah. Yeah, a...a voosh!" },
            { 738209980, "ハッ" },
            { 738209981, "Yeah, I gotta get back to where I gotta be through a...a voosh!" },
            { 738209982, "Voosh! Hah!" },
            { 738209983, "You will get back to where you need to be. Voosh." },
            { 738209984, "Yes! Voosh!" },
            { 738209985, "Voosh!" },
            { 738209986, "Show yourself, interloper!" },
            { 738209987, "Company..." },
            { 738209988, "Stay here." },
            { 738209989, "Wonder whose voice that was..." },
            { 738209990, "Whoever it was, we need to be careful." },
            { 738209991, "Can't believe Robian was alive this whole time..." },
            { 738209992, "The peasant girl is in for the shock of her life." },
            { 738209993, "We are the soldiers of the Tanta Sila. You are in our realm." },
            { 738209994, "You are to come with us." },
            { 738209995, "That's not a thing that's happening." },
            { 738209997, "What about the journals?" },
            { 738209998, "Didn't the peasant girl ask you to fetch them for her?" },
            { 738209999, "Are you sure you want to leave that old man alone in that place?" },
            { 738210000, "Okay, we gotta grab what we can." },
            { 738210001, "It's over, interloper." },
            { 738210002, "Whoa!" },
            { 738210003, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738210004, "Shit! The journals!" },
            { 738210038, "Shit. Is Cipal on fire?" },
            { 738210039, "It does appear to be smoldering somewhat." },
            { 738210040, "What happened here?" },
            { 738210041, "She walks among us! Tanta Sila!" },
            { 738210042, "She seeks the one called Frey!" },
            { 738210043, "Me?" },
            { 738210044, "Your arrival must have sent tremors across Athia." },
            { 738210045, "Your presence here has the Tanta frightened!" },
            { 738210046, "Frey! You're back!" },
            { 738210047, "I was wrong. She didn't come to rescue us." },
            { 738210048, "You did." },
            { 738210049, "I...I'm no hero." },
            { 738210050, "Tanta Sila has Auden!" },
            { 738210051, "Auden? My Auden?" },
            { 738210052, "Shit, wait—Bob! Breakbob!" },
            { 738210053, "Your concern for the madman is admirable, but first, we must stop Sila." },
            { 738210054, "It's okay. I'll try and fix this." },
            { 738210055, "No! Absolutely not. You're gonna stay here and find somewhere to hide." },
            { 738210059, "Don't you care about what's happening in the city?" },
            { 738210060, "They said Sila is looking for you." },
            { 738210061, "Aren't you worried about the peasant girl?" },
            { 738210062, "She is the one who freed the demon!" },
            { 738210063, "Please, Your Highness, your anger will not serve us now!" },
            { 738210064, "Tell Tanta Sila where she is, child!" },
            { 738210065, "Where is the interloper, child?" },
            { 738210066, "The one who dares trespass upon my realm!" },
            { 738210067, "Tanta Sila!" },
            { 738210068, "I am Robian Keen!" },
            { 738210069, "Father?" },
            { 738210070, "Auden!" },
            { 738210071, "I served faithfully under Tanta Cinta!" },
            { 738210072, "My wife, Calista, was a general in your army." },
            { 738210073, "You have to save the peasant girl." },
            { 738210074, "She would do the same for you." },
            { 738210075, "Ugh, fuck. I know." },
            { 738210076, "We have to do something." },
            { 738210077, "See if you can sneak up behind her..." },
            { 738210079, "Try to blend in with the crowd." },
            { 738210080, "I could blend in a whole lot better if you shut the fuck up!" },
            { 738210082, "Hang in there, Auden. I'm coming!" },
            { 738210083, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738210084, "Hey, c'mon!" },
            { 738210085, "I'll explain shit later." },
            { 738210086, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738210087, "Interloper!" },
            { 738210088, "Stop! You must stop. She can save us!" },
            { 738210089, "She can end your madness!" },
            { 738210090, "Move!" },
            { 738210091, "Father!" },
            { 738210092, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738210093, "What..." },
            { 738210094, "No..." },
            { 738210095, "Behold the countless fallen!" },
            { 738210096, "And all because of this demon!" },
            { 738210097, "You saw what she did. She will kill us all!" },
            { 738210098, "Surely, Councilwoman Bellette, surely you agree with me?" },
            { 738210099, "Yes. Seize her!" },
            { 738210100, "No, no, no, no, no! Th-this young woman is our protector!" },
            { 738210101, "She'll save us!" },
            { 738210102, "He is as corrupted as she is!" },
            { 738210103, "Seize them all before the darkness spreads!" },
            { 738210104, "We will do nothing of the kind!" },
            { 738210105, "Robian Keen is wise beyond measure, and has always been a man of his word." },
            { 738210106, "Had we known he was still alive, he would be sitting on the Council—not you." },
            { 738210107, "And this young woman has brought him back to us!" },
            { 738210108, "Welcome home, old friend." },
            { 738210109, "Tanta Sila's attack shows us one thing." },
            { 738210110, "The enemy of our enemy is our friend." },
            { 738210111, "And how many further agonies must we suffer?" },
            { 738210112, "Her presence has cost us too many lives!" },
            { 738210113, "Councilwoman Bellette is right." },
            { 738210114, "Tanta Sila will surely visit her wrath upon us once more." },
            { 738210115, "A clear majority!" },
            { 738210116, "The girl must be surrendered to Tanta Sila at once!" },
            { 738210117, "No need." },
            { 738210118, "I'll go to her myself." },
            { 738210119, "Start Challenge?" },
            { 738210120, "Yes" },
            { 738210121, "No" },
            { 738210122, "Phew..." },
            { 738210123, "Flagging already?" },
            { 738210124, "The first moments of any battle are crucial." },
            { 738210125, "And you're telling me that now?" },
            { 738210126, "Time is of the essence, Frey!" },
            { 738210127, "Is that supposed to be helpful?" },
            { 738210128, "This is getting old..." },
            { 738210129, "I was just starting to enjoy myself!" },
            { 738210130, "Time for a few words of wisdom from yours truly, perhaps?" },
            { 738210131, "Literally the last thing I need." },
            { 738210132, "Tired yet?" },
            { 738210133, "Only of talking to you!" },
            { 738210134, "Oh, man... Is this ever gonna end!?" },
            { 738210135, "Don't stop now!" },
            { 738210136, "You seem a little weary." },
            { 738210137, "Yeah, of you never shutting up!" },
            { 738210138, "You know, it's the effort that counts." },
            { 738210139, "Thanks. Do I get a gold star?" },
            { 738210146, "I think it's hungry." },
            { 738210147, "Well, you are rather offering yourself up on a plate." },
            { 738210148, "Are you fond of animals, Frey?" },
            { 738210149, "More than I am of humans." },
            { 738210150, "Aww. I love fluffballs." },
            { 738210151, "I suppose that's...a valid opinion." },
            { 738210152, "What do you think of this one?" },
            { 738210153, "Eh. Not my type." },
            { 738210154, "Wow. Next, please!" },
            { 738210155, "I'm sure it finds you equally appealing." },
            { 738210156, "I guess not all four-legged critters can be cute..." },
            { 738210157, "And why would you expect them to be?" },
            { 738210158, "Well? Finally starting to see this one's adorable side?" },
            { 738210159, "Not happening. Ever." },
            { 738210160, "Ahhh, life takes so many wondrous forms..." },
            { 738210161, "And the Break fucks them up beyond belief." },
            { 738210162, "This thing repulses me on every level." },
            { 738210163, "Surely not?" },
            { 738210164, "Slow the fuck down!" },
            { 738210165, "You really are a poet..." },
            { 738210166, "You might want to pick up the pace." },
            { 738210167, "Uh, you do realize I'm about as fast as my species gets?" },
            { 738210168, "Watch its movements carefully." },
            { 738210169, "You kidding? I'm getting dizzy just trying to keep up!" },
            { 738210170, "How did you get to be so big, fella?" },
            { 738210171, "A sudden growth spurt, perhaps?" },
            { 738210172, "Don't just run in swinging—that thing's enormous." },
            { 738210173, "Fine. What do you suggest?" },
            { 738210174, "Ooh. Big fellow." },
            { 738210175, "It's not so big we can't beat its ass." },
            { 738210176, "Ugh. I can barely stand to look at it." },
            { 738210177, "Let me smack it outta the sky for ya." },
            { 738210178, "More of our flying friends." },
            { 738210179, "Such is the price of popularity." },
            { 738210180, "Why can't you fly?" },
            { 738210181, "I don't know if you've noticed, but not a lot of humans can." },
            { 738210233, "How are you holding up?" },
            { 738210234, "I've got some juice left." },
            { 738210236, "Don't worry, I'm still good to go." },
            { 738210237, "Wonderful. Then let's get moving, shall we?" },
            { 738210239, "Tired?" },
            { 738210240, "Yeah. Must be all the dead weight I'm being forced to carry." },
            { 738210241, "Hmph. You're fine, clearly." },
            { 738210242, "Getting a little tired?" },
            { 738210243, "Oh, you have no idea. It's hard being me." },
            { 738210244, "I meant... Never mind." },
            { 738210245, "I swear I'm way fitter than I was back in New York." },
            { 738210246, "That'll be the magic at work." },
            { 738210247, "And not all the nonstop shit we've been doing? Way to piss on my gains." },
            { 738210248, "'Kay, maybe I am starting to get tired..." },
            { 738210249, "Oh yes? Anything troubling you in particular?" },
            { 738210250, "Yeah. My right wrist." },
            { 738210251, "I'm so tired. Say something to wake me up, will you?" },
            { 738210252, "Wake up, wake up, WAKE UP!" },
            { 738210253, "Nope, no good. I'm about to pass out." },
            { 738210254, "Man, I am sleepy as hell." },
            { 738210255, "Fatigue setting in? Not surprising, really." },
            { 738210256, "Better find someplace to rest." },
            { 738210257, "You're falling asleep." },
            { 738210258, "Wanna sing me a lullaby?" },
            { 738210259, "Not entirely sure this is the best place to bed down..." },
            { 738210260, "Sleeping while walking is not advisable." },
            { 738210261, "But strangely appealing right now..." },
            { 738210263, "Open your eyes!" },
            { 738210264, "Believe me, I would if I could." },
            { 738210265, "I think it's time you got some rest, don't you?" },
            { 738210266, "You look like you're about to keel over." },
            { 738210267, "Mm-hm..." },
            { 738210268, "Hm. Not good..." },
            { 738210278, "Y'know, I like this cloak. Kind of an interdimensional wanderer vibe, no?" },
            { 738210279, "A what? It isn't...entirely unflattering, I suppose." },
            { 738210280, "Yeah, look, if you're gonna be half-ass on your compliments, you can keep 'em." },
            { 738210281, "Yeah... Lightweight, easy to move in... I like this cloak." },
            { 738210282, "It's got quite a nice design. Suits you." },
            { 738210283, "Why don't I trust you when you're being nice...?" },
            { 738210284, "Frey—you're fraying!" },
            { 738210285, "Huh? Oh, my cloak. No biggie." },
            { 738210286, "Say that when you're tripping over the tatters." },
            { 738210287, "How come I feel stronger when I'm wearing this cloak?" },
            { 738210288, "Never underestimate the power of the mind, Frey." },
            { 738210289, "Huh. I wonder if I can force myself to like you..." },
            { 738210290, "You think Sila liked her cloaks this comfy? Can't really see it, myself." },
            { 738210291, "Well, she was a Tanta. Nice clothes rather come with the territory." },
            { 738210292, "So she had no choice, huh? Well, I can think of worse problems to have..." },
            { 738210293, "Oof. This is one heavy cloak." },
            { 738210294, "Which is what makes it so good at repelling blows." },
            { 738210295, "Huh. Wonder if Sila's whole army wore stuff like this." },
            { 738210296, "Certainly has a distinct...Pravishness about it, doesn't it?" },
            { 738210297, "The cloak? Yeah. Real, uh...establishment vibes." },
            { 738210298, "I'll say—even you look respectable in it." },
            { 738210299, "Ah, I love this cloak. Not too warm, not too cold." },
            { 738210300, "Well, Prav was charged with maintaining balance in all things." },
            { 738210301, "Perhaps that's the idea with this little number." },
            { 738210302, "A rather dignified cloak, that one." },
            { 738210303, "I dunno. You don't think it's a little...over-formal?" },
            { 738210304, "Uh, not if you're wearing it, no." },
            { 738210305, "You seem...wiser, all of a sudden." },
            { 738210306, "Hah. Must be the cloak, 'cause it's definitely not me." },
            { 738210308, "Hmm. Looks like it's made of pretty sturdy stuff." },
            { 738210309, "My cloak? Yeah, it is." },
            { 738210310, "This place is rather windy, I suppose. We don't want it flapping about everywhere." },
            { 738210311, "The Tantas gave their cloaks pretty unique looks, huh?" },
            { 738210312, "Perhaps it's to do with the pigments that each realm is able to produce." },
            { 738210313, "Or maybe they just had favorite colors like everybody else." },
            { 738210314, "This cloak is from Junoon, huh?" },
            { 738210315, "It's kinda...comforting. Feels nice..." },
            { 738210316, "Don't let's get too warm and fuzzy now." },
            { 738210317, "They like their cloaks pretty showy in Junoon, huh?" },
            { 738210318, "Well, they were always quite a theatrical people." },
            { 738210319, "Hm. Guess that explains it." },
            { 738210320, "How does that one feel to wear?" },
            { 738210321, "It's...soft. And it smells nice. Like herbs or something." },
            { 738210322, "Ah yes. They were famous for their herbs over in Junoon. Must have scented it with some." },
            { 738210323, "What the devil do you look like?" },
            { 738210324, "Designed this cloak myself. Sick, right?" },
            { 738210325, "What is it you say again...? Agree to disagree?" },
            { 738210326, "Man, still can't believe I'm designing my own outfits now." },
            { 738210327, "Well, it's certainly...unbelievable in one respect." },
            { 738210328, "Did I ask for your opinion?" },
            { 738210329, "Do you think that cloak might be a little too...you? You'll stick out like a sore thumb." },
            { 738210330, "You know I don't give a shit what people think, right?" },
            { 738210331, "Oh, believe me—I know." },
            { 738210332, "The Break's really spreading." },
            { 738210333, "Only a matter of time before it swallows Cipal..." },
            { 738210334, "Indeed." },
            { 738210335, "This used to be the bustling heart of Athia, you know." },
            { 738210336, "How come they built Cipal in the first place?" },
            { 738210337, "It was originally intended as a meeting place for the Tantas, I believe." },
            { 738210338, "Cipal's kind of like an island, huh?" },
            { 738210339, "If one imagines the Break as a sea, yes." },
            { 738210340, "Yeah. A sea filled with man-eating crazyfish." },
            { 738210341, "People were flocking to Cipal from all over Athia long before the Break appeared." },
            { 738210342, "So it's been super important to them since way back?" },
            { 738210343, "Yes. And now it is where they will make their final stand..." },
            { 738210344, "Kinda drab around here, don'tcha think?" },
            { 738210345, "That's by design, I would imagine. This used to be a sort of political neutral zone." },
            { 738210346, "Catering to all tastes inevitably makes things a little bland." },
            { 738210347, "Not exactly hospitable around these parts." },
            { 738210348, "That's what makes the inhabitants so formidable." },
            { 738210349, "Survival of the fittest, huh? Brutal." },
            { 738210350, "Well, this place is fun. There's nothing here but rocks. Look at that rock!" },
            { 738210351, "Its Tanta intended her realm to be unforgiving in every respect." },
            { 738210352, "Sounds about right. Man, I would so not have been Team Sila." },
            { 738210353, "You could break an ankle running on this stuff." },
            { 738210354, "That's what made it so perfect for toughening up soldiers." },
            { 738210355, "Yeah. And so not perfect for a relaxing getaway." },
            { 738210356, "Ugh, the air's so dry..." },
            { 738210357, "Dear old Sila. She really didn't want anyone having any fun." },
            { 738210358, "Laugh it up. You don't have to breathe this stuff." },
            { 738210359, "The locals used to do a roaring trade in military hardware." },
            { 738210360, "Oh yeah. Johedy made weapons here, right?" },
            { 738210361, "Yes. Not a skill she's had much use for since relocating to Cipal..." },
            { 738210362, "Ahhh. This place is nuts, but I'm getting to like the whole fresh air thing." },
            { 738210363, "I should hope so, too. You're very lucky to be breathing it." },
            { 738210364, "Wow. Bitter much?" },
            { 738210365, "Kinda...coldly warm here..." },
            { 738210366, "Meaning...what, exactly?" },
            { 738210367, "Uh... Forget it." },
            { 738210368, "Sure are a lot of plants around here." },
            { 738210369, "Herbal medicines were Junoon's stock-in-trade." },
            { 738210370, "Well, that oughta come in handy." },
            { 738210371, "The people of Junoon have always been keen artists." },
            { 738210372, "Nice. I'll keep an eye out for stuff I can sell." },
            { 738210373, "I think the bottom might have dropped out of the market somewhat..." },
            { 738210374, "Individual expression was valued above all else here." },
            { 738210375, "Which made it very difficult for people to ever agree on anything." },
            { 738210376, "Why is there always a downside with you?" },
            { 738210377, "Ugh, just being in this place makes me miserable." },
            { 738210378, "It's definitely not the most welcoming of realms." },
            { 738210380, "I believe the prison where they kept the worst of Athia's wrongdoers was somewhere in this realm." },
            { 738210381, "Great. Now I like it even less." },
            { 738210382, "Something to do with the...rap sheet you mentioned?" },
            { 738210383, "Ugh, it's so damp here." },
            { 738210384, "The watery bounties of this fair realm know no limits, milady." },
            { 738210385, "Yeah? Well, I fucking hate it." },
            { 738210386, "Air here's kinda cold..." },
            { 738210387, "What did you expect? This is the home of the charming Tanta Prav, after all." },
            { 738210389, "The prison here was said to be impossible to escape." },
            { 738210390, "Oh yeah? Well, whoever started that rumor never met me." },
            { 738210391, "Convinced you'd have ended up there, eh?" },
            { 738210407, "Gotta love being out in the open like this." },
            { 738210408, "Yes, until you're spotted by an enemy from miles away." },
            { 738210409, "Thanks, Professor Mood-Killer." },
            { 738210410, "You know what? We should have a picnic. And I say that as someone who has never had a picnic in their life." },
            { 738210411, "Of course, just pop yourself down. I'm sure you'll have a few peaceful moments before you're set upon." },
            { 738210412, "Oh, lighten up, already!" },
            { 738210413, "It's rather picturesque here, no?" },
            { 738210414, "I guess. Not sure I'm in the mood to enjoy it..." },
            { 738210415, "No bad thing, I'd say. It's always best to stay alert." },
            { 738210416, "Look at all these trees." },
            { 738210417, "It's a forest, Frey. They do tend toward the heavily wooded." },
            { 738210418, "Yes, I know, Cuff. I'm just thinking I need to be careful where I put my feet, is all." },
            { 738210419, "The depths of the forest hide its greatest dangers." },
            { 738210420, "Just like in the fairy tales, huh?" },
            { 738210421, "All stories contain a kernel of truth..." },
            { 738210422, "The trees almost seem like they're alive." },
            { 738210423, "Do they? They look like they're just standing there to me." },
            { 738210424, "Standing there growing in any which way they please. I'm kinda jealous..." },
            { 738210425, "How the hell am I supposed to keep my kicks clean in this shit?" },
            { 738210426, "Well, if you will insist on such inappropriate footwear." },
            { 738210427, "You know how hard these were to get my hands on!? Ugh!" },
            { 738210428, "Kinda squishy around here." },
            { 738210429, "Squishiness. The most harrowing of nature's torments." },
            { 738210430, "How about I squish you right into the mud?" },
            { 738210431, "Do you mind hurrying up? I can almost feel myself rusting." },
            { 738210432, "Can you rust?" },
            { 738210433, "I'm not 100% certain. But better safe than sorry." },
            { 738210434, "I can literally feel the moisture being sucked out of my skin." },
            { 738210435, "Really? I have no complaints." },
            { 738210436, "Want me to give you something to complain about?" },
            { 738210437, "Whoa! Nearly slipped there!" },
            { 738210438, "A hazard of the terrain, unfortunately." },
            { 738210440, "Wouldn't want to trip here..." },
            { 738210441, "Well, now that you've tempted fate, we can almost guarantee that you will." },
            { 738210442, "Great. I'll be sure to fall right on my vambrace." },
            { 738210443, "Cuff, you're freezing my freaking arm off here!" },
            { 738210444, "Well, forgive me for existing. You have noticed the weather?" },
            { 738210445, "Can't you—I dunno—change what you're made of or something?" },
            { 738210446, "I'm fucking freezing! YOU'RE fucking freezing!" },
            { 738210447, "Yes. Not exactly my fault, you know." },
            { 738210448, "It will be if I die of cold!" },
            { 738210449, "C-c-can't feel my hands... How am I supposed to fight?" },
            { 738210450, "You'll soon warm up once you get moving." },
            { 738210451, "Thanks for the pep talk, Coach." },
            { 738210452, "Okay, we are not staying here one second longer than we have to." },
            { 738210453, "Then try not to slip and break your neck." },
            { 738210454, "Inspirational as ever, Cuff." },
            { 738210455, "Just one foot out of place and we're dead..." },
            { 738210456, "I'd quite like to stay alive if it's all the same to you." },
            { 738210457, "For once, we can agree on something." },
            { 738210458, "Going's a little dicey around here." },
            { 738210459, "Indeed. You might want to pick your battles if you can." },
            { 738210460, "Yeah, I tend not to get too much choice on that front." },
            { 738210461, "I never imagined myself climbing mountains." },
            { 738210462, "Acquiring a taste for alpine pursuits, are we?" },
            { 738210463, "More...learning to appreciate flat, safe ground." },
            { 738210464, "It is not safe up here." },
            { 738210465, "Yes. One slip-up and you'll be a sudden and very unwilling valley-dweller." },
            { 738210466, "Exactly what I'm trying to avoid, thanks." },
            { 738210467, "You might be able to make it all the way up in one go, you know." },
            { 738210468, "Are we looking at the same mountain?" },
            { 738210469, "Where there's a will, there's a way, Frey." },
            { 738210470, "It wouldn't hurt to polish me once in a while, you know." },
            { 738210471, "What do you think you are, designer jewelry?" },
            { 738210472, "No. I'm simply suggesting that you might take better care of your most vital lifeline and companion." },
            { 738210473, "There must be a way I can use my \"New York street smarts\" to make a quick buck around here..." },
            { 738210474, "And where would you fritter away your ill-gotten gains?" },
            { 738210475, "Who says \"fritter\"? And good question." },
            { 738210476, "Ugh... I just wanna sit down..." },
            { 738210477, "Are you ever not tired?" },
            { 738210478, "Come to think of it, no. It's a...young person thing. Maybe." },
            { 738210479, "So you really don't remember anything about being in New York?" },
            { 738210480, "Not a sausage, I'm afraid. It's all just a...haze." },
            { 738210481, "Well gee, Sleeping Beauty. Guess we'll never know what adventures you had in that junk shop." },
            { 738210482, "Damn, I'm hyper-fucking-sonic! Like, pro level, right?" },
            { 738210483, "Oh, definitely. Very, very...pro." },
            { 738210484, "...You know what? I'll take it." },
            { 738210485, "It's nice and quiet." },
            { 738210486, "Quiet, yeah. Nice...the jury's out." },
            { 738210487, "Suit yourself." },
            { 738210488, "Man, I could murder a knish." },
            { 738210489, "Is that all you can talk about?" },
            { 738210490, "Believe me, if you know, you know." },
            { 738210491, "Athia has so much to offer the dedicated explorer, don't you think?" },
            { 738210492, "Sure, if you don't mind almost dying every place you go." },
            { 738210493, "Well, what is life, if not a series of brushes with death, hm?" },
            { 738210494, "You ever feel like just breaking into a run for the hell of it?" },
            { 738210495, "No." },
            { 738210496, "You literally have no soul." },
            { 738210497, "There's nothing here. Shall we turn around and head back?" },
            { 738210498, "I dunno. It feels like a waste of time if we don't find...something, you know?" },
            { 738210499, "What an oddly mercenary way of thinking." },
            { 738210500, "There's gotta be somebody out here, no?" },
            { 738210501, "I doubt it. Certainly not anyone alive." },
            { 738210502, "Guess this wasn't a popular area code even before shit went down..." },
            { 738210503, "Isn't it about time you took a rest?" },
            { 738210504, "All good here. Why, you worried about me?" },
            { 738210505, "...Just checking." },
            { 738210506, "Ugh, I am so bored of having only you to talk to." },
            { 738210507, "I'm sure some of our Break-addled friends would love a chat." },
            { 738210508, "Yeah...they just don't seem to get me, you know?" },
            { 738210509, "Just listen to that wind..." },
            { 738210510, "What wind?" },
            { 738210511, "Tsk. If only you had ears to listen..." },
            { 738210512, "Kind of a dry heat around here." },
            { 738210513, "Give me dry over humid every time." },
            { 738210514, "Gotta keep the rust at bay, huh?" },
            { 738210515, "I'm getting sleepy here..." },
            { 738210516, "Shall I keep you awake with a hilarious anecdote?" },
            { 738210517, "Hell no. I'll be out in seconds." },
            { 738210518, "Guess you've never had a cup of coffee?" },
            { 738210519, "I'm afraid not. Tasty?" },
            { 738210520, "Nah, it's fucking gross. You'd probably love it." },
            { 738210521, "You wouldn't mind giving me a quick dust down, would you?" },
            { 738210522, "Ah, do it yourself." },
            { 738210523, "You know very well that I can't." },
            { 738210524, "うわっ！" },
            { 738210525, "What is it?" },
            { 738210526, "Bug got in my mouth. Gross." },
            { 738210527, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738210528, "What's gotten into you?" },
            { 738210529, "Oh, nothing. Just humming a happy tune." },
            { 738210530, "Ahh, just taste that air!" },
            { 738210531, "What does it taste of?" },
            { 738210532, "Uhh... Strawberries." },
            { 738210533, "Do I always have to be the one to start the conversation?" },
            { 738210534, "Not at all. Feel free to shut the fuck up. Forever." },
            { 738210535, "...I'm speechless." },
            { 738210536, "My skin is so dry..." },
            { 738210537, "Mine too." },
            { 738210538, "And here I thought you had the perfect complexion." },
            { 738210539, "Ooh, my back is killing me." },
            { 738210540, "The back you don't have?" },
            { 738210541, "Just...trying it on for size." },
            { 738210542, "Man, if only I could use my phone." },
            { 738210543, "What would you do with it?" },
            { 738210544, "Uh...kill some time, I guess?" },
            { 738210545, "Must you insist on wearing the same old cloak day in, day out?" },
            { 738210546, "And what exactly would you prefer me to wear, O Master of Style?" },
            { 738210547, "Oh, I don't know. Just something...different, you know?" },
            { 738210548, "Ugh, why do they have to look so gross?" },
            { 738210549, "I seem to remember you being equally unimpressed with a monster that tried to take a more adorable approach." },
            { 738210550, "Thanks for going there. Still trying to forget that one." },
            { 738210551, "It does get a little dull being stuck to your wrist all day..." },
            { 738210552, "Hey, look, I'm happy to swap. You can do the walking for once." },
            { 738210553, "If you're ever irreversibly incapacitated, I might consider it." },
            { 738210554, "Imagine if I coulda used magic back in New York..." },
            { 738210555, "And what would you have used it for, exactly?" },
            { 738210556, "Uh...playing with Homer?" },
            { 738210557, "Gosh, that was a close one!" },
            { 738210558, "What? What is it?" },
            { 738210559, "Oh, an insect nearly landed on me, but you moved at just the right moment. Thanks." },
            { 738210560, "The buildings here are something else." },
            { 738210561, "Yes. I believe it's where the great and the good of Cipalian society live." },
            { 738210563, "It's certainly very different from the lower city up here." },
            { 738210564, "Why, though? What's so special about this part of town?" },
            { 738210565, "These days, that it offers just that little extra distance from the Break." },
            { 738210566, "No one's doing very much, are they? Suppose there's not a lot to do..." },
            { 738210567, "Yeah, even in the lower city only a few of the people seemed actually busy." },
            { 738210568, "I suppose there's only so much work to go around." },
            { 738210569, "It's like somebody made an entire city out of back alleys." },
            { 738210570, "Which makes them...front alleys now, I suppose." },
            { 738210572, "I doubt there are many places for criminals to hide in a town this small." },
            { 738210573, "Yeah. Not much in the way of crowds to slip into, either." },
            { 738210574, "All in all, not the best place to exercise one's villainous urges." },
            { 738210575, "Feels a little more—I dunno, cheerful—in the lower city." },
            { 738210576, "When food is short and one's days are numbered, every moment is a gift, I suppose." },
            { 738210577, "So they're happy because they can't afford to be sad? That's fucking depressing." },
            { 738210578, "I'd imagine the town relies on the produce grown here." },
            { 738210579, "Yeah. And it wouldn't take much to put the place out of commission..." },
            { 738210580, "They've done well to survive as long as they have." },
            { 738210581, "What are they growing?" },
            { 738210582, "Some sort of grain, I'd imagine. Relatively easy to cultivate, and highly versatile." },
            { 738210583, "Hey! We could make a knish, maybe! Hmm..." },
            { 738210584, "The workers all appear to be from the lower city, while the bosses are up-towners." },
            { 738210585, "Must be hard, sweating to grow stuff and not getting to keep it for yourself." },
            { 738210586, "If the land and its produce are considered to be municipal property, it seems entirely reasonable." },
            { 738210587, "They keep sheep in the cemetery?" },
            { 738210588, "I imagine they don't have much choice." },
            { 738210590, "Looks like some sort of murderous demon." },
            { 738210591, "Nope. Just a sheep." },
            { 738210592, "You keep telling yourself that." },
            { 738210593, "You know what I like about animals? They just can't be evil." },
            { 738210594, "They can't be good, either. They just...exist." },
            { 738210595, "Well, they're still more likable than you." },
            { 738210596, "How come they don't have more...fun stuff here?" },
            { 738210597, "In case you haven't noticed, they're somewhat busy with other things." },
            { 738210598, "Yeah, but a few more bars at least couldn't hurt." },
            { 738210599, "Okay, can you try to keep the chat to a minimum while we're in Cipal?" },
            { 738210600, "It's a little late to start worrying about people finding you strange, you know." },
            { 738210601, "Guess I better figure out how to force you to shut up..." },
            { 738210602, "I am really missing my cat right now..." },
            { 738210603, "When you have a delightful companion right here on your wrist?" },
            { 738210604, "Because of the \"delightful companion.\"" },
            { 738210605, "Heeere, kitty, kitty! Come to mama!" },
            { 738210606, "What is it about them that addles your brain so thoroughly?" },
            { 738210607, "Are you kidding? Kitty power, that's what." },
            { 738210608, "Kinda busy around here." },
            { 738210609, "The trick is to look through the people, not at them." },
            { 738210610, "Uh, yeah, I've got some previous experience with crowded streets, thanks." },
            { 738210611, "Not exactly peaceful here, is it?" },
            { 738210612, "I'm used to it." },
            { 738210613, "Ahhh, yes. You're from a filthy, noisy, awful place too." },
            { 738210614, "Do they sell Cipal souvenirs somewhere?" },
            { 738210615, "And who, pray tell, would buy them if they did?" },
            { 738210616, "Hm, guess you're right. Not exactly a tourist hot spot..." },
            { 738210617, "The people here aren't very adventurous when it comes to clothes, are they?" },
            { 738210618, "Guess there isn't a whole lot of choice." },
            { 738210619, "Unless you're a member of the Council, it seems. Talk about rubbing it in..." },
            { 738210620, "Not a whole lot of people my age in Cipal, huh?" },
            { 738210621, "Well, it was almost exactly 21 years ago that the Break first appeared..." },
            { 738210622, "Wait. So they all...? Shit." },
            { 738210623, "I wonder what you'd be like if you'd grown up here..." },
            { 738210624, "My guess is \"even more fucking miserable than I am already.\"" },
            { 738210625, "How delightfully upbeat of you." },
            { 738210626, "They really took the whole medieval thing and ran with it here, huh?" },
            { 738210627, "...If you say so." },
            { 738210628, "Yeah, except when it came to you. I mean, c'mon, can you \"thee\" and \"thou\" it up a little bit?" },
            { 738210629, "No offense, but it would be nice to be able to talk with someone other than you from time to time." },
            { 738210630, "Knock yourself out. Just don't come to me looking for tips on how to be effortlessly charming." },
            { 738210631, "Now those I would love to hear..." },
            { 738210632, "Tell me a story, Cuff. Something funny." },
            { 738210633, "Oh well, that hardly narrows it down. I am literally a living encyclopedia of side-splitting yarns." },
            { 738210634, "You know what? Mm. Changed my mind." },
            { 738210635, "I think it's probably bedtime, don't you?" },
            { 738210636, "You really think you can just sit there on my wrist just telling me what to do?" },
            { 738210637, "I can't very well sit anywhere else, I'm afraid." },
            { 738210638, "Okay, I need to eat. Like, now." },
            { 738210639, "Good luck finding a square meal in this town." },
            { 738210640, "Yeah. Slim pickings..." },
            { 738210641, "Look out!" },
            { 738210642, "Okay, sometimes I don't completely hate you." },
            { 738210643, "Incoming!" },
            { 738210644, "Get out of the way!" },
            { 738210645, "Well? Do something!" },
            { 738210646, "Alright! How about this?" },
            { 738210647, "This looks like a big one!" },
            { 738210648, "Shit." },
            { 738210649, "I don't like the look of this!" },
            { 738210650, "What's the matter? Afraid it's gonna hurt?" },
            { 738210651, "Uh-oh!" },
            { 738210652, "Look out!" },
            { 738210665, "Perhaps avoiding attacks would be better than using me to fend them off?" },
            { 738210666, "Aww. Worried you might get a little scratch?" },
            { 738210667, "I sometimes wonder what you think I'm here for, you know." },
            { 738210668, "I sometimes wonder how come a little guy like you makes such a good shield." },
            { 738210669, "Do you think you might consider getting hit a little less?" },
            { 738210670, "What do you think I am? Superhuman?" },
            { 738210671, "This one's something of a handful." },
            { 738210672, "I don't mind. Keeps me on my toes." },
            { 738210673, "I do feel pain, you know." },
            { 738210674, "Lemme guess—\"Mentally, at least.\"" },
            { 738210675, "You're good, right?" },
            { 738210676, "I wouldn't say \"good,\" exactly..." },
            { 738210677, "Ow! Can you block a little better?" },
            { 738210678, "Ha! Can you rely on me a little less?" },
            { 738210679, "I can't keep you safe from harm forever, you know." },
