            { 738210798, "Who exactly are you trying to impress?" },
            { 738210799, "This could totally become a thing." },
            { 738210800, "Among the countless magic users out there, you mean?" },
            { 738210801, "You could have managed a little more than that, no?" },
            { 738210802, "You bet your ass I could!" },
            { 738210803, "Fuck yeah!" },
            { 738210804, "How very nimble of you." },
            { 738210805, "That was really quite spectacular." },
            { 738210806, "Guess it was, huh?" },
            { 738210807, "That does look rather exhilarating." },
            { 738210808, "Oh ho ho, it is!" },
            { 738210809, "Alriiight!" },
            { 738210810, "Let's not get too full of ourselves." },
            { 738210811, "You look like you're having fun." },
            { 738210812, "That is because I fucking am! Woo!" },
            { 738210813, "Hup!" },
            { 738210814, "Not bad." },
            { 738210815, "Don't make yourself dizzy, will you?" },
            { 738210816, "Ha! Not gonna happen!" },
            { 738210817, "...Yes. Top marks. Lovely spin, that." },
            { 738210818, "Easy peasy!" },
            { 738210819, "I'm the gymnastic fantastic! Heh heh... Yeah, that sounded better in my head." },
            { 738210820, "Some sort of Earth...celebration?" },
            { 738210821, "Woo! Perfect ten!" },
            { 738210822, "Well, that rather depends on what we're judging you on..." },
            { 738210823, "Get over here, damn you!" },
            { 738210824, "Ah, yes. That'll entice them to come closer." },
            { 738210825, "You need to close the distance!" },
            { 738210826, "Easier said than done..." },
            { 738210827, "That won't work from this far away!" },
            { 738210828, "You don't have to rub it in!" },
            { 738210829, "Worth altering your approach, perhaps?" },
            { 738210830, "Gimme a second to think, will ya?" },
