            { 738210912, "Thanks. ...Wait, what?" },
            { 738210913, "Hmm... Not bad." },
            { 738210914, "It's kinda heavy, but... Yeah, feels good." },
            { 738210915, "Well, you could do worse." },
            { 738210916, "This one's nice and easy to move in." },
            { 738210917, "It's designed to be worn in battle, I believe." },
            { 738210918, "Praenost was all about the warrior shit, huh?" },
            { 738210919, "Mmm. Very warlike." },
            { 738210920, "Would be pretty sweet if this made me as strong as Sila." },
