            { 738210936, "Yeah. Better hope we're not dealing with the emperor's new clothes." },
            { 738210937, "Well? Feeling clear-headed and razor-focused?" },
            { 738210938, "Yeah, give or take the occasional interruption from a shit-talking bracelet." },
            { 738210940, "It's weird. Everything gets quiet when I put this one on." },
