            { 738210946, "Wow. Love the feel of this one!" },
            { 738210947, "I really don't see how a texture can be quite so exciting." },
            { 738210948, "It's not just that, it's... I felt different as soon as I put it on." },
            { 738210949, "And? How is Junoon's very own signature cloak?" },
            { 738210950, "I dunno. I feel kinda...at home in it, weirdly enough." },
            { 738210952, "What's that one made of? I'm not familiar with the materials." },
