            { 738210964, "Whoa, my arms! I feel jacked!" },
            { 738210965, "Not an unexpected effect when taking on Sila's powers, I suppose." },
            { 738210966, "Hey, does that mean I'll be an axe-swinging badass, too?" },
            { 738210967, "You're going with that one, are you?" },
            { 738210968, "Yeah. Feel like ripping off some heads and spitting down some necks!" },
            { 738210969, "Hmhm. Easy, now." },
            { 738210970, "Feel like I can concentrate better with this one on." },
            { 738210971, "You make it sound like you spend most of the time hopelessly distracted." },
            { 738210972, "Thanks to you, I do." },
            { 738210973, "That's a lot of power to be concentrated in one object." },
            { 738210974, "You think it's dangerous?" },
            { 738210975, "I'm not sure. Regardless, it should prove useful." },
            { 738210976, "Why does this thing feel so...heavy?" },
            { 738210977, "It's probably just your imagination." },
            { 738210979, "I can feel the power coming off that thing from here." },
            { 738210980, "I only hope you can put it to good use." },
