            { 738210982, "My head feels weirdly...clear all of a sudden." },
            { 738210983, "If that's the case, I'd recommend never taking that thing off again." },
            { 738210984, "Aaand the effect is ruined. Thanks, asshole." },
            { 738210985, "You feel that? My magic just got a serious boost." },
            { 738210986, "Glad to hear it. Shall we find a victim to try it out on?" },
            { 738210988, "Mm... Feel super calm with this one on..." },
            { 738210991, "Why do I feel...cozy just putting this thing on?" },
            { 738210992, "It certainly doesn't look particularly warming." },
