            { 738210994, "This thing is beautiful. Can't fault these Junoon guys on their craftsmanship." },
            { 738210995, "It was the realm of artistry, after all." },
            { 738210996, "Could get some serious cash for a piece like this back in New York..." },
            { 738210997, "You're really going to use...that?" },
            { 738210998, "What? I sweated blood over this thing!" },
            { 738210999, "Oh, I'm sure it works just fine, it's just...why call it that?" },
            { 738211000, "What do you think of my masterpiece?" },
            { 738211001, "Umm..." },
            { 738211002, "Forget it. You've said enough." },
            { 738211003, "That is one formidable artifact." },
            { 738211004, "It better be. Wasn't easy putting this thing together." },
