            { 738211050, "You really are quite something!" },
            { 738211051, "You bet I am! Ha!" },
            { 738211052, "You think I'm done? I'm not even close!" },
            { 738211053, "I could get used to this..." },
            { 738211054, "Are you ever going to stop?" },
