            { 738211311, "Oh, let's just say I'm...pleasantly surprised." },
            { 738211312, "Not fucking bad." },
            { 738211313, "If only you were always such a success..." },
            { 738211314, "Can't bring me down, Cuff." },
            { 738211315, "How do you feel?" },
            { 738211316, "Like maybe I'm a genius?" },
            { 738211317, "Let's not get carried away..." },
            { 738211318, "Pretty decent." },
            { 738211319, "It is what it is." },
            { 738211320, "What's that supposed to mean?" },
            { 738211321, "About as good as could be expected..." },
            { 738211322, "Are you trying to piss me off?" },
            { 738211323, "Trying is what I'd recommend you start doing." },
            { 738211324, "Meh. Not the worst..." },
            { 738211325, "You almost seemed to be settling into a rhythm there." },
            { 738211326, "Yeah, yeah. I'll do better next time." },
            { 738211327, "What was that mess?" },
            { 738211328, "Don't even, Cuff." },
            { 738211329, "Well, do better next time!" },
            { 738211330, "Ugh! I am not on form today." },
            { 738211331, "Are you ever?" },
            { 738211332, "Oh, fuck off." },
            { 738211333, "I really hope you can do better than that." },
            { 738211334, "Hah! Well, this is me. Get used to it." },
            { 738211335, "It isn't and I shan't." },
            { 738211336, "That's a new record." },
            { 738211337, "Nice." },
            { 738211338, "Don't go resting on your laurels, though. Keep at it." },
            { 738211339, "That was my best yet, right?" },
            { 738211340, "I'm happy to say that it was. Well done." },
            { 738211341, "Was that...honest praise? Ugh, weird." },
            { 738211342, "That was very good." },
            { 738211343, "Eh. Thanks, I guess." },
            { 738211344, "A pleasure. ...I think?" },
            { 738211345, "I'm on fire!" },
            { 738211346, "With yours truly to help, how could you not be?" },
            { 738211347, "All you did was weigh down my arm." },
            { 738211348, "Your least unacceptable attempt yet." },
            { 738211349, "What, still not good enough for you?" },
            { 738211351, "We should be safe here." },
            { 738211352, "Good. I'm exhausted." },
            { 738211353, "Anybody home?" },
            { 738211354, "Thankfully not." },
            { 738211355, "\"Beyond the door, she was greeted by the most unimaginable sight—\"" },
            { 738211356, "An actual bed." },
            { 738211357, "\"Beyond the door, she was greeted by the most miraculous sight—\"" },
            { 738211358, "Somewhere to lie the fuck down." },
            { 738211359, "At last." },
            { 738211360, "Yes, very fortuitous timing, I must say." },
            { 738211361, "Quite a long rest this one, no?" },
            { 738211362, "What can I say? I'm wiped out." },
            { 738211363, "All the same, one only has so much time in life. Seems a shame to waste it." },
            { 738211364, "Someone used to live here, huh?" },
            { 738211365, "Indeed. I wonder what became of them..." },
            { 738211366, "Let's not go there." },
            { 738211367, "What are you pacing back and forth for? Do you need me to sing you a lullaby?" },
            { 738211368, "Fuck no. Then I'll never get to sleep." },
            { 738211369, "Couldn't bear to miss a note, eh? Understandable, I suppose." },
            { 738211370, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738211371, "A song from your beloved homeland?" },
            { 738211372, "Maybe? Just kinda stuck in my head." },
            { 738211373, "It's awfully dusty in here." },
            { 738211374, "Wha... How do you even know that?" },
            { 738211375, "I sense what you sense. We're connected." },
            { 738211376, "Wish I could turn you into a cat." },
            { 738211377, "One of those grubby little creatures? Ugh." },
            { 738211378, "Actually, scratch that. You'd need a total personality transplant." },
            { 738211379, "Are you missing your homeland?" },
            { 738211380, "Why do you care?" },
            { 738211381, "Sorry for asking..." },
            { 738211382, "So you don't ever need to eat?" },
            { 738211383, "A vambrace? Getting hungry? Don't be ridiculous!" },
            { 738211384, "Oh yeah, because you talking is totally normal." },
            { 738211385, "How can you be sure we're safe here?" },
            { 738211386, "Same way I can be sure you'll never stop being an asshole, I guess." },
            { 738211387, "How very charming." },
            { 738211388, "Time to catch some Zs." },
            { 738211389, "Do sleep well, won't you?" },
            { 738211390, "Huh? Sorry. Uh, you being...normal freaks me out." },
            { 738211391, "I'm still waiting for my thank-you..." },
            { 738211392, "Eh? For what?" },
            { 738211393, "Oh, I don't know—saving your life countless times in battle?" },
            { 738211394, "Man, feel like I need some serious \"me time.\"" },
            { 738211395, "I'm not sure what that is, but I don't think I want to be part of it." },
            { 738211396, "Oh, fiiine by me." },
            { 738211397, "Not the most uplifting place to spend the night, eh?" },
            { 738211398, "Hey, I can sleep here. That's all I care about." },
            { 738211399, "How very utilitarian of you." },
            { 738211400, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738211401, "Sounds like it might be bedtime..." },
            { 738211402, "Mmm... In a minute..." },
            { 738211403, "What would you do if a monster came smashing up through the floor?" },
            { 738211404, "Kick its ass. Throw it out. Go to sleep." },
            { 738211405, "Suppose I should have expected about that level of imagination..." },
            { 738211406, "Gimme a torana!" },
            { 738211407, "What's the matter!? Is something there?" },
            { 738211408, "Heh. Nah, just felt like saying it." },
            { 738211409, "Vambrace, vambrace, vambrace, vambrace, vambrace..." },
            { 738211410, "Nope! Cuff. Not about to change my mind." },
            { 738211411, "Not even if I keep repeating it until I drive you half-mad?" },
            { 738211412, "Maybe we should make something while we're here." },
            { 738211413, "Ooh, yes. What about something to keep the rain off?" },
            { 738211414, "You want me to invent the umbrella?" },
            { 738211415, "You seem a little tense. Time for a rest, perhaps?" },
            { 738211416, "Not sure I'll be able to sleep..." },
            { 738211417, "Lie dooown... You are feeling veeery sleepy..." },
            { 738211418, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738211419, "I'm not sure who you think toughing it out will impress. Just heal up, will you?" },
            { 738211420, "I didn't say anything..." },
            { 738211421, "Could have let me sleep a little longer..." },
            { 738211422, "You told me to wake you up!" },
            { 738211423, "Awake?" },
            { 738211424, "Wish I wasn't..." },
            { 738211425, "Think I might go back to sleep..." },
            { 738211426, "But I've only just woken you up!" },
            { 738211427, "You have a snooze button I could hit?" },
            { 738211428, "Hit me and I'll never wake you up again." },
            { 738211429, "I do not want to get out of bed." },
            { 738211430, "Well, you have to. So there." },
            { 738211431, "Up. Now." },
            { 738211432, "Ahhh, c'mon! Five more minutes!" },
            { 738211433, "Ready to get up?" },
            { 738211434, "As I'll ever be..." },
            { 738211436, "You look like you slept rather well." },
            { 738211437, "Woulda slept a whole lot better without you whining in my ear." },
            { 738211438, "Ugh... Tired..." },
            { 738211439, "Feel like I could use a little more rest..." },
            { 738211440, "Well, don't let me stop you." },
            { 738211441, "Are you sure you're properly rested?" },
            { 738211442, "Honestly? No." },
            { 738211443, "Hardly feel like I slept at all..." },
            { 738211444, "A little while longer, perhaps?" },
            { 738211445, "I could catch a few more Zs..." },
            { 738211446, "Be my guest." },
            { 738211447, "Shall we get going?" },
            { 738211448, "I dunno... Might need a little more R&R." },
            { 738211449, "Just a few minutes more? Pleeease?" },
            { 738211450, "Do what you like." },
            { 738211451, "I feel fucking great!" },
            { 738211452, "I'm very glad to hear it." },
            { 738211454, "I am back! And badder than ever!" },
            { 738211455, "Good. Can we get going, then?" },
            { 738211456, "Certainly seemed like you needed that." },
            { 738211457, "Break time's over. Let's get moving." },
            { 738211458, "Says the guy who can't even open the door to leave..." },
            { 738211459, "Why would I need to? I have you." },
            { 738211460, "Alright, let's move." },
            { 738211461, "Yes. We've a long way to go yet." },
            { 738211462, "Ugh. Mood killer." },
            { 738211463, "Another day's adventure awaits!" },
            { 738211464, "You make it sound like what we're doing is fun." },
            { 738211465, "Forgive me for trying to lighten the mood." },
            { 738211466, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738211467, "Very ladylike." },
            { 738211468, "What, I can't even yawn now?" },
            { 738211469, "Where are we off to today, then?" },
            { 738211470, "Not sure yet." },
            { 738211471, "No plan? Don't you think you ought to make one?" },
            { 738211472, "Finally. A chance to relax." },
            { 738211473, "Yeah. At last." },
            { 738211474, "Ta-da!" },
            { 738211475, "You're getting good at that." },
            { 738211476, "Quick breather?" },
            { 738211477, "Please. I'm out on my feet here." },
            { 738211482, "There's something soothing about a roaring blaze, isn't there?" },
            { 738211483, "Uh... Fire and I have a kinda...checkered past." },
            { 738211484, "Well, each to their own." },
            { 738211485, "Getting kinda sleepy..." },
            { 738211486, "A rest might not be a bad idea, but try to keep an eye open for danger." },
            { 738211487, "Hey, that's your job. Not like you'll be catching any Zs." },
            { 738211488, "Don't get too close, will you?" },
            { 738211489, "You worried you're gonna melt or something?" },
            { 738211490, "It's not entirely outside the realm of possibility." },
            { 738211491, "Anything we can cook?" },
            { 738211492, "One of the ghoulish creatures lurking just beyond the firelight, perhaps?" },
            { 738211493, "Uh, I was thinking more like marshmallows." },
            { 738211494, "Now, settle down and I'll tell you a story..." },
            { 738211495, "Ha. No." },
            { 738211496, "It's a good one... No? Well, you had your chance." },
            { 738211497, "You hear all those bugs?" },
            { 738211498, "I hope that's what they are..." },
            { 738211499, "Ugh. Thanks." },
            { 738211500, "I'm rather tired, you know." },
            { 738211501, "Oh yeah? Hard day sitting there on my arm?" },
            { 738211502, "I don't think you realize how much I— Never mind." },
            { 738211503, "So, uh...what would happen if you melted?" },
            { 738211504, "I'm not entirely sure I like where this is going..." },
            { 738211505, "What do you mean? I'm just...interested, that's all." },
            { 738211506, "Staring into the fire is nice, but one mustn't get too distracted." },
            { 738211507, "What do you—ow!" },
            { 738211508, "Exactly my point." },
            { 738211509, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738211510, "When the opportunity presents itself, the wise warrior rests." },
            { 738211511, "Yes, master." },
            { 738211512, "You know what your problem is? You're too short with people." },
            { 738211513, "Wow. Pot, meet kettle." },
            { 738211514, "I suppose they do say that imitation is the sincerest form of flattery..." },
            { 738211515, "Maybe I should put some more wood on this fire..." },
            { 738211516, "It's fine as it is, Frey. Or do you want to bring monsters running from miles around?" },
            { 738211517, "Pfft. Fine." },
            { 738211518, "A nice, soft bed wouldn't go amiss." },
            { 738211519, "Yeah, and a good, hot meal." },
            { 738211520, "Perhaps we'd better find somewhere you can get some proper sleep." },
            { 738211521, "Ugh. I'm struggling here." },
            { 738211522, "Would returning to Cipal be an idea, perhaps?" },
            { 738211523, "Nah. Too much hassle." },
            { 738211524, "We certainly had some tough customers on our hands today, didn't we?" },
            { 738211525, "Yeah? Hm, I seem to remember beating them all." },
            { 738211526, "I trust you know who's really responsible for all your victories..." },
            { 738211527, "Ugh, we're leaving already?" },
            { 738211528, "Yes. Because you decided to!" },
            { 738211529, "Alright, nap time's over!" },
            { 738211530, "What? That's all I get?" },
            { 738211531, "Out of time already?" },
            { 738211532, "Assuming you meant to adhere to the limit that you set, yes." },
            { 738211533, "I've changed my mind. Can we chill a little longer?" },
            { 738211534, "Certainly. Just don't count on me waking you up this time." },
            { 738211535, "Can I get a little more time to relax?" },
            { 738211536, "You can do what you like." },
            { 738211537, "Time's up. I said, TIME'S UP!" },
            { 738211538, "I can hear you. I just wish I couldn't." },
            { 738211539, "Mmm... That was nice. Quick stretch..." },
            { 738211540, "Oof! Are you sure it's healthy cracking your joints like that?" },
            { 738211542, "Awake at last. Thank goodness. I've been bored stiff." },
            { 738211543, "Well, thanks for keeping your mouth shut for once." },
            { 738211544, "How does a person manage to sleep for so long?" },
            { 738211545, "That was not a long enough rest." },
            { 738211546, "Nothing to stop you having another..." },
            { 738211547, "Ughh, does that even count as a rest?" },
            { 738211548, "If you need to take longer, you should." },
            { 738211549, "Do you think perhaps you ought to rest for a little longer?" },
            { 738211550, "Mmm... Might not be a bad idea..." },
            { 738211551, "Could have done with a little more sleep." },
            { 738211552, "A luxury we can't always afford, sadly." },
            { 738211553, "Well? Shall we make a move?" },
            { 738211554, "Gimme a sec..." },
            { 738211555, "Still not feeling a hundred percent..." },
            { 738211556, "Well, you're free to rest a little longer if you need it." },
            { 738211557, "Wow. Feeling super floaty." },
            { 738211558, "The sign of a good rest, I'd say." },
            { 738211560, "You certainly seem better for having taken a break." },
            { 738211561, "Hell yeah. Feel like I could take on the world!" },
            { 738211562, "Adequately rested and raring to go?" },
            { 738211563, "Can we get moving, please?" },
            { 738211564, "Yeah, yeah..." },
            { 738211565, "Less of the attitude, young lady." },
            { 738211566, "Alright, let's move out." },
            { 738211567, "You have put that fire out properly, haven't you?" },
            { 738211568, "Seriously? Yes, alright?" },
            { 738211569, "If you've quite finished lazing around." },
            { 738211570, "Easy for you to say. Must be nice getting carried around all day." },
            { 738211571, "The total and utter lack of freedom does rather spoil things..." },
            { 738211572, "Wait, wait. I feel like I'm forgetting something..." },
            { 738211573, "Please! Whatever it is, it's definitely not important!" },
            { 738211574, "You don't know that!" },
            { 738211575, "Let the adventure continue!" },
            { 738211576, "Uh, what the fuck was that?" },
            { 738211577, "Just...trying something out." },
            { 738211578, "What the fuck?" },
            { 738211579, "Seems someone's keen for a moment of your time." },
            { 738211580, "The feeling is not mutual." },
            { 738211581, "This is the last thing I need..." },
            { 738211582, "Just get rid of them." },
            { 738211583, "Eesh. Can't a girl have a meal in peace?" },
            { 738211584, "Uninvited guests." },
            { 738211585, "Rude." },
            { 738211586, "Feel free to send them packing." },
            { 738211587, "Shit! What now?" },
            { 738211588, "Just calm down and assess the situation." },
            { 738211589, "Man, I was so looking forward to taking a nap..." },
            { 738211590, "Have they no manners?" },
            { 738211591, "And me a lady and all!" },
            { 738211592, "Quite." },
            { 738211593, "This should be easy enough." },
            { 738211594, "If only that were true of every battle..." },
            { 738211595, "I'd imagine you'll have this wrapped up pretty quickly." },
            { 738211596, "Yup, no sweat." },
            { 738211597, "Don't worry, this'll be quick." },
            { 738211598, "I do hope so." },
            { 738211599, "Fancy your chances?" },
            { 738211600, "I'll give it my best shot." },
            { 738211601, "Seems kinda slow." },
            { 738211602, "Yes, that might not be your only concern here..." },
            { 738211603, "This one seems like something of a handful." },
            { 738211604, "Yeah. Better start pulling your weight." },
            { 738211605, "This one certainly stands out from the crowd." },
            { 738211606, "Whoopee..." },
            { 738211607, "You think I got this?" },
            { 738211608, "Only one way to find out..." },
            { 738211609, "Do run away if your death seems imminent, won't you?" },
            { 738211610, "You're not joking, are you?" },
            { 738211611, "Fighting animals isn't the same as fighting humans, Frey." },
            { 738211612, "Think I could have figured that one out myself, thanks." },
            { 738211613, "I hate fighting the cute ones..." },
            { 738211614, "An enemy is an enemy, Frey. The worst thing you can do is sympathize." },
            { 738211615, "Looks like a flighty one. Try to keep up." },
            { 738211616, "So a regular cat then? I got this." },
            { 738211617, "Only one way to win here: knock 'em outta the sky." },
            { 738211618, "I'd say so. You can't fly, after all—er, not the last time I checked, anyway..." },
            { 738211619, "Birds have an annoying habit of attacking from above. Be careful." },
            { 738211620, "Gotta try and bring them down to earth..." },
            { 738211621, "What the hell is this thing?" },
            { 738211622, "Something you should probably try to defeat as quickly as possible." },
            { 738211623, "Whatever you do, don't get bitten!" },
            { 738211624, "As if I'd choose for that to happen!" },
            { 738211625, "That's some serious armor right there." },
            { 738211626, "There's always a weak spot somewhere..." },
            { 738211627, "I am not a reptile person." },
            { 738211628, "Aim for the gaps between its scales!" },
            { 738211629, "Imagine these guys as stuffed toys! Aww..." },
            { 738211630, "What would you use them for? Frightening children to sleep?" },
            { 738211631, "Careful. These things are quicker than they look." },
            { 738211632, "How is that possible for something so...pudgy?" },
            { 738211633, "Not one to approach head-on, I'd say." },
            { 738211634, "Back attack, you mean? On it." },
            { 738211635, "Hope these things go down easy." },
            { 738211636, "You're not the only one." },
            { 738211637, "Horns like that aren't just for show, you know." },
            { 738211638, "Yeah, kinda got that just from looking at 'em." },
            { 738211639, "You wouldn't think these were herbivorous, would you?" },
            { 738211640, "Guess eating that fucked-up Break grass will do that to ya!" },
            { 738211641, "They may once have been human, but you can't afford to be sentimental." },
            { 738211642, "Yeah, think I can manage that, thanks." },
            { 738211643, "Your choices here are beat them or join them, I'd say." },
            { 738211644, "Roger that." },
            { 738211645, "Won't be making any new pals here." },
            { 738211646, "Business as usual for you, no?" },
            { 738211647, "Okay, now I've seen it all." },
            { 738211648, "You really do have to marvel at nature's endless imagination." },
            { 738211649, "It's...beautiful..." },
            { 738211650, "Tell me you're not fucking serious." },
            { 738211651, "Can barely make out what it used to be. Looks gnarly, though..." },
            { 738211652, "Not exactly the word I would have chosen, but...yes." },
            { 738211653, "I'd make a swift exit if I were you." },
            { 738211654, "I'm trying! Shit! Outta my way!" },
            { 738211655, "Don't fight them. It's a waste of time!" },
            { 738211656, "I know, but...ugh, fuck!" },
            { 738211657, "Just get the fuck outta my way, will you?" },
            { 738211658, "Quickly! We have to shake them off!" },
            { 738211659, "I need you to listen to me, Frey—" },
            { 738211660, "Yeah, no need. Get the fuck outta here, right?" },
            { 738211661, "We've been spotted!" },
            { 738211662, "Shit, shit, fuck, shit, shit!" },
            { 738211663, "I think it might be time for some extreme evasive maneuvers." },
            { 738211664, "No shit!" },
            { 738211665, "Don't let them outflank you!" },
            { 738211666, "Not gonna happen." },
            { 738211667, "There are slightly more of them than I'd like..." },
            { 738211668, "Hah, this'll be a pushover." },
            { 738211669, "What one might call a gaggle of troublemakers." },
            { 738211670, "The weak ones hunt in packs, huh?" },
            { 738211671, "Keep your wits about you." },
            { 738211672, "Very much in the room, thanks." },
            { 738211673, "How many of them are there?" },
            { 738211674, "I'm gonna say...a party's worth. Let's dance!" },
            { 738211675, "Looks like everybody showed up." },
            { 738211676, "Might as well make the most of the opportunity." },
            { 738211677, "This one's going to be a chore." },
            { 738211678, "Not the pep talk I needed." },
            { 738211679, "Wow. Quite a crowd." },
            { 738211680, "The mob mentality. Disgraceful, really." },
            { 738211681, "Are we surrounded?" },
            { 738211682, "Who cares? Just need to fight our way out." },
            { 738211713, "Do try to remember that magic is a finite resource." },
            { 738211714, "Oh, quit nagging." },
            { 738211715, "We got this, right?" },
            { 738211716, "Assuming you don't waste precious magic, yes." },
            { 738211717, "Now, Frey, you may think you're invincible—" },
            { 738211718, "But don't get careless, right? Yeah, yeah." },
            { 738211719, "Are you in any fit state to be fighting?" },
            { 738211720, "What are you worried about? I'm fine." },
            { 738211721, "Wish I had, like...unlimited magic ammo." },
            { 738211722, "Unfortunately for both of us, magic simply doesn't work that way." },
            { 738211723, "So...I should probably figure out how many more spells I've got in the tank..." },
            { 738211724, "Oh, you think so, do you?" },
            { 738211725, "Well, looks like you'll have to fight whether you like it or not." },
            { 738211726, "Really? Running kinda low on gas here..." },
            { 738211727, "How many...magic zaps we got left?" },
            { 738211728, "Safest to assume not many, I think." },
            { 738211729, "Ready to do this?" },
            { 738211730, "Not if I don't have to..." },
            { 738211731, "Oh, shit!" },
            { 738211732, "Might I suggest that we withdraw?" },
            { 738211733, "You...might not want to stick around." },
            { 738211734, "Yeah, no shit." },
            { 738211735, "My magic!" },
            { 738211736, "It's of no use to you now!" },
            { 738211743, "Quick freshen-upper?" },
            { 738211744, "Seems the rest did you good..." },
            { 738211745, "Was just thinking I could use a workout." },
            { 738211746, "Well, you have your wish." },
            { 738211747, "You're not too stiff, are you?" },
            { 738211748, "Come on, I barely sat down!" },
            { 738211753, "Again?" },
            { 738211754, "I think this one's taken a shine to you." },
            { 738211755, "Think I've got a fan club." },
            { 738211756, "Such is the price of notoriety." },
            { 738211757, "I think this one likes me." },
            { 738211758, "Well, all that glitters is definitely not gold." },
            { 738211763, "Oh, you wanna go? Bring it!" },
            { 738211764, "Well, there's certainly no faulting your enthusiasm, at least." },
            { 738211765, "Caught you by surprise there..." },
            { 738211766, "Yeah, dick move. It must be taking lessons from you." },
            { 738211767, "Is carelessness a hobby of yours or something?" },
            { 738211768, "Fuck off." },
            { 738211773, "That'll teach you!" },
            { 738211774, "Yeah, what he said!" },
            { 738211775, "Now's your chance!" },
            { 738211776, "On it!" },
            { 738211777, "Much obliged!" },
            { 738211778, "Well? Finish the job!" },
            { 738211779, "Stick that in your pipe and smoke it!" },
            { 738211780, "Hah! Uhhh...yeah!" },
            { 738211781, "Now's your chance!" },
            { 738211782, "Here it comes!" },
            { 738211783, "Now! Quickly!" },
            { 738211784, "Alriiight!" },
            { 738211785, "Go on! Put the boot in!" },
            { 738211786, "Don't need to tell me twice!" },
            { 738211787, "It's now or never!" },
            { 738211788, "Go, go!" },
            { 738211789, "Whoa! Did we just—" },
            { 738211790, "Yes! Now finish the job!" },
            { 738211863, "I wish someone would house-train these awful creatures." },
            { 738211864, "I wish someone would house-train you..." },
            { 738211865, "Let that be the end of it." },
            { 738211866, "Yeah. And don't be so annoying next time!" },
            { 738211867, "Down, boy!" },
            { 738211868, "Oh, that's just mean." },
            { 738211869, "That's your wings well and truly clipped!" },
            { 738211870, "Snappy." },
            { 738211871, "You're grounded." },
            { 738211872, "Ha. Yes, we did rather bring that one down to earth." },
            { 738211873, "Well, that was no fun." },
            { 738211874, "Yeah. Flying is for assholes." },
            { 738211875, "I must say, armor plating's rather an unsporting touch." },
            { 738211876, "Yeah. That shit is no fun." },
            { 738211877, "All done." },
            { 738211878, "And we didn't get bitten to death! Nice." },
            { 738211879, "Is it over?" },
            { 738211880, "Man, those things are like rock." },
            { 738211881, "Finally managed to clobber it, did you?" },
            { 738211882, "Yeah. One tough customer..." },
            { 738211883, "Little bear stew for dinner, perhaps?" },
            { 738211884, "Not a thing. Wait. It's not, right?" },
            { 738211885, "It's not just playing dead, is it?" },
            { 738211886, "Wanna poke it and find out?" },
            { 738211887, "And thus concludes the hunt!" },
            { 738211888, "Yeah. Feel kinda bad..." },
            { 738211889, "The strong eat the weak. It's the law of the jungle." },
            { 738211890, "Wait. We have to eat it?" },
            { 738211891, "Is this what guilt feels like?" },
            { 738211892, "I know. We'll just have to make sure it wasn't for nothing." },
            { 738211893, "はあ……" },
            { 738211894, "Still not comfortable killing your own kind, eh?" },
            { 738211895, "Sweet salvation awaits, friend." },
            { 738211896, "I hope you're right." },
            { 738211897, "Rest in peace." },
            { 738211898, "Fight now, mourn later." },
            { 738211899, "Has it dropped anything good?" },
            { 738211900, "Not much point fighting it if it didn't." },
            { 738211901, "Phew! Glad that's over." },
            { 738211902, "I think you'll find it was well worth the effort." },
            { 738211903, "Not bad." },
            { 738211904, "Oh yeah!" },
            { 738211905, "They just keep coming, don't they?" },
            { 738211906, "Fuck!" },
            { 738211907, "What's with these fucking things!?" },
            { 738211908, "Just don't bother fighting them!" },
            { 738211909, "There's too many of them!" },
            { 738211910, "Oh, you think?" },
            { 738211911, "Did we actually just do that?" },
            { 738211912, "I...believe we did, yes..." },
            { 738211913, "Holy shit! Am I a fucking badass or what?" },
            { 738211914, "Yes. Thanks to me." },
            { 738211915, "Well I must say, I feel marvelous." },
            { 738211916, "Is it me, or are we just, like, really fucking good at this?" },
            { 738211941, "Hah. Finished in record time!" },
            { 738211942, "The poor quality of the opposition did help quite a bit..." },
            { 738211943, "You don't hang around, do you?" },
            { 738211944, "No point wasting time." },
            { 738211945, "Didn't even give 'em time to blink!" },
            { 738211946, "Exactly what purpose is that ridiculous exaggeration supposed to serve?" },
            { 738211983, "It can't be very satisfying facing enemies of this caliber." },
            { 738211984, "Yeah, it does feel kinda pointless." },
            { 738211985, "Kinda want more of a challenge." },
            { 738211986, "I'm very glad to hear it." },
            { 738211987, "Can't complain about an easy ride." },
            { 738211988, "Can't you? Doesn't exactly get the blood pumping." },
            { 738211989, "Hoo yeah!" },
            { 738211990, "That's the stuff! Now let's find something we can really get our teeth into!" },
            { 738211991, "Do I sense you getting better at this, Frey?" },
            { 738211992, "How could I not? It's that or get my ass whooped." },
            { 738211993, "Had to work a little there." },
            { 738211994, "Only a little?" },
            { 738211995, "Fuck... Guess that went pretty well, all things considered." },
            { 738211996, "I'll say. I can't believe you won." },
            { 738211997, "Just gonna come out and say this: I am now a major-league badass." },
            { 738211998, "You're not thinking of getting rid of me, are you? Oh, wait..." },
            { 738211999, "I am giving myself an A for effort on that one." },
            { 738212000, "And so you should. Top marks!" },
            { 738212055, "Think that's all of them." },
            { 738212056, "Seems like it. Nice work." },
            { 738212057, "Tired after that little performance?" },
            { 738212058, "Hey, I'm always tired." },
            { 738212059, "Looks like we're done here." },
            { 738212060, "It does, doesn't it?" },
            { 738212061, "I put in some serious work there." },
            { 738212062, "It was an acceptable effort, yes." },
            { 738212063, "Reasonably impressive, I suppose." },
            { 738212064, "\"Reasonably\"? Kiss my ass." },
            { 738212065, "Done, I guess." },
            { 738212066, "You almost sound disappointed." },
            { 738212067, "Whoa, that was a lot." },
            { 738212068, "Well, it seems to be over now." },
            { 738212069, "I think that's that." },
            { 738212070, "It damn well better be! That was one hell of a workout." },
            { 738212071, "Were you counting how many asses we kicked there?" },
            { 738212072, "Sorry. I stopped after the first few." },
            { 738212079, "Are we clear?" },
            { 738212080, "Seems so, yes." },
            { 738212081, "Something about living to fight another day, right?" },
            { 738212082, "Exactly. And technically, you didn't lose." },
            { 738212083, "Hate it when things don't go my way." },
            { 738212084, "Noted. I'll add it to the list." },
            { 738212085, "I must say, you really do run from battle with a certain aplomb." },
            { 738212086, "A certain a-what? Anyway, thanks." },
            { 738212087, "It is sometimes better to run than fight. Sometimes." },
            { 738212088, "Subtle." },
            { 738212089, "No point in fighting when you don't have to." },
            { 738212090, "Whatever makes you feel better..." },
            { 738212091, "And here we are again." },
            { 738212092, "Doesn't look like much has changed..." },
            { 738212093, "You never know. Quick look round, perhaps?" },
            { 738212094, "People!" },
            { 738212095, "All the people. In the whole world. Literally." },
            { 738212096, "Which is why it's so good to see them." },
            { 738212097, "I'm hooome!" },
            { 738212098, "I suppose we'd better ask around and see what's new." },
            { 738212099, "Yeah. Where does everybody hang out again?" },
            { 738212100, "Feels safer here, huh?" },
            { 738212101, "But not entirely safe. Don't let your guard down." },
            { 738212102, "Anyone ever told you you're a broken record?" },
            { 738212103, "Well, it's a familiar vista, if nothing else." },
            { 738212104, "Hey, familiar works for me." },
            { 738212105, "I suppose that's one way of looking at it..." },
            { 738212106, "Feel like I can breathe easier when Cipal comes into view." },
            { 738212107, "Because fresh supplies are close at hand?" },
            { 738212108, "No, because there are actual human beings there." },
            { 738212109, "Phew, it's hot..." },
            { 738212110, "No sweating on the vambrace!" },
            { 738212111, "Ugh. Fine." },
            { 738212112, "Ugh. So dry. It's gross." },
            { 738212113, "Yes, the sun is rather relentless." },
            { 738212114, "Not nearly as relentless as you, pal." },
            { 738212115, "Horribly hot and painfully dry..." },
            { 738212116, "Not a great combo." },
            { 738212117, "Well, at least we don't have to live here." },
            { 738212118, "One could almost imagine living in Visoria..." },
            { 738212119, "I guess. If you're into that sorta thing." },
            { 738212120, "I'd take it over Praenost or Avoalet any day." },
            { 738212121, "Wind feels nice." },
            { 738212122, "Yes, until an unexpected gust blows you off a cliff." },
            { 738212123, "I dunno. Could be kinda fun." },
            { 738212124, "The Break seems oddly out of place here." },
            { 738212125, "Yeah. No Break and no monsters, and this would be a pretty peaceful scene." },
            { 738212126, "True of everywhere else in Athia, I suppose..." },
            { 738212127, "It's fucking f-f-freezing!" },
            { 738212128, "Don't lose your footing in the snow." },
            { 738212129, "Don't worry. I've spent my whole life picking my way through this shit." },
            { 738212130, "I'm frosting up." },
            { 738212131, "Well, think warm thoughts or something." },
            { 738212132, "Or you could just light a fire..." },
            { 738212133, "Starting to wish we were back in Praenost..." },
            { 738212134, "Really? Wouldn't be my first choice." },
            { 738212135, "Anything's better than this damn cold." },
            { 738212136, "All set?" },
            { 738212137, "As ready as I'll ever be." },
            { 738212138, "Alright, let's do this." },
            { 738212139, "Alright, let's hit the road!" },
            { 738212140, "Oh, so you're the boss now?" },
            { 738212141, "Sorry. Just thought it might make a nice change..." },
            { 738212142, "We are out of here." },
            { 738212143, "Sure you've done everything you need to do?" },
            { 738212144, "A hundred percent! Okay, ninety." },
            { 738212145, "See ya, Cipal." },
            { 738212146, "If you need to go back for anything, now's the time." },
            { 738212147, "Great. And now I'm worried I do. Thanks a bunch." },
            { 738212148, "Any foes we face from here on out will be much less agreeable." },
            { 738212149, "Uh-huh. \"So be on your guard, Frey.\" Something super useful like that?" },
            { 738212150, "I'm only trying to help..." },
            { 738212151, "Time to wave goodbye to the city." },
            { 738212152, "Well, you can drink your fill of ale when we return." },
            { 738212153, "You think that's all I'm looking forward to?" },
            { 738212154, "Whew. Will not be missing that place." },
            { 738212155, "But the brutally inhospitable climate was so charming!" },
            { 738212157, "Ahhh... Feels cooler already." },
            { 738212158, "Yes. Even the wind in Praenost was unbearably hot." },
            { 738212159, "Yeah. Dried my throat out like crazy." },
            { 738212160, "Blissful, sandstorm-free pastures await..." },
            { 738212161, "Why do you care about sandstorms? You're a cuff." },
            { 738212162, "A vambrace. And a vambrace with feelings, thank you very much." },
            { 738212163, "Ugh, this is so weird. Can't tell what's real anymore..." },
            { 738212164, "Can't blame you. Visoria would have that effect on anyone." },
            { 738212166, "We're clear, right?" },
            { 738212167, "Of Visoria? Just about, yes." },
            { 738212168, "Thought we'd never make it out of there..." },
            { 738212169, "I wonder where we are, exactly." },
            { 738212170, "Somewhere nice and safe and non-insane, right?" },
            { 738212171, "Let me get back to you on that..." },
            { 738212172, "Ahhh, I can breathe again!" },
            { 738212173, "The air doesn't seem to be any different to me." },
            { 738212174, "Believe me, it's different." },
            { 738212175, "What's the matter? Tired?" },
            { 738212176, "Nah, just...coming here makes me think of courtrooms." },
            { 738212177, "Yes. You do have rather a talent for being taken prisoner, don't you?" },
            { 738212178, "Mmm, finally getting some warmth back in my bones." },
            { 738212179, "Yes, I can feel it too." },
            { 738212180, "Good. It's no fun having a freezing cold hunk of metal on your wrist." },
            { 738212181, "Hey yo, anybody here?" },
            { 738212182, "Highly unlikely, I'm afraid." },
            { 738212183, "We found Bob, didn't we?" },
            { 738212184, "Ooh, perhaps we can rest here—perhaps not." },
            { 738212185, "Yeah. Not my idea of relaxing." },
            { 738212186, "Honestly, some people are absolute slobs." },
            { 738212187, "Anything around here we can swipe?" },
            { 738212188, "You've barely even walked through the door." },
            { 738212189, "Well, we obviously can't sleep here. Might as well get something out of it." },
            { 738212190, "Nobody's home." },
            { 738212191, "Nope. But they were once." },
            { 738212192, "Yes. Sad to see the remnants of people's former lives..." },
            { 738212193, "People used to live here." },
            { 738212194, "People who may have left valuables behind..." },
            { 738212195, "Hmm. Might as well take a look around, I guess." },
            { 738212196, "Was this...a village?" },
            { 738212197, "Maybe once." },
            { 738212198, "Hm. Not the most uplifting sight." },
            { 738212208, "Check it out. Fortress." },
            { 738212209, "Well, it'll be a good chance to flex our muscles." },
            { 738212210, "Uh, I never said we're going." },
            { 738212211, "What a wonderful place for a massacre." },
            { 738212212, "Great. Now you've said that, we're definitely gonna get jumped." },
            { 738212213, "I do so love to tempt fate." },
            { 738212214, "My gut is saying \"run.\"" },
            { 738212215, "The old animal instinct, eh?" },
            { 738212216, "Who're you calling an animal?" },
            { 738212217, "Do try not to plummet to your doom." },
            { 738212218, "You cannot help yourself, can you?" },
            { 738212219, "Oh, I'm deadly serious, believe me." },
            { 738212220, "Aaah! Do. Not. Move." },
            { 738212221, "You have no idea how much that makes me want to." },
            { 738212222, "Yeah, talk it up. You're the one getting the easy ride." },
            { 738212223, "What an impressively long way down." },
            { 738212224, "Yeah. How did they even build this thing?" },
            { 738212225, "Sadly, I believe that knowledge died long ago." },
            { 738212226, "Thanks for having me!" },
            { 738212227, "So rare to meet a polite young lady these days." },
            { 738212228, "One must do one's best. How did I do?" },
            { 738212229, "I'm certainly glad to leave that dusty little hellhole." },
            { 738212230, "Why would a hunk of metal give a shit about dust?" },
            { 738212231, "It sticks to one's surface awfully! Ugh!" },
            { 738212232, "Was kinda hoping to find some kick-ass treasure in there..." },
            { 738212233, "One can expect too much of dilapidated shacks, young Frey." },
            { 738212234, "Guess so." },
            { 738212235, "Don't go getting all maudlin, will you?" },
            { 738212236, "What the fuck is \"maudlin\"? Not me, anyway." },
            { 738212237, "Good. The place is beyond saving." },
            { 738212238, "These places really bum me out sometimes." },
            { 738212239, "That little scene we just left behind, you mean?" },
            { 738212240, "Yeah. Must've been so...alive back in the day." },
            { 738212241, "Well, that place didn't exactly fill me with joy." },
            { 738212242, "Look on the bright side! The inhabitants might all have escaped to Cipal." },
            { 738212243, "Guess you're right. Hope so." },
            { 738212253, "Well, there wasn't much to write home about in there." },
            { 738212254, "Yes, give or take a horde of mindless, murderous horrors." },
            { 738212255, "Eh. You can keep 'em." },
            { 738212256, "So if they built a fortress, does that mean there was a war here back in the day?" },
            { 738212257, "There is always war, Frey." },
            { 738212258, "Whoa. Cool it, Mini Sila." },
            { 738212259, "That was some mad monster action. I'm beat..." },
            { 738212260, "Time to take a breather, perhaps?" },
            { 738212261, "Definitely not your worst idea." },
            { 738212262, "Hey, the bridge didn't collapse. Nice." },
            { 738212263, "Why would it?" },
            { 738212264, "I dunno, just...felt like it was gonna." },
            { 738212265, "Glad no one attacked us while we were on that thing." },
            { 738212266, "Yes, I doubt they would have considered how much weight it could hold." },
            { 738212267, "Ugh, they probably would've rushed us even if it took the whole bridge down. Stupid fuckers." },
            { 738212268, "It's rather sad to think of that old bridge once having been a bustling thoroughfare." },
            { 738212269, "Yeah. Someone went through a whole lot of trouble to build that thing." },
            { 738212270, "Well, at least you're making use of it." },
            { 738212271, "There's some Break here, right?" },
            { 738212272, "Not enough to worry about, but yes." },
            { 738212273, "Still, good to know." },
            { 738212274, "Careful. Break..." },
            { 738212275, "Not much though, right? Ah, I think we're good." },
            { 738212276, "Hm, famous last words..." },
            { 738212277, "You feel that? It's the Break, right?" },
            { 738212278, "I think it is, yes. Thankfully, it's only mild." },
            { 738212279, "Mild's good. Let's try to keep away from where it gets worse." },
            { 738212280, "We're getting a little deeper here..." },
            { 738212281, "Into the Break, you mean? Okay, lemme know if it gets worse." },
            { 738212282, "Of course. Just don't rely entirely on me." },
            { 738212283, "The Break's getting thicker." },
            { 738212284, "It certainly seems so. Careful." },
            { 738212285, "Oh, c'mon. When am I not careful?" },
            { 738212286, "Hmm, it's getting stronger." },
            { 738212287, "Huh? What is?" },
            { 738212288, "The Break, what else? Keep your wits about you." },
            { 738212289, "Hold tight. It's getting bad in here..." },
            { 738212290, "I really don't think I can hold any tighter." },
            { 738212292, "Proceed with extreme caution, Frey." },
            { 738212293, "Or we could...I dunno, go around?" },
            { 738212294, "Turning back is always an option." },
            { 738212295, "Okay, this is not good." },
            { 738212296, "The Break is rather intense here, yes. Be on your guard." },
            { 738212297, "Don't worry. Not looking to die just yet." },
            { 738212298, "Huh? Where'd the Break go?" },
            { 738212299, "I think we're free of it for now." },
            { 738212300, "Was so thin I barely noticed..." },
            { 738212301, "We're clear of the Break." },
            { 738212302, "We are? When did that happen?" },
            { 738212303, "I'm not surprised you didn't notice—it was only mild." },
            { 738212304, "Feel like I can breathe a little easier now." },
            { 738212305, "Really? There wasn't even that much Break." },
            { 738212306, "There was enough, alright?" },
            { 738212307, "There's no Break here." },
            { 738212308, "Ah, thought I felt a little spring in my step!" },
            { 738212309, "Count yourself lucky to be able to be so flippant about it." },
            { 738212310, "Are we out of the Break?" },
            { 738212311, "It would seem so. But don't relax just yet." },
            { 738212312, "Dude, you tell me that so often, it would be a miracle if I could." },
            { 738212313, "Finally, a little room to breathe." },
            { 738212314, "I was breathing just fine." },
            { 738212315, "Well, there's breathing and there's breathing." },
            { 738212316, "Glad we're out of there." },
            { 738212317, "Yes, the air in there didn't seem particularly pleasant." },
            { 738212318, "Nah. It just felt...ugh." },
            { 738212319, "Frey! My goodness, you've sprouted horns!" },
            { 738212320, "Huh? I have!?" },
            { 738212321, "No, of course you haven't. Didn't think you'd actually fall for it..." },
            { 738212322, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212323, "Gosh, are you...are you alright? Is it the Break?" },
            { 738212324, "Hah! Gotcha on that one." },
            { 738212325, "What were we doing again? Get your act together, will you?" },
            { 738212326, "Yeah, yeah." },
            { 738212327, "What were we supposed to be doing, again?" },
            { 738212328, "Don't look at me. Think, why don't you?" },
            { 738212329, "What's on the agenda today?" },
            { 738212330, "A little light monster-pummelling, perhaps?" },
            { 738212331, "Journey's end." },
            { 738212332, "Whoa, that was quick." },
            { 738212333, "We're here!" },
            { 738212334, "That really was miraculously fast." },
            { 738212335, "Uh, why are we here again?" },
            { 738212336, "Please tell me you're joking." },
            { 738212337, "Best foot forward, now." },
            { 738212338, "Yeah, thanks." },
            { 738212339, "Well, that didn't go very well." },
            { 738212340, "Just don't say a word, Cuff." },
            { 738212341, "Not my day." },
            { 738212342, "Just breathe and think. Breeeathe...and thiiink." },
            { 738212343, "Wakey wakey!" },
            { 738212344, "Huh? I'm awake!" },
            { 738212345, "Shall we make a move?" },
            { 738212346, "You don't make moves. You just sit there being a prick." },
            { 738212347, "You looked like you were miles away." },
            { 738212348, "I was deep in very serious thought, thank you very much." },
            { 738212355, "Not good..." },
            { 738212356, "Not at all..." },
            { 738212357, "If only you were made of sterner stuff." },
            { 738212358, "Yeah, well I'm not, alright?" },
            { 738212359, "You're looking a little green around the gills." },
            { 738212360, "You think there might be a reason for that?" },
            { 738212361, "Frey!" },
            { 738212362, "Fuuuck..." },
            { 738212363, "Pull yourself together!" },
            { 738212364, "No... Not now..." },
            { 738212365, "Ngh... Not good..." },
            { 738212366, "Frey! Can you hear me, Frey!?" },
            { 738212367, "Goodness! What's happened to you?" },
            { 738212368, "At least try to sound concerned!" },
            { 738212369, "Oof! I don't feel so good..." },
            { 738212370, "Come on! Snap out of it!" },
            { 738212371, "I can't protect you like this!" },
            { 738212372, "I fucking know already!" },
            { 738212373, "Now might be a good time to heal yourself." },
            { 738212374, "I am very aware of that, thanks!" },
            { 738212375, "Think we're in a bit of a pickle here." },
            { 738212376, "Yeah. Need to heal up." },
            { 738212377, "I'm in trouble here..." },
            { 738212378, "Then stop talking and heal yourself!" },
            { 738212397, "Nailed it!" },
            { 738212398, "Don't push your luck, young lady." },
            { 738212399, "Couldn't just take the long way round?" },
            { 738212400, "I think you know the answer to that." },
            { 738212401, "You seem to have survived that in one piece." },
            { 738212402, "Oh, please. That was nothing." },
            { 738212403, "Ooh, floaty." },
            { 738212404, "More like...slow-fall-y, but...yes." },
            { 738212405, "Bending the rules of nature. Impressive." },
            { 738212406, "Prav had some killer tricks up her sleeve, huh?" },
            { 738212407, "Are you mad?" },
            { 738212408, "Look, this is the quickest way, alright?" },
            { 738212409, "Ah, shit. My clothes are dragging me down." },
            { 738212410, "What did you expect?" },
            { 738212411, "I suppose you're going to tell me this was our only choice?" },
            { 738212412, "What do you care? You can't feel it." },
            { 738212413, "Well, at least we landed in water." },
            { 738212414, "Y-you mean you didn't look before you jumped!?" },
            { 738212415, "Well, I suppose I can't fault your commitment." },
            { 738212416, "Thanks. I'm a bold and decisive thinker." },
            { 738212417, "That was quite the fall, huh?" },
            { 738212418, "Yes, you wouldn't mind warning me next time, would you?" },
            { 738212419, "Dry land! At last!" },
            { 738212420, "Yes, I did feel a little exposed out there, I must admit." },
            { 738212421, "A nice, thorough wipe-down, if you please!" },
            { 738212422, "In your dreams. You can drip dry like everybody else." },
            { 738212423, "Fucking drenched here." },
            { 738212424, "You'll soon walk yourself dry, I'm sure." },
            { 738212429, "Something wrong?" },
            { 738212430, "Yes... The air feels...different all of a sudden." },
            { 738212432, "I sense something distinctly unpleasant." },
            { 738212433, "You think maybe we should try and go around?" },
            { 738212434, "I'll leave that decision to you. But caution is strongly advised." },
            { 738212435, "Something's up, I can feel it." },
            { 738212436, "It's often best to trust such feelings." },
            { 738212437, "Okay. I'll keep a lookout." },
            { 738212444, "There's no escaping now!" },
            { 738212445, "Shit. What do we do...?" },
            { 738212446, "Hunker down. You can't fight this." },
            { 738212447, "Fuck, fuck, fuck. Not good. Not good." },
            { 738212448, "Stop panicking and find somewhere safe." },
            { 738212449, "On it." },
            { 738212450, "Well, this is unfortunate..." },
            { 738212451, "I guess we hide, right?" },
            { 738212452, "That might be safest, yes." },
            { 738212459, "It's over." },
            { 738212460, "Looks that way..." },
            { 738212461, "And...breathe." },
            { 738212462, "I think that's it." },
            { 738212463, "Man, that was nuts." },
            { 738212464, "Let's try to avoid it next time, shall we?" },
            { 738212465, "You still with me?" },
            { 738212466, "I can prove it with a quick clip round the ear if you like." },
            { 738212467, "Try it and die." },
            { 738212474, "Is this a...town?" },
            { 738212475, "A town that requires its residents to fly, apparently." },
            { 738212476, "Not sure it'd be that easy even then..." },
            { 738212519, "You think we could turn this place back to how it used to be?" },
            { 738212520, "You'd probably be better off trying to build an entirely new city." },
            { 738212659, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212660, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212661, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212662, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212663, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212664, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212665, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212666, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212667, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212668, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212669, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212670, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212671, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212672, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212673, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212674, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212889, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212890, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212891, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212892, "You...!" },
            { 738212893, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212894, "How dare you!?" },
            { 738212928, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212929, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212930, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212931, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212932, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738212933, "Take this!" },
            { 738212935, "Die!" },
            { 738212960, "You will pay for your crimes!" },
            { 738212961, "Prepare to die!" },
            { 738212962, "By the cleansing waters!" },
            { 738212963, "Worthless fool!" },
            { 738212964, "No time to repent!" },
            { 738212965, "Witness my might!" },
            { 738212966, "The weight of your crimes grows heavy..." },
            { 738212967, "Now you suffer, as all wrongdoers must!" },
            { 738212968, "Now finally you suffer for your crimes!" },
            { 738213346, "Very impressive." },
            { 738213347, "Just try not to \"catch some air\" into a seriously early grave." },
            { 738213348, "I can run like the wind! And I'm not even getting tired!" },
            { 738213350, "Please try not to get too carried away..." },
            { 738213352, "I believe the way onward is o'er yonder." },
            { 738213356, "Say something if you can hear me!" },
            { 738213357, "Not a sound..." },
            { 738213364, "Well, it did get crushed by all that rubble..." },
            { 738213365, "Great. So much for our dead dragon." },
            { 738213366, "Alive and kicking. And very, very cross." },
            { 738213367, "Try not to get killed." },
            { 738213369, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738213370, "Forgive me." },
            { 738213371, "I am Auden Keen." },
            { 738213374, "No!" },
            { 738213380, "DEBUG START(CHAPTER)" },
            { 738213381, "CHAPTER 4" },
            { 738213382, "CHAPTER 4 DEPARTURE" },
            { 738213383, "CHAPTER 5 BOSS" },
            { 738213392, "Wouldn't mind if these guys were a little smaller." },
            { 738213393, "Like me, you mean? How kind." },
            { 738213394, "Gotta love that they can't talk smack at least." },
            { 738213395, "Ugh. Only if you prefer squawks, screeches, and incoherent bellowing." },
            { 738213396, "Awww, I bet it has cute little paws!" },
            { 738213397, "I'd advise against letting it hit you so you can check." },
            { 738213398, "Not adorable." },
            { 738213399, "Certainly not pet material, I agree." },
            { 738213400, "I suppose one could grow fond of this one in time..." },
            { 738213401, "Ha. Good luck with that." },
            { 738213402, "Are appearances really so important?" },
            { 738213403, "Hey, it's not just how this thing looks. It's how it sounds, how it moves... Ugh." },
            { 738213404, "If you stare long enough, it almost starts to seem less hideous..." },
            { 738213405, "Ugh, agree to disagree. I'd rather poke my fucking eyes out." },
            { 738213406, "You won't be giving this one a snuggle anytime soon." },
            { 738213407, "Yeah. I don't think it's the snuggling type." },
            { 738213408, "It's rude to judge by appearances, you know." },
            { 738213409, "Uh, okay. Can I judge it by its overwhelming sense of grossness instead?" },
            { 738213410, "Mind if I close my eyes to fight this one?" },
            { 738213411, "I wouldn't recommend it..." },
            { 738213412, "You'll need to either outmaneuver this one or stop it altogether." },
            { 738213413, "The \"hit and hope\" approach not working for you?" },
            { 738213414, "Are you serious!? How do you even move that fast?" },
            { 738213415, "Asks the girl who runs from everything!" },
            { 738213416, "How come you can't get that big, Cuff?" },
            { 738213417, "If I could, do you think I'd still be stuck to you?" },
            { 738213418, "Could use one of Alice's magic cakes to make this guy smaller." },
            { 738213419, "Ah, yes. The ones one finds absolutely everywhere." },
            { 738213420, "Damn! Could use one of those Wonderland cakes..." },
            { 738213421, "Of course. Wonderland. Where you seem to insist on living..." },
            { 738213422, "Would be kinda cool to be able to fly..." },
            { 738213423, "If you wish hard enough, perhaps you'll sprout a pair of wings." },
            { 738213424, "Ugh! Why do they have to attack from up there!?" },
            { 738213425, "I suppose you'll just have to learn to fly." },
            { 738213426, "Hey, you can't turn into a flying carpet, can you?" },
            { 738213427, "A flying carpet? I've never heard such utter nonsense in my life." },
            { 738213434, "Did that cloak use to belong to some sort of...vagrant?" },
            { 738213435, "Wow. Anyone ever tell you, \"If you can't say something nice, don't say anything at all?\"" },
            { 738213436, "Well, if I've got to be a matching accessory, I'd rather be matched with something presentable." },
            { 738213437, "This cloak's pretty nicely made, huh?" },
            { 738213438, "They certainly didn't scrimp on the materials." },
            { 738213439, "Hmm. Not bad, craftspeople of Athia." },
            { 738213440, "Was Sila better with magic or a sword?" },
            { 738213441, "I'd say she was equally terrifying with both." },
            { 738213442, "...Suddenly feeling very lucky to have beat her." },
            { 738213443, "Looks nice and warm, that one." },
            { 738213444, "Huh? Oh, my cloak. Yeah. Perfect for cold nights." },
            { 738213445, "Certainly a worthwhile consideration for anyone wandering the wilds of Praenost." },
            { 738213446, "So that's how they make their cloaks in Avoalet, is it?" },
            { 738213447, "Uh-huh. It doesn't really scream \"fun\"..." },
            { 738213448, "Very much like the land of its origin." },
            { 738213449, "This cloak is super warm." },
            { 738213450, "I expect they used some kind of material unique to the region." },
            { 738213451, "Nice..." },
            { 738213452, "Why do I have the urge to pick up a book all of a sudden?" },
            { 738213453, "I'd hazard a guess that it's something to do with your cloak being from Visoria." },
            { 738213454, "We'd better keep an eye out for some riveting reads." },
            { 738213455, "Olas's cloak. Certainly has the look of a quality piece..." },
            { 738213456, "Something tells me there's a \"but.\"" },
            { 738213457, "Well, she was rather fond of illusions." },
            { 738213458, "That cloak doesn't look like it would protect you from much." },
            { 738213459, "Feels pretty hard-wearing, though. Must be made of pretty good materials." },
            { 738213460, "It wouldn't surprise me—certainly seems very nicely put together." },
            { 738213461, "This cloak belonged to Cinta, right?" },
            { 738213462, "Well, it was made in Junoon, at least." },
            { 738213463, "Never mind." },
            { 738213464, "So...Cipal's the only place people have left, huh?" },
            { 738213465, "Yes. ...For now." },
            { 738213466, "...You're the worst." },
            { 738213467, "Sila oversaw the defense of all Athia." },
            { 738213468, "She must have had quite an army." },
            { 738213469, "Indeed. Stationed in the fortifications she was forever building." },
            { 738213470, "So this was Cinta's turf..." },
            { 738213471, "Sorry, but this is no time for wistful musing." },
            { 738213472, "...Yeah, thanks." },
            { 738213473, "What a strange place." },
            { 738213474, "It certainly seems to have a lot of surprises up its sleeve..." },
            { 738213476, "It's weirdly quiet here." },
            { 738213477, "I wonder if that's the idea..." },
            { 738213478, "Do not say another word! I already feel like I'm in a fucking horror movie." },
            { 738213479, "I think they might have once farmed livestock here." },
            { 738213480, "Definitely didn't see much of that in New York." },
            { 738213481, "I'd imagine you didn't see many monsters there, either." },
            { 738213482, "So what else was special about Visoria?" },
            { 738213483, "Well, Olas was a tireless seeker of knowledge." },
            { 738213484, "More than in the archives back in Cipal? Whoa." },
            { 738213485, "This place puts me on edge." },
            { 738213486, "Not a fan of unsettling silences?" },
            { 738213487, "Yep, just the input I needed. Thanks." },
            { 738213488, "Guess Olas must have left a ton of intel about Athia on record, huh?" },
            { 738213489, "Good luck finding it. She did rather enjoy hiding things." },
            { 738213490, "Well, no harm in looking..." },
            { 738213491, "The architectural vibe around here's pretty...severe." },
            { 738213492, "Well, most of Athia's governmental ministries were based here." },
            { 738213493, "Yeah, not my scene at all. Let's not stick around." },
            { 738213500, "Oh, mmm... What's that smell?" },
            { 738213501, "Some kind of fragrant grass, I believe." },
            { 738213502, "It's nice. Kinda...relaxing." },
            { 738213503, "Take care—there's nowhere to hide in terrain like this." },
            { 738213504, "Why hide when we can kick ass instead?" },
            { 738213505, "Yes, yes. Just promise me you'll run if you find yourself outmatched, will you?" },
            { 738213506, "Almost feels like you might see fairies in a place like this..." },
            { 738213507, "If fairies are some sort of vicious monster, I wholeheartedly agree." },
            { 738213508, "Ugh. Why do you have to be so...you?" },
            { 738213509, "This isn't one of those woods you can never escape from once you've gone in it, is it?" },
            { 738213510, "If you're worried, perhaps you should leave some kind of trail?" },
            { 738213511, "Sure. Got any breadcrumbs?" },
            { 738213512, "Any squirrels around here?" },
            { 738213513, "Some sort of Earth foodstuff?" },
            { 738213514, "What? No! ...I think." },
            { 738213515, "Ugh, I'm filthy!" },
            { 738213516, "Could you try to keep me clean at least?" },
            { 738213517, "Oh, quit whining. You're wipe-clean." },
            { 738213518, "Shit. This is tough going..." },
            { 738213519, "An ambush here could spell serious trouble. You need to keep moving." },
            { 738213520, "Easy for you to say..." },
            { 738213521, "Try not to get a foot stuck. You don't want to fall over." },
            { 738213522, "And there I was thinking I'd love for that to happen!" },
            { 738213523, "I wouldn't put it past you..." },
            { 738213524, "I doubt anything would grow here..." },
            { 738213525, "Aww, thinking of starting a little garden?" },
            { 738213526, "My hands are quite full with trying to keep you from dying, thank you very much." },
            { 738213527, "We'd better hope that dust cloud dies down soon." },
            { 738213528, "What are you so worried about?" },
            { 738213529, "You've clearly never been covered head to toe in filth before..." },
            { 738213530, "Man, I'm glad I kept my sneakers on." },
            { 738213531, "Are they really as incredible as you insist?" },
            { 738213532, "Oh, these babies are literally the pinnacle of human ingenuity." },
            { 738213533, "Into bone-chilling, soul-sapping ice, perhaps? There's an idea..." },
            { 738213534, "Is it snowing again?" },
            { 738213535, "Ugh, I hate the cold! Makes me moody as hell." },
            { 738213536, "Ha. What doesn't?" },
            { 738213537, "Snowing again. Thought it got cold suddenly." },
            { 738213538, "Keep your eyes on the ground ahead of you." },
            { 738213539, "Yeah, yeah. Oop... Steady as she goes..." },
            { 738213540, "I think I'm starting to freeze up." },
            { 738213541, "Don't you have, like, a heater setting or something?" },
            { 738213542, "Hmph. Don't you have, like, the ability to light a fire or something?" },
            { 738213543, "Fighting up here may not be the best idea." },
            { 738213544, "Well, you don't have to attack every enemy you see." },
            { 738213545, "Go around, you mean? ...I'll think about it." },
            { 738213546, "You might want to think about what would happen if you fell here." },
            { 738213547, "And you might want to shut the fuck up." },
            { 738213548, "I'm only trying to help." },
            { 738213549, "Don't look down, don't look down, don't look down..." },
            { 738213550, "Would looking down not be advisable?" },
            { 738213551, "Only if you want me to freak the fuck out and slip." },
            { 738213552, "Bear in mind that if you fight, it needs to be somewhere safe." },
            { 738213553, "Uhh, you don't think I have enough to think about already?" },
            { 738213554, "Not if you don't want to end up in a monster's belly, no." },
            { 738213555, "Climbing really takes it out of you, huh?" },
            { 738213556, "Which is why charging recklessly upward can be a recipe for disaster." },
            { 738213557, "Yeah, especially if someone's waiting for you at the bottom..." },
            { 738213558, "Not the most forgiving of routes..." },
            { 738213559, "Don't worry. I've got this." },
            { 738213560, "Glad to hear it. Let's hope your surplus of pride isn't followed by the proverbial fall." },
            { 738213561, "This seems like a good place to take a rest, don't you think?" },
            { 738213562, "Well, look who's starting to understand where humans can and can't sleep." },
            { 738213563, "Rather a...niche skill, I'd imagine. But thank you." },
            { 738213564, "I had hoped that we might get some shelter from the wind and rain." },
            { 738213565, "Yeah, this thing looks a little full of holes for that..." },
            { 738213566, "Shall we seek out another, perhaps?" },
            { 738213567, "What's the deal with this hut?" },
            { 738213568, "...Very little, as far as I can tell." },
            { 738213569, "Waste of fucking time..." },
            { 738213570, "...Nobody home. Not much of a surprise, I guess." },
            { 738213571, "If there were someone here, you'd need to be very wary of them indeed." },
            { 738213572, "Ugh, don't—this place is freaky enough as is." },
            { 738213573, "Rather in need of a spring clean, wouldn't you say?" },
            { 738213574, "Yeah. The last one must have been a good twenty springs ago." },
            { 738213575, "Well, no use in staying here any longer than we have to..." },
            { 738213576, "Anything good in he—whoa!" },
            { 738213577, "Get it out—quickly!" },
            { 738213578, "Way ahead of you. Geez, that made me jump..." },
            { 738213579, "A cluster of buildings..." },
            { 738213580, "Pff. Monster nests, more like." },
            { 738213582, "Nothing like a ghost town to make you feel right at home..." },
            { 738213583, "I'm sure the welcoming committee will be along soon enough." },
            { 738213584, "Yeah, not helping." },
            { 738213585, "An entire town, just left to rot..." },
            { 738213586, "Does a place still count as a town if nobody lives in it?" },
            { 738213587, "I'm not actually sure, you know." },
            { 738213588, "There's beauty in this desolation." },
            { 738213589, "There is? 'Cause all I see is a bunch of ruins." },
            { 738213590, "Well, I wasn't expecting much in the way of a response, but..." },
            { 738213591, "Kinda sad, thinking about all the people who used to live here..." },
            { 738213592, "The thought of what they might have left behind does rather cheer one up, though." },
            { 738213593, "True. Maybe we should take a look." },
            { 738213594, "Twenty years of weather does more damage than one would think." },
            { 738213595, "The Break must have played a part though, no?" },
            { 738213596, "Not if the walls of Cipal are anything to go by." },
            { 738213615, "Huh. Long way up..." },
            { 738213616, "Oh, stop moaning and climb. You never know what you might find." },
            { 738213617, "Alright, alright. Pain in the ass..." },
            { 738213618, "No one's gonna be reading the books here anytime soon..." },
            { 738213619, "All the more reason to take any promising specimens with you—the dead can't complain." },
            { 738213620, "Ugh. Now I just feel like leaving them where they are." },
            { 738213621, "What could they have been studying here, I wonder?" },
            { 738213622, "The Break wasn't around back then, right? So...magic or something?" },
            { 738213623, "I'd say that's probably as good a guess as any." },
            { 738213624, "Careful—the place could be crawling with undesirables." },
            { 738213625, "They really do get everywhere, huh?" },
            { 738213626, "Be on your guard..." },
            { 738213627, "It's too dark around here. I don't like it." },
            { 738213628, "Would you like me to hold your hand, little one?" },
            { 738213629, "I've made it pretty clear I'd like you to let the fuck go. So no." },
            { 738213630, "You never know what you might spot from the top..." },
            { 738213631, "Kinda like being up high, too." },
            { 738213632, "Yes. Very bracing." },
            { 738213633, "These old fortresses do tend to attract a lot of monstrous types, don't they?" },
            { 738213634, "Guess they used to attract a lot of people too." },
            { 738213635, "Yes, I suppose they did. Anyway, stay alert." },
            { 738213636, "Perhaps you should liberate a weapon or two." },
            { 738213637, "Yeah, I'm not exactly martial arts savvy." },
            { 738213638, "Hm. Probably best avoided, then. Don't want you chopping a leg off." },
            { 738213639, "Sila built these places, right?" },
            { 738213640, "Yes. Her approach when it came to fortifications was best summed up as \"more is more.\"" },
            { 738213641, "Well, I can't say I agree. With that or with pretty much anything else she did." },
            { 738213642, "How come they built all of these? Did they use to have a lot of wars?" },
            { 738213643, "That rather depends on your perspective. Does war ever truly end?" },
            { 738213644, "Uhh, I don't know, Professor Philosophy—does it?" },
            { 738213645, "I suppose it's not entirely surprising to find these fortresses full of former humans." },
            { 738213646, "What, they couldn't take a day off from guarding even when they got monsterfied?" },
            { 738213647, "\"Guarding?\" Rather a dignified term for it, wouldn't you say?" },
            { 738213648, "Wonder when they stopped using this place." },
            { 738213649, "I'd say they are still using it, wouldn't you?" },
            { 738213650, "I mean— Ah, screw you. You know exactly what I mean." },
            { 738213651, "Can this thing stop moving so much?" },
            { 738213652, "Possibly. If you can be a little lighter on your feet." },
            { 738213654, "This thing looks like it could fall apart any second..." },
            { 738213655, "Even if it does, what's the worst that can happen?" },
            { 738213656, "You're kidding, right?" },
            { 738213657, "You'd better hurry across before the wind picks up." },
            { 738213658, "I'm going, alright? Geez..." },
            { 738213659, "Just trying to be helpful..." },
            { 738213660, "What is it I like about this bridge?" },
            { 738213661, "I guess it's kinda pretty. In a...super basic kinda way." },
            { 738213662, "So there's an aesthete in you after all? I'm so relieved to hear it." },
            { 738213663, "Nothing like a nice, sturdy bridge." },
            { 738213664, "Not a sentiment often uttered..." },
            { 738213665, "When you've had to fight on enough shittily made ones, you learn to appreciate craftsmanship." },
            { 738213666, "A bridge atop which one could quite happily break a few heads, no?" },
            { 738213667, "What makes you think we'd need to?" },
            { 738213668, "Well, based on experience, it seems safest to assume we might." },
            { 738213669, "I'm starting to see why walls are so important." },
            { 738213670, "You know, it's such a privilege to witness your intellectual blossoming firsthand." },
            { 738213671, "Hey, I'd be happier in a world where I didn't have to think about this stuff at all." },
            { 738213672, "The roof isn't gonna fall in or anything, right?" },
            { 738213673, "Who knows? Ahh, the suspense is killing me!" },
            { 738213674, "You do realize you'd be screwed, too, right?" },
            { 738213675, "Place is falling to pieces. But it's better than nothing, I guess." },
            { 738213676, "Better than literally nothing, yes..." },
            { 738213677, "Ever the optimist." },
            { 738213678, "Why do they smash up the buildings?" },
            { 738213679, "I don't think it's deliberate. They're...casualties of monstrous excess, let's say." },
            { 738213680, "Like when shit gets destroyed in superhero movies? Cool..." },
            { 738213681, "If anything jumps out at you, strike first and ask questions later." },
            { 738213682, "And what if that \"anything\" happens to be an actual person?" },
            { 738213683, "Highly unlikely, I'm afraid." },
            { 738213684, "Man. The right picture of this place would probably break the Internet." },
            { 738213685, "Umm..." },
            { 738213686, "Let's just say I'm seeing some genuinely mind-blowing shit out here." },
            { 738213687, "I sense the power of a Tanta somewhere nearby..." },
            { 738213688, "Fuck! Where!?" },
            { 738213689, "Not an actual Tanta, you understand. This is something different..." },
            { 738213690, "What do you think these were built for?" },
            { 738213691, "I've no idea. Who am I to ponder what drives the mighty to their strange excesses?" },
            { 738213692, "You could at least try. Not like you've got anything better to do." },
            { 738213693, "You think they built these before the Break spread?" },
            { 738213694, "Erecting them while the people were suffering would have been rather...insensitive." },
            { 738213695, "Not if there was a good reason for doing it..." },
            { 738213696, "What're we gonna find here, I wonder?" },
            { 738213697, "A curse, perhaps? A new and even deadlier affliction?" },
            { 738213698, "So you agree we're gonna find something?" },
            { 738213699, "I kinda hate that we've had to lean on the Tantas' powers so much, don't you?" },
            { 738213700, "I understand your feelings on the matter, but beggars really can't be choosers." },
            { 738213701, "Guess not." },
            { 738213702, "Is that one of those Tanta stone thingies?" },
            { 738213703, "Why not take a closer look?" },
            { 738213704, "Guess I'll only forget if I don't check it out now..." },
            { 738213705, "Seems the Break hasn't taken hold too thoroughly here yet." },
            { 738213706, "This is more than enough, thanks." },
            { 738213708, "Break..." },
            { 738213709, "Not enough to be a problem, at least." },
            { 738213710, "Not for you, anyway." },
            { 738213711, "This amount of broken-ness doesn't feel so bad." },
            { 738213712, "Not for you, maybe. Normal human beings, on the other hand..." },
            { 738213713, "Hey! I am a normal human being, thank you very much!" },
            { 738213714, "Hmm. Seems we've entered the Break." },
            { 738213715, "Really? I didn't even notice." },
            { 738213716, "It's not too heavy just yet, but things change quickly in here. Careful." },
            { 738213717, "Is that a little Break I'm feeling?" },
            { 738213718, "It would seem so. Not enough to have much of an effect for now, though." },
            { 738213719, "I'll keep an eye on it." },
            { 738213723, "What IS Break, though?" },
            { 738213724, "Dangerous, that's what." },
            { 738213725, "Thanks. That much I knew already." },
            { 738213726, "How come the Break does nothing to me?" },
            { 738213727, "Or me?" },
            { 738213728, "...You're a bracelet, idiot." },
            { 738213729, "Is the Break getting worse?" },
            { 738213730, "Possibly. Watch where you're going." },
            { 738213731, "Yeah, yeah." },
            { 738213732, "The Break's getting thicker. Hold tight to anything important." },
            { 738213733, "What, like my hopes and dreams?" },
            { 738213734, "You still have those? Goodness..." },
            { 738213735, "This shit may not affect me, but I still can't see a damn thing." },
            { 738213736, "I have just the thing for that." },
            { 738213737, "You do? Oh, yeah... You do!" },
            { 738213738, "Wonder if breathing this shit in is bad for me." },
            { 738213739, "It probably won't do you much harm. But it might not taste too nice." },
            { 738213740, "Kinda... Nah, I'm kidding. Tastes of nothing, actually." },
            { 738213741, "Wow. This is some real fantasy novel shit right here." },
            { 738213742, "As ever, no idea..." },
            { 738213743, "Come to think of it, YOU'RE some real fantasy novel shit." },
            { 738213744, "When the Break's this thick, I start feeling like I'm going a little crazy." },
            { 738213745, "Goodness. Are you alright?" },
            { 738213746, "Are you being nice to me? Okay, maybe I am losing my mind..." },
            { 738213747, "Breathtaking, really, isn't it?" },
            { 738213748, "This weird shit? You got some strange tastes, my friend." },
            { 738213749, "Hmph. As if you have the first clue about taste..." },
            { 738213750, "The Break's getting really quite bad." },
            { 738213751, "Yeah. Kinda...gateway to hell vibes." },
            { 738213752, "Ooh, very evocative. For once, I wholeheartedly agree." },
            { 738213753, "Whoa... I think I might be losing my mind a little bit..." },
            { 738213754, "Things do get rather surreal this deep inside the Break." },
            { 738213755, "You can say that again." },
            { 738213756, "This weird shit's all because of the Break, isn't it?" },
            { 738213757, "I would imagine so, yes." },
            { 738213758, "Damn. What the fuck is the Break, anyway...?" },
            { 738213759, "Okay, well, this is well and truly fucked." },
            { 738213760, "Yes, I'd say that's a reasonable assessment." },
            { 738213762, "Quickly! Look for somewhere to wait out the storm!" },
            { 738213763, "On it!" },
            { 738213765, "We need to get the fuck out of here." },
            { 738213766, "We most certainly do. I doubt this is one we can fight our way out of." },
            { 738213767, "Need to find someplace safe..." },
            { 738213768, "Keep moving and try not to draw attention to yourself." },
            { 738213769, "Oh, don't worry. I'm not getting mixed up in whatever the fuck this is." },
            { 738213770, "Just remember, if you are spotted—run!" },
            { 738213771, "Holy shit! How many of them are there!?" },
            { 738213772, "Find somewhere to hide. Right now." },
            { 738213773, "Don't need to tell me twice!" },
            { 738213774, "This is like some kind of fucked-up fever dream." },
            { 738213775, "It...what?" },
            { 738213776, "It's messed up. That's all you need to know." },
            { 738213777, "Okay, you don't...not have a point. But shut the fuck up." },
            { 738213778, "Not much point in making money you can't spend." },
            { 738213779, "I'm sure your fellow young persons would be intrigued to hear that." },
            { 738213780, "There's a sort of surface presentability to these people, but they're all a little scruffy round the edges." },
            { 738213781, "Who thinks about fashion at a time like this?" },
            { 738213782, "Those who want to escape reality, I'd imagine." },
            { 738213783, "Still can't walk around up here without feeling on edge." },
            { 738213784, "You did rather give them the runaround." },
            { 738213785, "They did rather throw me in jail for no reason." },
            { 738213786, "So they grow stuff in the upper city too." },
            { 738213787, "Supplementing their rations with home-grown produce. Not a bad idea." },
            { 738213788, "Eating like kings while others starve? Wow. Guess rich people are the same everywhere..." },
            { 738213789, "Buildings around here look a little shabby. Maybe we could help fix things up." },
            { 738213790, "I'd imagine it's more a lack of materials than a lack of will. Wood, in particular." },
            { 738213791, "Yeah, guess it must be hard finding more if you can't leave the city." },
            { 738213792, "Some people could really do with making themselves more useful, don't you think?" },
            { 738213793, "Are you trying to make some kind of a point?" },
            { 738213795, "Ugh! Why can't people watch where they're going?" },
            { 738213796, "It is a little crowded. Well, keep your wits about you." },
            { 738213798, "What do you think you might grow if you had a plot of your own?" },
            { 738213799, "I don't know. Fruit, maybe? You know, you can just eat it right off the plant." },
            { 738213800, "Instant gratification, eh? Why am I not surprised." },
            { 738213801, "If you were gonna grow something here, what would it be?" },
            { 738213802, "Flowers, I think. A little nourishment for the soul." },
            { 738213803, "Wow. Okay. That was...not what I was expecting to hear." },
            { 738213804, "The ballow tree is something of a symbol of the city." },
            { 738213805, "Like the Statue of Liberty?" },
            { 738213806, "...Probably." },
            { 738213807, "What do these animals eat?" },
            { 738213808, "Grass, I'd imagine." },
            { 738213809, "That's it? And they don't just die of...deficiencies? Wow, kudos." },
            { 738213810, "What's that look? You're not about to tell me you know what these creatures are thinking, are you?" },
            { 738213811, "Nah, just...they must be so desperate to see the outside world too. Poor things." },
            { 738213812, "They'll see it soon enough. Once the Tantas are gone." },
            { 738213813, "I'd never seen farm animals up close before I came here." },
            { 738213814, "Well, get a good look while you can. You'll be eating them for dinner soon enough." },
            { 738213815, "Spoken like a true asshole." },
            { 738213816, "To be honest, it's something of a miracle they even have the one." },
            { 738213817, "Is it me, or are we going in circles?" },
            { 738213818, "Shut up." },
            { 738213819, "Not just me, then? Glad we cleared that up." },
            { 738213820, "Ever get the feeling you're forgetting something?" },
            { 738213821, "What, exactly? Some sort of errand, perhaps? A favor for someone? ...A birthday?" },
            { 738213822, "I'll never be able to remember if you don't shut the fuck up!" },
            { 738213823, "I think I'd like a surname. Something dignified." },
            { 738213824, "Yeah, something with a ring to it. Like, uh...Mister Fuckingunbelievableannoyance." },
            { 738213825, "Charmed, I'm sure, Miss Woefullypredictable." },
            { 738213826, "I don't see any stores." },
            { 738213827, "They used to have them, but they're a little pointless these days." },
            { 738213828, "Do I like the idea of a world where money is meaningless? Still haven't decided..." },
            { 738213829, "Time to steal another apple, perhaps?" },
            { 738213830, "Look, I don't make a habit of taking people's shit, okay?" },
            { 738213831, "Alright, alright. I just thought you might be hungry." },
            { 738213832, "Oh, believe me, I'll be stopping the first chance I get!" },
            { 738213833, "Wonder if this stuff could cure your attitude, Cuff." },
            { 738213834, "Doesn't seem to have done much for yours..." },
            { 738213835, "Woohoo, that hits the spot." },
            { 738213836, "Quite fancy a little taste myself..." },
            { 738213837, "Something's there. What shall we do?" },
            { 738213838, "Ugh, could pretend we didn't notice..." },
            { 738213839, "They can't see me, they can't see me..." },
            { 738213840, "Indulge your little fantasy if you like. Just don't get yourself killed." },
            { 738213841, "You really don't know me." },
            { 738213842, "I almost miss the commotion when there's no one around, don't you?" },
            { 738213843, "Believe me, you're plenty of commotion all by yourself." },
            { 738213844, "There's no one around. Did you do something to annoy them all?" },
            { 738213845, "What didn't I do..." },
            { 738213846, "Run, Frey! Run like something's trying to kill you!" },
            { 738213847, "I don't need your encouragement, thanks." },
            { 738213848, "I wanna go higher." },
            { 738213849, "All you have to do is try." },
            { 738213850, "Ohmygodthatwasinsane!" },
            { 738213851, "Just try not to fall..." },
            { 738213852, "That's not even half of what I can do." },
            { 738213853, "Then I shall look forward to seeing what happens when you actually apply yourself." },
            { 738213854, "You're starting to cover some impressive distances." },
            { 738213855, "I am pretty amazing, huh?" },
            { 738213856, "Oh, I can do better than that!" },
            { 738213857, "Practice makes perfect." },
            { 738213858, "Hahaaa! This shit is so addictive!" },
            { 738213859, "Judging by how excitable it makes you, I'd be inclined to agree." },
            { 738213860, "Okay, spun a little bit too much there." },
            { 738213861, "Vomit on me, and suffer." },
            { 738213862, "You're nearly out." },
            { 738213863, "Ugh. What a pain..." },
            { 738213864, "We got a couple more still?" },
            { 738213865, "Yes, but only a couple." },
            { 738213866, "Frey, you're—" },
            { 738213867, "Running low. Yeah, yeah." },
            { 738213876, "Ha ha! See ya later!" },
            { 738213877, "I'm not sure it's very sporting to laugh..." },
            { 738213878, "Well that was a piece of cake." },
            { 738213879, "Yes, almost disappointing..." },
            { 738213880, "Not sure you needed my help there, really..." },
            { 738213881, "Probably not." },
            { 738213882, "Everything alright?" },
            { 738213883, "Hell yeah! We just kicked some ass!" },
            { 738213884, "That went pretty well!" },
            { 738213885, "Things usually do when I'm involved." },
            { 738213886, "Excellent form!" },
            { 738213887, "Gotta bring my A game!" },
            { 738213888, "Beautifully executed, Frey!" },
            { 738213889, "You weren't so bad yourself." },
            { 738213890, "We don't make such a bad team, you and me." },
            { 738213891, "Unexpected, but...thanks." },
            { 738213892, "Shit, Cuff! We did it!" },
            { 738213893, "We did indeed!" },
            { 738213894, "Not bad, I guess." },
            { 738213895, "Yes. Ought to come in handy." },
            { 738213896, "Better than nothing, I suppose." },
            { 738213897, "I'll be the judge of that." },
            { 738213898, "A fitting reward for my efforts." },
            { 738213899, "Your efforts? At what? Being a sarcastic pain in the ass?" },
            { 738213900, "Ooh..." },
            { 738213901, "That certainly makes it all worthwhile." },
            { 738213902, "Damn, Cuff! Check this out!" },
            { 738213903, "I might even be inclined to describe that as \"awesome,\" you know." },
            { 738213904, "Finds like this make all the running around worthwhile." },
            { 738213905, "Hell yeah, they do!" },
            { 738213906, "Wait, wait. I'm still reading..." },
            { 738213907, "Must you do this now?" },
            { 738213956, "Alright. Let's just go for it." },
            { 738213957, "Best not to overthink these things, eh?" },
            { 738213958, "Ha ha! I am literally the best." },
            { 738213959, "Yes. Not bad." },
            { 738213960, "I should make an effort more often." },
            { 738213961, "Well, that went better than expected." },
            { 738213962, "Better than you expected, maybe." },
            { 738213963, "Yes, yes. Very well done." },
            { 738213964, "Well? Aren't you gonna say something?" },
            { 738213965, "Woohoo! Amazing! You're the best, Frey! ...Can I please stop now?" },
            { 738213966, "Very funny." },
            { 738213967, "Hmm. A solid \"just about okay.\"" },
            { 738213968, "Sadly, not quite good enough to earn one of my much-sought-after compliments." },
            { 738213969, "\"Sought-after\"? Not by me..." },
            { 738213970, "So that's about your level, is it?" },
            { 738213971, "No. That's about our level." },
            { 738213972, "I suppose they do say that a bad workman always blames his tools..." },
            { 738213973, "Hmm." },
            { 738213974, "Just about scraped through, I'd say." },
            { 738213975, "I didn't ask for your opinion." },
            { 738213976, "Anything you want to say about that little performance?" },
            { 738213977, "Oy, where do I start?" },
            { 738213978, "Well, there's always next time." },
            { 738213979, "Ugh..." },
            { 738213980, "Something on your mind?" },
            { 738213981, "Yeah, the fact that I should have done way better than that." },
            { 738213982, "Not the most inspirational performance." },
            { 738213983, "That's putting it mildly." },
            { 738213984, "Another try, perhaps?" },
            { 738213985, "What can I say? I have high standards." },
            { 738213986, "I'm impressed." },
            { 738213987, "Had a feeling that was gonna go my way." },
            { 738213988, "Here's to many more like it." },
            { 738213989, "G'bye, bed. Love you." },
            { 738213990, "You could take the covers with you as a souvenir." },
            { 738213991, "Blanket cloak? Oh yeah, I like that..." },
            { 738213992, "I changed my mind. I want to rest some more." },
            { 738213993, "We're up now. Come on, let's shake a leg." },
            { 738213994, "You wouldn't be saying that if you knew how comfy that bed was." },
            { 738213995, "Phew. Let's stop here for a while." },
            { 738213996, "Alright, but stay alert." },
            { 738213997, "Not quite blazing yet, is it?" },
            { 738213998, "Better throw another branch on." },
            { 738213999, "Shoulda brought a book..." },
            { 738214000, "Haven't you got some?" },
            { 738214001, "I mean a book written in a language that doesn't give me a headache to read." },
            { 738214002, "I'm feeling rather chilly." },
            { 738214003, "Damn, you're freezing." },
            { 738214004, "Ugh! Get your grubby little fingers off me!" },
            { 738214005, "Could use a bath..." },
            { 738214006, "A little dip wouldn't hurt, I'm sure." },
            { 738214007, "If you think I'm getting my clothes wet, you must be crazy." },
            { 738214008, "You're becoming quite the firestarter." },
            { 738214009, "Fat lot of good that'll do me back in New York." },
            { 738214011, "I pulled off some pretty sweet moves today, huh?" },
            { 738214012, "Yes. It was like...watching a baby bird stretch its scrawny little wings." },
            { 738214013, "If that was a compliment, it was a fucking weird one." },
            { 738214020, "At last, some entertainment." },
            { 738214021, "Oh! You got a little bored while I was resting up?" },
            { 738214022, "Alright, guess we better do this..." },
            { 738214023, "What's the matter? I thought a rest would have done you good." },
            { 738214024, "I really am flattered, but I'm afraid I'm strictly a one-wrist vambrace." },
            { 738214025, "Believe me. If I could give him away, I would." },
            { 738214026, "Isn't it nice being popular?" },
            { 738214027, "Be nicer if it didn't mean getting hit in the face all the time." },
            { 738214028, "Ow! Someone oughta teach you some manners!" },
            { 738214029, "Don't let's get carried away." },
            { 738214030, "Do you two have an old score to settle or something?" },
            { 738214031, "It's...possible." },
            { 738214038, "There's no rule that says you have to kick everyone's ass, is there?" },
            { 738214039, "I'm no expert, but...probably not." },
            { 738214040, "I think we've lost them." },
            { 738214041, "Yeah. Let's hope they stay lost." },
            { 738214042, "You really are good at running away from things, aren't you?" },
            { 738214043, "What can I say? I've had a lot of practice." },
            { 738214044, "Was that the right thing to do?" },
            { 738214045, "Guess we'll find out soon enough." },
            { 738214046, "Yes. Very shrewd of you." },
            { 738214047, "Just didn't feel like fighting." },
            { 738214048, "See ya!" },
            { 738214049, "I sincerely hope we don't." },
            { 738214050, "Good luck predicting the weather in this place." },
            { 738214051, "I expect that's what makes the scenery so varied." },
            { 738214052, "Hmm. Yeah, I guess that's sort of a good thing." },
            { 738214053, "Ahhh, so many memories..." },
            { 738214054, "Yeah, none of them good." },
            { 738214055, "Charming." },
            { 738214056, "Why do I always feel like I've known this place since way back?" },
            { 738214057, "I expect it's all the happy memories." },
            { 738214058, "Hah! Definitely not." },
            { 738214059, "Why do I always feel weird when I leave this place?" },
            { 738214060, "\"Weird\" how, exactly?" },
            { 738214061, "I kinda...I dunno. Ah, forget it." },
            { 738214062, "You can pick up the pace if you like." },
            { 738214063, "Huh? What's your deal?" },
            { 738214064, "Let's just say the fewer enormous dragons I have to meet, the happier I tend to remain." },
            { 738214065, "Strange, huh? Thinking about how it all started in Junoon." },
            { 738214066, "Yes. It really did..." },
            { 738214067, "It's been one hell of a ride." },
            { 738214068, "Let me guess. You wanna go see what's at the top." },
            { 738214069, "Well, towers are built to be climbed..." },
            { 738214071, "That's a tall one." },
            { 738214072, "Shall we? I'm sure there'll be treasure of some kind inside." },
            { 738214073, "Yeah, and bad guys too. You reeeally wanna do this?" },
            { 738214074, "Oh, look! A tower!" },
            { 738214075, "You see pretty well for a lump of metal." },
            { 738214076, "When I need to, yes." },
            { 738214077, "The moment she set foot in the ruin, up went the most awful noise—" },
            { 738214078, "Stop it." },
            { 738214079, "Why do I bother?" },
            { 738214080, "There's nothing here. Well, nothing left, at least." },
            { 738214081, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738214082, "I'd save your sympathy. There are far too many of these places to mope about every last one." },
            { 738214083, "Wonder what happened here..." },
            { 738214084, "I hesitate to even hazard a guess." },
            { 738214085, "Just think, people used to live here... Fuck." },
            { 738214086, "Whew! I was worried you might try being a \"badass\" by jumping off the top." },
            { 738214087, "No, I'm a badass, not an idiot." },
            { 738214088, "That's...encouraging, I suppose." },
            { 738214089, "Getting down from there was a real bitch." },
            { 738214090, "Worse than it was going up?" },
            { 738214091, "Oh yeah. Way worse." },
            { 738214092, "Phew! All those stairs! Exhausting!" },
            { 738214093, "Right. Musta been a real back-breaker for you..." },
            { 738214094, "Oh, stop it. I'm being sympathetic." },
            { 738214095, "There's a ton of these ruins with no roofs, huh?" },
            { 738214096, "Something must have hit the buildings hard." },
            { 738214097, "You can say that again. Hard to imagine what could do that..." },
            { 738214098, "Forgetting something?" },
            { 738214099, "No! Wait, am I?" },
            { 738214100, "Wouldn't want to leave any goodies behind..." },
            { 738214101, "Escaped in one piece. Thank goodness for that." },
            { 738214102, "Yeah. Doubt that thing'll still be standing next time we're here." },
            { 738214103, "Well, do feel free to stop and say a last goodbye." },
            { 738214104, "Fuck, I feel awful." },
            { 738214105, "I'd say you need some sort of medicine..." },
            { 738214106, "I'm going to hazard a guess that you're feeling somewhat peaky." },
            { 738214107, "If that means \"like shit,\" then yeah, I'm feeling peaky." },
            { 738214108, "Tell me...this isn't happening..." },
            { 738214109, "No... No!" },
            { 738214110, "Sorry, Cuff... I'm done..." },
            { 738214111, "Well, I would say I'll miss you, but..." },
            { 738214112, "Might be an idea to fall back a little..." },
            { 738214113, "Oh, might it?" },
            { 738214114, "Next one's gonna hurt." },
            { 738214115, "I hope that's all it does..." },
            { 738214116, "This is really, really bad, right?" },
            { 738214117, "If you know that, then why aren't you doing something?" },
            { 738214118, "Do you think urgent action might be an idea?" },
            { 738214119, "Shut up! Gotta find the right moment..." },
            { 738214122, "Oh yeah." },
            { 738214123, "Very nicely done." },
            { 738214124, "I commend you on your catlike grace." },
            { 738214125, "Yeah, it's kind of a thing of mine." },
            { 738214126, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738214127, "You can clap if you like. Oh, wait...." },
            { 738214128, "You're just going to walk off like that, are you?" },
            { 738214129, "Do I look like I got a change of clothes?" },
            { 738214130, "At least the water was clean." },
            { 738214131, "Ugh, you'll be drinking it next..." },
            { 738214132, "You'll soon dry off in this weather." },
            { 738214133, "Guess I will, huh?" },
            { 738214134, "Do you feel that, Frey?" },
            { 738214135, "Yeah. We need to make camp. And fast." },
            { 738214136, "Agreed. The less exposed we are, the better." },
            { 738214137, "What is that...?" },
            { 738214138, "I sense it too." },
            { 738214139, "Shit. Wish you didn't." },
            { 738214140, "Something extremely powerful is approaching." },
            { 738214141, "Let's try not to be here when it arrives..." },
            { 738214142, "It may be too late for that." },
            { 738214143, "This is not a feeling I'll be getting used to anytime soon!" },
            { 738214144, "A sentiment I'm sure very few would dispute." },
            { 738214145, "Ugh! My head..." },
            { 738214146, "We're caught up in this now. Frey, I want you to focus on self-preservation." },
            { 738214147, "You worried about me?" },
            { 738214148, "Your sudden and violent death would be rather an inconvenience, yes." },
            { 738214149, "Fuck. Talk about bad timing." },
            { 738214150, "Is there ever a good time for this? Just try not to die, alright?" },
            { 738214151, "Trust me, not on my to-do list." },
            { 738214152, "We're still alive. Wonderful." },
            { 738214153, "Might not be so lucky next time." },
            { 738214154, "I would strongly advise trying to avoid a next time." },
            { 738214155, "Never thought I'd be so glad just to be able to breathe." },
            { 738214156, "I wholeheartedly concur." },
            { 738214157, "Wait, what? You can't breathe. ...Can you?" },
            { 738214158, "Safe at last." },
            { 738214159, "I was not ready for that. Holy fuck, I'm beat." },
            { 738214160, "A rest certainly wouldn't be a bad idea." },
            { 738214251, "One, two, three, four..." },
            { 738214252, "You're counting them why?" },
            { 738214253, "Well? Whaddya think?" },
            { 738214254, "I think you've defeated several enemies." },
            { 738214255, "How are you bearing up?" },
            { 738214256, "How do I look like I'm \"bearing up\"?" },
            { 738214257, "Ahh, come on! This is too many!" },
            { 738214258, "Less talking, more fighting." },
            { 738214259, "This is getting ridiculous." },
            { 738214260, "Come on. It's...character-building." },
            { 738214261, "Okay, enough!" },
            { 738214262, "For you, perhaps. They seem more than happy to continue." },
            { 738214263, "More!? How is this fair?" },
            { 738214264, "I'm not sure they're having a great time either." },
            { 738214265, "Should we just run?" },
            { 738214266, "Don't be silly. You can do it!" },
            { 738214267, "Please let this be over soon!" },
            { 738214268, "You're not having fun, are you?" },
            { 738214277, "That was really quite something!" },
            { 738214278, "Pah. Just getting warmed up." },
            { 738214309, "I've been looking over some of my father's research. Sadly, it's all from a very long time ago." },
            { 738214310, "If you could only bring back his journals from the Cognoscent's Guild..." },
            { 738214311, "I'm sure they'll help us find a way to save Athia. You'll fetch them, won't you?" },
            { 738214312, "You like cats, don't you, Frey?" },
            { 738214313, "Me too!" },
            { 738214315, "Why do the children refuse to listen?" },
            { 738214316, "I will teach them of our history if it's the last thing I do!" },
            { 738214321, "Quick drink before you go?" },
            { 738214322, "Ask about the Cognoscents' Guild." },
            { 738214323, "Ask about Auden." },
            { 738214324, "Ask for the finest drink in the house." },
            { 738214325, "Nothing." },
            { 738214326, "The Cognoscents used to study things we mere mortals couldn't hope to understand." },
            { 738214327, "Old Treahy used to say that one of their books was worth more than a hundred loaves of bread." },
            { 738214328, "That's all I get from the guy who knows \"everything\"?" },
            { 738214329, "I told you—it's town I know about." },
            { 738214330, "And that place wasn't inside the city walls last time I checked." },
            { 738214331, "Come on, it was better than nothing. Poor chap..." },
            { 738214332, "Auden's a bit earnest, but she's got her head screwed on. And you won't find a kinder soul in Cipal." },
            { 738214333, "Granted, there are those who think she sometimes sticks her nose in where it doesn't belong." },
            { 738214334, "You can add me to that list, that's for certain." },
            { 738214335, "But her dad, Robian... He was well-respected enough that everybody knows her heart must be in the right place." },
            { 738214336, "Used to be a very good customer of mine, that one..." },
            { 738214337, "Don't you think you've had enough for one lifetime?" },
            { 738214338, "Now that's what I'm talking about! Some complex flavors going on here..." },
            { 738214339, "Hmm. Connoisseur, are we?" },
            { 738214340, "Alright, c'mon. Don't hold out on me—what's the secret ingredient?" },
            { 738214341, "Hey, I can't tell you that! It's more than my job's worth!" },
            { 738214342, "Suit yourself." },
            { 738214343, "Auden's putting a lot of faith in you, you know." },
            { 738214344, "I didn't ask her to." },
            { 738214345, "Oh, charming. Well, be seeing you again soon." },
            { 738214346, "This here's the only pub in town, after all." },
            { 738214354, "Bumped into Olevia, did you?" },
            { 738214355, "That girl..." },
            { 738214356, "She's sweet enough underneath it all though, trust me." },
            { 738214357, "The guards are busy searching for an escaped prisoner." },
            { 738214358, "Seems they've been pretty busy all around since you showed your face in town." },
            { 738214359, "Wouldn't surprise me if they weren't a little grateful to have something to do for once!" },
            { 738214360, "You can use that room whenever you like." },
            { 738214361, "Just don't go breaking anything." },
            { 738214362, "We've barely got enough materials to keep Cipal from falling apart, never mind fixing your mess." },
            { 738214363, "Come again, eh?" },
            { 738214364, "Fair maiden! A moment, if you please?" },
            { 738214365, "Stay and listen." },
            { 738214366, "Leave." },
            { 738214367, "Very well. Then allow me to regale you with \"The Ballad of the Enormously Clever Person of Cipal\"!" },
            { 738214368, "Is that really the best title he could come up with?" },
            { 738214369, "Well? Did it speak to your soul?" },
            { 738214370, "Did the doleful melody conjure images of the encroaching miasma? The unearthly cries of its foul denizens?" },
            { 738214371, "The unlucky inhabitants of this fair city—myself among them—cursed never again to venture beyond its walls?" },
            { 738214372, "\"Again\"? Have you ever been out there?" },
            { 738214373, "But of course! What manner of minstrel would I be did I not go a-wandering o'er hill and dale?" },
            { 738214374, "In...my dreams, of course." },
            { 738214375, "A great shame indeed." },
            { 738214376, "You! Bard!" },
            { 738214377, "Escaped criminals roam the streets, and still you do not cease your racket! There is a crisis afoot!" },
            { 738214378, "Forgive me, but there is always a crisis afoot." },
            { 738214379, "Well, you may have a point there, but nonetheless—" },
            { 738214380, "She's a guard, Frey. We need to get out of here. Now." },
            { 738214381, "I, uh...guess I'll be on my way, then." },
            { 738214382, "Wait! You! You're—" },
            { 738214383, "So sorry to see you go, fair maiden, but go you must! And quickly." },
            { 738214384, "That was a little too close for comfort." },
            { 738214385, "But we got away, thanks to the fop." },
            { 738214386, "Dream-wanderings, indeed..." },
            { 738214387, "Yeah, and that song. What the hell even was that?" },
            { 738214388, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738214389, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738214390, "Sorry about this one. He's not the bravest." },
            { 738214391, "It's not often we see an unfamiliar face. Where did you spring from?" },
            { 738214431, "You like that place, don't you?" },
            { 738214432, "Do I? I guess the vibe in there is...acceptable." },
            { 738214433, "Oh, to be young and a familiar face at the local drinking hole!" },
            { 738214434, "Yeah. Sucks being you." },
            { 738214534, "I still can't quite believe my father is alive." },
            { 738214535, "You've given me back something I never thought I'd have again." },
            { 738214536, "I can't thank you enough." },
            { 738214537, "I still haven't thanked you properly, have I?" },
            { 738214538, "No need. We had a deal." },
            { 738214539, "Yes, the journals for my father's notes on the torana." },
            { 738214540, "The thing is...you've brought me so much more than a few journals. Truly, Frey!" },
            { 738214541, "Surely there must be something I can do? Come on—anything." },
            { 738214542, "Uh, okay... You could...make me something?" },
            { 738214543, "Can't remember the last time I had a home-cooked meal." },
            { 738214544, "Oh! Umm..." },
            { 738214545, "What?" },
            { 738214546, "Oh, n-nothing. A promise is a promise. Now, let's see..." },
            { 738214547, "You could have said something, you know..." },
            { 738214548, "Kinda surprised, though. You always struck me as Little Miss Perfect." },
            { 738214549, "Sadly not...as you can see." },
            { 738214550, "Yeah. I can see." },
            { 738214551, "Everything on the table is burned to a crisp..." },
            { 738214552, "Well, you went to all the trouble. Here goes nothing..." },
            { 738214553, "I...don't think I can eat that..." },
            { 738214554, "Looks delicious! Chow time!" },
            { 738214555, "It's...pretty much what I expected." },
            { 738214556, "There's no need to force yourself, really." },
            { 738214557, "Hey, like I said, this is the first time anyone's cooked for me in a while." },
            { 738214558, "Yep." },
            { 738214559, "You're right... Don't worry, I'll have it." },
            { 738214560, "Uh... You will?" },
            { 738214561, "Yes, I...I think perhaps I'll boil it in sheep's milk. That should help." },
            { 738214562, "And you wonder how you wound up with this mess in the first place." },
            { 738214563, "What?" },
            { 738214564, "The crispier the better, if you ask me! Brings out all the flavor!" },
            { 738214565, "Oh, yeah. Mmm." },
            { 738214566, "Th-thank you, Frey. You're too kind, really." },
            { 738214567, "Sorry again..." },
            { 738214568, "Hey, I'm the one who asked you to cook." },
            { 738214569, "And besides...I had fun." },
            { 738214570, "Me too." },
            { 738214572, "How about we just make it a drink next time?" },
            { 738214573, "I'd like that, yes." },
            { 738214574, "Well, I must say you're braver than me." },
            { 738214575, "I would have given it to the poor girl straight." },
            { 738214576, "\"I wouldn't feed this disaster to my worst enemy!\" Something along those lines." },
            { 738214577, "Believe me, I was close..." },
            { 738214677, "Oh, I meant to say—that was good, what you did for Robian." },
            { 738214678, "Haven't seen Auden that happy in a long time." },
            { 738214679, "You two friends?" },
            { 738214680, "She tells me things. She's been coming here ever since she could read." },
            { 738214681, "She told me all about you." },
            { 738214682, "So, which is it? Do you want to go home, or do you want to be a hero?" },
            { 738214683, "I want to go home. The sooner the better." },
            { 738214684, "I want Sila to pay." },
            { 738214685, "None of your business." },
            { 738214701, "The one who used her amazing powers to drive back the monsters!" },
            { 738214702, "Can't believe I'm talking to the hero who saved the city!" },
            { 738214703, "Decided to take me up on my offer?" },
            { 738214704, "Ask Pilo to show you around." },
            { 738214705, "Decline." },
            { 738214706, "Okay, bet. Gimme the tour." },
            { 738214707, "Great! This is great!" },
            { 738214708, "Alright. We'll start at the square in the lower city. This way!" },
            { 738214709, "Maybe some other time." },
            { 738214710, "I'll be waiting! Just let me know when you're ready!" },
            { 738214711, "Come on, follow me!" },
            { 738214717, "It's downright frightening, it is! Fancy letting someone like that roam the streets unsupervised!" },
            { 738214719, "Hey mummy, mummy! That's the lady—" },
            { 738214720, "Shush, you! And you don't go near her, you hear?" },
            { 738214721, "Hey, that's no way to—" },
            { 738214722, "It's cool. I'm used to it." },
            { 738214723, "Shame. I was rather hoping to see that fiery temper of yours in action." },
            { 738214724, "Petty, small-minded gossips! Although, I suppose it is pretty frightening..." },
            { 738214725, "With your power, you could turn the whole town on its head just like that!" },
            { 738214726, "Yeah... You're something else, alright." },
            { 738214727, "Not this shit again... I'm nobody! Get over it already!" },
            { 738214728, "Shall we?" },
            { 738214731, "Over here's where we keep all the livestock." },
            { 738214732, "We don't get to eat meat very often, but...we do alright, I suppose." },
            { 738214733, "Hey! You can't create food out of thin air, can you? Um...never mind." },
            { 738214734, "The big, open area is the graveyard. Rich or poor, we all end up there in the end." },
            { 738214736, "A farm in a cemetery. You don't see that often." },
            { 738214737, "Really? It's quite a good arrangement. The animals help keep the grass down." },
            { 738214740, "They're not shy, that's for sure." },
            { 738214741, "Well, we don't get many new faces in town." },
            { 738214742, "Hey, why don't you try feeding them?" },
            { 738214743, "Really? Is that...allowed?" },
            { 738214744, "Of course! Wait here, I'll go and grab some food." },
            { 738214748, "There you are, Frey! I was starting to worry!" },
            { 738214755, "Try not to get lost, won't you?" },
            { 738214759, "This is the mausoleum." },
            { 738214760, "Our souls come here when we die." },
            { 738214761, "What are you doing here? And you! You belong in the lower city!" },
            { 738214762, "Yes! You have no right to be here, neither of you! Begone!" },
            { 738214763, "Ugh, of all the people to run into..." },
            { 738214764, "Frey saved the city! If anyone deserves to be here, it's her!" },
            { 738214765, "If she wanted, she could turn you to ashes in a heartbeat! But she'd never do that! Isn't that right, Frey!" },
            { 738214766, "Okay, can you fucking let it go, already?" },
            { 738214767, "Wha..." },
            { 738214768, "What's wrong with you all of a sudden?" },
            { 738214769, "If you wanna save your city, do it your fucking self!" },
            { 738214770, "You're not dragging me into this!" },
            { 738214771, "The lower city is where all the refugees live. And the square here is its heart." },
            { 738214772, "Are you a refugee?" },
            { 738214773, "Please, Frey! Wait!" },
            { 738214774, "Listen, okay? I never said I'd help you. With anything. Ever. Got that?" },
            { 738214775, "I-I'm sorry, I just... I got carried away, I suppose..." },
            { 738214776, "Look, let me take you to one last place." },
            { 738214777, "Fuck no." },
            { 738214778, "Come onnn! Pleeease?" },
            { 738214779, "I'm not sure he's going to take no for an answer..." },
            { 738214780, "One look at whatever the hell it is, and I'm out." },
            { 738214781, "Thank you so, so much! Come on, it's this way!" },
            { 738214782, "Wait, wh-what the hell is this?" },
            { 738214783, "Thank you so much for beating Tanta Sila!" },
            { 738214784, "Our mums said we're not supposed to talk to you, but..." },
            { 738214785, "But you helped us." },
            { 738214786, "Thank you, Frey!" },
            { 738214787, "They've been wanting so badly to show you how grateful they are." },
            { 738214788, "Uh, I... It was nothing." },
            { 738214789, "That's not true, and you know it. We're all in your debt. Me included." },
            { 738214790, "Wait, is...is this why you came and found me in the first place?" },
            { 738214791, "Pilo! You'd better not let me find you slackin' off, you little runt!" },
            { 738214792, "Oh no!" },
            { 738214793, "Sorry, Frey! I have got to go!" },
            { 738214794, "Hey. The reason I came and found you..." },
            { 738214795, "It's... Well, it's because I think you're really...nice." },
            { 738214796, "Round here's basically our turf." },
            { 738214797, "A shame it's barely fit for human habitation..." },
            { 738214798, "Do the buildings around here just not get fixed?" },
            { 738214860, "Foul creature! Still you refuse to leave the city?" },
            { 738214861, "You, who brought Tanta Sila's wrath upon us!" },
            { 738214862, "Say it was my fault one more time. I dare you." },
            { 738214863, "C-Councilman Jennesh!" },
            { 738214864, "Cease your wickedness, demon!" },
            { 738214865, "Do not approach her! All who do shall surely die!" },
            { 738214866, "Those who consort with her will perish in agony—just like the child!" },
            { 738214867, "What the fuck did you just say?" },
            { 738214868, "Calm down, Frey. Don't let him get to you." },
            { 738214869, "You think because you returned that feeble-minded old dotard to us that something has changed?" },
            { 738214870, "Well, think again! You are a blight upon us all! A bringer of doom!" },
            { 738214880, "The councilman speaks the truth! Leave this place! Begone!" },
            { 738214881, "Fuck!" },
            { 738214887, "Ugh." },
            { 738214888, "Well, if it isn't our favorite councilperson!" },
            { 738214891, "Begone, demon!" },
            { 738214892, "I suppose you saw that? They just will not listen to me..." },
            { 738214893, "Something tells me he gets that a lot." },
            { 738214894, "The children of Athia place no value on their education! None!" },
            { 738214895, "The blame is not entirely theirs, of course. My teachings will not fill their bellies." },
            { 738214896, "Not today, at any rate. But if they do not learn to think of tomorrow..." },
            { 738214897, "If they would only let me teach them." },
            { 738214898, "But no, they will not hear a word of it." },
            { 738214899, "Can't really blame 'em. They've been through a lot." },
            { 738214900, "None save dear Olevia, that is... Poor child. She, at least, was kind enough to listen." },
            { 738214901, "Had I only been able to teach her to read, I am sure her love of learning would have blossomed..." },
            { 738214902, "You mean they can't even read? Maybe you could, I dunno...start with some simple rhymes or something?" },
            { 738214912, "Yes... What a fine idea. I could certainly do worse than try." },
            { 738214913, "Thank you! The gift of wisdom is a precious one indeed. I will experiment with the method you suggest." },
            { 738214914, "Now, if you will excuse me." },
            { 738214919, "Wait, children! Come back, I haven't—" },
            { 738214923, "Ah, I meant to thank you again for returning Robian to us." },
            { 738214924, "His importance to the city of Cipal cannot be overstated." },
            { 738214925, "You! What are you still doing in Cipal?" },
            { 738214926, "You will not escape Tanta Sila's wrath, you know." },
            { 738214927, "Her enemies receive no quarter. None!" },
            { 738214928, "Is she from Praenost? Seems rather keen on Sila." },
            { 738214929, "Hmm. Maybe she can tell us more about her." },
            { 738214930, "What should I ask her about Sila?" },
            { 738214952, "The next stage of the plan will require the townspeople to be evacuated to a suitable—" },
            { 738214956, "You think you're capable of killing a Tanta?" },
            { 738214957, "Then you are utterly deluded." },
            { 738215026, "Not going in?" },
            { 738215027, "Not sure how much I feel like celebrating." },
            { 738215028, "Because of Sila?" },
            { 738215029, "I told you. We were close once." },
            { 738215030, "I only went there to smith for her. But she taught me so much..." },
            { 738215031, "Sounds like you had a lot of respect for her." },
            { 738215032, "I admired her idealism—for as long as it lasted." },
            { 738215033, "Anyway, here." },
            { 738215034, "You still know nothing about Athia." },
            { 738215035, "Uh...thanks?" },
            { 738215044, "Frey's amazing, isn't she? Can't believe we're best friends!" },
            { 738215045, "We heard you the first time, mate. Stop going on about it!" },
            { 738215046, "Oh, Frey! Cheers! Wait—do you have a drink?" },
            { 738215047, "It's busy in here tonight." },
            { 738215048, "Of course it is! We're celebrating the return of our hero!" },
            { 738215049, "Rather a novelty being welcome for once, isn't it?" },
            { 738215050, "I didn't do it for you guys. I just had a score to settle, that's all." },
            { 738215051, "That's as may be, but you saved the city nonetheless. So you have our thanks, whether you want them or not." },
            { 738215052, "A song for our hero, perhaps?" },
            { 738215053, "I suppose it can't hurt..." },
            { 738215054, "May I?" },
            { 738215055, "Thanks, but, uh...I don't dance." },
            { 738215056, "You'll be fine! Just follow me." },
            { 738215057, "What do I do!?" },
            { 738215058, "Relax and enjoy yourself, that's what!" },
            { 738215059, "Very nice!" },
            { 738215060, "You're good at this!" },
            { 738215061, "Dearie me..." },
            { 738215062, "Are you alright?" },
            { 738215063, "Amazing! I won't be forgetting that in a hurry!" },
            { 738215064, "No need to blow smoke up my ass. But...that was fun." },
            { 738215065, "You did very well, Frey! But I expected no less of our hero!" },
            { 738215066, "I'm not your fucking hero...and what's that got to do with dancing, anyway?" },
            { 738215067, "I suppose you can't be good at everything..." },
            { 738215068, "I told you. I don't dance." },
            { 738215069, "I'm so glad you did, though. That was priceless!" },
            { 738215070, "Thanks for that!" },
            { 738215071, "You'll dance with me again sometime?" },
            { 738215072, "I'll think about it." },
            { 738215073, "Thanks again for dancing with me." },
            { 738215074, "Hope we get the chance to do it again sometime!" },
            { 738215095, "Hi, you. Thanks again for the gift. I'll treasure it." },
            { 738215096, "See you around, okay?" },
            { 738215107, "Take the wounded to the council chambers! Hurry!" },
            { 738215113, "Well, look who it is! Heard about what you did." },
            { 738215114, "Can't believe you got rid of Tanta Sila!" },
            { 738215115, "Drinks are on the house. It's the least you deserve." },
            { 738215116, "You've got more important things to worry about than us! Go on, go!" },
            { 738215117, "So Tanta Sila is no more." },
            { 738215118, "While I had grown to despise her...I cannot confess to being overjoyed." },
            { 738215119, "I only hope that peace will now return to the city." },
            { 738215120, "The Corruption...within the city walls...!" },
            { 738215121, "Go! Go on, then! Get to the council chambers! Quickly!" },
            { 738215122, "Well met, fair savior!" },
            { 738215123, "I trust the festivities meet with your approval?" },
            { 738215124, "Not everyone made it to safety. Some remain outside..." },
            { 738215125, "So Tanta Sila's gone..." },
            { 738215126, "Good. Perhaps now we can live in peace." },
            { 738215127, "See you soon, Frey!" },
            { 738215128, "Daddy! Daddy!!!" },
            { 738215342, "Are you sure you should be up and about, Frey?" },
            { 738215343, "Yeah, I'm all good. Thanks to you." },
            { 738215344, "Oh, don't be silly. It was...nothing, really..." },
            { 738215345, "You think Auden's okay?" },
            { 738215346, "She doesn't look like she's slept in a few days..." },
            { 738215347, "Auden collapsed, you say?" },
            { 738215348, "Well, what do you expect? She's been running around looking after people nonstop." },
            { 738215350, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738215351, "I heard you worked yourself so hard you passed out. You okay?" },
            { 738215352, "I-I'm fine." },
            { 738215353, "Whoa. Okay. I think you need to take your own advice and look after yourself." },
            { 738215354, "I can't just do nothing. People need my help." },
            { 738215355, "Well, one certainly can't fault her sense of duty." },
            { 738215357, "Look, why don't I help out instead? What do you need?" },
            { 738215358, "I can't, you—you're injured." },
            { 738215359, "Yeah, and now I'm doing better thanks to you. So tell me. What do you need?" },
            { 738215361, "Thank you. If you really don't mind...I'm sure it won't take long." },
            { 738215362, "Consider it done." },
            { 738215363, "It...hurts..." },
            { 738215366, "Ow, ow, ow..." },
            { 738215367, "Thank you." },
            { 738215368, "Don't thank me. Thank Auden. I'm just her stand-in." },
            { 738215369, "I-is she alright?" },
            { 738215370, "She'll be fine. She just needs some rest, that's all." },
            { 738215372, "Oh, good. I was worried about her. She wasn't sleeping at all as far as I could tell." },
            { 738215373, "You just worry about yourself, okay?" },
            { 738215374, "Yes. Thanks again." },
            { 738215375, "Thought I told you not to thank me? Anyway, you're all fixed up." },
            { 738215376, "Ouch! Could you take a little more care?" },
            { 738215377, "Whatever. You're not even hurt that badly." },
            { 738215378, "Well, you're not a patch on Robian's daughter, I'll tell you that for nothing." },
            { 738215379, "Uh-huh. Sucks to be you, I guess." },
            { 738215380, "Hey, don't cry." },
            { 738215381, "B-but it hurts... It hurts so much..." },
            { 738215382, "It's gonna be okay. Hey listen, you wanna know how to make it hurt less?" },
            { 738215383, "What will make it hurt less?" },
            { 738215389, "What's the matter? Worried about the peasant girl?" },
            { 738215392, "Alright. Time to head back." },
            { 738215393, "And what are you up to now, hm?" },
            { 738215394, "Oh, Auden's taking a break, so I'm helping out with a few things." },
            { 738215395, "That girl... It was inevitable that she would work herself to exhaustion in the end." },
            { 738215396, "Yeah, how come she does that? Literally helps people until she passes out?" },
            { 738215397, "Hmm... You know already that she lost both parents while she was still young, yes?" },
            { 738215398, "Though Robian has returned—Tantas be praised. Nonetheless, the thought of losing anyone else must trouble her horribly." },
            { 738215399, "And so, I suspect she does what she can to ensure that won't happen—even at the expense of her own well-being." },
            { 738215400, "Right, but...if she pushes it too far, she won't be able to help anybody." },
            { 738215401, "And yet who among us can convince her to stop? Only she can make that choice." },
            { 738215402, "Until then, perhaps a little giril might provide temporary respite..." },
            { 738215403, "Giril? What's that?" },
            { 738215404, "A powerful herb that can soothe the mind." },
            { 738215405, "So, first on the agenda...tending to the sick." },
            { 738215406, "I get to see your bedside manner? Oh, this should be good..." },
            { 738215407, "Shut the hell up. I've got this." },
            { 738215414, "Thank you for helping, Frey. So many people need it." },
            { 738215415, "Thank you, Frey." },
            { 738215416, "Hey, you helped me, I helped you." },
            { 738215417, "You know, people are worried about you." },
            { 738215418, "Really?" },
            { 738215419, "Yeah. So rest your stubborn ass up before you head back out there, okay?" },
            { 738215420, "I suppose it would be a little inconvenient for everyone if I collapsed again..." },
            { 738215421, "I really am grateful, Frey. And I promise to get some proper rest—right now, in fact." },
            { 738215442, "This is the place on Johedy's map, isn't it? Are you planning on retrieving her smithing gear?" },
            { 738215443, "Might as well while we're here." },
            { 738215444, "Besides, I want to know more about Sila. And Johedy knew her." },
            { 738215445, "Well, as ever, it seems we have a few things to attend to first." },
            { 738215446, "Odvaha ore, eh?" },
            { 738215447, "You've seen this stuff before?" },
            { 738215448, "I've made armor out of it. For Tanta Sila, no less." },
            { 738215449, "Whoa. You made that armor?" },
            { 738215450, "Does that mean you can do something cool with this stuff?" },
            { 738215451, "I could." },
            { 738215452, "But I'd need the right tools." },
            { 738215453, "And where can I find those?" },
            { 738215454, "In Praenost." },
            { 738215455, "Alright. Shall we start looking for this place, then?" },
            { 738215456, "Easier said than done. Check out this map—Johedy can't draw for shit." },
            { 738215457, "Well, it can't be far." },
            { 738215458, "Looks like this is the place." },
            { 738215459, "Well, in we go." },
            { 738215460, "Fuck!" },
            { 738215461, "They get everywhere, don't they?" },
            { 738215463, "All done." },
            { 738215464, "What the hell is this?" },
            { 738215465, "What did you expect? A full suit of armor? You'd have needed a damned sight more ore for that." },
            { 738215466, "No, I—it's cool, I just..." },
            { 738215467, "Like it or lump it. That's the last bit of smithing I'll be doing for a while." },
            { 738215468, "How come you gave up being a blacksmith, anyway?" },
            { 738215469, "Quite the opposite. I wanted to help her more. We made a promise, and I wasn't about to let it be broken..." },
            { 738215470, "Like I told you, I made all her gear." },
            { 738215471, "And on the day I finished her crown, we swore an oath." },
            { 738215472, "Incredible... Who could doubt their purpose on the battlefield dressed in such finery?" },
            { 738215473, "Swear to me. Swear that you will continue to do all that you can to help protect our land." },
            { 738215474, "I swear it. I'll fight. And I'll keep on fighting. For as long as I live." },
            { 738215475, "For Athia." },
            { 738215476, "For Athia." },
            { 738215477, "And not long after that...she lost her mind." },
            { 738215478, "The Corruption came on so quickly, we barely stood a chance. So many died..." },
            { 738215479, "What she did was unforgivable." },
            { 738215480, "There's no way of knowing if she even remembered it by the end. But that wasn't going to stop me honoring it." },
            { 738215481, "When I walked away from Praenost, I walked away from smithing." },
            { 738215482, "Alright. Let's try again." },
            { 738215487, "That's a lot of books..." },
            { 738215488, "A letter..." },
            { 738215489, "It's from Sila. Presumably before she lost her mind." },
            { 738215490, "No good. Can't make out any of the writing. Shame." },
            { 738215562, "Frey! I'm so glad you're alright. I made it out too...somehow..." },
            { 738215563, "But so many didn't... People we were smiling and dancing with only yesterday..." },
            { 738215564, "I just want someone to wake me up and tell me this was all a bad dream..." },
            { 738215565, "Why did this have to happen!?" },
            { 738215597, "Stopped by to pay your respects too, huh?" },
            { 738215598, "You miss her?" },
            { 738215599, "Shit. Sorry. I know you do..." },
            { 738215617, "You should be able to find ballow trees in the town surrounding the castle in Avoalet." },
            { 738215618, "Whether sap still flows through their veins or not is another matter..." },
            { 738215634, "How dare you come here?" },
            { 738215637, "Well, look who it is! Feeling better?" },
            { 738215638, "Sure." },
            { 738215639, "Wait, this is the good stuff, right?" },
            { 738215640, "It is indeed. You said you liked it." },
            { 738215641, "Yeah, it is pretty special." },
            { 738215642, "The secret ingredient...is a certain spice from Avoalet." },
            { 738215643, "That's Cipal for you." },
            { 738215644, "We like to mix together elements from all over." },
            { 738215645, "Doesn't always work, of course." },
            { 738215646, "You like it here though, don't you?" },
            { 738215647, "Still can't make my mind up on that one." },
            { 738215648, "Well, maybe you should." },
            { 738215649, "Seems odd to go risking your life for a town you don't even like." },
            { 738215650, "In case you forgot, I also nearly got the place destroyed." },
            { 738215651, "Any more of that talk, and you're barred." },
            { 738215652, "Fair enough. You're always welcome." },
            { 738215653, "So? Did it taste of Avoalet?" },
            { 738215654, "How the hell would I know?" },
            { 738215655, "Those spices he was talking about don't come cheap, you know." },
            { 738215656, "If I had to guess, I'd say he doesn't serve them to just any old customer..." },
            { 738215657, "Our friend the innkeeper may love this city, but it's not going to help." },
            { 738215658, "What are you talking about?" },
            { 738215659, "Well, no matter how much he loves it, he's just a man. He doesn't have the power to change anything." },
            { 738215660, "No. He needs someone with real power to do that for him..." },
            { 738215661, "Oh, my—give it a rest, okay?" },
            { 738215662, "Robian's one of a kind. He really is!" },
            { 738215663, "The times we've had..." },
            { 738215664, "Poor Auden." },
            { 738215665, "Auden's certainly been keeping herself busy." },
            { 738215666, "But what with her dad and everything, I'm worried she's taking it too far, you know?" },
            { 738215667, "Fool! I cannot believe you would say such a thing!" },
            { 738215668, "Forgive me, but I must focus on my work." },
            { 738215669, "I fear I will be of little use to anyone today..." },
            { 738215670, "He was rather attached to his father, if I recall..." },
            { 738215671, "But \"murderer\"? Goodness me." },
            { 738215672, "He thinks I'm a..." },
            { 738215673, "You must forgive young Eleph." },
            { 738215674, "His father was lost to the Corruption." },
            { 738215675, "He became...something other than human..." },
            { 738215676, "And you...you..." },
            { 738215677, "No..." },
            { 738215678, "But I must make the boy see sense." },
            { 738215679, "He must be made to understand that there was no other way." },
            { 738215680, "There wasn't..." },
            { 738215681, "No. I once served Tanta Prav." },
            { 738215682, "She is no longer herself. There can be no denying that." },
            { 738215683, "And so, in her absence, we must learn to judge right and wrong for ourselves." },
            { 738215684, "And to teach others, too, to judge fairly, and without bias." },
            { 738215685, "That is our role now. Our new purpose." },
            { 738215686, "Well, he's certainly not lacking for conviction." },
            { 738215687, "That child really had it in for you, didn't he?" },
            { 738215688, "But it wasn't your fault. It was Prav's. Don't forget that." },
            { 738215689, "He's her victim, not yours." },
            { 738215690, "And if something isn't done, there'll be more victims before too long." },
            { 738215691, "Ugh, just...leave me alone!" },
            { 738215692, "You killed my daddy!" },
            { 738215693, "I'll never forgive you! Never!" },
            { 738215748, "Don't worry about me. There are others who need your help more." },
            { 738215754, "Frey! It's...Robian, he..." },
            { 738215755, "You should head to the council chambers..." },
            { 738215762, "Oh, Robian..." },
            { 738215763, "We lost you once already, old friend..." },
            { 738215765, "What are you doing here? You should be at the council chambers." },
            { 738215768, "You need to go and see Robian. Before it's too late." },
            { 738215769, "Frey! It's Sir Robian! You must go to him!" },
            { 738215770, "To the council chambers! Right away!" },
            { 738215771, "Alas, it seems Auden's father is..." },
            { 738215772, "Daddy..." },
            { 738215925, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738215926, "Why's she gotta be like this?" },
            { 738215927, "Hmm..." },
            { 738215928, "What am I saying? She's always been like this." },
            { 738215929, "And yet you're leaving her a gift..." },
            { 738215930, "I don't have to explain shit to you." },
            { 738215938, "Didn't you hear me? You won't find any answers here. Be off with you!" },
            { 738215939, "I told you, Junoon's that way." },
            { 738215940, "If you're done with Athia, you're done with me. And that suits me just fine." },
            { 738215961, "So the old man is finally dead? What do I care?" },
            { 738215962, "Why did you hate him so much?" },
            { 738215963, "The people suffered, and still he thought of nothing but his precious research. He abandoned us all." },
            { 738215964, "Yeah, to try and find a way to help you! And he found one! How is that wrong?" },
            { 738215965, "What good are such temporary measures when people continue to die!?" },
            { 738215966, "They are meaningless! Can you not see that?" },
            { 738215967, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738215968, "Did she step in to save so much as a single one of us when the Corruption arose?" },
            { 738215969, "No. We were abandoned! Junoon was left to rot by the very woman charged with protecting it!" },
            { 738215970, "You dare look upon me that way? I spit on your pity!" },
            { 738215971, "Go on, get out of my sight! I can't stand to look at you!" },
            { 738215990, "No more resin to be had... No great surprise." },
            { 738215991, "The resin you brought us has been put to good use in healing the afflicted." },
            { 738215992, "You have my deepest thanks. Robian, too, would have—" },
            { 738215993, "The people come here to pay their respects to Tanta Prav. The very one who died by your hand." },
            { 738215994, "Which of our beloved rulers will you kill next, I wonder? Olas? Cinta?" },
            { 738215995, "It's nothing to do with me anymore. I'm leaving. For good, this time." },
            { 738215996, "Nothing to do with you? You murdered my mistress." },
            { 738215997, "Look, I—" },
            { 738215998, "Take this." },
            { 738215999, "Your duty is not yet done." },
            { 738216000, "Tanta Sila said those words when she gave me that." },
            { 738216001, "You trying to tell me something?" },
            { 738216002, "And it will follow you wherever you go. You would do well to remember that." },
            { 738216009, "Alright? Stop and have a drink, why don't you?" },
            { 738216010, "Does it really taste that much worse?" },
            { 738216011, "How the fuck should I know? I'm not an expert in this shit." },
            { 738216012, "Could the days of the legendary \"good stuff\" truly be at an end..." },
            { 738216013, "Shouldn't you be with Auden?" },
            { 738216014, "After all, her dad's just..." },
            { 738216015, "Still can't believe the news about Robian." },
            { 738216016, "It's only thanks to him the rest of us are still alive." },
            { 738216017, "He never stopped working for the people of Athia, right up to the end." },
            { 738216018, "Frey... I was sorry to hear of Sir Robian's passing." },
            { 738216019, "Perhaps Wallace was right after all. Perhaps we really are powerless..." },
            { 738216020, "Even so...I refuse to give up." },
            { 738216021, "Naught can be done. Nothing." },
            { 738216022, "And in such a time and such a place...surely 'tis a crime to love?" },
            { 738216023, "Come now, Eleph. You can't just sit there forever." },
            { 738216024, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738216025, "I am sorry to report that the boy refuses to relinquish his grudge against you." },
            { 738216026, "I must confess, I am at a loss as to what can be done." },
            { 738216027, "You killed my dad." },
            { 738216028, "Forgive him, please. I fear he cannot be made to see sense on the matter." },
            { 738216029, "Do you not see? Our actions have consequences—all things are interconnected." },
            { 738216030, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738216087, "But he was far from the only guilty party. Our own Tanta was as bad—worse, in fact." },
            { 738216089, "\"True power can only be wielded by those prepared to see their duty done.\"" },
            { 738216090, "I'm so sorry, Frey. I put so much pressure on you. I shouldn't have." },
            { 738216091, "Don't be stupid." },
            { 738216092, "I...hurt you." },
            { 738216093, "Yeah, and I might have deserved that." },
            { 738216094, "No, you didn't. It's just...it's so hard not being able to do anything myself." },
            { 738216095, "I should..." },
            { 738216096, "Thank her for believing in me." },
            { 738216097, "Tell her she's too hard on herself." },
            { 738216098, "Just hug her." },
            { 738216099, "I...thought I couldn't trust you." },
            { 738216100, "That you were just using me to get what you wanted." },
            { 738216101, "I..." },
            { 738216102, "But that wasn't true. You believed in me." },
            { 738216103, "You believed I could be a hero. Right from the start." },
            { 738216104, "You look pretty beat up for someone who doesn't think they can do anything." },
            { 738216105, "Oh, this is nothing compared to what you've been through." },
            { 738216106, "You sure? You look pretty fucked up from where I'm standing." },
            { 738216107, "Perhaps I should fetch a mirror?" },
            { 738216108, "How about we call it even?" },
            { 738216109, "Sorry. I...just don't know how to say the right thing sometimes." },
            { 738216110, "And I've never had an Auden in my life before." },
            { 738216111, "Oh, Frey..." },
            { 738216112, "I'm sorry if I hurt you." },
            { 738216113, "I'm sorry too." },
            { 738216114, "I'll save the city. You'll see." },
            { 738216115, "Frey, please..." },
            { 738216116, "Promise me you'll come back from this in one piece." },
            { 738216117, "I'd better go." },
            { 738216118, "Wait. Here." },
            { 738216119, "I mixed up a little something with those herbs you gave me." },
            { 738216120, "Be careful, won't you?" },
            { 738216121, "Don't worry. I'll be back before you know it." },
            { 738216162, "I am teaching them another rhyme." },
            { 738216163, "The wisdom you have given me will help to fill these children's bellies one day, I am sure of it." },
            { 738216164, "So please... You must make sure that you live to see it." },
            { 738216165, "Fear not. I will keep the people safe." },
            { 738216166, "You, too, must do your duty." },
            { 738216168, "Alright? Quick drink before you go?" },
            { 738216169, "Sorry. Old habits die hard." },
            { 738216170, "We'll be up and running again soon though, I'm sure." },
            { 738216171, "Pop by the tavern when this is all over, eh? We'll be waiting." },
            { 738216172, "Frey! You may leave things here in our hands." },
            { 738216173, "This entryway and the people within will be safe as long as I remain standing." },
            { 738216174, "And as long as we have music to lift our spirits." },
            { 738216175, "Please... Do all that you can." },
            { 738216176, "Luck be with you, bold hero!" },
            { 738216177, "I can do little more than offer up a song." },
            { 738216178, "But there are those who tell me that the power of my humble craft brings courage in these desperate times." },
            { 738216179, "And so, I shall play on. For as long as I am able." },
            { 738216180, "I-I..." },
            { 738216181, "……" },
            { 738216402, "Oh, hi, Frey! Are you off somewhere?" },
            { 738216403, "Not that I'm worried, of course. You always make it home safe." },
            { 738216404, "Have a nice trip!" },
            { 738216406, "I've been learning to cook, you know." },
            { 738216407, "I'm still no good, but it's fun trying new recipes." },
            { 738216408, "I know how capable you are, Frey. You're a better fighter than any of us." },
            { 738216409, "But please don't take any unnecessary risks. I worry about you." },
            { 738216532, "Frey! What a coincidence meeting you here!" },
            { 738216533, "Hey, have you noticed the square looking tidier lately?" },
            { 738216534, "Actually, I have. You been helping out?" },
            { 738216535, "Yeah. I saw how much you were doing for the city, and I thought I'd better start doing my bit." },
            { 738216536, "Hey, since you're here, can I maybe show you around a little more?" },
            { 738216537, "Oh, I, uh...I think I know the place pretty well by now, thanks." },
            { 738216538, "I'll bet you don't know how to find all the people who want to thank you for everything you've done." },
            { 738216539, "And they'll all be very happy to see you!" },
            { 738216540, "Do we really have to waste our time on this nonsense?" },
            { 738216541, "Not sure you're right about them being happy, but..." },
            { 738216542, "Guess it can't hurt." },
            { 738216543, "Not right now. Maybe another time." },
            { 738216544, "Yes! Alright, follow me!" },
            { 738216545, "Oh...that's a shame." },
            { 738216546, "Changed your mind?" },
            { 738216547, "Sure. Let's do the rounds." },
            { 738216548, "This area was a total mess, but things are really coming along now." },
            { 738216549, "We're a little low on raw materials since we still can't go outside the city." },
            { 738216550, "But there's no shortage of people willing to help out. You know why?" },
            { 738216551, "Why?" },
            { 738216552, "Because I'm not the only one who was inspired by that speech you gave at the archives!" },
            { 738216553, "You gave a speech? And I missed it? Oh, that's just typical." },
            { 738216554, "Yeah, you can forget you ever heard that. Thanks." },
            { 738216555, "I'm the mighty Tanta Sila! You'll never defeat me!" },
            { 738216556, "I am Frey the Invincible! The Tanta-slaying hero! Prepare to lose!" },
            { 738216557, "It's Frey! The real Frey!" },
            { 738216558, "Will you play with us?" },
            { 738216559, "Maybe later. I'm kind of busy right now." },
            { 738216560, "Alright, but that's a promise! And you have to play with us too, Pilo!" },
            { 738216561, "Huh? Me?" },
            { 738216562, "Fine. But I get to be Frey, okay?" },
            { 738216563, "Let's head for the pasture next. There's something I want to show you." },
            { 738216564, "What is it?" },
            { 738216565, "You'll just have to wait and see!" },
            { 738216566, "He really has no idea how annoying he is, does he?" },
            { 738216567, "So glad you guys are all okay." },
            { 738216568, "Stop that! You've already eaten! So greedy!" },
            { 738216569, "You've been looking after them?" },
            { 738216570, "Well, there was nobody else to do it. But never mind that. Look!" },
            { 738216571, "Wow. You've been busy, huh?" },
            { 738216572, "She's your favorite, isn't she?" },
            { 738216573, "Yeah. You remembered." },
            { 738216574, "Oh, I remember everything about you, Frey." },
            { 738216575, "I told you, no more food!" },
            { 738216576, "Ahh, how far our painfully unpopular little malcontent has come..." },
            { 738216577, "You okay?" },
            { 738216578, "I'm fine. We'll, uh...visit the mausoleum next." },
            { 738216579, "Can I suggest that we do something else? Anything else?" },
            { 738216580, "I was just thinking we should head there." },
            { 738216581, "Yep, okay, good, nobody cares what I say. Fine. I'm fine." },
            { 738216582, "Great. Come on." },
            { 738216583, "Thank you so much for the flowers, Pilo, dear. And for all your help tidying up." },
            { 738216584, "Oh, it was nothing. Somebody had to do it, right? Anyway, don't mind me." },
            { 738216585, "Well, if it isn't Frey herself!" },
            { 738216586, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738216587, "Look, I..." },
            { 738216588, "Just accept it, alright? They want to thank you for all you've done." },
            { 738216589, "Ugh. Fawning hangers-on. Disgusting." },
            { 738216590, "We owe you everything, Frey. Everything." },
            { 738216591, "Uh... You're welcome." },
            { 738216592, "Alright, where to next?" },
            { 738216593, "Oh, excuse me, I...I hate to bother you, but I...well, I don't have enough food for my cat." },
            { 738216594, "You don't? Oh, I suppose she does have a few new mouths to feed." },
            { 738216595, "Pilo, dear... I was rather hoping to find some lovely flowers to leave at the mausoleum..." },
            { 738216596, "There you are, Pilo! The bench down at the dump is broken!" },
            { 738216597, "W-wait a moment. So—hang on—what do you all need again?" },
            { 738216598, "You want some help?" },
            { 738216599, "I—no, it's fine! This is what I'm here for." },
            { 738216600, "Sorry, Frey. I'm going to have to run. I'll make it up to you next time, alright?" },
            { 738216601, "You think he'll be able to manage all of that?" },
            { 738216602, "Food for a cat, some \"lovely\" flowers, and...fixing a bench, was it? I think he'll survive." },
            { 738216604, "Nah... We should give him a hand." },
            { 738216605, "You just can't help yourself, can you?" },
            { 738216606, "So, first of all, the bench. I found some nice, strong cord to..." },
            { 738216607, "Well...heroes will be heroes, I suppose." },
            { 738216608, "Oh, no problem." },
            { 738216609, "Oh, I'm just trying to make myself useful." },
            { 738216610, "Haven't managed to do much yet, though..." },
            { 738216611, "Ah, don't say that. You're—" },
            { 738216612, "I don't suppose you'd be able to spare some of that cord you have there, would you?" },
            { 738216613, "Our instruments have taken quite a battering, you see." },
            { 738216614, "Of course. It's all yours. I don't need it now anyway." },
            { 738216615, "You're too kind, really. Now we'll be able to perform again at last!" },
            { 738216616, "\"Haven't managed to do much,\" huh?" },
            { 738216617, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738216618, "Not bad. Think I can work with this." },
            { 738216619, "May I have this dance?" },
            { 738216620, "O-of course!" },
            { 738216621, "Can't believe I missed out on today's rations..." },
            { 738216622, "Wonder if we can find some cat owners with food to spare." },
            { 738216623, "Well, if it isn't everybody's hero! An honor as always!" },
            { 738216624, "Can I help you with something?" },
            { 738216625, "How're you doing?" },
            { 738216626, "Wanna dance?" },
            { 738216627, "Pretty well, thanks to you! I've been thinking about what I can do to help." },
            { 738216628, "But maybe I should just get out there and start helping...like you did." },
            { 738216629, "Great idea!" },
            { 738216630, "Thanks, that was fun!" },
            { 738216631, "Thanks! That was so much fun! Allow me to present you a gift in recognition of your skills!" },
            { 738216632, "Frey!" },
            { 738216633, "Whoa. What's the matter, Jo?" },
            { 738216634, "I've been looking for you." },
            { 738216635, "Uh-huh. Something wrong?" },
            { 738216636, "I've been reading up on Tanta Cinta." },
            { 738216637, "Thought there might be something in the archives that could be of use to you." },
            { 738216638, "That's...weirdly helpful of you." },
            { 738216639, "I'll tell you more at the archives. Come by when you have a moment." },
            { 738216731, "Nice day, huh?" },
            { 738216732, "When did you two become best friends?" },
            { 738216733, "When you were too busy to notice, clearly." },
            { 738216734, "Olevia... Ever since I met you, I..." },
            { 738216735, "It's lonely without her, huh?" },
            { 738216736, "Don't think I'll ever get over losing her..." },
            { 738216737, "But it's nice to have someone to share that with." },
            { 738216738, "Hanging out here with you helped me realize that." },
            { 738216739, "Wait. The penlight!" },
            { 738216740, "The trinket you gave the child?" },
            { 738216741, "Yeah. I used to use it to play a game with Homer." },
            { 738216742, "Ah. Normal service has resumed, I see." },
            { 738216743, "Shut up." },
            { 738216762, "Shit! What the hell happened here?" },
            { 738216763, "Whatever it was, it seems our friend's no longer here." },
            { 738216764, "Damn..." },
            { 738216779, "Is it true that you're Master Treahy's teacher, Frey?" },
            { 738216780, "I should call you Miss Frey then, shouldn't I? Will you teach us a new rhyme, Miss Frey?" },
            { 738216781, "A fine idea, child. After all, my own hackneyed verses must be wearing thin by now." },
            { 738216782, "Uh, I guess I could teach you the one I used to say to help me remember all the states..." },
            { 738216783, "Oh, yes! That sounds useful!" },
            { 738216784, "Alright, children. I think that's enough for today." },
            { 738216785, "Here you go, Master Treahy! It's the same thank-you as always!" },
            { 738216786, "Tanta Olas believed that by learning from the past, we could build a better future." },
            { 738216787, "Her most fervent wish was that all Athians be granted an education." },
            { 738216788, "And though she may be forgotten, that desire is not. Indeed, it lives on in me." },
            { 738216789, "Though we can never know for certain, it is my belief that she died in order to protect us all." },
            { 738216790, "She could not bear to inflict further harm on we, her beloved people. Fanciful, perhaps, but a comfort nevertheless." },
            { 738216791, "No harm in believing it if it makes you feel better, right?" },
            { 738216792, "I suppose so. Yet again, you teach me something of myself. You have my thanks, Frey." },
            { 738216793, "If you have a moment to spare, perhaps you could teach a lesson or two in my place." },
            { 738216794, "The children would love it, I'm sure." },
            { 738216810, "You! Is that where I told you to stand?" },
            { 738216813, "Alright? Can I get you something?" },
            { 738216814, "It's not so bad." },
            { 738216815, "I dunno." },
            { 738216816, "\"The Frey.\" Now that is priceless." },
            { 738216817, "Yeah, very funny." },
            { 738216818, "No, imagine: toiling away all day, desperate to quench your thirst with...a delicious glass of Newark street criminal." },
            { 738216819, "If you don't get over this, and fast, we're gonna have a problem." },
            { 738216820, "Rebuilding's going well." },
            { 738216821, "Think the place might even end up looking better than before!" },
            { 738216822, "Here's to a bright future for Cipal!" },
            { 738216823, "Who ever thought we'd be harvesting our own spices right here in the city?" },
            { 738216824, "Just think of all the delicious drinks we'll be able to make now!" },
            { 738216825, "Let's all raise a Frey to a tasty future!" },
            { 738216826, "All is well, Frey. You need not worry." },
            { 738216827, "I feel that I could do more for the city." },
            { 738216828, "Perhaps you could spare some time to help me with my training?" },
            { 738216829, "The rebuilding of the city continues apace." },
            { 738216830, "But we must not forget that the Corruption yet remains." },
            { 738216831, "I cannot neglect my duties even for a moment." },
            { 738216832, "My comrades and I have been training with renewed vigor of late." },
            { 738216833, "After all, the bar you have set is a high one. We must all do our best to protect the city." },
            { 738216834, "Greetings, fair hero! Some music, perhaps?" },
            { 738216835, "Milia is more dedicated to her work than ever of late." },
            { 738216836, "So, did you guys... Or did it all go...you know." },
            { 738216837, "Why ask a question like that? What if she broke the poor fool's heart?" },
            { 738216838, "'Tis hard indeed to say for certain." },
            { 738216839, "Hard to discern much at all in the face of such dazzling wonderment..." },
            { 738216840, "Uh..." },
            { 738216841, "But wait! You must hear my latest. It is a triumph!" },
            { 738216842, "You will do me the honor, of course?" },
            { 738216843, "Listen to his new song?" },
            { 738216844, "Sure." },
            { 738216845, "Not right now." },
            { 738216846, "Then, if it please you, I present...\"A Shiny, Shiny Bright and New Cipal\"!" },
            { 738216847, "Still no progress on those naming skills, I see..." },
            { 738216848, "This latest was inspired by your brave deeds, and by our fair city...and above all, by a certain special someone." },
            { 738216849, "I owe you more than words can say. Perhaps this will go some way, at least, to repaying my debt." },
            { 738216850, "Should e'er the urge to hear a song come upon you, you need only say the word." },
            { 738216851, "A pity indeed. Perhaps another time." },
            { 738216852, "You have decided to hear me play, perhaps?" },
            { 738216853, "The Ballad of the Enormously Clever Person of Cipal." },
            { 738216854, "The Horrible Terror of Praenost." },
            { 738216855, "A Shiny, Shiny Bright and New Cipal." },
            { 738216856, "Not right now." },
            { 738216857, "For your listening pleasure: \"The Ballad of the Enormously Clever Person of Cipal\"!" },
            { 738216858, "I give you: \"The Horrible Terror of Praenost\"!" },
            { 738216859, "Ladies and gentlemen, \"A Shiny, Shiny Bright and New Cipal\"!" },
            { 738216860, "A pity indeed." },
            { 738216861, "Lady Frey!" },
            { 738216862, "Forgive me. As I say, I threw the knife away." },
            { 738216863, "Did you need it for something?" },
            { 738216864, "Ugh. Sycophantic drivel." },
            { 738216865, "You may not have murdered the man, but the child can hardly be blamed for seeing it that way." },
            { 738216866, "Well, if nothing else, we've learned they'll forgive you for pretty much anything." },
            { 738216867, "Hero this, hero that! Ugh, truly vomit-inducing." },
            { 738216868, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738216869, "Leave me alone." },
            { 738216870, "Hey, look." },
            { 738216871, "Is that the knife the idiot monk threw away?" },
            { 738216872, "This is yours, right?" },
            { 738216873, "Wh-why would you..." },
            { 738216874, "I found it." },
            { 738216875, "I..." },
            { 738216876, "Look, I killed Sila. Because she killed Olevia." },
            { 738216877, "What are you gonna do about it?" },
            { 738216878, "I..." },
            { 738216879, "Think about it." },
            { 738216880, "And when you figure it out, I'll be waiting." },
            { 738216881, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738216882, "See you around, kid." },
            { 738216883, "Are you trying to get yourself killed?" },
            { 738216884, "No. But I want him to make a choice." },
            { 738216885, "If he really wants to try and take revenge, I'm not gonna stop him." },
            { 738216886, "But I'm here to stay, whether he likes it or not." },
            { 738216887, "Daddy..." },
            { 738216888, "Lady Frey! I found another knife for you!" },
            { 738216889, "It is not the same one, but I hope it will make a suitable replacement." },
            { 738216890, "You wanted a knife, did you not?" },
            { 738216891, "Please, you need not stand on ceremony! You are our hero, and what you want, you must have!" },
            { 738216892, "You are going to throw that away, aren't you?" },
            { 738216893, "No. I'm gonna hang onto it." },
            { 738216894, "There's probably other kids like Eleph around. Other orphans..." },
            { 738216895, "Can't let myself forget that. Ever." },
            { 738216950, "Nah. Maybe later." },
            { 738216951, "It's been a long time since I had someone to sit down for a nice long chat and a drink with." },
            { 738216952, "It's so much more relaxing than cooking, don't you think?" },
            { 738216953, "I can't wait!" },
            { 738216954, "You've probably got a lot on your mind." },
            { 738216955, "The city is safe now, thanks to you!" },
            { 738216956, "You deserve to relax for once. Promise me you will?" },
            { 738216957, "You can do it, Frey. I believe in you." },
            { 738216958, "Now go and finish this." },
