            { 738217207, "よい…しょっと！" },
            { 738217208, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217209, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217210, "Yeah!" },
            { 738217211, "Woo!" },
            { 738217212, "Whoa!" },
            { 738217216, "Hmmm..." },
            { 738217217, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217218, "Mm..." },
            { 738217219, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217220, "Mm." },
            { 738217221, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217222, "Alright." },
            { 738217223, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217224, "Okay." },
            { 738217225, "Let's go." },
            { 738217226, "It also has GPS, which would usually tell me exactly where I am." },
            { 738217227, "So where are you?" },
            { 738217228, "Somewhere between purgatory and hell." },
            { 738217229, "It told you that?" },
            { 738217230, "Sure did." },
            { 738217241, "All this woman is guilty of is surviving the corrupted lands." },
            { 738217242, "We have much to learn from her." },
            { 738217243, "Until now, we have only met her with blades. Perhaps we could extend her a hand of kindness." },
            { 738217244, "The devil will accept your kindness as it bites your hand, spreading its venomous corruption into your veins." },
            { 738217245, "We must deal with this interloper swiftly." },
            { 738217246, "Councilwoman Bellette, please!" },
            { 738217247, "Well, this is serendipitous." },
            { 738217248, "And don't you want to know what she wants? It's quite the mystery." },
            { 738217249, "More interested in the food at the moment." },
            { 738217250, "Hey!" },
            { 738217251, "Sorry. I didn't see you—" },
            { 738217252, "Give it back!" },
            { 738217253, "C'mon." },
            { 738217254, "Second rule of pickpocketing:" },
            { 738217255, "Never give back what you stole." },
            { 738217256, "What's the first rule?" },
            { 738217257, "Don't get caught." },
            { 738217258, "What is it anyway?" },
            { 738217259, "Something that ain't worth crap here." },
            { 738217260, "Well, if it isn't worth anything, why can't I have it?" },
            { 738217261, "Wonder where she came from?" },
            { 738217262, "What about the peasant girl?" },
            { 738217263, "Where are you going, Frey?" },
            { 738217264, "Come and join me." },
            { 738217265, "I thought you were going to have a drink?" },
            { 738217266, "I could give you his findings." },
            { 738217267, "And..." },
            { 738217268, "Here it comes." },
            { 738217269, "In return, I want you to find his research notes on the Break." },
            { 738217270, "They are—" },
            { 738217271, "Follow me and I'll show you." },
            { 738217272, "Come on, it'll be fine! I'll be with you, after all!" },
            { 738217273, "Not comforted." },
            { 738217274, "You have another big day tomorrow." },
            { 738217275, "Wait, this might come in handy." },
            { 738217276, "Before the Tantas went mad..." },
            { 738217278, "Shame there's no one here to read them." },
            { 738217280, "Wonder how many floors this place has." },
            { 738217281, "This isn't what we're looking for either..." },
            { 738217282, "GRAAARGH!" },
            { 738217283, "Yes, but you..." },
            { 738217284, "Okay, Bob. Bob, come on, we gotta go!" },
            { 738217285, "You good?" },
            { 738217286, "I'll take that as a yes." },
            { 738217287, "I think we lost them." },
            { 738217288, "He's completely mad." },
            { 738217289, "Yep. Too far gone for anyone's good." },
            { 738217290, "Corrupted by the Break." },
            { 738217291, "Well, Breakbob here is the best shot I got at leaving, so..." },
            { 738217292, "That's quite worrisome." },
            { 738217293, "To be honest, I don't care what you think." },
            { 738217294, "I do have an investment in your decisions." },
            { 738217295, "Where thou goest, there go I, and all that." },
            { 738217296, "Yeah, well, whatever magic bound us when I got here hopefully will unbind when I get back." },
            { 738217297, "Pity. I was growing so fond of our partnership." },
            { 738217298, "Wish I could say the same." },
            { 738217299, "You say something, dear?" },
            { 738217300, "Oh, no, just thinking out loud!" },
            { 738217301, "Wonderful! I do that a lot." },
            { 738217302, "Or I think I do." },
            { 738217303, "Maybe I don't—hard to separate the voice inside my head from any other..." },
            { 738217304, "You know what? I understand you completely." },
            { 738217305, "Tell me about where you come from." },
            { 738217306, "It's a city much bigger than Cipal." },
            { 738217307, "It's called New York." },
            { 738217308, "Oh! Ah, yes! I know it!" },
            { 738217309, "You do!?" },
            { 738217310, "Or I don't." },
            { 738217311, "Th-the name is sitting there on the edge of memory, peeking through the fog...or maybe I dreamt it." },
            { 738217312, "I-it sounds like a place I should know..." },
            { 738217313, "Perhaps I've heard it spoken of..." },
            { 738217314, "Have you told me of it?" },
            { 738217315, "Maybe that! Maybe...you said something. Yes." },
            { 738217316, "Oh, he's going to be essential." },
            { 738217317, "Knock it off." },
            { 738217318, "Olevia, what is all this?" },
            { 738217319, "I can help." },
            { 738217320, "Have mercy on my daughter!" },
            { 738217321, "But your entreaties are futile!" },
            { 738217322, "Your daughter aids the interloper." },
            { 738217323, "And what's worse, she refuses to reveal her whereabouts!" },
            { 738217324, "Someone must pay for such treacheries!" },
            { 738217325, "Tanta Sila!" },
            { 738217326, "Stand aside." },
            { 738217327, "Listen to me!" },
            { 738217328, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217329, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217330, "So, how do we get to this Cognoscents' Guild place?" },
            { 738217331, "If I'm reading the peasant girl's map correctly, we'll need to leave the city by the south gate." },
            { 738217332, "Alright. Let's get going then." },
            { 738217333, "We came this way last night, right?" },
            { 738217335, "Please don't do anything to draw attention to yourself." },
            { 738217336, "Can we just get on and find this Guild?" },
            { 738217337, "Looks like the gate is closed." },
            { 738217338, "I expect they're on high alert after our daring escape last night." },
            { 738217339, "A pond. Kinda...quaint, you know?" },
            { 738217340, "I suppose. If you consider the drudgery of laundry and floor-scrubbing to be quaint." },
            { 738217341, "Wow. That is a ton of junk right there." },
            { 738217342, "I suppose there's nowhere else to put it all if they can't leave town..." },
