            { 738217540, "Stranded in Another World" },
            { 738217543, "DEBUG MENU" },
            { 738217546, "W-wait! Where are you going, children?" },
            { 738217547, "Y-you're..." },
            { 738217548, "It's him—from the Council!" },
            { 738217549, "N-no, wait! I won't call the guards, I promise!" },
            { 738217550, "Violence solves nothing! Surely you know that?" },
            { 738217551, "Knowledge. Knowledge is the answer. It nourishes. Sustains." },
            { 738217552, "He does have the look of a man who knows his onions. Shall we see if we can get anything useful out of him?" },
            { 738217553, "Might as well. Hey, old guy—about this knowledge of yours..." },
            { 738217585, "Why are you still in Cipal, child?" },
            { 738217586, "We allowed you to go free only because you said you would go to Tanta Sila yourself." },
            { 738217587, "I would advise you not to go back on your word." },
            { 738217588, "Perhaps this will help you find your way to her." },
            { 738217589, "Wait. Is that...Olevia's name?" },
            { 738217590, "Among others, yes. This is a record of those who perished." },
            { 738217591, "Rather a morbid thing to be jotting down, don't you think?" },
            { 738217592, "Your recklessness resulted in the deaths of many innocents." },
            { 738217593, "My recklessness? I wasn't the one who almost got Auden killed!" },
            { 738217594, "Better to lose one life than countless others." },
            { 738217595, "Or do you disagree?" },
            { 738217596, "Is it better to sacrifice one life for the sake of many?" },
            { 738217597, "I guess I don't disagree, exactly." },
            { 738217598, "No. It can't be." },
            { 738217599, "I don't fucking know." },
            { 738217600, "That what you wanted to hear?" },
            { 738217601, "Good. I guess since you're such a believer, you won't mind being the one making the sacrifice next time." },
            { 738217602, "I..." },
            { 738217603, "Yeah. Now if you're done preaching." },
            { 738217604, "And why not?" },
            { 738217605, "Because it sucks for the person making the sacrifice!" },
            { 738217606, "But I guess you know that's never gonna be you, right?" },
            { 738217607, "Yeah. I'm not interested in your thoughts on this particular subject. Thanks." },
            { 738217608, "What I do know is why it's so easy for people like you to spout that shit." },
            { 738217609, "Because you're never the ones making the sacrifice." },
            { 738217610, "I..." },
            { 738217611, "So yeah—I don't know. And I don't wanna know." },
            { 738217612, "Look, let me make it simple for you. Sila's going down." },
            { 738217613, "I have to say, I'm not hugely convinced by the people in charge around here." },
            { 738217614, "With that kind of attitude, they'll have sacrificed the whole city before long." },
            { 738217615, "Don't get me started." },
            { 738217616, "Tanta Sila is waiting, child." },
            { 738217620, "And no one is getting sacrificed. Least of all me." },
            { 738217621, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738217622, "Ahh...the people are smiling again at last." },
            { 738217623, "Didn't expect to see her letting her hair down like that." },
            { 738217624, "Yeah. And in the lower city too." },
            { 738217625, "And so, to Avoalet, hm?" },
            { 738217626, "Home of Prav, Tanta of Justice. Punisher of crimes." },
            { 738217627, "For the people's sake if nothing else, I will pray for your safe return." },
            { 738217628, "Robian... Are we to lose you now too?" },
            { 738217629, "The people look to you. Where will they look when you are gone?" },
            { 738217630, "So it's true..." },
            { 738217631, "You're leaving. I had hoped you might—" },
            { 738217632, "Never mind." },
            { 738217633, "May the Tantas smile upon you, whichever path you choose." },
            { 738217634, "Forgive me." },
            { 738217635, "A moment, if you please." },
            { 738217636, "You go to face a demon." },
            { 738217637, "You will have need of this." },
            { 738217638, "I had thought you the people's only hope." },
            { 738217639, "Ah, stop it. You're making me blush." },
            { 738217640, "But no. I see the truth now." },
            { 738217641, "We cannot place our hope in the hands of others." },
            { 738217642, "We must begin to make efforts on our own behalf." },
            { 738217643, "Damn right. Let me know how you get on with that." },
            { 738217644, "Be good not to have to help you guys out all the time." },
            { 738217645, "We will keep our promise to you." },
            { 738217646, "But you, too, must survive." },
            { 738217647, "Tanta's blessings go with you." },
            { 738217648, "Nice. Was just thinking I needed a snack." },
            { 738217649, "An apple a day keeps Frey's hunger at bay!" },
            { 738217650, "Yeah, it wasn't funny the first time." },
            { 738217651, "The whole city busies itself with rebuilding, and yet here you are, footloose and fancy-free." },
            { 738217652, "Wonderful. Caught red-handed by the teacher." },
            { 738217653, "I have been meaning to talk to you." },
            { 738217654, "Come and see me at the council chambers." },
            { 738217655, "And put that apple back before you do." },
            { 738217656, "Oh! Uh...sure." },
            { 738217657, "Ah. There you are." },
            { 738217658, "You still do not understand the value of a simple apple, do you? Well..." },
            { 738217659, "And so, you see, even a single piece of fruit is as vital to Athia's future as—" },
            { 738217660, "Okay! Yeah, I get it, I get it! Lecture received, loud and clear!" },
            { 738217661, "Good. Now, to the real reason I summoned you here." },
            { 738217662, "Ugh, you mean there's more? Hasn't she tortured us enough?" },
            { 738217663, "For you." },
            { 738217664, "\"Thus, their names herein recorded, The lost are their due worth afforded.\"" },
            { 738217665, "This, among other things, was entrusted to me by Tanta Prav." },
            { 738217666, "It brings with it a grave lesson." },
            { 738217667, "That to promise to bring peace and to do so are two very different things." },
            { 738217668, "I pray that we need never again speak of sacrifice." },
            { 738217669, "But you do not wish to hear more of my \"preaching,\" I am sure." },
            { 738217670, "Don't worry about it. You're good." },
            { 738217671, "My words on this matter were of little use, I suspect..." },
            { 738217672, "Nah. I'm glad you were honest with me." },
            { 738217673, "I, too, failed to understand the true meaning of the word." },
            { 738217674, "Perhaps I still fail to grasp it." },
            { 738217675, "Maybe we're not meant to understand it." },
            { 738217676, "Anyway, there won't be any more sacrificing happening anytime soon." },
            { 738217677, "The people of Cipal will not soon forget the promise we made you, Tanta Frey." },
            { 738217678, "Is it really practical to be carrying such a doorstop of a book around with you?" },
            { 738217679, "Not really, no." },
            { 738217680, "But it means a hell of a lot more than a pocketful of apples." },
            { 738217681, "You put the apple back, so I let you off this time." },
            { 738217682, "But if I catch you stealing again...you will be back in the Tower of Binnoi before you know it." },
            { 738217683, "I pray that the record of the departed will grow no thicker." },
            { 738217684, "Alas, the march of death cannot be stopped entirely." },
            { 738217685, "Still, it does not hurt to dream of such things." },
            { 738217686, "Should you ever wish to learn the true value of an apple again, you need only say the word." },
            { 738217687, "Though it need not be an apple. An onion, a loaf of bread, a sheep... The lesson is the same." },
            { 738217688, "Did you hear that, children? To make bread, we need flour, and to make flour, we need—" },
            { 738217689, "\"Miss Frey,\" indeed. Someone's moving up in the world." },
            { 738217690, "And if the teacher of one's teacher is a teacher, that makes me one too. Taught you everything you know, after all." },
            { 738217691, "Uh, since when?" },
            { 738217692, "Gonna maybe hold off on letting you have that one for now." },
            { 738217693, "\"New York.\" \"Knish.\" \"Motherfucker.\"" },
            { 738217694, "So many new and exotic words!" },
            { 738217695, "I must open my mind and expand my knowledge ever further!" },
            { 738217696, "Did you know dried flowers make the most charming bookmarks?" },
            { 738217697, "I remember Auden giving Robian a bookmark when she was a little girl... I never saw him so happy..." },
            { 738217698, "Bring calamity upon us no more!" },
            { 738217699, "Wandering the city, dispensing insights hither and yon. I may have to revise my opinion of you, Frey." },
            { 738217700, "I wasn't exactly trying to inspire the guy...but I'll take it." },
            { 738217703, "Nor can his value to me. He is a treasured friend indeed." },
            { 738217839, "You really do have the magic touch." },
            { 738217840, "Swear I've seen it before somewhere..." },
            { 738217842, "Hm? The cat that was just here? Oh yes, I know it." },
            { 738217843, "Poor, wretched creature was all little Olevia had..." },
            { 738217845, "I did it. I killed her. Not sure you'd even be happy to hear that..." },
            { 738217846, "Hey." },
            { 738217847, "It looked as if it was trying to tell you something." },
            { 738217848, "Yeah. I wonder where it went." },
            { 738217863, "Be careful. I am guarding a dangerous criminal." },
            { 738217866, "Former Councilman Jennesh is imprisoned here." },
            { 738217867, "He is charged with agitating against the Council, and betraying the people of Cipal." },
            { 738217868, "How can a man once so celebrated for his wisdom have fallen so low..." },
            { 738217872, "Thought I'd find you here." },
            { 738217873, "Huh." },
            { 738217874, "It's not running away for once." },
            { 738217875, "Well, it can sit there all it wants. Olevia's not coming back." },
            { 738217876, "I'd love to see her too, believe me." },
            { 738217877, "But..." },
            { 738217878, "Sorry." },
            { 738217879, "Frey!" },
            { 738217889, "And so to battle." },
            { 738217890, "Yup. Got me a duty to perform. And then hopefully a quiet life of cat-petting to look forward to." },
            { 738217891, "Here. It pays to lay in supplies before going to war." },
            { 738217892, "I must confess, I...I struggled to forgive you. My mistress's death was a savage blow." },
            { 738217893, "But I see now what I did not before." },
            { 738217894, "My true struggle was with the truth." },
            { 738217895, "I bore witness to her crimes, but refused to recognize them for what they were." },
            { 738217896, "Must be hard accepting that your Tanta killed innocent people." },
            { 738217897, "You must think my blindness foolish." },
            { 738217898, "Not really. I killed your boss." },
            { 738217899, "Please...I have to know. How did she face her fate?" },
            { 738217900, "On second thoughts, I—never mind. Go. I will stand guard over those who shelter here." },
            { 738217901, "You've got your duty too, huh? Alright. I'll be counting on you." },
            { 738217909, "Yes?" },
            { 738217910, "I am a little busy, as you can see." },
            { 738217911, "If your business is not urgent, it will have to wait." },
            { 738217912, "No such thing as an easy life round here, eh?" },
            { 738217913, "Especially not since Councilwoman Dax turned the defense of the city from a duty into an outright obsession!" },
            { 738217914, "Your coming here certainly put the cat among the pigeons!" },
            { 738217917, "This is easy enough, no?" },
            { 738217918, "Piece of cake!" },
            { 738217919, "I'm just getting started!" },
            { 738217920, "Big talk for someone fighting small fry." },
            { 738217921, "Doesn't feel like quite enough to satisfy the old bloodlust, eh?" },
            { 738217922, "Ha. Feels like plenty to me." },
            { 738217923, "They may be weak, but man there's a lot of them!" },
            { 738217924, "The old \"strength in numbers\" approach." },
            { 738217925, "Nice try. You'd be annoying any size." },
            { 738217926, "Well, we can't all be immune to it." },
            { 738217927, "Uh-huh. Thanks for the blind guess, Professor." },
            { 738217928, "Stand back and assess things from afar, perhaps?" },
            { 738217929, "Wait, so does that mean we...can...?" },
            { 738217930, "These kinds of fans I can do without." },
            { 738217931, "What? Ew. No." },
            { 738217932, "It's a thing! ...Never mind." },
            { 738217933, "You're becoming quite the battle-hardened veteran." },
            { 738217934, "You say that like it's a good thing..." },
            { 738217935, "I. Am. Beat." },
            { 738217936, "There's. A. Surprise." },
            { 738217937, "What am I even doing this for?" },
            { 738217938, "Existential crisis, eh? Very sophisticated." },
            { 738217939, "Oh why don't you try being zapped here from another world..." },
            { 738217940, "I'd like to see anybody else from Earth land in Athia and start kicking some major monster butt." },
            { 738217941, "In my experience, those who \"kick butt\" most talk about it least." },
            { 738217942, "You need to match the magic you use to the foe you are facing." },
            { 738217943, "Instead of charging in head-first, you mean? Where's the fun in that?" },
            { 738217944, "Oh my fuck, they are so annoying!" },
            { 738217945, "You're not exactly a picnic yourself, you know." },
            { 738217946, "One must always be aware of one's limits, Frey." },
            { 738217947, "Uh, thank you, Sensei." },
            { 738217951, "Sila ruled over one joyless realm, huh?" },
            { 738217952, "Or did she make it joyless, I wonder?" },
            { 738217953, "Hmm. Deep." },
            { 738217954, "Oh yeah, like it's you keeping me alive. Sure." },
            { 738217956, "What do you think this place used to be?" },
            { 738217957, "It is rather fun to imagine, isn't it?" },
            { 738217958, "You're fucking with me, right?" },
            { 738217959, "This place was well and truly erased from existence." },
            { 738217960, "No kidding. There's literally nothing left." },
            { 738217961, "Alas, naught stands that time teareth not asunder..." },
            { 738217962, "Whoa. What kind of shitstorm happened here?" },
            { 738217963, "Something truly deserving of the word, I'd say." },
            { 738217964, "Yep. A full-blown fucking catastrophe." },
            { 738217965, "Nowhere to hide around here, huh?" },
            { 738217966, "More's the pity. I'd rather we weren't spotted if we didn't have to be." },
            { 738217967, "Losing your love of my trademark in-your-face approach, Cuff?" },
            { 738217968, "What kind of building once stood here, I wonder?" },
            { 738217969, "Something big, by the look of it." },
            { 738217970, "And bustling with life, I daresay. So sad..." },
            { 738217971, "Hard to fight with all this shit in the way." },
            { 738217972, "Really? I'd much rather have something to hide behind." },
            { 738217973, "Agree to disagree." },
            { 738217974, "Wow. A lot of people must have lived here." },
            { 738217975, "The Tantas have always attracted their fair share of hangers-on." },
            { 738217976, "Who did pretty well out of the deal from what I can see..." },
            { 738217977, "Feels pretty different from Cipal, huh?" },
            { 738217978, "One must not forget that Cipal as it is now grew from the chaos of those fleeing the Break." },
            { 738217979, "So this is the real Athia?" },
            { 738217980, "So each of the Tantas had a city like this, right?" },
            { 738217981, "I believe so, yes." },
            { 738217982, "And now all of them have gone to shit. Man..." },
            { 738217983, "You know, I could see myself living in a place like this..." },
            { 738217984, "Really? Um...you might want to take a closer look." },
            { 738217985, "I meant before it got fucked up by the Tantas, idiot." },
            { 738217986, "Perhaps we'll find somewhere pleasant to take a rest for a change." },
            { 738217987, "Assuming we don't get sniffed out by a Tanta..." },
            { 738217988, "Well, yes. That rather goes without saying." },
            { 738217989, "Wonder what this place was like back when it was full of people." },
            { 738217990, "A good deal more cheerful, I'd think." },
            { 738217991, "I wish I could have seen it..." },
            { 738217992, "You can almost taste the violence in the air..." },
            { 738217993, "The castle was once the jewel in Athia's military crown." },
            { 738217994, "Guess that explains it." },
            { 738217995, "The Break is getting worse..." },
            { 738217996, "...Meaning we're fucked?" },
            { 738217997, "That's rather up to you." },
            { 738217998, "So this was, like, meadows and shit before, right?" },
            { 738217999, "Can't you tell?" },
            { 738218000, "Uh, not based on what I'm seeing, no." },
            { 738218001, "You know me so well." },
            { 738218002, "Undo, undo!" },
            { 738218003, "You okay, Cuff?" },
            { 738218004, "I guess. The worse it tastes, the better it works, right?" },
            { 738218005, "Good. Because it tasted like crap." },
            { 738218006, "Wait, seriously? Uh, I guess I could...sprinkle some on you..." },
            { 738218007, "You're not funny." },
            { 738218008, "Damn! Whatcha make of that?" },
            { 738218009, "Not bad for a beginner, I suppose..." },
            { 738218010, "Yeah, ha ha ha! That was amazing!" },
            { 738218011, "You just enjoy yourself." },
            { 738218012, "Feelin' good!" },
            { 738218013, "Don't get carried away." },
            { 738218014, "You're getting rather good at that." },
            { 738218015, "C'mon, one more time!" },
            { 738218016, "Can it, smartass." },
            { 738218017, "Well, don't say I didn't warn you." },
            { 738218018, "Feel weirdly at home in this one." },
            { 738218019, "I think that's probably the best that can be said for it." },
            { 738218020, "Clearly you're a fan." },
            { 738218021, "Well? Whaddya think?" },
            { 738218022, "Yes... Really brings out your wanton viciousness..." },
            { 738218023, "Huh... Was kinda hoping for a compliment." },
            { 738218024, "Not bad, huh?" },
            { 738218025, "Eh, I guess." },
            { 738218026, "I enjoyed that!" },
            { 738218027, "Thanks for the assist!" },
            { 738218028, "Marvelous!" },
            { 738218029, "Aren't I always?" },
            { 738218030, "Did that have the desired effect?" },
            { 738218031, "Sure looks that way!" },
            { 738218032, "That felt good!" },
            { 738218033, "Can't argue with you there!" },
            { 738218034, "Fine work, Mr. Cuff!" },
            { 738218035, "Why thank you, Miss Frey." },
            { 738218036, "Not bad, Frey!" },
            { 738218037, "Hell yeah!" },
            { 738218038, "Worked like a charm!" },
            { 738218039, "Sure as hell did!" },
            { 738218040, "Ready, Cuff?" },
            { 738218041, "As I'll ever be!" },
            { 738218042, "Ready, Frey?" },
            { 738218043, "Do you really need to ask?" },
            { 738218044, "...Still feels weird when you're nice to me." },
            { 738218052, "Alright! It's our lucky day!" },
            { 738218053, "Change of career to treasure hunter, perhaps?" },
            { 738218054, "Nope!" },
            { 738218055, "Interesting..." },
            { 738218056, "I'm almost sad you don't need my help anymore." },
            { 738218057, "Anything worth our while?" },
            { 738218058, "Think so. I'll take a closer look later." },
            { 738218059, "Athian's pretty easy to read once you get used to it." },
            { 738218060, "I might have a future as a teacher, you know." },
            { 738218062, "Could probably chill here for a while." },
            { 738218063, "Wonderful. I for one can't wait to take a load off." },
            { 738218064, "Take a load off what?" },
            { 738218065, "I bet you've never had a piece of wristwear before that you could ask to wake you up." },
            { 738218066, "Uh, a watch, you mean? Yeah, I had one back in New York." },
            { 738218067, "Ahhh, so that's why you took so naturally to relying on me for every little thing." },
            { 738218068, "Damn right I did! Feeling good!" },
            { 738218069, "Shall we?" },
            { 738218070, "Let's do it." },
            { 738218071, "Just do what you do best." },
            { 738218072, "Is this really the time?" },
            { 738218073, "Um, maybe later..." },
            { 738218074, "Careful. These are the Tanta's chosen." },
            { 738218075, "Hope they're not as annoying as their boss." },
            { 738218076, "These are no mindless monsters. Proceed with caution." },
            { 738218077, "You know I'm not gonna do that." },
            { 738218078, "You really ready to die for your precious Tanta?" },
            { 738218079, "They're too far gone. Just put them out of their misery." },
            { 738218080, "Do I have to?" },
            { 738218081, "Well? Ready, willing, and able?" },
            { 738218082, "Two out of three." },
            { 738218083, "I am feeling dangerous!" },
            { 738218084, "A good rest really can work wonders." },
            { 738218085, "Ready for this?" },
            { 738218086, "You kidding? I was born ready." },
            { 738218087, "Alright, let's kick some ass!" },
            { 738218088, "Someone's raring to go." },
            { 738218089, "Boy, I am sick of the sight of you." },
            { 738218090, "It does get rather dull seeing the same old faces." },
            { 738218091, "Oop. This one's a live wire." },
            { 738218092, "Yeah. Not a fan." },
            { 738218093, "Just remember, the Tantas won't go down as easily..." },
            { 738218094, "Shut up and let me enjoy the win." },
            { 738218095, "Don't expect a medal for beating that one." },
            { 738218096, "Yeah, whatever." },
            { 738218097, "Just saying..." },
            { 738218098, "That's one in the eye for the Tantas!" },
            { 738218099, "Can it before you get some of the same." },
            { 738218100, "Hell yeah! You were watching that, right?" },
            { 738218101, "Oh, absolutely. Like a hawk." },
            { 738218102, "Gotta keep movin'. Time is money." },
            { 738218103, "Yes, and money is...completely useless in Athia." },
            { 738218104, "You're starting to mop up the baddies really rather quickly." },
            { 738218105, "Probably 'cause you're starting to make yourself useful." },
            { 738218119, "I'd be insulted, but I'm a little surprised myself." },
            { 738218120, "All's well then. Wonderful." },
            { 738218121, "Wow. Motivational gold." },
            { 738218122, "Who, me? Hell no. That was plenty." },
            { 738218123, "\"Seems to be\"? Very reassuring." },
            { 738218124, "Yes, yes. Well done." },
            { 738218125, "Um... Everything...alright?" },
            { 738218126, "Just peachy." },
            { 738218127, "I thought we'd lost you for a moment there." },
            { 738218128, "Just thinking. Pondering. Ruminating. All the big words." },
            { 738218129, "Something doesn't feel right..." },
            { 738218130, "Turn back, perhaps? Up to you, of course." },
            { 738218131, "Great. Thanks a bunch." },
            { 738218132, "It never gets any better, does it?" },
            { 738218133, "Oof. Thought it was just me." },
            { 738218134, "Certainly not. If you feel it, I feel it." },
            { 738218135, "Could you not fight with a little more...grace?" },
            { 738218136, "Why? It's the winning that counts." },
            { 738218137, "Why do they keep coming after us?" },
            { 738218138, "Because they've been driven mad by the Break, of course." },
            { 738218139, "Yeah, the Break you caused." },
            { 738218140, "I swear there was a scene exactly like this in a book I read once." },
            { 738218141, "Perhaps the author was also an unwilling visitor to Athia..." },
            { 738218142, "Fuck! We've been spotted!" },
            { 738218143, "Do not stand and fight! They'll just keep coming." },
            { 738218144, "Alright, alright! Alright, alright! Shit, shit, SHIT!" },
            { 738218145, "Frey, you need to run!" },
            { 738218146, "Man, I am so desperate to kick some ass!" },
            { 738218147, "Shut your mouth and move your feet! Now's not the time!" },
            { 738218148, "I...don't even understand what I'm looking at..." },
            { 738218149, "All you need to know is not to try and fight it. Run. Now." },
            { 738218150, "Uh-huh..." },
            { 738218151, "What the... Should I even be thinking about fighting that thing?" },
            { 738218152, "Absolutely not. Unless you're keen on pointlessly throwing your life away." },
            { 738218153, "Nah, I'm all good! I'm out!" },
            { 738218154, "People are so much more fragile than you realize." },
            { 738218155, "Is that a philosophical musing I hear?" },
            { 738218156, "Nah, just thinking about tearing zombies apart..." },
            { 738218157, "I've heard it said that flying enemies are best combated by taking to the sky oneself." },
            { 738218158, "Really? Guess I'll be flinging you into the air next time." },
            { 738218159, "Oh. Okay. So when you do all that stuff, you're just...flexing, I guess?" },
            { 738218160, "Magic isn't the answer to everything, huh?" },
            { 738218161, "If it was, Athia wouldn't be in this mess." },
            { 738218162, "True that." },
            { 738218163, "Once you've gotten used to this place, it feels kinda small." },
            { 738218164, "That or you've grown too big for your boots already." },
            { 738218165, "Sometimes I wish you had a mouth so I could just jam my fist into it." },
            { 738218166, "I do pity those who were born here." },
            { 738218167, "Why, because the outside world is so dangerous?" },
            { 738218168, "Yes. They'll never know anything but...this." },
            { 738218169, "Tell me this is all some kind of bad dream..." },
            { 738218170, "I can try to wake you up with a short, sharp blow to the face if you like." },
            { 738218171, "Yeah, you could try—if you were in the market for a dent or three." },
            { 738218172, "Bad guys nearby, right?" },
            { 738218173, "If you can call them that..." },
            { 738218174, "Nothing but small fry." },
            { 738218175, "No complaints here." },
            { 738218176, "Nothing much to worry about here." },
            { 738218177, "Don't get too cocky." },
            { 738218178, "Hmm. Might be worth finding another way around." },
            { 738218179, "Something nasty out there?" },
            { 738218180, "Shit. This one's gonna be tricky." },
            { 738218181, "Might be worth it for the practice, though." },
            { 738218182, "This one seems fairly formidable. Game for a challenge?" },
            { 738218183, "What? Why, when we can just go around it?" },
            { 738218184, "Umm... This one might be a little beyond us..." },
            { 738218185, "Yup, hard pass. Let's find another way." },
            { 738218187, "My gut's saying we should steer clear of this one." },
            { 738218188, "What a happy coincidence. Mine too." },
            { 738218189, "You'd be well advised not to approach this particular foe." },
            { 738218190, "Which...weirdly makes me want to take a closer look..." },
            { 738218191, "What an adorable creature." },
            { 738218192, "But...still a monster, right? Yeah. I'm learning." },
            { 738218193, "Wonder if these things would make good pets..." },
            { 738218194, "You'd better not be thinking what I think you're thinking." },
            { 738218195, "This could be one of those cat creatures you're so fond of." },
            { 738218196, "Like it hasn't been a single time before, you mean?" },
            { 738218197, "Is that some kind of bird?" },
            { 738218198, "It's some kind of rabid and dangerous animal. That's all you need to know." },
            { 738218199, "Ooh, this one can fly." },
            { 738218200, "Which means it'll be a royal pain in the ass to fight." },
            { 738218201, "We got a flyer." },
            { 738218202, "Knock it out of the sky." },
            { 738218203, "Careful—these ones can jump at you from the water." },
            { 738218204, "Yeah, they look pretty gnarly." },
            { 738218205, "Huh. Reptiles." },
            { 738218206, "You have these abominations back on Earth?" },
            { 738218207, "Bit of a slippery customer, this one." },
            { 738218208, "Geez. Keep still, already!" },
            { 738218209, "Whoa. Get a load of this guy." },
            { 738218210, "We've seen far worse than this, haven't we?" },
            { 738218211, "Beware: wild animals." },
            { 738218212, "Uh, thanks. I will." },
            { 738218213, "One to avoid, possibly?" },
            { 738218214, "I mean, I've dealt with worse." },
            { 738218215, "At least this one probably won't try to eat me." },
            { 738218216, "Based on looks alone, I'd tend to agree." },
            { 738218217, "Think we can just walk on by?" },
            { 738218218, "Yes, but do watch your back." },
            { 738218219, "I don't think horns are meant to grow that big." },
            { 738218220, "Very much an \"approach with caution\" situation, I'd say." },
            { 738218221, "Your plan?" },
            { 738218222, "Hey, if nobody starts anything, I'm cool." },
            { 738218223, "No need to fight here unless we want to." },
            { 738218224, "I think I'm good." },
            { 738218225, "Really? Here?" },
            { 738218226, "I suppose people must have lived here once..." },
            { 738218228, "Holy. Shit. Check that out." },
            { 738218229, "One to avoid unless you're feeling very confident indeed, wouldn't you say?" },
            { 738218231, "No reason to put your neck on the line here." },
            { 738218232, "But it could be worth it, right?" },
            { 738218233, "Up for a challenge?" },
            { 738218234, "Uh...lemme get back to you." },
            { 738218235, "Discretion might be the better part of valor here." },
            { 738218236, "I'm with you on that." },
            { 738218237, "I'd keep clear if you can." },
            { 738218238, "Yup. No point fighting these guys." },
            { 738218239, "Shit! How many are there?" },
            { 738218240, "Calm down. You don't need to fight them." },
            { 738218241, "I'm sensing something really quite formidable." },
            { 738218242, "Don't go that way, then? Gotcha." },
            { 738218243, "Walk away, Frey. Walk away." },
            { 738218244, "Yeah. Suddenly I'm not in the fighting mood." },
            { 738218245, "Fuck. Okay, might not get too close to this one." },
            { 738218246, "Probably wise." },
            { 738218247, "Some of our friend's underlings." },
            { 738218248, "Enemy troops, huh?" },
            { 738218249, "Servants of the Tanta." },
            { 738218250, "Guess we're getting close." },
            { 738218251, "Bad guys." },
            { 738218252, "Might be worth whittling down their numbers..." },
            { 738218253, "A manageable number, I think." },
            { 738218254, "Yeah. We'll be done in no time." },
            { 738218255, "There's a few of them." },
            { 738218256, "Tread carefully, now." },
            { 738218257, "Could be worse, I suppose." },
            { 738218258, "Says the guy who's not gonna be fighting." },
            { 738218259, "Don't let them surround you!" },
            { 738218260, "Ugh, this is all I need." },
            { 738218261, "There are quite a few of them, aren't there?" },
            { 738218262, "Don't worry—I'll mop 'em up nice and quick." },
            { 738218263, "Wow. Look at 'em all." },
            { 738218264, "They're no match for the mighty Frey, though, surely?" },
            { 738218266, "Gosh. That's a...a few more enemies than I'd like to be facing." },
            { 738218267, "Yeah, thanks for the warning." },
            { 738218268, "Come on! What the fuck!?" },
            { 738218269, "Rather a lot of enemies, that's what." },
            { 738218270, "Goodness. What did you do to upset this little lot?" },
            { 738218271, "What? Me? Nothing!" },
            { 738218272, "Things to do, people to see..." },
            { 738218273, "Yeah, yeah. Let's get going." },
            { 738218274, "Alright... Let's do this... Go team..." },
            { 738218275, "Can you please take this more seriously?" },
            { 738218276, "Onward, ever onward." },
            { 738218277, "Do we have a choice?" },
            { 738218278, "Not the most exciting errand in the world." },
            { 738218279, "For you, maybe." },
            { 738218280, "Let's just move our asses and get this done!" },
            { 738218281, "Yes, let's." },
            { 738218282, "Perhaps the odd diversion isn't so bad." },
            { 738218283, "Glad you agree." },
            { 738218284, "That-a-way!" },
            { 738218285, "This-a-way!" },
            { 738218286, "Destination confirmed!" },
            { 738218287, "You seem strangely keen." },
            { 738218288, "Your feelings on this one?" },
            { 738218289, "Ready when you are." },
            { 738218350, "Just a little farther." },
            { 738218351, "That's some first-class GPS-ing. Keep it up." },
            { 738218353, "Well? I'm gonna say \"stern and in control.\" Thoughts?" },
            { 738218354, "True of the cloak, less so of the wearer." },
            { 738218356, "Oh yeah. I love how this feels." },
            { 738218357, "Really? It doesn't look like much." },
            { 738218358, "It's not about how it looks! Ah, forget it." },
            { 738218359, "Kind of losing track of what's real here..." },
            { 738218360, "I could always give you a firm slap around the face." },
            { 738218361, "Go ahead. If you want to wind up in the junkyard." },
            { 738218363, "A passable display." },
            { 738218364, "That's your idea of a compliment?" },
            { 738218365, "All done?" },
            { 738218366, "Yeah. Kinda tired after that..." },
            { 738218367, "Well, that was straightforward enough." },
            { 738218368, "Easy for you to say." },
            { 738218369, "Fair to middling, I suppose." },
            { 738218370, "I'll give you \"middling,\" asshole." },
            { 738218371, "Guess that's it." },
            { 738218372, "I suppose it is." },
            { 738218373, "Done and done." },
            { 738218374, "Hardly one for the history books." },
            { 738218375, "Done, d-d-done, done, done!" },
            { 738218376, "Not a particularly exacting opponent." },
            { 738218377, "Coulda done that with my eyes shut." },
            { 738218378, "Well, I'm glad you didn't." },
            { 738218379, "One almost wishes they'd make it a little more interesting." },
            { 738218380, "Nah. All good with nice, easy wins, thanks." },
            { 738218381, "Is that really it?" },
            { 738218382, "Craving a slightly stiffer challenge?" },
            { 738218383, "They're gonna have to try harder than that." },
            { 738218384, "Let's pray that they don't try too hard." },
            { 738218385, "Needn't have worried about you coming out of that one unscathed." },
            { 738218386, "Aww, you were worried about me?" },
            { 738218387, "What a fucking pain in the ass that was..." },
            { 738218388, "As expressive as always." },
            { 738218389, "Nice work." },
            { 738218390, "Yeah, \"work\"'s about right..." },
            { 738218391, "Am I glad that's over." },
            { 738218392, "Yes, it was a little grueling." },
            { 738218393, "Are you alright? You didn't exactly breeze through that one..." },
            { 738218394, "Hey, I won, didn't I?" },
            { 738218395, "Gotta do better next time." },
            { 738218396, "I hope you do, for both our sakes." },
            { 738218397, "You certainly made a meal of that one." },
            { 738218398, "You think giving me shit about it's gonna help?" },
            { 738218415, "???" },
            { 738218416, "Newscaster" },
            { 738218417, "Crowd" },
            { 738218418, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218419, "Yep. C'mon." },
            { 738218420, "I'd prefer it if you were taking those off." },
            { 738218421, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218422, "Sure." },
            { 738218423, "How you doin'?" },
            { 738218424, "Could be better." },
            { 738218425, "Ugh, this place has no soul." },
            { 738218426, "So, who's the judge in charge of my case today?" },
            { 738218427, "You'll find out soon enough. Keep walking." },
            { 738218428, "Didn't think I'd be back here again so soon." },
            { 738218429, "Hope they get this over with quickly." },
            { 738218430, "You guys should really consider redecorating." },
            { 738218431, "It's enough to make a girl wanna leave and never come back." },
            { 738218432, "That's the whole idea." },
            { 738218433, "Alright, Frey. You got this." },
            { 738218434, "Do we understand one another?" },
            { 738218435, "I wasn't left outside the Queens-Midtown Tunnel, because that would have been an awful last name." },
            { 738218436, "Homer must be starving." },
            { 738218438, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218439, "Is that...?" },
            { 738218442, "You sure this is a good idea?" },
            { 738218443, "I mean, aren't you gonna get yourself in trouble?" },
            { 738218444, "Don't worry about me." },
            { 738218445, "Besides, I couldn't just stand idly by while they treated you so unfairly." },
            { 738218446, "So, where are we going exactly?" },
            { 738218447, "We should make our way to the lower city." },
            { 738218448, "The lower city. Got it." },
            { 738218449, "What were you even doing at the courtroom?" },
            { 738218450, "No one has arrived from outside the city for many years." },
            { 738218451, "Everyone in town wants to know who you are." },
            { 738218452, "The price of notoriety, I guess." },
            { 738218453, "You're right." },
            { 738218454, "Looks like the Break didn't come this far yet." },
            { 738218455, "You think those journals might be here?" },
            { 738218456, "Judge Bird saw right through me." },
            { 738218457, "Perhaps we should take a look around..." },
            { 738218458, "Hey Cuff, can you read what it says here?" },
            { 738218459, "How can you not read their language when you can understand their words?" },
            { 738218460, "Beats me. You're Mister \"Languages share commonalities across many dimensions.\"" },
            { 738218461, "I suppose I'll have to teach you then, will I? Fine..." },
            { 738218463, "Hmm. This book contains some interesting tidbits about mysterious shards that were found after the Break occurred." },
            { 738218464, "So...\"Breakshards\"?" },
            { 738218465, "Well, if you like." },
            { 738218466, "The Tantas painted unique patterns on their fingernails with their blood in order to unlock certain special powers." },
            { 738218468, "Huh. So maybe I can use them to get the same powers?" },
            { 738218469, "I couldn't say for certain. But I suppose we could do worse than try." },
            { 738218471, "Okay, nails aren't really my thing." },
            { 738218472, "Weren't you going to look for the journals?" },
            { 738218473, "Yeah, I know." },
            { 738218474, "I suppose the journals you were looking for weren't here after all." },
            { 738218475, "I took my chances. Let's just keep looking upstairs." },
            { 738218477, "Feels like it's getting brighter." },
            { 738218478, "Could that be one of the journals?" },
