            { 738218826, "Hey, that cat..." },
            { 738218827, "You think it's waiting for her to come back?" },
            { 738218828, "I hope not. Putting your faith in humans is a great way to guarantee disappointment." },
            { 738218829, "Hey! It's not like she wanted to leave him behind, asshole." },
            { 738218830, "Alright, alright. I'm sorry I spoke." },
            { 738218831, "You want me to have this?" },
            { 738218832, "Skittish little thing, eh?" },
            { 738218833, "It's a cat, Cuff." },
            { 738218834, "Olevia used to wear that, didn't she?" },
            { 738218835, "Guess it's kitty's way of saying thanks." },
            { 738218836, "Oh, look. Kitty dropped something..." },
            { 738218837, "Are you really just going to leave? That's—" },
            { 738218838, "You really don't get it, do you?" },
            { 738218839, "Faithful to the end, huh?" },
            { 738218840, "Thanks. I owe you one." },
            { 738218841, "You know, I wish you were half as nice as this cat." },
            { 738218842, "If you could see your way to freeing me, I'd be happy to bring you as many trinkets as you like." },
            { 738218843, "You can borrow the penlight whenever you want, okay?" },
            { 738218844, "What do you want with me, demon?" },
            { 738218847, "The people's faith in you is utterly misplaced." },
            { 738218848, "But if you believe that you can save the city, then by all means try." },
            { 738218854, "Girl" },
            { 738218855, "Boy" },
            { 738218856, "Boy" },
            { 738218864, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218868, "Fuuuck! I'm f-freezing!" },
            { 738218869, "Well, of course you are." },
