            { 738218890, "???" },
            { 738218891, "Gang Member" },
            { 738218892, "Gang Member" },
            { 738218893, "Police Officer" },
            { 738218894, "Man" },
            { 738218895, "\"Tanta\"" },
            { 738218896, "\"Frey\"" },
            { 738218897, "Waiter" },
            { 738218898, "Let's move." },
            { 738218899, "Before we begin, perhaps you should reacquaint yourself with your many previous encounters with the law." },
            { 738218900, "Next time you end up in front of me, I will not be as lenient." },
            { 738218901, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218902, "Get. The car. Back." },
            { 738218903, "It's not that easy. It's been impounded." },
            { 738218904, "What's so special about this car anyway?" },
            { 738218905, "It's none of your damn business!" },
            { 738218906, "Our boss—Mr. Giggan—is very unhappy." },
            { 738218907, "So unless you get it back, one of us is gonna be in a lot of pain." },
            { 738218908, "Do I get to pick?" },
            { 738218909, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218910, "Keep joking." },
            { 738218911, "We will leave your body in this fucking alley, and I promise you: no one is gonna miss you." },
            { 738218912, "No one." },
            { 738218913, "Okay. Okay fine, look..." },
            { 738218914, "Just tell your boss, Mr...." },
            { 738218915, "...Chicken." },
            { 738218916, "Giggan." },
            { 738218917, "Gicken?" },
            { 738218918, "It's Giggan!" },
            { 738218919, "G-Guigan." },
            { 738218920, "GIGGAN!" },
            { 738218921, "G-Giggin!" },
            { 738218922, "You deaf!?" },
            { 738218923, "Alright, G-G-Gig-Giggan! G-Gig... I-I—just tell him..." },
            { 738218924, "I...I need some more time." },
            { 738218925, "B-but for now...here's some collateral!" },
            { 738218926, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218927, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218928, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218929, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218930, "Home sweet hell." },
            { 738218931, "Can't wait to be any other place but this..." },
            { 738218932, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218933, "Shit!" },
            { 738218934, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218935, "Homer! Girl, come on! We gotta go!" },
            { 738218936, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218937, "<UnknownFormatting>\"FOUND YOU\"" },
            { 738218938, "Motherfuckers!" },
            { 738218939, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218940, "Frey, wait. If you're in trouble, I can help you, Frey!" },
            { 738218941, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218942, "I'm sorry, Homer." },
            { 738218943, "You're better off without me." },
            { 738218944, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218945, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218947, "Whoa. Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa! Wait, wait! Wait, wait! Stop! Stop!" },
            { 738218948, "Shit, shit, shit, shit! Ohhh, wait! No!" },
            { 738218949, "Oh...oh g—" },
            { 738218950, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218951, "Come on!" },
            { 738218952, "Well, not what you would call \"Earth,\" anyway..." },
            { 738218953, "I swear to god, asshole! Show yourself!" },
            { 738218954, "Show myself? I've shown. I'm showing." },
            { 738218955, "I can't get more show-ed. Show myself, indeed." },
            { 738218956, "You won't last long without anything to eat." },
            { 738218957, "Fine. And how exactly do you plan on getting out?" },
            { 738218958, "I believe climbing that wall might be our best option." },
            { 738218964, "Nice try, munchkin." },
            { 738218965, "Now scram." },
            { 738218966, "Alright, let's hear it. This isn't gonna last long." },
            { 738218967, "You can have this after you help me." },
            { 738218968, "I need you to find them and bring them back." },
            { 738218969, "I will do everything in my power to help you get home." },
            { 738218970, "You have my word." },
            { 738218971, "Cross your heart and hope to die?" },
            { 738218972, "An apple, maybe?" },
            { 738218973, "Sure." },
            { 738218974, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218976, "But in this case, I guess I can make an exception." },
            { 738218977, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218978, "C'mon." },
            { 738218979, "Robian Keen..." },
            { 738218980, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738218981, "Good morning, Frey." },
            { 738218982, "Here are the notes on the torana I promised you." },
            { 738218983, "Look... About our deal..." },
            { 738218984, "Your dad's journals all got burned up in the Guild when we escaped." },
            { 738218985, "It's fine!" },
            { 738218986, "Frey, you brought him back! That's far more important." },
            { 738218987, "That's more than I could ever have hoped for." },
            { 738218988, "Here." },
            { 738218989, "Thank you." },
            { 738218990, "So, uh...where can I find Sila?" },
            { 738218991, "You should visit the archives in Upper Cipal. You'll be able to find out more about her there." },
            { 738218992, "The archives. Got it." },
            { 738218993, "Auden!" },
            { 738218994, "Sorry to bother you, but I just saw your father wandering off." },
            { 738218995, "Forgive me, Frey. I need to go and find him." },
            { 738218996, "So I was right... The only way back home is to use one of those torana things." },
            { 738218997, "But you've tried already. And we both know how splendidly that went." },
            { 738218998, "Maybe we just don't know how to do it yet." },
            { 738218999, "Y'know, Bob might know something. Worth a shot, no?" },
            { 738219000, "By the way, thanks for saving our skin yesterday." },
            { 738219001, "How did you pull off all that...trickery?" },
            { 738219002, "Hell if I know." },
            { 738219003, "Right. Off to the archives we go." },
            { 738219004, "I am kinda worried about Bob, though." },
            { 738219005, "He is my ticket out of here..." },
            { 738219006, "Do what you want..." },
            { 738219007, "But remember, we have a Tanta to defeat." },
            { 738219008, "Damn. Breakbob used to be quite the genius, huh?" },
            { 738219009, "Which makes it all the more disturbing to see what's become of him. Tragic, really..." },
            { 738219010, "Speaking of Bob, how come he didn't turn into a zombie?" },
            { 738219011, "He came right through the Break with us." },
            { 738219012, "I'd say he was mostly Breakzombie already, wouldn't you?" },
            { 738219013, "Well, no new info on the torana here..." },
            { 738219014, "Sadly, given his condition, I'm starting to think that even asking the man himself won't yield much of use..." },
            { 738219015, "Please, you've got to stop this at once!" },
            { 738219016, "Sounds like trouble." },
            { 738219017, "Yeah. I think it's coming from over by that weird tree..." },
            { 738219018, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219019, "Yo, what's going on here?" },
            { 738219020, "Sir Robian's trying to desecrate our lovely old ballow tree!" },
            { 738219021, "He's, uh...got himself a mite worked up." },
            { 738219022, "It's the hue of blue! And the bloomers too!" },
            { 738219023, "We've tried explaining to him that he can't just run amok in the Grove like this." },
            { 738219024, "That there is our last ballow!" },
            { 738219025, "Alright, just cut him some slack, okay?" },
            { 738219026, "He's been living in the Break for the past twenty years." },
            { 738219027, "He's just...taking some time to adjust." },
            { 738219028, "He'll be back to himself soon." },
            { 738219029, "You keep telling yourself that." },
            { 738219030, "Father!" },
            { 738219031, "Father!" },
            { 738219032, "It's Auden." },
            { 738219033, "Auden..." },
            { 738219034, "Audie! My dear girl! What are you doing here?" },
            { 738219035, "I was supposed to see you there! I cannot see you there if you are here!" },
            { 738219036, "It's alright." },
            { 738219037, "I will take you there, and we will be there together." },
            { 738219038, "Apologies." },
            { 738219039, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219040, "Be a good man, Sir Robian, and hand it over." },
            { 738219041, "Please, Father. Give it to them." },
            { 738219042, "Please." },
            { 738219043, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219044, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219045, "Thank you. We'll take it from here." },
            { 738219046, "Just make sure that he doesn't—" },
            { 738219047, "He won't. You have my word." },
            { 738219048, "Oh, Auden... I'm such a fool." },
            { 738219049, "You are no fool! I believe in you." },
            { 738219050, "I told them you wouldn't harm the tree. But I never said that I wouldn't..." },
            { 738219051, "Now is our chance." },
            { 738219052, "Once again, breakin' the law." },
            { 738219053, "I don't do it proudly. But...all I do is for Athia." },
            { 738219054, "And if my father believes this could help, then I believe it too." },
            { 738219055, "Hey, Bob." },
            { 738219056, "Strange young girl from another world!" },
            { 738219057, "Yeah. I, uh...have your notes on the portals..." },
            { 738219058, "Um... The torana?" },
            { 738219059, "Ooh, my! He's much worse than I believed." },
            { 738219060, "Forgive me. My mind's a-a-a little wibbly-wobbly...wobbly-wibbly." },
            { 738219061, "Uh... Voosh?" },
            { 738219062, "Ha! Voosh! Voosh! Voosh!" },
            { 738219063, "Yes! Voosh!" },
            { 738219064, "I need to voosh back home! Where I came from!" },
            { 738219065, "After I kill this crazy lady...if I survive..." },
            { 738219066, "You will." },
            { 738219067, "I will go back home or...I will kill the crazy lady?" },
            { 738219068, "One or the other. Maybe both. Maybe neither. Ah!" },
            { 738219069, "Who's to know?" },
            { 738219070, "Sounds promising." },
            { 738219071, "Yes, yes, yes, I promise." },
            { 738219072, "I will work on making you voosh. You have my word." },
            { 738219073, "Let us proceed to the archives, then." },
            { 738219074, "It's in the upper city, right?" },
            { 738219075, "Kinda weird that they let us through without any hassle..." },
            { 738219076, "They're probably all petrified of you after seeing what you did." },
            { 738219077, "Huh. So these are the archives." },
            { 738219078, "Catch." },
            { 738219079, "Whoa! What is this? And who are you?" },
            { 738219080, "I'm the archivist." },
            { 738219081, "Auden told me you were clever. How do you not know what a book is?" },
            { 738219082, "No, I know what a book is—" },
            { 738219083, "Ah ah ah ah." },
            { 738219084, "You don't look like an archivist." },
            { 738219085, "You don't look like a hero." },
            { 738219086, "That's because I'm not." },
            { 738219087, "I used to be a blacksmith...before." },
            { 738219088, "Built weapons for the very woman that raided our city." },
            { 738219089, "She and I were quite close. She trusted me. And I trusted her." },
            { 738219090, "Sorry." },
            { 738219091, "No matter. It was another time. She was another woman. As was I..." },
            { 738219092, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219093, "Wh-what the..." },
            { 738219094, "Keep up!" },
            { 738219095, "Is everybody in this town batshit crazy?" },
            { 738219096, "Okay, so how do you go from a blacksmith to a librarian?" },
            { 738219097, "Archivist! And a smart woman knows when to shift her purpose for the needs of her people." },
            { 738219098, "Catch." },
            { 738219099, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219100, "What is this?" },
            { 738219101, "It's the floor plan of Sila's castle." },
            { 738219102, "What are you? My fairy godmother?" },
            { 738219103, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219104, "Name's Johedy." },
            { 738219105, "You're the one that's planning on facing off with Sila." },
            { 738219106, "Well, the name's Frey, and it sounds like you don't think I'm up to the task." },
            { 738219107, "Tanta Sila is the strongest and most formidable of all the Tantas." },
            { 738219108, "She controlled the army. Crushing the weak, even without the weapons that I forged for her." },
            { 738219109, "Crushing them with her bare hands!" },
            { 738219110, "I'm beginning to have second thoughts about this..." },
            { 738219111, "This batty old harridan needs to shut her mouth." },
            { 738219112, "You would be doing our land a great service by killing her." },
            { 738219113, "Rid us of Tanta Sila, and the corruption in her realm will stop spreading." },
            { 738219114, "But no, I doubt you'll actually succeed." },
            { 738219115, "That's enough for now." },
            { 738219116, "Think I'm pretty clued up on the Tanta basics." },
            { 738219117, "Then I suggest we depart." },
            { 738219121, "I wanna check to see if Bob's doing okay." },
            { 738219122, "Let's look around town and see if we can find him." },
            { 738219123, "As you wish." },
            { 738219128, "Don't you think we'd better learn more about Sila before charging off into the wilds?" },
            { 738219129, "Might I suggest learning a little more about Sila before we depart?" },
            { 738219130, "We cannot leave the city yet." },
            { 738219131, "How are we to defeat an enemy we know nothing of?" },
            { 738219132, "Auden seemed worried. I wonder if Bob's okay..." },
            { 738219133, "I need to ask Bob about those toranas..." },
            { 738219134, "Can't stop thinking where Bob might have gotten to..." },
            { 738219135, "Anything else you need to do before we leave?" },
            { 738219136, "Hurry up if you're still not done with what you need to do here." },
            { 738219137, "Are you ready, then?" },
            { 738219138, "Yeah." },
            { 738219139, "Time to go kill that bitch." },
            { 738219140, "We have a long journey ahead of us." },
            { 738219141, "I suggest we make our way to the fortress first." },
            { 738219142, "It's not too far from the castle." },
            { 738219143, "You really do know everything, don't you?" },
            { 738219144, "No. I simply happen to have looked at the map." },
            { 738219145, "This looks so different from Junoon." },
            { 738219146, "Madness is like a fingerprint—no two alike, as unique as the individual mind it springs from." },
            { 738219147, "Why are you so determined to get back to Newark?" },
            { 738219148, "New York. And because this place is insane." },
            { 738219149, "Plus...I made a mistake. I gave away my cat." },
            { 738219150, "My girl, Homer. Which was...not cool." },
            { 738219151, "I gotta fix that. She's all I got." },
            { 738219152, "Olevia..." },
            { 738219153, "Barely knew the kid, but...she just stuck with me..." },
            { 738219154, "She had fire." },
            { 738219155, "And now it's been extinguished." },
            { 738219156, "Somebody has to pay." },
            { 738219157, "What's so special about this \"New York\" of yours, then?" },
            { 738219158, "Central Park in the fall...and knish." },
            { 738219159, "Knish?" },
            { 738219160, "Potato pockets of toasty heaven!" },
            { 738219161, "My troubles seem to disappear for the three to five minutes it takes for me to demolish one." },
            { 738219162, "You paint such a...vivid picture." },
            { 738219163, "Strange how Auden seems to love Bob so much." },
            { 738219164, "Strange? Why?" },
            { 738219165, "Well, I don't exactly think the world of my parents." },
            { 738219166, "I guess being left on your own for years doesn't hit everybody the same way." },
            { 738219167, "And why should it?" },
            { 738219168, "Humans are horrendously complex creatures, after all." },
            { 738219169, "So, how come you came to Athia back...whenever that was?" },
            { 738219170, "What do you mean?" },
            { 738219171, "You said you came here from somewhere else, right?" },
            { 738219172, "How come?" },
            { 738219173, "I suppose you could say I was sent here as a messenger." },
            { 738219174, "But by the time I arrived, things between the Tantas had deteriorated to the point where they had no desire to listen." },
            { 738219175, "They didn't want to hear what I had to say...so they silenced me." },
            { 738219176, "Damn. So they turned you into a cuff? That sucks." },
            { 738219177, "What do you think made the Tantas go mad?" },
            { 738219178, "If I remember correctly, dissension grew between them. It led to a power struggle." },
            { 738219179, "A rift opened up. A rift from which the corruption grew." },
            { 738219180, "And where once they worked in perfect harmony, now they stand divided." },
            { 738219181, "They retreated to the safety of their kingdoms, and the Break soon spread in their wake." },
            { 738219182, "So did the Break cause the madness, or the other way around?" },
            { 738219183, "It all seems to have happened at around the same time." },
            { 738219184, "So that's the fortress?" },
            { 738219185, "Looks like they missed a maintenance bill or two." },
            { 738219186, "Neglect has certainly played its part, but these are the effects of the Break above all else." },
            { 738219187, "I don't like how quiet it is here." },
            { 738219188, "I find it rather peaceful." },
            { 738219189, "Would you rather be battling more Breakbeasts?" },
            { 738219190, "No. It's just... In horror movies, it's always moments like this when shit starts to hit the fan." },
            { 738219191, "And there it is..." },
            { 738219192, "Hide!" },
            { 738219193, "How did I get on this dragon's shitlist?" },
            { 738219194, "It really has it out for me." },
            { 738219195, "It does seem that way." },
            { 738219196, "But I'd suggest you don't fight it." },
            { 738219197, "Yep! I'll second that." },
            { 738219198, "Still no sign of Sila's castle..." },
            { 738219199, "There's no easy way over these mountains." },
            { 738219200, "You should head down into the valley and through that way." },
            { 738219201, "Let me guess. You've been studying the map again?" },
            { 738219202, "Indeed. As you should too." },
            { 738219203, "At last! There it is. Onward!" },
            { 738219204, "Gimme a sec." },
            { 738219205, "Whoa." },
            { 738219206, "It is quite breathtaking." },
            { 738219207, "I was thinking more \"impenetrable and foreboding.\"" },
            { 738219208, "What the hell is this!?" },
            { 738219209, "It seems we've entered an area where the Break is at its most intense!" },
            { 738219210, "Ya think?" },
            { 738219214, "Easier said than done!" },
            { 738219215, "Can't see a thing!" },
            { 738219216, "I'm trying to find us somewhere to take shelter!" },
            { 738219217, "Just keep yourself together for a little longer!" },
            { 738219218, "What the hell are those things?" },
            { 738219219, "They don't look like animals or humans!" },
            { 738219220, "I believe they are life-forms born from the Break itself." },
            { 738219221, "They're like my worst nightmares come to life..." },
            { 738219222, "Don't push yourself too hard." },
            { 738219223, "Our main priority should be to find shelter." },
            { 738219224, "There's a cave nearby!" },
            { 738219225, "We should hide there until the storm passes!" },
            { 738219226, "Sounds good to me. Lead on!" },
            { 738219227, "Holy fucking shit!" },
            { 738219228, "Looks like someone got an extra-big helping of the Break!" },
            { 738219229, "I don't think it's gonna let us pass..." },
            { 738219230, "Sadly, I agree." },
            { 738219231, "But if you don't think you can beat it, there's no need to go charging in either." },
            { 738219232, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219233, "You want to know why I want to go home?" },
            { 738219234, "Because this place fucking sucks!" },
            { 738219235, "I do understand that that may have been a bit intense—" },
            { 738219236, "Intense?" },
            { 738219237, "That was batshit crazy!" },
            { 738219238, "I might live on the streets of New York with a cat as company..." },
            { 738219239, "But I would rather be there alone than spend one more minute in this fucking hellhole!" },
            { 738219240, "Well, try to get some sleep." },
            { 738219241, "Things will be better in the morning." },
            { 738219242, "Yeah, sure. Much better." },
            { 738219263, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219264, "Feeling better?" },
            { 738219265, "Not really." },
            { 738219266, "I had a nightmare and it was ten times better than this." },
            { 738219267, "Hmm... It is quite beautiful." },
            { 738219268, "Yeah, in a...\"everything here wants to kill you\" kinda way." },
            { 738219269, "No, I just mean that even amongst the madness, there's a sort of...delicate grace." },
            { 738219270, "Destruction and corruption are forms of creation in themselves." },
            { 738219271, "Wow. You sound like a serial killer." },
            { 738219272, "Uh. What?" },
            { 738219273, "\"Destruction and corruption are beautiful forms of creation in themselves!\"" },
            { 738219274, "I don't sound like that." },
            { 738219275, "You absolutely sound like that." },
            { 738219276, "You're fucking stupid." },
            { 738219277, "Perhaps the front door isn't the best option." },
            { 738219278, "What? You don't think I could take them?" },
            { 738219279, "I'm simply saying there might be a way in that would involve less stabbing and...bleeding..." },
            { 738219280, "I was half-kidding." },
            { 738219281, "I'm fond of my blood on the inside." },
            { 738219282, "But we may not have a choice." },
            { 738219283, "Might it be worth at least seeing what's around the back?" },
            { 738219284, "Hmm... Let's check to see if the front gate is locked or not first." },
            { 738219285, "Didn't you say you were going to check the front gate?" },
            { 738219286, "I just wanted to do some recon before I go in." },
            { 738219287, "Or are you simply lost?" },
            { 738219288, "I didn't expect the place to be so...dead." },
            { 738219289, "I'd count my blessings if I were you." },
            { 738219290, "Let's hurry up and find Sila, shall we?" },
            { 738219291, "Who's there?" },
            { 738219292, "Looks like the poor souls who used to live here." },
            { 738219293, "Sorry, but I need to get by." },
            { 738219294, "So these Breakzombies, they're..." },
            { 738219295, "Victims of the Break that consumed Tanta Sila's realm, I'd say." },
            { 738219296, "How could she do this to the people she was supposed to protect?" },
            { 738219297, "Ruler of Praenost, my ass." },
            { 738219299, "We must be getting closer." },
            { 738219300, "Don't expect any respite from here on in." },
            { 738219301, "Fuck! Won't be getting in this way." },
            { 738219302, "Blocking the entrance to keep out would-be infiltrators..." },
            { 738219303, "I suppose we should have expected no less from the Tanta of Strength." },
            { 738219304, "Perhaps there's a way in round the back?" },
            { 738219305, "Wait, wasn't there a side passage somewhere?" },
            { 738219306, "You saw it on the floor plan too, right?" },
            { 738219307, "Yes, but that plan was made a long time ago." },
            { 738219308, "I doubt such a vulnerability would have survived all these years..." },
            { 738219309, "We need to go and check. Just in case." },
            { 738219310, "If you must." },
            { 738219311, "Where are you going?" },
            { 738219312, "The floor plan showed a passage leading in from the side of the castle." },
            { 738219313, "If we can find it, we might be able to sneak in undetected." },
            { 738219314, "The passage should be somewhere nearby." },
            { 738219315, "As I mentioned, the floor plan is quite old." },
            { 738219316, "I doubt Sila would have left such a gap in her defenses unplugged for so long." },
            { 738219317, "I think we might have to reconsider our approach." },
            { 738219318, "Or we could look up for the way in..." },
            { 738219319, "Really? Are you sure that's a good idea?" },
            { 738219320, "See, what did I tell you? O ye of little faith!" },
            { 738219321, "So much for plugging the gap in her defenses..." },
            { 738219322, "Alright, let's go find where this bitch is hiding." },
            { 738219323, "Why did she build a castle on top of this stupid cliff?" },
            { 738219324, "Possibly so she could look down on all of her enemies?" },
            { 738219325, "Sounds like a fun hobby." },
            { 738219326, "I know this guy. It's the same as the one I fought in Cipal." },
            { 738219327, "And it's not alone this time." },
            { 738219328, "Don't let your guard down, Frey." },
            { 738219329, "Ugh, why do they have to fly around like that?" },
            { 738219330, "Try to work out when they're about to stop moving." },
            { 738219331, "This looks like a way in." },
            { 738219332, "Better be on my guard..." },
            { 738219333, "The Purge of the Rheddig..." },
            { 738219334, "Yeah, I saw that mentioned in a book from the archives." },
            { 738219335, "It looks like Athia was invaded by the...Rheddig, was it?" },
            { 738219336, "And that is Tanta Sila." },
            { 738219337, "But she doesn't look crazy, like she did in Cipal." },
            { 738219339, "I don't think that's a thing." },
            { 738219340, "So that's them, huh?" },
            { 738219341, "Not anymore." },
            { 738219342, "Let's keep moving, shall we?" },
            { 738219343, "I wonder why they turned on their own people..." },
            { 738219344, "Yep, you can tell she's the one in charge." },
            { 738219345, "Looks tough as hell, too. Very impressive." },
            { 738219346, "No wonder the people trusted her to lead them into battle." },
            { 738219347, "Pfft. Propaganda." },
            { 738219348, "She looks smart." },
            { 738219349, "She was the Tanta of Wisdom." },
            { 738219350, "I had a teacher like her. Same look in her eye." },
            { 738219351, "You went to school?" },
            { 738219352, "Believe it or not, I didn't spend my entire childhood developing a tough street girl persona." },
            { 738219353, "Mmm. Could have fooled me..." },
            { 738219354, "Looks a little judgy...but fair, I guess." },
            { 738219355, "The Tanta of Justice." },
            { 738219356, "I could tell. Spent plenty of time standing in front of women like that." },
            { 738219357, "Lawbreaker, eh?" },
            { 738219358, "I'm not proud of it. Look, I didn't make society, I just had to survive in it." },
            { 738219359, "Wow, she's beautiful." },
            { 738219360, "Yes. She does possess a certain...aesthetic appeal." },
            { 738219361, "No, I mean, like, from the inside. It shines through her." },
            { 738219362, "She was the Tanta of Love." },
            { 738219363, "Those eyes... So kind... So comforting..." },
            { 738219364, "So tragic. For all that innocent purity to be twisted by madness..." },
            { 738219365, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219366, "Frey..." },
            { 738219367, "No name for a demon..." },
            { 738219368, "I am surprised you made it this far." },
            { 738219369, "I'm impressed." },
            { 738219370, "Is that actually you? Or are you hiding behind one of your puppets again?" },
            { 738219371, "I am the one you seek. The one and only Tanta Sila." },
            { 738219372, "So, face-to-face with the kiddy killer herself." },
            { 738219373, "There will always be casualties in war." },
            { 738219374, "Great! No war, no casualties. Sounds good to me." },
            { 738219375, "Simpleminded. Silly girl. Naive. There will always be war." },
            { 738219376, "No. There doesn't have to be." },
            { 738219377, "But you and your goons don't care who you hurt." },
            { 738219378, "You killed a child. A little girl." },
            { 738219415, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219416, "That was for you, Olevia..." },
            { 738219417, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219418, "All will be well..." },
            { 738219419, "What is happening?" },
            { 738219420, "I'm not sure..." },
            { 738219421, "What's wrong? You're awfully quiet." },
            { 738219422, "I just took someone's life..." },
            { 738219423, "With good reason." },
            { 738219424, "The people of Cipal will thank you for it." },
            { 738219425, "I really thought it would...I dunno." },
            { 738219426, "I...I just wanted to punish her." },
            { 738219427, "Thought it would make me feel better." },
            { 738219428, "But it didn't?" },
            { 738219429, "No." },
            { 738219430, "It's no easy thing to take the life of another." },
            { 738219431, "Well, I've taken out Breakzombies...but only in self-defense." },
            { 738219432, "This...I did out of anger. It was premeditated." },
            { 738219433, "It was self-preservation." },
            { 738219434, "She was never going to stop coming after you." },
            { 738219435, "More innocents would have died." },
            { 738219436, "More Olevias." },
            { 738219437, "I guess. Kill one to save many, right?" },
            { 738219438, "Exactly." },
            { 738219439, "We gotta keep our heads on a swivel." },
            { 738219440, "What?" },
            { 738219441, "It's just a way to say we need to keep our eyes peeled." },
            { 738219442, "Ugh! That sounds disgusting." },
            { 738219443, "Forget it. Just stay alert." },
            { 738219444, "There might be monsters." },
            { 738219445, "Peeled eyes, indeed." },
            { 738219446, "You do realize we're not the monsters here?" },
            { 738219447, "You didn't do badly, you know. She was no ordinary opponent." },
            { 738219448, "Was that...a compliment?" },
            { 738219449, "Don't point at it. How do you feel?" },
            { 738219450, "Mentally, a four. Physically, a ten." },
            { 738219451, "Oddly, I feel pretty good for a girl who's just had the shit kicked out of her." },
            { 738219452, "You absorbed Sila's energy. It restored your strength. Healed you." },
            { 738219453, "No shit. I was there." },
            { 738219454, "And, as you put it, you \"leveled up.\"" },
            { 738219455, "The binding spell the Tantas placed upon me seems to have loosened a little too. Much obliged!" },
            { 738219456, "Well, whatever happened, it's gonna make surviving in this fun house easier for both of us." },
            { 738219457, "Brighter paths ahead!" },
            { 738219458, "Time to head back to Cipal and tell the people that Sila's shadow no longer hangs over them!" },
            { 738219459, "By the way, I think I'm starting to understand these Athian letters." },
            { 738219460, "How very impressive. Swift learner, eh?" },
            { 738219461, "I actually picked up on French pretty quickly when I was in school." },
            { 738219462, "Is that another Earth language?" },
            { 738219463, "Oui, monsieur." },
            { 738219464, "That's a yes, I take it?" },
            { 738219465, "Seems awfully inconvenient having different languages in the same world." },
            { 738219466, "Yeah? I actually think it's quite useful." },
            { 738219467, "Especially when you wanna say something to someone but you don't want them to understand..." },
            { 738219468, "Mon petit connard." },
            { 738219469, "Now Sila's gone, I just need to get Bob to teach me how to use the torana." },
            { 738219470, "Then I'm outta here." },
            { 738219471, "You really think he's in a fit state to teach you anything?" },
            { 738219472, "I have to believe he is. Gotta think positive." },
            { 738219473, "Can't wait to click my heels three times..." },
            { 738219474, "Is that how your people celebrate victory or something?" },
            { 738219475, "You really do have the strangest customs." },
            { 738219476, "Frey! It's so good to see you back!" },
            { 738219477, "Yeah. It was...intense. But I made it." },
            { 738219478, "I, uh...I killed Sila." },
            { 738219479, "I'm sorry. It must have been awful..." },
            { 738219480, "But thanks to you, the Break has stopped advancing!" },
            { 738219481, "You have given us a glimmer of hope." },
            { 738219482, "Oh, I'm meant to tell you! There's a celebration at the tavern." },
            { 738219483, "You'll stop by, won't you?" },
            { 738219496, "Just imagine what they'll give you for killing all four." },
            { 738219497, "No thanks." },
            { 738219500, "Perhaps they'll name a village after you." },
            { 738219501, "Actually, yeah. That would be pretty cool." },
            { 738219502, "But no. No, I'm not planning on killing any more Tantas." },
            { 738219503, "I barely survived this one." },
            { 738219536, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219537, "Look! It's the hero of the hour!" },
            { 738219539, "Look at these people celebrating our victory!" },
            { 738219540, "Ah, you're just jealous they don't know who you are." },
            { 738219541, "Well, I did play a vital role in your much-vaunted triumph, you know." },
            { 738219542, "Hah! I guess you're right. Well, I appreciate you, Cuff." },
            { 738219543, "Thanks. I...couldn't have done it without you." },
            { 738219544, "Could this be... Are we becoming...friends?" },
            { 738219545, "Alright, whoa. I'd say...civil colleagues who tolerate each other." },
            { 738219546, "Well, if it isn't our mighty savior!" },
            { 738219547, "Stop and celebrate, why don't you?" },
            { 738219548, "I haven't seen this much excitement in town for years!" },
            { 738219549, "And it's all because of you." },
            { 738219550, "Ahhh, the ale's never tasted so good!" },
            { 738219551, "You have my thanks, hero." },
            { 738219553, "Everyone looks so happy!" },
            { 738219554, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219555, "The Corruption is coming!" },
            { 738219556, "The Corruption is coming from Avoalet!" },
            { 738219557, "What the hell?" },
            { 738219558, "So Johedy was right." },
            { 738219559, "Your killing Sila has provoked a response from Prav." },
            { 738219560, "Are you blaming me for this!?" },
            { 738219561, "This is not my fault!" },
            { 738219562, "No. You did what was necessary." },
            { 738219563, "How were you supposed to predict such a response?" },
            { 738219564, "Just when you think things might finally get less shitty..." },
            { 738219565, "Wait—a minute ago, they were..." },
            { 738219566, "People." },
            { 738219567, "And now they're..." },
            { 738219568, "This is awful. This is fucking awful!" },
            { 738219569, "There's nothing you can do now! Just put them out of their misery!" },
            { 738219570, "What? No, I can't!" },
            { 738219571, "You have to!" },
            { 738219572, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219573, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219574, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219575, "Get out of the Break and head for the upper city!" },
            { 738219576, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219577, "You're wounded." },
            { 738219578, "No shit." },
            { 738219579, "Thank goodness." },
            { 738219580, "It looks like we're clear of the Break." },
            { 738219581, "Stay strong, Frey." },
            { 738219582, "I'm okay. I think. I'm just...tired." },
            { 738219583, "The upper city isn't far now." },
            { 738219584, "We shouldn't have to deal with any more Breakborn." },
            { 738219585, "These poor people..." },
            { 738219586, "It took them completely by surprise." },
            { 738219587, "No one could have predicted this." },
            { 738219588, "I'm exhausted..." },
            { 738219589, "Keep going." },
            { 738219591, "Frey! Tanta's mercy!" },
            { 738219592, "You're badly hurt." },
            { 738219593, "There were so many of them... They came so fast..." },
            { 738219594, "This destruction is because of you, demon!" },
            { 738219595, "The Tantas were fucking this place up long before I got here." },
            { 738219596, "Your lies and treachery know no limits." },
            { 738219597, "I should kill you here and now!" },
            { 738219598, "This is not the time or place, Jennesh." },
            { 738219599, "I will do what we should have done the day this curse was visited upon us!" },
            { 738219600, "Out of my way!" },
            { 738219601, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738219602, "Unhand me!" },
            { 738219603, "Stop this foolishness now!" },
            { 738219604, "This is from the ballow." },
            { 738219605, "It will soothe the people's pain." },
            { 738219606, "It won't reverse the damage, but it will stop the spread." },
            { 738219607, "Jennesh, you've crossed the line." },
            { 738219608, "Now is the time to be pulling together, not threatening each other with knives!" },
            { 738219609, "Councilwoman Bellette, are you going to let this stand?" },
            { 738219610, "No." },
            { 738219611, "Jennesh, your behavior has brought disgrace upon this council." },
            { 738219612, "As of this moment, I am relieving you of your seat." },
            { 738219613, "Take him." },
            { 738219614, "You mark my words. One day you will see I was right." },
            { 738219615, "She is a demon, I tell you! No good will come of this! None!" },
            { 738219616, "I told you there would be repercussions." },
            { 738219617, "But you're not done yet." },
            { 738219618, "Before you came, the people had resigned themselves to their fate." },
            { 738219619, "Cowering in fear of the Tantas... Held captive by their madness." },
            { 738219620, "But now, because of you, they're starting to think they might just stand a chance." },
            { 738219621, "What are you saying, Jo?" },
            { 738219622, "I'm saying you need to kill the other Tantas." },
            { 738219623, "End this once and for all." },
            { 738219624, "What?" },
            { 738219625, "The wound cannot begin to heal until the bleeding stops." },
            { 738219626, "No, that's...that's straight-up murder. I'm not killing any...anyone else!" },
            { 738219627, "Then what do you propose to do about this?" },
            { 738219628, "I...I don't know..." },
            { 738219629, "This is not my fight!" },
            { 738219630, "Ah! Awake at last!" },
            { 738219631, "I was starting to go out of my mind with no one to talk to." },
            { 738219632, "Believe me, I'd much rather stay in bed." },
            { 738219633, "So? What's our next step?" },
            { 738219634, "Find Breakbob and peace the fuck out." },
            { 738219635, "Save your strength." },
            { 738219636, "My father and Councilman Treahy are seeking a source of more ballow mist." },
            { 738219637, "We must be patient." },
            { 738219638, "Didn't you say you were going to find Bob?" },
            { 738219639, "Are you sure you want to leave the city now?" },
            { 738219640, "He can't die. He's my only hope." },
            { 738219641, "Well, if it's Avoalet you're looking for, I believe it's south of here." },
            { 738219642, "Shall we?" },
            { 738219643, "You hear that?" },
            { 738219644, "The cries of the turned." },
            { 738219645, "And this was all caused by Prav?" },
            { 738219646, "I believe so." },
            { 738219647, "You know, what Johedy said is right." },
            { 738219648, "You're the only one who can—" },
            { 738219649, "No! Absolutely not." },
            { 738219650, "I am not killing another one." },
            { 738219652, "I will not be responsible for more pain." },
            { 738219653, "I'm just saying—" },
            { 738219654, "No. We're done here." },
            { 738219655, "Are you still irritated with me?" },
            { 738219656, "I'll take that as a yes." },
            { 738219657, "Sorry. I didn't mean to strike a nerve." },
            { 738219658, "It's just that you clearly care about the people here." },
            { 738219659, "Well—some of them, at least." },
            { 738219660, "I didn't want you going back to New York with any regrets." },
            { 738219661, "That's even if I get the chance to. If Breakbob doesn't make it, then..." },
            { 738219662, "Indeed. That is a complication." },
            { 738219663, "What's a \"rap sheet\"?" },
            { 738219664, "'Scuse me?" },
            { 738219665, "A \"rap sheet.\" You said it was one of the two things you had." },
            { 738219666, "It's... Well... I did some things that were against the law." },
            { 738219667, "But I had to do them to survive." },
            { 738219668, "I see." },
            { 738219669, "You know, Tanta Prav set the moral code for all of Athia." },
            { 738219670, "She was known for her infallible sense of justice." },
            { 738219671, "Her ability to find a fitting punishment for any crime." },
            { 738219672, "Ah, yeah. Justice. I see." },
            { 738219673, "An eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth." },
            { 738219674, "Precisely!" },
            { 738219675, "She loved taking body parts when someone was guilty of a crime." },
            { 738219676, "What? No, wait, I didn't mean literally!" },
            { 738219677, "If someone was tried and convicted of stealing, it was, \"Off with their hands!\"" },
            { 738219678, "Well, I definitely would have lost a few limbs for my offenses." },
            { 738219679, "Goodness. How many are we talking about?" },
            { 738219680, "More than I'd like to admit. Let's leave it at that." },
            { 738219681, "You know, the smell of ballow resin reminds me of the pancakes one of my foster moms used to make." },
            { 738219682, "What is a \"foster mom\"?" },
            { 738219683, "It's someone who takes you in when you don't have a real mom or dad around." },
            { 738219684, "I see..." },
            { 738219685, "And a lot of the time they don't really care about you." },
            { 738219686, "But there was this one... Eva." },
            { 738219687, "She was nice. Made me tasty pancakes, smothered in syrup." },
            { 738219688, "She was the one who got me into reading." },
            { 738219689, "What happened to her?" },
            { 738219690, "She got married and had her own family." },
            { 738219691, "I'm sorry..." },
            { 738219692, "But never mind that now. Let's go find us some ballow trees." },
            { 738219693, "They're Prav's minions. And they don't look like they're keen to let us through." },
            { 738219694, "Guess we're just gonna have to be extra persuasive." },
            { 738219695, "Oh boy. Don't tell me—this one's even worse than the rest?" },
            { 738219696, "I'm afraid so. You might want to keep an eye on those scales." },
            { 738219697, "Yeah, not getting a good feeling about this..." },
            { 738219698, "Never seen so many trees..." },
            { 738219699, "Yes. Avoalet's certainly a more green and pleasant land than Praenost." },
            { 738219700, "But the Break's just as bad here, right?" },
            { 738219701, "I'm afraid so. And it only gets worse from here..." },
            { 738219702, "I think we're here." },
            { 738219703, "And surprise, surprise, this place is just as fucked up as the last realm we visited." },
            { 738219704, "Well, we just need to find some ballow trees and collect their resin, and then we can leave." },
            { 738219705, "But how do we know which are the right ones?" },
            { 738219706, "You have a point. The councilman said that some might still have resin to offer. But he didn't say which ones." },
            { 738219707, "Well, they probably don't look as worn out as the one they drained back in Cipal, right?" },
            { 738219708, "It's a start. C'mon. Let's scout out some sap. Can't be that hard." },
            { 738219716, "Shit. No luck." },
            { 738219717, "\"Can't be that hard,\" she says..." },
            { 738219718, "Shut the fuck up for a second." },
            { 738219719, "Okay, think... The tree in Cipal was all dried up, right?" },
            { 738219720, "So the resiny ones probably won't look like that..." },
            { 738219721, "Well, all I see is trunks, leaves, blue bits..." },
            { 738219722, "Wait. Didn't Bob say something about blue? Something, uh..." },
            { 738219723, "\"It's the hue of blue, and the bloomers too.\"" },
            { 738219724, "That was his catchphrase, right? Maybe it's a clue!" },
            { 738219725, "Or maybe it was the meaningless rambling of a madman..." },
            { 738219735, "Head up this hill. See what you can see." },
            { 738219736, "Up the hill, like Jack and Jill." },
            { 738219737, "Jack...and Jill?" },
            { 738219738, "Oh, never mind. Whoever that might be, just get yourself up there." },
            { 738219739, "You know what? Forget it." },
            { 738219741, "Oh, whoa! What the fuck happened to this place?" },
            { 738219742, "Looks like they had a huge earthquake and then...gravity lost its shit." },
            { 738219743, "This is what happens when a Tanta's power goes haywire." },
            { 738219744, "Be prepared for even more twisted terrain ahead." },
            { 738219745, "As if I needed any more reasons to steer clear of this woman..." },
            { 738219755, "This one's resined out too." },
            { 738219757, "Whoa! What the fuck?" },
            { 738219758, "The territorial instinct really is a marvel." },
            { 738219759, "Great. This is just what we need." },
            { 738219762, "No resin in this tree, either." },
            { 738219763, "Is there something in Bob's rhyme we're missing?" },
            { 738219764, "\"It's the hue of blue, and the bloomers too...\"" },
            { 738219765, "The bloomers..." },
            { 738219766, "Wait... I think he means flowers." },
            { 738219767, "So not just the blue veins, but flowers as well!" },
            { 738219768, "I...suppose that could be it..." },
            { 738219769, "That, or the old loon's rubbing off on you." },
            { 738219770, "Only one way to find out!" },
            { 738219771, "Whoa. Something turned these houses inside out." },
            { 738219772, "Never mind Prav's sense of justice—what about the people who lived here? They oughta sue her ass!" },
            { 738219773, "Ought to...what her what?" },
            { 738219784, "Whoa. It's growing sideways." },
            { 738219785, "Incredible how life can thrive no matter where it finds itself, no?" },
            { 738219786, "Very deep, Cuff." },
            { 738219787, "And a tree that tenacious is sure to be overflowing with resin." },
            { 738219804, "They have offered an alternative to fighting..." },
            { 738219805, "You could turn yourself in." },
            { 738219806, "Hard pass!" },
            { 738219807, "I mean, of course, \"request an audience.\"" },
            { 738219808, "I am not requesting an audience with someone who enjoys dismembering people!" },
            { 738219809, "Then you'll have to keep fighting." },
            { 738219810, "They're only giving as good as they get." },
            { 738219811, "I'm trying to de-escalate and defuse." },
            { 738219812, "Come to a place of nonviolence!" },
            { 738219813, "Wow. How very zen of you." },
            { 738219814, "Well, let me tell you, I've come to a place of \"me or them.\"" },
            { 738219815, "And I pick me." },
            { 738219816, "Suit yourself." },
            { 738219817, "We're surrounded." },
            { 738219818, "How many of them are there?" },
            { 738219819, "What the hell was all that shit about back there?" },
            { 738219820, "What \"shit\"?" },
            { 738219821, "The shit about surrendering myself to them?" },
            { 738219822, "It was distracting, and it almost got me killed!" },
            { 738219823, "That was not my intention." },
            { 738219824, "Oh, so what was your intention?" },
            { 738219825, "Why the hell do you want me to \"request an audience\" with Prav?" },
            { 738219826, "The Tantas rarely leave their throne rooms." },
            { 738219827, "I was thinking that if you give yourself up, it might draw her out." },
            { 738219828, "And once she's broken cover—" },
            { 738219829, "You better not say, \"Then you kill her.\"" },
            { 738219830, "Then you kill her." },
            { 738219831, "You know this is the way to Prav's castle, don't you?" },
            { 738219832, "Can I take this to mean you've made up your mind to kill her?" },
            { 738219833, "No, you fucking can't." },
            { 738219834, "I'm grabbing some more resin, then I'm heading back to the city. That's it." },
            { 738219835, "Damn, look at the size of that ballow tree!" },
            { 738219836, "That bad boy'd make the record books for sure!" },
            { 738219837, "\"Bad boy\"?" },
            { 738219838, "Never mind. Let's just say I think we're good for resin." },
            { 738219839, "There we go. That should be enough." },
            { 738219840, "Not what I was expecting..." },
            { 738219841, "Anything you want to tell me about Prav before I face her?" },
            { 738219842, "Prav is the arbiter of truth." },
            { 738219843, "There's no use lying to her. She can see through any falsehood." },
            { 738219844, "So you're saying her superpower is a law degree and a bullshit radar?" },
            { 738219845, "No. It's much more than that. She can do...other things as well." },
            { 738219846, "\"Other things,\" huh?" },
            { 738219847, "Well, that's clear as mud. Thanks." },
            { 738219848, "If you seek answers, there may still be a way to find them." },
            { 738219849, "How so?" },
            { 738219850, "Our friend Breakbob worked closely with Tanta Cinta once upon a time." },
            { 738219851, "He may hold the key to unlocking your past." },
            { 738219852, "There's still time to make it back to Cipal with the ballow resin." },
            { 738219853, "Yeah... Okay." },
            { 738219854, "We must hurry if you want to save the old man—and the others who've been ravaged by the Break." },
            { 738219855, "Alright. Let's get the hell out of here and head back to Cipal." },
            { 738219924, "Are you alright?" },
            { 738219925, "Got a lot on my mind." },
            { 738219926, "Still can't stop thinking about what Prav said..." },
            { 738219927, "None of this makes sense." },
            { 738219928, "My mother, who happens to be a powerful sorceress, left me by the side of the road in another dimension?" },
            { 738219929, "I can't pretend to understand the motives of the mad." },
            { 738219930, "I will say there was plenty of trouble brewing between the Tantas at the time." },
            { 738219931, "They were already well along the road to ruin." },
            { 738219932, "It's just so messed up..." },
            { 738219933, "Perhaps if we were to find her, she might help you understand it all." },
            { 738219934, "No, fuck that. There is no way I want to meet her." },
            { 738219935, "Understandable...I suppose." },
            { 738219936, "Anyway, at least we have an idea now of why the Break doesn't affect you like it does everyone else." },
            { 738219937, "But does that mean I'll eventually go crazy too?" },
            { 738219938, "Interesting question...and one that I am sure will be answered in time." },
            { 738219939, "Great. You mean the only way we find out is when I start losing my mind?" },
            { 738219940, "Precisely." },
            { 738219941, "Well, that's comforting." },
            { 738219942, "Did you have an alternative method in mind?" },
            { 738219943, "Look, just let me know if I start acting weird, okay?" },
            { 738219944, "With pleasure." },
            { 738219945, "Although your behavior does tend toward the eccentric most of the time..." },
            { 738219946, "I do hope I'll be able to tell." },
            { 738219947, "Very helpful, Cuff. Very helpful." },
            { 738219948, "I'm starting to feel like finding you in that shop was no coincidence." },
            { 738219949, "You think higher powers were at work?" },
            { 738219950, "Well, I'm not one for fairy tales or religion or anything like that." },
            { 738219951, "But for some reason...I feel like I was destined to meet you, Cuff." },
            { 738219955, "And what if I am a Tanta's daughter? How am I supposed to tell everybody?" },
            { 738219956, "Might I suggest that you don't?" },
            { 738219957, "The people have turned against the Tantas." },
            { 738219958, "I'm not sure they'd be overjoyed to discover that you're part of the family." },
            { 738219976, "You could have gone a little easier on her." },
            { 738219977, "Stay out of it." },
            { 738219978, "Her father just—" },
            { 738219979, "Yes, I know what happened!" },
            { 738219980, "You need to pull yourself together." },
            { 738219981, "Don't tell me what to do!" },
            { 738219982, "I am sick of killing myself for everybody else!" },
            { 738219983, "Why can't I just do what I want for once?" },
            { 738219984, "You are an Athian. You should want what they want." },
            { 738219985, "Fuck no!" },
            { 738219986, "I may have been born here, but I am a New Yorker through and through, asshole, and there is no place like home!" },
            { 738219987, "I am not giving up. I am finding a way out of here." },
            { 738219988, "There's gotta be something in those archives." },
            { 738219989, "Frey, please. If we could just take a moment—" },
            { 738219990, "No more moments. No more from you." },
            { 738219991, "There must be more about the torana in the archives. I just need to find it." },
            { 738219992, "Doesn't need to be much..." },
            { 738219993, "Just some kind of hint. Something to tell me where to look next..." },
            { 738219994, "To Junoon then?" },
            { 738219995, "Guess we don't have much choice." },
            { 738219996, "Jo was right. Cinta must know about the toranas." },
            { 738219997, "I'll either make her send me back to New York, or...one of us will kill the other." },
            { 738219998, "Whatever happens, this fucking saga will be over." },
            { 738219999, "I'm not so sure that's a good idea." },
            { 738220000, "Why don't we go and visit Tanta Olas in Visoria first instead?" },
            { 738220001, "We can end her madness and fortify ourselves with her power before facing your mother." },
            { 738220002, "This is not a democracy. You don't get a vote." },
            { 738220003, "Oh, don't I? Remember, \"Where thou goest, there go I\"?" },
            { 738220004, "If I'm lucky, I get back to New York. You go with me that far." },
            { 738220005, "Then I find someone to cut you off, and I sell you to a jeweler." },
            { 738220006, "That is unusually cold." },
            { 738220007, "Welcome to the real Frey." },
            { 738220008, "I don't believe that." },
            { 738220009, "You fucking better." },
            { 738220012, "I keep wondering how Alice was so sure at the end that the whole thing was a dream." },
            { 738220013, "What if Wonderland was the part that was real?" },
            { 738220014, "Oh, nice. The new one's out today." },
            { 738220015, "Should grab one on the way home." },
            { 738220016, "Huh. Everything's so neat." },
            { 738220017, "Could Homer finally be pulling her weight around here?" },
            { 738220018, "My favorite kicks." },
            { 738220019, "As always, I could stare at you guys all day." },
            { 738220020, "Shit. Never made it to the gym." },
            { 738220021, "Ah well. I'll go tomorrow." },
            { 738220022, "I hope her interview goes well." },
            { 738220023, "Alright, let's roll." },
            { 738220024, "Hey, Frey!" },
            { 738220025, "Thanks for fixing that light switch the other day!" },
            { 738220026, "Don't worry about it. It was nothing." },
            { 738220027, "I'll bring you over some strudel when you get back." },
            { 738220028, "It's the least I can do." },
            { 738220029, "Aw, thank you." },
            { 738220031, "Where you headed, kiddo?" },
            { 738220032, "I'm going out to grab a coffee." },
            { 738220034, "Nice. Have a good one!" },
            { 738220035, "You too!" },
            { 738220036, "What are you guys plotting?" },
            { 738220037, "Huh?" },
            { 738220038, "Oh shit, it's Frey." },
            { 738220039, "You two really need to start getting your act together. You know that?" },
            { 738220040, "We won't be causing any more trouble, we promise." },
            { 738220041, "Fuck it. Let's go, Chrissy." },
            { 738220042, "Be safe, girls!" },
            { 738220043, "Oh, shoot. I'm late." },
            { 738220044, "I gotta hurry." },
            { 738220057, "Is she gone?" },
            { 738220058, "No, I can still feel her presence." },
            { 738220059, "We just can't see her. Be careful, Frey." },
            { 738220060, "I'll try. But we need to get the fuck out of this shithole." },
            { 738220061, "Alright, point me to the exit. I just want out of this illusion!" },
            { 738220062, "Unfortunately, it's not quite that simple." },
            { 738220063, "This is Olas's world. We have no choice but to play by her rules." },
            { 738220064, "Just keep moving for now. We'll work it out as we go along." },
            { 738220065, "Copy that." },
            { 738220066, "There's some kind of...invisible wall here." },
            { 738220067, "Seems she doesn't want us going this way..." },
            { 738220068, "What's with the lamp?" },
            { 738220069, "This isn't from the New York I know." },
            { 738220070, "If anything seems out of place, it's probably a hint at what's behind the illusion." },
            { 738220071, "They all disappeared when I broke the lamp..." },
            { 738220072, "It must have been amplifying her illusory powers somehow..." },
            { 738220073, "Do you really think a head-on approach is wise?" },
            { 738220074, "That's quite a few foes to be facing at once." },
            { 738220075, "You're right. Guess we gotta find a different route." },
            { 738220076, "Why don't we take to the rooftops?" },
            { 738220077, "Good idea." },
            { 738220078, "There's so many of them..." },
            { 738220079, "Don't waste time fighting them all." },
            { 738220082, "Motherfuckers!" },
            { 738220083, "They keep coming at me from above!" },
            { 738220090, "This one looks stronger than the others." },
            { 738220091, "Then you'll just have to show it we're not to be messed with." },
            { 738220092, "Exactly what I was thinking." },
            { 738220093, "I am on a roll right now!" },
            { 738220095, "Yeah, but let's not forget it—this city is my turf." },
            { 738220096, "We're the ones with the advantage here." },
            { 738220097, "Did you hear something?" },
            { 738220098, "I believe it came from near the cafe." },
            { 738220099, "Maybe the alley?" },
            { 738220100, "I've been here before. In more ways than one." },
            { 738220101, "A memory of the good old days in New York?" },
            { 738220102, "Something like that. Call it déjà vu." },
            { 738220103, "Except this time...I can fight back." },
            { 738220104, "Imagine if I had magic before..." },
            { 738220105, "Keen to revisit the past?" },
            { 738220106, "Nah, not exactly. Was just thinking, that's all." },
            { 738220107, "Hindsight's a beautiful thing." },
            { 738220108, "I see..." },
            { 738220130, "I had so much hope for her..." },
            { 738220131, "Good child... So I thought. But I was wrong..." },
            { 738220132, "We all had hope." },
            { 738220133, "Such a disappointment." },
            { 738220134, "She seemed like she wanted to do it!" },
            { 738220135, "She was hesitant, but she was taking our lead..." },
            { 738220136, "She seemed brave." },
            { 738220137, "Very brave, but...she wasn't." },
            { 738220138, "Only so long as favors were met." },
            { 738220139, "I thought she would be brave enough to do this, but..." },
            { 738220140, "She's too selfish to finish it." },
            { 738220141, "So...many lives..." },
            { 738220142, "Could have been saved, but...so many lives were lost." },
            { 738220143, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738220144, "Tanta's blessings!" },
            { 738220145, "I... What happened?" },
            { 738220146, "You collapsed." },
            { 738220147, "Do you mind if I examine your wound?" },
            { 738220148, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738220149, "Be honest with me. Was this place always this bad, or did I bring this shitstorm with me?" },
            { 738220150, "Athia was on the path to ruin long before your arrival." },
            { 738220151, "This latest tragedy was decades in the making." },
            { 738220152, "Me being here isn't helping." },
            { 738220153, "Wherever I go, trouble follows." },
            { 738220154, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738220155, "Frey...don't say such things." },
            { 738220156, "You deserve more kindness than you've been shown." },
            { 738220157, "More than you show yourself..." },
            { 738220158, "You're healing nicely, but please, Frey..." },
            { 738220159, "Look after yourself." },
            { 738220160, "Hey! Bob!" },
            { 738220161, "Hey. Look, I, uh...I really need to get vooshed back. Like, yesterday." },
            { 738220162, "Can you show me how to use those torana things?" },
            { 738220163, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738220164, "Robian!" },
            { 738220165, "Whoa, hey! Easy, dude!" },
            { 738220166, "You must rest, my friend." },
            { 738220167, "You don't look so good. You okay?" },
            { 738220168, "The test of time hits one hard..." },
            { 738220169, "As the years flitter-flutter..." },
            { 738220170, "I fear his condition is worsening." },
            { 738220171, "Bob, you've gotta keep it together." },
            { 738220172, "Remember." },
            { 738220173, "It's the hue of blue, and the bloomers too." },
            { 738220174, "The Corruption's grip grows stronger with each day." },
            { 738220175, "I fear he has not long left." },
            { 738220176, "What? No, he can't give in to it now!" },
            { 738220177, "What about the ballow stuff?" },
            { 738220178, "It could certainly stabilize him. Stop it from spreading further." },
            { 738220179, "Well then, let's go get some more of it, like—" },
            { 738220180, "It's no use." },
            { 738220181, "Whatever we had, we used in the aftermath of last night's massacre." },
            { 738220182, "We came here in search of more." },
            { 738220183, "Alas, not a drop remains." },
            { 738220184, "Shit! He can't die! Auden needs him. I need him." },
            { 738220185, "Shit, Athia needs him!" },
            { 738220186, "There's gotta be more!" },
            { 738220187, "Ballow trees come originally from Avoalet." },
            { 738220188, "Perhaps you will find more there." },
            { 738220189, "Great. Show me where. I'll go get it." },
            { 738220190, "You must make for the castle town." },
            { 738220191, "Look for more trees like this one." },
            { 738220197, "What exactly are you doing?" },
            { 738220198, "Uh... Practicing." },
            { 738220199, "You do know there's no one here to fight, don't you?" },
            { 738220200, "I do indeed, my good sir!" },
            { 738220201, "What a complete and utter waste of energy." },
            { 738220202, "Just making sure everything's in working order." },
            { 738220203, "Ooh, you see that? Nice, huh?" },
            { 738220204, "Yes, if entirely pointless..." },
            { 738220205, "Just not finding my flow, you know?" },
            { 738220206, "Perhaps if you were to try it on an, ooh I don't know, an actual enemy?" },
            { 738220207, "Are you...seeing something I'm not?" },
            { 738220208, "No, just visualizing, you know? Ninja training?" },
            { 738220209, "Your skills are coming along." },
            { 738220210, "Guess so, huh?" },
            { 738220211, "I'm getting a feel for this." },
            { 738220212, "You certainly seem to be, yes." },
            { 738220213, "Ooh... Feeling kinda fresh!" },
            { 738220214, "Quick fight to see what's new?" },
            { 738220215, "I'm getting to be one tough customer." },
            { 738220216, "I'd say you're becoming reasonably deadly, yes." },
            { 738220217, "I'm kind of a spell expert at this point, no?" },
            { 738220218, "Please don't let it go to your head..." },
            { 738220219, "You're looking a little more...accomplished all of a sudden." },
            { 738220220, "And feeling it too!" },
            { 738220229, "DRAGON" },
            { 738220231, "Try this for size!" },
            { 738220232, "Ooh, this one!" },
            { 738220233, "Time for my favorite!" },
            { 738220234, "Might wanna run!" },
            { 738220235, "My ace in the hole!" },
            { 738220236, "This'll do it!" },
            { 738220237, "Thank you, Sila!" },
            { 738220238, "Smokin'!" },
            { 738220239, "Prav says hey!" },
            { 738220240, "Hated the Tanta, LOVE her spells!" },
            { 738220241, "Ohoho, Olas!" },
            { 738220242, "Yeah, this one's freaky." },
            { 738220243, "Sorry!" },
            { 738220244, "And STAY back!" },
            { 738220245, "That's close enough!" },
            { 738220246, "Goodnight!" },
            { 738220247, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738220248, "This should come in handy." },
            { 738220249, "Ooh, gross..." },
            { 738220250, "It's not much but...you never know." },
            { 738220251, "Hm. Might as well hold on to this." },
            { 738220252, "Ooh! Nice find!" },
            { 738220253, "That's quite a find." },
            { 738220254, "Whoa, look at this!" },
            { 738220255, "Ooh, treasure!" },
            { 738220256, "Whatever you just picked up is very powerful indeed." },
            { 738220257, "Huh. What's this...?" },
            { 738220258, "Might as well pocket this..." },
            { 738220259, "Did you find something?" },
            { 738220260, "Finders keepers!" },
            { 738220261, "I can use this." },
            { 738220262, "That's a good find." },
            { 738220263, "Actual treasure!" },
            { 738220264, "I can make something seriously good with this!" },
            { 738220265, "Quite the lucky find indeed!" },
            { 738220266, "You're mine!" },
            { 738220267, "DIE!" },
            { 738220378, "You need to tailor your approach!" },
            { 738220379, "Whatever helps get this over with." },
            { 738220380, "Think before you act! Which ability will work best?" },
            { 738220381, "I'm thinking, I'm thinking!" },
            { 738220382, "You know which spell to use, correct?" },
            { 738220383, "Yes! So shut up!" },
            { 738220384, "All set?" },
            { 738220385, "All set!" },
            { 738220386, "Exploit your enemy's every weakness!" },
            { 738220387, "Have you finally gone full bad guy?" },
            { 738220388, "This is yours to lose now, Frey!" },
            { 738220389, "Why did you have to say it like that!?" },
            { 738220391, "Think I might be getting a taste for this stuff." },
            { 738220392, "There are worse habits, I suppose." },
            { 738220393, "Might be better to keep your powder dry for the real thing." },
            { 738220395, "Kind of a nice view." },
            { 738220396, "I wasn't aware that you knew what one of those was." },
            { 738220397, "Now you're just projecting." },
            { 738220398, "If it wasn't for the bad guys, this'd be a pretty nice spot." },
            { 738220399, "It might be rather dull without them, don't you think?" },
            { 738220400, "I most definitely do not." },
            { 738220401, "Look, Frey..." },
            { 738220402, "Wow. Yeah, that's quite a view." },
            { 738220403, "No, I mean look where you're going." },
            { 738220404, "Well, this is rather pleasant." },
            { 738220405, "You like it up high, huh?" },
            { 738220406, "Oh, gosh, yes. Who wants to be scrabbling around down there in the dirt?" },
            { 738220407, "Makes you feel kinda free..." },
            { 738220408, "Nothing could make me feel free." },
            { 738220409, "Man, you are just so depressing." },
            { 738220410, "Feels a lot bigger than New York..." },
            { 738220411, "Is it really so small?" },
            { 738220412, "Not small, just...cramped. You wouldn't get it." },
            { 738220503, "That was some real picture-postcard shit right there." },
            { 738220504, "Did you manage to scout out our next destination?" },
            { 738220505, "Nope. But I sure hope you did!" },
            { 738220506, "Are we leaving already?" },
            { 738220507, "What, did you wanna stick around forever?" },
            { 738220508, "Well, no, but...never mind." },
            { 738220509, "Alright, let's head down." },
            { 738220510, "Don't fall, will you?" },
            { 738220511, "Uh, not by choice." },
            { 738220512, "Now that was a sight for sore eyes." },
            { 738220513, "Yeah. Would've made a hell of a picture." },
            { 738220514, "They're never as good as the real thing though, are they?" },
            { 738220515, "Whew, we were pretty high up back there." },
            { 738220516, "Yes. A long climb, and a very short fall." },
            { 738220517, "Always with the gloomy shit..." },
            { 738220518, "Quite the heady height, eh?" },
            { 738220519, "Yeah. Felt like I was way up in the clouds." },
            { 738220520, "Other than the occasional bird, you might be the only one ever to have enjoyed that particular vista." },
            { 738220565, "Head to Sila's Castle" },
            { 738220570, "You know, I think you might be ready to—" },
            { 738220571, "Right? Wanna try and take this fucker down?" },
            { 738220572, "So sad that we're irreversibly attached..." },
            { 738220573, "I don't get it. So you can stretch and move around like that, but you can't just...let go of me?" },
            { 738220574, "How can I put this... The part of me that's attached to you is very firmly attached indeed." },
            { 738220575, "There's such a thing as relying on magic too much, you know." },
            { 738220576, "Says a guy who's basically a bunch of metal held together by the stuff." },
            { 738220577, "You know, it's not the ability to use magic that matters. It's what you do with it." },
            { 738220578, "Yeah, thanks. Kinda guessed that already." },
            { 738220579, "Good. Then I won't need to tell you again." },
            { 738220580, "Meh. Not bad, I guess." },
            { 738220581, "Very nice." },
            { 738220582, "If you say so." },
            { 738220583, "Did I...do it right?" },
            { 738220584, "Could be a little neater..." },
            { 738220585, "Ah, gimme a break." },
            { 738220586, "Does that look good?" },
            { 738220587, "Good enough to warrant the fuss of putting it on? Probably not." },
            { 738220588, "Hey, as long as it works." },
            { 738220589, "I think you might be getting the hang of that." },
            { 738220590, "Feel like I need to get even more creative with it though, you know?" },
            { 738220591, "You might have slightly more important things to worry about..." },
            { 738220592, "I'm...kinda starting to dig this." },
            { 738220593, "I can't imagine why." },
            { 738220594, "Maybe if I did some on you, you'd get it?" },
            { 738220595, "Try not to get any on me, won't you?" },
            { 738220596, "Ah c'mon, it'd probably rub right off." },
            { 738220597, "Yes, it's the \"probably\" part I worry about..." },
            { 738220598, "You're really putting a lot into that." },
            { 738220599, "What can I say? Got a new hobby." },
            { 738220600, "Well, as long as you don't forget what we're actually supposed to be doing." },
            { 738220601, "Wonder what this one'll do..." },
            { 738220602, "Little fight to find out, perhaps?" },
            { 738220603, "Yeah, good idea." },
            { 738220604, "This design's pretty crazy, right?" },
            { 738220605, "Yes. It feels...significant somehow. No idea how, exactly." },
            { 738220606, "Great. Uh, thanks for the contribution?" },
            { 738220607, "Whoa! I am good at this!" },
            { 738220608, "Thinking of taking it up professionally?" },
            { 738220609, "Hey, the fancier the design, the better the effect, right?" },
            { 738220610, "I've got a very good feeling about this one." },
            { 738220611, "Good for you. Not my field of expertise, sadly." },
            { 738220612, "I could talk you through the basics?" },
            { 738220613, "...Maybe later." },
            { 738220614, "That's a rather unique design." },
            { 738220615, "Right? I'm getting to be quite the artist." },
            { 738220616, "You may have to seek enthusiastic agreement on that elsewhere." },
            { 738220617, "Did you mean to do them differently on each hand?" },
            { 738220618, "Yeah. It's a look, okay?" },
            { 738220619, "...I'll take your word for that." },
            { 738220620, "Is that a favorite of yours?" },
            { 738220621, "Yeah, you could say that." },
            { 738220623, "Yeah, that looks pretty good..." },
            { 738220624, "You've done that one before." },
            { 738220625, "Yeah. I like it. Is that a crime?" },
            { 738220626, "Ooh, yes. Very evocative." },
            { 738220627, "Right? Feels like it must have some kind of...hidden meaning, you know?" },
            { 738220628, "How uncharacteristically earnest of you to say so." },
            { 738220629, "Wonder if I could paint you a nice new color, Cuff..." },
            { 738220630, "If that's supposed to be a joke, it's not a very funny one." },
            { 738220632, "So? Feeling any different?" },
            { 738220633, "A little, yeah. Time for a test drive!" },
            { 738220635, "Is that not a little bit of a waste of valuable resources?" },
            { 738220636, "What? This right here is my masterpiece!" },
            { 738220638, "Boom! Done!" },
            { 738220639, "Hmm. Not at all bad..." },
            { 738220641, "I don't think I've ever seen you so engaged." },
            { 738220642, "Huh? Oh. I just do this for practical reasons, you know?" },
            { 738220643, "Of course you do. Hence the manic glint in your eye." },
            { 738220644, "Think I'm happy never getting comfortable with that, thanks." },
            { 738220645, "Well, that felt absolutely fantastic!" },
            { 738220646, "Uh... You okay?" },
            { 738220647, "Our magic's better than your magic!" },
            { 738220648, "Hah! Yeah!" },
            { 738220649, "You're outta here!" },
            { 738220650, "That's what comes of picking the wrong side." },
            { 738220651, "If you like." },
            { 738220652, "Oh, you want me to make things more interesting for ya?" },
            { 738220653, "Meh. Maybe a little." },
            { 738220654, "Only inasmuch as I'm done for if you get yourself killed." },
            { 738220655, "Nah, I'm good. It's not like I'm in training for the world title." },
            { 738220656, "...Just shut up and let me take this in." },
            { 738220658, "Wonder where he lost...whatever it was." },
            { 738220659, "Well, he did get in a bit of a scuffle with those guards..." },
            { 738220660, "What's the matter, Bob?" },
            { 738220661, "It was here, I know it was. Here and then it disappeared. Yes..." },
            { 738220662, "It was no small thing. Not to me. No bauble. No, and certainly no trifle." },
            { 738220663, "So he's...lost something important? Sorry, my gibberish is patchy." },
            { 738220664, "Yeah, seems like it." },
            { 738220665, "Guess we better help him find it." },
            { 738220666, "What? Why?" },
            { 738220667, "Never know—might have something to do with the torana." },
            { 738220668, "I suppose... Just don't forget what you're actually meant to be doing." },
            { 738220669, "People sure love Bob, huh?" },
            { 738220670, "You looking for something?" },
            { 738220671, "And who do we have here, hm?" },
            { 738220672, "Hey. You seen Robian around?" },
            { 738220673, "Robian? Ah, Master Keen, you mean? Sorry, young lady." },
            { 738220674, "Oh, no worries. Thanks anyway." },
            { 738220675, "No luck there..." },
            { 738220676, "Seems the old man still commands a fair amount of respect even now." },
            { 738220677, "Yeah. Guess he's given a lot for these people." },
            { 738220679, "Hey. You're one of the guards from before, right?" },
            { 738220680, "Hm? Oh. You're the one who was with Auden." },
            { 738220681, "Yeah. So Bob—I mean, Robian—he didn't drop anything when you were...restraining him, did he?" },
            { 738220682, "Not that I remember." },
            { 738220683, "I did see him coming this way from the upper city a little while back, though." },
            { 738220684, "Maybe someone he passed along the way saw something." },
            { 738220685, "Okay. Uh...thanks." },
            { 738220686, "Um, excuse me—miss!" },
            { 738220690, "Hey, Bob." },
            { 738220691, "Really? What more can the old loon possibly tell us?" },
            { 738220692, "Oh, hello. I have a question for you. A riddle? Yes, perhaps." },
            { 738220693, "Jog my memory—what means more to me than anything else in the entire world?" },
            { 738220694, "What means most to Bob?" },
            { 738220695, "Athia" },
            { 738220696, "The Ballow Mist" },
            { 738220697, "Auden" },
            { 738220698, "Hmm..." },
            { 738220699, "The protection of Athia is a concern, of course. A matter of most maximal importance." },
            { 738220700, "But our land will eventually be saved... At least, I think it will...won't it?" },
            { 738220701, "We'd better get going. For his sake as much as anyone's." },
            { 738220702, "Yes! Yes, that's right!" },
            { 738220703, "Audie is more important to me than anything! Well, except perhaps Calista. Family. Yes, family!" },
            { 738220704, "Thank you, Frey." },
            { 738220705, "Nothing to thank me for." },
            { 738220706, "I'll be back as soon as I've got that resin. Hang in there until then, okay?" },
            { 738220707, "I want you to have this." },
            { 738220708, "It is...a memory of a better time. Hold it close." },
            { 738220709, "Wow. I, uh...I will." },
            { 738220710, "Family, huh..." },
            { 738220711, "Still thinking about what the old man said?" },
            { 738220712, "Not really, just..." },
            { 738220713, "Guess I never really thought about how deep the whole family thing went for Bob until now..." },
            { 738220714, "We brought back the resin...but we still couldn't save him." },
            { 738220715, "There was nothing you could have done. And blaming yourself will get you exactly nowhere." },
            { 738220716, "I literally cannot do anything without fucking shit up!" },
            { 738220718, "Thanks again, Bob." },
            { 738220719, "I found a way home in the end, you know." },
            { 738220720, "But, uh...I'm gonna stick around and look after your home instead, if that's okay." },
            { 738220722, "Just how powerful is she?" },
            { 738220723, "Why did she come after me?" },
            { 738220724, "What was she like?" },
            { 738220725, "I've heard enough." },
            { 738220726, "She is the Tanta of Strength. Blessed with the power to fortify both mind and body." },
            { 738220727, "That sounds...tricky to deal with..." },
            { 738220728, "And her gifts do not end there. She is a leader under whose unflinching discipline whole armies cower." },
            { 738220729, "Her mere presence on the battlefield is enough to strike terror into the hearts of her enemies." },
            { 738220730, "Okay, I get it! She's one stone-cold badass bitch." },
            { 738220731, "You trespassed upon her realm. You are a threat, and as such, are not to be tolerated." },
            { 738220732, "Just because I walked over some imaginary line?" },
            { 738220733, "Shit. Shoulda brought a passport." },
            { 738220734, "There is no \"just\" when it comes to trespass on sacred ground, girl." },
            { 738220735, "Especially not when the ground in question belongs to one so powerful." },
            { 738220736, "It was your fault the city was attacked. Tanta Sila wished only to drive out the threat." },
            { 738220737, "And she clearly wasn't the only one..." },
            { 738220738, "She was hard on others. But no harder than she was on herself. Beneath that stern exterior lies a warmer heart." },
            { 738220739, "Her desire to protect the people of Athia—this is what drives her." },
            { 738220740, "\"Protect\"? Is that what you call smashing shit up and killing people?" },
            { 738220741, "What use is there in talking to one as corrupted as you?" },
            { 738220742, "Sorry I asked." },
            { 738220743, "Why do I even care who she is or who she used to be? She killed Olevia. That's all that matters." },
            { 738220744, "As long as you remain, the city remains in danger. Tanta Sila may yet be forced to destroy us all." },
            { 738220745, "You must go to her and be punished for your crimes." },
            { 738220746, "Oh, I'll go to her, alright. And when I find her, she's dead." },
            { 738220747, "What should I ask him about?" },
            { 738220748, "Ask about the Cognoscents' Guilds." },
            { 738220749, "Ask about Athia." },
            { 738220750, "It's too risky. Shut him up." },
            { 738220751, "Nothing." },
            { 738220752, "Why would you ask such a question?" },
            { 738220753, "Wait...you've been talking to Auden, haven't you? Honestly, that child..." },
            { 738220754, "I suppose it was only to be expected that she would inherit Robian's sense of justice and Calista's dauntless spirit..." },
            { 738220755, "You know her?" },
            { 738220756, "But of course. I, too, am a Cognoscent, just like her father. He and I are old friends." },
            { 738220757, "The Guilds were once great centers of learning. They hold many powerful secrets." },
            { 738220758, "You wish to know the history of our land?" },
            { 738220759, "Why, this is just what I was trying to teach those ungrateful children before they deserted me!" },
            { 738220760, "Where to begin? You know, at least, that there are four Tantas who watch over Athia?" },
            { 738220761, "They each established realms molded in their own image, over which they ruled as they saw fit." },
            { 738220762, "All was as they decreed it should be: the climate, the landscape, the means by which their people lived—" },
            { 738220763, "Yeah, that'll do, thanks." },
            { 738220764, "It's no wonder the children ran for the hills..." },
            { 738220765, "N-no, I—wait! I said I would not call the guards, and I meant it!" },
            { 738220766, "I wish to know more of you, that I might make an informed judgment of your character." },
            { 738220767, "My fellow Council members' wariness of you is to be understood." },
            { 738220768, "Bellette remains faithful to Tanta Prav, and Dax to Tanta Sila." },
            { 738220769, "So that's why they're all so damnably set in their ways..." },
            { 738220770, "But my memories of my own ruler, Tanta Olas, are...vague. I know not why, exactly." },
            { 738220771, "What would she have made of your appearance in our land, I wonder..." },
            { 738220772, "The answer to that question escapes me." },
            { 738220773, "I am a man of my word. I will not call the guard." },
            { 738220774, "But Cipal is not so big a city that you will escape detection forever." },
            { 738220775, "Promise me, at least, that you will make your escape with the minimum of violence." },
            { 738220776, "Can't have been too upset if it left you that." },
            { 738220777, "This is where we grieve our dead." },
            { 738220778, "Tanta Sila included." },
            { 738220786, "Are you alright? The poor creature was only trying to—" },
            { 738220787, "I don't care. It's not my problem anymore." },
            { 738220788, "Nothing here is. I am done with this place." },
            { 738220789, "The noble councilwoman would seem to have something of a grudge against you." },
            { 738220790, "But not so much of one that she can't be convinced to—" },
            { 738220791, "Didn't I tell you? This shit has nothing to do with me anymore!" },
            { 738220792, "The rebuilding of the city is progressing well." },
            { 738220793, "Its pride, too, must be restored." },
            { 738220794, "Which means we have a great deal of work ahead." },
            { 738220795, "If I were younger, I would spar with you myself." },
            { 738220796, "I think I could learn a lot from you. Your style is nothing if not pragmatic." },
            { 738220797, "You do not wish for some soldiers of your own to command?" },
            { 738220798, "You have the makings of a leader. It would be a shame to waste such talent." },
            { 738220889, "Quick prayer, perhaps?" },
            { 738220890, "Uhh..." },
            { 738220891, "There's a monument nearby." },
            { 738220892, "Nice. Wonder if it's hiding anything good..." },
            { 738220893, "That's one of those Tanta things, right?" },
            { 738220894, "Looks like it. What joys await, I wonder?" },
            { 738220895, "Power really does encourage shameless self-promotion, doesn't it?" },
            { 738220896, "What? Oh. Spotted a Tanta stone?" },
            { 738220897, "It's one of those stones the Tantas left behind." },
            { 738220898, "Shall we take a closer look?" },
            { 738220899, "Can you feel that? That's Tanta power—no mistaking it." },
            { 738220900, "Must be something there." },
            { 738220901, "Tanta power...you can almost taste it." },
            { 738220902, "One of those monuments nearby?" },
            { 738220903, "About time for a rest, do you think?" },
            { 738220904, "Sure. Lead the way." },
            { 738220905, "Looks like we can take a break there. Four walls and a roof—finally!" },
            { 738220906, "Let's head over and take a look, shall we?" },
            { 738220907, "How does a safe haven sound?" },
            { 738220908, "If it has walls, a roof, and—please!—a bed, I am all over it." },
            { 738220909, "Bed! Bedbedbedbedbed!" },
            { 738220910, "I thought you'd been pining for something..." },
            { 738220911, "Looks like a good place to rest up." },
            { 738220912, "Wouldn't mind a few hours' sleep for sure..." },
            { 738220913, "Nice! Somewhere safe!" },
            { 738220914, "You won't be safe until you're inside." },
            { 738220915, "There's something nearby. Shall we take a look?" },
            { 738220916, "Sure. As long as it's something good." },
            { 738220917, "Let's go check that out." },
            { 738220918, "Always worth a look just in case..." },
            { 738220919, "Alright, point me to something that I won't think is a total waste of time." },
            { 738220920, "Now you really are asking for miracles." },
            { 738220921, "Ooh, is that...? Look—over there." },
            { 738220922, "Alright, alright. I'm going, already." },
            { 738220923, "It often pays to take the odd detour or two, you know." },
            { 738220924, "Oh, believe me. I know." },
            { 738220925, "There's something there, right?" },
            { 738220926, "Would I be pointing you in that direction otherwise?" },
            { 738220927, "Now is really not the time!" },
            { 738220928, "What are you doing!? Either fight or run!" },
            { 738220929, "Will you concentrate!?" },
            { 738220930, "I'm a little busy right now, you know!" },
            { 738220931, "\"Not right now,\" right?" },
            { 738220932, "If you know, why ask!?" },
            { 738220933, "Do you really think that's appropriate right now?" },
            { 738220934, "Well, that was a complete waste of time." },
            { 738220935, "Tell me how you really feel." },
            { 738220936, "If you want compliments, earn them." },
            { 738220937, "Okay, that was dogshit." },
            { 738220938, "I take it that means \"I did terribly\"—something along those lines?" },
            { 738220939, "Are you even trying?" },
            { 738220940, "I—Ugh... Alright, alright. I admit it—that was weak." },
            { 738220941, "How am I so bad at this...?" },
            { 738220942, "Because you're not taking it seriously?" },
            { 738220943, "Wait, no—it's because I am stuck with a pain in the ass, nagging wrist-idiot." },
            { 738220944, "Shit. Alright, lemme go again." },
            { 738220945, "Only if you promise to actually try this time." },
            { 738220946, "Oh, I'll try. I'm about to smash this!" },
            { 738220947, "All great successes are built on failure...?" },
            { 738220948, "I'd be more convinced hearing that from someone successful." },
            { 738220949, "...Next time. You'll see." },
            { 738220950, "Not here, Frey." },
            { 738220951, "Ah, it was worth a try." },
            { 738220952, "No good, huh? Thought as much." },
            { 738220953, "Nope. No good at all." },
            { 738220954, "You need to try that somewhere else." },
            { 738220955, "Ugh. Pain in the ass." },
            { 738220956, "Oh, come on. Here's fine!" },
            { 738220957, "There's such a thing as being too blasé, you know." },
            { 738220958, "Do you really think this is the best place for a rest?" },
            { 738220959, "Uh, just kidding." },
            { 738220960, "Do we have some ruined-hut-related business I'm not aware of?" },
            { 738220961, "Shut up. There might be something here." },
            { 738220962, "If you're planning on getting some sleep, I don't think this is the place." },
            { 738220963, "Just curious, that's all." },
            { 738220964, "Wonder how long this thing's been here." },
            { 738220965, "Certainly longer than you've been alive." },
            { 738220966, "Looks like a town." },
            { 738220967, "One whose inhabitants have long since left, sadly..." },
            { 738220968, "I wonder if there's anybody here." },
            { 738220969, "Shut up. You're freaking me out." },
            { 738220970, "This place gives me the creeps." },
            { 738220971, "Yes. What is it about deserted houses?" },
            { 738220972, "I find an elevated perspective often helps, don't you?" },
            { 738220973, "Yeah, well it's not you doing the climbing." },
            { 738220974, "What do you say? Little trip to the top?" },
            { 738220975, "Please, after you." },
            { 738220976, "Wonder what's at the top of this one." },
            { 738220977, "Hopefully not monsters." },
            { 738220978, "Okay, whaddya say? Kick some ass, take some names?" },
            { 738220979, "Feeling a little bloodthirsty, are we?" },
            { 738220980, "Hostile forces could be hiding anywhere..." },
            { 738220981, "\"So keep your wits about you.\" You really need some new material." },
            { 738220982, "Keen to put your skills to the test, eh?" },
            { 738220983, "Can think of worse ways to pass the time." },
            { 738220984, "Athian bridge is falling down, falling down...fuck...falling down..." },
            { 738220985, "Do you really think now is the time?" },
            { 738220986, "I'm not sure we can guarantee it won't fall down while you're inside, you know." },
            { 738220987, "If you're trying to lighten the mood, it's really not working." },
            { 738220988, "What is this? A hut, maybe?" },
            { 738220989, "An ex-hut. Emphasis on the \"ex.\"" },
            { 738220990, "Looks like this one hasn't completely collapsed." },
            { 738220991, "Better check it out quick then." },
            { 738221304, "Ugh, I can barely swim like this..." },
            { 738221305, "Well, you're hardly dressed for it." },
            { 738221306, "Big swimmer, are you? Can't say I'm a fan." },
            { 738221307, "Thanks. I totally care." },
            { 738221308, "Maybe keeping my shoes on wasn't the best idea..." },
            { 738221309, "Yes, it will be rather...squelchy when you get out." },
            { 738221310, "You'll give me a thorough wipe-down when we get out, won't you?" },
            { 738221311, "Nope." },
            { 738221312, "Wonder if the water's safe to drink." },
            { 738221313, "It might not kill you. But you might wish it had..." },
            { 738221314, "I'll pass." },
            { 738221315, "Argh, this is such a pain in the ass..." },
            { 738221316, "As is almost everything, as far as I can ascertain." },
            { 738221317, "Hey, there's a scale, okay? And this is way up there." },
            { 738221318, "Do you have to flail your arms around like that?" },
            { 738221319, "Th-th-the...the water, it's—" },
            { 738221320, "It's quite the swimming style, I'll admit." },
            { 738221321, "Might you consider something a little less hard on the wrist area, though?" },
            { 738221322, "Do we really need to go this fast?" },
            { 738221323, "Urgh, just get me back to shore..." },
            { 738221324, "This is really quite impressive, especially considering how you're dressed." },
            { 738221325, "Oh. A...a compliment? From me? Heaven forbid. Ahem." },
            { 738221326, "Be very, very careful indeed." },
            { 738221327, "Ugh... This is sketchy as hell." },
            { 738221328, "Just. Don't. Slip." },
            { 738221329, "Okay, this has \"instant death\" written all over it." },
            { 738221330, "Just don't do anything foolish." },
            { 738221331, "Normally, that would make me wanna do it more. ...Normally." },
            { 738221332, "A word of advice: don't die." },
            { 738221333, "Gee, thanks for stating the obvious." },
            { 738221334, "Just focus. You're in serious danger." },
            { 738221335, "Okay, this looks...deadly." },
            { 738221336, "Well, you certainly would die if you fell." },
            { 738221337, "Uh-huh..." },
            { 738221338, "You do realize that your death would be quite a big setback for me, don't you?" },
            { 738221339, "Oh, I'm well aware of that, thanks." },
            { 738221340, "Good. Then I won't have to say it again." },
            { 738221341, "Don't take any unnecessary risks." },
            { 738221342, "Oh, you think that might be a bad idea?" },
            { 738221343, "Just because it is doesn't mean you wouldn't do it." },
            { 738221344, "This is as far as we go." },
            { 738221345, "You don't think it's maybe worth a try?" },
            { 738221346, "Certainly, if you want to waste valuable time." },
            { 738221347, "Think we can go any farther?" },
            { 738221348, "No." },
            { 738221349, "Thought as much." },
            { 738221350, "You never know—it might be worth scrabbling around in a futile attempt to find a way onward." },
            { 738221351, "Hilarious." },
            { 738221352, "Aren't I, though?" },
            { 738221354, "You can't get up there on your own?" },
            { 738221355, "If I were able to, believe me, I'd be off like a shot." },
            { 738221356, "Oh, I don't doubt that." },
            { 738221357, "Oh, to be young and thoughtless." },
            { 738221358, "Better than being fucking pointless." },
            { 738221359, "I think thankless sums up my situation rather better." },
            { 738221360, "Think we might have to go the long way around." },
            { 738221361, "Ahh, such is life." },
            { 738221362, "And what exactly do you know about life, Mr. Inanimate Object?" },
            { 738221363, "Alright... Guess that means I need to look before I leap." },
            { 738221364, "Finally she's learning." },
            { 738221365, "Once we've gone this way, we won't be coming back." },
            { 738221366, "Why, where we headed? The fiery pits of the underworld?" },
            { 738221367, "Hopefully not. But I couldn't say for certain." },
            { 738221368, "They should put a One Way sign up here." },
            { 738221369, "If it's not obvious enough before descending, it very much will be afterward." },
            { 738221370, "Yeah, might be a little late by then." },
            { 738221371, "It looks like we can get down from here." },
            { 738221372, "What about back up?" },
            { 738221373, "I wouldn't count on it." },
            { 738221374, "Alright, down we go!" },
            { 738221375, "You won't be coming back that way, you realize?" },
            { 738221376, "You trying to talk me out of this?" },
            { 738221377, "We can easily get down from here." },
            { 738221378, "Yes, the question is, can we get back up?" },
            { 738221379, "Uhhh...that part may not be so easy." },
            { 738221380, "Almost feels like you could fly if you jumped off, doesn't it?" },
            { 738221381, "Yeah. That or fall to an early death." },
            { 738221382, "Not quite ready to try it yet? Fair enough." },
            { 738221383, "I don't think you're ready for this yet." },
            { 738221384, "But I will be?" },
            { 738221385, "How am I supposed to know? I'm not a fortune-teller." },
            { 738221386, "I think I might be able to pull this off, don't you?" },
            { 738221387, "If you exploit every ounce of your powers to complete perfection, maybe." },
            { 738221388, "That's pretty much a yes, right?" },
            { 738221389, "You can do it." },
            { 738221390, "Uhh, can I? You've seen how high up we are, right?" },
            { 738221391, "I have. And you're ready. Trust me." },
            { 738221392, "Alright, it's now or never!" },
            { 738221393, "You won't forget to use the right spell, will you?" },
            { 738221394, "You think so little of me." },
            { 738221395, "Use your magic to protect yourself from the fall." },
            { 738221396, "Aw yeah, magic is the shit." },
            { 738221397, "Yes—as long as you remember to use it..." },
            { 738221398, "You might want to consider turning back." },
            { 738221399, "Yeah. Don't think we can go any farther." },
            { 738221400, "Shoreward we go, then." },
            { 738221401, "I'd advise against swimming any farther." },
            { 738221402, "...Have you any idea how dangerous a cramp can be in open water? It's—" },
            { 738221403, "I get it, I get it! I'm turning back!" },
            { 738221404, "Hah... Really...takes it outta ya..." },
            { 738221405, "Swimming fully clothed? Yes. Unsurprisingly, it does." },
            { 738221406, "Ugh... Can you just...pull me to shore...?" },
            { 738221407, "And how do you propose I do that, exactly?" },
            { 738221408, "Should probably turn back." },
            { 738221409, "I think that's maybe one of the few sensible things you've ever said." },
            { 738221410, "Wonder if you can drown a \"vambrace\"..." },
            { 738221411, "You've swum quite a distance. Time to head back, perhaps?" },
            { 738221412, "Hope I can make it..." },
            { 738221413, "We may be in something of a pickle if you can't..." },
            { 738221414, "Why is the shore so far away?" },
            { 738221415, "Yes. Not ideal." },
            { 738221416, "Better get back there before my arms give out..." },
            { 738221420, "Somebody Has to Pay" },
            { 738221421, "Head to the Grove" },
            { 738221422, "Heading to the Archives" },
            { 738221423, "Learn About the Tantas" },
            { 738221424, "Head for the Cipal Gate" },
            { 738221425, "Head to the Fortress" },
            { 738221426, "Head to Sila's Castle" },
            { 738221427, "Weathering the Storm" },
            { 738221428, "Head to the Cave" },
            { 738221429, "Auden's Advice" },
            { 738221430, "Read Bob's Notes" },
            { 738221431, "To Sila's Castle" },
            { 738221432, "Black Dragon in Flight" },
            { 738221433, "The Breakstorm Arrives" },
            { 738221434, "Escape" },
            { 738221435, "After the Storm" },
            { 738221436, "Looks like we can get down from here." },
            { 738221437, "Through these clouds? I can barely see a thing!" },
            { 738221438, "Oh, be quiet and get moving. And try not to slip." },
            { 738221439, "What the fuck is down there?" },
            { 738221440, "Somewhere a little more dangerous than our usual haunts. But you'll be fine. Probably." },
            { 738221441, "Comforting. Thanks." },
            { 738221442, "Is it...clouds all the way down?" },
            { 738221443, "Oh, there's solid ground somewhere under there. Somewhat...Break-tainted, but you can't have everything." },
            { 738221444, "Guess we don't have much choice..." },
            { 738221445, "The effects of the Break get worse from here on out." },
            { 738221446, "Meaning what?" },
            { 738221447, "Meaning it's dangerous, but you'll just have to grin and bear it." },
            { 738221448, "This isn't an actual lake, is it?" },
            { 738221449, "No. It leads to an area that's been particularly badly affected by the Break." },
            { 738221450, "Guess at least we can breathe down there..." },
            { 738221451, "Well? Jump in!" },
            { 738221452, "Uh-uh, fuck that. No way that's ending well." },
            { 738221453, "Oh, you'll be fine...as long as you're careful." },
            { 738221454, "Well, we won't be going anywhere until you've beaten this one." },
            { 738221455, "I don't get a say in this, do I?" },
            { 738221456, "We'll be getting near the castle soon." },
            { 738221457, "Yeah, except someone seems to be in our way." },
            { 738221458, "Hmm. Won't be getting by without a scrap, I'd say." },
            { 738221459, "What the fuck?" },
            { 738221460, "The castle's not far. Just try not to draw attention to yourself." },
            { 738221461, "Yeah, I don't think we'll just be strolling through." },
            { 738221462, "Ooh, look! That means—ahem. Nothing." },
            { 738221463, "Wait, what? Spill it." },
            { 738221464, "Do you feel that? The weather's changing." },
            { 738221465, "Weather chat. With a bracelet. What am I doing with my life?" },
            { 738221466, "I often ask myself the same thing." },
            { 738221467, "There's something weird in the air." },
            { 738221468, "Yes. Two weather systems colliding, if I'm not mistaken." },
            { 738221469, "Hope I don't catch a cold..." },
            { 738221470, "Shiiiiiit!" },
            { 738221471, "That's one way to do it, I suppose." },
            { 738221473, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221474, "Please try to be a little more dignified." },
            { 738221475, "You think I can help it!?" },
            { 738221476, "Fuck, fuck, shit, fuck fuuuuuuck!" },
            { 738221477, "Will you calm down?" },
            { 738221479, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221480, "Nothing more to say than that?" },
            { 738221481, "Fuck you!" },
