            { 738221507, "Olevia" },
            { 738221508, "Enter Praenost" },
            { 738221509, "On the Way to the Fortress 1" },
            { 738221510, "On the Way to the Fortress 2" },
            { 738221511, "On the Way to the Fortress 3" },
            { 738221512, "On the Way to the Fortress 4" },
            { 738221513, "On the Way to the Fortress 5" },
            { 738221514, "The Fortress Comes into View" },
            { 738221515, "Scars of the Break" },
            { 738221516, "In the Breakstorm" },
            { 738221517, "A Waking Nightmare" },
            { 738221518, "Cuff's Counsel" },
            { 738221522, "Shit. It's dark in here." },
            { 738221523, "Watch your step." },
            { 738221524, "I'm trying, believe me." },
            { 738221525, "Do you know this one? \"Deep in a dark, dank cave there lived a—\"" },
            { 738221526, "Please don't. Don't. Don't." },
            { 738221527, "Hmph. Well, that's story time ruined." },
            { 738221528, "Ugh, so depressing..." },
            { 738221529, "Is that existential angst, I hear?" },
            { 738221530, "No. Just me wondering how the fuck I wound up with you." },
            { 738221531, "How is one expected to see in these conditions?" },
            { 738221532, "Yeah, it's dark as— Wait. \"See\"?" },
            { 738221533, "I'm speaking hypothetically, of course." },
            { 738221534, "Well, it's kinda dank in here, but at least it's safe." },
            { 738221535, "Yes, not much room for unwanted guests to hide." },
            { 738221536, "How do you ventilate a cave...?" },
            { 738221537, "It's rather dark..." },
            { 738221538, "What's the matter? Scared?" },
            { 738221539, "Adorable. But no." },
            { 738221540, "Where do you think this leads?" },
            { 738221541, "Nowhere, I'd imagine. But there might be something in here." },
            { 738221542, "Should we check it out?" },
            { 738221543, "If there aren't any monsters lurking in here, I'll eat my hat." },
            { 738221544, "Oh, I would pay to see that." },
            { 738221545, "Best to assume I'm right for now, though, eh? Careful..." },
            { 738221546, "Not...super into the idea of going in here." },
            { 738221547, "Whyever not? You'll be hidden from foes, sheltered from the wind and rain..." },
            { 738221548, "Damp, cramped and miserable?" },
            { 738221549, "What a perfect place to get some rest." },
            { 738221550, "A dank, shitty hole? Glass is really half-full with you, isn't it?" },
            { 738221551, "Not a compliment, I take it?" },
            { 738221552, "What do we do if someone's in here?" },
            { 738221553, "Um, say hello? Comment on the weather?" },
            { 738221554, "I'm pretty sure they won't be the chatty type." },
            { 738221555, "Quick snooze while we're here?" },
            { 738221556, "Take a look around. Not exactly what I'd call cozy." },
            { 738221557, "And you're not exactly spoilt for choice." },
            { 738221558, "Heh. That felt weird." },
            { 738221559, "Looked it, too." },
            { 738221560, "Guess that's what being on the moon feels like." },
            { 738221561, "You make it sound rather enjoyable." },
            { 738221562, "I feel all...drifty..." },
            { 738221563, "How marvelously impressionistic." },
            { 738221564, "Oh, but now I wanna try it from even higher!" },
            { 738221565, "Do try not to push your luck..." },
            { 738221567, "Down we go. Careful." },
            { 738221568, "Wait. You're not serious, are you?" },
            { 738221569, "Deadly." },
            { 738221570, "What's the matter? Come on. Chop, chop!" },
            { 738221571, "This is a bad idea." },
            { 738221572, "Oh, it's fine. Just some highly concentrated Break, that's all." },
            { 738221573, "That's about the size of it, yes. Get to it!" },
            { 738221574, "Okay, this is bad." },
            { 738221575, "Bad or not, we've got to get through." },
            { 738221576, "Ugh, music to my ears." },
            { 738221577, "Oh, I couldn't possibly spoil the surprise." },
            { 738221578, "This will take us somewhere new." },
            { 738221579, "And we can just walk through?" },
            { 738221580, "Who's going to stop us? A particularly conscientious monster?" },
            { 738221581, "Eh, same diff." },
            { 738221584, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221585, "Are you enjoying this?" },
            { 738221586, "Here we go!" },
            { 738221587, "Wait! How far down is—" },
            { 738221588, "It's farther than it looks, isn't it?" },
            { 738221589, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221590, "Well, one can't fault your form." },
            { 738221591, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221592, "Never mind." },
            { 738221643, "The Sacred Peaks" },
            { 738221644, "The Barren Plains" },
            { 738221645, "Dead Man's Ledge" },
            { 738221646, "The Blessed Plains" },
            { 738221647, "The Pilgrims' Path" },
            { 738221648, "The Guardians' Way" },
            { 738221649, "Dianthus Wood" },
            { 738221650, "Brass Hollow" },
            { 738221651, "Home of Heroes" },
            { 738221652, "Middle Praenost" },
            { 738221653, "The Citadel" },
            { 738221654, "The Path of Glory" },
            { 738221655, "Pioneers' Plain" },
            { 738221656, "Opal Hills" },
            { 738221657, "Fields of the Fallen" },
            { 738221658, "Mount Garrison" },
            { 738221659, "The Mustering Ground" },
            { 738221661, "Cinta" },
            { 738221662, "Woman" },
            { 738221663, "Woman" },
            { 738221664, "Unjust Enforcer" },
            { 738221665, "Pitiless Arbiter" },
            { 738221666, "Girl" },
            { 738221667, "Girl" },
            { 738221668, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221669, "What the—!?" },
            { 738221670, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221671, "Get your ass outta my way! Move!" },
            { 738221672, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221673, "Outta the way!" },
            { 738221674, "Dammit, Frey!" },
            { 738221675, "When I get my hands on your scrawny kale-eating ass I'm gonna bust your—!" },
            { 738221676, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221677, "She threw a brick at me!" },
            { 738221678, "Damn you, Frey!" },
            { 738221681, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221682, "You will burn!" },
            { 738221683, "Fuck!" },
            { 738221684, "Huh...?" },
            { 738221685, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221686, "Oh, bring it, you mangled monsters!" },
            { 738221687, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221688, "Just follow me!" },
            { 738221689, "Huh. Nice." },
            { 738221690, "Yes. A pity we don't have...oh, I don't know...a penlight?" },
            { 738221691, "Well, now. That's curious..." },
            { 738221692, "What is?" },
            { 738221693, "And depending on what patterns they painted, those powers would change accordingly..." },
            { 738221694, "Huh, okay. I guess that could be useful...somehow..." },
            { 738221695, "Now that I did not expect. There's rather an intriguing connection between those two books, you know." },
            { 738221696, "Which is...?" },
            { 738221697, "Your \"Breakshards\" are said to be imbued with the blood of the Tantas." },
            { 738221698, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221699, "Why is Tanta Sila in Cipal!?" },
            { 738221700, "No... There's no way we can defeat her!" },
            { 738221701, "How has she grown so cruel?" },
            { 738221702, "Why is she attacking the city?" },
            { 738221703, "What's she doing here after all these years?" },
            { 738221704, "Must she torture us so mercilessly?" },
            { 738221705, "Tanta Sila's destroying the city!" },
            { 738221706, "It's not the real Tanta Sila! It can't be!" },
            { 738221707, "What the hell kind of craziness is this!?" },
            { 738221708, "Tanta Sila has the power to change the state of matter and being." },
            { 738221710, "We must proceed with caution." },
            { 738221711, "And I'm getting...weaker..." },
            { 738221712, "The conditions here are too severe, even with your resistance to the Break!" },
            { 738221714, "You will burn for humiliating me!" },
            { 738221715, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221716, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221717, "Shit! What now?" },
            { 738221722, "Ah! If it isn't my fairy ungodmother." },
            { 738221723, "Thought they taught you not to judge a book by its cover." },
            { 738221724, "No? 'Kay. Thought you'd get that one, being a librarian and all." },
            { 738221725, "Archivist!" },
            { 738221726, "Look. The point is, I did it." },
            { 738221727, "Aren't you impressed?" },
            { 738221728, "Should I be?" },
            { 738221729, "Well yeah, it wasn't a walk in the park." },
            { 738221730, "No. I don't imagine it was." },
            { 738221731, "But I fear this is only a temporary victory." },
            { 738221732, "The Tantas are deeply connected." },
            { 738221733, "They may be at odds with one another now, but their bond is ancient." },
            { 738221734, "Like the four wheels of a wagon, together they keep things on track." },
            { 738221735, "Break one, and they're all off-kilter." },
            { 738221736, "Clank!" },
            { 738221737, "There will be repercussions." },
            { 738221738, "What kind of repercussions?" },
            { 738221739, "That I can't predict. But something tells me we'll find out soon enough." },
            { 738221749, "Oh, I hope they stay that way..." },
            { 738221750, "I'm sorry I doubted you." },
            { 738221751, "We're all very grateful for what you did." },
            { 738221752, "Oh, hello! Would you like to join us?" },
            { 738221753, "I'd love to see you dance!" },
            { 738221754, "Gosh!" },
            { 738221755, "I've never seen so much food in my life!" },
            { 738221756, "That looks so fun!" },
            { 738221757, "I want to dance too!" },
            { 738221758, "It's not safe here!" },
            { 738221759, "Run!" },
            { 738221760, "Head for the upper city!" },
            { 738221761, "You'll die if you go down there!" },
            { 738221762, "It's over..." },
            { 738221763, "This is the end of the city!" },
            { 738221764, "Don't touch the Corruption!" },
            { 738221765, "You'll turn into one of them!" },
            { 738221766, "Why did this have to happen?" },
            { 738221767, "What did we do to deserve this?" },
            { 738221770, "I can't find my daughter!" },
            { 738221771, "Has anyone seen her?" },
            { 738221772, "Where can we run to?" },
            { 738221773, "Nowhere's safe! Nowhere!" },
            { 738221774, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221775, "I'm scared, mummy..." },
            { 738221777, "No! Ah... This can't be happening..." },
            { 738221778, "Where's mummy?" },
            { 738221779, "Mummy!" },
            { 738221780, "Wh-what's going on?" },
            { 738221781, "Please! Tell me what to do..." },
            { 738221782, "It...hurts!" },
            { 738221784, "Someone...help me..." },
            { 738221785, "Just kill me...please..." },
            { 738221786, "Why did this happen? Why!?" },
            { 738221788, "I...c-can't walk anymore..." },
            { 738221789, "Please... Please... Just end this quickly..." },
            { 738221790, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221791, "Mummy..." },
            { 738221792, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221793, "It hurts...so much..." },
            { 738221794, "Why are you stopping?" },
            { 738221795, "This is where the kid died." },
            { 738221796, "Feels like a million years ago..." },
            { 738221797, "You avenged her death." },
            { 738221798, "Avenged..." },
            { 738221799, "Yeah." },
            { 738221800, "She was so sweet to me." },
            { 738221801, "Life dealt her such a shitty hand, but she was so sweet to me." },
            { 738221802, "She had so much ahead of her." },
            { 738221803, "The people here understand that life can be short." },
            { 738221804, "They live in the long shadow of death cast by the Tantas." },
            { 738221805, "Perhaps the constant sense of her own mortality amplified the child's kindness to others." },
            { 738221806, "She was so young... And then people like me get twenty-one years. Twenty-one useless years! It—" },
            { 738221807, "It just doesn't seem fair." },
            { 738221808, "Oh, come now. There's so much still to live for." },
            { 738221809, "Yeah. Sure, what...what have I got? A cat and a long-ass rap sheet." },
            { 738221810, "At least in New York I don't get other people killed." },
            { 738221811, "Tanta's blessings." },
            { 738221812, "You think after all the misery and destruction they've caused that they still have blessings to give?" },
            { 738221813, "Yes. I do." },
            { 738221814, "They represented the best in us." },
            { 738221815, "That idea doesn't die just because their current selves are corrupted." },
            { 738221816, "Frey... I came to tell you that I was mistaken." },
            { 738221817, "Say what?" },
            { 738221818, "I misjudged you." },
            { 738221819, "The people are afraid." },
            { 738221820, "I am afraid." },
            { 738221821, "They look to me and the Council for a hope that we cannot give them." },
            { 738221822, "But maybe...you can." },
            { 738221823, "Flowers! This one must be full of resin!" },
            { 738221824, "Careful, now. Haste makes waste." },
            { 738221825, "It's alright! Look. Just...one little...cut right here, and..." },
            { 738221826, "Whoa..." },
            { 738221827, "Whoa, wh—" },
            { 738221828, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221831, "That was a close one." },
            { 738221832, "So much for going unnoticed." },
            { 738221833, "Huh?" },
            { 738221834, "Whoa! I-I don't wanna fight!" },
            { 738221835, "Okay? I just came to get some ballow resin, and then I'm gone." },
            { 738221836, "Over and out." },
            { 738221837, "Tanta Prav has summoned you." },
            { 738221838, "She wishes to talk." },
            { 738221839, "She's right inside..." },
            { 738221840, "And there I was thinking you were serious about your \"nonviolent\" solution." },
            { 738221841, "Prav doesn't deserve your mercy." },
            { 738221842, "Okay, I've said it once before, but apparently it bears repeating." },
            { 738221843, "Not going to happen! I'm not gonna kill her!" },
            { 738221844, "But if you don't kill this madwoman, everyone in Cipal could die!" },
            { 738221845, "You have a gift that no one else possesses. It's your duty to use it." },
            { 738221846, "The people need your help." },
            { 738221847, "Not my problem!" },
            { 738221848, "Look, I'm gonna take the ballow resin back to Cipal, save Breakbob, and get the fuck back to New York!" },
            { 738221849, "Done and done!" },
            { 738221850, "You know countless people will suffer and die because of Prav, don't you?" },
            { 738221851, "Are you really going to abandon them at their most vulnerable!?" },
            { 738221852, "Hah. Yes, I see. Like mother, like daughter." },
            { 738221853, "Fuck you! That's—" },
            { 738221854, "True?" },
            { 738221855, "I..." },
            { 738221856, "No, no, no. Fine. Fine! Let's be on our way then, shall we?" },
            { 738221857, "Come on! Let's get back to, uh...back to Cipal with you." },
            { 738221858, "That's what you want, isn't it?" },
            { 738221859, "Yeah..." },
            { 738221860, "Mother fuck!" },
            { 738221861, "Is there a problem?" },
            { 738221862, "Maybe I can reason with her." },
            { 738221863, "She's the Tanta of Justice, right?" },
            { 738221864, "Halt!" },
            { 738221865, "My name's Frey Holland." },
            { 738221866, "Prav summoned me. Can you take me to her?" },
            { 738221867, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221868, "You are charged with the murder of Tanta Sila." },
            { 738221869, "Bring her in." },
            { 738221870, "Wha—what?" },
            { 738221871, "What the f—" },
            { 738221872, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221873, "Hail, interloper, bold upstart." },
            { 738221874, "So fair of face, yet black of heart." },
            { 738221875, "Your eyes tell all, lay bare your lies." },
            { 738221876, "Pray, come—in judgment, be baptized." },
            { 738221877, "Oh, I, uh...didn't come here to be judged. I came here to talk." },
            { 738221878, "Look, will you stop destroying the city and leave the people alone?" },
            { 738221879, "Such certitude, such righteous poise!" },
            { 738221880, "Yet all is demon-sullied noise." },
            { 738221881, "Shit, alright, if you're going to rhyme everything, then just kill me now." },
            { 738221882, "Dissemble not! Confess your crime!" },
            { 738221883, "A Tanta, slaughtered in her prime!" },
            { 738221884, "She ordered her soldiers to attack innocent people!" },
            { 738221885, "Children died!" },
            { 738221886, "And have you proof to back this claim?" },
            { 738221887, "Pray come, stand trial, let truth be heard!" },
            { 738221888, "Bear witness with both deed and word!" },
            { 738221889, "If pure you are, there's naught to fear." },
            { 738221890, "If devil-sullied, all must hear!" },
            { 738221891, "Okay, look, lady. I'm kind of in a rush here, but clearly this isn't going anywhere—" },
            { 738221892, "A tale of woe, a severed past..." },
            { 738221893, "A child let go, returned at—" },
            { 738221894, "\"Child let go\"? What the fuck are you talking about?" },
            { 738221895, "No! No! No!" },
            { 738221896, "Quiet! Quiet! Quiet!" },
            { 738221897, "I am the asker of questions! You are the answerer!" },
            { 738221898, "Do you understand, consort of demons?" },
            { 738221899, "Okay, what I said about the rhyming thing—I don't mind it so much anymore!" },
            { 738221900, "I said quiet!" },
            { 738221901, "I seek to know, child, nothing more." },
            { 738221902, "I crave fact, not a settled score." },
            { 738221903, "So trust yourself unto the scales." },
            { 738221904, "By judgment's test, the truth prevails." },
            { 738221905, "You know the truth of what you hear." },
            { 738221906, "Admit it. The way forward's clear." },
            { 738221907, "C-crystal..." },
            { 738221908, "Today, we hear the case of one Frey, on trial for the crime of Tantacide." },
            { 738221909, "Specifically, the senseless slaughter of the mighty Tanta Sila." },
            { 738221910, "May Her essence find its rest." },
            { 738221911, "How do you plead?" },
            { 738221912, "If you plead guilty, they'll execute you immediately!" },
            { 738221913, "Not guilty!" },
            { 738221914, "Lies, and yet more monstrous lies!" },
            { 738221915, "She drowns! No more of this! She dies!" },
            { 738221916, "What!? I thought you said if I pled not guilty she wouldn't kill me! I-I..." },
            { 738221917, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221918, "Now come, face the time-honored test." },
            { 738221919, "If innocent, these foes you'll best." },
            { 738221920, "What? How is that a Trial by Water?" },
            { 738221921, "Succeed, and execution's stayed." },
            { 738221922, "Succumb, and your crime's price is paid." },
            { 738221923, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221924, "Very impressive." },
            { 738221925, "All in a day's work!" },
            { 738221926, "Crow not—the Trial is far from done." },
            { 738221927, "Alright, quit fucking around and let me go." },
            { 738221928, "I passed your \"trial\" fair and square." },
            { 738221929, "No, you didn't!" },
            { 738221930, "We haven't reached a final verdict yet!" },
            { 738221931, "You still have so much to prove!" },
            { 738221932, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221933, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221934, "Alright, cut the bullshit." },
            { 738221935, "Just promise me you will stop attacking the people of Cipal, and I'll gladly fuck off." },
            { 738221936, "The trial is passed. Now, justice done." },
            { 738221937, "The law dictates thy freedom's—" },
            { 738221938, "Lost forever! You will die in this watery prison, girl!" },
            { 738221939, "What?" },
            { 738221940, "But no! This cannot—will not—stand!" },
            { 738221941, "The Tantas' word sustains the land!" },
            { 738221942, "Exactly! Which is why there must be no mercy for a Tanta-killer! None!" },
            { 738221943, "Okay. Uh...you guys clearly have some stuff to discu—" },
            { 738221944, "Silence!" },
            { 738221945, "One more word, and you will lose your tongue!" },
            { 738221946, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221947, "What the fuck?" },
            { 738221948, "What is happening?" },
            { 738221949, "It seems you've inspired her to pull out all the stops!" },
            { 738221950, "Fuck it, let her! This sham of a trial is ending anyway!" },
            { 738221951, "We're on her turf here, remember! Don't get careless!" },
            { 738221952, "Whoa!" },
            { 738221953, "Criminal! Wrongdoer!" },
            { 738221954, "I sentence you to be hung, drawn, and quartered!" },
            { 738221955, "Try it, you whacked-out piece of shit!" },
            { 738221956, "Damn you...demon..." },
            { 738221957, "I will...end you!" },
            { 738221958, "Enough! It is time to move on..." },
            { 738221959, "Dear sister... Oh, the price she pays..." },
            { 738221960, "Her daughter lost... Her loving gaze..." },
            { 738221961, "Wh... \"Daughter\"?" },
            { 738221962, "Wh-what are you talking about?" },
            { 738221963, "Tell me! What does that mean?" },
            { 738221964, "The demon. Child of Cinta... Child...of..." },
            { 738221965, "Child of Cinta? Wh-wha—" },
            { 738221966, "What's happening?" },
            { 738221967, "Prav is dead." },
            { 738221968, "I'd assume that most of her enchantments died with her..." },
            { 738221969, "And?" },
            { 738221970, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221971, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221972, "Did you know?" },
            { 738221973, "Know what?" },
            { 738221974, "All of that \"child of Cinta\" shit." },
            { 738221975, "Did you know?" },
            { 738221976, "Are you saying you believed that madwoman?" },
            { 738221977, "I...I don't know..." },
            { 738221978, "I mean, if it is indeed the truth...I can't imagine the turmoil you must be going through..." },
            { 738221979, "Wait. Does that mean she could still be somewhere in Athia?" },
            { 738221980, "I believe it could, yes..." },
            { 738221981, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738221982, "Whatever." },
            { 738221983, "Whoever she is, she's still the monster who abandoned her baby." },
            { 738221984, "Come along now, Frey. Chin up." },
            { 738222004, "Yeah. They don't exactly spread sunshine and cheer wherever they go, huh?" },
            { 738222005, "Sooner or later, you'll have a big decision to make, you know." },
            { 738222006, "You mean whether or not I should kill my mother?" },
            { 738222007, "When the time comes, whatever you decide, I'll be there with you to do what needs to be done." },
            { 738222008, "For now, let's go and see if we can get some answers out of dear old Bob." },
            { 738222009, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222010, "Hey, old man. How's it going?" },
            { 738222011, "Tip-top, young Frey." },
            { 738222012, "Tip-top." },
            { 738222013, "Hang in there." },
            { 738222014, "I...I need you to fight through this." },
