            { 738222017, "I know... I know." },
            { 738222018, "You want to go back home, my child. Voosh." },
            { 738222019, "Not just \"voosh\"..." },
            { 738222020, "I have so many questions..." },
            { 738222021, "I see." },
            { 738222022, "You seem to have already found your way home...no?" },
            { 738222023, "You knew?" },
            { 738222024, "Wasn't sure until now. Your eyes..." },
            { 738222025, "Protect Athia." },
            { 738222029, "Voosh." },
            { 738222030, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222031, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222032, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222033, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222034, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222035, "Fuck!" },
            { 738222036, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222037, "Breakbob was my last shot at getting out of this place and now I'm stuck in this insanity!" },
            { 738222038, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222039, "Apologies if my father's death has inconvenienced you." },
            { 738222040, "That's not what I meant. I—" },
            { 738222041, "No?" },
            { 738222042, "I have lost the father who I only was just reunited with..." },
            { 738222043, "Who I was hoping to spend more time with." },
            { 738222044, "Who was all I had left." },
            { 738222045, "I'm sorry that's been so hard on you." },
            { 738222046, "No, I didn't—" },
            { 738222047, "Didn't what? Think?" },
            { 738222048, "No. Your only concern is for yourself." },
            { 738222049, "That's..." },
            { 738222050, "My people have lost so much." },
            { 738222051, "They can't just \"get out\" of this \"insanity.\"" },
            { 738222052, "This is their home—my home!" },
            { 738222053, "But don't let our grief and assured destruction get in the way of your self-pity." },
            { 738222054, "Okay, that's fair!" },
            { 738222055, "\"Fair\"? You want to talk about \"fair\"?" },
            { 738222056, "What's unfair is the only person capable of helping us is too self-absorbed to do so!" },
            { 738222057, "I've shed blood for this place!" },
            { 738222058, "Our people welcomed you." },
            { 738222059, "They were frightened—rightfully so—but they still welcomed you." },
            { 738222060, "They needed me!" },
            { 738222061, "What's wrong with that?" },
            { 738222062, "People need each other!" },
            { 738222063, "We help one another without complaint. It's the Athian way." },
            { 738222064, "Not that I should have expected you to understand that." },
            { 738222065, "After all, you're not one of us." },
            { 738222066, "No." },
            { 738222067, "No, you know what? You are right." },
            { 738222068, "I didn't grow up here." },
            { 738222069, "Give me everything you've got on the goddamn torana." },
            { 738222070, "Still hell-bent on leaving, I see." },
            { 738222071, "Yes. I'm not wanted here." },
            { 738222072, "Auden made that clear. My dear old mother made that very clear when she—" },
            { 738222073, "When she..." },
            { 738222074, "When she banished me from Athia!" },
            { 738222075, "Yeah." },
            { 738222076, "Your dear \"Tanta of Love\" is my dear, darling mother." },
            { 738222077, "The same woman who tossed me through a torana the first fucking chance she got." },
            { 738222078, "Makes sense." },
            { 738222079, "What?" },
            { 738222080, "Excuse me?" },
            { 738222081, "I just told you I'm the living heir to a Tanta, and you look at me like I've done the fucking dishes?" },
            { 738222082, "Well, you clearly don't think much of your lineage, so why should I?" },
            { 738222083, "Perhaps you haven't noticed, but I'm sat here scrambling, trying to fix a cataclysm!" },
            { 738222084, "So if you're not here to help, then good riddance to you." },
            { 738222085, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222086, "Yeah, that sounds about right. People only give a shit when they want something from you." },
            { 738222087, "Being an heir to a Tanta is an honor, not a curse." },
            { 738222088, "If you can't understand that already, there are plenty of books here that will teach you what it truly means." },
            { 738222089, "You'll have plenty of time to read them when we're all dead!" },
            { 738222090, "The guilt trip isn't working! I am done helping a world that doesn't want me here!" },
            { 738222091, "And there you have it." },
            { 738222092, "Sorry, if you came here looking for a way to get home, all your answers died with Robian." },
            { 738222093, "There's only one woman left in the world that might have something of use to you." },
            { 738222094, "Junoon is that way." },
            { 738222095, "But I—" },
            { 738222096, "Tanta's blessings go with you." },
            { 738222098, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222099, "……ダメ！" },
            { 738222100, "You'll never defeat me, foolish child!" },
            { 738222101, "I am the evil Tanta Cinta! Ha ha!" },
            { 738222102, "I've got a few tricks up my sleeve!" },
            { 738222103, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222104, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222105, "……は！　うわあ！" },
            { 738222106, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222107, "You're the Tanta slayer!" },
            { 738222108, "The savior of Athia! Right?" },
            { 738222109, "Is there really no way of convincing you to go and face Tanta Olas first?" },
            { 738222110, "I said no." },
            { 738222111, "Facing your mother will be hard, Frey. Harder than you can imagine. You should prepare as best you can." },
            { 738222112, "Olas's power would give—" },
            { 738222113, "Olas is their problem, not mine. Got it?" },
            { 738222114, "Huh?" },
