            { 738222202, "And there's only one person capable of creating a false reality. Isn't that right, Olas?" },
            { 738222203, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222204, "Alright." },
            { 738222219, "Stop hurting it, Frey!" },
            { 738222220, "Olevia!?" },
            { 738222221, "No. It can't be! You're not real!" },
            { 738222222, "Why didn't you save me?" },
            { 738222223, "No! I-I tried, but..." },
            { 738222224, "Snap out of it, Frey!" },
            { 738222225, "Olevia died, remember?" },
            { 738222226, "Why are you doing this..." },
            { 738222227, "Stop this... Please!" },
            { 738222228, "Olas is trying to use your guilt against you." },
            { 738222229, "Don't let her get inside your head!" },
            { 738222230, "Won't you stay with me? Please, Frey..." },
            { 738222231, "Olas, I will not let you fuck with me!" },
            { 738222232, "Let me out of this place!" },
            { 738222233, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222234, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222235, "You know what to do." },
            { 738222236, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222237, "I...I..." },
            { 738222238, "You would be better off." },
            { 738222239, "Isn't that what you believe?" },
            { 738222240, "I can see it so clearly in your mind. You feel you lack purpose." },
            { 738222241, "A place in the world." },
            { 738222242, "I mean, who would miss you?" },
            { 738222243, "Who cares if you live or die?" },
            { 738222244, "I care." },
            { 738222245, "They will let you down." },
            { 738222254, "Which to choose, which to choose..." },
            { 738222255, "Better pick a good one..." },
            { 738222256, "Try not to take all day." },
            { 738222257, "Let's give this one a try." },
            { 738222258, "Got a good feeling about this one." },
            { 738222259, "Finally made your choice, hm?" },
            { 738222260, "New powers. Nice." },
            { 738222261, "Okay, look out, world!" },
            { 738222262, "Can't wait to try this one!" },
            { 738222263, "Do try to make good use of your power." },
            { 738222264, "Onward and upward, eh?" },
            { 738222265, "That particular skill should serve you well." },
            { 738222266, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222267, "What do I feel like today...?" },
            { 738222268, "Just pick, will you?" },
            { 738222269, "That'll do!" },
            { 738222270, "Okay, that's what's up." },
            { 738222271, "All done? Thank goodness..." },
            { 738222272, "These bad boys pack a punch, I can feel it." },
            { 738222273, "Now that's a killer look." },
            { 738222274, "I think you might be onto something there." },
            { 738222275, "Yeah, that could work..." },
            { 738222276, "Ooh, I know!" },
            { 738222277, "Oh yeah, that'll look sick." },
            { 738222278, "What was I gonna make again...?" },
            { 738222279, "Alright, let's do this." },
            { 738222280, "Thinking of making something?" },
            { 738222281, "Aaand done!" },
            { 738222282, "I like it!" },
            { 738222283, "You've done quite a nice job there..." },
            { 738222284, "Olas caused you to be swallowed by the Break. Trapped you in her world of illusion." },
            { 738222285, "I tried to get through to you, but I couldn't seem to reach you directly." },
            { 738222286, "So it was you sending me all those weird messages!" },
            { 738222287, "Honestly? I, uh..." },
            { 738222288, "Doesn't matter what you want now." },
            { 738222289, "Oh yeah? How do you figure?" },
            { 738222290, "The people have decided to believe in you." },
            { 738222291, "So you'd better not let them down." },
            { 738222292, "Now clear off. I've got things to do." },
            { 738222293, "Huh? What's this?" },
            { 738222294, "The sly old devil must have slipped it in there when you weren't looking." },
            { 738222295, "I'm busy." },
            { 738222296, "You've got better things to do than bother me." },
            { 738222297, "Shhh! Quiet in the archives!" },
            { 738222300, "You're not heading to the tavern?" },
            { 738222301, "Celebrate if you like. Just don't overdo it." },
            { 738222302, "You'd probably better do some mingling." },
            { 738222303, "You're why they're all so happy, after all." },
            { 738222304, "You don't need to worry about me." },
            { 738222305, "Got a few things on my mind, is all..." },
            { 738222316, "Huh? Aren't there any in town?" },
            { 738222317, "I'll draw you a map and give you the key. You'll have to do the rest yourself." },
            { 738222318, "If you can bring them back—and that's a big \"if\"—I'll make you something with that ore of yours." },
            { 738222319, "What? I didn't offer to run errands for you!" },
            { 738222320, "Like I say, I'm not expecting much. You'll do it or you won't." },
            { 738222321, "Yeah, looks that way. Let's break some heads." },
            { 738222340, "I came to Cipal, and I found new tools. New methods." },
            { 738222341, "Killing Sila..." },
            { 738222342, "She was a warrior." },
            { 738222343, "That happened. And we've you to thank." },
            { 738222344, "It's like I told you—the wound can't heal until the bleeding stops." },
            { 738222345, "You're the only one who can take on the Tantas. But you have to choose to do it." },
            { 738222346, "Oh. And you might as well take this." },
            { 738222347, "What is it?" },
            { 738222348, "Auden had me make it. Said she wanted to make sure you stayed safe." },
            { 738222349, "Did she." },
            { 738222350, "She did. Now get lost." },
            { 738222351, "Here." },
            { 738222352, "Don't forget: this is where you belong now. These are your people." },
            { 738222353, "Do you ever leave this place, Jo?" },
            { 738222354, "Athia needs saving. And I have to do everything I can to help." },
            { 738222355, "For Sila. And for all the Tantas. They died for this." },
            { 738222356, "Guess they did, huh." },
            { 738222357, "You've got things to be doing too. Heroic reputations don't uphold themselves, you know." },
            { 738222358, "Yeah, yeah. See ya later!" },
            { 738222359, "I'm trying to find out how you managed to make the Corruption disappear from Cipal." },
            { 738222360, "There has to be a way to save Athia." },
            { 738222361, "You looking for a book?" },
            { 738222388, "Rank" },
            { 738222389, "High Score" },
            { 738222390, "Reward" },
            { 738222391, "First-Time Bonus" },
            { 738222392, "TIPS" },
            { 738222393, "TIME" },
            { 738222394, "SCORE" },
            { 738222395, "RESULT" },
            { 738222396, "Base Score" },
            { 738222397, "Time Bonus" },
            { 738222398, "Total Bonus" },
            { 738222399, "Total Score" },
            { 738222400, "REWARD" },
            { 738222402, "START" },
            { 738222403, "RETRY" },
            { 738222404, "QUIT" },
            { 738222405, "REWARDS" },
            { 738222406, "New Record!" },
            { 738222407, "CLOSE" },
            { 738222415, "Surviving the Trial" },
            { 738222416, "Prav's Castle" },
            { 738222417, "Frey Vs. Prav" },
            { 738222418, "Frey's Secret" },
            { 738222419, "Prav's Court" },
            { 738222420, "Trial by Water 1" },
            { 738222432, "en001" },
            { 738222433, "Score" },
            { 738222434, "3" },
            { 738222435, "2" },
            { 738222436, "1" },
            { 738222437, "GO" },
            { 738222448, "Time Warp" },
            { 738222449, "Start" },
            { 738222450, "Clear" },
            { 738222456, "Which meant that there were more books here than anywhere else in Athia." },
            { 738222459, "Oh my—it's New. Fucking. York." },
            { 738222461, "Register" },
            { 738222462, "Result" },
            { 738222465, "Take out all the enemies within the time limit." },
            { 738222470, "Keep the townspeople safe for the allotted time." },
            { 738222475, "Save the townspeople from the enemies within the time limit." },
            { 738222480, "Reach your destination within the time limit." },
            { 738222483, "Defeating consecutive foes without taking any damage will earn you a bonus." },
            { 738222484, "The more townspeople you manage to keep safe, the higher the bonus you'll receive." },
            { 738222485, "The more quickly you beat the boss, the higher the bonus you'll receive." },
            { 738222486, "The sooner you arrive at your destination, the higher your score will be." },
            { 738222487, "The more quickly you wipe out all the enemies, the higher the bonus you'll receive." },
            { 738222527, "Susurrus" },
            { 738222528, "Alright. Where do I start?" },
            { 738222529, "What exactly are we starting? Are you planning on becoming some sort of...errand person?" },
            { 738222530, "Oh I'm sorry, I'm sure you have some suitably grandiose term for it. \"Breakwarden\"?" },
            { 738222531, "Just to be clear, \"we\" aren't starting anything." },
            { 738222532, "I'm gonna use you to clean up the mess you made." },
            { 738222533, "Hmph. You know this is just the beginning?" },
            { 738222534, "You can't keep me like this forever." },
            { 738222535, "I'll drive you out of your mind soon enough." },
            { 738222536, "Yeah. Good luck with that." },
            { 738222537, "\"Breakwarden,\" though... I kinda like it." },
            { 738222538, "You always did love my ideas." },
            { 738222539, "Oh, shut it." },
            { 738222540, "Oh! We're saved!" },
            { 738222541, "You know what? None of this is my fault. This is all your fucking fault." },
            { 738222542, "Fantastic." },
            { 738222543, "You're telling me." },
            { 738222544, "Did you say something?" },
            { 738222545, "Why don't your \"trust issues\" extend to the street urchin, I wonder?" },
            { 738222546, "Because I've been there, alright?" },
            { 738222547, "Let's just leave it at that." },
            { 738222548, "Terrific! The word of a senile old has-been! Ironclad!" },
            { 738222549, "Great." },
            { 738222550, "What am I doing in the Grove?" },
            { 738222551, "Let's get you home." },
            { 738222552, "Audie!" },
            { 738222553, "Yes!" },
            { 738222554, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222555, "Come on." },
            { 738222556, "Before you go, I would suggest that you learn all that you can about the Tantas." },
            { 738222557, "The archives... Full of books about them." },
            { 738222558, "Definitely not my fairy godmother." },
            { 738222559, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222560, "In case you forgot, I'm on my way to battle a boss bitch tomorrow." },
            { 738222561, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222562, "FUCK!" },
            { 738222563, "Oh no. \"You absolutely sound like that.\"" },
            { 738222564, "Yeah—see? Two can play at that game." },
            { 738222565, "Well, perhaps not everyone has the sensitivity and subtlety required to appreciate the beauty inherent in chaos." },
            { 738222566, "Sure, Hannibal." },
            { 738222567, "Who? Oh, yeah. Earth joke." },
            { 738222568, "Bingo." },
            { 738222569, "Well, before we set off, we might as well take a look at this floor plan that Johedy gave us." },
            { 738222570, "Finally! We're going to the castle!" },
            { 738222571, "Forgive me if I'm not excited." },
            { 738222572, "Damn. They did not hold back on the fortifications, huh?" },
            { 738222573, "Not entirely surprising for the so-called Tanta of Strength." },
            { 738222574, "We'll need to be careful." },
            { 738222575, "This is a woman who faced entire armies—" },
            { 738222576, "How do we get inside?" },
            { 738222577, "—countless thousands met their fate at the end of her blade—" },
            { 738222578, "Okay, listen, you don't have to—" },
            { 738222579, "—then she bathed in the blood of her enemies!" },
            { 738222580, "Okay, okay! No one ever said that!" },
            { 738222581, "I'm adding color." },
            { 738222582, "Yeah, don't." },
            { 738222583, "Let's just try the gate first." },
            { 738222584, "Her blood is on your hands." },
            { 738222585, "No. It is you who trespassed on my land." },
            { 738222586, "You who set this battle in motion." },
            { 738222587, "You disregard rules, and then act as if you are the victim?" },
            { 738222588, "Take responsibility for your actions, as I will for mine." },
            { 738222589, "No time like the present." },
            { 738222590, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222591, "The hell?" },
            { 738222592, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222593, "This is how you wish to proceed?" },
            { 738222594, "So be it." },
            { 738222595, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222599, "This may not be good. Her anger is fueling her power..." },
            { 738222600, "Well, you know what? She's not the only one who's pissed off." },
            { 738222601, "Time to finish this!" },
            { 738222602, "Whoa..." },
            { 738222603, "Sure." },
            { 738222604, "I hear there's a celebration in your honor at the Shady Tree." },
            { 738222605, "You should go and revel in your victory, Tanta Slayer." },
            { 738222610, "I think I've earned this pint." },
            { 738222611, "A cheers for our liberator!" },
            { 738222615, "It's here in Cipal!" },
            { 738222616, "Fuck this!" },
            { 738222617, "Let's just keep going." },
            { 738222618, "These are not my people! I..." },
            { 738222619, "I have enough blood on my hands!" },
            { 738222620, "If not you, then who?" },
            { 738222621, "I don't...give a shit, just...leave me the fuck alone!" },
            { 738222622, "There's no resin left in this one." },
            { 738222623, "So Bob was trying to tell us something!" },
            { 738222624, "I'll have to thank him when I get back." },
            { 738222625, "Not so fast. We can't go back to Cipal without more resin." },
            { 738222626, "Hmm. The lamp seems to be able to conjure monsters out of thin air." },
            { 738222627, "Shit. Then we'd better hurry up and break it." },
            { 738222628, "It doesn't feel like I'm doing shit to this lamp!" },
            { 738222629, "I'm not sure how exactly, but I think the monsters are protecting it." },
            { 738222630, "So we need to get rid of them first? Great. Got it." },
            { 738222631, "If you can jump across there, we might be able to get behind them without being spotted." },
            { 738222632, "Yeah, I see it!" },
            { 738222633, "You might want to think about clearing out those nuisances up above you first." },
            { 738222634, "See if you can find a way up there." },
            { 738222644, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222645, "Are you alright?" },
            { 738222646, "What the hell was that?" },
            { 738222647, "Tanta Olas used her abilities to penetrate your psyche." },
            { 738222648, "She exploited your deepest desires...but it's over now." },
            { 738222649, "Are you sure?" },
            { 738222650, "Yes. This is reality." },
            { 738222651, "Okay, and where in reality are we, exactly?" },
            { 738222652, "By the looks of it, Visoria. Olas's realm." },
            { 738222653, "Is that her castle?" },
            { 738222654, "I believe so. Anyway...what next?" },
            { 738222655, "We're going after her." },
            { 738222656, "……" },
            { 738222657, "What's the matter? Still disoriented from the illusion?" },
            { 738222658, "No, I was just thinking..." },
            { 738222659, "Do tell." },
            { 738222660, "Well...you were right about doing this before we go after Cinta." },
            { 738222661, "Say that again." },
            { 738222662, "Why?" },
            { 738222663, "Oh, just something about \"You were right.\"" },
            { 738222664, "Shut up." },
            { 738222665, "By the way, you said I was swallowed by the Break, right?" },
            { 738222666, "I can't help worrying about everybody back in Cipal..." },
            { 738222667, "Yes, their welfare is something of a concern." },
            { 738222668, "And the best way to help them is to stop Olas before the Break engulfs the city entirely." },
            { 738222669, "Yeah, yeah, I get it. Come on..." },
            { 738222670, "We must go and defeat Olas before we do anything else." },
            { 738222671, "If we don't, all of Cipal will be swallowed by the Break." },
            { 738222672, "If you don't hurry up and turn around, it will be too late." },
            { 738222673, "Fine!" },
            { 738222674, "This place isn't much to look at, huh?" },
            { 738222675, "The entire realm is usually under the sway of Olas's powers." },
            { 738222676, "Not much need for decoration when you can make it appear however you please." },
            { 738222677, "Well, whatever fake shit she conjures up this time, she's still going down." },
            { 738222678, "So, what happens after?" },
            { 738222679, "After what?" },
            { 738222680, "Say I kill all the Tantas—then what?" },
            { 738222681, "Their mad rule is over. You win." },
            { 738222682, "Okay, great, but what happens then? To Athia, I mean." },
            { 738222683, "Why does that matter?" },
            { 738222684, "Well, look around you. The place is screwed." },
            { 738222685, "It's not, like, \"poof,\" all better." },
            { 738222686, "The Break stays even when the Tantas die." },
            { 738222687, "It just stops getting worse..." },
            { 738222688, "What happens to you when all this is over?" },
            { 738222689, "I can't say with any certainty..." },
            { 738222690, "But let's not worry about me for now." },
            { 738222691, "We have places to be." },
            { 738222692, "Copy that." },
            { 738222693, "It's weird." },
            { 738222694, "There was a part of Tanta Olas that seemed...I don't know...sane. Lucid." },
            { 738222695, "I don't see how." },
            { 738222696, "The Corruption has been wearing away at the Tantas' minds for years now." },
            { 738222697, "Yeah, just all that stuff about \"sacrifices\" and \"victims\"..." },
            { 738222698, "You think there was any truth behind it?" },
            { 738222699, "She's broken inside." },
            { 738222700, "She was playing with your emotions." },
            { 738222701, "She would have said anything to keep you under her spell." },
            { 738222702, "I guess..." },
            { 738222703, "Alright, who builds a castle at the bottom of a hole?" },
            { 738222704, "It is rather a unique look, isn't it?" },
            { 738222708, "Is that who we have to convince to let us in?" },
            { 738222709, "Looks like it." },
            { 738222712, "That's the same kind of lamp we saw in not-New-York, right?" },
            { 738222714, "Try smashing it." },
            { 738222715, "I'm on it." },
            { 738222716, "Not again! I'm not even scratching this thing!" },
            { 738222717, "Just calm down and focus on the enemies around it first." },
            { 738222718, "Yeah, I remember how it's done, thank you very much." },
            { 738222724, "Holy crap." },
            { 738222725, "Well, you simply need to—" },
            { 738222726, "Oh, lemme guess. \"Keep my guard up and stay alert,\" something like that?" },
            { 738222727, "I got this, Cuff. And you got my back, right?" },
            { 738222728, "Indeed." },
            { 738222729, "Oh, great! A welcoming committee!" },
            { 738222730, "All very funny until someone gets hurt." },
            { 738222731, "Looks like it's just me and you, tough guy!" },
            { 738222732, "Let's get this over with, shall we?" },
            { 738222733, "Well, that wasn't much fun." },
            { 738222734, "On the bright side, the way is clear." },
            { 738222735, "True. Shall we?" },
            { 738222759, "Oh yeah, no, this is just a regular library." },
            { 738222760, "Not entirely surprising for the home of the Tanta of Wisdom." },
            { 738222761, "Shame we don't see eye to eye... Wouldn't mind spending some quality time here." },
            { 738222764, "Another lamp. And it's a biggie." },
            { 738222765, "I would imagine that whatever illusion it's generating affects the entire castle." },
            { 738222766, "Well, that explains the bouncer." },
            { 738222767, "Let's get this over with, shall we?" },
            { 738222769, "Having her illusions shattered can't be doing Olas much good." },
            { 738222770, "We should find her before she regains her composure." },
            { 738222771, "Hello?" },
            { 738222772, "I'm here!" },
            { 738222773, "I'm done playing games." },
            { 738222774, "Face me!" },
            { 738222775, "Curious." },
            { 738222776, "Hello?" },
            { 738222777, "She's dead?" },
            { 738222778, "Oh." },
            { 738222779, "Which means we don't have to fight her. Lucky us." },
            { 738222780, "What kind of a sick joke is this?" },
            { 738222781, "Perhaps the strain of maintaining all those illusions wore her out." },
            { 738222782, "Let's go. You know the drill." },
            { 738222783, "Hey. What are you doing?" },
            { 738222786, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222787, "And for the last time..." },
            { 738222788, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222789, "Don't. Call. Me. Cuff." },
            { 738222790, "I think I get it now..." },
            { 738222791, "Gasp! You don't mean..." },
            { 738222792, "That's what the Tantas were talking about..." },
            { 738222793, "Oh, I want you to say it. Please say it!" },
            { 738222794, "They weren't talking about me at all!" },
            { 738222795, "Say it... Say it!" },
            { 738222796, "It's you..." },
            { 738222797, "You're the demon!" },
            { 738222798, "Huzzah! Finally!" },
            { 738222799, "The Tantas weren't afraid of you, Frey." },
            { 738222800, "It was what you carried inside." },
            { 738222801, "It was me!" },
            { 738222802, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222803, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222804, "And thank you so much for your help." },
            { 738222805, "Returning me to my former glory..." },
            { 738222806, "Helping me to defeat my captors, and allowing me to fulfill my destiny!" },
            { 738222807, "Destiny?" },
            { 738222808, "Revenge." },
            { 738222809, "Payback for an unforgivable crime." },
            { 738222810, "Do you really think the Rheddig would just crawl away and die after what the Tantas did to them? Oh, no, no, no." },
            { 738222814, "See Frey run! Run from the law, run from responsibility, run from herself!" },
            { 738222815, "Whiny, ungrateful, selfish child." },
            { 738222816, "You think a few days of \"noble deeds\" make you a hero?" },
            { 738222817, "Awww, did you think we were actually becoming \"best buds\"?" },
            { 738222818, "I do hope I haven't made your \"trust issues\" even more nauseatingly all-consuming." },
            { 738222819, "Well, this has been fun, but I think it's time I do what you couldn't and finally put you out of your misery." },
            { 738222832, "You have no idea how insufferable it's been waiting for this day!" },
            { 738222833, "Really, have you ever listened to yourself?" },
            { 738222834, "Just give up, Frey! Why prolong the inevitable?" },
            { 738222835, "Nowhere to run, nowhere to hide..." },
            { 738222836, "Already out of breath? I'm just getting warmed up." },
            { 738222845, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222846, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222847, "Well, it's been fun, Frey! But all things must come to an end." },
            { 738222848, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222849, "Oh, isn't this touching. The mother tries to save her child." },
            { 738222850, "\"Mother\"? Holy shit..." },
            { 738222851, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222852, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222853, "Is that it?" },
            { 738222854, "Sorry to cut this reunion short!" },
            { 738222863, "Arise, daughter of Cinta." },
            { 738222864, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222865, "Where am I?" },
            { 738222866, "This is Svargana, the Wellspring." },
            { 738222867, "The resting place for the knowledge and history of Athia, and the souls of Tantas long since gone." },
            { 738222868, "It's time you learned the truth." },
            { 738222869, "Long ago, we Athians went to war with the Rheddig, inhabitants of a land not so far from our own..." },
            { 738222870, "The war was won. But it was a hollow victory." },
            { 738222871, "The scars left by the war were deep and many. Resources began to dwindle." },
            { 738222873, "Though I tried to enact new laws to limit the damage, I could not stem the tide." },
            { 738222874, "Each of us believed the problem should be solved differently." },
            { 738222875, "Though we knew one another as we knew ourselves, a rift grew between us." },
            { 738222876, "I searched desperately for a way to bridge the growing gap." },
            { 738222877, "We were so distracted by our infighting that we were blind to the Rheddig's final act of war." },
            { 738222878, "They sent an unspeakable evil. A creature of untold power, utterly devoid of mercy." },
            { 738222879, "Susurrus. With great effort, we contained its wickedness." },
            { 738222880, "This battle won, soon another began..." },
            { 738222881, "The demon lived on inside each of us." },
            { 738222882, "Taunting us. Driving us mad." },
            { 738222883, "Desperate to diffuse its strength, we resolved to distance ourselves from one another." },
            { 738222884, "Our sanity lost, we were no longer our people's protectors." },
            { 738222885, "Instead, we were a threat." },
            { 738222886, "It's my fault he's free!" },
            { 738222887, "This place..." },
            { 738222888, "It feels...so familiar..." },
            { 738222889, "Wow. That's one hell of a crib." },
            { 738222890, "Who's the lucky kid?" },
            { 738222891, "Alice in Wonderland..." },
            { 738222892, "What's this doing here?" },
            { 738222893, "Hold on, this...this was in fake New York..." },
            { 738222894, "Wonder who it's for." },
            { 738222895, "Whose room is this?" },
            { 738222896, "Could this be—no..." },
            { 738222897, "Alfre..." },
            { 738222898, "This is the room where you were born." },
            { 738222899, "The room where we would have spent so many happy hours together..." },
            { 738222900, "Why did you abandon me?" },
            { 738222901, "I was already carrying you when we contained the demon." },
            { 738222902, "As its curse took hold, I feared I would lose my mind entirely..." },
            { 738222903, "I could not risk your coming to harm by my hand." },
            { 738222904, "And so..." },
            { 738222905, "I sent you away..." },
            { 738222907, "I never thought I'd see you again..." },
            { 738222908, "You must hate me for what I did." },
            { 738222909, "Well, yeah." },
            { 738222910, "But I...guess you did what you thought was best." },
            { 738222911, "As a mother, I wish more than anything you did not have to face the battle ahead." },
            { 738222912, "As a Tanta, I cannot help but pray you will choose to fight for Athia." },
            { 738222913, "But only you can make that choice." },
            { 738222914, "You need some time to think? That is understandable." },
            { 738222915, "Have you made your decision?" },
            { 738222916, "I have to talk to Cinta." },
            { 738222917, "Can't put this off much longer..." },
            { 738222918, "I gotta get back." },
            { 738222919, "This is your choice? So be it." },
            { 738222920, "Goodbye, Alfre." },
            { 738222921, "I will always love you." },
            { 738222922, "I can't just let go of what he did." },
            { 738222923, "And I need to kick his ass for it." },
            { 738222924, "But I don't have any powers! They were all his!" },
            { 738222925, "No, my child." },
            { 738222926, "You are a Tanta. The power lies within you." },
            { 738222927, "And you will have your mother by your side." },
            { 738222928, "Sorry, Homer..." },
            { 738222929, "Alright." },
            { 738222930, "Let's do this." },
            { 738222931, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222933, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222934, "We have to help them!" },
            { 738222935, "Hang in there, everyone..." },
            { 738222936, "You alright?" },
            { 738222937, "Thank you!" },
            { 738222938, "Can you still walk?" },
            { 738222939, "Yes...I think I can." },
            { 738222940, "Made it. Just in time!" },
            { 738222941, "You saved my life!" },
            { 738222942, "Are you hurt?" },
            { 738222943, "No, I think I'll be okay." },
            { 738222944, "You're safe now." },
            { 738222945, "Thank you!" },
            { 738222946, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222947, "Shit! I didn't make it..." },
            { 738222948, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222949, "Fuck!" },
            { 738222950, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222951, "I'm sorry..." },
            { 738222952, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222953, "This can't be happening..." },
            { 738222954, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738222955, "ウソ……！" },
            { 738222960, "That's one of the big fuckers down." },
            { 738222961, "I've gotta do something about the rest." },
            { 738222962, "Should check if there's any more of the big guys left..." },
            { 738222963, "I think that's all of them." },
            { 738222964, "This way!" },
            { 738222965, "Mummy? Daddy?" },
            { 738222966, "Bloody well hurry up!" },
            { 738222967, "Mummy! Daddy! Mummy! Da..." },
            { 738222968, "Come on, love." },
            { 738222969, "Councilman." },
            { 738222970, "Is that everybody?" },
            { 738222971, "Wasn't sure you'd be back." },
            { 738222972, "Me neither." },
            { 738222973, "Took you long enough." },
            { 738222974, "I came as fast as I could." },
            { 738222975, "No—to figure out that Athia's your home." },
            { 738222976, "Thanks." },
            { 738222977, "Auden!" },
            { 738222978, "Frey!" },
            { 738222979, "Are you okay?" },
            { 738222980, "Yes, considering." },
            { 738222981, "The Break from Visoria finally stopped, and then something much worse appeared!" },
            { 738222982, "Calm down, everyone. Calm down!" },
            { 738222983, "Please, please! You will all be safe in here!" },
            { 738222984, "\"Safe\"? Councilman, we are huddled in the archives! There is nowhere safe left!" },
            { 738222985, "Listen to me! Listen to me, everyone!" },
            { 738222986, "Do not lose hope!" },
            { 738222987, "I don't want to die! My sister, she could be still out there!" },
            { 738222989, "I'm not gonna let this demon take more than he already has." },
            { 738222990, "Hey! Hey! Everybody! Everybody, listen up!" },
            { 738222991, "There's a demon coming." },
            { 738222992, "And no, it's not me. Okay?" },
            { 738222993, "I'm gonna take it on." },
            { 738222994, "I'm gonna put an end to this madness, but I need you to promise me something." },
            { 738222995, "I need you to rebuild. I need you to restore peace to Athia." },
            { 738222996, "Come on, Frey. You've got this." },
            { 738222997, "Is that the best you can do, Cinta?" },
            { 738222998, "Your beloved sisters aren't here to help you this time!" },
            { 738222999, "You can't so much as scratch me on your own!" },
            { 738223000, "Pitiful, corruption-ravaged creature!" },
            { 738223002, "Time to end this fucker." },
            { 738223003, "Oh, just look at the two of you. How adorable." },
            { 738223004, "But what you're doing is completely futile. You have no idea what you're up against!" },
            { 738223005, "What could you possibly do when even the four Tantas couldn't stop me?" },
            { 738223006, "Shame. I had been hoping for a challenge." },
            { 738223026, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223027, "Fuck!" },
            { 738223028, "You can't protect your child from me!" },
            { 738223030, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223031, "You couldn't then, and you can't now!" },
            { 738223032, "Graaargh!" },
            { 738223033, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223034, "No! No..." },
            { 738223035, "You can't die. Not yet, not now, I..." },
            { 738223036, "I have so much to say, I have so many questions..." },
            { 738223037, "I... No, no..." },
            { 738223038, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223039, "No... No please, please don't go..." },
            { 738223040, "I don't need your powers... I need you!" },
            { 738223041, "Please, don't die!" },
            { 738223042, "Thank you, Alfre." },
            { 738223043, "I am so lucky to have you." },
            { 738223044, "And I will always be with you..." },
            { 738223045, "Beloved..." },
            { 738223046, "Your protector has fallen." },
            { 738223047, "So...how do you fancy your chances on your own?" },
            { 738223048, "You going to put up a fight?" },
            { 738223049, "I warned you to be careful what you wish for." },
            { 738223055, "You have not defeated me yet!" },
            { 738223056, "Cuff, can't we just—" },
            { 738223057, "Vengeance will be mine!" },
            { 738223058, "You will pay for this, Frey!" },
            { 738223059, "I won't be the one paying, pal." },
            { 738223060, "Huh?" },
            { 738223061, "Sorry. I'm not letting you break Cipal." },
            { 738223083, "Cuff... I don't get why you—" },
            { 738223084, "You will never \"get\" me, Frey." },
            { 738223085, "How could you? You purposeless, meaningless wretch!" },
            { 738223086, "You're right. I probably wouldn't." },
            { 738223087, "But one thing I do get is you're not alone..." },
            { 738223088, "Even when you think you are." },
            { 738223089, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223090, "Oh, spare me." },
            { 738223091, "No, please! Please don't, please—" },
            { 738223092, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223093, "It's been nice knowing you, Frey." },
            { 738223094, "But it's time to say goodbye!" },
            { 738223095, "Frey, can you hear me?" },
            { 738223096, "Please wake up!" },
            { 738223097, "Frey... Frey!" },
            { 738223098, "Well, get up, girl!" },
            { 738223099, "What're you doing, lying there?" },
            { 738223100, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223101, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223102, "Careful." },
            { 738223103, "What happened?" },
            { 738223104, "Thanks, Mom..." },
            { 738223105, "Frey, Cipal is thriving now that you've cleared the Break." },
            { 738223106, "But it's still out there in all the realms..." },
            { 738223107, "And I lost the power to reverse it. I wish I could figure out how to do it again..." },
            { 738223108, "I'll continue to study my father's notes on reversing the Break." },
            { 738223109, "You know, if there was someone who would have known, it was Bob." },
            { 738223110, "Indeed." },
            { 738223111, "You know, the Council would welcome you as a member." },
            { 738223112, "We're alive and prospering because of you." },
            { 738223113, "Look, okay. Don't think I did all of this just for Athia." },
            { 738223114, "News flash: I'm not that altruistic." },
            { 738223115, "Uh-huh." },
            { 738223116, "Look, the Council gig, it's...not for me." },
            { 738223117, "But I can think of someone who'd be pretty good at it." },
            { 738223118, "Who?" },
            { 738223119, "You, dumbass!" },
            { 738223120, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223121, "You're the glue that holds this whole place together! You step up." },
            { 738223122, "You look after the injured. You inspire people." },
            { 738223123, "I couldn't think of anyone else better for the job." },
            { 738223124, "There you are, Auden." },
            { 738223125, "Johedy's been looking for you." },
            { 738223126, "Oh, yes. Of course." },
            { 738223127, "Would you look at that—you're needed!" },
            { 738223128, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738223129, "Alright, see you later." },
            { 738223130, "Say hi to Jo for me." },
            { 738223131, "And now the real work begins." },
            { 738223132, "TO NEXT" },
            { 738223137, "The castle town used to be filled with people, you know." },
            { 738223138, "Maybe one day it will come alive again." },
            { 738223139, "When the Tantas are gone..." },
            { 738223140, "Cuff..." },
            { 738223141, "Don't worry. I'm sure there are plenty of other people with incredible powers around who can kill them instead of you." },
            { 738223142, "I am seriously warning you." },
            { 738223143, "What? I'm just thinking aloud!" },
            { 738223144, "No, you're not. You're trying to guilt trip me." },
            { 738223145, "Not in the slightest." },
            { 738223287, "NEXT" },
            { 738223288, "CHAPTER 1" },
            { 738223289, "CHAPTER 2" },
            { 738223290, "CHAPTER 3" },
            { 738223292, "CHAPTER 5" },
            { 738223293, "CHAPTER 6" },
            { 738223294, "CHAPTER 7" },
            { 738223295, "CHAPTER 8" },
            { 738223296, "CHAPTER 9" },
            { 738223297, "CHAPTER 10" },
            { 738223298, "CHAPTER 11" },
            { 738223299, "CHAPTER 12" },
            { 738223300, "Contents Location Test" },
            { 738223301, "Location Cleared" },
            { 738223328, "Don't worry. Auden told me about you." },
            { 738223329, "Don't go near the gate. It's crawling with guards." },
            { 738223330, "Well, now! I've not seen you around before. Hello!" },
            { 738223331, "Did you know there are monsters out there that can fly? Actually fly! Fancy that!" },
            { 738223332, "Not that you believe me, of course. No one does..." },
            { 738223333, "Tanta's blessings be upon you." },
            { 738223334, "You! You are the escapee!" },
            { 738223335, "P-please, I beg of you! Do not harm the children!" },
            { 738223336, "Tanta's blessings! Hang on—who the heck are you?" },
            { 738223337, "You're not the one they're saying came from outside the city, are you?" },
            { 738223338, "Well, just don't go causing any mischief, you hear?" },
            { 738223339, "There's even more guards out looking for you than yesterday." },
            { 738223340, "And Councilwoman Dax is in charge of them. Be warned: she's not to be messed with." },
            { 738223341, "That soup they served us today didn't taste of anything at all!" },
            { 738223342, "And that rotten councilman said we'd get the same food as the upper city!" },
            { 738223343, "A likely story! Liars, the lot of them!" },
            { 738223344, "Hey, hey! Are you the girl I heard about? The one who came from outside the city?" },
            { 738223345, "What's it like out there? Come on! Tell me, tell me! I want to know!" },
            { 738223346, "Oh, wait—my mum says I'm not supposed to talk to strangers..." },
            { 738223347, "I'm so glad they have cats in Athia too..." },
            { 738223348, "Why, exactly? Do you have some special attachment to the ridiculous little creatures?" },
            { 738223349, "Huh? What? No!" },
            { 738223350, "Miss ya, Homer..." },
            { 738223351, "Tanta Sila's in the city! And she's out for blood!" },
            { 738223352, "People are dying!" },
            { 738223353, "Auden! She's up in the square! You have to hurry!" },
            { 738223354, "Is it true you mean to face Tanta Sila on your own?" },
            { 738223355, "I must say, you don't look like a girl with a death wish." },
            { 738223356, "Did the Cognoscents' Guild really collapse?" },
            { 738223357, "Just think how much priceless knowledge must have been lost..." },
            { 738223358, "The other Guilds remain standing, of course, but...for how long?" },
            { 738223359, "There was a dear, sweet young girl used to come here, you know. Name of Olevia." },
            { 738223360, "Such a bright spark! A real breath of fresh air, she was. And then..." },
            { 738223361, "Why, Tanta Sila... Why?" },
            { 738223362, "Robian Keen, returned to us at last! Who would have thought it!" },
            { 738223363, "I'm from Junoon, you know. Same as him." },
            { 738223364, "Does a lot for the old civic pride, having countrymen like that, I can tell you." },
            { 738223365, "You're not really going after Tanta Sila, are you?" },
            { 738223366, "Suppose it's better than you loitering around town any longer..." },
            { 738223367, "Y-you're here to read, you say!?" },
            { 738223368, "Oh! I-I'm sorry, it's just...no one in Cipal has any interest in books these days." },
            { 738223369, "Auden's over the moon to have her father back." },
            { 738223370, "I don't think I've ever seen her so happy!" },
            { 738223371, "I'd say we owe you a thank-you." },
            { 738223372, "You're the criminal who came from the Corruption, aren't you?" },
            { 738223373, "Well, stay out of the upper city! We don't want you tainting us with it!" },
            { 738223374, "I'm so happy the crops weren't ruined!" },
            { 738223375, "My dad said if we didn't have any grain, we'd all starve to death..." },
            { 738223376, "The cats in the upper city certainly aren't afraid of anyone, are they?" },
            { 738223377, "Yeah. They're cute. But they're not Homer." },
            { 738223378, "I don't know how you even tell one from another, to be honest..." },
            { 738223379, "Look at him! He looks like he's standing guard." },
            { 738223380, "That, or he's still petrified after everything that's happened." },
            { 738223381, "Yeah, I guess they do have a pretty keen sense of danger, don't they?" },
            { 738223429, "A beverage fit for a king." },
            { 738223430, "There's kind of a bitter edge to it... Could get used to that." },
            { 738223445, "Oh, that's a shame. Ah, well..." },
            { 738223451, "Thanks a million! You're the best!" },
            { 738223452, "Here, this is for you." },
            { 738223504, "RETURN TO TITLE SCREEN" },
            { 738223506, "Return to the title screen." },
            { 738223507, "Are you sure you want to exit to the title screen?" },
            { 738223508, "Select difficulty level." },
            { 738223509, "EASY" },
            { 738223510, "NORMAL" },
            { 738223511, "HARD" },
            { 738223512, "Ideal for players who want to enjoy the story at their own pace." },
            { 738223513, "Recommended for those who want to enjoy the action." },
            { 738223514, "Perfect for players who enjoy a challenge." },
            { 738223516, "You actually managed to exercise some self-control. I'm impressed." },
            { 738223517, "Not as impressed as I am." },
            { 738223518, "They're not worth your time. You did the right thing." },
            { 738223522, "You only went and killed Tanta Sila, didn't you?" },
            { 738223523, "Good on you! That's no mean feat!" },
            { 738223524, "It's...good to see you back safe and sound." },
            { 738223525, "Auden will be relieved, that's for certain." },
            { 738223526, "They're making special food at the tavern, I heard!" },
            { 738223527, "We never had special food ever!" },
            { 738223528, "They're having a celebration at the tavern because you beat Tanta Sila!" },
            { 738223529, "I'm not sure why that's a good thing, but...if everyone's happy, I'm happy." },
            { 738223533, "The Corruption! Here in Cipal! Will it reach even to the upper city!?" },
            { 738223534, "Please! I am too young to die!" },
            { 738223535, "Why... Why!?" },
            { 738223536, "Save us! Someone save us!" },
            { 738223537, "I can't die now!" },
            { 738223538, "I never even got to see those flying monsters!" },
            { 738223539, "Mum! Where are you!?" },
            { 738223540, "Demon! Accursed creature! This is all your fault!" },
            { 738223541, "It was you who brought the Corruption to our doorstep!" },
            { 738223542, "I tried to warn them! Again and again, I tried!" },
            { 738223543, "But no! They would not hear it! And now here we are." },
            { 738223544, "How the mighty are fallen. You know, I almost feel sorry for him." },
            { 738223545, "Well, I sure don't. Once an asshole, always an asshole." },
            { 738223546, "I have nothing more to say to you!" },
            { 738223547, "So many lie injured and dying..." },
            { 738223548, "Can this truly be the will of the Tantas?" },
            { 738223549, "Why is this happening? What have we done?" },
            { 738223550, "I don't deserve this! I'm a good person!" },
            { 738223551, "The pasture's been swallowed by the Corruption. How are we supposed to make what little food we have last now?" },
            { 738223552, "If only Tanta Prav were here. She'd help us find a way to share it fairly..." },
            { 738223553, "Except...she wouldn't. She can't. Not anymore." },
            { 738223554, "Robian Keen's a marvel, I tell you!" },
            { 738223555, "That ballow concoction of his might just save the city!" },
            { 738223556, "If one Tanta can come and attack the city, what's to stop the others?" },
            { 738223557, "Please, you must put an end to their madness once and for all!" },
            { 738223558, "I have a child to think about! Have you any idea how that feels?" },
            { 738223559, "You alright? You don't look so well." },
            { 738223560, "Auden's worried about you too." },
            { 738223561, "I'm surprised she even noticed. She's looking pretty worn out herself." },
            { 738223562, "We've lost half our livestock to the Corruption!" },
            { 738223563, "I need to get this little lot to safety, but where?" },
            { 738223564, "Those who were touched by the Corruption have been taken to the council chambers." },
            { 738223565, "But what if they turn into monsters and attack us all?" },
            { 738223566, "I found my mum...but she got hurt quite badly." },
            { 738223567, "She's resting up at home, but I'm really worried about her." },
            { 738223568, "Well, at least this little guy survived." },
            { 738223569, "For now, at least." },
            { 738223570, "Whoa. Poor thing's terrified." },
            { 738223571, "One's home falling apart around one's ears will tend to do that." },
            { 738223572, "They let you run free and imprison me?" },
            { 738223573, "Has the Council lost its collective mind!?" },
            { 738223574, "Or did you work your wicked influence?" },
            { 738223575, "You will not corrupt me, girl! Never!" },
            { 738223576, "Cipal's done for! Who's going to save us now?" },
            { 738223577, "And just when I thought things might finally be getting better..." },
            { 738223578, "Auden's father—he's..." },
            { 738223579, "You need to get to the council chambers right away." },
            { 738223580, "No matter what I do, I can't seem to calm this lot down." },
            { 738223581, "Hope it doesn't mean something else awful's on the way..." },
            { 738223582, "What brings you here?" },
            { 738223583, "What is this, anyway?" },
            { 738223584, "Something he went to the trouble of keeping..." },
            { 738223585, "Must be tough, feeling like your Tanta abandoned you..." },
            { 738223586, "The chain of unending sadness must be broken." },
            { 738223587, "Tanta's blessings go with you." },
            { 738223589, "My...my memories of Visoria are hazy... Why?" },
            { 738223590, "I have asked others among my countrymen, and it seems I am far from an isolated case." },
            { 738223591, "I shall not rest until this mystery is solved." },
            { 738223592, "Robian Keen is dead." },
            { 738223593, "If anyone could have saved Cipal, it was him." },
            { 738223594, "Suppose we'll just have to resign ourselves to our fate..." },
            { 738223595, "I haven't seen Auden yet today." },
            { 738223596, "She usually comes by to check on the sick and injured." },
            { 738223597, "Suppose it's no surprise after all that's happened, though..." },
            { 738223598, "Robian finally gave up the ghost, eh? Shame. He's the only one who believed my little stories." },
            { 738223599, "Would have been nice to be able to show him my flying monsters really do exist." },
            { 738223600, "Is it true you defeated another of the Tantas?" },
            { 738223601, "Gosh. You really are something." },
            { 738223602, "Not going to check on your little friend?" },
            { 738223603, "Not in the mood." },
            { 738223604, "Oh." },
            { 738223605, "Huh." },
            { 738223606, "Someone's warming to you..." },
            { 738223607, "Whatever. Let's go." },
            { 738223608, "We'll be safe in here!" },
            { 738223609, "Is everyone going to die?" },
            { 738223610, "We'll be fine! Frey will save the day, you'll see!" },
            { 738223611, "I'm going to do what you asked us. I'm going to make sure we survive." },
            { 738223612, "I have to do everything I can for these children." },
            { 738223613, "And there are things you have to do too, right? Good luck. And stay safe." },
            { 738223614, "Stay safe." },
            { 738223642, "Wonder what Jo wants to talk to me about..." },
            { 738223643, "Indeed." },
            { 738223647, "There you are." },
            { 738223648, "So? You had something to tell me about my mother?" },
            { 738223649, "You." },
            { 738223650, "And how does it feel to be Cipal's exalted savior?" },
            { 738223677, "Well, this is a turn-up for the books. Literally." },
            { 738223678, "Shut the fuck up." },
            { 738223679, "Gosh. Someone's clearly feeling touchy." },
            { 738223680, "This is literally the last thing I want to do. But I can't not go and ask him now." },
            { 738223682, "You're not going to thank him, are you?" },
            { 738223683, "Hah! No." },
            { 738223684, "So...what exactly are you doing?" },
            { 738223685, "Just...shut it, alright?" },
            { 738223686, "The former councilman...he escaped." },
            { 738223687, "We heard something and came as fast as we could, but he was already gone." },
            { 738223688, "Gone? Gone where?" },
            { 738223689, "Good question. He would have had to have left town, but..." },
            { 738223690, "Before you suggest it, there's no point looking for him. You're the last person he'll give himself up to." },
            { 738223691, "Do you think he was ever really loyal to my mom?" },
            { 738223692, "Faith undermined by perceived abandonment, sadness turned to hate... His stated motives are certainly plausible." },
            { 738223693, "Yeah. Think I might even know how he feels..." },
            { 738223694, "Tanta's blessings." },
            { 738223695, "The city is alive again at last!" },
            { 738223696, "Things haven't been like this since the time of the Tantas." },
            { 738223697, "The town is taking shape again around us." },
            { 738223698, "And a smile is no longer the rare sight it once was." },
            { 738223699, "You must speak to the people. I'm sure they would be overjoyed to greet their savior." },
            { 738223700, "We, too, must begin to look ahead." },
            { 738223701, "When all is restored, what kind of city do we want to see? What kind of world do we wish to live in?" },
            { 738223702, "I still can't quite believe I survived through everything." },
            { 738223703, "I owe you my life. We all do." },
            { 738223704, "I've been fraternizing with what you might call the \"common people.\" An intriguing bunch, I must say." },
            { 738223705, "I thought the lower city was nothing but street drunks and ne'er-do-wells, if I'm brutally honest." },
            { 738223706, "But now I see I was very much mistaken. Wonderful people. Just lovely." },
            { 738223707, "You know, I think we might have relied on the Tantas rather too much back in the day." },
            { 738223708, "It's time we took our fate into our own hands." },
            { 738223709, "I have been speaking with Master Treahy." },
            { 738223710, "He wishes to turn this place into a school of sorts. A noble scheme indeed." },
            { 738223711, "But I am glad it is not I who must raise it with the archivist. She is...an intimidating figure, to say the least." },
            { 738223712, "If only I had access to the boundless wisdom of Tanta Olas..." },
            { 738223713, "But no—to lament its loss is futile. We must learn to live without it." },
            { 738223714, "So many have died..." },
            { 738223715, "But perhaps brighter times are ahead." },
            { 738223716, "Wonderful news: the Corruption has cleared from the graveyard!" },
            { 738223717, "I pray that those who lie there may rest more peacefully now." },
            { 738223718, "Coming here cannot help but remind one of how many we have lost." },
            { 738223719, "Young Olevia among them... She watches over us, I am sure." },
            { 738223720, "The rebuilding's coming on in leaps and bounds. But there's a long way to go yet." },
            { 738223721, "And we need to think about how we're going to get there." },
            { 738223722, "There needs to be a shake-up at the Council." },
            { 738223723, "Councilwoman Bellette's...just about holding things together, sure." },
            { 738223724, "But we need someone to bring the upper and lower cities together. The lower city needs a voice." },
            { 738223725, "We used to have Tanta Prav to teach us about fairness and balance." },
            { 738223726, "But she's not with us anymore. We have to learn that lesson for ourselves now." },
            { 738223727, "D'you think Robian's ballow concoction can help drive back the Corruption?" },
            { 738223728, "Bit of a long shot, perhaps. But it's important to stay optimistic, don't you think?" },
            { 738223729, "The scholars have been teaching us all how to read." },
            { 738223730, "Imagine, one day I might be able to sit down and go through Robian's notes myself!" },
            { 738223731, "A few of us have been talking about how we might be able to grow more ballow trees." },
            { 738223732, "It won't be easy, but I'm going to do everything I can to make it happen." },
            { 738223733, "I've been praying for a long and happy life for my little one." },
            { 738223734, "Now that I think about it, perhaps the one I should have been praying to is you." },
            { 738223735, "This one's father was lost when the Corruption invaded the city..." },
            { 738223736, "I can't have that loss be for nothing. Our child will have a good life. I'll make sure of it." },
            { 738223737, "I've never seen a child so much like their father." },
            { 738223738, "If you've inherited even half your papa's kindness of spirit, we'll be blessed indeed." },
            { 738223739, "You'll never believe it, but people are coming in here and actually asking for books to read!" },
            { 738223740, "I can't tell you how happy it makes me!" },
            { 738223741, "There's talk of trying to grow more ballow trees, but I'm afraid that's easier said than done." },
            { 738223742, "It's not completely impossible, though. Where there's a will, there's a way!" },
            { 738223743, "I should think there are plenty of Tanta Olas's writings still out there in Athia." },
            { 738223744, "Perhaps one of them holds the key to finally ridding us of the Corruption entirely." },
            { 738223745, "Thank goodness the crops weren't ruined." },
            { 738223746, "If there's one thing that keeps me going, it's the thought of being able to keep everyone fed." },
            { 738223747, "You've been eating your fill too, I hope? Just say the word if you want a little bite to keep you going." },
            { 738223748, "I'm sure I can rustle you up a loaf of bread. It's not much, but it's something." },
            { 738223749, "Once the Corruption finally clears from around the city, we'll have more room to grow things." },
            { 738223750, "No guarantee that's going to happen, of course. But if and when it does, I'll be ready to do my bit!" },
            { 738223751, "Auden seems as rushed off her feet as ever." },
            { 738223752, "But she seems a little chirpier than she was, at least." },
            { 738223753, "Tanta's blessings to you." },
            { 738223754, "It's funny. Those words had started to ring very hollow until not so long ago." },
            { 738223755, "But it feels as natural saying it now as it ever did. And very glad I am too." },
            { 738223756, "My mum used to be a smith under Auden's mother's watchful eye, you know." },
            { 738223757, "It's funny how we're all connected one way or the other, eh?" },
            { 738223758, "I always wanted to see a flying monster in real life!" },
            { 738223759, "And then one came and saved the city! What a way for a wish to come true!" },
            { 738223760, "The soup's been a little tastier lately." },
            { 738223761, "My complaints must've made it up the chain at last!" },
            { 738223762, "Now if they could only see their way to putting a little meat in it..." },
            { 738223763, "Funny. Looking at you puts me in mind of the Tantas back in the good old days." },
            { 738223764, "Wonder what that's all about..." },
            { 738223765, "The pasture's been restored to its former glory." },
            { 738223766, "And not a moment too soon. My little lovelies missed it something awful!" },
            { 738223767, "The animals are over the moon to be back in the pasture." },
            { 738223768, "And I'm over the moon to see it. Warms the cockles of my heart!" },
            { 738223769, "It's still dangerous outside the city, what with the monsters roaming the highways and byways." },
            { 738223770, "But hopefully, one day it'll be safe enough for the animals to be put out there to pasture." },
            { 738223771, "Miss Frey! You couldn't teach me how to fight, could you?" },
            { 738223772, "I want to help the people as you do!" },
            { 738223773, "I'm going to grow big and strong so that I can protect the city." },
            { 738223774, "Can you look after things in the meantime?" },
            { 738223775, "Father tells me he once worked for one of the Tantas." },
            { 738223776, "And I'm hoping to follow in his footsteps...by working for you!" },
            { 738223777, "I shall be doing my best to toughen up in preparation!" },
            { 738223778, "Do you think we'll be able to go outside the city soon?" },
            { 738223779, "When my mum's better, I want to visit Junoon with her. That's where we're from." },
            { 738223780, "Master Treahy's teaching us about the history of Athia." },
            { 738223781, "And when everything's better, I'm going to go and see it all!" },
            { 738223782, "Do you like learning things, Frey?" },
            { 738223783, "My mum says I should learn everything I can because it will help me out in the future." },
            { 738223784, "It's funny... She never used to talk about the future at all." },
            { 738223785, "My dad says the crops are growing beautifully!" },
            { 738223786, "I hope that means we won't all be hungry all the time anymore." },
            { 738223787, "Maybe we'll even have enough for a feast!" },
            { 738223788, "Can I tell you a secret, Frey?" },
            { 738223789, "I might be having a little brother or sister!" },
            { 738223790, "I'm so excited!" },
            { 738223791, "You're a Tanta now, aren't you, Frey?" },
            { 738223792, "So does that mean when I say, \"Tanta's blessings,\" I mean...your blessings?" },
            { 738223793, "Frey's blessings to everyone!" },
            { 738223794, "Business as usual, huh, little guy?" },
            { 738223795, "How's life treating ya?" },
            { 738223796, "Looking bright-eyed and bushy-tailed, little friend!" },
            { 738223797, "So good to see you made it through all that shit in one piece." },
            { 738223798, "I'll bet it's nice to be back home again, huh?" },
            { 738223799, "Hey, we're friends, right? Good. Keep it that way." },
