            { 738225042, "GUR START" },
            { 738225043, "CHAPTER 4 DEPARTURE" },
            { 738225044, "CHAPTER 5 BOSS" },
            { 738225045, "CHAPTER 7-13" },
            { 738225046, "You think you can just wander in here uninvited?" },
            { 738225047, "How dare you disturb the sleep of the deserving!" },
            { 738225048, "Tanta Sila didn't come as far as the pasture. There's that to be thankful for, at least." },
            { 738225049, "These little lovelies are worth more to us now than ever." },
            { 738225050, "Wool, milk, meat, even parchment—you name it, we need them for it." },
            { 738225051, "That's the graveyard." },
            { 738225052, "Everyone who ever died in Cipal is buried there." },
            { 738225053, "Only trouble is, there's too many of them now to mourn..." },
            { 738225055, "SCS - Frey washes up on an island near the castle\nFrey: Did you know I was Cinta's daughter?\nCuff: That's a conversation for another time." },
            { 738225056, "LPEV - Cuff: Breakbob may know something.\nFrey: Guess we're going back to Cipal." },
            { 738225057, "Another Triumphant Return" },
            { 738225058, "Leave Avoalet" },
            { 738225059, "LPEV - Breakstorm" },
            { 738225060, "LPEV - Colossal Nightmare appears\nBreakstorm blocks escape\nSeeing Nightmare for first time lines" },
            { 738225062, "Defeat the Nightmare" },
            { 738225063, "Battle - Vs. Colossal Nightmare (Start)" },
            { 738225064, "LPEV - Vs. Colossal Nightmare (Hint)" },
            { 738225065, "Escape from the Nightmare" },
            { 738225066, "LPEV - Nightmare gives chase\nBlack Dragon attacks Nightmare\nEscape while they're fighting\nHAS - Black Dragon sends Nightmare flying" },
            { 738225067, "LPEV - Nightmare gives chase while the stairs crumble\nHAS - Black Dragon gives chase" },
            { 738225068, "LPEV - Breakstorm begins\nHAS - Nightmare attacks the stairs\nBlack Dragon starts charging a beam attack" },
            { 738225069, "LPEV - Escape to the sanctuary\nHAS - Black Dragon fires beam at Nightmare, Frey closes door just in time\nThat was close, let's get out of here" },
            { 738225074, "Return to Cipal" },
            { 738225075, "LPEV - Frey: Am I really a Tanta's kid?\nCuff: They were driven mad, remember?" },
            { 738225076, "LPEV - Cuff: That must be why you're unaffected by the Break.\nFrey: Am I going to go crazy too?" },
            { 738225077, "LPEV - Frey: I feel like meeting you wasn't just coincidence.\nCuff: So you believe in destiny now?" },
            { 738225078, "LPEV - Frey: What am I supposed to tell everyone now I know?\nCuff: You'd be wise to keep it to yourself." },
            { 738225079, "Return to the Council Courtroom" },
            { 738225080, "PEV - Auden crying in the hall.\nFrey realizes something bad must have happened.\nEnd of quest." },
            { 738225081, "SCS - Breakbob Dies\nEnd of Chapter 9." },
            { 738225141, "Oh man, I wish my in-laws weren't coming..." },
            { 738225142, "Sold out!? Shit! I'm dead!" },
            { 738225143, "I swear, if Grandma gives me another pair of socks this year..." },
            { 738225144, "How many ugly Christmas sweaters am I legally allowed to own?" },
            { 738225145, "Oh my god, I love that window. They always do something so pretty." },
            { 738225146, "That's the perfect gift! She's gonna love it!" },
            { 738225147, "I dropped so many hints even an idiot would know what to buy." },
            { 738225148, "Oh, crap! Gotta get my hair done before the Christmas party..." },
            { 738225149, "Shit. I better get home so we can start dinner..." },
            { 738225150, "Woo! Yeah! Best office party yet!" },
            { 738225151, "Jingle bells, jingle bells... Da-da-da-da-dah..." },
            { 738225152, "Oh, man. The kids are gonna love their new toys!" },
            { 738225153, "Ooh, wonder who my Secret Santa is..." },
            { 738225154, "Ugh, my feet! I can't wait to get inside and have an eggnog!" },
            { 738225155, "The city's so beautiful around the holidays." },
            { 738225156, "Fruitcake! Would you believe I actually like fruitcake?" },
            { 738225157, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738225158, "So the Tantas left these stones behind?" },
            { 738225159, "Yes. Although one can only wonder why..." },
            { 738225160, "Magical...fountain thingies, huh?" },
            { 738225161, "If they're related to the Tantas, perhaps we should go and take a look." },
            { 738225162, "So they used to rule Athia. And people used to like them..." },
            { 738225163, "Yes. Although you'd never guess that now." },
            { 738225165, "Wondering if maybe there's a quieter way in than the front door..." },
            { 738225166, "Sure you're not getting cold feet?" },
            { 738225167, "No. Just learning to look before I leap." },
            { 738225168, "According to the floor plan, that's where the throne room is." },
            { 738225169, "And that's where Sila will be." },
            { 738225170, "There's the gate! Seems as good a way in as any." },
            { 738225171, "Assuming it's not crawling with soldiers in there." },
            { 738225172, "Perhaps we'll get lucky and discover they're all out on maneuvers." },
            { 738225173, "Hey, that cliff..." },
            { 738225174, "The floor plan seems to show a narrow path running up it." },
            { 738225175, "Another way in, maybe." },
            { 738225176, "Another cliff." },
            { 738225177, "Sadly, nothing more than a cliff if the floor plan's anything to go by." },
            { 738225178, "Huh." },
            { 738225179, "I thought I told you—nothing but cliffs in this direction." },
            { 738225180, "Cliffs that lead up to the castle." },
            { 738225181, "We can get in where they least expect it." },
            { 738225182, "Man" },
            { 738225183, "Woman" },
            { 738225184, "Man" },
            { 738225185, "Woman" },
            { 738225186, "Boy" },
            { 738225187, "Don't think we'll be getting any more resin out of this one." },
            { 738225188, "Then I suppose we'd better find another..." },
            { 738225189, "Yeah, okay, that's uh...not gonna happen." },
            { 738225190, "I go with you, it ends bad for me." },
            { 738225191, "Mm-hmm." },
            { 738225192, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738225193, "Or do you merely run from blame?" },
            { 738225194, "Your journey ends here if you fail." },
            { 738225195, "What worth's a pardon lightly won?" },
            { 738225196, "You have got to be fucking kidding me." },
            { 738225197, "Oh, yeah, that seems fair. Score another one for justice!" },
            { 738225198, "Insolent, unrepentant, murderous creature!" },
            { 738225199, "How do I address you now, by the way? Is it \"Your...\"" },
            { 738225200, "\"Your Worship\"? \"Your Highness\"? \"Dame\"?" },
            { 738225201, "I didn't have a community that supported me. I couldn't go and drink with my friends at the bar." },
            { 738225202, "Go and take your inquiries up with your mother." },
            { 738225230, "I've gotta be at the Athian in an hour." },
            { 738225231, "Fine, well...hit me up when you're done, 'kay?" },
            { 738225232, "Alright, sounds good. Good luck!" },
            { 738225233, "Who would wanna go to work on a day like this?" },
            { 738225234, "The knish guy on this block's the best in the city!" },
            { 738225235, "What a beautiful day!" },
            { 738225236, "I got a good feelin' about today! Should definitely buy a lottery ticket." },
            { 738225237, "Maybe I'll skip the subway and walk today!" },
            { 738225238, "I just love buying gifts for people!" },
            { 738225239, "Wow! It's gonna be this sunny all week!" },
            { 738225240, "I could, like, totally go for an ice cream right now." },
            { 738225241, "It's the least I can do." },
            { 738225242, "They always do in the end." },
            { 738225243, "Just as you have let others down. Hm?" },
            { 738225244, "I know." },
            { 738225245, "It's what the Tantas would have wanted." },
            { 738225246, "Maybe between the two of us, we'll find a way." },
            { 738225247, "Damn! That is a lotta land for just one girl to cover." },
            { 738225262, "LPEV - Deal set amount of damage to Colossal Nightmare\nBlack Dragon appears" },
            { 738225263, "Good point. Let's head back over there and take a look." },
            { 738225264, "He didn't used to be like that, you know." },
            { 738225265, "So I hear." },
            { 738225266, "He was the one who brought everyone here when the Corruption swallowed Junoon. Should have been Tanta Cinta..." },
            { 738225267, "But...he was the only other person she would have trusted to do it. And now look at him..." },
            { 738225268, "Anyway, listen to me, talking your ear off. I'm sure you've got more important things to do." },
            { 738225269, "Here. Take this." },
            { 738225270, "Thanks for bringing him back to us." },
            { 738225271, "Uh...sure." },
            { 738225272, "Yes. Although I still struggle to picture the old him..." },
            { 738225273, "Hi. You didn't see Robian come this way, did you?" },
            { 738225274, "I did, yes. He walked past a little while ago." },
            { 738225275, "Dropped this, as a matter of fact." },
            { 738225276, "Huh. It's some kind of...animal bone, right?" },
            { 738225277, "Yes. The one the old man was wearing. But I'm not sure it's what we're looking for." },
            { 738225278, "Um, excuse me. You didn't see Robian around here, did you?" },
            { 738225279, "Hm? Robian Keen?" },
            { 738225280, "Yes, he was pottering about the place not so long ago, in fact. Looking for something, if I'm not mistaken." },
            { 738225281, "Then he seemed to have some sort of brain wave and wandered off." },
            { 738225282, "Rather put me in mind of the old days, I must say." },
            { 738225283, "He used to pace back and forth like a madman when he had something on his mind. Walked holes in many a carpet." },
            { 738225284, "Guess you knew him pretty well?" },
            { 738225285, "You could say that, yes. He was something of a mentor of mine." },
            { 738225286, "It's a dreadful shame, him having lost his memory to the Corruption...but I hold him in the highest regard nonetheless." },
            { 738225287, "Thanks for sharing." },
            { 738225288, "You know the funny old man, don't you?" },
            { 738225289, "The—oh, you mean Bob?" },
            { 738225290, "He dropped this earlier and walked off without noticing." },
            { 738225291, "Can you give it back to him?" },
            { 738225292, "Oh, nice! I've been looking for this...I think. Thanks." },
            { 738225293, "This book is mad old. Can barely even make out the words..." },
            { 738225294, "Luckily, the words are none of our concern. Can we hurry up and get it back to him?" },
            { 738225295, "Hey, Bob. The thing you were looking for—it was this book, right?" },
            { 738225296, "Hm. Seemingly not." },
            { 738225297, "For real? But I went all over to find this thing!" },
            { 738225298, "Father, I—oh, sorry. Were you two in the middle of something?" },
            { 738225299, "No. All good." },
            { 738225300, "I found this when I was tidying up." },
            { 738225301, "A bookmark?" },
            { 738225302, "I made it for him when I was little." },
            { 738225303, "I drew us all on it—Father, Mother...and there's me." },
            { 738225304, "You've found it at last! My heart, my past! Found it!" },
            { 738225305, "Thank you, Audie! My dear, darling girl!" },
            { 738225306, "Better leave them to it..." },
            { 738225309, "Bob never stopped thinking about Auden that whole time, huh?" },
            { 738225310, "A pity to think that he might still forget her after all he's been through..." },
            { 738225311, "Metallurgy...the history of Praenost...military tactics...and art history." },
            { 738225312, "Guess she was a keen reader even back then." },
            { 738225313, "Look at all these designs. Weapons, armor, shields..." },
            { 738225314, "She made all this stuff for Sila. Wow, she must regret it now..." },
            { 738225315, "It's some kind of ledger..." },
            { 738225316, "And Sila's crown is the last thing on the list." },
            { 738225317, "Yeah. The crown we smashed to pieces." },
            { 738225318, "You know, I do wonder how Johedy really feels about her old friend going batshit crazy..." },
            { 738225319, "Damn! This stuff is heavy!" },
            { 738225320, "The reassuring heft of odvaha." },
            { 738225321, "And Johedy spent all day every day hulking this shit around? What is she, part-monster?" },
            { 738225322, "\"Don't judge a book by its cover.\" Haven't I heard that somewhere before?" },
            { 738225323, "Fuck off." },
            { 738225324, "Head back to Cipal?" },
            { 738225325, "Yeah." },
            { 738225326, "No." },
            { 738225327, "Probably won't even do you much good, but...better than nothing, eh?" },
            { 738225328, "Couldn't bear to help Sila anymore after everything she did?" },
            { 738225329, "But the oath we swore? That was pure. And good. And true." },
            { 738225330, "What good had it done to help protect Athia, after all? None, that's what." },
            { 738225331, "And if I'm lucky, the people here will help me find a way to save Athia." },
            { 738225332, "I was never sure if it was the right thing to do..." },
            { 738225333, "She wanted to die in battle." },
            { 738225334, "I was doing some reading about her, and I found this book." },
            { 738225335, "And? Looks like all the others to me." },
            { 738225336, "It's about the fall of Junoon." },
            { 738225337, "The writer mentions Tanta Cinta...being pregnant." },
            { 738225338, "Okay..." },
            { 738225339, "If you go and speak to them, you might be able to learn more about your past." },
            { 738225340, "Wait. Who wrote it?" },
            { 738225341, "Jennesh." },
            { 738225342, "Please tell me you're kidding." },
            { 738225343, "I wish I was. You can take it with you." },
            { 738225344, "People seem very pleased with you indeed." },
            { 738225345, "How nice of them to forget that they once doubted you. Feared you. Cursed your very name." },
            { 738225346, "I need to ask you something." },
            { 738225347, "You knew I was Cinta's daughter, didn't you?" },
            { 738225348, "So that's what this is about." },
            { 738225349, "Very well. Ask what you must." },
            { 738225350, "What should I ask him about?" },
            { 738225351, "Ask about me." },
            { 738225352, "Ask about Cinta." },
            { 738225353, "Ask about my father." },
            { 738225354, "How did they not see it?" },
            { 738225355, "I knew those eyes before you were even born." },
            { 738225356, "They're the same as your mother's." },
            { 738225357, "And I despise them every bit as much." },
            { 738225358, "But how come you knew and nobody else did?" },
            { 738225359, "As far as we were aware, no Tanta had ever been with child before." },
            { 738225360, "So we kept it to ourselves. Me, Robian, and as small a number of her retinue as was practicable." },
            { 738225361, "There was a time when Cinta's love for Athia and its people was endless. Boundless." },
            { 738225362, "But then you began to grow inside her. Her love was compromised. And we were forsaken." },
            { 738225363, "No longer were her affection and dedication the sole province of her people. No... We were forced to share them with you!" },
            { 738225364, "That's—" },
            { 738225365, "And when the Corruption came, we learned what that truly meant." },
            { 738225366, "The skies of our beloved land darkened, and terror tore through the populace like a plague." },
            { 738225367, "But was Cinta's first thought for her people? No. She cared only for your safety." },
            { 738225368, "Junoon, once a realm of boundless wonder—of love—was abandoned by its Tanta long before she lost her mind." },
            { 738225369, "I know nothing of such things." },
            { 738225370, "It is possible that Robian might have done. The other Tantas certainly did not." },
            { 738225371, "Was he from Athia?" },
            { 738225372, "One can only speculate. But the fact that no Tanta had ever borne a child before could conceivably suggest otherwise." },
            { 738225373, "Had your father been Athian, we would surely have discovered it soon enough." },
            { 738225374, "Are you quite done?" },
            { 738225375, "Not quite. Why are you telling me all of this?" },
            { 738225376, "Because I have no desire to owe you anything. You saved the city. And now I have given you something in return." },
            { 738225377, "And I will give you one last thing." },
            { 738225378, "Huh?" },
            { 738225379, "We may not meet again. Consider this my parting gift." },
            { 738225380, "What do you think this key opens?" },
            { 738225381, "If not something here in the city, then something back in Junoon, perhaps?" },
            { 738225382, "Let's go check it out." },
            { 738225384, "A music box?" },
            { 738225385, "Wait..." },
            { 738225386, "I feel like I know this song..." },
            { 738225387, "<UnknownFormatting>\"To my dearest Alfre.\"" },
            { 738225388, "I find out you left me this now?" },
            { 738225389, "What am I supposed to do with that?" },
            { 738225390, "Why are you crying, Alfre?" },
            { 738225391, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738225392, "But I expect you've done a lot of crying, haven't you? I'm so sorry." },
            { 738225393, "I've wanted to do this for so long." },
            { 738225394, "I love you. I love you so much." },
            { 738225395, "I'll keep Athia safe, Mom." },
            { 738225396, "I promise." },
