            { 738227321, "You'll wear yourself out if you're not careful." },
            { 738227322, "Ugh! Do you ever stop nagging?" },
            { 738227323, "That's a fine way to talk to your esteemed mentor." },
            { 738227324, "Guess you never get tired, huh, Cuff? Must be nice." },
            { 738227325, "Believe me—being stuck to you is more than a little tiresome." },
            { 738227326, "Ha. Ha. You're not exactly a ton of fun yourself." },
            { 738227327, "Plenty still left in the tank!" },
            { 738227328, "Pride comes before a fall, you know." },
            { 738227329, "Trust me—I am nowhere near done." },
            { 738227330, "You look like you could do with a rest." },
            { 738227331, "Ahh, I'm fine...I think." },
            { 738227332, "Not entirely convincing..." },
            { 738227333, "I really think a rest might be in order." },
            { 738227334, "Maybe..." },
            { 738227335, "Just swallow your pride and stop for a while, will you?" },
            { 738227336, "You don't look well at all." },
            { 738227337, "Eh. It's just the light." },
            { 738227338, "Well, you've still got the energy to lie, at least." },
            { 738227339, "Are you alright? I wouldn't push yourself too hard." },
            { 738227340, "I know, I know..." },
            { 738227341, "I don't mean to be dramatic, but if you don't rest, you might actually die..." },
            { 738227342, "Ugh, shut up..." },
            { 738227343, "Ah! Good to see there's *some* life left in you at least." },
            { 738227344, "Getting kinda...tired..." },
            { 738227345, "Then stop being so stubborn and rest!" },
            { 738227346, "Mmm..." },
            { 738227347, "Don't you have some medicine or something?" },
            { 738227348, "Too tired to check..." },
            { 738227349, "You really are your own worst enemy." },
            { 738227350, "You are...alive, aren't you?" },
            { 738227351, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738227352, "Okay... I'll take that as a \"barely.\"" },
            { 738227353, "Frey? Frey! Snap out of it!" },
            { 738227354, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738227355, "Stop! Rest! Do something!" },
            { 738227356, "I'm a little worried that if you sleep now, you might not wake up again." },
            { 738227357, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738227358, "Okay, bad joke. Look, just stop somewhere, will you?" },
            { 738227359, "You're not invincible. Remember that." },
            { 738227360, "Tell me something I don't already know." },
            { 738227361, "I'm...pretty sure I got this." },
            { 738227362, "Wonderful. Try not to get killed, won't you?" },
            { 738227363, "Feeling kinda heavy, but...guess we better do this." },
            { 738227364, "You do have an escape plan if things go wrong, don't you?" },
            { 738227365, "Might have been worth resting up before diving in..." },
            { 738227366, "Might have been worth saying something sooner." },
            { 738227367, "Uh... Not feeling great." },
            { 738227368, "You mustn't push yourself so hard." },
            { 738227369, "You don't have to fight, you know." },
            { 738227370, "Good point..." },
            { 738227371, "I'm wondering if it might be an idea to skip this one..." },
            { 738227372, "I'm wondering the same thing..." },
            { 738227373, "You need to run." },
            { 738227374, "Believe me, I'm outta here the first chance I get." },
            { 738227375, "Think I maybe oughta run..." },
            { 738227376, "I think you may be right." },
            { 738227377, "Get away from her! Frey, you need to run!" },
            { 738227378, "Ugh..." },
            { 738227379, "Frey! Get out of there!" },
            { 738227380, "Damn it..." },
            { 738227381, "Fuuuck..." },
            { 738227382, "No heroics! Just run!" },
            { 738227383, "Happy to go on?" },
            { 738227384, "Happy as I'll ever be." },
            { 738227385, "One more round? Think I'm feeling lucky." },
            { 738227386, "Well, it's certainly good to see some enthusiasm." },
            { 738227387, "Happy to go on fighting?" },
            { 738227388, "I mean, if it's happening, it's happening, right?" },
            { 738227389, "Feeling weary at all?" },
            { 738227390, "Not—okay, maybe a little." },
            { 738227391, "Happy to soldier on?" },
            { 738227392, "Yeah, I'll survive." },
            { 738227393, "Getting kinda sore..." },
            { 738227394, "Quick breather?" },
            { 738227395, "Whew. I am worn out..." },
            { 738227396, "Rest now, or regret it later." },
            { 738227397, "I...may not be at my best." },
            { 738227398, "Let's find somewhere for you to put your feet up, shall we?" },
            { 738227399, "I think we could both do with a breather, don't you?" },
            { 738227400, "Eh, I guess..." },
            { 738227401, "Don't start flagging now." },
            { 738227402, "Hey, I'm trying here!" },
            { 738227403, "Perhaps a brief stop is in order?" },
            { 738227404, "You are still with me, aren't you?" },
            { 738227405, "More or less..." },
            { 738227406, "I think I need to take a break..." },
            { 738227407, "No one's stopping you. Shall we find somewhere?" },
            { 738227408, "Frey! Are you still with me, Frey?" },
            { 738227409, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738227410, "Damn..." },
            { 738227411, "We need to find somewhere safe. Now." },
            { 738227412, "Alright, this is getting ridiculous. Find somewhere to rest." },
            { 738227413, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738227414, "Ow!" },
            { 738227415, "If an \"ow\" is all you're walking away with, I'd say you're pretty lucky." },
            { 738227416, "Thanks for the sympathy, asshole." },
            { 738227417, "Oof. That looked painful." },
            { 738227418, "You can't just ask if I'm okay?" },
            { 738227419, "I'm not sure even nine lives would be enough for you, you know." },
            { 738227420, "Why even say anything?" },
            { 738227421, "Frey! Are you hurt?" },
            { 738227422, "What do you think, genius?" },
            { 738227423, "Ah, good. You're well enough to be unpleasant, at least." },
            { 738227424, "Are you trying to get yourself killed?" },
            { 738227425, "Oh yeah, that's exactly what I'm trying to do. Ow!" },
            { 738227426, "Shit. Thought I was dead for sure." },
            { 738227427, "You weren't the only one..." },
            { 738227428, "Frey!" },
            { 738227429, "No..." },
            { 738227430, "Frey! Stay with me!" },
            { 738227431, "Dammit..." },
            { 738227432, "But..." },
            { 738227433, "No!" },
