            { 738228418, "Really?" },
            { 738228419, "Hey, wait..." },
            { 738228420, "Is there something there?" },
            { 738228421, "Why not have a little look around?" },
            { 738228422, "Sure. Might as well." },
            { 738228423, "Ooh, I smell goodies." },
            { 738228424, "Then let's seek them out." },
            { 738228425, "I don't like the look of this." },
            { 738228426, "Me neither." },
            { 738228427, "Uhhh...this looks bad..." },
            { 738228428, "Couldn't agree more." },
            { 738228429, "Holy shit!" },
            { 738228430, "Calm down. Panicking won't solve anything." },
            { 738228431, "It's coming this way! Look out!" },
            { 738228432, "I AM looking out!" },
            { 738228433, "This one's not fucking around, huh?" },
            { 738228434, "I'd brace myself if I were you..." },
            { 738228435, "More!?" },
            { 738228436, "Better not relax just yet..." },
            { 738228437, "These fuckers don't know when to quit." },
            { 738228438, "More's the pity." },
            { 738228439, "Man! Give it up, will you?" },
            { 738228440, "Where did they even come from?" },
            { 738228441, "Reinforcements." },
            { 738228442, "Shit!" },
            { 738228443, "You're fucking kidding!" },
            { 738228444, "Well? Don't just stand there!" },
            { 738228445, "What is that!? That eyeball is bigger than I am!" },
            { 738228446, "It's something you need to be very wary of indeed." },
            { 738228447, "Fuck! This thing again?" },
            { 738228448, "Watch where it's looking!" },
            { 738228449, "Don't get too close, whatever you do!" },
            { 738228450, "Wasn't about to try, thanks!" },
            { 738228451, "A snake with hands? That's fucking weird." },
            { 738228452, "Don't let its hands distract you from its tail!" },
            { 738228453, "Fuck. Asshole snake alert." },
            { 738228454, "Try not to provoke it, alright?" },
            { 738228455, "Don't let it hypnotize you!" },
            { 738228456, "Yeah, thanks." },
            { 738228457, "What the actual fuck is that?" },
            { 738228458, "Highly unpredictable, that's what. Be careful." },
            { 738228459, "Ugh, gross. I hate this thing!" },
            { 738228460, "Yes, tentacles are rather hard to love..." },
            { 738228461, "Just calm down and try to predict its movements." },
            { 738228462, "Easy for you to say!" },
            { 738228463, "What is it? Some kind of huge...bird?" },
            { 738228464, "\"Huge\" almost doesn't cover it..." },
            { 738228465, "Best not to provoke it, I think." },
            { 738228466, "Oh, really?" },
            { 738228467, "It's huge! How can that thing even fly?" },
            { 738228468, "A very interesting question..." },
            { 738228469, "Another storm?" },
            { 738228470, "Careful..." },
            { 738228471, "Shit..." },
            { 738228472, "You might want to find somewhere to hide." },
            { 738228473, "Don't just rush blindly ahead!" },
            { 738228474, "I'm not, alright?" },
            { 738228475, "Hah! I need to get out of here..." },
            { 738228476, "...Or find somewhere to hide." },
            { 738228477, "Finally. Looks like it's calming down." },
            { 738228478, "Shall we see if we can get out?" },
            { 738228479, "Well, that was no fun." },
            { 738228480, "Hell no. But we made it through." },
            { 738228481, "You think we're safe now?" },
            { 738228482, "I think the worst is behind us, at least." },
            { 738228483, "Thank goodness that's over." },
            { 738228484, "Yeah. Let's not do that again." },
            { 738228485, "Shit, it's dark..." },
            { 738228486, "Ugh. Feels like something's gonna jump out at me..." },
            { 738228487, "Watch your step..." },
            { 738228488, "This place is a mess..." },
            { 738228489, "Not much room in here..." },
            { 738228490, "What the hell happened here?" },
            { 738228491, "Yesss!" },
            { 738228492, "Oh yeah!" },
            { 738228493, "It's my lucky day!" },
            { 738228494, "Woohoo!" },
            { 738228495, "Heh heh!" },
            { 738228496, "No fucking way!" },
            { 738228497, "Hell yeah!" },
            { 738228498, "Alright!" },
            { 738228499, "No!" },
            { 738228500, "Grrr!" },
            { 738228501, "Fuck!" },
            { 738228502, "Are you kidding me!?" },
            { 738228503, "What...?" },
            { 738228504, "Ah, man..." },
            { 738228505, "Shit..." },
            { 738228506, "Damn..." },
            { 738228507, "Whoa!" },
            { 738228508, "What the—!?" },
            { 738228509, "ひゃっ！" },
            { 738228510, "うわああーー！" },
            { 738228511, "Uh..." },
            { 738228512, "I, uh..." },
            { 738228513, "Wait, no..." },
            { 738228514, "Ugh, stop!" },
            { 738228515, "Enough, already." },
            { 738228516, "What?" },
            { 738228517, "It's nothing, alright?" },
            { 738228518, "Let's just go." },
            { 738228519, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738228520, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738228521, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738228522, "Hmph!" },
            { 738228523, "Whoa... Do you feel that?" },
            { 738228524, "You read about these in that book in the archives." },
            { 738228525, "Why not dive in and see what happens?" },
            { 738228526, "Really? In there?" },
            { 738228527, "...What the hell was that?" },
            { 738228528, "Did something happen?" },
            { 738228529, "I dunno. I feel more...powerful, I think." },
            { 738228530, "Hmm. Well, more power is always a good thing." },
            { 738228531, "Well, this doesn't look good." },
            { 738228532, "Yes. Something seems to have drawn the Break here." },
            { 738228533, "But I expect you can clear it away with your powers. Give it a try." },
            { 738228534, "Wait, what is that?" },
            { 738228535, "Shall we take a look?" },
            { 738228536, "I'm hitting the wall here." },
            { 738228537, "You need a rest, you mean? Alright..." },
            { 738228538, "You think we can rest up in there?" },
            { 738228539, "Let's go and see, shall we?" },
            { 738228540, "Think we'll be safe here." },
            { 738228541, "Yes, I think we might." },
            { 738228542, "Well? What are they waiting for?" },
            { 738228543, "They'll be out soon enough, I'm sure." },
            { 738228544, "And once they make their move on Cipal..." },
            { 738228545, "Here they come!" },
            { 738228546, "We'll never be able to beat that many..." },
            { 738228547, "Look, whatever we do, we're not going to survive this." },
            { 738228548, "So let's just try to make our deaths count for something, alright?" },
            { 738228549, "Come on! I'm taking a few of them with me, if it's the last thing I do!" },
            { 738228550, "No! They can't!" },
            { 738228551, "I don't think they have much choice..." },
            { 738228552, "No..." },
            { 738228553, "Somebody help me!" },
            { 738228554, "Tantas have mercy on my soul..." },
            { 738228555, "No!" },
            { 738228556, "Dammit! No time to get close!" },
            { 738228557, "The only option is a well-aimed spell or two, I'd say..." },
            { 738228558, "An ambush was the last thing we needed..." },
            { 738228559, "We've suffered severe casualties. Any word on reinforcements?" },
            { 738228560, "No luck. Signal fire's dead..." },
            { 738228561, "Then I'll just have to go and fetch them myself." },
            { 738228562, "No! You'll never make it!" },
            { 738228563, "I might, you know. You've seen me run." },
            { 738228564, "And it's not like anyone else is fit to make the trip." },
            { 738228565, "Sorry to have to ask this of you... Tanta's blessings go with you." },
            { 738228566, "And with you." },
            { 738228567, "I'd say that's where our friend is headed, wouldn't you?" },
            { 738228568, "Can't say for sure. Only one way to find out..." },
            { 738228569, "Th-thank you..." },
            { 738228570, "Stick with me, okay?" },
            { 738228571, "I...I can't run, I'm afraid. Look, just save your—" },
            { 738228572, "I won't hear of it. We're getting out of this. Together." },
            { 738228573, "Think we can keep them at bay?" },
            { 738228574, "We have to at least try!" },
            { 738228575, "To whosoever shall claim this power." },
            { 738228576, "Should your purpose in doing so be anything but pure, may your soul be consumed by the fires of the beyond." },
            { 738228577, "But if righteousness burns bright within you, may my might be the sword that carves the path of destiny." },
            { 738228578, "Tantas' blessings go with you." },
            { 738228579, "To whosoever shall claim this power." },
            { 738228580, "Never underestimate the power of righteousness to guide those lost in turmoil." },
            { 738228581, "May your light lead others along the winding path to truth." },
            { 738228582, "Tantas' blessings go with you." },
            { 738228583, "To whosoever shall claim this power." },
            { 738228584, "Skies clear, and despair gives way at last to hope for a brighter future." },
            { 738228585, "May this tragedy, once past, never again be repeated." },
            { 738228586, "Tantas' blessings go with you." },
            { 738228587, "To whosoever shall claim this power." },
            { 738228588, "Though loneliness and solitude assail you, you must never lose hope." },
            { 738228589, "May my power guide you, my spirit uplift you, and the way always open up ahead." },
            { 738228590, "Tantas' blessings go with you." },
            { 738228591, "Looks like this map shows the spread of the Break." },
            { 738228592, "But it's pretty different from how things are now. Must be from a few years ago." },
            { 738228593, "It's entirely useless, in other words. Wonderful." },
            { 738228594, "What's this?" },
            { 738228595, "Looks like someone left a note." },
            { 738228596, "Why did this have to happen to a little kid..." },
            { 738228597, "Irreconcilable differences, huh?" },
            { 738228598, "Some situations can't be settled with words alone." },
            { 738228599, "Guess so..." },
            { 738228602, "They just left them..." },
            { 738228603, "A hard choice to make, I'm sure. But necessary." },
            { 738228604, "So they're graves?" },
            { 738228605, "Well, memorials to those who died." },
            { 738228606, "Huh. Well, glorious death on the battlefield looks pretty miserable from where I'm standing." },
            { 738228607, "Whoa, look at this fucker. That is somethin' else." },
            { 738228608, "You'll need to keep your wits about you here..." },
            { 738228609, "Damn, that thing was tough." },
            { 738228610, "But you prevailed in the end...thanks to yours truly." },
            { 738228611, "Look, I... I'm too tired for the whole hilarious comeback thing right now. Sorry." },
            { 738228612, "Not a bad haul." },
            { 738228613, "I suppose things must float down here from farther upstream." },
            { 738228614, "Let's come again sometime. Might find some more." },
            { 738228615, "There's something in the middle of that pool, you know." },
            { 738228616, "Let's go take a look." },
            { 738228618, "Ah. An ambush. Just as I feared." },
            { 738228619, "What? Why the fuck didn't you say something!?" },
            { 738228620, "Looks like they were attacked as they were trying to escape." },
            { 738228621, "Yeah. Well, kinda dark, but...they don't need this stuff, right?" },
            { 738228622, "Oh, absolutely. Take it. It'll only go to waste otherwise." },
            { 738228625, "What the hell happened to this thing?" },
            { 738228626, "The Break. And it didn't hold back, by the look of it." },
            { 738228627, "Yeah, uh...not so sure I'll be walking away in one piece if I try and fight this one..." },
            { 738228628, "Holy shit... Wait, I won?" },
            { 738228629, "...I won. But you did very well to wield me so nicely." },
            { 738228630, "Holy SHIT! I am fucking unstoppable!" },
            { 738228631, "No, you— Never mind..." },
            { 738228632, "Whoa... This place is insane." },
            { 738228633, "Wait, this is..." },
            { 738228638, "I'm alive, right? Right. Holy shit..." },
            { 738228639, "We live to fight another day! Huzzah!" },
            { 738228640, "Okay, not liking the look of this at all." },
            { 738228641, "Whoever fought here certainly meant business..." },
            { 738228642, "Uh...what the hell is that?" },
            { 738228643, "Looks like we've got a fight on our hands..." },
            { 738228644, "Ooh, very classy." },
            { 738228648, "What is this place?" },
            { 738228649, "Whatever it is, it's been here for a very long time." },
            { 738228651, "Um...I think there might be more of them." },
            { 738228652, "Yeah, I can see that!" },
            { 738228653, "So this place was some kind of training facility." },
            { 738228654, "Yes. I believe Sila's troops used to come here to hone their skills." },
            { 738228656, "Huh. What's this place?" },
            { 738228657, "Looks like they started this party without me." },
            { 738228658, "Ooh, very blasé." },
            { 738228659, "Are we not done yet!?" },
            { 738228660, "Certainly doesn't look that way. What's the plan?" },
            { 738228661, "Uh, kill everyone?" },
            { 738228662, "And with that, we are done with this shithole!" },
            { 738228663, "Well, as long as you had fun." },
            { 738228664, "Whoa. Somebody loved books..." },
            { 738228665, "Visoria was said to be the storehouse of Athia's wisdom." },
            { 738228666, "Well, the storehouse looks like a bomb hit it. But maybe there's something in here we can use..." },
            { 738228667, "Found out anything of interest?" },
            { 738228668, "Yeah, that Olas wrote a shit ton of books." },
            { 738228669, "Okay, there's a lot of these guys." },
            { 738228670, "Yes, probably best not to think about exactly how many." },
            { 738228671, "There's more!?" },
            { 738228672, "What do you think? Make a run for it?" },
            { 738228673, "No way! Let's kick some ass!" },
            { 738228674, "Need a rest after that..." },
            { 738228675, "Yes. And I can't help thinking it was a bit of a waste of time..." },
            { 738228676, "Think it. Don't say it." },
            { 738228677, "Must have been a library..." },
            { 738228678, "Shit! Fucker was hiding between the bookcases!" },
            { 738228679, "Perhaps they were trying to sniff out a good read." },
            { 738228680, "I'm not sure these guys are into that..." },
            { 738228681, "Look at this..." },
            { 738228682, "Yes, lovely. Our friend must have been a reader." },
            { 738228683, "Wonder what it says..." },
            { 738228684, "Would you mind moving the wondering outside?" },
            { 738228685, "Whoa... Score!" },
            { 738228686, "Ooh, yes. Quite a find." },
            { 738228687, "Well, whatever happened here, it wasn't good." },
            { 738228688, "Yes..." },
            { 738228689, "Looks like an execution." },
            { 738228690, "Yes. Seems they killed those who tried to escape..." },
            { 738228691, "Mmm. Monster...nest. My favorite." },
            { 738228692, "You never know—they might want to play." },
            { 738228693, "You can't just experiment on people..." },
            { 738228694, "And if no one makes a sacrifice? How else is progress to be made?" },
            { 738228702, "Looks like kids used to play here." },
            { 738228703, "Yes. Long-since-dead ones." },
            { 738228704, "You have no filter, do you?" },
            { 738228705, "Hey! Come back here!" },
            { 738228706, "Not again!" },
            { 738228707, "Ugh, geez. Glad that's finally over." },
            { 738228708, "Well, it was a nice little workout, if nothing else." },
            { 738228709, "What's this thing doing here?" },
            { 738228710, "I have absolutely no idea." },
            { 738228711, "How many of these assholes are there!?" },
            { 738228712, "I suppose even Break-addled creatures must retain enough sense to know there's strength in numbers." },
            { 738228713, "Better not be any more of them. I'm exhausted..." },
            { 738228714, "So did they just sit here reading until they keeled over and died?" },
            { 738228715, "Possibly. What's the book about?" },
            { 738228716, "Where the hell did these guys come from?" },
            { 738228717, "I'm not sure. But they don't look pleased..." },
            { 738228718, "Guess they think we're trying to steal their lunch." },
            { 738228721, "Man, nearly jumped out of my skin back there." },
            { 738228722, "Well, as I say, the power of love is not to be underestimated, even among monsters." },
            { 738228723, "Are you really still trying with that one?" },
            { 738228724, "I mean, I'm sure they had their reasons, but...did they really have to do this?" },
            { 738228727, "Nice. Another book." },
            { 738228728, "They're not really all that rare, you know." },
            { 738228729, "Useful ones are. And this might be one." },
            { 738228730, "How did they even wind up here?" },
            { 738228731, "I'm not sure. Swam here after some particularly tasty prey, perhaps?" },
            { 738228732, "Guess they are pretty fucking relentless." },
            { 738228733, "Lotta room in here." },
            { 738228734, "Wait—something's there..." },
            { 738228735, "Heck of a lot more skulls than skeletons in this place, no?" },
            { 738228736, "Yes. But why collect them? Suggests a sense of purpose I'm not sure many monsters possess." },
            { 738228737, "You think whoever did this was still human? Ugh. Must have been a total psycho..." },
            { 738228738, "They're all just kids..." },
            { 738228739, "Looks that way, yes." },
            { 738228740, "Why were there no adults here to help them?" },
            { 738228741, "Looks like this is where their luck finally ran out..." },
            { 738228742, "Man, that's so sad..." },
            { 738228743, "You think they're trying to protect it?" },
            { 738228744, "I really couldn't say..." },
            { 738228745, "Hey, look—we know that name." },
            { 738228746, "Well, Avoalet was her home once upon a time." },
            { 738228747, "Okay, that is a shit ton of bones. You think they did all of this?" },
            { 738228748, "Can't help feeling a certain sense of foreboding..." },
            { 738228749, "That is a shit ton of bones. You think that thing did all of this?" },
            { 738228750, "I'd say that's a reasonable assumption, yes." },
            { 738228751, "Fascinating stuff." },
            { 738228752, "Sounds like a pain in the ass to me." },
            { 738228753, "How do you even research shit like this?" },
            { 738228754, "By putting your life at very great risk indeed..." },
            { 738228757, "Did one of them...summon the others?" },
            { 738228758, "Probably. Nice to have friends to back you up, huh?" },
            { 738228759, "Don't tell me you're jealous?" },
            { 738228760, "Behold, the bitter brutality of the friendless..." },
            { 738228761, "Shut up." },
            { 738228762, "This oughta come in handy." },
            { 738228763, "Taking an interest in a scholarly work, eh? That's not like you." },
            { 738228764, "Your infiltration skills are coming along in leaps and bounds." },
            { 738228765, "I know, right?" },
            { 738228766, "What the hell is that thing doing here?" },
            { 738228767, "So they were doing some kind of experiment...?" },
            { 738228768, "So this is about Bob's ballow stuff?" },
            { 738228769, "Looks like they were researching it here for some time." },
            { 738228770, "Whoa! Okay, I did not mean to disturb you guys. Seeing myself out!" },
            { 738228771, "I'm not sure politeness is going to solve this..." },
            { 738228772, "Looks like it's about Sila's powers..." },
            { 738228773, "These guys look nasty as hell..." },
            { 738228774, "Yes. Best steer clear, I'd say." },
            { 738228775, "For once, I will not be contradicting you." },
            { 738228778, "Fuckers..." },
            { 738228779, "What men wouldn't do in the quest for knowledge, eh?" },
            { 738228780, "So that's why there's all this shit lying around." },
            { 738228781, "Looks like they were researching Prav's powers..." },
            { 738228782, "Hmm. Well that might certainly be of use." },
            { 738228783, "Check out this place..." },
            { 738228784, "Nice. Guess we should pick up some of this stuff if we find it, huh?" },
            { 738228785, "Yes. Looks like it'll come in very handy indeed." },
            { 738228786, "Olas's powers were totally different from Sila and Prav's, huh?" },
            { 738228787, "Indeed they were." },
            { 738228788, "Mmm... I can't make out what it used to say—there's too much missing." },
            { 738228789, "Looks to be about a sophisticated device of some sort..." },
            { 738228790, "Meh. Nothing much I didn't already know." },
            { 738228791, "Sounds like someone's ready to become a Cognoscent themselves..." },
            { 738228792, "You think maybe he doesn't like visitors?" },
            { 738228793, "I think maybe we're in trouble..." },
            { 738228794, "Looks like somebody had the same idea as me..." },
            { 738228797, "Hey, this is about Cinta's powers..." },
            { 738228798, "Sadly, it seems to be missing quite a few pages." },
            { 738228799, "Gatekeeper's outta the way. How do we get in?" },
            { 738228800, "You've blown doors off their hinges in the past, no? Could be an approach here..." },
            { 738228801, "What the fuck!?" },
            { 738228802, "It's an old portrait of Cinta..." },
            { 738228803, "They used to grow herbs all around here." },
            { 738228804, "And that information is of use to us how?" },
            { 738228805, "Whoa! Shit!" },
            { 738228806, "Okay, real talk—can you guys quit it?" },
            { 738228807, "Really? Now?" },
            { 738228808, "Yes, really! So keep your wits about you!" },
            { 738228810, "No way! Never knew that..." },
            { 738228811, "You're...oddly more engaged than usual." },
            { 738228812, "What could make a hole like that?" },
            { 738228813, "Something trying to get out in a hurry. Or in..." },
            { 738228814, "This thing just screams \"Prav.\"" },
            { 738228815, "Why not try it on?" },
            { 738228816, "Mmm. Court. My favorite." },
            { 738228817, "You're not going to finish reading it?" },
            { 738228818, "This looks like the same stuff Bob was researching, right?" },
            { 738228819, "Who knows—he might even have been involved." },
            { 738228820, "Heh. Piece of cake." },
            { 738228821, "Are you sure about that?" },
            { 738228822, "Well? Are you going to say it again?" },
            { 738228823, "Hah... Piece of...fucking... Fucking cake... Yeah..." },
            { 738228824, "So they're...illusions?" },
            { 738228825, "Great! And what am I supposed to do about that!?" },
            { 738228826, "Oh... Oh my... Finally..." },
            { 738228827, "Something of a shame you had to break it..." },
            { 738228828, "So Sila's troops once helped the defenseless citizens of Praenost find their way to Cipal..." },
            { 738228829, "And they weren't immune to the Break like me. That takes guts." },
            { 738228830, "\"Calista...Keen...\" Hey, that's Auden's mom." },
            { 738228831, "The peasant girl? Intriguing." },
            { 738228832, "Some pretty fucked up shit happened here." },
            { 738228833, "Yes, and Sila appears to have enjoyed her part in things a little too much..." },
            { 738228834, "Seriously? There's more of you guys?" },
            { 738228835, "Gimme a fucking break here!" },
            { 738228836, "You could just run away, you know..." },
            { 738228837, "It's some kind of...war diary..." },
            { 738228838, "And by the look of it, whoever wrote it had plenty to write about." },
            { 738228839, "Rather astute as opponents go, wouldn't you say?" },
            { 738228840, "Not \"astute\" enough to stop me from kicking their ass." },
            { 738228841, "Thing's full of junk." },
            { 738228842, "Well, we can't always hit the jackpot." },
            { 738228843, "There may be more of them..." },
            { 738228844, "Good. Let's go find them." },
            { 738228845, "There weren't enough of them already!?" },
            { 738228846, "I sense a record-breaking performance in the offing!" },
            { 738228847, "Holy shit. I cannot believe I made it through that..." },
            { 738228848, "As I predicted—a new record!" },
            { 738228849, "What are you even talking about?" },
            { 738228853, "I don't like the look of this place. Are you sure about this?" },
            { 738228854, "Not until we get a little closer." },
            { 738228857, "Hey—those are the things we saw in not-New-York." },
            { 738228858, "I wonder how many she made..." },
            { 738228859, "Look—they're holding something." },
            { 738228860, "Must have been very important to whoever it was..." },
            { 738228861, "Will we be storming the battlements, then?" },
            { 738228862, "Unless you have a better plan..." },
            { 738228863, "Looks like the old guard logs. Hey, wait..." },
            { 738228864, "We know that name, don't we?" },
            { 738228865, "Seems like there was one hell of a fight here..." },
            { 738228866, "Looks like this was one of their last lines of defense." },
            { 738228868, "More? Ugh!" },
            { 738228869, "Look—it says \"Bellette\" here." },
            { 738228870, "Well, that's certainly given us some insight into how things used to be." },
            { 738228873, "Didn't think there'd be anything left here, never mind a book." },
            { 738228874, "And you're going to read it? It's got...dead person on it." },
            { 738228875, "Is that a bear? Here!?" },
            { 738228876, "I think it must be lost." },
            { 738228877, "You think that body was someone the bear killed?" },
            { 738228878, "I find it hard to believe the creature could have been loitering here for quite that long." },
            { 738228879, "No way. So this is what Cipal looked like back in the day?" },
            { 738228880, "I think we may have brought friends running from miles around." },
            { 738228881, "Great. Just what I needed." },
            { 738228882, "Whoa, get a load of this." },
            { 738228883, "Pfft. Whatever keeps you entertained." },
            { 738228884, "Where the hell did they come from?" },
            { 738228885, "Well, you're not exactly inconspicuous." },
            { 738228886, "Too easy." },
            { 738228887, "Here come the reinforcements!" },
            { 738228888, "Don't look now, but we've got some rather ugly-looking company." },
            { 738228889, "Kinda looked already." },
            { 738228890, "Whoa!" },
            { 738228891, "Something tells me our friend here is protecting something." },
            { 738228892, "I can see why this was worth protecting..." },
            { 738228893, "Wow. Place used to be pretty..." },
            { 738228894, "Yes, I suppose it was." },
            { 738228895, "Think we could get something for this." },
            { 738228896, "Yes, if we can find someone in Cipal who happens to be putting together an art collection." },
            { 738228897, "This place really used to be something, huh?" },
            { 738228898, "No love lost between these guys." },
            { 738228899, "No. If the others hadn't succumbed so quickly, we would have had quite the fight on our hands." },
            { 738228900, "Now that spells trouble with a capital T." },
            { 738228901, "Yes. Why are there so many of them...?" },
            { 738228902, "Reading until the very end, huh?" },
            { 738228903, "Must have been an important book..." },
            { 738228904, "Must have belonged to whoever lived here." },
            { 738228905, "Looks like it, yes." },
            { 738228906, "A picture. Nice." },
            { 738228907, "Didn't have you down as an art lover..." },
            { 738228908, "What the fuck? I mean, this just goes to show, nothing good ever happens in a courtroom." },
            { 738228909, "The more the madness took her, the less she was prepared to listen to reason..." },
            { 738228910, "I would not have liked this place." },
            { 738228911, "I think deterring criminals was probably one of the things they had in mind when they built it." },
            { 738228912, "Visoria actually used to be pretty nice..." },
            { 738228913, "Yes, well, I wouldn't recommend a move just yet." },
            { 738228914, "Fuck. This is so sad..." },
            { 738228915, "It's a little late to be pitying them." },
            { 738228916, "Still... Ugh, this is dark." },
            { 738228917, "Guess our friend here must have really loved this book." },
            { 738228918, "Guessing's about all we can do at this stage..." },
            { 738228919, "Looks like this used to be one hell of a dangerous zoo." },
            { 738228920, "And what exactly is a zoo when it's at home?" },
            { 738228921, "It's kinda fucked up, but a place where you go to look at animals." },
            { 738228922, "Just...look at them? But...why?" },
            { 738228923, "Guess I never thought about how he really felt." },
            { 738228924, "And that changes how you feel about him?" },
            { 738228925, "...Nope. Still an asshole." },
            { 738228926, "This place used to be so beautiful..." },
            { 738228927, "What the hell is that!?" },
            { 738228928, "The reason Robian was unable to return to town, I'd say..." },
            { 738228929, "Fucker. If only that thing hadn't been here..." },
            { 738228930, "Then what? It's not like the creature killed Robian, is it?" },
            { 738228931, "No...but if it hadn't stopped him, he could have made it back to Cipal. The Break never would have...broken him." },
            { 738228932, "Will it ever look like this again?" },
            { 738228933, "Not as long as the Break remains, I fear..." },
            { 738228934, "These people weren't fighting monsters..." },
            { 738228935, "They were fighting each other." },
            { 738228937, "This place is like a maze." },
            { 738228938, "Just don't get lost." },
            { 738228939, "So Visoria's always just been a bunch of fields, huh?" },
            { 738228940, "Yes. I suppose it has been less noticeably changed by the Break than the other realms." },
            { 738228941, "Another one of those weird lamps..." },
            { 738228942, "And something else odd, too..." },
            { 738228943, "Uh... What is this place?" },
            { 738228946, "Hey..." },
            { 738228947, "What's that doing here?" },
            { 738228948, "Quite the welcome." },
            { 738228949, "If that's what you wanna call this..." },
            { 738228950, "Dreaming of a new life... Yeah, I can sympathize with that." },
            { 738228951, "A heady mix of hope and anxiety. It's never easy upping sticks and moving..." },
            { 738228952, "There was a battle here." },
            { 738228953, "Looks more like a massacre to me..." },
            { 738228954, "Wonder if anybody made it outta here alive." },
            { 738228955, "If they did, I'm not sure they would have made it very far..." },
            { 738228956, "No dead bodies here. Not too much damage, either." },
            { 738228957, "The place must have been evacuated without incident." },
            { 738228958, "Guess some were more lucky than others..." },
            { 738228959, "So this is where Auden's mom was from." },
            { 738228960, "Sila's most trusted general..." },
            { 738228963, "No way. She's the hero who saved the village?" },
            { 738228964, "Why are you so surprised?" },
            { 738228965, "No offense, but she does not seem like the type." },
            { 738228966, "They were all murdered..." },
            { 738228967, "...Bob tried to get them to leave." },
            { 738228968, "But their belief in Sila stopped them from escaping." },
            { 738228969, "Holy shit. Is this...?" },
            { 738228970, "It either belonged to Sila, or they were planning on giving it to her." },
            { 738228971, "Not too sure how I feel about this, but...guess it can't hurt." },
            { 738228975, "Sila's goons." },
            { 738228976, "I suppose they must have patrolled all of Praenost once upon a time." },
            { 738228977, "Man... How many bodies are there?" },
            { 738228978, "The Break must have advanced very suddenly, and swallowed them all up with it." },
            { 738228979, "Wait, is this...a bar?" },
            { 738228980, "It certainly was once." },
            { 738228981, "Reminds me of the Shady Tree." },
            { 738228982, "Don't you guys have any respect?" },
            { 738228983, "You deserve a drink after that." },
            { 738228984, "Yeah, if I can find one..." },
            { 738228985, "What's this...?" },
            { 738228986, "So Bellette had to write all the laws?" },
            { 738228987, "The life of a councilperson is a tedious one indeed." },
            { 738228988, "So this is what Prav looked like way back when." },
            { 738228989, "Seems so. What do you make of the old her?" },
            { 738228990, "Not much. Just...they look like more peaceful times." },
            { 738228991, "Wonder where everybody went." },
            { 738228992, "Yes. And I wonder if any of them survived..." },
            { 738228993, "Sounds like Treahy didn't have it easy back then, either." },
            { 738228994, "Yes, the life of a public servant was ever a thankless one." },
            { 738228995, "Uh-huh. And what would you know about that, exactly?" },
            { 738228996, "Says here this whole place was wiped out by a single monster." },
            { 738228997, "Sadly, even one monster can be more than a match for a gaggle of ill-prepared peasants." },
            { 738228998, "Wonder if anyone's inside." },
            { 738228999, "If there is, they won't be human anymore..." },
            { 738229002, "Look at that. Olas back before all this shit went down." },
            { 738229003, "I doubt there's anyone left who remembers when she looked like this." },
            { 738229004, "Look at all these graves." },
            { 738229005, "At least they were given proper burials. It's more than can be said for most." },
            { 738229006, "Oh...! So this is where that asshole grew up?" },
            { 738229007, "Well, he wasn't one to shirk on his studies, by the look of it." },
            { 738229010, "They tried to fight back the monsters..." },
            { 738229011, "...And failed miserably." },
            { 738229012, "This place was wiped out too." },
            { 738229013, "It seems they all were." },
            { 738229014, "Looks like they left in a hurry." },
            { 738229015, "Which means more goodies for us." },
            { 738229016, "Who would do something like that?" },
            { 738229017, "Someone no longer burdened with the inconvenience of a conscience." },
            { 738229018, "Geez. Poor Bob..." },
            { 738229019, "It's sad. But it's the path he chose." },
            { 738229020, "Cipal was right there. He could have just..." },
            { 738229021, "And most would have done. But not that stubborn old goat." },
            { 738229022, "Damn it... If only I could have been here..." },
            { 738229023, "I'm sure you would have done something very heroic. But it's too late for that now." },
            { 738229024, "They weren't allowed to leave...?" },
            { 738229025, "Prav always was a stickler for the rules..." },
            { 738229028, "This was an experiment?" },
            { 738229029, "I hope the poor innocents who suffered because of it weren't aware of that." },
            { 738229031, "The power of the Tantas is not to be sniffed at." },
            { 738229032, "It's about Bob..." },
            { 738229033, "I'm rather keen to know what happened next, aren't you?" },
            { 738229034, "Holy fuck. Look at them all..." },
            { 738229035, "But you're not worried, are you? Not the mighty Frey. No..." },
            { 738229036, "Okay. Guess that wasn't a total waste of time." },
            { 738229037, "All's well that ends well." },
            { 738229038, "This place is insane..." },
            { 738229039, "This is what happens when Prav's power really gets out of hand." },
            { 738229442, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229443, "Wha—? Where...where'd she go?" },
            { 738229444, "Huh? Well? Fucking answer me! Where'd she go!?" },
            { 738229447, "You say another fucking word..." },
            { 738229449, "What? Uh, no. Please—after you." },
            { 738229450, "Company. Company. Ooh! Time for tea." },
            { 738229451, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229452, "I have not heard that name in a long time." },
            { 738229453, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229454, "She was using one of her minions as a vessel." },
            { 738229455, "You die now, interloper." },
            { 738229456, "I think we just leveled up." },
            { 738229460, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229461, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229462, "Frey!" },
            { 738229465, "The fun never stops, does it?" },
            { 738229466, "Seriously? This is bullshit!" },
            { 738229467, "I never wanna see another crocodile for as long as I live." },
            { 738229468, "Yes. Might be wise to be wary around lakes, ponds, and other bodies of water from now on..." },
            { 738229471, "Looks like somebody was expecting us." },
            { 738229472, "Well, there's only one way onward. You know what to do." },
            { 738229473, "So glad that's over." },
            { 738229474, "Quite. Shall we?" },
            { 738229475, "Another gate." },
            { 738229476, "And quite possibly another ne'er-do-well lying in wait. Keep your wits about you." },
            { 738229477, "Guess our pal here's the gatekeeper." },
            { 738229478, "Indeed." },
            { 738229479, "Alright, let's move." },
            { 738229480, "Well, aren't we determined?" },
            { 738229481, "What the hell...?" },
            { 738229482, "You'll need to go through it if you want to get to Sila." },
            { 738229483, "Ugh, really?" },
            { 738229484, "What's happening...?" },
            { 738229485, "The Break is especially highly concentrated here. As to what that means..." },
            { 738229486, "Okay, so there's dangerous...but this place feels super dangerous." },
            { 738229487, "I wholeheartedly agree. Try not to get killed." },
            { 738229488, "Another one." },
            { 738229489, "Well, onward and...onward!" },
            { 738229490, "Oh. Surprise, surprise." },
            { 738229491, "Indeed." },
            { 738229492, "Figured we'd find another one in Junoon." },
            { 738229493, "And find one we have." },
            { 738229494, "Trader" },
            { 738229495, "Courier" },
            { 738229496, "Quartermaster" },
            { 738229497, "……" },
            { 738229498, "You okay?" },
            { 738229499, "I've...not been feeling so great lately, if I'm honest. My work's starting to suffer." },
            { 738229500, "Oh yeah? What do you do?" },
            { 738229501, "I deliver food to people around town for the Council." },
            { 738229502, "I cover the entire lower city. People aren't going to be able to eat if I don't get my act together." },
            { 738229503, "Help deliver the rations?" },
            { 738229504, "Sure." },
            { 738229505, "Nah." },
            { 738229506, "A cat." },
            { 738229507, "Where's it going?" },
            { 738229508, "How about I go instead of you?" },
            { 738229509, "Let's see..." },
            { 738229510, "You'd do that? I hate to ask, really I do." },
            { 738229511, "Ugh... Shit..." },
            { 738229512, "But if you could go to the stores and pick up the goods, I'd be ever so grateful." },
            { 738229513, "Damn, lost it." },
            { 738229514, "If you could bring them to me, I'll do the rest." },
            { 738229515, "I can't abandon my duties completely, after all." },
            { 738229516, "Oh, one thing to mention—last time I was there, they didn't give me as much as they normally do." },
            { 738229517, "Guess it spotted me." },
            { 738229518, "Wouldn't surprise me if the ratbag who hands the stuff out has been at the merchandise." },
            { 738229519, "Hmm... Just remembered they gave me some seriously wrinkly vegetables last time..." },
            { 738229520, "Odd colors, even odder shapes. Not inedible, but...certainly not prime produce..." },
            { 738229521, "Luckily, the produce has been in tip-top shape of late, so I expect you won't face any problems." },
            { 738229522, "What am I going to do?" },
            { 738229523, "Man! It got away!" },
            { 738229524, "ああ……" },
            { 738229525, "Hm? Where's the one who usually comes?" },
            { 738229526, "He's not feeling so good, so...I'm here instead." },
            { 738229527, "Fair enough." },
            { 738229528, "Here. This should be all of it." },
            { 738229529, "Well? Are you going after it?" },
            { 738229530, "You again?" },
            { 738229531, "Your usual guy's still sick." },
            { 738229532, "Blimey. Doesn't sound good." },
            { 738229533, "Anyway, here." },
            { 738229534, "Say something about the rations?" },
            { 738229535, "What's the plan, then?" },
            { 738229536, "This can't be everything..." },
            { 738229537, "These are some...odd-looking veggies..." },
            { 738229538, "Thanks." },
            { 738229539, "Shouldn't there be more than this?" },
            { 738229540, "Flighty little creature. Worth chasing it down, perhaps?" },
            { 738229541, "Eh?" },
            { 738229542, "C'mon. Hand over the rest." },
            { 738229543, "Pah. Fine. But that really is your lot." },
            { 738229544, "Ask for even more?" },
            { 738229545, "It's still not enough." },
            { 738229546, "I have a strange feeling that cat wants us to follow it..." },
            { 738229547, "Thank him and leave." },
            { 738229548, "Quit holding out on me, will you?" },
            { 738229549, "Are your scales busted or something?" },
            { 738229550, "Can't kid a kidder, you know." },
            { 738229551, "No one's trying to swindle you, alright?" },
            { 738229552, "Now take what you're given and clear off!" },
            { 738229554, "These vegetables...they look like shit." },
            { 738229555, "You what?" },
            { 738229556, "You don't have any fresher ones?" },
            { 738229557, "Pff. Fine. Take these instead." },
            { 738229558, "Complain some more?" },
            { 738229559, "These are just as bad." },
            { 738229561, "Thank him and leave." },
            { 738229562, "You really think these are any better?" },
            { 738229563, "They're as crappy as the other ones." },
            { 738229564, "Look at them. Are you kidding me?" },
            { 738229565, "Oh, forgive me. Didn't realise I was dealing with an expert." },
            { 738229566, "Here, Your Majesty. The special reserve. For the most discerning gourmands only." },
            { 738229567, "Here. Brought your stuff." },
            { 738229568, "Thanks so much! Let's take a look, shall we?" },
            { 738229569, "Hey! Hold up!" },
            { 738229570, "Hmm... There should be more than this..." },
            { 738229571, "Curse that thieving so-and-so..." },
            { 738229572, "But I can't complain—you did me a real favor there. Thanks." },
            { 738229573, "Hmm... Fobbed off with the seconds again, eh?" },
            { 738229574, "Any food's good food though, I suppose..." },
            { 738229575, "Thanks for going and getting this lot for me." },
            { 738229576, "Hurry—it's getting away." },
            { 738229577, "Look at this little lot! And it's the good stuff, too! Nice work!" },
            { 738229578, "They're going to love me when I show up with a haul like this! Thanks so much!" },
            { 738229579, "Where do you think it's taking us?" },
            { 738229580, "Wherever it is, I hope it turns out to be worth the trouble." },
            { 738229581, "Wait, it stopped!" },
            { 738229582, "So this is where you were taking us?" },
            { 738229583, "What'd you want us to find here?" },
            { 738229584, "Aww, is this for me?" },
            { 738229585, "You led me here on purpose, didn't you?" },
            { 738229586, "For me? Aww, you shouldn't have!" },
            { 738229587, "You're no Homer. But you're cute." },
            { 738229588, "You're not afraid of me, huh?" },
            { 738229589, "Aww, aren't you just the cutest?" },
            { 738229590, "What's this?" },
            { 738229591, "It's a partha. From Junoon." },
            { 738229592, "So they're, like...Athian dice?" },
            { 738229593, "They're made of animal bones." },
            { 738229594, "You roll one, and if it lands on one of the little symbol things, you're in for a lucky day." },
            { 738229595, "Wow. Sounds fun." },
            { 738229596, "Oh, that's all it is. No one takes it too seriously." },
            { 738229597, "Go on—give it a go." },
            { 738229598, "Well, would you look at that?" },
            { 738229599, "Nice! Rolled a...whatever that is!" },
            { 738229600, "Guess it's my lucky day." },
            { 738229601, "Ugh. No luck, huh?" },
            { 738229602, "And it's a big. Fat. Nothing." },
            { 738229603, "Figures." },
            { 738229604, "Why not try your luck again tomorrow?" },
            { 738229605, "Quick drink while you're here?" },
            { 738229606, "I've got something for every taste, you know." },
            { 738229607, "What'll it be?" },
            { 738229608, "You sure? Alright, then." },
            { 738229609, "Coming right up." },
            { 738229621, "Sorry, you couldn't lend a quick hand, could you?" },
            { 738229622, "I need someone to help me feed the animals." },
            { 738229623, "You're a lifesaver! Here." },
            { 738229624, "You've done this kind of thing before, I assume?" },
            { 738229625, "Amazing. Alright, away you go!" },
            { 738229626, "You're leaving? But you haven't finished yet." },
            { 738229627, "Can't be helped, I suppose. Let me know if you change your mind." },
            { 738229628, "Ooh, somebody's hungry." },
            { 738229629, "Not a big eater, huh?" },
            { 738229630, "Oh. Not a fan?" },
            { 738229631, "Oh. Not good enough for you, huh?" },
            { 738229632, "Wonder if you actually like this stuff..." },
            { 738229633, "That's it for today, thanks." },
            { 738229634, "Can't have this lot eating all our supplies." },
            { 738229635, "Anything take your fancy?" },
            { 738229637, "Well? Show me the goods!" },
            { 738229638, "Let's have a look, shall we?" },
            { 738229639, "Oh. Alright. Another time, maybe." },
            { 738229640, "Thanks. Got quite a collection going on now." },
            { 738229641, "Thank you very much. And...here." },
            { 738229642, "That's just not enough. Sorry." },
            { 738229643, "You're going to have to do better, I'm afraid." },
            { 738229644, "Do come again!" },
            { 738229645, "Pleasure doing business with you!" },
            { 738229646, "It's very kind of you, but you've given me more than enough already." },
            { 738229647, "Sorry, but I've got nothing left to swap with you." },
            { 738229648, "Nothing left for you, I'm afraid. Sorry." },
            { 738229649, "Watch and learn!" },
            { 738229650, "Like this!" },
            { 738229651, "Just do what I do!" },
            { 738229652, "Aaand this!" },
            { 738229653, "Theeen this!" },
            { 738229654, "Aaand freeze!" },
            { 738229656, "If I had to guess, I'd say they're offering up prayers to the dead." },
            { 738229657, "Doesn't look like praying's done much for Athia so far." },
            { 738229658, "Well, the habits of a lifetime are hard to break." },
            { 738229659, "And who can blame them for seeking a little solace after all they've lost?" },
            { 738229660, "...Yeah, guess you're right." },
            { 738229661, "If only I could have protected you..." },
            { 738229662, "I know I can't change anything now, but..." },
            { 738229663, "Still wish I could have spoken to you one last time..." },
            { 738229664, "You knew I was Cinta's daughter..." },
            { 738229665, "But you still believed I could save this place. Why?" },
            { 738229666, "Sure wish I could ask you to your face, Bob..." },
            { 738229667, "Sila, Prav, Olas...Mom." },
            { 738229668, "I'll save Athia. I swear." },
            { 738229669, "Just please...show me how..." },
            { 738229670, "You were watching over me the whole time..." },
            { 738229671, "But I'm okay now. Promise." },
            { 738229672, "Rest in peace, Mom." },
