            { 738229721, "Okay. What the hell do I do here!?" },
            { 738229722, "Fighting might be an idea." },
            { 738229723, "There! That must be its weak point!" },
            { 738229724, "I knew it would have a weak point!" },
            { 738229725, "Is this even doing anything!?" },
            { 738229726, "I think so! Keep chipping away!" },
            { 738229727, "C'mon! Drop dead already!" },
            { 738229728, "I'm afraid our reptilian friend seems as stubbornly healthy as ever." },
            { 738229729, "That's the stuff. Keep at it!" },
            { 738229730, "That's it! Show that beast what it means to mess with a vambrace!" },
            { 738229731, "Whoa! Did you see that?" },
            { 738229732, "So gratifying to see my hard work paying dividends." },
            { 738229733, "Not bad for an amateur, I suppose..." },
            { 738229734, "Hey. You wanna do the fighting here?" },
            { 738229736, "Wouldn't want to get on the wrong end of those fangs..." },
            { 738229737, "Ah! Fuck!" },
            { 738229738, "Ugh. Dragon drool." },
            { 738229739, "Careful! You're about to get badly bitten!" },
            { 738229740, "You were saying?" },
            { 738229741, "Even the best of us make mistakes." },
            { 738229742, "Doing nothing isn't going to get us out of here any sooner, you know." },
            { 738229743, "I'll make my move when I damn well feel like it, okay?" },
            { 738229744, "Here's an idea: stop faffing around and do something!" },
            { 738229745, "Hey! Dude! Get off my back." },
            { 738229746, "What's the matter? Frozen with fear?" },
            { 738229747, "Let me guess... I'm gonna need more cover." },
            { 738229748, "And quickly!" },
            { 738229749, "Don't worry, you're not going to die! Unless you get hit, of course." },
            { 738229750, "Has anyone ever told you how sloppily you move?" },
            { 738229753, "What did I do to deserve this!?" },
            { 738229754, "Don't let up now!" },
            { 738229755, "Do be careful not to let me get scratched." },
            { 738229756, "Don't panic." },
            { 738229757, "Steady on, now." },
            { 738229758, "Doesn't look like we'll have much cover here..." },
            { 738229759, "Let's hope our dragon friend doesn't succumb to the urge to blast us with its beam of death again." },
            { 738229760, "I just can't catch a break..." },
            { 738229761, "You alright?" },
            { 738229762, "As alright as I can be..." },
            { 738229763, "That stung a little..." },
            { 738229764, "No time to recuperate. Stay on your feet!" },
            { 738229765, "I don't think I can do this..." },
            { 738229766, "Heal yourself! Come on!" },
            { 738229767, "うわあ！" },
            { 738229768, "Shit! Let go of me!" },
            { 738229769, "Please don't let us end up as this dragon's dinner..." },
            { 738229770, "Cut it out, you piece of shit lizard!" },
            { 738229771, "I hate to think what it might do if it could understand you." },
            { 738229772, "Holy fuck. I thought I was dead for sure." },
            { 738229773, "You must be as unappetizing as you look." },
            { 738229774, "What the fuck!? Where'd it go!?" },
            { 738229775, "Far, far away... One would hope." },
            { 738229776, "It's gone again!" },
            { 738229777, "Stay alert. Try to work out where it will attack from next." },
            { 738229778, "Where is it!?" },
            { 738229779, "Above you! Look out!" },
            { 738229780, "Whoa, whoa, whoa!" },
            { 738229781, "You'll need to predict its movements if you want to stay alive!" },
            { 738229782, "Here it comes again!" },
            { 738229783, "Hey yo, back the fuck off!" },
            { 738229784, "Keep at it! I think you're finally getting somewhere!" },
            { 738229785, "Nice work! Show it what you've got!" },
            { 738229786, "It's attacking from above!" },
            { 738229787, "Still planning on learning how to fly?" },
            { 738229788, "Now is not the time!" },
            { 738229789, "Frey. You need to get directly in front of it. Now." },
            { 738229790, "What!? Are you trying to get me killed!?" },
            { 738229791, "It has a blind spot! Trust me!" },
            { 738229792, "Holy shit!" },
            { 738229793, "What kind of insane super-dragon *is* this!?" },
            { 738229794, "Different from the ones in Newark, is it?" },
            { 738229795, "Aha. Just as I planned." },
            { 738229796, "Yeah, sure you did." },
            { 738229797, "Now, Frey!" },
            { 738229798, "No need to tell me twice!" },
            { 738229812, "Listen, Frey. This is the only way." },
            { 738229813, "Stay focused, and keep those attacks coming!" },
            { 738229814, "I sure hope you're right about this!" },
            { 738229815, "When am I ever wrong?" },
            { 738229816, "Whatever. Alright, let's get this over with!" },
            { 738229821, "It's in bad shape now! We're nearly there!" },
            { 738229822, "Let's finish this!" },
            { 738229823, "More, Frey! More!" },
            { 738229824, "I'm giving it all I've got!" },
            { 738229825, "Fuck! Off! You big-ass! Lizard!" },
            { 738229826, "That's the spirit!" },
            { 738229830, "Ready! We'll go on your signal!" },
            { 738229831, "Alright... Let's kick some fucking ass!" },
            { 738229835, "Dammit! This is crazy!" },
            { 738229836, "Fuck... This is batshit insane..." },
            { 738229838, "This is it!" },
            { 738229839, "It's working!" },
            { 738229840, "Don't start panicking now!" },
            { 738229842, "I must say, you're doing better than I expected." },
            { 738229843, "Just a little longer..." },
            { 738229844, "Well, you may be stubborn, but we're even stubborner!" },
            { 738229845, "Wait, who the hell are these guys!?" },
            { 738229846, "Mindless automata whose only loyalty is to Sila." },
            { 738229847, "Well, they're not zombies, but they're still creepy as fuck." },
            { 738229848, "They're merely husks. They feel nothing. Not even pain." },
            { 738229850, "Dammit! Can't get past their shields!" },
            { 738229851, "You need to wait for an opening!" },
            { 738229852, "Aim for its head!" },
            { 738229853, "Those shields are a pain in the ass!" },
            { 738229854, "So if Sila isn't actually here...where is she?" },
            { 738229855, "Watching you from the safety of her castle, most likely." },
            { 738229856, "This one's no run-of-the-mill Sila drone." },
            { 738229857, "I still can't believe she would do this..." },
            { 738229858, "The Tantas are tyrants. The sooner you learn that, the better." },
            { 738229859, "We need to take this thing down—and fast." },
            { 738229860, "She'll only hurt more innocents if we don't." },
            { 738229861, "Huh? My magic isn't doing anything!" },
            { 738229862, "It must be protected somehow..." },
            { 738229863, "Crap! What is it with flying assholes trying to kill me!?" },
            { 738229864, "Try and knock it down to the ground!" },
            { 738229865, "Huh? What's up with our friend?" },
            { 738229866, "Losing one's wings does make flying something of a challenge..." },
            { 738229867, "Looks like I shut it down." },
            { 738229868, "It appears to be helpless without its wings." },
            { 738229869, "Let's finish this once and for all!" },
            { 738229870, "Come! Face me!" },
            { 738229871, "Shall we dance?" },
            { 738229872, "Show me what you're made of!" },
            { 738229873, "I had hoped you might be a challenge..." },
            { 738229874, "Surely this isn't all you are capable of." },
            { 738229875, "You dare question my authority, demon!?" },
            { 738229876, "Those foolish enough to challenge me are soon put in their place." },
            { 738229877, "You were naive to provoke me, demon." },
            { 738229878, "Give me a fight worth winning!" },
            { 738229879, "A true warrior does not fear death!" },
            { 738229880, "Tell me—what turns the tide of war? The strength of the body? Or the mind?" },
            { 738229881, "Face my blade!" },
            { 738229882, "Stop running from your fate!" },
            { 738229883, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229884, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229885, "If you won't come to me, I'll come to you!" },
            { 738229886, "And how do you hope to defeat me from there?" },
            { 738229887, "As I suspected...you are no warrior." },
            { 738229888, "Do not cower in fear! Fight!" },
            { 738229889, "Coward! Weakling! Are you too craven to face me?" },
            { 738229890, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229891, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229892, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229893, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229894, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229895, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229896, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229897, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229898, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229899, "This is far from over!" },
            { 738229900, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229901, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229902, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229903, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229904, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229905, "Flames consume you!" },
            { 738229906, "Taste my true power!" },
            { 738229907, "Burn, demon!" },
            { 738229908, "You dare face the Tanta of War?" },
            { 738229909, "I will cut you to ribbons!" },
            { 738229910, "Off with your head!" },
            { 738229911, "Time to play!" },
            { 738229912, "I will fell you where you stand!" },
            { 738229913, "Prepare to suffer!" },
            { 738229914, "Try not to lose your head!" },
            { 738229915, "How do you like this!?" },
            { 738229916, "Nowhere to hide!" },
            { 738229917, "My soldiers will make mincemeat of you!" },
            { 738229918, "Wicked demon! This place shall be your grave!" },
            { 738229919, "Shrivel and die, worm!" },
            { 738229920, "Soldiers of Praenost! Give the demon no quarter!" },
            { 738229922, "Forward! Justice must be done!" },
            { 738229923, "Loathsome creature! You shall be hounded to your doom!" },
            { 738229924, "Victory belongs to the righteous!" },
            { 738229925, "We shall never concede! For Praenost!" },
            { 738229927, "So...you have slain my finest..." },
            { 738229928, "You think you have the better of me, demon? Ha!" },
            { 738229929, "Their deaths shall not be in vain!" },
            { 738229930, "One slip, demon, and this battle is done!" },
            { 738229938, "Too slow!" },
            { 738229939, "Suffer!" },
            { 738229940, "Soldiers of Praenost, to me!" },
            { 738229953, "You think you can defeat me? Do your worst!" },
            { 738229954, "Well? Have you had your fill?" },
            { 738229955, "What's the matter? No longer so hungry for revenge?" },
            { 738229956, "All your talk merely amounted to this!?" },
            { 738229961, "Die!" },
            { 738229962, "Burn!" },
            { 738229968, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229969, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738229988, "You are quicker than you look, demon." },
            { 738229989, "Perhaps it is not luck alone that brought you here." },
            { 738229990, "Let us see what else you have to show me." },
            { 738229991, "Do you despise me for killing the child?" },
            { 738229992, "Then show me! Let your rage be your guide!" },
            { 738229993, "It is too late to regret your choices now!" },
            { 738229994, "Huh. Was about to say the same to you." },
            { 738229995, "How can you just murder people without a second thought?" },
            { 738229996, "I told you—there will always be casualties in war." },
            { 738229997, "Only a fool would lament the inevitable." },
            { 738229998, "Don't rest on your laurels. She hasn't yet shown you what she's capable of." },
            { 738230001, "What's the matter? Thought you were supposed to be tough." },
            { 738230002, "Impudent child!" },
            { 738230003, "An opening! Now, Frey!" },
            { 738230004, "Huh. Finally, a challenge..." },
            { 738230005, "Dodging fireballs isn't easy." },
            { 738230006, "Might these pillars protect you from the worst of them, perhaps?" },
            { 738230007, "Be very careful! She's lethal up close!" },
            { 738230010, "The old bait-and-counter, eh? Could work..." },
            { 738230012, "Her power extends to conjuring weapons out of thin air, I see." },
            { 738230014, "Get back, quickly!" },
            { 738230015, "It's raining rocks now!? This shit ain't fair!" },
            { 738230021, "Champions of Praenost! Seize her!" },
            { 738230022, "Hiding behind your minions again? I thought Tantas were supposed to be powerful!" },
            { 738230023, "Foolish child. This has been nothing but sport." },
            { 738230024, "It is time for you to learn what my soldiers are truly capable of." },
            { 738230025, "Ow! These guys are such a pain in my ass!" },
            { 738230028, "To rout her soldiers and gain the advantage or go straight for Sila herself..." },
            { 738230029, "Ahh, isn't this exciting?" },
            { 738230030, "Ugh! Screw you!" },
            { 738230032, "It appears defeating her minions hasn't tempered her will to fight..." },
            { 738230033, "Fuck! That hurts, you know!" },
            { 738230035, "All evil must be purged!" },
            { 738230036, "Did you think I would let you leave here unscathed!?" },
            { 738230037, "Die!" },
            { 738230038, "Pound her into dust!" },
            { 738230039, "There is nowhere to run!" },
            { 738230040, "Doesn't mean you can't get out of the way!" },
            { 738230041, "I see you won't go down without a fight..." },
            { 738230042, "Another weapon? You gotta be kidding me..." },
            { 738230043, "The more you anger me, the stronger I become!" },
            { 738230044, "You wanna talk about angry? Please. Get on my level." },
            { 738230045, "You will not outrun this!" },
            { 738230046, "Do try not to get incinerated!" },
            { 738230047, "Stay calm. You've avoided worse." },
            { 738230049, "Guess friendly fire isn't a concern for you, huh?" },
            { 738230050, "My soldiers would gladly lay down their lives for my cause!" },
            { 738230059, "Tell me, demon—what do you make of my blade?" },
            { 738230060, "Its edge has been honed on the flesh of a thousand enemies!" },
            { 738230061, "Oh, please. I'm ending your bullshit. Now." },
            { 738230062, "Do your worst! My sword screams out for the taste of your blood!" },
            { 738230063, "It has been too long since my last worthy opponent!" },
            { 738230064, "You know, I don't think she's getting any calmer..." },
            { 738230065, "What are you waiting for? I am right here!" },
            { 738230066, "This is going nowhere! Do something, Frey!" },
            { 738230067, "This is for all the people you killed!" },
            { 738230068, "All nameless sacrifices for a greater good!" },
            { 738230069, "This is nowhere near over!" },
            { 738230070, "Relentless, isn't she?" },
            { 738230071, "Gaze upon its beauty if you dare!" },
            { 738230072, "Is it just me, or is she getting more psycho by the minute?" },
            { 738230073, "Watch your step!" },
            { 738230074, "Shit, gotta find somewhere safe!" },
            { 738230093, "Careful—they're deadly at range." },
            { 738230094, "Knock their arrows out of the sky!" },
            { 738230095, "Steer well clear of these ones—they explode!" },
            { 738230096, "Hoisted by one's own petard. Tragic, really." },
            { 738230097, "They're out of arrows! Now, Frey!" },
            { 738230098, "It appears to be weighing its next move..." },
            { 738230099, "It's healing itself!" },
            { 738230100, "You won't be getting anywhere until that barrier's gone." },
            { 738230101, "Those barriers go off with quite a bang, don't they?" },
            { 738230102, "You might want to try destroying them first." },
            { 738230170, "The trial begins. Your stage awaits." },
            { 738230171, "Come, trust unto the hand of fate." },
            { 738230172, "So all we have to do is beat this little lot?" },
            { 738230173, "The law denies its light to none," },
            { 738230174, "By cleansing waters, evil's purged." },
            { 738230175, "You speak of wrongs? Of Sila's sins?" },
            { 738230176, "Such strength, and yet such crushing doubt..." },
            { 738230222, "Looks like you've riled her enough to finally make her do her own dirty work." },
            { 738230223, "I really didn't wanna fight another Tanta..." },
            { 738230224, "Well, you had no choice. She wasn't going to listen to reason." },
            { 738230225, "Watch your step!" },
            { 738230226, "Get out of the water! Quickly!" },
            { 738230227, "Those spheres... You might be able to destroy them." },
            { 738230228, "We're in big trouble if you don't get rid of those spheres!" },
            { 738230229, "She seems to have an endless supply of these things, doesn't she?" },
            { 738230230, "Fuck! They just keep coming!" },
            { 738230233, "She's gathering her power..." },
            { 738230234, "That huge sphere! She's going to make it explode!" },
            { 738230235, "Look out! She's building up for another explosion!" },
            { 738230236, "Well, that was very nimble of you." },
            { 738230237, "Quick thinking. I'm impressed." },
            { 738230238, "How is she even fucking doing this!?" },
            { 738230239, "Don't panic. Stay calm, and wait for your moment." },
            { 738230240, "I'm getting dizzy..." },
            { 738230241, "Oh no. What now?" },
            { 738230242, "She's using her power to manipulate gravity." },
            { 738230243, "Fuck! Can't fucking move!" },
            { 738230244, "Try something! Anything!" },
            { 738230245, "Ugh! Why can't I...move...?" },
            { 738230246, "Calm down and think. There must be something you can do." },
            { 738230247, "Give me my gravity back!" },
            { 738230248, "Magic spheres incoming! Destroy them before they touch you!" },
            { 738230249, "Get away! She's building up to something!" },
            { 738230250, "Look out! Here she comes!" },
            { 738230251, "Above you! Watch out!" },
            { 738230252, "Here she comes again! Keep your eyes open!" },
            { 738230253, "She's distracted. Now's your chance!" },
            { 738230254, "I wonder what it's like to not be able to get along with yourself..." },
            { 738230255, "There she goes, falling out with herself again... Now's your chance!" },
            { 738230256, "Had enough yet?" },
            { 738230257, "Remember, demon, to whom you speak." },
            { 738230258, "No crime goes unpunished by the Tanta of Justice!" },
            { 738230259, "How can she still want to keep doing this!?" },
            { 738230260, "She lost any semblance of reason long ago." },
            { 738230261, "The only way to stop her is to defeat her." },
            { 738230262, "No... No... This trial is...far from over..." },
            { 738230263, "Give it up already! Just admit it—I'm not guilty!" },
            { 738230264, "Remember, Frey—Avoalet's protector is no more." },
            { 738230265, "The woman before you is a despot and a lunatic." },
            { 738230267, "Think of Cipal and all the people you've met!" },
            { 738230268, "She's going to attack! Get out of the water!" },
            { 738230269, "This is no time for a leisurely swim!" },
            { 738230270, "What about this looks \"leisurely\" to you!?" },
            { 738230275, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738230308, "Succumb..." },
            { 738230309, "Let me ease your suffering..." },
            { 738230310, "Do not resist..." },
            { 738230311, "After her..." },
            { 738230312, "There you are..." },
            { 738230313, "You cannot run..." },
            { 738230314, "Do it..." },
            { 738230315, "Sleep... Dream..." },
            { 738230316, "Go..." },
            { 738230317, "Just give in..." },
            { 738230343, "Why do you struggle?" },
            { 738230344, "So meaningless to fight..." },
            { 738230345, "You're here now..." },
            { 738230346, "Sleep tight, dear child..." },
            { 738230347, "Stay with me...forever..." },
            { 738230348, "There is no way out..." },
            { 738230349, "You understand so little..." },
            { 738230350, "A closed mind is a sin..." },
            { 738230351, "No place to belong..." },
            { 738230352, "Nobody who needs you..." },
            { 738230353, "The truth is a double-edged sword..." },
            { 738230354, "How can you see when you have been blinded?" },
            { 738230355, "Escaping this reality is beyond your means..." },
            { 738230356, "All paths are closed..." },
            { 738230357, "Stay, Frey, in my exquisite prison..." },
            { 738230361, "Olas is trying to keep you here." },
            { 738230362, "And if you die here, you'll be trapped forever." },
            { 738230363, "Great. Uh, look...if it looks like she's getting to me again..." },
            { 738230364, "I'll be here to make you see sense. Don't worry." },
            { 738230365, "Both Sila and Prav died by your hand..." },
            { 738230366, "But I have no intention of killing you." },
            { 738230367, "I just want you...to sleep." },
            { 738230369, "What do you gain by saving Athia?" },
            { 738230370, "The others, they use you for their own ends..." },
            { 738230372, "But I can save you." },
            { 738230373, "I see your weariness... The burden you bear..." },
            { 738230374, "You could have it all here." },
            { 738230375, "Enticing. But you got one thing wrong." },
            { 738230376, "Surrender to the corruption within you..." },
            { 738230377, "Ugh... I feel faint..." },
            { 738230378, "Shit... I'm getting sleepy..." },
            { 738230379, "This is not how I go down!" },
            { 738230381, "I am not gonna let you feed me your bullshit!" },
            { 738230382, "Take a moment to focus!" },
            { 738230384, "Let's do this, Cuff!" },
            { 738230385, "Nice!" },
            { 738230386, "Full steam ahead!" },
            { 738230388, "It's defenseless!" },
            { 738230389, "Now's our chance!" },
            { 738230390, "Strike while it's down!" },
            { 738230392, "Uh...what's that weird light?" },
            { 738230393, "Whoa!" },
            { 738230394, "Don't go any closer! She'll try to get inside your head!" },
            { 738230395, "Huh? The ground's shaking..." },
            { 738230396, "I have a bad feeling about this..." },
            { 738230397, "Frey! Are you alright?" },
            { 738230398, "Uh...kinda?" },
            { 738230399, "You can predict when it's about to strike." },
            { 738230400, "Don't let it force you into an unfavorable position." },
            { 738230401, "Great. It's invisible. Just what I needed." },
            { 738230402, "Incoming!" },
            { 738230403, "In front of you!" },
            { 738230404, "Behind you!" },
            { 738230405, "To the left!" },
            { 738230406, "On your right!" },
            { 738230407, "Now!" },
            { 738230410, "Get closer." },
            { 738230412, "Get back!" },
            { 738230414, "Well, Frey? Have you begun to fear my power?" },
            { 738230415, "Rest, Frey. Rest..." },
            { 738230416, "You're just being used, Frey..." },
            { 738230417, "Why can't you see?" },
            { 738230419, "Clones!? Just what I needed." },
            { 738230423, "Have you noticed? The clones look slightly different from the original." },
            { 738230425, "You might try thinning their numbers a little." },
            { 738230427, "My word, it's getting a bit crowded in here." },
            { 738230428, "Not for long!" },
            { 738230429, "Thanks for coming, but this party's over." },
            { 738230430, "Exeunt, stage left!" },
            { 738230432, "My...my faithful servant..." },
            { 738230433, "Guess you weren't such hot shit after all." },
            { 738230436, "When this dream comes crashing down, you will be buried with it." },
            { 738230437, "It looks stronger than before. Keep your eyes open." },
            { 738230443, "Nowhere to go, nobody to turn to." },
            { 738230444, "Is that a life worth living?" },
            { 738230448, "Even if you defeat me, you will not have won." },
            { 738230449, "The real battle still awaits you." },
            { 738230450, "Against my mother, you mean?" },
            { 738230451, "Yeah, I'm looking forward to it." },
            { 738230452, "There is no home for you in Athia." },
            { 738230453, "Make a home for yourself here. Alone. Forever." },
            { 738230454, "Shut up, shut up, shut up!" },
            { 738230463, "I am not...giving up...!" },
            { 738230465, "Fuck...!" },
            { 738230466, "Frey! Hang in there!" },
            { 738230467, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738230468, "Frey! Are you with me?" },
            { 738230471, "I'll kill you a hundred times if I have to!" },
            { 738230472, "Let's see Olas try to stop us now!" },
            { 738230475, "And stay down!" },
            { 738230476, "Where you belong!" },
            { 738230478, "Wicked demon!" },
            { 738230479, "It's that force field again, Frey—" },
            { 738230480, "I noticed! Stay away, right?" },
            { 738230481, "Ugh... I can't..." },
            { 738230483, "It gets worse the longer you're in it!" },
            { 738230485, "Here we go again!" },
            { 738230487, "Focus on the ground!" },
            { 738230489, "Doing alright?" },
            { 738230490, "Just peachy." },
            { 738230491, "She'll need some new tricks if she wants to outsmart us!" },
            { 738230492, "You have to dodge at just the right moment!" },
            { 738230495, "What is this shit!?" },
            { 738230496, "This isn't making her any easier to keep track of it." },
            { 738230497, "Huh? What happened? I don't feel anything..." },
            { 738230498, "It appears we can no longer read our opponent." },
            { 738230499, "She's attacking all our senses at once!" },
            { 738230500, "Just hang on, it'll be over soon enough!" },
            { 738230501, "I can't see anything!" },
            { 738230502, "Well? Can you see yet?" },
            { 738230503, "Fuck! I'm blind again!" },
            { 738230504, "No! Now I can't hear anything!" },
            { 738230505, "...Oof! Okay, my hearing's back." },
            { 738230507, "Something doesn't feel right..." },
            { 738230508, "I can't seem to sense the enemy's movements." },
            { 738230509, "What's happening? I can't s-stop shaking!" },
            { 738230510, "Another one of Olas's tricks..." },
            { 738230511, "My magic's gone weird!" },
            { 738230512, "Try a different spell!" },
            { 738230513, "Okay. Magic's back to normal." },
            { 738230514, "Glad to hear it! Care to start putting it to use?" },
            { 738230694, "The price of your crimes is far from paid!" },
            { 738230695, "Accept your punishment!" },
            { 738230696, "You will suffer as my sister suffered!" },
            { 738230697, "Does it hurt, demon?" },
            { 738230698, "Are you in pain? Only death shall free you from it!" },
            { 738230699, "Alas, demon—you are not long for this world..." },
            { 738230700, "What now? Will you drown, or will you fight?" },
            { 738230701, "Running scared, wretched demon?" },
            { 738230704, "Head to the Throne Room" },
            { 738230705, "ATHLETIC" },
            { 738230706, "I think I should." },
            { 738230707, "Not right now." },
            { 738230708, "Say a prayer?" },
            { 738230709, "You okay?" },
            { 738230710, "I'm fine. It's just—just a little dizzy, that's all." },
            { 738230711, "Don't overdo it, alright?" },
            { 738230712, "Seems the peasant girl isn't entirely without her admirers." },
            { 738230713, "Charming! Pitiful ingrate didn't even say thank you!" },
            { 738230714, "Of all the rotten luck... Why did this have to happen to me?" },
            { 738230715, "Blowing on the painful spot." },
            { 738230716, "Laughing like crazy." },
            { 738230717, "The magic of swear words." },
            { 738230718, "Try blowing on it." },
            { 738230719, "R-really?" },
            { 738230720, "Yeah. A puff or two, and the pain goes right away, I swear." },
            { 738230721, "ふー……ふー……" },
            { 738230722, "It feels funny..." },
            { 738230723, "Laugh as hard as you can. You'll soon forget it hurts at all." },
            { 738230724, "Well? Come on! HA HA HA HA HA!" },
            { 738230725, "Ha ha ha ha! Heh heh heh!" },
            { 738230726, "You're silly!" },
            { 738230727, "Alright. Can you say, \"motherf—\" Um, actually, how about...\"stinky butts\"? Yeah. That oughta do it." },
            { 738230728, "What's that? What does \"stinky butts\" mean?" },
            { 738230729, "It's magic. A spell to make the pain go away." },
            { 738230730, "Alright... Stinky butts! Those words sound silly!" },
            { 738230731, "Thank you, nice lady." },
            { 738230732, "Well, you're certainly one for the cutting-edge therapeutic approaches, I'll give you that." },
            { 738230734, "All done?" },
            { 738230735, "Yup. Alright, next up. Looks like...going to fetch people's food rations." },
            { 738230736, "Wait. There's more?" },
            { 738230737, "Seems like there's a place in town where they hand out everyone's food." },
            { 738230738, "Better head to that place where they hand out all the food." },
            { 738230739, "Well, this promises to be no fun whatsoever." },
            { 738230740, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738230741, "You okay?" },
            { 738230742, "Urgh... I'm fine." },
            { 738230743, "I'm here to collect some rations." },
            { 738230744, "And who might you be, exactly?" },
            { 738230745, "I'm Auden's stand-in. What's it to you?" },
            { 738230746, "Oh, sorry." },
            { 738230747, "Yeah, so she sent me to pick up the rations for all the sick and injured." },
            { 738230748, "But I'm not doing too swimmingly myself...as you can see." },
            { 738230749, "You couldn't go and grab them for me, could you?" },
            { 738230750, "It's just over there." },
            { 738230751, "He's in charge of the whole operation." },
            { 738230752, "Alright, so just head over there and grab the stuff, right?" },
            { 738230753, "Yes. Sorry to have to ask this of you..." },
            { 738230754, "You're not the luckiest guy in town, huh?" },
            { 738230755, "I'm sorry, alright?" },
            { 738230756, "Look, I'm here to pick up food for the injured." },
            { 738230757, "Oh, yeah. Auden sent me to do it, but as you can see, I'm not doing too well myself." },
            { 738230758, "I-if you can just wait a little—" },
            { 738230759, "No. It's no good. You'll have to get them for me." },
            { 738230760, "Off I go then, I guess." },
            { 738230761, "See the explanation of what you need to do?" },
            { 738230762, "Sure." },
            { 738230763, "No need." },
            { 738230764, "See if they'll chuck a little extra in, won't you? Those people need all the nutrition they can get." },
            { 738230765, "Come and speak to me again when you've got the rations." },
            { 738230766, "Sure." },
            { 738230767, "And you think it would help Auden?" },
            { 738230768, "It might help her to relax, at least." },
            { 738230769, "Like the ballow tree, it is found in Avoalet." },
            { 738230770, "Avoalet, eh? Well, if we're headed there in search of resin, we might as well have a look." },
            { 738230771, "But first, we need to take this food back to Auden." },
            { 738230772, "Please, you must take care not to overstretch yourself as she has." },
            { 738230773, "I've just heard dreadful news—the land where the animals used to graze has been swallowed by the Corruption." },
            { 738230774, "Well, our crops are safe, and we must be grateful for that—but there's little else to give thanks for." },
            { 738230775, "No... We can't give up now..." },
            { 738230776, "There must be something I can do..." },
            { 738230777, "We'd better hurry up and get to Avoalet, for Auden's sake as well as her father's." },
            { 738230778, "You think this is that giril stuff?" },
            { 738230779, "I think it might be, you know. Let's see if it calms the poor girl down as promised." },
            { 738230780, "Just that resin to find now, and we're all set." },
            { 738230787, "You're right. Let's go." },
            { 738230788, "Owww... Argh!" },
            { 738230789, "Don't worry! I know how to stop it hurting!" },
            { 738230790, "Just blow on it, like this!" },
            { 738230791, "You just have to laugh as loud as you can!" },
            { 738230792, "Just shout, \"Stinky butts!\"" },
            { 738230793, "What?" },
            { 738230794, "It'll make the pain go away...probably." },
            { 738230795, "Huh. You know what? I do feel a little better. Thanks, little one." },
            { 738230811, "Up until now, we've been living one day at a time." },
            { 738230812, "Now we can finally start to think of the future." },
            { 738230813, "And it's all thanks to you. We owe you so much." },
            { 738230814, "People are being ever so good about helping with the rebuilding. But it's not all plain sailing." },
            { 738230815, "I must do everything I can to keep things on track." },
            { 738230816, "I can't let my best friend's effort go to waste, after all." },
            { 738230817, "Do you have time for a quick drink, Frey?" },
            { 738230818, "Our friend behind the bar tells me he's concocting something very special indeed." },
            { 738230819, "Woman" },
            { 738230820, "I don't see why. You've been asleep for ages." },
            { 738230821, "Fed the sheep." },
            { 738230822, "Fed the chickens." },
            { 738230823, "Fed the cat." },
