            { 738230893, "CHAPTER 13" },
            { 738230894, "Any more minions you wanna send my way? I'm getting bored." },
            { 738230895, "Do resist the urge to provoke her..." },
            { 738230896, "Please. These are minor-league baddies at best." },
            { 738230897, "They're not very fast, but look out for those axes." },
            { 738230898, "She doubts not that her cause is just." },
            { 738230900, "Okay, I admit it. This is getting pretty fucking tiring." },
            { 738230901, "I told you not to provoke her..." },
            { 738230902, "I do NOT need this shit on top of everything else!" },
            { 738230903, "Well, we're not going anywhere, so you'd better get used to it." },
            { 738230904, "But Tanta's end is end of all..." },
            { 738230905, "Its balance lost, the land would fall..." },
            { 738230906, "I told you, there's no point reasoning with her. End this, Frey." },
            { 738230907, "Only Prav's death can ensure their safety!" },
            { 738230910, "What's this?" },
            { 738230911, "Looks like some sort of mineral. And quite a special one at that." },
            { 738230912, "Huh. Okay." },
            { 738230913, "I most certainly shall. Despite having no idea what it means." },
            { 738230920, "Breakbob." },
            { 738230921, "The Tantas." },
            { 738230922, "Cinta." },
            { 738230926, "Who should I pray for?" },
            { 738230927, "Olevia." },
