            { 738231116, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231117, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231118, "We will find you, Frey!" },
            { 738231119, "Happy holidays." },
            { 738231120, "Catch you guys later." },
            { 738231121, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231122, "Come on, let's go! Let's go!" },
            { 738231123, "It's my fault. I believed in her and I..." },
            { 738231124, "...helped her escape the Tower of Binnoi..." },
            { 738231125, "No, it's not." },
            { 738231126, "I'm to blame." },
            { 738231127, "Wherever I go turns to shit." },
            { 738231128, "It's always been this way." },
            { 738231129, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231130, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231131, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231132, "N-no, no, I-I did this!" },
            { 738231133, "I'm so sorry, I—" },
            { 738231134, "You are nothing but a selfish leech." },
            { 738231135, "Athia's better off without you." },
            { 738231137, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231138, "And pray some still have resin to give." },
            { 738231139, "Got it." },
            { 738231140, "I should go." },
            { 738231141, "So, uh, I am just gonna go walk through this door." },
            { 738231142, "Okay. So I'll ask her to stop the Break, and everybody wins." },
            { 738231143, "Right?" },
            { 738231144, "Wait! I declare a mistrial!" },
            { 738231145, "A mistrial?" },
            { 738231146, "That's what the demon said." },
            { 738231147, "We must honor such a declaration! Always!" },
            { 738231148, "Must we?" },
            { 738231149, "We must." },
            { 738231150, "Then another trial must be called—a Trial by Water!" },
            { 738231151, "Yes! A Trial by Water!" },
            { 738231152, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231153, "あははははは……" },
            { 738231154, "Let's see how long your lies sustain you!" },
            { 738231155, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231156, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231157, "Your only choice, then—to prevail!" },
            { 738231158, "Damn! And I thought courts in New York were bad..." },
            { 738231159, "But whatever." },
            { 738231160, "Bring it!" },
            { 738231161, "Wait, what? You mean there's more?" },
            { 738231162, "Man, fuck you!" },
            { 738231163, "Once more unto the breach..." },
            { 738231164, "You will rot here forever! Forever!" },
            { 738231165, "Sadly, I don't think we'll be getting out of this without another fight..." },
            { 738231166, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231167, "And so..." },
            { 738231168, "We're about to get very wet indeed!" },
            { 738231169, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231170, "Shut the fuck up." },
            { 738231171, "That's my girl." },
            { 738231172, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231173, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231174, "Cinta's waiting. Can you just quit messing around and do the thing, Cuff?" },
            { 738231176, "I am their last and loudest laugh." },
            { 738231177, "The endgame. The end of the Tantas. The end of Athia. The end...of you." },
            { 738231178, "Now, if you would be so good as to die so I can get on with the havoc-wreaking and what have you." },
            { 738231179, "I'm twenty-one years behind schedule." },
            { 738231180, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231181, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231182, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231184, "Shit! My powers... They're gone!" },
            { 738231185, "Your powers? They were never yours!" },
            { 738231186, "Without me... You. Are. Nothing." },
            { 738231187, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231188, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231189, "You can't escape me, Frey!" },
            { 738231198, "After all, that is why Cinta brought you here." },
            { 738231199, "What have I done..." },
            { 738231200, "\"All will be well.\"" },
            { 738231201, "Do you remember those words, daughter of Cinta?" },
            { 738231202, "\"All will be well.\"" },
            { 738231203, "You were able to stop us before Athia was completely destroyed." },
            { 738231204, "You have nothing to lament." },
            { 738231205, "We are so grateful for all that you have done." },
            { 738231206, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231207, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231208, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231209, "No! No, no! No!" },
            { 738231210, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231211, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231212, "I'll clean up down here. You keep that bastard busy." },
            { 738231213, "Just...try and survive through this, okay? You're Athians!" },
            { 738231214, "Stay in the archives. You'll be safe here." },
            { 738231215, "Who do you think you are?" },
            { 738231216, "I'm Tanta Frey!" },
            { 738231217, "Daughter of Cinta! Protector of Athia!" },
            { 738231218, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231219, "And I'm here to fuck you up!" },
            { 738231220, "How..." },
            { 738231221, "How has the power of the four Tantas..." },
            { 738231222, "Correction: the five." },
            { 738231223, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231224, "I can't believe you fell for that." },
            { 738231225, "What?" },
            { 738231227, "No! No, no—" },
            { 738231230, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231231, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231232, "Tanta's blessings! You did it!" },
            { 738231233, "Really?" },
            { 738231234, "Really." },
            { 738231235, "Ow..." },
            { 738231236, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231237, "No, really. Ow." },
            { 738231238, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231239, "But it's a good thing I'm not doing it on my own." },
            { 738231240, "Isn't that right, Cuff?" },
            { 738231241, "It's Vambrace." },
            { 738231242, "Above you!" },
            { 738231243, "Well, that was a little hairy..." },
            { 738231244, "That's your idea of encouragement!?" },
            { 738231245, "Hey, fuck off!" },
            { 738231246, "Try to predict its next movement." },
            { 738231247, "Well!? Don't just stand there! Kill her!" },
            { 738231248, "Ugh...! Useless fools!" },
            { 738231249, "Inconceivable..." },
            { 738231250, "This demon's power...is greater than I imagined..." },
            { 738231251, "Crumble to ashes!" },
            { 738231252, "Embrace the flames!" },
            { 738231253, "Foolish child." },
            { 738231254, "Your carelessness shall cost you your life!" },
            { 738231255, "She must not escape!" },
            { 738231256, "Do not allow the demon to flee!" },
            { 738231257, "This ends now!" },
            { 738231258, "You will pay for your insolence!" },
            { 738231259, "You leave me little choice!" },
            { 738231260, "Kneel before me and suffer!" },
            { 738231261, "Return to the darkness from whence you came!" },
            { 738231262, "I will run you through!" },
            { 738231263, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231264, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231265, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231266, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231267, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231268, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231269, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231270, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231271, "There!" },
            { 738231272, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231273, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231274, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231275, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231276, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231277, "Death comes swiftly!" },
            { 738231278, "Fire and steel!" },
            { 738231279, "A fatal mistake!" },
            { 738231280, "I will crush every bone in your body!" },
            { 738231281, "How much pain can you endure, I wonder?" },
            { 738231282, "Feast your eyes upon the true power of a Tanta!" },
            { 738231283, "There is no escape for the enemies of Athia!" },
            { 738231284, "Entertain me! DIE!" },
            { 738231285, "And now you breathe your last!" },
            { 738231286, "All shall be razed before me!" },
            { 738231291, "Don't let her provoke you! Concentrate!" },
            { 738231292, "There's no way I'm letting myself lose to this bitch." },
            { 738231293, "I'm glad to hear it. And the street urchin would be too." },
            { 738231294, "Damn! The pillar!" },
            { 738231295, "Yes... She is rather strong, isn't she?" },
            { 738231296, "Not another one!" },
            { 738231297, "We'd best wrap this up quickly." },
            { 738231298, "Fuck! There goes my cover!" },
            { 738231299, "Nowhere left to hide, eh? Buckle up!" },
            { 738231300, "Maybe try not getting hit next time." },
            { 738231301, "You're panicking. Try to anticipate her next move." },
            { 738231302, "Come on! You're better than that!" },
            { 738231303, "They don't really leave much room for cover..." },
            { 738231304, "It appears you've put a dent in the mighty Sila's armor..." },
            { 738231305, "That dent's about to get a lot bigger." },
            { 738231306, "No... My fearless warriors..." },
            { 738231307, "You're next, bitch!" },
            { 738231308, "Insolent wretch! You think you can defeat me?" },
            { 738231309, "Damn right I do." },
            { 738231310, "Just a little more! She's got no one to defend her now!" },
            { 738231311, "Oh, go purge yourself." },
            { 738231312, "Bring it on!" },
            { 738231313, "Here they come!" },
            { 738231314, "Careful, Frey!" },
            { 738231315, "Come, demon! Give me all that you have!" },
            { 738231316, "Gladly!" },
            { 738231317, "Strike me down, demon—if you can!" },
            { 738231318, "Well, since you asked so nicely!" },
            { 738231319, "This is nothing..." },
            { 738231320, "You've come too far to fall now!" },
            { 738231321, "Steady, Frey! Take her down!" },
            { 738231322, "Impressive..." },
            { 738231323, "Damn right. I didn't come here to lose!" },
            { 738231324, "Your power...may just rival my own..." },
            { 738231326, "She's certainly got more than a few tricks up her sleeve..." },
            { 738231327, "Flames of war, strike down my foe!" },
            { 738231328, "I would say \"take cover,\" but she hasn't left us much to work with..." },
            { 738231329, "Try as you might, there is no escape!" },
            { 738231330, "Shit! Okay, this is not how I'm going to die!" },
            { 738231331, "Your wretched life ends here and now!" },
            { 738231332, "Sorry, gonna have to disappoint you there!" },
            { 738231333, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231334, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231335, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231336, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231337, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231338, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231339, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231340, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231341, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231342, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231343, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231344, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231345, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231346, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231347, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231348, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231349, "Hah. Won't even break a sweat." },
            { 738231350, "But by its glare are lies undone." },
            { 738231351, "Thus proven, innocents emerge." },
            { 738231352, "How come you're not the one having to \"prove\" this shit!?" },
            { 738231353, "You seek transgressors? Look within!" },
            { 738231354, "You think I'll listen to anything you have to say when you're putting me through this shit?" },
            { 738231355, "A home's no thing to be without..." },
            { 738231356, "Hah! I can dodge those in my sleep." },
            { 738231357, "That what she does is what she must." },
            { 738231358, "\"Just\"!? She is a Tanta-killer! And she must die for what she has done!" },
            { 738231359, "Someone seems set on giving you the death sentence..." },
            { 738231360, "Fuck. Gimme a break..." },
            { 738231361, "She is a criminal! A committer of unforgivable sins! Ignore her! Destroy her!" },
            { 738231362, "Yo, tell your crazy side this is a private conversation." },
            { 738231363, "All I want is to help those people!" },
            { 738231364, "Foul demon! Your shameless hypocrisy is as vile as your lies!" },
            { 738231365, "She has a case, I sense her plight," },
            { 738231366, "A fair trial is her due, her right..." },
            { 738231367, "\"Right\"!? She has no rights! Preposterous! Ridiculous!" },
            { 738231368, "And avoid falling in at all costs..." },
            { 738231369, "Uh...what!? Okay. Destroy the giant sphere. Got it." },
            { 738231370, "Wh-what...is happening...!?" },
            { 738231371, "The trial was passed. The accused is innocent." },
            { 738231372, "Lies! Deceit! The trial means nothing!" },
            { 738231373, "The killer must be put to death!" },
            { 738231374, "N-not...again...!" },
            { 738231375, "The verdict is passed. The accused must be acquitted." },
            { 738231376, "The accused is guilty! Her penalty must be death!" },
            { 738231377, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231378, "It is our sworn duty to see fair judgment passed." },
            { 738231379, "NO! We punish those who break our laws! That is our purpose!" },
            { 738231380, "Leave me...be..." },
            { 738231381, "No more punishment shall be meted out today." },
            { 738231382, "Collusion! You are in league with the accused!" },
            { 738231383, "Silence! SILENCE!!!" },
            { 738231384, "Why...must you interfere...?" },
            { 738231385, "It is long past time. This trial must end." },
            { 738231386, "No! No, nooo!!!" },
            { 738231387, "Not until her debt is paid!" },
            { 738231388, "Shut up! Shut up, shut up!!!" },
            { 738231389, "I am judge...jury...and executioner!" },
            { 738231390, "No more! Hold your tongue!" },
            { 738231392, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231393, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231394, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231395, "There is no need to suffer. Let me keep you safe." },
            { 738231396, "I hate coffee!" },
            { 738231397, "So you can trap me in this surrealist shit show?" },
            { 738231398, "No thanks." },
            { 738231399, "Stay with me, Frey!" },
            { 738231400, "Sleep and you'll never open your eyes again!" },
            { 738231401, "Your wish is my command!" },
            { 738231402, "Something nasty, I'm sure. Be careful." },
            { 738231403, "She's up to something..." },
            { 738231404, "Pay attention to what you can feel and hear." },
            { 738231405, "If you don't stop whining, you'll never hear it coming." },
            { 738231406, "Damn it..." },
            { 738231407, "Ignore her. We can do this." },
            { 738231408, "You can't make me!" },
            { 738231409, "Can you, like, not?" },
            { 738231410, "Relax, Frey. I'm still with you." },
            { 738231411, "Their quantity's no match for our quality. Wouldn't you say?" },
            { 738231412, "Abso-fucking-lutely." },
            { 738231413, "Hmm... I thought its death would free us from this illusion..." },
            { 738231414, "But nothing's changed..." },
            { 738231415, "Wait. You're not saying...we're stuck here forever?" },
            { 738231416, "If I teach you one thing, Frey..." },
            { 738231417, "Huh?" },
            { 738231418, "It will be that nothing but despair awaits you..." },
            { 738231419, "What the—!? That thing's supposed to be dead!" },
            { 738231431, "Sounding a little stressed there!" },
            { 738231432, "Precisely." },
            { 738231433, "She must be obstructing your ability to feel pain." },
            { 738231434, "But rest assured—you're still being injured. Don't get careless." },
            { 738231435, "We'll just have to wait it out..." },
            { 738231436, "Just calm down! It can't last forever!" },
            { 738231437, "Huh. Yeah." },
            { 738231438, "You'll just have to rely on your ears!" },
            { 738231439, "What do you think I am, a bat!?" },
            { 738231440, "Really? What about now?" },
            { 738231441, "Cuff? Can you hear me?" },
            { 738231442, "Yes, I can hear you just fine!" },
            { 738231443, "I couldn't go outside and play with the kids. I couldn't walk on beautiful landscapes." },
            { 738231444, "I didn't have a mother or a father that wanted me!" },
            { 738231445, "Or loved me." },
            { 738231446, "So no." },
            { 738231447, "I don't care what happens to Athia." },
            { 738231448, "If it's saved, or if it burns." },
            { 738231449, "I. Don't. Give a shit, because this place is not my home!" },
            { 738231450, "Just leave." },
            { 738231451, "Leave!" },
            { 738231452, "With fucking pleasure." },
            { 738231453, "Are you the Tanta slayer?" },
            { 738231454, "You got the wrong girl." },
            { 738231455, "No?" },
            { 738231456, "The savior of Athia..." },
            { 738231457, "Can I at least get an apology for the part where you threatened to sell me to the highest bidder?" },
            { 738231458, "I'll add you to the list." },
            { 738231459, "It's looking pretty long..." },
            { 738231460, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231461, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231462, "Homer..." },
            { 738231463, "Aren't I glad to see you." },
            { 738231464, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231465, "Thank you!" },
            { 738231466, "The super finally got our heat fixed. Nice and toasty in here, huh?" },
            { 738231467, "Finally! Damn cats outside stopped their wailing!" },
            { 738231468, "Smells like pie... Who do I have to bribe for a slice?" },
            { 738231469, "I found some kittens out by the trash! Brought 'em in, and now I can't bear to let 'em go..." },
            { 738231472, "Cut the bullshit and let me outta here." },
            { 738231473, "You know I can't do that." },
            { 738231474, "You created this, so I'll say it again: Cut the bullshit and let me. The fuck. Outta here." },
            { 738231475, "I will not accept the same fate as my sisters." },
            { 738231476, "Frey! Finally!" },
            { 738231477, "Where the fuck have you been?" },
            { 738231478, "I will explain later." },
            { 738231479, "First, let's find a way out of this madwoman's nightmare!" },
            { 738231480, "Auden, Johedy, the people of Cipal..." },
            { 738231481, "And Homer. Hmm." },
            { 738231482, "Better if you die here, now." },
            { 738231483, "No one will ever even have to know." },
            { 738231484, "Don't listen, Frey! I care! I'm with you!" },
            { 738231485, "No..." },
            { 738231486, "No! No! This is...this is another one of your mind games!" },
            { 738231487, "Isn't that right, Olas?" },
            { 738231488, "Huh? What's the matter? Too scared to face me yourself?" },
            { 738231489, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231490, "Shit..." },
            { 738231491, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231492, "Aaaaaaggghhh!" },
            { 738231493, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231494, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231495, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738231496, "Dragon" },
            { 738231502, "Well, I can't have you dying out here and leaving me stranded." },
            { 738231503, "Yeah, maybe save me before the fall next time?" },
            { 738231504, "I don't have to save you at all!" },
            { 738231505, "I aid you of my own free will, not because I—" },
            { 738231506, "Yeah, whatever." },
