            { 738231601, "A Change in Lower Cipal" },
            { 738231634, "It is so cold today!" },
            { 738231635, "What should I get her...?" },
            { 738231636, "Maybe I should go home early today..." },
            { 738231637, "Need to get myself a new coat..." },
            { 738231638, "Those decorations just remind me of when I was a kid!" },
            { 738231639, "Can't believe how great this year has been!" },
            { 738231640, "Can't wait to open my presents!" },
            { 738231641, "Damn! I'm gonna be late for the party!" },
            { 738231642, "Everyone is waiting for me. Better hurry." },
            { 738231643, "Oh man, I love it when we all get together like that!" },
            { 738231644, "I hope she likes my present." },
            { 738231645, "Can't wait to see the kids' faces!" },
            { 738231646, "Ah, what the hell. A standing rib roast!" },
            { 738231647, "Can't wait to get home and see everybody!" },
            { 738231648, "Ah, just look at it. The city at Christmastime." },
            { 738231649, "I'm starving!" },
            { 738231655, "Hello! Anyone home?" },
            { 738231656, "Nice. I could use a rest." },
            { 738231659, "And of course now we have to deal with an even bigger one." },
            { 738231660, "Lucky me!" },
            { 738231661, "Not bad." },
            { 738231662, "Thanks, Professor." },
            { 738231663, "I told you to call me Vambrace." },
            { 738231664, "Sure, Cuff. Sure." },
            { 738231665, "Looks like no one's been here for a while." },
            { 738231666, "I wonder how long everything's been in this shitty state..." },
            { 738231667, "Perhaps we should find somewhere else to search." },
            { 738231668, "What the hell happened here?" },
            { 738231669, "Not only is it completely empty, but...this place is...twisted." },
            { 738231670, "Perhaps it has something to do with the strange creatures prowling about the place." },
            { 738231671, "No one there... No one at all..." },
            { 738231672, "Where the hell did everyone go?" },
            { 738231673, "Your guess is as good as mine." },
            { 738231674, "What's with this weird tree?" },
            { 738231675, "Interestingly, I don't think it looks like that because of the Break..." },
            { 738231676, "This blue glow—what's that about?" },
            { 738231677, "The essence of life distilled, if some are to be believed..." },
            { 738231678, "It's all shriveled up..." },
            { 738231679, "An unavoidable result of harvesting the sap, unfortunately." },
            { 738231680, "So that's it? This tree's basically dead now?" },
            { 738231681, "Couldn't say for certain. Given a few years it might perk up, but that's time we don't have." },
            { 738231683, "I think I'll just go to a cafe and read my book." },
            { 738231684, "Knish for lunch again? Don't mind if I do!" },
            { 738231685, "It's a perfect day for a walk in the park!" },
            { 738231686, "Ugh... Worst hangover ever..." },
            { 738231687, "What was with that verdict? Unbelievable..." },
            { 738231688, "Damn. Still need to go order that cake..." },
            { 738231689, "Hope Mom and Dad make it here on time..." },
            { 738231690, "Can't remember the last time it was so warm this early in the year..." },
            { 738231803, "Added to Archive\nNotes on the Torana" },
            { 738231842, "Suppose our only choice is to keep looking." },
            { 738231843, "Burst Shot" },
            { 738231844, "Fires forth lumps of explosive rock that deal area damage." },
            { 738231845, "Shield Shot" },
            { 738231846, "Creates a defensive shield while charging, which is blasted forward in pieces when released." },
            { 738231847, "Scatter Shot" },
            { 738231848, "Fires a steady stream of rocks while charging, then unleashes a high-impact, long-range projectile when released." },
            { 738231849, "Arc Slice" },
            { 738231850, "A lightning-quick area slice with a huge magical sword. In midair, it won't go as far, but will deal more damage." },
            { 738231851, "Blast Slice" },
            { 738231852, "Throws a magical spear at an enemy that damages them and the surrounding area. Flies further and hits harder from midair." },
            { 738231853, "Rage Slice" },
            { 738231854, "Unleashes a flurry of magical punches while charging, then sends enemies flying with explosive force when released." },
            { 738231855, "Chain Bolt" },
            { 738231856, "Fires an arrow upon charging, and another upon release. If both strike in the same place, bonus damage is dealt." },
            { 738231857, "Fan Bolt" },
            { 738231858, "Fires a spray of magically linked arrows out in front of you, dealing damage over the entire area they cover." },
            { 738231859, "Cluster Bolt" },
            { 738231860, "Fires an arrow which breaks up in midair, raining down bolts that deal damage over a wide area." },
            { 738231861, "Pulse Dart" },
            { 738231862, "Sends beams of light at any darts embedded in enemies that shoot right through them, dealing damage as they go." },
            { 738231863, "Storm Dart" },
            { 738231864, "Emits electrical energy while charging, then unleashes a shockwave when released that will also strike any darts embedded in enemies." },
            { 738231865, "Seeker Dart" },
            { 738231866, "Emits an electrical attack that arcs between any darts embedded in enemies." },
