            { 738232025, "Athia's destruction has long been written!" },
            { 738232026, "Oh yeah? Then why do you sound so nervous?" },
            { 738232027, "All four Tantas together were powerless to stop me." },
            { 738232028, "What makes you think you can triumph alone?" },
            { 738232029, "Surrender now, and I'll make this painless." },
