            { 738232309, "Added to Archive\nNotes on Bob 1\nRobian was once a scholar working under Cinta.\nHe was well versed in a wide variety of subjects, including magic, hist..." },
            { 738232310, "Added to Archive\nNotes on Bob 2\nWhen the Break appeared, Robian took charge, leading his people to Cipal for safety." },
            { 738232311, "Added to Archive\nNotes on Bob 3\nOnce things had settled down, Robian started conducting research on the Break.\nAt some point he was swallowed up into ..." },
            { 738232312, "SCS - Johedy\nFrey is given a map of Sila's Castle by the librarian.\nHer name is Johedy.\nGather information about the Tanta" },
            { 738232313, "Added to Archive\nNotes on the Tanta 1\nWhat are Monuments?" },
            { 738232314, "Added to Archive\nNotes on the Tanta 2\nWhat are the Tanta Springs?" },
            { 738232315, "Added to Archive\nNotes on the Tanta 3\nThe cause for the Break seems to be linked to the Tanta in some way.\nThe Break has continued to spread, and the ..." },
            { 738232316, "Added to Archive\nNotes on the Tanta 4\n2 years ago, the Tanta were thought of as kind, wise rulers of their respective realms." },
