            { 738232359, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232360, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232361, "Well, that was disappointing." },
            { 738232362, "The end of Athia is nigh!" },
            { 738232363, "There's no one left to stop me now!" },
            { 738232364, "If only you'd run home like a good little girl." },
            { 738232365, "What is...this power...?" },
            { 738232366, "No! Why!? How can this be!?" },
            { 738232367, "Defeat...is unthinkable..." },
            { 738232368, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232369, "I'm stubborn, remember? You know that better than anyone." },
            { 738232370, "So...it's come to this." },
            { 738232371, "Frankly, I'm surprised. But you go no further." },
            { 738232372, "You can still give up, you know." },
            { 738232373, "After you." },
            { 738232374, "At last, my time in Athia comes to an end." },
            { 738232375, "And not a moment too soon." },
            { 738232376, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232379, "Why go to such extraordinary lengths?" },
            { 738232380, "So you don't get the satisfaction of winning!" },
            { 738232381, "You think you're the righteous one here?" },
            { 738232382, "How many have you killed, hm?" },
            { 738232383, "Too many. But I'm gonna make up for it. By stopping you." },
            { 738232384, "Can you feel it, Cuff? The beginning of the end?" },
            { 738232385, "...Hmph. Let's see who's the last one standing." },
            { 738232386, "Cuff..." },
            { 738232387, "There is nothing more to say!" },
            { 738232388, "Why do you insist on resisting the inevitable?" },
            { 738232389, "Why do you insist on tearing everything to pieces?" },
            { 738232390, "I told you—it is my life's purpose!" },
            { 738232391, "I've been trying to run away this whole time." },
            { 738232392, "But I'm done running from my problems. And I'm done running from you." },
            { 738232394, "Time to finish this." },
            { 738232395, "No...I can't lose..." },
            { 738232396, "I am not dying now!" },
            { 738232397, "I can't...let them down..." },
            { 738232398, "Hang in there, Frey..." },
