            { 738232474, "Can't remember the last time I saw you outside the archives." },
            { 738232475, "That's them dealt with." },
            { 738232476, "Let's take a look inside the castle." },
            { 738232477, "What the f—" },
            { 738232478, "Mom?" },
            { 738232479, "Wh-where are you going?" },
            { 738232480, "I'd say she wants you to follow her." },
            { 738232481, "What's this box? Huh. There's a keyhole here." },
            { 738232482, "I suppose this must be what that key was for." },
            { 738232483, "Hey, is this—" },
            { 738232484, "She's gone..." },
            { 738232488, "What's this?" },
            { 738232489, "<UnknownFormatting>\"Know that wherever you may be, I am always with you.\"" },
            { 738232490, "I wanted them as a memorial for someone, you see." },
            { 738232491, "And she'll be more than happy with what you've given me. Thanks again." },
            { 738232496, "Of course—something you were perfectly capable of doing anyway. Ingenious." },
            { 738232497, "Oh yeah! The treasure-seeker strikes again!" },
            { 738232498, "Failed Deleting Save Data" },
            { 738232505, "That or they all loved one another very much, and now you're in trouble for hurting their friends." },
            { 738232506, "Hilarious. I'm laughing on the inside." },
            { 738232507, "Yes. Shame they're long since dead." },
            { 738232509, "How the hell am I supposed to fight a dragon!?" },
            { 738232510, "Anything that big must have a weak point!" },
            { 738232511, "I'm not hurting it at all!" },
            { 738232512, "Perhaps we're not quite ready for this particular opponent yet..." },
            { 738232513, "Look out!" },
            { 738232514, "Try not to get stepped on." },
            { 738232515, "Whoa!" },
            { 738232516, "Okay, this is bad. Very bad!" },
            { 738232517, "Take cover!" },
            { 738232524, "Ugh..." },
            { 738232525, "This is not good..." },
            { 738232536, "Damn! Talk about tough!" },
            { 738232537, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232538, "Wicked demon!" },
            { 738232539, "How dare you besmirch my armor!?" },
            { 738232540, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232541, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232542, "You will regret this!" },
            { 738232543, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232544, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738232545, "Not if this is the best you've got!" },
            { 738232546, "I need to get in close and hit him with the big guns!" },
            { 738232547, "Why don't you busy yourself with my friends here?" },
            { 738232548, "It's over!" },
            { 738232549, "Is that all Athia's hero has to offer?" },
            { 738232550, "I underestimated you." },
            { 738232551, "Yeah. I get that a lot. Not many people see my—" },
            { 738232552, "Potential?" },
            { 738232553, "No. My anger and resentment." },
            { 738232554, "But I see yours." },
            { 738232555, "You are pissed at the Tantas. You would do anything to settle old scores." },
            { 738232556, "And you don't care if innocent people have to die." },
            { 738232557, "My caring is beside the point." },
            { 738232558, "I was given a duty. And duties are meant to be performed." },
            { 738232559, "I am so tired of your bullshit." },
            { 738232560, "Take accountability for your actions." },
            { 738232561, "I was given life that Athia might burn!" },
            { 738232562, "Her people, her precious Tantas—all must die!" },
            { 738232563, "You think justice will be served by your defeating me?" },
            { 738232564, "I couldn't care less about justice." },
            { 738232565, "All I care about is kicking your ass." },
            { 738232566, "All must die! A new world shall be built upon Athia's ashes!" },
            { 738232567, "The will of the Rheddig must be done!" },
            { 738232568, "But is it what you really want?" },
            { 738232569, "Curse you, Tanta!" },
            { 738232570, "Why...why!? Why do you still stand!?" },
            { 738232571, "Because people are counting on me." },
            { 738232572, "All that remains is to decide the fate of Athia!" },
            { 738232573, "No!" },
            { 738232574, "Ready, Cuff?" },
            { 738232591, "Yield! There is nowhere left to run!" },
            { 738232592, "Not a chance in hell!" },
