            { 738232601, "Thanks ever so much, dear." },
            { 738232602, "These are the three sorts of flowers I'm looking for. Let me know if you manage to find any, won't you?" },
            { 738232607, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Wonderful—as if things weren't bad enough, it seems we've a hulking great monstrosity to deal with. As I'm sure you've guessed, thi..." },
            { 738232608, "<iconChapterSumVfx>I think you might want to run, you know. Regardless of your newfound powers, you're no match for these kinds of numbers. Finding so..." },
            { 738232609, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Good—I think we managed to give those awful creatures the slip. And we seem to have found our way to somewhere a little more promis..." },
            { 738232610, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Don't ask me why, but monsters don't seem to want to approach this particular building. Which makes it the perfect place to take a ..." },
            { 738232611, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well? Feeling better for a little rest? There may be horrors lurking around every corner, but you have to try to block it out and e..." },
            { 738232612, "<iconChapterSumVfx>So it wasn't Sila after all. That matter-changing magic of hers is really rather disconcerting. But her minions aren't to be trifle..." },
            { 738232613, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Look at these people—they're over the moon. To think it wasn't so long ago that they cowered at the very sight of you! You've learn..." },
            { 738232614, "<iconChapterSumVfx>You're badly hurt, Frey. If you don't get help quickly, you'll be in serious trouble. The Break hasn't reached as far as the upper ..." },
            { 738232615, "<iconChapterSumVfx>That was a little too close for comfort... Anyway, now we know what we're looking for—a blue glow and flowers. I still can't quite ..." },
            { 738232616, "<iconChapterSumVfx>It seems we've been tracked down by some of Prav's faithful retainers. They seem quite insistent that you go and talk to her. What ..." },
            { 738232617, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Prav certainly seems to be in very little doubt that you're guilty of Sila's murder. But the final judgment will be left to this \"t..." },
            { 738232618, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Oh. There's more than one leg of this trial, is there? They could have said so. I suppose they can't make it too easy for criminals..." },
            { 738232619, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Two rounds down, and she's still not prepared to declare you innocent, eh? I'm beginning to think she might be enjoying this. I sup..." },
            { 738232620, "<iconChapterSumVfx>You prove your innocence by submitting yourself to that ridiculous ordeal, and she sentences you to death regardless? I think it's ..." },
            { 738232621, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well, we made it back to town in one piece—that's something to be grateful for. Let's go and find the old man, shall we? He already..." },
            { 738232622, "Woke up in this place called...Svargana, I think. All the Tantas are here...I thought they were dead. Sila says it's time I learned the truth. What is..." },
            { 738232623, "So I freed the demon the Tantas sealed away. Shit. What the hell do I do with that? And now I'm here, transported by some weird light into...a kid's r..." },
            { 738232624, "Cinta sent me away to keep me safe. I finally know the truth. I finally know why she... And now I have a choice to make: Do I go back to New York? Or ..." },
            { 738232625, "As soon as I left the archives, there he was... But I am not going to let him tear this place apart. Alright, Frey, you can do this. Cinta's on your s..." },
            { 738232626, "<iconChapterSumVfx>It's not over, you know. This is just the beginning. You're not strong enough to keep me down forever, and you know it. I drove the..." },
            { 738232641, "Go to bed." },
