            { 738232657, "There's a couple of places I want to go check out." },
            { 738232658, "Are there now? Why, if you don't mind me asking?" },
            { 738232659, "Was thinking I might learn something if I put my skills to the test." },
            { 738232664, "Sila next, eh?" },
            { 738232665, "Yeah. Although I'm pretty amazed I beat her the first time..." },
            { 738232666, "Ah, the site of Prav's delightful \"trial.\"" },
            { 738232667, "Yeah. Thought I'd been in some tough courtrooms, but she really raised the bar." },
            { 738232668, "Oh. Isn't this where we found Olas's body?" },
            { 738232669, "Yeah. Oh, and where you stabbed me in the fucking back." },
            { 738232670, "We've been back to all of them now." },
            { 738232671, "Yes, and may I say what an enchanting trip down memory lane it's been." },
            { 738232672, "I'm gonna do this. I'm gonna figure out how to save this place." },
            { 738232673, "And I'll do everything I can to make that happen." },
            { 738232674, "This is one of the places you wanted to visit?" },
            { 738232675, "Yeah. I'm still not good enough at this magic shit to get rid of the Break." },
            { 738232676, "Goodness. Well, I admire your commitment to revisiting the past, but this will not end well, I assure you." },
            { 738232677, "Says the guy who lost. Prepare to get your ass re-handed to you." },
