            { 738233522, "The encroaching Corruption has caused so many of the old ways to be lost." },
            { 738233523, "In days gone by, this would have been the season for our most sacred ceremony of peace and remembrance." },
            { 738233524, "Yet now, few seem to even remember its existence..." },
            { 738233525, "The Rite of Remembrance... It offered such solace in times of loss." },
            { 738233526, "What I would not give to see it now. Such a moving spectacle..." },
            { 738233527, "To see the sacred lanterns rise once more is a blessing beyond words!" },
            { 738233528, "We must ensure that the ceremony never again goes unobserved." },
