            { 738233928, "Olas: Tanta of Wisdom" },
            { 738233929, "A lifelong lover of learning who strove for equal access to education for all.\n\nShe made it her mission to provide every Athian with tools that would ..." },
            { 738233930, "Olevia: Gone Too Soon" },
            { 738233931, "A young girl tragically killed when Sila ordered a raid on Cipal.\n\nIn the aftermath of the attack, Frey was distraught to discover her young friend's ..." },
            { 738233932, "Olevia: A Cause for Kindness" },
            { 738233933, "One of the many heartbreaking casualties of the violence wrought on Cipal.\n\nHaving lost her parents at an early age, Olevia was more aware than anyone..." },
            { 738233934, "Olevia: Fleeting Shadow" },
            { 738233935, "A specter of Frey's departed friend conjured up by Tanta Olas.\n\nThe phantom's plaintive pleas gave Frey serious pause for thought, and although she wa..." },
            { 738233936, "Olevia's Cat" },
            { 738233937, "A cat that was once very close to Olevia.\n\nEven Frey has no luck approaching this wary feline, which flees whenever anyone draws near. Olevia was the ..." },
            { 738233938, "Olevia's Cat: New Best Friends" },
            { 738233939, "A cat that until recently only ever allowed Olevia to come near it.\n\nLittle by little, Frey's efforts won it over, and it now appears to understand th..." },
            { 738233940, "Pilo: Lord of the Dance" },
            { 738233941, "The irrepressible carpenter's apprentice couldn't have been happier to hear that Frey had defeated Sila.\n\nAnd he wasn't the only one buoyed by the new..." },
            { 738233942, "Pilo: Man of the People" },
            { 738233943, "An eager carpenter in the making whose enthusiasm still slightly outweighs his skill.\n\nInspired by Frey's speech in the archives, Pilo decided to do w..." },
            { 738233944, "Finished saying goodbye to your little friends, Frey?" },
            { 738233945, "The fragments protect the vulnerability at its center!" },
            { 738233946, "Disperse them and strike at its heart!" },
            { 738233947, "Cinta will help you! Fight as one!" },
            { 738233948, "On it." },
            { 738233949, "I will annihilate you both!" },
            { 738233950, "Susurrus" },
            { 738233951, "A contraption created by Tanta Olas to project her illusions onto the world. Since the Break arose, it has been imbued with the memories of Breakbeast..." },
            { 738233952, "A contraption created by Tanta Olas to project her illusions onto the world. Since the Break arose, it has been imbued with the memories of Breakbeast..." },
            { 738233953, "An Errant Soldier brought into being by a phantom lantern. It's indistinguishable from its real-world counterpart in both appearance and actions, but ..." },
            { 738233954, "A Recreant Knight brought into being by a phantom lantern. It's indistinguishable from its real-world counterpart in both appearance and actions, but ..." },
            { 738233955, "An Unjust Enforcer brought into being by a phantom lantern. It's indistinguishable from its real-world counterpart in both appearance and actions, but..." },
