            { 738233979, "5/18/3874: Liberation" },
            { 738233980, "\"Proclamation Upon the Expulsion of the Rheddig from the Lands of Athia\n\nOn the eighteenth day of the fourth month of the year 3874, our beloved Tanta..." },
            { 738233981, "Tales of the Tantas: The Wellspring" },
            { 738233982, "\"Long, long ago, the Tantas created the land of Athia. As Athia's population grew, the Tantas created realms, and castles, and all manner of other won..." },
            { 738234055, "Eleph: Rage and Resentment" },
            { 738234056, "A brokenhearted boy who lost his father—and his happiness—to the Break.\n\nWhen the Corruption encroached upon Cipal, many of its citizens were transfor..." },
            { 738234072, "Huh? This isn't the right way." },
            { 738234073, "Damn. Must have taken a wrong turn." },
            { 738234074, "Think I better turn back." },
            { 738234075, "Huh. Thought I was going the right way..." },
            { 738234076, "Shit! Wrong way!" },
            { 738234077, "No, no, no! Not this way!" },
            { 738234078, "Can't go this way!" },
            { 738234079, "You won't be getting through here." },
            { 738234080, "Dammit! Better turn back." },
            { 738234081, "There's no way through." },
            { 738234082, "Better go back!" },
            { 738234083, "Looks like a dead end." },
            { 738234084, "No choice but to head back, I fear." },
            { 738234085, "You know this is the wrong way?" },
            { 738234086, "Yeah, yeah. I'm turning back already..." },
            { 738234087, "Where exactly are you going?" },
            { 738234088, "Uh... Can't a girl take a little detour?" },
            { 738234089, "Interesting choice of route, I must say..." },
            { 738234090, "Damn. Think we better turn back." },
            { 738234091, "Uhh... Is this the right way?" },
            { 738234092, "...Quick course correction, perhaps?" },
            { 738234093, "Must have taken a wrong turn somewhere..." },
            { 738234094, "There's no shame in retracing your steps, you know." },
            { 738234095, "You, uh...about ready to head back?" },
            { 738234096, "I think it might be wise, yes." },
            { 738234097, "I think you might want to turn around." },
            { 738234098, "I think you might enjoy stating the obvious." },
            { 738234099, "Something tells me a U-turn might be in order." },
            { 738234100, "You read my mind." },
            { 738234101, "Not thinking of heading back at all?" },
            { 738234102, "...Maybe a little." },
            { 738234103, "This is the way, right?" },
            { 738234104, "Umm...no." },
            { 738234105, "Think I better—" },
            { 738234106, "Turn around? Yes. I think you better had." },
            { 738234107, "Wait—am I...?" },
            { 738234108, "Going completely the wrong way? Unfortunately, yes." },
            { 738234109, "You do know there's no one to fight in that direction, don't you?" },
            { 738234110, "Fine. Let's head back." },
            { 738234111, "And where exactly do you think you're going?" },
            { 738234112, "Ugh. I just got turned around, alright?" },
            { 738234113, "We headed the right way?" },
            { 738234114, "In a word, no." },
            { 738234115, "Is this really the time to be running away?" },
            { 738234116, "Fine!" },
            { 738234117, "Frey!" },
            { 738234118, "About to nag me to turn around? Don't bother." },
            { 738234119, "Fuck. Can't go this way." },
            { 738234120, "Indeed not. Back to it, now!" },
            { 738234121, "Wrong way." },
            { 738234122, "Shit. Better turn back." },
            { 738234123, "You do know we're heading in entirely the wrong direction?" },
            { 738234124, "Fuuuuck. Alright, back we go." },
            { 738234125, "Uhh... Pick another route, maybe?" },
            { 738234126, "I think that might be wise, yes." },
            { 738234127, "I'm not sure you could have chosen a less correct direction to head in, you know." },
            { 738234128, "Hey, cut me some slack! Turning back..." },
            { 738234129, "Are you trying to run away or something?" },
            { 738234130, "Uhh...no." },
            { 738234131, "So yeah... So this is not where I am supposed to be." },
            { 738234132, "You know full well it isn't. Come on, back to it." },
            { 738234133, "Feeling good?" },
            { 738234134, "Better than good! I feel unstoppable!" },
            { 738234135, "I'd strike while the iron was hot if I were you." },
            { 738234136, "Don't have to tell me twice!" },
            { 738234137, "I'd say we're at the height of our powers right now." },
            { 738234138, "Then we'd better get to kicking some ass!" },
            { 738234139, "Oh yeah. I'm in the zone!" },
            { 738234140, "Best get to work then, eh?" },
            { 738234141, "It'll take something with a real sting in it to hurt you now." },
            { 738234142, "If it's all the same to you, I'd rather not take my chances." },
            { 738234143, "Concentrate on attacking—I've got the defense side of things covered." },
            { 738234144, "Don't mind if I do!" },
            { 738234145, "If you're feeling like throwing caution to the wind, I'd say now's the time." },
            { 738234146, "Happy to oblige!" },
            { 738234147, "Fuck yeah! I feel invincible!" },
            { 738234148, "Go ahead and let off some steam! I've got you covered!" },
            { 738234149, "Something's draining our power..." },
            { 738234150, "Dammit!" },
            { 738234151, "You seem less chirpy all of a sudden." },
            { 738234152, "Feel like the strength's gone right outta me..." },
            { 738234153, "Are you sure you're feeling fighting fit?" },
            { 738234154, "What does it matter? Still gotta do this, right?" },
            { 738234155, "Shit! I'm not hitting anywhere near as hard as I should!" },
            { 738234156, "Your strength's been sapped, I'm afraid..." },
            { 738234157, "I...may not be able to protect you as well as I usually do." },
            { 738234158, "Great. That's all I need." },
            { 738234159, "You might want to try and avoid getting hit for a little while..." },
            { 738234160, "Oh, might I?" },
            { 738234161, "Maybe don't go charging in for the minute, hm?" },
            { 738234162, "Sure. Thanks for the heads-up." },
            { 738234163, "Can't afford to get hit." },
            { 738234164, "You really can't. Stay on your toes." },
            { 738234165, "Does that make things a little easier?" },
            { 738234166, "More than a little." },
            { 738234167, "How are you feeling?" },
            { 738234168, "A whole lot better than I did a minute ago." },
            { 738234169, "Now that's what I call a pick-me-up." },
            { 738234170, "Glad you're feeling on top of your game." },
            { 738234171, "Phew. Feels like I can breathe easy all of a sudden." },
            { 738234172, "I'm very happy for you." },
            { 738234173, "Very nicely done." },
            { 738234174, "Alright, what's our next move?" },
            { 738234175, "I'd say now's the time to strike." },
            { 738234176, "No shit." },
            { 738234177, "That went well." },
            { 738234178, "You bet it did. That asshole's going nowhere!" },
            { 738234179, "Gotcha!" },
            { 738234180, "The advantage is ours!" },
            { 738234181, "I doubt many attacks will be getting through this." },
            { 738234182, "Then we better let it rip!" },
            { 738234183, "Hmm, yes. Very solidly constructed. I approve." },
            { 738234184, "Nothing's gonna touch me now!" },
            { 738234185, "The perfect defense." },
            { 738234186, "Yup. Let's kick some ass." },
            { 738234187, "Not bad, huh?" },
            { 738234188, "Certainly looks like it'll keep the attacks at bay." },
            { 738234189, "I am fucking invincible!" },
            { 738234190, "How hubristic of you to say so." },
            { 738234191, "How do you feel?" },
            { 738234192, "Like everything's crystal clear. It's fucking awesome!" },
            { 738234193, "You seem very focused all of a sudden." },
            { 738234194, "Yeah. Feeling super sharp." },
            { 738234195, "I am in a one-hit kill kinda mood." },
            { 738234196, "Well, feel free to demonstrate." },
            { 738234197, "Alright, time for some surgical striking." },
            { 738234198, "This should be good..." },
            { 738234199, "That ought to help you stay healthy." },
            { 738234200, "Yeah. For a while, at least." },
            { 738234201, "Well, that's certainly an intriguing power..." },
            { 738234202, "Yeah. Should help us get around a little easier." },
            { 738234203, "How do you feel?" },
            { 738234204, "Kinda...less stressed than usual. Which is nice." },
            { 738234205, "Huh. I feel lighter on my feet somehow." },
            { 738234206, "The magic's protecting you. Make the most of it." },
            { 738234207, "Look at that—your wounds are healing." },
            { 738234208, "Yeah. Pretty handy, huh?" },
            { 738234209, "Blessed by magical healing powers." },
            { 738234210, "Gotta say, it feels pretty damn good." },
            { 738234211, "I can literally see my wounds healing..." },
            { 738234212, "Behold the power of restorative magic." },
            { 738234213, "Hoo... Feel all...fuzzy..." },
            { 738234214, "How charmingly imprecise." },
            { 738234215, "Try a little evasive action. If it goes well—" },
            { 738234216, "I'll be able to kick ass even harder, right?" },
            { 738234217, "Duck, dodge and dive, Frey! Duck, dodge and dive!" },
            { 738234218, "...Huh. Feel like I know that from somewhere." },
            { 738234219, "This could really help us turn the tables, Frey!" },
            { 738234220, "Better get my dodge on." },
            { 738234221, "Nice. Now's our chance!" },
            { 738234222, "Yes. You'll need to evade a blow or two to get things moving." },
            { 738234223, "Well, this is interesting..." },
            { 738234224, "Kinda weird, huh?" },
            { 738234225, "Hmm... So we can tiptoe past without being spotted..." },
            { 738234226, "Or...sneak right up and strike." },
            { 738234227, "Hah! Can't touch what you can't see, assholes!" },
            { 738234228, "Wonderful. Go ahead and tempt fate, why don't you?" },
            { 738234229, "Whoa! I'm...see-through!" },
            { 738234230, "I think we both are. How intriguing..." },
            { 738234231, "Can you wriggle free?" },
            { 738234232, "No! I'm fucking stuck!" },
            { 738234233, "Are you able to move at all?" },
            { 738234234, "What do you think!?" },
            { 738234235, "What the hell is this shit!?" },
            { 738234236, "Oh dear..." },
            { 738234237, "Let. Me. GO!" },
            { 738234238, "Look out, Frey!" },
            { 738234239, "Frey? Frey! What's wrong!?" },
            { 738234240, "Can't...move..." },
            { 738234241, "Quickly! Move!" },
            { 738234242, "Would if I...could..." },
            { 738234243, "Can't fucking...move..." },
            { 738234244, "Stay with me! It'll be over soon enough!" },
            { 738234245, "What...the fuck...?" },
            { 738234246, "It'll only last a moment! Just tough it out!" },
            { 738234247, "Do not waste any energy, I'm warning you." },
            { 738234248, "Not something I try to make a habit of..." },
            { 738234249, "Well, this is bad." },
            { 738234250, "Fuck, fuck, fuck, fuck, fuck..." },
            { 738234251, "Umm... Are you alright?" },
            { 738234252, "Do I LOOK alright!?" },
            { 738234253, "Something's draining my powers..." },
            { 738234254, "I'd avoid wasting any spells for the moment if I were you." },
            { 738234255, "Frey! What's the matter?" },
            { 738234256, "Can't fucking...see straight..." },
            { 738234257, "Watch where you're going!" },
            { 738234258, "I would if I could!" },
            { 738234259, "My eyes..." },
            { 738234260, "Please tell me you're alright." },
            { 738234261, "Shit! Can't see a fucking thing!" },
            { 738234262, "Just breathe! It'll be over soon enough!" },
