            { 738234862, "Follow Cinta." },
            { 738234864, "Help those in need (3 remaining)." },
            { 738234865, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Not our first time in the upper city, of course, but a rather sobering reminder of its advantages over Lower Cipal, nonetheless. Oh..." },
            { 738234866, "<iconChapterSumVfx>This must be it—dear, sweet Johedy's former workplace. It's certainly seen better days. Is that just age, or has the place been ran..." },
            { 738234867, "<iconChapterSumVfx>That's that lot out front dealt with. Time to search the castle itself. You couldn't hurry up and find a clue or something, could y..." },
            { 738234868, "<iconChapterSumVfx>That...can't have been Cinta, can it? Well, whoever she was, she seemed fairly keen for you to follow. Goodness only knows where sh..." },
            { 738234876, "Can't say I envy these people. Their rulers did some super fucked-up shit." },
            { 738234877, "I doubt many of them would disagree." },
            { 738234878, "Wait. It was the Tantas who caused the Break? What the hell happened to them?" },
            { 738234879, "I think more than a few of their former subjects came to wonder the same thing." },
            { 738234880, "No?" },
            { 738234881, "Whoa. Look at this..." },
            { 738234882, "Looks to me like it might have something to do with Sila..." },
            { 738234883, "Indeed it does..." },
            { 738234884, "Didn't we see a similar one in Sila's castle...?" },
            { 738234885, "Are they hunting deer?" },
            { 738234886, "Judging by the numbers, I'd say they were the ones being hunted." },
            { 738234887, "Are they calling for backup!?" },
            { 738234888, "I think you'd better shut them up, don't you" },
            { 738234891, "Must be a picture of Sila from a while back." },
            { 738234892, "Good to see she hit upon the air of simmering menace nice and early in her career." },
            { 738234893, "I don't like look of this thing." },
            { 738234894, "Yes. It does have a certain sinister air, doesn't it?" },
            { 738234901, "You went and fought Tanta Prav for us. What more could we have asked?" },
            { 738234902, "It's awful what happened to Robian. But it's not your fault." },
            { 738234903, "Thanks, Pilo." },
            { 738234904, "You did everything you could! You've done nothing wrong." },
            { 738234905, "Looks like I could have chilled in a place like this." },
            { 738234906, "Sadly, those days are long since gone." },
