            { 738235012, "<buttonMenu>: Open the MAGIC Menu" },
            { 738235013, "You can spend mana here to learn new spells. Mana is gained by leveling up, and can also occasionally be found out in the field." },
            { 738235014, "Let's add a new spell to your skill set.\nHold down <buttonEnter> to learn it." },
