            { 738235799, "If you manage to break your enemy's composure, they'll often open themselves up to a brutally damaging attack that will exploit Cuff's capabilities to..." },
            { 738235800, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235801, "Healing Draughts and Health" },
            { 738235802, "Frey can drink healing draughts in order to restore her health.\n\nIf her health drops to zero, it's game over, so if in doubt, use one.\n\nYou can do so ..." },
            { 738235803, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235804, "Gathering Resources" },
            { 738235805, "Athia is full of useful resources such as ore and medicinal plants. You just have to know where to look.\n\nThey'll prove extremely useful on your upcom..." },
            { 738235806, "BATTLE TUTORIAL" },
            { 738235807, "Cuff's Protective Powers" },
            { 738235808, "Cuff is able to protect you from enemy attacks, reducing the damage dealt.\n\nYou won't need to do anything to make him block, but you will need to keep..." },
            { 738235809, "BATTLE TUTORIAL" },
            { 738235810, "Last-Chance Block" },
            { 738235811, "If Frey receives a blow heavy enough to reduce her health to zero, Cuff will become unable to protect her for a short while, putting her in a very dan..." },
            { 738235812, "GAME SYSTEMS" },
            { 738235813, "Swimming" },
            { 738235814, "If Frey finds herself in deep water, be it a river or a lake, she'll be able to swim to shore." },
            { 738235815, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235816, "Founts of Blessing" },
            { 738235817, "Sacred spots where it is said that dormant magical abilities can be awakened.\n\n\nYou may even be able to learn a new spell or two." },
            { 738235818, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235819, "Points of Interest and Rewards" },
            { 738235820, "There are spots all over Athia where you can earn rewards that can help develop Frey's skills further.\n\nYou'll need to meet the conditions laid out at..." },
            { 738235821, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235822, "Locked Chests" },
            { 738235823, "Sealed chests may well contain highly valuable items.\n\nLuckily, all you have to do to unlock them is defeat any nearby enemies." },
            { 738235832, "BATTLE TUTORIAL" },
            { 738235833, "Piercing Attacks" },
            { 738235834, "Certain powerful attacks can pierce right through Cuff's defenses, dealing a lot of damage if Frey doesn't evade them in time.\n\nIf you see the telltal..." },
            { 738235835, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235836, "Monuments" },
            { 738235837, "Monuments are sacred stones in which the Tantas once stored a portion of their power.\n\nThese landmarks are now tainted by the Break, but freeing them ..." },
