            { 738235845, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738235846, "Select an objective to set it as your destination." },
            { 738235848, "<iconChapterSumVfx>And here I was thinking that one dragon encounter was more than enough for a lifetime. Well, this is an opponent you can't hope to ..." },
            { 738235850, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well, that was utterly hair-raising. But on the plus side, it's over—for now, at least. And you've learned to do as you're told. Ex..." },
            { 738235851, "<iconChapterSumVfx>We haven't hurt the blasted thing at all! This is bordering on unsportsmanlike. And its temper doesn't seem to be improving, either..." },
            { 738235852, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Phew. Well, it was close, but we got out in one piece, at least. Where would you be without me and my lifesaving advice, eh? Don't ..." },
            { 738235853, "ふー……ふー……" },
            { 738235854, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738235855, "Stinky butts!" },
            { 738235856, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235857, "Continue on your way, and take out any enemies." },
            { 738235858, "Careful—this world is full of monsters who won't hesitate to attack you. If they come for you, you'll need to be ready to fight back." },
            { 738235859, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235860, "Explore the Abandoned Village" },
            { 738235861, "Investigate the three quest objectives. You might find something that will help you figure out how to proceed." },
            { 738235862, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235863, "Escape from the pack of bears." },
            { 738235864, "A pack of bears has appeared. You'll need to use magic parkour to escape them.\n\n<buttonParkour>: Use Magic Parkour\n\nCareful—if you're too slow or you ..." },
            { 738235865, "<buttonMenu>: Open the Journal" },
            { 738235866, "MISC." },
            { 738235867, "Attack Magic: Burst Shot Lv. 1" },
            { 738235868, "Fires forth lumps of rock that explode once they've traveled a little way, dealing area damage." },
            { 738235869, "MISC." },
            { 738235870, "Attack Magic: Shield Shot Lv.1" },
            { 738235871, "Creates a defensive shield while charging, which is blasted forward in pieces when released." },
            { 738235872, "MISC." },
            { 738235873, "Attack Magic: Scatter Shot Lv.1" },
            { 738235874, "Fires a steady stream of rocks while charging, then unleashes a high-impact, long-range projectile when released." },
            { 738235875, "MISC." },
            { 738235876, "Support Magic: Disperse" },
            { 738235877, "Causes flowers to spring up in a spot of your choosing that pick up nearby rocks and fling them at enemies." },
            { 738235878, "MISC." },
            { 738235879, "Support Magic: Screen" },
            { 738235880, "Surrounds you with stones that improve your defenses. Useful when fighting stronger enemies." },
            { 738235881, "MISC." },
            { 738235882, "Break Magic: Genesis Lv. 1" },
            { 738235883, "Summons barbed branches which are fired out in front of you, skewering enemies over a wide area." },
            { 738235884, "<buttonMenu>: Open the Resources Menu" },
            { 738235885, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235886, "Fall Damage" },
            { 738235887, "If Frey falls from too high up when she's out of stamina, she can take serious damage.\n\nEven a little stamina will allow her to avoid this by using ma..." },
            { 738235888, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235889, "Setting Up Camp" },
            { 738235890, "If you find some suitable firewood, you can use it to set up camp, allowing you to rest up, restore health, and craft items to help you on your advent..." },
            { 738235891, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235892, "Detours" },
            { 738235893, "The citizens of Cipal don't just offer interesting side events, they also have other tasks to offer, some of which can be very rewarding.\n\nJust walk u..." },
            { 738235894, "BATTLE TUTORIAL" },
            { 738235895, "Status Ailments" },
            { 738235896, "Certain enemy attacks can inflict status ailments such as poisoning or stamina draining.\n\nThese can make battle extremely difficult, so try to avoid t..." },
            { 738235897, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235898, "Flashbacks" },
            { 738235899, "Certain monuments will allow you to take on challenges that will earn you mana and other rewards if you can complete them.\n\nYou can attempt them as ma..." },
            { 738235900, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235901, "Extermination" },
            { 738235902, "Defeat as many enemies as you can within the time limit.\n\nBeating consecutive foes without taking damage will earn you a bonus." },
            { 738235903, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235904, "Deliverance" },
            { 738235905, "Protect the citizens from the attacking monsters. If they all die, you'll fail the challenge.\n\nThe more citizens you save, the higher your score will ..." },
            { 738235906, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235907, "Sprint" },
            { 738235908, "Reach the destination within the time limit.\n\nThe quicker you get there, the higher your score will be, but be aware that any enemies encountered on t..." },
            { 738235909, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738235910, "Takedown" },
            { 738235911, "Take down the specified target within the time limit. You won't start out right next to them, so you'll need to find them fast and take them down as q..." },
            { 738235912, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235913, "The Depths of Corruption" },
            { 738235914, "These are the places where the Break is most highly concentrated, and consequently, the deadliest. This means tougher enemies and a tougher challenge ..." },
            { 738235916, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738235917, "Giant Nightmares" },
            { 738235918, "Certain Nightmares are even more terrifying than their standard counterparts thanks to their prodigious size. Frey won't have a hope of defeating them..." },
            { 738235919, "Hold <buttonCuffCompas>: Use Cuff Compass" },
