            { 738235967, "Shit!" },
            { 738235968, "It might be wiser to run this time." },
            { 738235969, "That was close... Where the hell are we now?" },
            { 738235970, "The big city, I suppose?" },
            { 738235971, "Still no sign of any people..." },
            { 738235972, "Well, let's keep looking. You should probably keep an eye out for somewhere to rest, too." },
