            { 738236466, "And neither am I." },
            { 738236493, "What are they doing?" },
            { 738236494, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Goodness. That's quite a display she's putting on. She won't be holding anything back now. Which means you'll need to show her you'..." },
            { 738236495, "I'd imagine it belonged to one of Cinta's most trusted attendants." },
