            { 738236893, "Variable Rate Shading (VRS)" },
            { 738236894, "Enabling this can help boost frame rate without adversely affecting image quality." },
            { 738236895, "Well, painstakingly wrought artistic renderings can be deceiving." },
            { 738236896, "<iconChapterSumVfx>I know you're a little conflicted about what you did to Sila, but you really had no choice. She would never have stopped. And you w..." },
