            { 738237279, "<iconChapterSumVfx>It's some sort of phantasmal representation of one of Sila's minions. But its shield looks real enough. See if you can find a way o..." },
            { 738237280, "<iconChapterSumVfx>It's a false—no, a phantasmal—version of one of Sila's more elite minions. You wouldn't think it moved so fast to look at it, but t..." },
            { 738237281, "<iconChapterSumVfx>It's a phantasmal version of one of Prav's minions. It's light on its feet and quick with its bow—a deadly combination. I think tra..." },
            { 738237282, "<iconChapterSumVfx>I think even Prav would raise an eyebrow at this little illusion. It changes tack according to the tide of battle, but it has a tel..." },
            { 738237283, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Phantasmal wolves, eh? Whatever will they think of next? Well, doesn't look too different from the real thing—its only real advanta..." },
            { 738237284, "<iconChapterSumVfx>I mean, it's only a wild dog at the end of the day—and not even a real one, at that—but you still wouldn't want to run into a pack ..." },
            { 738237285, "<iconChapterSumVfx>It may be an illusion, but by golly, it's an impressive one. That tail must be as hard as tempered steel. I'd keep a respectful dis..." },
            { 738237286, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Oh, you love these things, don't you? Cats, was it? Are you as fond of the illusory ones? I'd be respectful of it, at the very leas..." },
            { 738237287, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Don't look now, but I think we've found someone with an even shorter fuse than your good self. It's constantly on the lookout for o..." },
            { 738237288, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well, that's certainly the most noble phantasm I've seen all week. You need to try and finish it off before it can get really angry..." },
            { 738237289, "<iconChapterSumVfx>This particular phantasmal beast is more of your hunted than your hunter. Just look at those antlers—they must weigh a ton. Couple ..." },
            { 738237290, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Phantasmal or not, that muscle definition really is quite something. If it jumps into the air, it'll come back down with a bang. If..." },
            { 738237291, "<iconChapterSumVfx>And the winner of the \"illusion with the most enormous antlers\" award is... Sorry. Trite, I know. I wouldn't stand directly in fron..." },
            { 738237292, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Don't lull yourself into thinking you've got nothing to worry about with an illusory grass-chewer like this one. Get it good and an..." },
            { 738237293, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Illusion plus mutation equals...this, I suppose. Steer clear of those horns. And if you're looking to counterattack, do it carefull..." },
            { 738237294, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Can you feel that? Those horns are literally pouring out Break. Any missteps when you counter this one, and you'll be in trouble. T..." },
            { 738237295, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Just because it's an illusion doesn't mean you can't be good and frightened of it. I'm not sure I've got it in me to block anything..." },
            { 738237296, "<iconChapterSumVfx>\"Big, phantasmal, and extremely annoying\" would be my assessment. Run in swinging, and you'll be eating paw before you know it. Oh,..." },
            { 738237297, "<iconChapterSumVfx>I'm not sure an illusion can give off much more concentrated waves of Corruption than that. Try not to get in front of it, especial..." },
            { 738237298, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Surely not even you think this phantasmal pest is adorable? Would you call those...gutmouths? Whatever they are, they're disgusting..." },
            { 738237299, "<iconChapterSumVfx>An illusion of a creature built like one giant mouth. You wouldn't want that crashing down on you from above... But if you can gain..." },
            { 738237300, "<iconChapterSumVfx>You know, I'm strangely intrigued by this one. Very...refined for a fang-laden death illusion, wouldn't you say? And what fangs—the..." },
            { 738237301, "<iconChapterSumVfx>There's nothing illusory about the thickness of this one's skin. Don't pick away at it from a distance—get up close and lay it on t..." },
            { 738237302, "<iconChapterSumVfx>The phantasmal version is no less hyper-vigilant than its real-world counterpart, it seems. If you're going in close, keep your eye..." },
            { 738237303, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Am I the only one who thinks this one looks like a giant phantasmal fish? There's no beating it in the water, so I wouldn't even bo..." },
            { 738237304, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Unsurprisingly, the illusory version is no less creepy, or indeed crawly, than its corporeal counterpart. And its claws and fangs a..." },
            { 738237305, "<iconChapterSumVfx>So it even has illusory poison? I hadn't stopped to think about it, but...how exactly does that work? Well, regardless, it does. Do..." },
            { 738237306, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Hyper-evolved and entirely illusory... Fascinating. It can create highly inconvenient clouds of toxic filth, so I'd recommend riddi..." },
            { 738237307, "<iconChapterSumVfx>These phantasmal birds really shouldn't give you much bother, so don't waste your time picking them off one by one. A good blast of..." },
            { 738237308, "<iconChapterSumVfx>I mean, I know they're all mindless illusions, but this one seems somehow...more mindless, don't you think? Wait it for it to rush ..." },
            { 738237309, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Even the illusory ones are awful show-offs, it seems. White feathers, indeed... Looks to be some sort of scout. Get rid of it befor..." },
            { 738237310, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Do you think the phantasmal ones eat carrion, too? I don't suppose they need to. Their stomach acid is no less ferocious for being...." },
            { 738237311, "<iconChapterSumVfx>They're a pain when they're in the air, but even the illusory ones get tired. Wait for it to pop down for a rest, then unleash merr..." },
            { 738237312, "<iconChapterSumVfx>An extremely convincing and rather intimidating illusion made all the more imposing by a healthy dose of the Break. Its gastric jui..." },
            { 738237313, "<iconChapterSumVfx>An illusion of a human lost to the Break. Somehow that's...even more depressing, isn't it? Still, no room for pity here—put it out ..." },
            { 738237314, "<iconChapterSumVfx>An illusion of a former human. Not only is it a rather tough customer, it's also able to heal itself. You might find poisoning it a..." },
            { 738237315, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Forget its phantasmal nature, this one's as formidable as they come. Gird your loins if you're really planning on doing this, becau..." },
            { 738237316, "<iconChapterSumVfx>My goodness. It's quite the snappy mover, isn't it? Awful breath, though. Just awful. Stop it moving, then get in close and hammer ..." },
            { 738237317, "<iconChapterSumVfx>There's nothing illusory about this one's somewhat spiky personality. However, you may be surprised to learn that the up-close appr..." },
            { 738237318, "<iconChapterSumVfx>A crafty illusion. That's...not something you see every day. It's going to try to get behind you, so keep your distance and pepper ..." },
            { 738237319, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Small for a phantasm, but not to be underestimated. A well-organized gang of these blighters will soon overwhelm you. They'll try t..." },
            { 738237320, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Phantasmal wings are still wings, you know. And they'll keep this one out of reach just as handily. Irksome stuff. Oh, and whatever..." },
            { 738237321, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Quite possibly not the time, but those wings really are magnificent, aren't they? Anyway, this one's phantasmal nature makes its mo..." },
            { 738237322, "<iconChapterSumVfx>What an odd way of moving—very unsettling, even for an illusion. The Break really does some awful things, doesn't it? Keep your eye..." },
            { 738237323, "<iconChapterSumVfx>I don't know what's more warped—this thing's head, or the mind behind it. It's easy enough to follow on the ground, but once it's u..." },
            { 738237324, "<iconChapterSumVfx>It's a sort of illusory outline of a creature, isn't it? But don't think that renders it defenseless—it hits very hard indeed. One ..." },
            { 738237325, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Hmm... Quite the ominous look, eh? And a phantasm to boot. Gosh. I'd recommend not taking your eyes off it for even a moment. And i..." },
            { 738237326, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Calling this sort of...blob of illusion a bird seems rather generous, doesn't it? Well, whatever it is, I'd say it's building up to..." },
            { 738237327, "<iconChapterSumVfx>An illusion of a monstrosity that may have once appeared human, though any resemblance to the living is hard to discern in its curr..." },
