            { 738237512, "<iconChapterSumVfx>So that's her little bargain, eh? If we want to know more about the torana, we need to bring back these red books? Assuming that re..." },
            { 738237513, "<iconChapterSumVfx>The peasant girl is alive, it seems. And the old loon has Sila distracted. I'd say now's our chance to sneak up and liberate the po..." },
            { 738237514, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Look...I know you're upset about the little girl. And it's entirely understandable. You two shared a bond. I just want you to know ..." },
            { 738237515, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well, we made it to the fortress. But so did our friend the dragon. I really do wonder what we did to upset it so much... Still, Si..." },
            { 738237516, "<iconChapterSumVfx>So, ballow resin's the order of the day, is it? Suppose we've got to try and save the old loon somehow. And our friend the councilm..." },
            { 738237517, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Seems these lantern contraptions amplify Olas's powers of illusion. In which case, we'll just have to smash them all to pieces. If ..." },
            { 738237518, "I am Frey, daughter of Cinta, heir to the power of the Tantas. And the future of Athia is in my hands. Bring it on, Cuff—it's time to end this." },
