            { 738237779, "If I get caught one more time, my life is over. Which is why I gotta get the hell out of town. Homer's waiting for me at home—need to get back there." },
            { 738237781, "I was in New York a minute ago, but now I'm...here—wherever \"here\" is. What the hell was the deal with that bracelet?" },
            { 738237783, "Fuck. How does this keep happening to me? Okay, think. I need to break out of here. Nothing good is going to happen if I just sit on my ass." },
            { 738237784, "Didn't mind the threads Auden gave me, but there was no way I was giving up my kicks. Anyway, got me some journals to find if I want to get home to Ne..." },
            { 738237785, "I promise you, Olevia: Tanta or no, Sila's going down hard. I've just got to learn how to find her." },
            { 738237786, "Looks like Sila's castle's pretty far from Cipal. There'll be a shit-ton of monsters out there, so I'd better make sure I'm good and ready." },
            { 738237787, "That Breakstorm was batshit insane. Never fucking again. But forget that—need to get my act together. Sila's castle can't be far..." },
            { 738237788, "I still hate Sila for what she did...so why do I feel so shitty about kicking her ass? But now isn't the time. I should get back to Cipal." },
            { 738237789, "I thought beating Sila would help—why the fuck is the Break in the city!? I'd better see if anyone needs me..." },
            { 738237790, "Man, my head... At least things have calmed down. Better go find Bob and figure out how to get back to New York before some other disaster happens." },
            { 738237791, "Bob needs ballow resin to get better. There's none left in the city, so it's Avoalet or bust..." },
            { 738237792, "Great. Handcuffs again. Something tells me Prav's not my biggest fan. Well, I'll just tell her to stop attacking the city, and she should let me get b..." },
            { 738237793, "Can't stop thinking about what Prav said... I can't be that woman's daughter...can I? Ugh, screw this. Gotta head back to Cipal." },
            { 738237794, "First we lose Bob, now I'm fighting with Auden. Fan-fucking-tastic. Well, I know when I'm not wanted. I'm finding me a torana and getting the hell out..." },
            { 738237795, "Huh. Must've had a weird dream last night. Ah, well—Homer's doing good and I've gotta get going. Places to go, people to see..." },
            { 738237796, "Back in Athia at last—never thought I'd be so glad to see the place. That was a dirty trick...and Olas is gonna pay for it." },
            { 738237797, "Svargana... What is this place? And why are the Tantas here? I need to talk to them. I have to learn more about Cuff." },
            { 738237798, "Sorry, Homer. But I have to stay. I have to save everyone...before it's too late." },
            { 738237799, "Time to settle this once and for all. Could be my last chance to speak with everyone—better say goodbye..." },
            { 738237800, "This isn't over—it's just the beginning. I'll find a way to stop the Break...no matter what it takes." },
            { 738237801, "A guy named Pilo wants to show me around town. Might as well take a look, I guess..." },
            { 738237802, "Sounds like Bob's lost something important. Something to do with the torana, maybe? Better see what I can do..." },
            { 738237803, "Auden's worked herself way too hard... Well, she's done a ton for me, so it's about time I repaid the favor." },
            { 738237804, "Johedy said she'd make me something from that metal I found—I've just gotta get her tools first." },
            { 738237805, "Pilo wants to give me another tour. Guess I haven't had much time to kill lately... Might even be fun to tag along." },
            { 738237806, "Johedy said she's been trying to find out more about my mom. Better go see what she's managed to dig up..." },
            { 738237807, "If I'm going to get rid of the Break once and for all, I'll need to be on top of my game. We're putting in some serious training...whether Cuff likes ..." },
