            { 738238362, "Frey can now open portals through which she can move from one place to another. While moving in this way, she will be immune to all damage.\n\nUse <butt..." },
            { 738238364, "Restrain Tanta Sila." },
            { 738238371, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738238372, "Ramparts" },
            { 738238373, "The Tantas' castles are protected by ramparts designed to keep invaders at bay.\nPowerful foes lurk within these walls, and you won't be able to escape..." },
            { 738238374, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738238375, "Highly Corrupted Areas" },
            { 738238376, "The Break makes some areas extremely dangerous indeed, mainly due to the presence of the frighteningly powerful enemies known as Nightmares.\n\nMake sur..." },
            { 738238377, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738238378, "Flotsam and Jetsam" },
            { 738238379, "Items often collect at the foot of this waterfall, having been washed downstream.\n\nIt's worth stopping by once in a while to see what you can scavenge..." },
            { 738238380, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738238381, "Inter-Enemy Conflict" },
            { 738238382, "When enemies of different kinds meet, they may start fighting among themselves.\n\nAllowing them to wear one another down before jumping in to finish th..." },
            { 738238383, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738238384, "Founts of Blessing and Magic" },
            { 738238385, "In order to gain the magical benefits of a given Fount of Blessing, you'll need to be able to use the magic of the associated type.\nWhen you find a ne..." },
            { 738238386, "Genesis" },
            { 738238387, "Conflagration" },
            { 738238388, "Cataract" },
            { 738238389, "Tempest" },
            { 738238390, "Summons barbed branches which are fired out in front of you, skewering enemies over a wide area." },
            { 738238391, "Calls forth a fiery column that spatters enemies with magma, which remains on the ground for a short while after the attack." },
            { 738238392, "Spins up a watery vortex that sucks in enemies, damaging them as it does so." },
            { 738238393, "Calls up lightning from the earth to electrocute enemies over a wide area." },
            { 738238394, "An everyday cloak worn by citizens of Cipal.\nDoesn't have any extra effects, but it's sturdy and hard-wearing." },
            { 738238395, "A cloak worn by very important individuals.\nInflicting critical hits on foes can restore health to the wearer." },
            { 738238396, "A top-quality cloak made from the finest materials by a master craftsperson.\nShortens the length of negative status effects." },
            { 738238397, "A cloak commissioned by Tanta Sila herself.\nCauses Surge Magic to charge when Cuff blocks." },
            { 738238398, "A cloak once worn by Tanta Sila in battle.\nConverts damage taken when Cuff blocks into stamina." },
            { 738238399, "An uncharacteristically luxurious cloak once worn by Tanta Sila.\nIncreases the damage dealt by spells cast while parkouring, and also reduces fall dam..." },
            { 738238400, "A cloak once beloved of Tanta Prav.\nProtects the wearer from being dazed." },
            { 738238401, "A cloak once worn by Tanta Prav that was made with formal occasions in mind.\nImproves the chance of inflicting critical hits when health is high." },
            { 738238402, "A highly decorative cloak once worn by Tanta Prav.\nImbued with various magical effects." },
            { 738238403, "A cloak once worn by Tanta Olas on her sojourns into the field.\nWhen Cuff blocks while stamina is at maximum, some of the damage received will be take..." },
            { 738238404, "A cloak once worn by Tanta Olas for important ceremonial occasions.\nCauses Surge Magic to charge more quickly when Attack Magic is used while parkouri..." },
            { 738238405, "A cloak once worn by Tanta Olas for feasts and other celebrations.\nImbued with various magical effects." },
            { 738238406, "A cloak once used as everyday casual wear by Tanta Cinta.\nBoosts defense when healing items are used." },
            { 738238407, "A cloak once worn by Tanta Cinta for business outside the castle.\nRestores health when enemies are defeated." },
            { 738238408, "A cloak of Tanta Cinta's that was designed for maximum functionality.\nImbued with various magical effects." },
            { 738238409, "A cloak designed and made by Frey herself.\nImbued with various magical effects." },
            { 738238410, "A necklace once worn by Tanta Sila. Its name means \"hope.\"\nIncreases the effects of Sila's signature red magic." },
            { 738238411, "A necklace once worn by Tanta Sila. Its name means \"heirloom of the warrior maidens.\"\nIncreases the effects of Sila's signature red magic." },
            { 738238412, "A necklace once worn by Tanta Prav. Its name means \"lion.\"\nIncreases the effects of Prav's signature blue magic." },
            { 738238413, "A necklace once worn by Tanta Prav. Its name means \"steely victor.\"\nIncreases the effects of Prav's signature blue magic." },
            { 738238414, "A necklace designed by the gifted mind of Tanta Olas.\nIncreases the effects of Olas's signature green magic." },
            { 738238415, "A necklace once worn by Tanta Olas. Its name means \"treasure of Athia.\"\nIncreases the effects of Olas's signature green magic." },
            { 738238416, "A necklace once worn by Tanta Cinta. Its name means \"flower.\"\nIncreases the effects of Frey's signature purple magic." },
            { 738238417, "An eye-catching necklace once worn by Tanta Cinta. Its name means \"hearty cry.\"\nIncreases the effects of Frey's signature purple magic." },
            { 738238418, "A necklace made by Frey using her crafting skills.\nBoosts all of the wearer's magical abilities." },
            { 738238419, "A necklace made from odvaha ore by the formidable Johedy.\nIncreases the effects of Sila's signature red magic." },
            { 738238420, "A necklace made as a present from Auden to Frey by Johedy.\nIncreases the effects of Frey's signature purple magic." },
            { 738238421, "A nail design thought to bring vigor and good cheer.\nIncreases the rate at which health is restored." },
            { 738238422, "A nail design thought to encourage proactivity.\nIncreases the damage dealt by Support Magic when Surge Magic is fully charged." },
            { 738238423, "A nail design thought to maximize potential.\nIncreases the damage dealt by Attack Magic when Surge Magic is fully charged." },
            { 738238424, "A nail design thought to improve healing abilities.\nIncreases the rate at which health is recovered when it drops below a certain level." },
            { 738238425, "A nail design thought to encourage swiftness.\nShortens the time before Support Magic can be used again." },
            { 738238426, "A nail design thought to summon powers from within.\nIncreases the speed at which Attack Magic can be charged." },
            { 738238427, "A nail design thought to symbolize capitalizing on one's experience.\nIncreases the speed at which Surge Magic charges based on the number of spells le..." },
            { 738238428, "A nail design thought to call on the power of one's ancestors.\nIncreases damage dealt based on the number of spells learned." },
            { 738238429, "A nail design thought to make one stronger.\nIncreases the damage dealt by Attack Magic spells charged beyond a certain level." },
            { 738238430, "A nail design thought to call on the power of darkness.\nOccasionally causes Attack Magic spells charged beyond a certain level to inflict poison." },
            { 738238431, "A nail design thought to symbolize the power of blazing flames.\nOccasionally causes Attack Magic spells charged beyond a certain level to set foes on ..." },
            { 738238432, "A nail design thought to symbolize the decay of living beings.\nLengthens any negative effects Frey inflicts on foes." },
            { 738238433, "A nail design thought to symbolize a proud and powerful woman.\nIncreases damage from Sila spells based on the number of Sila spells learned." },
            { 738238434, "A nail design thought to call on the power of ice.\nOccasionally causes Attack Magic spells charged beyond a certain level to stop enemies where they s..." },
            { 738238435, "A nail design with a certain mysterious connection to Avoalet.\nLengthens the duration of negative effects inflicted on foes with Prav spells." },
            { 738238436, "A nail design made up of various potent symbols and patterns.\nIncreases damage from Prav spells based on the number of Prav spells learned." },
            { 738238437, "A nail design thought to call on untapped reserves of power.\nIncreases the speed at which Surge Magic charges." },
            { 738238438, "A nail design which symbolizes the power of lightning.\nOccasionally causes Attack Magic spells charged beyond a certain level to electrify foes." },
            { 738238439, "A nail design thought to improve mental acuity.\nIncreases damage from Olas spells based on the number of Olas spells learned." },
            { 738238440, "A nail design thought to symbolize the chaos at the heart of a raging inferno.\nLengthens the duration of negative effects inflicted on foes with Sila ..." },
            { 738238441, "A nail design thought to symbolize elegance and grace.\nCauses Killer Blows to emit a shockwave when they land, damaging nearby enemies." },
            { 738238442, "A nail design said to be made up of art styles from all over the world.\nLengthens the duration of negative effects inflicted on foes with Olas spells." },
            { 738238443, "A nail design said to encourage personal development.\nIncreases damage from Frey spells based on the number of Frey spells learned." },
            { 738238444, "A nail design said to symbolize taking one's personal development to the next level.\nEnables another Killer Blow to be performed immediately after suc..." },
            { 738238445, "A nail design said to encourage cool under pressure.\nIncreases damage inflicted based on the number of nearby enemies." },
            { 738238446, "A nail design said to promote well-being.\nIncreases damage dealt when health is higher." },
            { 738238447, "A nail design said to symbolize fruitful cooperation.\nMakes it easier to knock enemies to the ground the more spells Frey has learned." },
            { 738238448, "A nail design said to maximize one's individuality.\nImproves the chance of landing a critical hit." },
            { 738238449, "A nail design said to symbolize the sadness of solitude.\nIncreases damage inflicted the lower Frey's health becomes." },
            { 738238450, "A nail design said to summon forth great power.\nIncreases the chance of landing a critical hit based on the number of spells Frey has learned." },
