            { 738238472, "A simple, bold, and stylish necklace for the true connoisseur.\n\nIts design is unique enough that Frey knows her crafting skills can't improve on it, a..." },
            { 738238473, "A bright, bold, and stylish necklace for the true connoisseur.\n\nIts design is unique enough that Frey knows her crafting skills can't improve on it, a..." },
            { 738238474, "A design made up of mysterious, eye-catching patterns, parts of which glow an otherworldly blue.\n\nThe symbols used clearly aren't anything Tanta-relat..." },
            { 738238475, "A design featuring bold, futuristic line-based designs.\n\nThe patterns clearly aren't anything Tanta-related, but that doesn't prevent them from being ..." },
            { 738238476, "A design whose origins have been lost to time.\n\nThe small dots at the top of each nail symbolize the magical effects that radiate outward from within...." },
            { 738238477, "A design whose origins have been lost to time.\n\nWhile each of the tiny pieces that make up the different patterns on each nail are said to represent w..." },
            { 738238478, "A design whose origins have been lost to time.\n\nThe unique geometrical patterns it's made up of are said to represent the various stages of a tree's d..." },
