            { 738238588, "Earn trophies by progressing through Frey's story." },
            { 738238589, "You can earn a trophy by completing the \"Cipal Reborn\" quest, which can be undertaken by speaking to Pilo from Chapter 13 onward.\n\nApparently, he can ..." },
            { 738238590, "You can earn a trophy by completing the \"Lost Lullabies\" quest, which can be undertaken by speaking to Johedy from Chapter 13 onward.\n\nApparently, she..." },
            { 738238591, "You can earn a trophy by completing the \"Dancing in Cipal: Finale\" challenge.\n\nThe order of the buttons doesn't change, so keep a keen eye open, and y..." },
            { 738238592, "The mausoleum, in the upper city, is where the people of Cipal go to pay their respects to the dead.\n\nCheck in there occasionally as Frey's story prog..." },
            { 738238593, "There's a certain person in Cipal who collects little dolls known as \"poppets.\"\nIf you find any, you can trade them for items and equipment.\n\nThere ar..." },
            { 738238594, "You can make camp when out in the field by holding the down directional button.\nHowever, you'll need some firewood in order to do so." },
            { 738238595, "Try taking on a flashback challenge at one of the Monuments to Wisdom dotted around Athia.\nYou can earn a trophy regardless of the rating you earn—you..." },
            { 738238596, "Try taking on ten flashback challenges at the Monuments to Wisdom dotted around Athia.\nYou can earn a trophy regardless of the rating you earn—you jus..." },
            { 738238597, "Try taking on all the flashback challenges at the Monuments to Wisdom dotted around Athia.\nYou can earn a trophy regardless of the rating you earn—you..." },
            { 738238598, "There are monuments to the Tantas all over Athia.\nThey can be cleared of the Breakshards that cling to them with magic, enabling you to take a closer ..." },
            { 738238599, "Try taking a close look at twenty or more of the monuments to the Tantas located all over Athia.\nAs long as they're Monuments to Love, Strength, or Ju..." },
            { 738238600, "Try taking a closer look at fifty of the monuments to the Tantas located all over Athia.\nAs long as they're Monuments to Love, Strength, or Justice, y..." },
            { 738238601, "There are points of interest all over Athia for you to investigate.\nTry visiting ten of them.\n\nEach of them will have a challenge for you to complete—..." },
            { 738238602, "There are points of interest all over Athia for you to investigate.\nTry visiting fifty of them." },
            { 738238603, "There are points of interest all over Athia for you to investigate.\nTry visiting one hundred of them.\n\nYou may need to use magic parkour, fast travel,..." },
            { 738238604, "If you happen across one of the Founts of Blessing located across Athia, be sure to dive right on in.\nNot only will it improve your magic, you can ear..." },
            { 738238605, "Founts of Blessing can't be located using Cuff Scan.\nYou'll have to rely on the sounds they make, and the way the controller vibrates when they're nea..." },
            { 738238606, "Try unlocking a new spell via the MAGIC menu.\nYou can earn a new trophy, as well as a new ability to experiment with." },
            { 738238607, "Try unlocking all the spells available via the MAGIC menu.\n\nYou'll need mana in order to do so. This can be earned by leveling up, as a reward for per..." },
            { 738238608, "You can craft new items at workbenches, or when you make camp.\nWhy not try making a healing draught or something? You'll get a trophy for your trouble..." },
            { 738238609, "As well as healing draughts, you can also craft a special cloak and necklace.\nYou can earn a trophy if you craft them all.\n\nCollect the necessary ingr..." },
            { 738238610, "See if you can put together a complete collection of cloaks.\n\nYou can earn new ones by progressing through the\nstory, exploring every corner of Athia,..." },
            { 738238611, "See if you can put together a complete collection of nail designs.\n\nYou can learn new ones by progressing through the\nstory, and exploring every corne..." },
            { 738238613, "You can earn a trophy by collecting every available piece of equipment.\n\n(You do not have to obtain certain equipment that can only be earned from sub..." },
            { 738238614, "You can unlock new spells by progressing through the story, by visiting Founts of Blessing, and via the MAGIC menu." },
            { 738238615, "Try using the Shimmy ability five times in a row. It can be learned by visiting Founts of Blessing.\nIf you stop using magic parkour or trigger a diffe..." },
            { 738238616, "You can earn a trophy by performing magic parkour continuously for twenty seconds.\nTo keep going for that long, raise your stamina by progressing thro..." },
            { 738238617, "You can earn a trophy by traveling 100 km (62 mi) in total using magic parkour.\n\nIn order to do so, try to remember to use it no matter what you're do..." },
            { 738238618, "You can earn a trophy by using the Float spell to stay in the air for ten seconds or more.\nAs well as trying to level Frey up enough that her AP incre..." },
            { 738238619, "You can earn a trophy by using magic parkour to jump over a total of ten enemies.\n\nThis shouldn't be too tricky to achieve, as it will happen automati..." },
            { 738238620, "You can earn a trophy by performing a total of ten or more precision counters.\nNote that these are not the same as regular counters.\n\nIf you're having..." },
            { 738238621, "You can earn a trophy by performing a total of thirty or more Killer Blows.\n\nThere's no rush, though—it's a running count, so you can achieve this ove..." },
            { 738238622, "You can earn a trophy for finishing three or more enemies with a single blast of Surge Magic.\n\nYou need to be sure to defeat them, though—simply hitti..." },
            { 738238623, "You can earn a trophy by using the \"Disperse\" Support Spell three times in a single battle.\n\nNote that this isn't a running count—all three uses need ..." },
            { 738238624, "Try using the \"Bind\" Support Spell to tie up an enemy.\nA quick switch to Sila's spell set and a few swift attacks should earn you this trophy in no ti..." },
            { 738238625, "Try using the \"Tempest\" Surge Magic spell on a group of three or more enemies.\nAny foes it hits will be instantly electrified.\n\nFlashbacks and points ..." },
            { 738238626, "Try using an ability from each of the four spell sets in a single battle.\nAttack Magic, Support Magic, Surge Magic—it doesn't matter, as long as you u..." },
            { 738238627, "You'll need to search in the following places to find the Abominations:\n- The ruins of the village of Koshish in Junoon.\n- The Rock Beds in Praenost." },
            { 738238628, "You'll need to search in the following places to find the Abominations:\n- The Sunken Lands in Avoalet.\n- The Boneyard in Visoria." },
            { 738238629, "The Abominations are all extremely formidable enemies.\nMake sure you're all set with items and the best possible equipment, and don't be afraid to go ..." },
            { 738238630, "You can discover new archive entries by progressing through the story, exploring points of interest and detours,\ndefeating certain enemies, and collec..." },
            { 738238631, "Frey can learn a spell which will render her invisible.\nCast it, and stay dead still—don't even move the camera!" },
