            { 738239048, "Dancing in Cipal" },
            { 738239049, "Press <button1dance>, <button2dance>, <button3dance>, or <button4dance> at precisely the right moment. If you nail them all, you'll complete the chall..." },
            { 738239050, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738239051, "Detours, AKA Side Quests" },
            { 738239052, "If you visit certain marked locations or talk to marked NPCs, you can occasionally take on special side quests.\n\n\nAs the story progresses, these may b..." },
            { 738239055, "Harvest some ballow resin." },
            { 738239056, "Put on a jacket and head out." },
            { 738239057, "Face the demon." },
            { 738239058, "Escape from the demon." },
            { 738239059, "Shit..." },
            { 738239060, "Indeed." },
            { 738239066, "I doubt you'll be squeezing your way to freedom through there." },
            { 738239067, "No shit." },
            { 738239068, "Perhaps you could use them to get the same powers." },
            { 738239069, "Seriously?" },
            { 738239070, "Sila, Tanta of Strength. But you knew that already, of course." },
            { 738239071, "Tanta Prav herself." },
            { 738239072, "Ah. That would be Tanta Cinta." },
            { 738239073, "And I don't have a clue how to get rid of it. Wish I could figure it out..." },
            { 738239074, "Those are powerful magical energies indeed..." },
            { 738239075, "You never know what surprises might be waiting up ahead. Be ready for anything." },
            { 738239076, "Yeah, thanks for the pep talk." },
            { 738239077, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239078, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239079, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239080, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239081, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239082, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239083, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239084, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239085, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239086, "Search for more ballow trees." },
            { 738239087, "Defeat the enemy." },
            { 738239088, "The venerable Tanta Olas." },
            { 738239089, "Head for Visoria Castle." },
            { 738239090, "Oop. My bad." },
            { 738239091, "...What the fuck was that?" },
            { 738239092, "Worth treading carefully, perhaps?" },
            { 738239093, "Uh-huh..." },
            { 738239094, "The fuck is up with the animals here?" },
            { 738239095, "They did seem somewhat...altered, didn't they? Makes you wonder what can have caused such a mutation..." },
            { 738239096, "Yeah. Like, what happened here?" },
            { 738239097, "Whoa. What the hell? What is this weird feeling?" },
            { 738239098, "There seems to be some sort of...malignant miasma in the air." },
            { 738239099, "Oookay. Turning back now." },
            { 738239100, "It doesn't seem to be affecting you, though, does it? Besides, I doubt there'd be much benefit in retracing your steps." },
            { 738239101, "So this...\"miasma\"—what exactly is it?" },
            { 738239102, "It's quite mysterious, isn't it? I suspect it might be what's causing all the local wildlife to look so...peculiar." },
            { 738239103, "So how come it doesn't affect me?" },
            { 738239104, "How come indeed? Could it be thanks to your commendable choice of traveling companion, perhaps?" },
            { 738239105, "Nope. Not that. Definitely not that." },
            { 738239106, "So much for clean air and bright skies." },
            { 738239107, "I try to escape to someplace better, and where do I wind up? Someplace ten times worse..." },
            { 738239108, "Poor you." },
            { 738239109, "Is there not a single person left?" },
            { 738239110, "It very much seems that way. Perhaps this oddness with the air drove them to escape to safer climes." },
            { 738239111, "Hope so. At least that would mean they're still alive..." },
            { 738239112, "Well, this place is fun..." },
            { 738239113, "I imagine it was once. Happy, smiling faces on every corner—I can picture it now." },
            { 738239114, "Damn. Everything just looks...broken." },
            { 738239115, "Not exactly the most poetic of descriptions, but...yes, I suppose it does." },
            { 738239116, "Is there nowhere that's not, like, broken by this shit?" },
            { 738239117, "I suppose there might be somewhere..." },
            { 738239118, "Sounds like trouble." },
            { 738239119, "Yes. And given what we've seen so far, I'd say you need to be very careful in case you're planning on investigating." },
            { 738239120, "Shit! What is it now!?" },
            { 738239121, "It looks like the miasma is worsening somehow." },
            { 738239122, "Perfect. What do we do?" },
            { 738239123, "For the moment, I'd say running away might be a sensible first step." },
            { 738239124, "Is this the break-shit's doing, too?" },
            { 738239125, "I believe so. It corrupts everything it touches. Before destroying it completely..." },
            { 738239126, "Now hurry up and get out of here while you still can." },
            { 738239127, "So the Tantas had superpowers that they used to keep Athia safe." },
            { 738239128, "And the people loved them for it. Worshipped them, even. But then something changed." },
            { 738239129, "Instead of protecting the people, they started making them suffer. And then the Break appeared..." },
            { 738239130, "An admirably pithy précis." },
            { 738239131, "But it doesn't make any sense. Why would they just go crazy like that?" },
            { 738239135, "So the Tantas caused the Break, right?" },
            { 738239136, "It certainly seems that way. After all, it appears to be thickest around the castle." },
            { 738239137, "So if we get rid of them, we get rid of the Break too?" },
            { 738239138, "I'd say it's a possibility. But I wouldn't get your hopes up too high." },
            { 738239139, "Why not?" },
            { 738239140, "It just seems rather persistent. You might stop it from getting worse, but as for getting rid of it entirely—who knows?" },
            { 738239141, "Check out these paintings." },
            { 738239142, "I most certainly will—as should you. Know your enemy, and all that." },
            { 738239143, "So the Athians fought a war way back when?" },
            { 738239144, "Yes. The Rheddig were their opponents, I believe." },
            { 738239145, "And the Tantas led their people into battle." },
            { 738239146, "Indeed they did. Quite literally—they fought on the very front lines." },
            { 738239147, "Wow. They were pretty good leaders before they went batshit crazy, huh?" },
            { 738239148, "Well? Feeling more knowledgeable on the subject of all things Tanta?" },
            { 738239149, "Uh, yeah. A little, I guess." },
            { 738239150, "Wonderful. Then shall we go and meet a real one?" },
            { 738239151, "Why don't we try out your new gifts?" },
            { 738239152, "Yeah. Why not." },
            { 738239153, "Whoa! Okay." },
            { 738239154, "Now keep an eye out for places where you can put your new skills to use." },
            { 738239155, "...Huh?" },
            { 738239156, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239157, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239158, "More new powers?" },
            { 738239159, "Yup. From Prav this time." },
            { 738239160, "Well? Shall we try them out?" },
            { 738239161, "Huh...?" },
            { 738239162, "What the hell...?" },
            { 738239163, "Am I seeing things...?" },
            { 738239164, "Okay, I need some sleep." },
            { 738239165, "Look at that—the barrier's down." },
            { 738239166, "Must have been connected to the lamp somehow..." },
            { 738239167, "Another barrier?" },
            { 738239168, "Looks like Olas's handiwork." },
            { 738239169, "Shit! How do we get out of here!?" },
            { 738239170, "Smash the lamp. That should weaken Olas's influence." },
            { 738239171, "I don't think killing them is getting us anywhere." },
            { 738239172, "Smash the lantern, or they'll just keep coming!" },
            { 738239173, "Ignore the goons! Focus on the lamp!" },
            { 738239174, "They're protecting the lamp somehow." },
            { 738239175, "Kill them all first, then attack it!" },
            { 738239176, "There's no point attacking the lantern until you've got rid of this lot!" },
            { 738239177, "Focus on the enemy first!" },
            { 738239178, "Look carefully—you need to beat the ones connected to the lamp." },
            { 738239179, "Now's your chance! The lantern's unprotected!" },
            { 738239180, "Nice work! Now smash that lantern!" },
            { 738239181, "Give that lamp what-for!" },
            { 738239182, "It's now or never!" },
            { 738239183, "Something's not right... Quickly, Frey—destroy the lantern!" },
            { 738239184, "Hurry! They'll be back any moment now!" },
            { 738239185, "There's no end to them!" },
            { 738239186, "More of them!? Come on!" },
            { 738239187, "Cinta?" },
            { 738239190, "Where do we go now...?" },
            { 738239191, "Let us bring things to an end at last." },
            { 738239192, "People of Cipal... Miserable creatures of Athia... Your time has come!" },
            { 738239193, "There are people inside the tavern. I can't let these fuckers get close." },
            { 738239194, "Gotta keep them away from the tavern!" },
            { 738239195, "Stay the fuck back! You're not getting near those people!" },
            { 738239196, "No! The tavern!" },
            { 738239197, "Shit! They're too close!" },
            { 738239198, "Fuck! They're gonna get in!" },
            { 738239199, "Guess somebody called for backup..." },
            { 738239200, "More? Really!?" },
            { 738239201, "Don't you have somewhere else to be!?" },
            { 738239202, "Can't give up now." },
            { 738239203, "Need to get these fucking birds out of the way!" },
            { 738239204, "Cinta! You're up!" },
            { 738239205, "How many are there!?" },
            { 738239206, "Shit! More!" },
            { 738239207, "What the hell?" },
            { 738239208, "Something tells me this little lot aren't too fond of each other." },
            { 738239209, "Good. Let's use it to our advantage." },
            { 738239214, "What is this? Can I...go in there?" },
            { 738239215, "You never know what you might find—for better or worse." },
            { 738239216, "Are you going in?" },
            { 738239217, "No! ...But I mean, it's kind of asking for it." },
            { 738239218, "Hmm... Wonder what's in there..." },
            { 738239219, "Well? What are we waiting for?" },
            { 738239220, "It's dark in here..." },
            { 738239221, "It is rather. Should have brought a lantern..." },
            { 738239222, "Can't see a fucking thing." },
            { 738239223, "And you're not going to—oh, I don't know—use magic to light your way?" },
            { 738239224, "What's the deal with this place?" },
            { 738239225, "Shall we head further in and see?" },
            { 738239226, "Interesting..." },
            { 738239227, "Shall we?" },
            { 738239228, "Something's there..." },
            { 738239229, "Yes. And it's not friendly..." },
            { 738239230, "Shit! Surrounded!" },
            { 738239231, "It does rather seem that way." },
            { 738239232, "Not good..." },
            { 738239233, "Please don't die. The thought of being stranded in this ghastly place..." },
            { 738239234, "Might be in trouble here..." },
            { 738239235, "No shit!" },
            { 738239236, "Path splits here..." },
            { 738239237, "Choices, choices..." },
            { 738239238, "Which way?" },
            { 738239239, "As long as you hurry up and decide, I honestly don't mind." },
            { 738239240, "Niiice!" },
            { 738239241, "Ooh. It is rather, isn't it?" },
            { 738239242, "Check this out!" },
            { 738239243, "Perhaps it was worth coming here after all." },
            { 738239244, "Yesss!" },
            { 738239245, "Not bad..." },
            { 738239246, "Whoa!" },
            { 738239247, "Watch your step." },
            { 738239248, "Not exactly safe around here..." },
            { 738239249, "Tread carefully." },
            { 738239250, "Dead end." },
            { 738239251, "Then I suppose we turn back." },
            { 738239252, "Seems this is the end of the road." },
            { 738239253, "Back we go..." },
            { 738239260, "LEVEL" },
            { 738239261, "TO NEXT" },
            { 738239263, "Revenge will soon be mine!" },
            { 738239264, "I have waited too long for this day!" },
            { 738239265, "A crib?" },
            { 738239266, "The locations mentioned have been added to the world map." },
            { 738239267, "The locations marked on Auden's map have been added to the world map." },
            { 738239268, "You're lacking the ingredients required to perform this upgrade." },
            { 738239269, "Equipment effects can now be applied through crafting.\nYou can duplicate the effects of any necklaces or cloaks you own,\nand apply them to other piece..." },
            { 738239270, "Select a Piece of Equipment to Upgrade" },
            { 738239271, "Select an Equipment Effect" },
            { 738239272, "The current effect will be replaced." },
            { 738239273, "Shit—look!" },
            { 738239274, "Ah, if it isn't our dear old friend." },
            { 738239275, "That fucking thing again?" },
            { 738239276, "I almost get the sense it's looking for you..." },
            { 738239277, "Frey! Up there!" },
            { 738239278, "Guy really gets around, huh?" },
            { 738239279, "Seriously—I think it's following me." },
            { 738239280, "Oh to be so sought-after..." },
            { 738239281, "This thing is dead, right?" },
            { 738239282, "Give it a kick and make sure, maybe?" },
            { 738239283, "What happened here?" },
            { 738239284, "I'd say there was a fight. And our enormous friend wasn't the victor." },
            { 738239285, "Well, this is certainly a sizeable specimen." },
            { 738239286, "If it moves, we're outta here." },
            { 738239287, "What do they say again? \"Let sleeping monsters lie\"?" },
            { 738239288, "If they do, I wholeheartedly concur." },
