            { 738239299, "Head for the Cognoscents' Guild." },
            { 738239300, "Destroy the lantern." },
            { 738239301, "Make your way to the throne room." },
            { 738239311, "Olevia has given you some balm flax.\nUse the crafting bench to turn it into a healing draught." },
            { 738239312, "You can use crafting to improve your equipment.\nLook around the dump and see if you can find some crafting materials." },
            { 738239313, "You've found some grainstone.\nUse it to improve your cloak on the crafting bench." },
            { 738239314, "You've found some crafting materials.\nUse them to improve your cloak on the crafting bench." },
            { 738239315, "You can find all kinds of crafting materials while out exploring the world.\nCollect enough of them, and you'll be able to make new items and improve y..." },
