            { 738239431, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239432, "Huh?" },
            { 738239433, "What the—I'm floating!" },
            { 738239434, "I suppose it must be something to do with how heavy the Break is here." },
            { 738239435, "Huh. No way..." },
            { 738239436, "This place is so weird." },
            { 738239437, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738239438, "Yes, yes. I'm sure it's intensely amusing. Now, shall we be on our way?" },
            { 738239440, "<iconChapterSumVfx>An underground cavern bursting at the seams with great clouds of Corruption? Well, I don't know about you, but I can't wait to dive..." },
            { 738239441, "Okay." },
            { 738239442, "Places Where Materials Can Be Gathered" },
            { 738239443, "Enemy Habitats" },
            { 738239448, "Point of Interest" },
            { 738239451, "Powerful Enemy Elimination" },
            { 738239457, "Hey, Homer. Sorry—it's been a while, I know." },
            { 738239458, "You miss me?" },
            { 738239459, "Been so busy recently..." },
            { 738239460, "Oh, well, you know... Important stuff." },
            { 738239461, "Holding court, slaying demons..." },
            { 738239462, "I'll let you in on a secret, but I'm...a pretty big deal." },
            { 738239463, "Like, actually. I'm kind of a big deal now." },
            { 738239464, "Everybody needs me. I mean, I'm not a big fan of the whole \"hero\" thing, but..." },
            { 738239465, "Look, just tell Judge Bird I took her advice, okay?" },
            { 738239466, "I'm finally using my gifts to help others." },
            { 738239467, "Tell her...thanks for the almost-birthday present." },
            { 738239468, "Kinda wanted to be there to say it myself, but...it's probably better coming from you, girl." },
            { 738239469, "...It's been a pretty good day, you know. Wish they could all be this good." },
