            { 738239611, "Locked Labyrinth" },
            { 738239612, "My ballow tree sense is tingling..." },
            { 738239613, "Let's see what we can find, shall we?" },
            { 738239614, "I think there might be a ballow tree nearby." },
            { 738239615, "Alright. Let's see..." },
            { 738239616, "Smells like that ballow tree back in Cipal..." },
            { 738239617, "Good. Then there must be one nearby." },
            { 738239618, "Where are we gonna find more ballow trees...?" },
            { 738239619, "Perhaps through that door?" },
            { 738239620, "Touch these to return to the entrance." },
            { 738239621, "Places of note already discovered.\n<Unknown1>" },
            { 738239622, "Are you sure you want to restore all the currently selected settings to their defaults?" },
            { 738239623, "Grants Auto-Heal Effect after Use" },
            { 738239624, "Let me guess—more weird Break-related shit." },
            { 738239625, "It would seem so..." },
            { 738239626, "Wait, am I breathing underwater?" },
            { 738239627, "The thicker the Break becomes, the less the rules of the normal world apply." },
            { 738239628, "Well, not much is gonna surprise me after this..." },
            { 738239629, "But you and I both know that's not how it goes." },
            { 738239630, "Listen, you ever get lonely, you just remember..." },
            { 738239631, "Remember that you are not alone." },
            { 738239632, "Even if you find yourself with nowhere to turn, and no clue where to go or what to do next..." },
            { 738239633, "You can't give up hope." },
            { 738239634, "You might think there's nothing left to live for. That nobody cares." },
            { 738239635, "But the truth is...you matter. Even when you can't see it." },
            { 738239636, "Granted, you might fuck up along the way." },
            { 738239637, "But you'll find your way home in the end, I promise. I did." },
            { 738239638, "Look at me now, huh? Tanta Frey!" },
            { 738239639, "Daughter of Cinta..." },
            { 738239640, "Protector of Athia." },
            { 738239641, "I'll come back for you, I promise." },
            { 738239642, "Just...look out for me, okay?" },
