            { 738240100, "6_CH13 Chase the Striped Cat Clear" },
            { 738240101, "7_CH13 Chase the Striped Cat 2 Clear" },
            { 738240102, "Chase the Cat CH13(After Clear version)" },
            { 738240103, "End your current quest and return to just before it started.\n\n\nIf you are finding enemies to be too tough, try adjusting the difficulty setting by sel..." },
            { 738240104, "Load saved data.\n\n\nIf you are finding enemies to be too tough, try adjusting the difficulty setting by selecting 'Gameplay Balance' from the SETTINGS ..." },
            { 738240105, "Load your most recent saved data." },
            { 738240106, "End the current game and return to the title screen." },
            { 738240108, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738240109, "You strayed a little too far, so will be returned to the quest area." },
            { 738240128, "<iconChapterSumVfx>You have to admire the commitment to the whole \"insane wild dog\" aesthetic. I imagine that coating of minerals doesn't make it huge..." },
            { 738240129, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well, it's certainly no less volatile-looking than its cousins. I'd try to eliminate it before it has a chance to get too worked up..." },
            { 738240130, "<iconChapterSumVfx>If these creatures were ever adorable, I'd say those days are long since past—torso mouths do tend to have that effect. I'd try to ..." },
            { 738240131, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well, based on the yellow plumage, I'd say this one's no shrinking violet. It seems to be some kind of scout. Get rid of it quickly..." },
            { 738240136, "Cipal Road to Recovery Clear" },
