            { 738240180, "Approach the light." },
            { 738240181, "Follow the guiding light." },
            { 738240182, "Overcome Cinta's trial." },
            { 738240183, "Follow the guiding light." },
            { 738240184, "Overcome Cinta's trial." },
            { 738240185, "Follow the guiding light." },
            { 738240186, "Overcome Cinta's trial." },
            { 738240187, "Follow the guiding light." },
            { 738240188, "Enter the torana?" },
            { 738240192, "Explore the memories." },
            { 738240193, "Follow the guiding light, and learn the truth about what happened to Athia." },
            { 738240194, "Approach the light in order to visit the memories." },
            { 738240200, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738240201, "Guiding Lights" },
            { 738240202, "Guiding lights will lead you toward certain recollections of Cinta's that she wishes to share with Frey.\n\n\nFollow them to find out the truth about wha..." },
            { 738240206, "Visit Cinta's memories and find out what happened to Athia." },
            { 738240208, "Frey can now use her spell set again." },
            { 738240209, "Frey can now use Olas's spell set." },
            { 738240210, "Frey can now use Prav's spell set again." },
            { 738240211, "Frey can now use Sila's spell set again." },
            { 738240212, "Let's see...\"A Study of Miracles.\"" },
            { 738240213, "It appears to be an in-depth analysis of what makes the Tantas' magic so powerful." },
            { 738240214, "I wonder if you might learn something from it. Pick up some tips and tricks for your own magic, perhaps?" },
            { 738240215, "Yeah, maybe. I could use the help." },
            { 738240216, "Messages left by the first-ever Tanta... Interesting." },
            { 738240217, "I'd quite like to get my hands on an ancient relic or two, personally." },
            { 738240218, "Wouldn't hurt to learn more about the Tantas, either. Guess we could keep an eye out." },
            { 738240219, "That thing we read... It was written by the first-ever Tanta..." },
            { 738240220, "And it sounds like there might still be more of them to find." },
            { 738240221, "Wouldn't hurt to learn more. Guess we could keep an eye out." },
            { 738240222, "Okay. Who are the...archery enthusiasts?" },
            { 738240224, "I've gotta get out of here!" },
            { 738240225, "Shit, shit!" },
            { 738240226, "Shut. The fuck. Up!" },
            { 738240227, "Think, Frey... Come on... You gotta get out of this..." },
            { 738240228, "What an...excitable young man." },
            { 738240229, "You know...I've never gotten flowers before." },
            { 738240230, "And let's hope it never happens again. Shall we?" },
            { 738240231, "This looks like it might work..." },
            { 738240232, "How about this?" },
            { 738240233, "This one looks promising...I think." },
            { 738240234, "Cat Lover" },
            { 738240235, "Book Collector" },
            { 738240238, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738240239, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738240272, "Hey, what's that over there?" },
            { 738240273, "How very peculiar..." },
            { 738240274, "Maybe we'll find one of those messages from the first Tanta in here..." },
            { 738240275, "Shall we have a look?" },
            { 738240276, "Wow. This place sure is something." },
            { 738240277, "It does rather pique one's interest." },
            { 738240278, "This feels...foreboding." },
            { 738240279, "That's never stopped you before." },
            { 738240280, "There's something in there—I can feel it." },
            { 738240281, "Then let's venture inside and see what it is." },
            { 738240282, "Feels like it's saying...\"Stay the hell out.\"" },
            { 738240283, "Let me guess: that makes you want to go in all the more?" },
            { 738240284, "Could be something cool inside." },
            { 738240285, "Shall we test your instincts?" },
            { 738240286, "Might be a good chance to flex my skills." },
            { 738240287, "I applaud your enthusiasm." },
            { 738240288, "Where are we?" },
            { 738240289, "Somewhere underground, I think..." },
            { 738240290, "This place gives me the creeps..." },
            { 738240291, "Stay on your guard—I sense enemies ahead." },
            { 738240292, "It is way too quiet in here." },
            { 738240293, "Ah, the calm before the storm." },
            { 738240294, "The air feels...almost charged in here." },
            { 738240295, "I'd say there's definitely something interesting going on..." },
            { 738240296, "Wonder how old this place is..." },
            { 738240297, "I'd guess fairly ancient." },
            { 738240298, "Adrenaline is pumping!" },
            { 738240299, "Thrill-seeker, eh?" },
            { 738240300, "Let's look for treasure! There's gotta be treasure." },
            { 738240301, "Let's hope it's particularly shiny." },
            { 738240302, "What's this doing here?" },
            { 738240303, "Who cares? I'll take it." },
            { 738240304, "Nice! Always good in a pinch." },
            { 738240305, "Do try not to waste it." },
            { 738240306, "Was just thinking I could use something like this!" },
            { 738240307, "As long as you use it wisely." },
            { 738240308, "You can use that to heal yourself." },
            { 738240309, "Good. Something tells me I'll need it." },
            { 738240310, "You'll need that if there are nasties lurking about the place." },
            { 738240311, "Better keep it close." },
            { 738240312, "Not a great welcome." },
            { 738240313, "At least you got a welcome." },
            { 738240314, "Oh shit. So many of them!" },
            { 738240315, "You know what to do!" },
            { 738240316, "Alright, let's dance." },
            { 738240317, "By \"dance,\" I assume you mean \"batter one another until someone falls over\"?" },
            { 738240318, "Hey! Come at me! ...Or are you scared?" },
            { 738240319, "Let's show them a thing or three!" },
            { 738240320, "Here we go..." },
            { 738240321, "Such enthusiasm..." },
            { 738240322, "Alright, get in line. Who wants me first?" },
            { 738240323, "I don't think they're about to form an orderly queue..." },
            { 738240324, "Oh, look. More asses to kick." },
            { 738240325, "Do it quickly so we can move on." },
            { 738240326, "Why am I not surprised?" },
            { 738240327, "And why are there so many of them?" },
            { 738240328, "Dammit! This is not treasure!" },
            { 738240329, "Patience. It's not far off, I'm sure." },
            { 738240330, "Are they...sleeping?" },
            { 738240331, "Maybe we should just tiptoe past them?" },
            { 738240332, "Please don't wake up... Please don't wake up..." },
            { 738240333, "They won't if you stop talking." },
            { 738240334, "Look at 'em, just lying there..." },
            { 738240335, "If you're going to do it, do it quickly." },
            { 738240336, "This thing is unreal..." },
            { 738240337, "You might have to pull out all the stops for this one..." },
            { 738240338, "Why!? Why is this a thing!?" },
            { 738240339, "I wonder if it might be this place's guardian..." },
            { 738240340, "Uh, how am I supposed to fight something that looks like that!?" },
            { 738240341, "I suppose you could always run and hide!" },
            { 738240342, "I think I can do this...maybe...sort of. Not really." },
            { 738240343, "There's nothing for it but to try!" },
            { 738240344, "How about I show you what I can do?" },
            { 738240345, "What \"we\" can do, surely?" },
            { 738240346, "No fooling around this time. This is not going to be easy." },
            { 738240347, "I got this!" },
            { 738240348, "Boss battle!" },
            { 738240349, "A challenge might be good..." },
            { 738240350, "Ready, Cuff?" },
            { 738240351, "Whenever you are." },
            { 738240352, "Whoa. Look at that thing..." },
            { 738240353, "Ah. Yes. Er...good luck." },
            { 738240354, "That guy looks tough as nails..." },
            { 738240355, "I'm inclined to agree with your assessment." },
            { 738240356, "I actually have to fight this thing, don't I?" },
            { 738240357, "Only if you want to know what lies ahead." },
            { 738240358, "Uh...what? Why are there so many of them!?" },
            { 738240359, "It's do or die, Frey. Quite literally, in fact." },
            { 738240360, "Yo, this room is way over capacity." },
            { 738240361, "Time to thin things out a little." },
            { 738240362, "Fuck that thing, fuck that, fuck everything about this place." },
            { 738240363, "No more complaining! It's time to prove yourself, Frey." },
            { 738240364, "Oh shit. Think I might have pissed them off." },
            { 738240365, "When will you learn to be more careful?" },
            { 738240366, "Uh...do they look a little...irritated to you?" },
            { 738240367, "No prizes for guessing who might have provoked them." },
            { 738240368, "Someone doesn't look so happy..." },
            { 738240369, "And whose fault is that, exactly?" },
            { 738240370, "Whoa, so many of them..." },
            { 738240371, "Yes. Quite the welcome." },
            { 738240372, "What's with these guys!? They're so annoying!" },
            { 738240373, "Let's bring them down to earth, shall we?" },
            { 738240374, "Ugh. Stop flapping around and let me fight you!" },
            { 738240375, "You could always try bringing them to the ground." },
            { 738240376, "What is this thing...?" },
            { 738240377, "Something ancient. And apparently broken." },
            { 738240381, "Is that...?" },
            { 738240382, "One of these things again..." },
            { 738240383, "What a weird place..." },
            { 738240384, "Thought I'd find you here." },
            { 738240385, "It's broken." },
            { 738240386, "Wonder what happened all those years ago..." },
            { 738240387, "Wonder what stories you've got to tell..." },
            { 738240388, "Wow. Not bad at all." },
            { 738240389, "We could certainly have done worse." },
            { 738240390, "Now that's fancy." },
            { 738240391, "Wow. Imagine something like this just sitting here..." },
            { 738240392, "Oh okay, I can totally make this work." },
            { 738240393, "Hell yeah!" },
            { 738240394, "We did it!" },
            { 738240395, "Nice! Check this out!" },
            { 738240396, "Wow. This is incredible..." },
            { 738240397, "A demon? What demon...?" },
            { 738240398, "So there were monsters in Athia far before the arrival of the Break..." },
            { 738240399, "An ancient demon...? Interesting..." },
            { 738240400, "Wonder how many years ago that was..." },
            { 738240401, "A demon...? Could she mean...?" },
            { 738240402, "Oh, look! Is this you she's talking about?" },
            { 738240403, "I'm flattered, really. She describes the essence of my mission with such color, wouldn't you say?" },
            { 738240404, "Hey, what if this is about that dragon?" },
            { 738240405, "It does match the description..." },
            { 738240406, "Say, don't you think this \"demon\" sounds an awful lot like our old friend?" },
            { 738240407, "That's awful... He's not getting away with this." },
            { 738240409, "Wow. She's a badass." },
            { 738240410, "It certainly sounds like it was a trying battle for all parties involved." },
            { 738240411, "She paints a picture of a most spectacular battle." },
            { 738240412, "So Susurrus was defeated before... What made him come back all those years later?" },
            { 738240414, "The making of the first Tanta. Damn." },
            { 738240415, "I wonder what she'd have to say about the sorry state of the Tantas today..." },
            { 738240416, "The first Tanta certainly sounds like a visionary." },
            { 738240417, "Yeah. You can only wonder what she'd think about the Tantas today." },
            { 738240418, "So that's how the whole Tanta thing got started..." },
            { 738240419, "So someone got trapped by the first Tanta, huh?" },
            { 738240420, "I was not \"trapped.\" I was merely...biding my time." },
            { 738240421, "So this place is meant as a warning, huh?" },
            { 738240422, "So it would seem. A salutary reminder to future generations to prepare for the worst." },
            { 738240423, "This place was built as a means of communicating the threat posed by this Susurrus fellow." },
            { 738240424, "So basically the message is \"Watch out\"..." },
            { 738240426, "She trapped Susurrus in here..." },
            { 738240427, "Apparently, yes. Don't see him when you look around, though, do you?" },
            { 738240428, "The demon Susurrus might have been bound within this very chamber..." },
            { 738240429, "He was trapped in here..." },
            { 738240431, "An ancient weapon...?" },
            { 738240432, "Curious..." },
            { 738240433, "An ancient weapon...? They've gotta mean Cuff..." },
            { 738240434, "\"Ancient weapon\" gives you too much credit." },
            { 738240435, "I prefer the term \"apocalypse incarnate\" myself." },
            { 738240436, "So this place was strictly off-limits..." },
            { 738240437, "And the Break doesn't make dungeon-diving any more likely now." },
            { 738240438, "Wonder if the Tantas kept people out to make sure Susurrus stayed in..." },
            { 738240439, "I assume you're the reason no one was ever allowed in here." },
            { 738240440, "They thought someone might free me. Guess they were right." },
            { 738240441, "A weapon? In here...?" },
            { 738240442, "Apparently so. And whoever was searching for it appears to have been rather overenthusiastic." },
            { 738240443, "A weapon? In here...?" },
            { 738240444, "I'm surprised your ego fit in here." },
            { 738240445, "You're not the only one." },
            { 738240446, "Where were they taking it?" },
            { 738240447, "Wherever it was, I bet they were trying to gather all the parts in a single location." },
            { 738240448, "Wonder where they were taking it..." },
            { 738240449, "Let me guess: they gathered all those parts to try and put you back together." },
            { 738240450, "Excellent deductive skills." },
            { 738240451, "So this was the instruction manual..." },
            { 738240452, "Well, I'm afraid any useful information it might have contained is long gone. A crying shame..." },
            { 738240453, "Ugh. What a waste..." },
            { 738240454, "A way to shut you down forever, huh?" },
            { 738240455, "She must have taught the Tantas how to contain me. ...A lot of good that did them." },
            { 738240456, "Guess that's what you get for stealing from a Tanta." },
            { 738240457, "They were certainly trying to keep the contents of this place well hidden." },
            { 738240458, "Can't blame her for trying to keep him locked up in here." },
            { 738240459, "Sounds like she pulled out all the stops to keep you in here." },
            { 738240460, "But you just can't keep a good demon down. As you too will discover in your turn..." },
            { 738240461, "He was just...stuck in here..." },
            { 738240462, "A most terrible Tanta trap." },
            { 738240463, "I can't believe these people just threw away their lives for him..." },
            { 738240464, "To think, if he'd failed, all of this shit might never have happened." },
            { 738240465, "Good point. Do you think it's too late to write him a thoughtful thank-you note?" },
            { 738240466, "Whoa! Is that...a cat!?" },
            { 738240467, "In the middle of the Break!?" },
            { 738240468, "I assume that is no ordinary cat." },
            { 738240469, "It's gone!" },
            { 738240470, "It didn't appear to be harmful, thank goodness. I wonder if we'll run into it again..." },
            { 738240471, "I hope so—it was kinda cute..." },
            { 738240472, "Look over there. What's that weird statue?" },
            { 738240473, "Hmm. It looks like one of those cat things you so enjoy." },
            { 738240474, "Why do I get the feeling a cat is watching us...?" },
            { 738240475, "Well, there's a bizarrely specific instinct to have." },
            { 738240476, "I bet one of those cool cats is nearby..." },
            { 738240477, "Look around, then...if you must." },
            { 738240478, "Hey, that statue! That must mean..." },
            { 738240479, "A cat. Please excuse me while I contain my excitement." },
            { 738240480, "Hey, I think I heard a cat..." },
            { 738240481, "Your powers of cat detection are truly inspiring." },
            { 738240482, "It seems to have noticed you..." },
            { 738240483, "It's okay. I'm used to this." },
            { 738240484, "It doesn't look particularly friendly..." },
            { 738240485, "Typical cat behavior from a not-so-typical cat." },
            { 738240486, "Hey, kitty, kitty! Let's be friends, okay?" },
            { 738240487, "I'm slightly embarrassed that you're trying so hard..." },
            { 738240488, "Hey, kitty! Wanna come over here?" },
            { 738240489, "What if it doesn't like being called \"kitty\"?" },
            { 738240490, "Hmm... Where should I pet you first?" },
            { 738240491, "Does it even matter?" },
            { 738240492, "Okay. Now to figure out the right angle of approach..." },
            { 738240493, "You are taking this far too seriously." },
            { 738240494, "Don't be scared! I'm friendly, I promise!" },
            { 738240495, "Hey, buddy. Whatcha doing all the way out here?" },
            { 738240496, "Does that feel good?" },
            { 738240497, "Yeah, bet that hits the spot." },
            { 738240498, "How about some rubs right here?" },
            { 738240499, "How's that feel?" },
            { 738240500, "There, there." },
            { 738240501, "Yeah, you like that, don't you?" },
            { 738240502, "Aww, good kitty!" },
            { 738240503, "Goodness. You're a regular cat charmer." },
            { 738240504, "You're no Homer, but you're pretty damn cute." },
            { 738240505, "These creatures are rather easily swayed, aren't they?" },
            { 738240506, "Aww. It likes me!" },
            { 738240507, "Very good, very good..." },
            { 738240508, "Did I just make your day, little guy?" },
            { 738240509, "Must not have been a very exciting day." },
            { 738240510, "Damn. Guess it didn't want to be friends." },
            { 738240511, "Oh, how tragic." },
            { 738240512, "It did not look happy..." },
            { 738240513, "Why are you traipsing around offending Athia's cats?" },
            { 738240514, "Dammit!" },
            { 738240515, "Well, that was hard to watch." },
            { 738240516, "Ugh, there it goes..." },
            { 738240517, "Maybe if you come back later?" },
            { 738240518, "Something about that cat felt...different, don't you think?" },
            { 738240519, "Funny you mention that—I was just thinking I detected a hint of Tanta magic..." },
            { 738240520, "Huh. Could they be connected somehow? Wonder where it went..." },
            { 738240521, "Hey! That cat!" },
            { 738240522, "Did it...tail us here?" },
            { 738240523, "Awww. That's so sweet! Hey, little guy!" },
            { 738240524, "So the Tantas had familiars...huh. Like a pet?" },
            { 738240525, "Despite their catlike appearance, it sounds like these familiars are pure constructions of magic." },
            { 738240526, "Magic or not, that cat was super cute. Aw, I hope we get to meet his little familiar friends!" },
            { 738240527, "Oi! Miss!" },
            { 738240528, "Huh?" },
            { 738240529, "What's that shiny box thingy you've got?" },
            { 738240530, "What? Oh... Uh, that's a \"smartphone.\"" },
            { 738240531, "Um...how do I put this? It's like a thing that lets you talk to people far away, or turn what you see into pictures." },
            { 738240532, "Whoa! Does that mean...it could turn what you see into pictures? Of outside Cipal?" },
            { 738240533, "Yeah, I guess." },
            { 738240534, "I've only seen drawings of the outside in books! Could you...could you bring us pictures?" },
            { 738240535, "I don't see why not. Just don't expect too much, okay? I'm not a great photographer." },
            { 738240536, "I don't know what that is, but thank you! I'm so excited!" },
            { 738240537, "Not really a big camera person, to be honest..." },
            { 738240538, "I'm pretty sure they'd be delighted with anything you show them. It's not like they have much else to look forward to." },
            { 738240539, "Perhaps it wouldn't be so bad to stop by on occasion, lend them a little cheer?" },
            { 738240540, "You're right. It won't cost me much, and I bet it would mean a lot to them." },
            { 738240541, "We might be able to take a nice picture for those kids around here." },
            { 738240542, "You're the expert." },
            { 738240543, "Hey, this place looks pretty unique. Should I take a picture?" },
            { 738240544, "Just try not to dillydally." },
            { 738240545, "Oh, man. I bet the kids in town would love to see this." },
            { 738240546, "It would make for a striking picture, I suppose." },
            { 738240547, "Alright, let's take this photo." },
            { 738240548, "In the frame you go..." },
            { 738240549, "Gotta get a good angle..." },
            { 738240550, "This'll be a good one." },
            { 738240551, "Nice." },
            { 738240552, "Passable." },
            { 738240553, "That's that!" },
            { 738240554, "Guess that'll do." },
            { 738240555, "Can't wait to show this to the kids." },
            { 738240556, "They'll certainly have plenty to be excited about." },
            { 738240557, "Oh, it's you! Did you bring us lots of pictures?" },
            { 738240558, "Sure did. Here you go." },
            { 738240559, "That's amazing! Is that really what it looks like out there?" },
            { 738240560, "I want to see more! Please, oh please!" },
            { 738240561, "Okay, okay, I gotcha. I'll be back with more pictures later." },
            { 738240562, "Do you have more pictures of outside?" },
            { 738240563, "Oh, yeah. A ton of them." },
            { 738240564, "Oh, they're so pretty! I've never seen anything like them!" },
            { 738240565, "Wow... Thank you so much!" },
            { 738240566, "You're very welcome." },
            { 738240567, "I can't wait to see what the rest of Athia looks like!" },
            { 738240568, "I wonder what you'll show us!" },
            { 738240569, "Thank you so much for showing us all those pictures!" },
            { 738240570, "Next time you'll have to tell us all about your adventures out there!" },
            { 738240571, "Interested in these here books, are you?" },
            { 738240572, "You've got a good eye! They're treasures of a sort, all rescued from the abandoned Cognoscents' Guilds." },
            { 738240573, "Huh, cool. ...Hey, this one actually looks useful. It's about crafting." },
            { 738240574, "It certainly seems like it might be worth your while." },
            { 738240575, "I'd be happy to give it to you—for a price. I collect old things, see. Find some, and I might just be persuadable." },
            { 738240576, "Alright, I'll see what I can do." },
            { 738240577, "What about this old coin?" },
            { 738240578, "Well, now, isn't that a beauty! I'll need more than one of those depending on the book—but here, have a look." },
            { 738240579, "Hey, I used to buy stuff like this for my cat..." },
            { 738240580, "Well spotted! I did think you had the look of a cat lover!" },
            { 738240581, "If you'd like something, we could make a trade. Always happy to help a fellow ailurophile!" },
            { 738240582, "Oh, wow. Thanks! I'll come back when I have something good to trade." },
            { 738240583, "Hmm... Could I get anything for this old coin?" },
            { 738240584, "Are you seriously going to fill your pockets with this rubbish?" },
            { 738240585, "That looks lovely, dear. Take your pick!" },
            { 738240586, "Do my eyeballs deceive me? A living human, all the way out here?" },
            { 738240588, "...Did that zombie just talk?" },
            { 738240589, "A refreshing change, considering his less friendly counterparts..." },
            { 738240590, "Uh...hey, Mister Breakzombie." },
            { 738240591, "Ahem! Don't be fooled by my alarming appearance! I am fully human where it counts!" },
            { 738240592, "It's not very nice to label others, you know." },
            { 738240593, "Oh! Uh, sorry...Sir." },
            { 738240594, "No harm done! I'm just glad you're here! It's not often I get visitors of the living, breathing kind." },
            { 738240595, "Aha! Why not help yourself to a gift? You'll find my curios...delightfully stimulating." },
            { 738240596, "Really? You're just gonna give one to me?" },
            { 738240597, "Well...if you have any trinkets to offer in exchange." },
            { 738240598, "Damn, fresh outta trinkets. But I'll keep an eye out." },
            { 738240599, "I've only got this coin..." },
            { 738240600, "Oooh! Is that old Athian currency?" },
            { 738240601, "Yes, this will do! Now what would you like?" },
            { 738240602, "Anything take your fancy?" },
            { 738240605, "What would you like?" },
            { 738240606, "The kitties adore that one!" },
            { 738240607, "I'm afraid you don't have enough, dear..." },
            { 738240608, "Which of my treasures most intrigues you?" },
            { 738240609, "A mutually advantageous trade!" },
            { 738240610, "You'll need more coins for curios of this caliber!" },
            { 738240611, "Well, look at that! You've cleared me out!" },
            { 738240612, "What can I say? You had some good stuff. Thanks, they were really helpful." },
            { 738240613, "You must be a smart one to have no trouble with books like that! They're a bit above my head, I'm afraid." },
            { 738240614, "What? Oh, no, I'm nothing special..." },
            { 738240615, "I suppose it's a good thing you took them off his hands. Imagine all that knowledge going to waste..." },
            { 738240616, "No more books to trade, I'm afraid. Maybe one day!" },
            { 738240617, "Oh, my. I've given you everything I have!" },
            { 738240618, "You clearly cherish nothing more than our feline friends!" },
            { 738240619, "Aw, thanks! I do love them, I guess." },
            { 738240620, "I'm not entirely convinced that was a compliment..." },
            { 738240621, "Nothing new for our little friends, I'm afraid." },
            { 738240622, "Oh, splendid! That was my last treasure!" },
            { 738240623, "This stuff has been amazing. Thank you so much." },
            { 738240624, "Thank YOU for my shiny new coin collection!" },
            { 738240625, "Um, can I ask you something? Do you...have a name?" },
            { 738240626, "I...I did. But I no longer remember it." },
            { 738240627, "That phase of my life is a blur, I'm afraid." },
            { 738240628, "Oh. I see..." },
            { 738240629, "The past is the past. We must celebrate the present! And as for the future...do come and see me again." },
            { 738240630, "Ooh, hello, old friend! No new treasures today! But I always enjoy a fellow human's company." },
            { 738240631, "That thing is handy!" },
            { 738240632, "I could certainly get used to this..." },
            { 738240633, "Very nifty." },
            { 738240634, "It is rather nice to be spared the trouble." },
            { 738240635, "Best curio ever!" },
            { 738240636, "Yes, yes..." },
            { 738240637, "Got 'em all!" },
            { 738240638, "This thing's great!" },
            { 738240639, "Truly a find for the ages." },
            { 738240644, "Wonder if I can find something cool around here..." },
            { 738240645, "Admit it. You just don't want to sit still." },
            { 738240646, "Where are you going?" },
            { 738240647, "Just gonna look around." },
            { 738240648, "Hey, I think I see something useful." },
            { 738240649, "Got a good feeling about this place..." },
            { 738240650, "I'll feel a lot safer with this thing around." },
            { 738240651, "That reassuring, eh?" },
            { 738240654, "I think I'm in the mood to make something." },
            { 738240655, "Do try to craft us something that's actually useful..." },
            { 738240662, "Time to curl up with a good book..." },
            { 738240663, "Let's see. Any interesting books?" },
            { 738240664, "Hmm, what are we in the mood for today..." },
            { 738240665, "Got some time to kill. Could read a book." },
            { 738240666, "Ooh, never seen that book before." },
            { 738240667, "Are you going to read something?" },
            { 738240668, "It's about time you learned something new." },
            { 738240669, "Anything intriguing?" },
            { 738240670, "In the mood for something in particular?" },
            { 738240671, "You do like your reading." },
            { 738240672, "Let's try practicing this technique." },
            { 738240673, "Hm, let's see how this goes." },
            { 738240674, "Challenge accepted!" },
            { 738240675, "This looks like it'll be worth my while." },
            { 738240676, "Practice makes perfect!" },
            { 738240677, "Time to work on that spell, then?" },
            { 738240678, "Interesting choice of task." },
            { 738240679, "This might be a tad tricky..." },
            { 738240680, "Alright, let's get on with it." },
            { 738240681, "You'd best be prepared before we head out." },
            { 738240682, "All done!" },
            { 738240683, "Nice!" },
            { 738240684, "Smooth!" },
            { 738240685, "And that is how it's done!" },
            { 738240686, "Not bad, if I do say so myself." },
            { 738240687, "You seem to have wrapped that up nicely." },
            { 738240688, "Satisfactory work." },
            { 738240689, "One more in the bag." },
            { 738240690, "Another one for the books! Literally, I mean." },
            { 738240691, "You certainly worked up a sweat." },
            { 738240692, "Do I look stronger? Because I definitely feel stronger." },
            { 738240693, "Ooph, can't wait to give this a test drive." },
            { 738240694, "Gonna get a lot of use out of this!" },
            { 738240695, "You can call me Super Frey." },
            { 738240696, "Onward and upward!" },
            { 738240697, "No doubt about it. You're getting better at this." },
            { 738240698, "You've certainly picked up some nice little tricks." },
            { 738240699, "That'll come in handy." },
            { 738240700, "You're surprisingly quick on the uptake, you know." },
            { 738240701, "What other gems do you have up your sleeve?" },
            { 738240702, "Indeed. A remarkable find." },
            { 738240703, "Well, perhaps it ought to thank you for saving it from a lifetime of collecting dust." },
            { 738240704, "Pop it on then, let's see!" },
            { 738240705, "Not bad, not bad at all..." },
            { 738240706, "And it was well worth the pain." },
            { 738240707, "A rather marvelous find." },
            { 738240708, "It'll certainly make for a striking look." },
            { 738240789, "Who were those people running the trial?" },
            { 738240790, "You mean the Council of Cipal? They're the leaders of our city. They settle all our disputes." },
            { 738240791, "Judge and jury all rolled into one, huh? Efficient." },
            { 738240792, "Stop!" },
            { 738240793, "Over here!" },
            { 738240794, "Quickly now!" },
            { 738240795, "Not that way!" },
            { 738240796, "I don't have any parents. I had some foster ones, but...they never really stuck." },
            { 738240797, "Cat Person" },
            { 738240798, "Happy Snapper" },
            { 738240799, "Above and Beyond" },
            { 738240800, "Befriend all the Tantas' familiars." },
            { 738240801, "Show pictures taken at all the photo spots to the children." },
            { 738240802, "Upgrade all your spells." },
            { 738240803, "Everyone has something they're willing to fight for." },
            { 738240804, "Could be family. Friends." },
            { 738240805, "Your beliefs. Your home." },
            { 738240806, "Doesn't matter who you are. There's just some things you have to protect." },
            { 738240807, "But what do you do when the world fights back?" },
            { 738240808, "Guess I know now." },
            { 738240809, "Wish I could go back in time and tell myself." },
            { 738240810, "...I see." },
            { 738240811, "<UnknownFormatting>\"PREVIOUS CRIMINAL HISTORY: Petit larceny, grand larceny, burglary in the third degree.\"" },
            { 738240812, "Not my best angle..." },
            { 738240813, "You've certainly got an impressive record." },
            { 738240814, "Look. I've been put in some pretty crappy situations." },
            { 738240815, "<UnknownFormatting>\"Newborn Found Near Holland Tunnel\"" },
            { 738240816, "Nothing like a trip down memory lane..." },
            { 738240817, "You're still angry at your parents." },
            { 738240818, "You mean the people who dumped me by the side of the road? No. I'm not angry. I'd have to care to be angry." },
            { 738240821, "Truth?" },
            { 738240822, "What truth?" },
            { 738240823, "Guess she means the whole \"Purge of the Rheddig\" thing..." },
            { 738240824, "And Cuff had something to do with that." },
            { 738240826, "So Athia won the war..." },
            { 738240827, "...but was still screwed." },
            { 738240828, "They couldn't get along, even after all that. Kinda sucks." },
            { 738240829, "The demon poisoned our minds. And the land in turn." },
            { 738240830, "Susurrus will not rest until all Athia is laid waste." },
            { 738240831, "And now it returns with a new target: Cipal. The last bastion of Athia's humanity...and hope." },
            { 738240832, "It falls to you to protect our people. No other remains who can answer the call." },
            { 738240833, "I...I can't. I'm sorry, but...I don't have any powers. They were his all along..." },
            { 738240834, "I actually believed I was a hero for a second there. You know, that I could finally fight back." },
            { 738240835, "But no. Once again, I try to do the right thing, and the rug gets pulled right from under me." },
            { 738240836, "I thought...maybe. Maybe things could be different here. But look at me. I'm nothing." },
            { 738240837, "I'm not your last hope. I'm nobody..." },
            { 738240838, "You are blind to the power you carry within." },
            { 738240839, "Huh? What are you talking about?" },
            { 738240840, "Come, child. There is still more to learn." },
            { 738240841, "Perhaps, having learned it, you will recognize your worth..." },
            { 738240842, "Even in my darkest hour, Alfre...you were always in my heart..." },
            { 738240843, "Twenty-one long years..." },
            { 738240844, "It is time you learned the truth of the fall of Athia... The truth of your birth..." },
            { 738240846, "Huh? Is this...Junoon Castle?" },
            { 738240847, "Or am I still in Svargana...?" },
            { 738240848, "What the hell...?" },
            { 738240849, "Is this...someone's memory?" },
            { 738240850, "It is true, Robian. I am with child." },
            { 738240851, "Oh, Tanta Cinta... That's wonderful news!" },
            { 738240852, "I knew that you would share in my excitement." },
            { 738240853, "Unfortunately, there are many who will perceive this blessing as a failure on my part." },
            { 738240854, "A child is always a blessing, Tanta Cinta! Children are the hope that binds worlds together!" },
            { 738240855, "My Audie has brought me more joy than I could ever have imagined!" },
            { 738240856, "She was happy... She wanted me..." },
            { 738240857, "Is this what really happened?" },
            { 738240858, "\"New York\"... A great city in a world far from our own." },
            { 738240859, "And yet, a moment away thanks to the power of the torana. Can the father of your child truly be from such a place?" },
            { 738240860, "It was remarkable, Robian. And quite unlike Athia." },
            { 738240861, "Dazzling lights at every turn... And so many people... Such chaos, and yet...such beauty!" },
            { 738240862, "I have never seen such inventions! Incredible..." },
            { 738240863, "Daddy, this is so yummy!" },
            { 738240864, "That, my dear Auden, is a \"knish.\"" },
            { 738240865, "My time away has only strengthened my conviction." },
            { 738240866, "Athia must embrace the new. We must evolve. Only then can we grow stronger." },
            { 738240867, "This age of petty warfare must be put behind us once and for all." },
            { 738240868, "So Cinta got to New York the same way I got to Athia. And met my dad there. Who the hell was he?" },
            { 738240870, "Tanta Cinta's happy! Happy, happy, happy!" },
            { 738240872, "Tanta Cinta's busy! Stop bothering her this instant!" },
            { 738240873, "Enough, Jennesh." },
            { 738240875, "Come, my dear. Say hello if you like." },
            { 738240876, "Oh, um... Hello in there! I'm looking forward to meeting you!" },
            { 738240877, "Hm hm. And you will, soon enough. You play nicely with my little one, won't you?" },
            { 738240878, "Of course! Hee hee! I can't wait!" },
            { 738240879, "Aww. Auden was a cutie." },
            { 738240880, "It's weird seeing Athia so peaceful..." },
            { 738240881, "Can you hear it, Alfre?" },
            { 738240882, "Your father introduced me to this song." },
            { 738240883, "And I learned it so that I might sing it to you one day." },
            { 738240884, "So many beautiful sights and sounds await you when you enter this world." },
            { 738240885, "And one day, you shall know your father...a hero in every sense of the word." },
            { 738240886, "I'm sorry, Al... You deserve to know about your daughter..." },
            { 738240887, "Our darling, precious Alfre... I can hardly wait for you to meet her." },
            { 738240892, "\"Al\"... My dad's name was Al..." },
            { 738240893, "Wait, she didn't...name me after him...?" },
            { 738240894, "What's this? I feel kinda...warm inside..." },
            { 738240895, "Alfre... My beloved, my hope..." },
            { 738240896, "There is great power in you. All you need to do is look within." },
            { 738240910, "A torana?" },
            { 738240918, "Those poor people..." },
            { 738240919, "Wow. She really cared about me..." },
            { 738240920, "What is that!? A g-golden demon!?" },
            { 738240921, "Is it the Rheddig!? Have they returned!?" },
            { 738240922, "Run! Save yourselves!" },
            { 738240923, "Noooooo!!!" },
            { 738240924, "Susurrus!? It cannot be..." },
            { 738240925, "We must evacuate as many as we can! At once!" },
            { 738240926, "I will draw its attention!" },
            { 738240927, "Understood! I will lead the people to safety!" },
            { 738240928, "The wounds of war have barely healed. They shall not be reopened!" },
            { 738240929, "Tell your Rheddig masters, demon! They may strike at Athia a thousand times over—we will remain unbending to the last!" },
            { 738240930, "Guess Olas had her own ideas about how to protect Athia..." },
            { 738240931, "The Tantas were good people. Before Susurrus ruined everything..." },
            { 738240932, "Susurrus... The demon the first Tanta brought to heel. ...But how? How did it escape its bonds?" },
            { 738240933, "All we can be certain of is that it will unleash utter carnage. We must imprison it once more without delay." },
            { 738240934, "I fear a long and bloody battle lies ahead. Your child may not escape our struggle unharmed—" },
            { 738240935, "I will stop at nothing to protect my child. Nor will I permit harm to befall my people." },
            { 738240936, "Cinta... Allow me to speak not as a Tanta, but as one individual to another." },
            { 738240937, "I am happy for you. Truly, I am. So please, promise—" },
            { 738240938, "Fear not, Olas. I will not throw my life away without good reason. I have a child to think of." },
            { 738240941, "Show us your power, Alfre!" },
            { 738240942, "Prove your worth! Earn your birthright!" },
            { 738240944, "I fear Susurrus will lay waste to this place too." },
            { 738240945, "Whatever may befall this place, the power of your lanterns will ensure that the children can continue their studies." },
            { 738240946, "We may flee, but wherever we go, I know you will not allow the flame of Athia's future to be extinguished." },
            { 738240947, "Tanta Olas, what are you going to teach us today?" },
            { 738240948, "I am afraid lessons are canceled for now. You must do as your teachers instruct and prepare to evacuate." },
            { 738240949, "...Alright. But promise you'll teach us lots and lots of things next time!" },
            { 738240950, "You can count on it. After all, the future of Athia is in your hands. It is you who will keep our hopes alive." },
            { 738240956, "This is not the end, Tantas! I am your destiny!" },
            { 738240957, "What are you doing? Wh-what am I seeing?" },
            { 738240958, "The moment we sealed the demon away." },
            { 738240959, "We hoped that by dividing the demon's malice among the four of us, he might be contained. Alas, it was not to be..." },
            { 738240960, "Alfre, you are the daughter of a Tanta. You have the power of a Tanta. You need only unlock it." },
            { 738240990, "Okay, now we're in Avoalet." },
            { 738240991, "Alright, what's next?" },
            { 738240992, "Guess that's where I'm headed." },
            { 738240993, "Alright, let's see what you've got to show me." },
            { 738240994, "The binds we placed upon Susurrus appear to hold." },
            { 738240995, "But that is not why I wished to consult with you. I would speak to you of the child you choose to bear." },
            { 738240996, "A child, lest we forget, fathered by one from another world." },
            { 738240997, "Cinta, we have a duty. You, of all people, should know—" },
            { 738240998, "Our duty is to the people. And my child will serve the people. Inspire them. Give them hope." },
            { 738240999, "Athia must move forward. And thanks to her, it shall." },
            { 738241013, "I don't think anybody's ever had that much faith in me..." },
            { 738241015, "How are we to rebuild, Bellette? To restore the peace that Athia once enjoyed?" },
            { 738241016, "With our current methods, Tanta Prav? ...Perhaps. But it will not be easy." },
            { 738241017, "An admirably pragmatic response." },
            { 738241018, "I wish Cinta were half so levelheaded." },
            { 738241019, "She dreams of other worlds and the knowledge they might offer us. A reckless vision that would put Athia at risk." },
            { 738241021, "The idea is compelling, of course. But the burden of duty prevents me from indulging such fantasies." },
            { 738241022, "Tanta Prav, if I may... Perhaps there is a time for such fantasies." },
            { 738241023, "You have more than earned the trust of your people. It was you who saved us when the Rheddig invaded our lands." },
            { 738241024, "If you should seek to trust our fate to another world, then we shall not doubt you, nor the future you fight for." },
            { 738241025, "People really loved the Tantas. Guess that's why they couldn't believe it when they lost their minds..." },
            { 738241026, "They must have hoped they'd come back to their senses, no matter how crazy they went..." },
            { 738241028, "Cinta, it is clear that you mean to bear this child and raise it as your own. We accept this, but there are conditions." },
            { 738241029, "Your heir will inherit your powers, but she cannot be suffered to use them." },
            { 738241030, "Indeed. Who knows what one so young might do with gifts they could not adequately control?" },
            { 738241031, "Then let her powers be suppressed until such time as she might need them." },
            { 738241032, "But if ever such a day should come..." },
            { 738241033, "Then use of them she shall have. Let it be so." },
            { 738241034, "Very well. May this child possess indomitable strength, that they might face down any danger." },
            { 738241035, "May this child possess unfailing judgment, that they might see things fairly and truly." },
            { 738241036, "May this child thirst for knowledge and have the wisdom to use it well." },
            { 738241037, "And last, but far from least, may this child know love. May she be cherished and adored." },
            { 738241039, "I... I was born with these powers... I had them all along..." },
            { 738241041, "Another one?" },
            { 738241042, "Fight, Alfre. Find the strength within." },
            { 738241053, "Remember. Remember who you truly are." },
            { 738241054, "Remember what sleeps within you, Alfre." },
            { 738241084, "So that's how it started... He was eating away at them..." },
            { 738241085, "That's why that painting was there... Seems like a Sila thing to do alright." },
            { 738241086, "Back in Sila's domain, huh?" },
            { 738241087, "Alright. Let's see what happened next..." },
            { 738241096, "Huh... Cuff was with me when I saw it... Wonder what he was thinking..." },
            { 738241098, "Susurrus assaults us even now. He claws ceaselessly at our minds from within." },
            { 738241099, "And yet you resist him still. You are stronger than any of us." },
            { 738241100, "Any strength I have is the gift of the child within me." },
            { 738241101, "Whatever it may be, you will surely outlast me. I fear I have but a few days left..." },
            { 738241102, "When I finally succumb, the Corruption will engulf not just Praenost, but Junoon as well." },
            { 738241103, "And I had so wanted to meet the one who sleeps inside you..." },
            { 738241104, "I beg of you, Cinta—see that my people come to no harm." },
            { 738241105, "Please, Sila, do not say such things. We all must keep fighting." },
            { 738241111, "The painting of the Purge is finally complete. Where would you like us to hang it?" },
            { 738241112, "At the head of the corridor that leads from the throne room." },
            { 738241113, "Tanta Sila, is that really—?" },
            { 738241114, "It is as much a part of our history as any other. Our children must know the true cost of war. The pain. The sacrifice." },
            { 738241115, "But, Tanta Sila—" },
            { 738241116, "Do you recall the tapestry I once gave you? And what I told you on that day?" },
            { 738241117, "Yes, of course! \"True power can only be wielded by those prepared to see their duty done.\"" },
            { 738241118, "I have carried those words with me ever since." },
            { 738241119, "As you should. You will soon be made general, Dax. And with greater power will come greater sacrifice." },
            { 738241123, "Tanta Sila, please...!" },
            { 738241124, "To exhibit weakness is a crime." },
            { 738241125, "A crime punishable by death. Proceed." },
            { 738241126, "Yes, Tanta Sila!" },
            { 738241127, "Aaaaggghhh!!!" },
            { 738241128, "Hah! The pitiful die just as they live." },
            { 738241129, "And the rest! The weak must be purged, that the strong might live!" },
            { 738241130, "Someone! Heeelp!" },
            { 738241131, "Nooooo!" },
            { 738241170, "Help! Somebody, please!" },
            { 738241171, "Please! Please, not my baby...!" },
            { 738241172, "Aaaaaahhh!" },
            { 738241173, "Eeeeeekkk!" },
            { 738241174, "Th-they're turning into monsters!" },
            { 738241175, "Everyone, this way! Through the torana, quickly!" },
            { 738241192, "But where are you going, Mummy?" },
            { 738241193, "I have to go to Praenost, Audie. I'm sorry, I can't come with you." },
            { 738241194, "Your mother is going to help people. She's a hero!" },
            { 738241198, "Aaaargh!" },
            { 738241199, "Tanta Cinta, please help us!" },
            { 738241200, "Hurry! Through the torana!" },
            { 738241201, "Tanta Cinta. I must ask that you see Auden to safety." },
            { 738241202, "Are you going somewhere, Robian?" },
            { 738241203, "I mean to travel across Athia and find a way to rid us of the Corruption." },
            { 738241204, "...Very well. I fear I can do little to aid you in my current state. But I will pray for your success." },
            { 738241205, "And I will not rest until I have succeeded." },
            { 738241206, "Daddy, aren't you coming with me?" },
            { 738241207, "Not right away, Audie. But I'll be back before you know it, I promise." },
            { 738241208, "No! Don't leave me, Daddy! Daddy, please!" },
            { 738241223, "Calista" },
            { 738241224, "Dammit! Nothing..." },
            { 738241225, "My magic's gone..." },
            { 738241226, "No! Why now!?" },
            { 738241227, "Seriously? Shit!" },
            { 738241228, "No good..." },
            { 738241229, "I NEED those powers!" },
            { 738241230, "Fucking Cuff..." },
            { 738241231, "I can't do shit on my own..." },
            { 738241232, "No. Nothing." },
            { 738241233, "Thanks, Olas!" },
            { 738241234, "Okay... I might just be able to do this..." },
            { 738241235, "Gotta make it through this so I can learn the truth." },
            { 738241236, "Maybe Prav wasn't so bad..." },
            { 738241237, "I can do this. I can do this." },
            { 738241238, "Time to do what's right." },
            { 738241239, "I owe you one, Sila!" },
            { 738241240, "Damn. Sila's power's still pretty legit." },
            { 738241241, "Okay. It's time. Let's take accountability for my actions." },
            { 738241242, "This power... Is it really mine...?" },
            { 738241243, "Yeah! This is for you, Cinta!" },
            { 738241244, "Alright. I'm ready." },
            { 738241245, "Let's do this!" },
            { 738241246, "Yeah, I'm back!" },
            { 738241247, "Nice!" },
            { 738241248, "No... This isn't right." },
            { 738241249, "Uh... No." },
            { 738241250, "Maybe not right now..." },
            { 738241251, "Shit. Not this way." },
            { 738241252, "Wrong way." },
            { 738241253, "Need to turn back." },
            { 738241254, "Can't go back to Cipal without my powers..." },
            { 738241255, "Is everyone alright...? Shit, I'm so worried..." },
            { 738241256, "I'm not getting in there without Cinta's help." },
            { 738241257, "Gotta stop him." },
            { 738241258, "Fuck you, Cuff. You're not getting away with this." },
            { 738241259, "Cipal needs me..." },
            { 738241260, "What's this...?" },
            { 738241261, "Don't mind if I do." },
            { 738241262, "Nice." },
            { 738241263, "Incoming!" },
            { 738241264, "Guess we're doing this..." },
            { 738241265, "Let's go!" },
            { 738241266, "Whoa!" },
            { 738241267, "Really!?" },
            { 738241268, "Here it comes!" },
            { 738241269, "Ngh..." },
            { 738241270, "Fuck... I'm screwed..." },
            { 738241271, "Ugh... No..." },
            { 738241272, "How did this get here?" },
            { 738241273, "Might be worth dropping by again." },
            { 738241274, "Looks like there was one hell of a fight here..." },
            { 738241275, "That's a lotta bones... I've got a bad feeling about this..." },
            { 738241276, "So many bones... Did that thing do all of this...?" },
            { 738241277, "Fucker. If only that thing hadn't been here..." },
            { 738241278, "Bob could have made it back to Cipal. The Break never would have...broken him." },
            { 738241279, "So Dax saved the people who lived here..." },
            { 738241280, "An entire village... Dead..." },
            { 738241281, "Thanks, Sila. This might come in handy." },
            { 738241282, "So weird seeing Prav like this..." },
            { 738241283, "She wouldn't let them leave... That's fucked up..." },
            { 738241284, "<UnknownFormatting>\"DIPLOMA - Hudson Pier High School\"" },
            { 738241285, "Haven't seen this in a while..." },
            { 738241287, "Why are you here, Frey? Grand larceny? Is that who you really are?" },
            { 738241288, "No, it's just... I needed the cash for... Never mind." },
            { 738241289, "Sooner or later, you're going to have to start taking accountability for your actions." },
            { 738241291, "...But." },
            { 738241292, "And I didn't like it. Not one bit." },
            { 738241302, "I hope I never see the inside of a courtroom again..." },
            { 738241303, "Whoa! You okay!?" },
            { 738241304, "Oh shit... I-I have to go, I'm so sorry!" },
            { 738241305, "<UnknownFormatting>\"HOLLAND TUNNEL\"\n\"ALFRE\"" },
            { 738241306, "The Holland Tunnel... Site of my folks' great disappearing act." },
            { 738241307, "Who leaves a newborn baby on the street?" },
            { 738241308, "Well, at least it wasn't the Queens-Midtown Tunnel. That would've been an awful last name." },
            { 738241309, "Fuck! The bag!" },
            { 738241310, "Frey, what's going on?" },
            { 738241319, "Full circle." },
            { 738241320, "Happy birthday to me..." },
            { 738241321, "Thanks, Mom!" },
            { 738241322, "...No. I'm better than that. No, I'm gonna fix things. Get Homer back. Finally get out of—" },
            { 738241323, "What...?" },
            { 738241324, "Definitely no one in here..." },
            { 738241325, "Seriously, who would just leave this?" },
            { 738241327, "Guess you could call it fate." },
            { 738241328, "Whatever it was, everything changed when I picked up that bracelet." },
            { 738241329, "And that is where it all began." },
            { 738241330, "What are you doing, Frey?" },
            { 738241331, "The right thing." },
            { 738241332, "I need some time to...to sort some stuff out. But I'll come back for her." },
            { 738241333, "It just...might take a while." },
            { 738241338, "Oh, Tanta’s blessings! Our hero!" },
            { 738241339, "Uh...what?" },
            { 738241340, "Why, the Corruption has stopped! The Corruption has stopped spreading!" },
            { 738241342, "And that can only mean that something happened to the Tanta!" },
            { 738241343, "You happened!" },
