            { 738241750, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738241751, "Photo Spots" },
            { 738241752, "Take pictures at the photo spots marked on the map so you can show them to the children back in Cipal.\n\nThe more pictures you take, the more Photo Mod..." },
            { 738241753, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738241754, "Taking Pictures" },
            { 738241755, "Follow the on-screen arrows to point Frey's smartphone at the subject of a picture, and adjust the zoom to get the perfect shot.\n\nWhen you get a good ..." },
            { 738241756, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738241757, "The Tantas' Familiars" },
            { 738241758, "The Tantas' familiars will appear near the monuments to them that stand in various spots across Athia.\n\nWhen you find one, try to also find the associ..." },
            { 738241759, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738241760, "Befriending Familiars" },
            { 738241761, "The Tantas' familiars will be shy at first, and will disappear at the first hint of anything they perceive as a threat.\n\n\nHold <buttonCrouch> to get l..." },
            { 738241762, "The familiars Frey befriends will come to visit her at any Pilgrim's Refuge she stays at.\n\nAnd if she manages to get hold of certain cat-friendly item..." },
            { 738241763, "Familiars will now come and visit Frey in her room as well." },
            { 738241764, "Photo Spot" },
            { 738241765, "Familiar Statue" },
            { 738241766, "Tanta's Familiar" },
            { 738241767, "<buttonPanCamera>: Locate Subject" },
            { 738241768, "<buttonZoomIn>/<buttonZoomOut>: Zoom In/Out" },
            { 738241770, "You still need to take this many pictures: <Unknown67>" },
            { 738241771, "Thank you, old friend. I have decided on a name, you know." },
            { 738241772, "\"Alfre.\" It means \"hope.\"" },
            { 738241773, "And that is what she will be. A guiding light for all Athia." },
            { 738241774, "A hope born of two worlds, that she might bring our world together." },
            { 738241775, "May it be as you say, Tanta Cinta! May your child be the herald of a golden age!" },
            { 738241779, "Within...me? But how the...?" },
            { 738241780, "This light..." },
            { 738241781, "I told you: the power was within you all along." },
            { 738241782, "I can feel it..." },
            { 738241784, "Wise words, as always, Bellette. You are a credit to the realm." },
            { 738241786, "Whoa. Another Tanta's power..." },
            { 738241787, "Indeed. No mere demon could grant such a gift." },
            { 738241788, "Your power was awakened on the day when you came home to us at last." },
            { 738241789, "I...I don't know what to say..." },
            { 738241790, "There may come a time when your duty will demand much of you. Remember those words, and let them give you strength." },
            { 738241791, "Holy shit. She completely changed." },
            { 738241792, "That was the Sila who attacked Cipal." },
            { 738241793, "How much blood is on Cuff's hands...?" },
            { 738241794, "Here we go again." },
            { 738241795, "Believe in yourself, Alfre. Trust in your powers!" },
            { 738241796, "Cinta...I finally feel it." },
            { 738241797, "This power, it feels right. It is mine." },
            { 738241798, "Precisely. You are my blood, Alfre. You are one of us." },
            { 738241799, "Our power is yours. And it shall bind us, always." },
            { 738241800, "Always." },
            { 738241802, "But...why did she leave me behind, then? If Cinta loved me so much, why'd she let me go?" },
            { 738241803, "Let's do this." },
            { 738241804, "Where am I now?" },
            { 738241805, "This looks like...Junoon..." },
            { 738241806, "Can't believe what the Break did to this place..." },
            { 738241807, "Fuck! So many innocent people..." },
            { 738241808, "Wow, Auden's always been a sweetheart." },
            { 738241821, "This building used to be here?" },
            { 738241822, "The truth of your power... And of the choice that awaits you..." },
            { 738241823, "I have seen what can be achieved in such a world." },
            { 738241824, "And my child shall bring that world about. She shall be our hope." },
            { 738241825, "I had never been so happy as when I carried you within me... So full of hope..." },
            { 738241826, "Would that those days could have lasted forever..." },
            { 738241827, "This is...Visoria, right?" },
            { 738241828, "What's Cinta going to show me next...?" },
            { 738241829, "You shall sully Visoria no longer!" },
            { 738241830, "His powers split between the four bracelets, the creature was kept in check. For a while, at least..." },
            { 738241831, "Thanks to you, I found the strength to fight him for longer than any of the others..." },
            { 738241832, "There is no higher honor than knowing my counsel might be of service to you." },
            { 738241833, "It was we who sealed Susurrus away in the bracelets. And we who locked our power away within you." },
            { 738241834, "Even imprisoned in the bracelets we created, the demon continued to spread its Corruption, and to poison our minds." },
            { 738241835, "But you were my rock. My everything. I resisted. And at last, you were born." },
            { 738241836, "Alas, the Corruption finally crept into Junoon not long afterward. The end beckoned..." },
            { 738241837, "Come now, Auden. You must step through the torana. You will be safe there. And your father will be fine, I am sure." },
            { 738241838, "This is so hard to watch..." },
            { 738241839, "I do not have...long left..." },
            { 738241840, "Soon, I will be the last to...to turn..." },
            { 738241841, "Just a few more to save, and then..." },
            { 738241842, "I must do one last thing..." },
            { 738241843, "No... Cinta..." },
            { 738241844, "What happened to it...?" },
            { 738241846, "It's time to do the right thing." },
            { 738241847, "It's time to use my powers. For Athia." },
            { 738241848, "And you shall." },
            { 738241851, "How I would have loved to hold you... To sing to you... To stay with you forever..." },
            { 738241852, "But you had to be protected. From the demon. From me. I had no choice..." },
            { 738241853, "And I sent you away just in time. I soon became...something else. Something...unspeakable." },
            { 738241854, "...There is no more to tell." },
            { 738241861, "Approach the light." },
            { 738241869, "I can do this without him." },
            { 738241870, "Yes!" },
            { 738241871, "Alright!" },
            { 738241872, "Am I supposed to follow that thing?" },
            { 738241873, "Guess we're going that way..." },
            { 738241874, "Hey, wait! Wait up!" },
            { 738241875, "Wonder what it wants to show me..." },
            { 738241876, "Where are you taking me?" },
            { 738241877, "Gotta keep going and learn more..." },
            { 738241878, "...Onward, I guess." },
            { 738241879, "Where now?" },
            { 738241880, "Do I touch this thing...?" },
            { 738241881, "What are you trying to show me?" },
            { 738241882, "Alright, let's see what you've got." },
            { 738241883, "A torana... Must be Cinta's doing." },
            { 738241884, "Where are we going next?" },
            { 738241885, "Another one, huh?" },
            { 738241886, "I'm with you all the way." },
            { 738241887, "Feel like I'm not done here yet..." },
            { 738241888, "Think I might be missing something..." },
            { 738241889, "Let's take another look around..." },
            { 738241890, "Nothing left to find here...I think." },
            { 738241891, "Pretty sure I've seen everything there is to see here..." },
            { 738241892, "Think it's time to get moving. Better make sure I'm ready..." },
            { 738241893, "That asshole's gonna pay. Just gotta make sure I'm ready." },
            { 738241894, "Can't go there yet. There's something I need to know first..." },
            { 738241895, "He'll get his. But not before I know everything." },
            { 738241896, "When I'm ready. There's stuff I still don't know about my past." },
            { 738241897, "Guiding Light" },
            { 738241898, "A glowing ball of light that shows Frey where to go next as she learns the truth about what happened in Athia 21 years ago.\n\nWhat she doesn't know is ..." },
            { 738241899, "Crater" },
            { 738241900, "Not a trace remains of the nursery Cinta once built for baby Alfre on this very spot.\n\nCinta struggled valiantly throughout her pregnancy to withstand..." },
            { 738241901, "Frey's Choice" },
            { 738241902, "Frey's journey across Athia to learn the truth of her past ends when Cinta presents her with a choice: Will she return to New York and Homer? Or will ..." },
            { 738241903, "Lost Memories 1: Cinta's New Hope" },
            { 738241904, "In search of a way to save a struggling Athia, Cinta traveled to many worlds before she finally arrived in New York. The city's vibrancy and beauty le..." },
            { 738241905, "Lost Memories 2: Susurrus, Silenced" },
            { 738241906, "The demon of legend, Susurrus, was once bound by the very first Tanta of Athia. Years later, invaders from Rheddah found a way to free him, unleashing..." },
            { 738241907, "Lost Memories 3: A Tanta's Power Sealed" },
            { 738241908, "For as long as anyone can remember, Tantas have been forbidden from bearing children. Frey's existence presented them with a dilemma—what would a chil..." },
            { 738241909, "Lost Memories 4: Madness" },
            { 738241910, "As Susurrus's corruption gradually ate away at the Tantas, Sila approached Cinta, knowing she had only a few days left. Believing Cinta's determinatio..." },
            { 738241911, "Lost Memories 5: Junoon's Fall" },
            { 738241912, "With all the Tantas but Cinta lost to Susurrus's influence, the Corruption from their realms eventually encroached on Junoon. Cinta did her best to sa..." },
            { 738241913, "I-I know...b-but..." },
            { 738241914, "I know, Audie. I'm going to miss you, too. Just remember that I love you." },
            { 738241915, "And I love you... I...I made something for you and Daddy..." },
            { 738241916, "What's this? A bookmark?" },
            { 738241917, "Oh, Audie, it's beautiful. What a lovely picture!" },
            { 738241918, "That's the three of us, together. Forever!" },
            { 738241919, "What is this place?" },
            { 738241920, "Alfre... We have shown you the past, that you might better understand the present." },
            { 738241921, "Susurrus means to destroy Cipal, and Athia with it." },
            { 738241922, "This will be your last and hardest battle. And your last and hardest choice. It is not to be made lightly." },
            { 738241923, "This is so hard to watch..." },
            { 738241924, "We have shown you the past, Child of Cinta, that you might better understand the present." },
            { 738241925, "As we speak, Susurrus ravages Cipal." },
            { 738241926, "No! Everyone's..." },
            { 738241927, "Your fellow Athians are in grave danger. You must go to them. Cinta will take you." },
            { 738241928, "She will...?" },
            { 738241929, "The time has come to go to your mother and learn the truth." },
            { 738241930, "There is a hollow carved into the earth of Junoon. You will find Cinta there—at the former site of her greatest hope." },
            { 738241931, "And when you have learned the full truth of your birth, we shall await your final decision." },
            { 738241932, "I'll be ready." },
