            { 738242090, "Possessing this will unlock the \"Forage\" option, which will allow you to gather items when camping." },
            { 738242091, "Possessing this will allow you to earn temporary effects simply by sleeping that will help you in combat." },
            { 738242092, "Possessing this will allow you to craft new cloaks and necklaces." },
            { 738242093, "Alright, show me the way." },
            { 738242094, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738242095, "Puzzle Locks" },
            { 738242096, "Athians use intricate puzzle locks to keep their valuables safe.\n\n\nThey can be unlocked by moving the pieces in order to connect sun and moon.\n\n\nYou c..." },
            { 738242097, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738242098, "Exchanging Old Coins" },
            { 738242099, "There are people in Athia with an interest in the old coins that can be found in various places.\n\n\nThey'll offer valuable items in exchange for them, ..." },
            { 738242100, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was a kindhearted warrior who was well-love..." },
            { 738242101, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was a legendary warrior who was renowned fo..." },
            { 738242102, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was a resourceful warrior most famous for h..." },
            { 738242103, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was the commander of the first Tanta's elit..." },
            { 738242104, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was the commander of a detachment that was ..." },
            { 738242105, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was a master tactician who only rarely appe..." },
            { 738242106, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe identity of its former owner is unknown, although some c..." },
            { 738242107, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was a warrior nicknamed \"Stonewall\" for her..." },
            { 738242108, "An ancient cloak that was sealed away in the depths of one of Athia's Locked Labyrinths.\n\nThe former owner was none other than the very first Tanta. L..." },
            { 738242109, "Athian silver was once quite valuable in the days before the Break. Families who could afford to do so would often have a stockpile of these precious ..." },
            { 738242110, "An ordinary cooking pot that has been converted by a cat lover into a cushioned cat container. Though they may require a little convincing before jump..." },
            { 738242111, "A cat convenience originally designed by a carpenter who grew tired of his sharp-clawed kitten ruining his walls. Other cat owners loved the idea, and..." },
            { 738242112, "When the Break forced countless Athians to evacuate to Cipal, many brought their pets with them, and the resulting overcrowding soon made it difficult..." },
            { 738242113, "This blend of grasses was developed by a keen-eyed Cognoscent who was inspired after spotting stray cats nibbling on the weeds outside his home. After..." },
            { 738242114, "A craftsman of Cipal created this toy on a whim after catching sight of a local cat trying to play with a much larger ball meant for children. Lightwe..." },
            { 738242115, "This curious lantern possesses the ability to draw magical energy from its surroundings. It was originally designed at the behest of the Tantas, and t..." },
            { 738242116, "This magical vessel is capable of altering the fundamental qualities of natural resources. It bears traces of both the Tantas' magic and Cognoscent-de..." },
            { 738242117, "A device that uses a magnetized needle to help the user find their way. Compasses aren't exactly cutting-edge technology in Frey's world, but they are..." },
            { 738242118, "Curling up with this pillow at a Pilgrim's Refuge or campsite will grant you a temporary beneficial effect in combat, much like the ones you might ear..." },
            { 738242119, "There's nothing particularly magical about this sewing kit—Frey just feels oddly inspired whenever she looks at it. Her adventuring needs mean she mos..." },
            { 738242120, "Mystic Locks" },
            { 738242121, "These enchanted locks have been around for so long that they even feature in old Athian folk tales. It is said that someone with a magic touch must ma..." },
            { 738242122, "Create cloaks or necklaces from raw materials." },
            { 738242123, "<Unknown1> can now be crafted." },
