            { 738242130, "Book Shop" },
            { 738242131, "Cat Lover" },
            { 738242132, "Curio Collector" },
            { 738242134, "Lief" },
            { 738242135, "Puissant" },
            { 738242136, "Divers" },
            { 738242137, "Fain" },
            { 738242138, "Bonifate" },
            { 738242139, "Whilom" },
            { 738242140, "Monsterful" },
            { 738242141, "Forfend" },
            { 738242142, "Veriment" },
            { 738242143, "Whoa. Check out the Robin Hood wannabes." },
            { 738242144, "And thanks for all you did to defend my fine establishment. Not that I'd expect anything less from you." },
            { 738242145, "Anyway, just be sure to pop by when this is all over, eh? I'll be waiting behind the bar." },
            { 738242146, "Nope. Just nope. This isn't happening." },
            { 738242147, "Oh, dear..." },
            { 738242148, "I can't do this anymore..." },
            { 738242149, "Come on, hang in there...and other vaguely supportive statements..." },
            { 738242150, "You know what? I'm just not in the mood." },
            { 738242151, "Excuses, excuses..." },
            { 738242152, "The dragon, you mean? I thought so too..." },
            { 738242153, "Y'know, if I'd read this before, I would have thought the demon was Cinta." },
            { 738242154, "Well, that's a bit rude, confusing me for your scaly mother." },
            { 738242155, "Yeah, no kidding." },
            { 738242156, "Once an asshole, always an asshole." },
            { 738242157, "Oh, why, thank you. I didn't think I'd lost my touch." },
            { 738242158, "Whatever it is, I'm pretty sure I wouldn't want to run into it in a dark alley..." },
            { 738242159, "She sure went to a lot of trouble making these places." },
            { 738242160, "I hope it was worth her while..." },
            { 738242161, "Just look at this place... I wonder if he got out..." },
            { 738242162, "Don't worry. I think I got a handle on him." },
            { 738242163, "If you still believe you'll defeat me, I suggest you keep dreaming." },
            { 738242164, "What's this?" },
            { 738242165, "What's what? That piece of old rubbish?" },
            { 738242166, "Hey, a partha! All the way out here." },
            { 738242167, "Well, Frey? Feeling lucky today?" },
            { 738242168, "Another partha." },
            { 738242169, "A common find, apparently." },
            { 738242170, "Shit. Looks like some kind of lock." },
            { 738242171, "You know some magic now. Perhaps you can simply will it open." },
            { 738242172, "Aaand it's locked." },
            { 738242173, "Well? Use a spell, blast it open!" },
            { 738242174, "Aw, man. Not another lock!" },
            { 738242175, "You're a hard worker, I'll give you that." },
            { 738242176, "Gotta unlock this too..." },
            { 738242177, "Happy lock-picking!" },
            { 738242178, "Frey, would you mind going and taking a closer look at that tower?" },
            { 738242179, "Uh, sure." },
            { 738242180, "I think it might help us get a better sense of our surroundings." },
            { 738242181, "You don't expect me to climb that, do you?" },
            { 738242182, "Some kind of lookout tower?" },
            { 738242183, "You're on Sila's turf now. I imagine her minions will be coming after you with a vengeance." },
            { 738242184, "Those insane soldiers, you mean?" },
            { 738242185, "The very same. Try not to get murdered, won't you?" },
            { 738242186, "I'll see what I can do." },
            { 738242187, "Still no sign of any ballow trees..." },
            { 738242188, "Which means we gotta go all the way to the castle town, right?" },
            { 738242189, "If Prav doesn't find you before you can get there, yes." },
            { 738242190, "I'm not fighting any more Tantas." },
            { 738242191, "There's no telling what Olas might throw at you. Keep your wits about you." },
            { 738242192, "Don't worry—I'm not about to get tricked by another one of her illusions." },
            { 738242193, "I'll raise the alarm if I see anything suspicious." },
            { 738242194, "Thanks. That would actually be helpful." },
            { 738242195, "Are you here for any reason in particular?" },
            { 738242196, "Nah, not really." },
            { 738242197, "A thought occurs..." },
            { 738242198, "Uh-huh?" },
            { 738242199, "Wouldn't \"Vambracea\" be a lovely name for this particular part of the world?" },
            { 738242200, "Uh...no." },
            { 738242201, "Anything left you were planning on doing?" },
            { 738242202, "Gee, I dunno. Fixing whatever else you fucked up?" },
            { 738242203, "Well, it's certainly nice to see that you've lost none of your fire." },
            { 738242204, "Just do what I tell you when I tell you, okay?" },
            { 738242205, "Nice doing business with you!" },
            { 738242206, "Sorry, looks like you're short of coins!" },
            { 738242207, "Thank you so much for saving the city!" },
            { 738242214, "Officer, please remove her cuffs." },
            { 738242216, "Gotta find Homer first!" },
            { 738242217, "Lisa did tell me I'd burn..." },
            { 738242218, "And now I had nothing. But I wasn't about to let Homer suffer for my mistakes." },
            { 738242219, "At least make it challenging..." },
            { 738242220, "That was a cinch." },
            { 738242221, "Boooring!" },
            { 738242222, "Poor lock never stood a chance." },
            { 738242223, "Click. Next!" },
            { 738242224, "You've got quite good at this." },
            { 738242225, "That went well." },
            { 738242226, "I just keep getting better!" },
            { 738242227, "You're passable, I suppose." },
            { 738242228, "Done!" },
            { 738242229, "I think that does it..." },
            { 738242230, "Oof. That was kinda tough." },
            { 738242231, "That was a tricky one." },
            { 738242232, "Ugh, what a pain." },
            { 738242233, "There'd better be something good inside..." },
            { 738242234, "Yes! Finally!" },
            { 738242235, "Well done, I suppose." },
            { 738242236, "Geez. That one took forever..." },
            { 738242237, "Surely the universe will reward us for your efforts?" },
            { 738242238, "Whew. I might need to close my eyes for a sec..." },
            { 738242239, "Well, that was exhausting." },
            { 738242240, "I think that one might have melted my brain..." },
            { 738242241, "You've done us both proud with your lock-picking prowess." },
            { 738242242, "But I was not ready to hear it." },
            { 738242243, "Switch Map" },
            { 738242244, "Talkative Breakzombie" },
            { 738242245, "Curio Collector" },
            { 738242246, "Nothing tickling your fancy, eh? Maybe next time, then." },
            { 738242247, "Nothing for you? Perhaps another time, then!" },
            { 738242248, "Going so soon?" },
            { 738242249, "Welcome to my showroom of the singular and strange!" },
            { 738242250, "Come, come! Let me see you up close!" },
            { 738242251, "Back to inspect my collection of curios?" },
            { 738242252, "Ah, that reminds me—Auden made Robian a bookmark once, many years ago. He treasured that gift more than anything..." },
            { 738242254, "Are you sure you want to end the flashback?" },
            { 738242255, "GAMEPLAY" },
            { 738242256, "Belfries" },
            { 738242257, "Perform a Cuff Scan (press <buttonCuffScan>) at any of the belfries located across Athia, and you'll be able to get an overview of the entire area.\n\nT..." },
            { 738242258, "As the Corruption spread, what did she do? She simply vanished!" },
            { 738242260, "Not the happiest of fellows, eh?" },
            { 738242262, "You knew Cinta had a child. Did you know it was me?" },
            { 738242263, "So we kept it to ourselves. Me, Robian, and as small a number of her retinue as was possible." },
            { 738242267, "Where was she when the worst of the Corruption came? When terror tore through the populace like a plague?" },
            { 738242276, "End your current flashback and return to the Monument to Wisdom." },
            { 738242277, "And I suppose you had no choice but to make crappy decisions." },
            { 738242279, "After years in the foster system, you're mad." },
            { 738242280, "No, you know what? It was super fun being tossed from home to home." },
            { 738242281, "And yet in spite of all that, you finished high school. You're smart." },
            { 738242282, "But now? You're just taking the easy way out." },
            { 738242283, "That was close... That judge might have just saved my ass..." },
            { 738242284, "Won't get that lucky again..." },
            { 738242285, "Hey! Excuse me! Your phone!" },
            { 738242286, "Oh, my gosh! Thank you so much!" },
            { 738242287, "No worries. Happens to all of us." },
            { 738242288, "You've saved my life, seriously. Happy holidays!" },
            { 738242289, "Um, happy holidays..." },
            { 738242290, "I should get back to Homer. Poor girl needs her dinner." },
            { 738242291, "うわっ" },
            { 738242292, "Alright. Homer's safe." },
            { 738242293, "Now what am I gonna do...?" },
            { 738242294, "I had to clear my head, so I started walking and didn't stop. And somehow, I ended up right back where it all began." },
            { 738242295, "Was I looking for answers? Or was I...led there? Not sure l'll ever know..." },
            { 738242296, "To think it would come to this..." },
            { 738242297, "That's right—we were abandoned! Junoon was left to rot by the very woman charged with protecting it!" },
            { 738242298, "Why Jennesh, of all people..." },
            { 738242299, "That's not true! I saw her evacuating the—" },
            { 738242300, "For years, it tormented me: Why did she abandon us? But when I realized who you were...I knew." },
            { 738242301, "She left us to die so that she could save you." },
            { 738242302, "That's..." },
            { 738242303, "I do not expect you, of all people, to understand." },
            { 738242304, "That old fool Robian might have done, I suppose." },
            { 738242305, "So Cinta didn't tell you about him? That he was from another world?" },
            { 738242306, "As I said, I know nothing of the sort. ...But he must have made an impression on your mother." },
            { 738242307, "One significant enough to cause her to lose sight of her obligations." },
            { 738242308, "This song..." },
            { 738242309, "Cinta's lullaby..." },
            { 738242312, "This thing might be old, but it's pretty damn comfy." },
            { 738242313, "Let's hope it doesn't fall apart the moment you move, shall we?" },
            { 738242314, "Mmm. Almost like a warm, fuzzy blanket..." },
            { 738242315, "I'm...sure that's an appropriate comparison." },
            { 738242316, "Something tells me you like that cloak." },
            { 738242317, "Yeah. Feels sorta...me." },
            { 738242318, "I don't know how you can bear to put on such dusty old relics." },
            { 738242319, "It's called vintage, Cuff. Look it up sometime." },
            { 738242320, "I don't think this has been worn much at all..." },
            { 738242321, "Perhaps its original owner wasn't hugely fond of it." },
            { 738242322, "It's your time to shine, little cloak." },
            { 738242323, "I cannot imagine what occasion might suit such a garment..." },
            { 738242324, "You're really going to wear that?" },
            { 738242325, "You're really trying to tell me how to dress now?" },
            { 738242326, "Time for a new look!" },
            { 738242327, "Do you know, I actually don't mind it." },
            { 738242328, "Why put that on now?" },
            { 738242329, "I dunno. Because I feel like it?" },
            { 738242330, "This thing's a bona fide antique." },
            { 738242331, "Bric-a-brac at best, I'd say." },
            { 738242332, "Vintage gold. I like it." },
            { 738242333, "Yes. Until it falls to pieces." },
            { 738242334, "I might actually go as far as to say that suits you." },
            { 738242335, "Whoa. What got into you?" },
            { 738242336, "I'm feeling this right now. Don't question it." },
            { 738242337, "I absolutely shall." },
