            { 738242415, "What, this? I just found it lying around the town." },
            { 738242416, "Exit" },
            { 738242417, "Belfries" },
            { 738242418, "These beautiful bell towers were erected as landmarks to help pilgrims find their way. The bells are not merely ornamental—they once served as a means..." },
            { 738242419, "Ancient Altar: Inscription 1" },
            { 738242420, "To those who would seek to serve Athia:\n\nOnce, the people of Rheddah were our allies.\n\nThis changed the day they sent a demon to our land.\n\nIt fed on ..." },
            { 738242421, "Ancient Altar: Inscription 2" },
            { 738242422, "To those who would seek to serve Athia:\n\nSusurrus filled our skies with fire and ash.\n\nThe mere sound of the creature's wings filled our hearts with c..." },
            { 738242423, "Ancient Altar: Inscription 3" },
            { 738242424, "To those who would seek to serve Athia:\n\nFor six days and six nights, I fought the demon.\n\nThe fields around us blazed like vast seas of fire.\n\nFinall..." },
            { 738242425, "Ancient Altar: Inscription 4" },
            { 738242426, "To those who would seek to serve Athia:\n\nThough Susurrus was weakened, he was not yet destroyed.\n\nI contained him for a time so that the people might ..." },
            { 738242427, "Ancient Altar: Inscription 5" },
            { 738242428, "To those who would seek to serve Athia:\n\nIf given the chance, Susurrus will return.\n\nBut I will not let this come to pass.\n\nI shall construct these la..." },
            { 738242429, "Ancient Altar: Inscription 6" },
            { 738242430, "To those who would seek to serve Athia—my Tantas:\n\nSusurrus is sealed within this chamber and others like it throughout the land.\n\nI pray that my bind..." },
            { 738242431, "3/14/3874: Writings of a Rheddig Soldier 1" },
            { 738242432, "We received the orders the second we made landfall. That in itself was unusual—I thought we'd have longer to get our bearings. But they say we're to l..." },
            { 738242433, "3/18/3874: Writings of a Rheddig Soldier 2" },
            { 738242434, "We have learned that the Athians call these dungeons \"locked labyrinths.\" Apparently, none of them are permitted inside—save for their Tantas, of cour..." },
            { 738242435, "3/22/3874: Writings of a Rheddig Soldier 3" },
            { 738242436, "Received a response from the commander today. It set me reeling. He thinks the strange objects we found were left here by Athia's first Tanta. But he ..." },
            { 738242437, "3/27/3874: Writings of a Rheddig Soldier 4" },
            { 738242438, "The mission is going well. We've retrieved several parts of the ancient weapon. We are to bring what we've found so far to a specific location, but as..." },
            { 738242439, "3/29/3874: Writings of a Rheddig Soldier 5" },
            { 738242440, "Crisis averted. We discovered that some of the first Tanta's inscriptions contained instructions on how to dismantle the weapon. Obviously, we had to ..." },
            { 738242441, "4/3/3874: Writings of a Rheddig Soldier 6" },
            { 738242442, "We suffered significant casualties today. Traps set by the Tanta that we did not foresee. We were extricating a part of the weapon, and we were excite..." },
            { 738242443, "4/6/3874: Writings of a Rheddig Soldier 7" },
            { 738242444, "I am a proud soldier of the army of Rheddah, and this will likely be the end of my story.\n\nWith today's success, we have collected nearly every piece ..." },
            { 738242445, "<colorTextRed>You cannot do this now.<colorEnd>\n<colorTextGrey><buttonCuffScan> Scan Your Surroundings<colorEnd>\n<colorTextRed>You cannot currently do..." },
            { 738242446, "Spellcraft Challenge" },
            { 738242447, "And we're right back where we started. Why did you bring me back here, Cinta? I mean, I want to know what happened to Athia—and to me—but what's with ..." },
            { 738242448, "December 22, A Courthouse in New York" },
            { 738242449, "Get the gym bag." },
            { 738242450, "Get out of the apartment." },
            { 738242451, "Overcome Cinta's trial." },
