            { 738243182, "There are twenty familiars in total.\nApproach them as carefully as you can, otherwise they'll turn tail and run." },
            { 738243183, "There are fifty photo spots in total.\nSee what scenic sights you can find as you roam the wilds of Athia." },
            { 738243184, "There are 105 spells in all to upgrade.\nYou can upgrade them in various ways, including via the books that can be found at Pilgrim's Refuges." },
