            { 738243195, "Partha" },
            { 738243196, "Materials acquired!" },
            { 738243198, "You are about to begin the final battle with Susurrus.\nMake sure you've done everything you need to do in Athia and made all the necessary preparation..." },
            { 738243200, "The spell you have selected is currently in use. As such, you can't convert it back to mana right now." },
            { 738243210, "Maybe I just imagined that stupid voice..." },
            { 738243211, "It was probably just the wind. After all, what could there possibly be worth finding out here in the middle of nowhere?" },
            { 738243212, "Frey..." },
            { 738243219, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243220, "Frey..." },
            { 738243221, "Whoa. What the...?" },
            { 738243222, "If you wish to save Athia, you must first know its past..." },
            { 738243223, "Wh-what are you talking about?" },
            { 738243228, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243229, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243230, "Ugh... Where am I?" },
            { 738243231, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243232, "Are they all...dead?" },
            { 738243233, "It would appear so..." },
            { 738243234, "Okay, that's it. I'm never trusting my Tanta instinct again." },
            { 738243235, "What am I wearing...?" },
            { 738243236, "Thalia..." },
            { 738243237, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243238, "You have to...run..." },
            { 738243239, "\"Thalia\"? Who's Thalia?" },
            { 738243240, "I think he was talking to you." },
            { 738243241, "He must have mistaken me for somebody else..." },
            { 738243257, "Place is crawling with soldiers..." },
            { 738243258, "You!" },
            { 738243259, "Shit!" },
            { 738243260, "Stop right there!" },
            { 738243261, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243262, "Stay back unless you wanna get hurt!" },
            { 738243263, "Alright..." },
            { 738243264, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243265, "Fuck! Fuckfuckfuckfuck! My magic's not working!" },
            { 738243266, "Well, if you're not you anymore, perhaps you don't have any..." },
            { 738243267, "You've gotta be kidding me." },
            { 738243268, "Wha...?" },
            { 738243269, "ちょっと！" },
            { 738243270, "Hold her still." },
            { 738243271, "Hey! Stop! Agh!" },
            { 738243272, "Get off! Don't touch me!" },
            { 738243273, "What is that!?" },
            { 738243274, "Frey..." },
            { 738243275, "You again? Who the hell are you?" },
            { 738243276, "I am the one who brought you here, that you might bear witness to the past." },
            { 738243277, "So we really did go back in time? Why? What do you want from me?" },
            { 738243278, "You seek answers." },
            { 738243279, "And here, you might begin to find them..." },
            { 738243280, "What? What are you talking about?" },
            { 738243281, "There is much for you to learn." },
            { 738243282, "For now, know this: You cannot change what has already come to pass." },
            { 738243283, "Change it? I don't even—" },
            { 738243284, "Now go..." },
            { 738243285, "Ah. Finally awake." },
            { 738243286, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243287, "Oh, great. This day just keeps getting better..." },
            { 738243288, "Indeed. We're in a dungeon somewhere beneath Visoria Castle." },
            { 738243289, "Oh, fuck. That guy... What did he do to me, anyway?" },
            { 738243290, "What is this, Cuff, a tattoo?" },
            { 738243291, "Sadly, I have no idea." },
            { 738243292, "Although I wouldn't know a \"tattoo\" if it bit me on the leg..." },
            { 738243293, "Great. Useful as ever." },
            { 738243294, "Well, I heard the voice again. It said it brought me here to...find answers..." },
            { 738243295, "I know. I heard it too." },
            { 738243296, "But I'm pretty sure we won't be finding any down here." },
            { 738243297, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243298, "Agreed. And I don't think we're getting out of here without any magic." },
            { 738243299, "Oh, surely you can't be out of ideas? Not the venerable Tanta Frey?" },
            { 738243300, "Hold on a second, aren't you supposed to be tight with the Rheddig? Why didn't you say something?" },
            { 738243301, "Need I remind you? Nobody else can hear me." },
            { 738243302, "And even if they could, I'm not sure how wise it would be to reveal your invisible friend." },
            { 738243303, "Wow, \"friends.\" That is...something." },
            { 738243304, "[Laughs]" },
            { 738243305, "...Fuck. I wish I had some magic!" },
            { 738243306, "Did I just do that?" },
            { 738243307, "At least there aren't any guards around." },
            { 738243308, "Not that we can see, anyway..." },
            { 738243311, "Huh? Was that...an earthquake...?" },
            { 738243312, "Whatever it is, I don't imagine it's good..." },
            { 738243323, "Frey, pull yourself together!" },
            { 738243324, "Why can't I...?" },
            { 738243325, "（バリアで攻撃を防ぐアドリブ）" },
            { 738243326, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243327, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243328, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243329, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243330, "Mom...?" },
            { 738243331, "Excuse me?" },
            { 738243332, "I mean—uh, Tanta Cinta?" },
            { 738243333, "What's your name?" },
            { 738243334, "Uh... Good question. Um—" },
            { 738243335, "So you are Thalia..." },
            { 738243336, "Olas was right..." },
            { 738243337, "What?" },
            { 738243338, "No matter. Come, we must leave this place." },
            { 738243339, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243340, "Where are we going?" },
            { 738243341, "Hold on a second!" },
            { 738243342, "What is it?" },
            { 738243343, "Sorry, I just...I have no idea what the hell is happening. Care to enlighten me?" },
            { 738243344, "...Fine. But we do not have much time." },
            { 738243345, "Um, so...did Olas ask you to come find me or something?" },
            { 738243346, "Is that so surprising? You were part of her guard, no?" },
            { 738243347, "Right. Yeah, her guard, that's, uh...yup." },
            { 738243348, "But uh, why send a Tanta to find one soldier? Don't you have more important things to do?" },
            { 738243349, "I...was bound for Visoria already. To assess the Rheddig threat." },
            { 738243350, "I offered to help you as a favor to Olas, nothing more." },
            { 738243351, "This is the oldest part of the city." },
            { 738243352, "It was built by Visoria's very first Tanta. She dwelt here with her subjects." },
            { 738243353, "Does anyone live here now?" },
            { 738243354, "No. The Cognoscents conducted their research here for a time, but few have ventured down here in recent years." },
            { 738243355, "At least...until the Rheddig arrived." },
            { 738243356, "What's with those guys, anyway?" },
            { 738243357, "You refer to the Rheddig?" },
            { 738243358, "Yeah. Why'd they attack Athia in the first place?" },
            { 738243359, "Were you not briefed on the invasion?" },
            { 738243360, "Uh...they did something to me when they caught me. Yeah, it...messed with my memory." },
            { 738243361, "I see... Well, no one is entirely sure why they are here. But..." },
            { 738243362, "But what?" },
            { 738243363, "We fear this may be more than a mere act of conquest." },
            { 738243364, "As to what their true intent might be...that we have yet to discover..." },
            { 738243365, "So where are the other Tantas?" },
            { 738243366, "Sila and Prav battle tirelessly to defend their realms from the Rheddig." },
            { 738243367, "Olas lends her aid where she can, and though the tide of battle has begun to turn in our favor..." },
            { 738243368, "Our position is precarious, and our advantage too small to count on." },
            { 738243369, "I see..." },
            { 738243370, "Have you heard enough?" },
            { 738243371, "Uh...yeah. Well, for now, at least." },
            { 738243372, "Good. Then come. There is no time to waste." },
            { 738243378, "Phew... A win's a win, I guess..." },
            { 738243379, "Your power..." },
            { 738243380, "Kinda groovy, right? I dunno what it is, exactly—but I just know I can use it." },
            { 738243381, "...I see." },
            { 738243382, "Is something wrong?" },
            { 738243383, "N-no, not at all. Just...tell me if you start to feel...unwell." },
            { 738243384, "Why would I feel \"unwell\"?" },
            { 738243385, "It's nothing to worry about. Just tell me. Agreed?" },
            { 738243386, "I guess..." },
            { 738243387, "Good. Then let's keep moving." },
            { 738243388, "You think she knows something about the magic? Or the tattoo?" },
            { 738243389, "Maybe. But it doesn't seem like she's in a sharing mood..." },
            { 738243390, "So this body belongs to a soldier named Thalia." },
            { 738243391, "Not just any soldier—a member of Olas's personal guard, no less." },
            { 738243392, "And Olas was too busy fighting to come help me herself." },
            { 738243393, "Good thing, I guess—wouldn't be hanging out with my mom if she had..." },
            { 738243394, "Did you say something?" },
            { 738243395, "Oh, no. Just, uh...thinking out loud." },
            { 738243401, "So the Rheddig have completely taken over Visoria?" },
            { 738243402, "Unfortunately, yes. They mounted an attack while our forces were concentrated elsewhere." },
            { 738243403, "Frankly, we were unprepared for the mettle they have shown." },
            { 738243404, "I met one of their generals earlier. At least I think he was." },
            { 738243405, "He, uh, stuck a...thing in my arm, and now I've got this weird tattoo—" },
            { 738243406, "Aldacor. One of their most formidable warriors." },
            { 738243407, "And if the rumors are to be believed, a man with a keen interest in human experimentation." },
            { 738243408, "Ooh. I think I'd like to get to know the good general a little better." },
            { 738243413, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243414, "Heeelp! Help meee!" },
            { 738243416, "There is no time!" },
            { 738243417, "But—" },
            { 738243418, "Aaahhh!!!" },
            { 738243419, "Quickly!" },
            { 738243420, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243421, "What was that thing!?" },
            { 738243422, "It is the result of one of Aldacor's experiments." },
            { 738243423, "Aldacor makes Breakbeasts!?" },
            { 738243424, "Shit!" },
            { 738243435, "Hey! That guy back there, how could you just leave him—" },
            { 738243436, "Now's not the time." },
            { 738243437, "...Fine." },
            { 738243438, "Is something the matter?" },
            { 738243439, "I was...thinking about before. That guy... How easy it was for Cinta to just abandon him..." },
            { 738243440, "She was trying to get you to safety." },
            { 738243441, "You can't save everyone, Frey. She made a choice. I don't see anything wrong with that." },
            { 738243442, "Yeah, you wouldn't." },
            { 738243443, "Do you think the Rheddig really can make Breakbeasts?" },
            { 738243444, "Well, they did make me. And I'd say that requires a lot more finesse." },
            { 738243445, "I guess. Just can't imagine anyone wanting to do something like that..." },
            { 738243446, "You sound almost scared. Surely not? The mighty Tanta Frey?" },
            { 738243447, "Wonder if this has something to do with what the voice was talking about..." },
            { 738243448, "Let's see what else we can learn about the Rheddig. Could tell us what we need to finally get rid of the Break." },
            { 738243449, "Rest if you must. You will need all of your strength if we're to make it out of here." },
            { 738243457, "This must be what is causing the crystals to grow." },
            { 738243458, "If we can destroy it, perhaps we will finally be able to leave." },
            { 738243459, "...The fuck am I looking at here?" },
            { 738243460, "That's the work of the Rheddig." },
            { 738243461, "What did you do to all these people?" },
            { 738243462, "We honored them. They gave their lives that this benighted land might be cleansed of sin." },
            { 738243463, "Oh, cut it with the cult crap, you fucking psycho!" },
            { 738243464, "Peace, child. You, too, shall be honored this day..." },
            { 738243465, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243467, "Did he just...break himself!?" },
            { 738243473, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243474, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243475, "Alright, let's see what happens when we destroy this thing." },
            { 738243476, "Ngh! Agh!!" },
            { 738243477, "Th-Thalia? What's wrong?" },
            { 738243478, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243479, "No... It's too soon!" },
            { 738243480, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243481, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243482, "Huh... I feel...stronger somehow..." },
            { 738243483, "Are you alright?" },
            { 738243484, "Yeah. Almost...better than before." },
            { 738243485, "Oh. Good." },
            { 738243486, "That's good. I'm glad to hear it." },
            { 738243487, "What do you think that guy meant? All that shit about \"honor\" and \"sin\"?" },
            { 738243488, "I got the sense those people were killed as some sort of sacrifice." },
            { 738243489, "Well that's not foreboding at all." },
            { 738243490, "Perhaps if you can find out why the Rheddig were sacrificing them, you might learn something useful." },
            { 738243491, "Yeah, maybe..." },
            { 738243492, "If I could learn how to control the Break like them...maybe it would help me save Athia." },
            { 738243493, "Yes. That, or it might consume you utterly..." },
            { 738243498, "Where are we?" },
            { 738243499, "Nearly there." },
            { 738243500, "Okay..." },
            { 738243501, "We must keep moving. This way." },
            { 738243515, "Imagine being so obsessed with guarding a tree." },
            { 738243516, "You shall not interfere with the rite!" },
            { 738243517, "Any news of the other realms?" },
            { 738243518, "The Tantas and their armies are putting up quite a fight, I hear." },
            { 738243528, "Gah...!" },
            { 738243529, "Okay... Glad that's over..." },
            { 738243530, "At least you're a little stronger for your efforts." },
            { 738243552, "Tantas be praised... You saved us..." },
            { 738243553, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243554, "Shit! It's gonna kill them all!" },
            { 738243555, "Tanta Cinta! Help us, please!" },
            { 738243556, "Get yourself to safety. Y-you'll be alright. Go!" },
            { 738243557, "Come. This way, to the tree." },
            { 738243558, "Hold on! You're a Tanta. Isn't it your job to keep everyone safe?" },
            { 738243559, "……（無言のアドリブ）" },
            { 738243560, "Help! Somebody, help!" },
            { 738243561, "Fine! You know what, I'll do it myself." },
            { 738243562, "Don't be a fool. You'll be killed." },
            { 738243563, "Just stay out of my way!" },
            { 738243564, "Well. That was a flashy exit." },
            { 738243565, "Oh shut up." },
            { 738243566, "Please tell me you're not actually going to do this. It's suicide." },
            { 738243567, "I thought I told you to shut up." },
            { 738243568, "Save us!" },
            { 738243569, "Please! I don't want to die!" },
            { 738243572, "This is going pretty well! I actually might not die!" },
            { 738243573, "Oh, that's reassuring." },
            { 738243574, "Aaah! Get away from me!" },
            { 738243575, "Shit!" },
            { 738243576, "Run!" },
            { 738243577, "Cinta? Man, am I glad to see you—" },
            { 738243578, "Please! ...Not now." },
            { 738243580, "Cinta, look. I know I said some shit before—" },
            { 738243581, "I saved you only because your death would cause more trouble than you know." },
            { 738243582, "Ha ha ha! What a delightful surprise." },
            { 738243583, "Welcome to Visoria, Tanta Cinta! I dare say it might have changed a bit since last you visited." },
            { 738243584, "......" },
            { 738243585, "Hey! Mister Tattoo Artist! What's the deal with this shit, huh?" },
            { 738243586, "Oh, my, my. Quite the cooperative vessel, aren't you? Saving me so much time and energy..." },
            { 738243587, "The fuck's that supposed to mean?" },
            { 738243588, "A better question would be why this noble Tanta is so hell-bent on saving one soldier when there is a war going on?" },
            { 738243589, "Okay, what's going on here? What are you not telling me?" },
            { 738243592, "Forgive me, I can't say." },
            { 738243593, "Oh, but where are my manners?" },
            { 738243594, "It must be so distressing to finally have to tell your charge the truth for a change. So please, allow me." },
            { 738243595, "It's really quite simple, girl: your beloved Tanta is planning to kill you." },
            { 738243596, "...That's not possible. She saved me. Again!" },
            { 738243597, "……(どう伝えるべきか悩むアドリブ）" },
            { 738243598, "Cinta, say something!" },
            { 738243599, "Your esteemed Tantas have stopped the Gloaming once, but they shall not do so a second time." },
            { 738243600, "Preparations are nearly complete. The end is at hand." },
            { 738243601, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243602, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243603, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243604, "Is it true?" },
            { 738243605, "...Yes." },
            { 738243606, "But why? And stop with the lying and the hiding shit, a-and just tell me the truth!" },
            { 738243609, "Very well." },
            { 738243610, "If I don't kill you before the day is through..." },
            { 738243611, "What?" },
            { 738243612, "Those markings—they mean you are now a weapon." },
            { 738243613, "We don't understand quite how, but...once marked, it's only a matter of time before the subject..." },
            { 738243614, "Before you explode...with cataclysmic force." },
            { 738243615, "You're saying I'm some kind of...bomb?" },
            { 738243616, "My task was to find you. Escort you someplace far away, and then..." },
            { 738243617, "Once there...at a safe distance from the people of Athia..." },
            { 738243618, "I know this...this must be difficult for you to hear, but us Tantas, we weighed up all our possible options..." },
            { 738243619, "Your death was the only way to avoid countless others." },
            { 738243620, "So that's why you were in such a rush to get out of there...and why you didn't stop to save those people." },
            { 738243621, "They would have died anyway. And so many others. Because of me..." },
            { 738243622, "It wasn't an easy choice to make." },
            { 738243623, "But nor are many we must make as Tantas. Sometimes we soil our hands with blood." },
            { 738243624, "All is for Athia. And no price is too great to pay." },
            { 738243625, "I get it." },
            { 738243626, "...You do?" },
            { 738243627, "I, uh...made a pretty big mistake once." },
            { 738243628, "Ooh! Are we talking about me?" },
            { 738243629, "I made a promise to never make that kind of mistake again." },
            { 738243630, "So if it means protecting the people of Athia, then...do it. Kill me." },
            { 738243631, "Thalia..." },
            { 738243632, "I beg your pardon!?" },
            { 738243633, "And, uh...thank you. For being honest with me." },
            { 738243634, "Would you mind if I asked you a few questions?" },
            { 738243635, "Please. I only hope I can tell you what you wish to know." },
            { 738243636, "So, just to be clear...these markings mean I'm some kind of Rheddig weapon, right?" },
            { 738243637, "And I'm stuck this way? Just...boom? No more Thalia?" },
            { 738243638, "It pains me to say it, but yes." },
            { 738243639, "You may recall Aldacor mentioning the Gloaming. It is a ceremony conducted at sunset." },
            { 738243640, "At its completion—or if you die before it's completed—you will...explode." },
            { 738243641, "Fuck. Okay, um...do you know why the mark spread to my other arm?" },
            { 738243642, "I do not. But your powers have grown as it has." },
            { 738243643, "Could this indicate a more devastating result when the inevitable finally occurs...?" },
            { 738243644, "Whoa, whoa, okay, hang on. If I explode, I kill everyone around me, right? Wouldn't that include the Rheddig themselves?" },
            { 738243645, "It would. And yet, seemingly they wish it nonetheless. I cannot pretend to understand their motives." },
            { 738243646, "Geez. What do they put in the water over there?" },
            { 738243647, "Why does it not surprise me that the concept of commitment is utterly alien to you?" },
            { 738243648, "How did you know to come and find me?" },
            { 738243649, "The Rheddig have attempted to perform the Gloaming once before." },
            { 738243650, "We managed to stop them...but only just." },
            { 738243651, "So I'm not the first person they've done this to." },
            { 738243652, "No. There was another. And she, too, I was forced to...eliminate..." },
            { 738243653, "When Olas sensed that another vessel had been created...I knew that I must do my duty once again." },
            { 738243654, "And by \"duty\" you mean...killing me. Right." },
            { 738243655, "What exactly is Aldacor trying to achieve?" },
            { 738243656, "By bringing about the Gloaming?" },
            { 738243657, "I do not know. But I worry we are perilously close to finding out." },
            { 738243658, "What even is the Gloaming? It can't just be about blowing me up?" },
            { 738243659, "No. I fear it cannot." },
            { 738243660, "There must be...more to it than simply that..." },
            { 738243661, "Why do I get the feeling I don't wanna find out?" },
            { 738243662, "So are these marks on my arms the reason I can use magic?" },
            { 738243663, "I believe so. At least, I cannot think what else might explain your newfound powers." },
            { 738243664, "Hmm... So why do you think destroying the tree's roots made me stronger?" },
            { 738243665, "I can only speculate. There was no tree, and no crystals, the last time the ceremony was performed..." },
            { 738243666, "Could you, uh...tell me a little about yourself?" },
            { 738243667, "What could you possibly wish to know?" },
            { 738243668, "Well, I just...I don't have much time left. Thought I'd try and get to know you while I can." },
            { 738243669, "Very well. What would you like to know?" },
            { 738243670, "Um, oh, I dunno... Let's see... Did you...ever maybe want to start a...family...?" },
            { 738243671, "A Tanta is not permitted to bear children. Surely you know this." },
            { 738243672, "Yeah, of course, but...if you take off your Tanta hat for just a second." },
            { 738243673, "Well, were I not a Tanta...I imagine having a family might be a rather wonderful thing." },
            { 738243674, "But I am a Tanta. Therefore such considerations are irrelevant." },
            { 738243675, "But...you're the Tanta of Love, aren't you?" },
            { 738243676, "Don't you think experiencing a mother's love for her child might maybe...add some perspective?" },
            { 738243677, "That would be a betrayal of my duty to Athia." },
            { 738243678, "Okay, okay, I get it. I just never had a mom, and...I dunno, you seem like you'd be a good one to have." },
            { 738243679, "That's an unusual compliment." },
            { 738243680, "Well, that's all I got, so...let's go kick Aldacor's ass and take back Visoria." },
            { 738243681, "Thalia... You do realize how this ends? I will have no choice but to—" },
            { 738243682, "Kill me. I know. But, well...Athia's my home too. So you do what you gotta do to keep it safe. Now let's go." },
            { 738243687, "Are we inside the castle?" },
            { 738243688, "Yes. Olas showed me this passage some years ago." },
            { 738243689, "It should lead us outside—perhaps we can find a way to the top from there." },
            { 738243690, "Can't wait to find Aldacor. Guy deserves a solid kick in the ass." },
            { 738243691, "Heh. He does indeed." },
            { 738243693, "Frey? Frey. You aren't seriously going to let Cinta kill you, are you?" },
            { 738243694, "What's the matter? Is big, bad Susurrus afraid?" },
            { 738243695, "Of you dying? No. Of being left here? Absolutely." },
            { 738243696, "I refuse to sit festering in the corpse of a nobody from yesteryear." },
            { 738243697, "I'm touched by your concern." },
            { 738243709, "Finally! I was worried you might have a change of heart." },
            { 738243710, "The Gloaming. What does it do?" },
            { 738243711, "It destroys Athia, of course." },
            { 738243712, "With the help of a vessel—that's you—and a flourishing Tree of Offering—like the one you see before you." },
            { 738243713, "What the hell does that mean?" },
            { 738243714, "My, has it flourished, thanks to you. You wouldn't believe the amount of life force this takes!" },
            { 738243715, "I had feared—despite my best efforts to secure a healthy supply—that there simply wouldn't be enough." },
            { 738243716, "But then you two came along, and you started killing all my soldiers...and voilà. Death begets life." },
            { 738243717, "Are you saying we helped you?" },
            { 738243718, "Oh, yes! And in more ways than one!" },
            { 738243719, "You were a perfectly adequate vessel before, but..." },
            { 738243720, "Thanks to the power you've absorbed, the Gloaming will now leave Athia with deeper wounds than we ever dreamed of!" },
            { 738243721, "All we need do...is await the inevitable. For when the core shines its brightest, the Gloaming will come to pass!" },
            { 738243722, "I am afraid we cannot allow that." },
            { 738243723, "Your wretched ceremony will fail. As will you!" },
            { 738243724, "Do you mean to challenge me?" },
            { 738243725, "Then I will show you what we Rheddig are truly capable of!" },
            { 738243726, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243727, "Still convinced of your chances!?" },
            { 738243728, "Fuck. It talks." },
            { 738243729, "Ooh. Can I turn into one of those?" },
            { 738243730, "How does he conjure up such power!?" },
            { 738243731, "Now... Come to me! And despair!!!" },
            { 738243732, "Not sure I like being this popular!" },
            { 738243733, "They are no match for us if we work together!" },
            { 738243734, "Alright—huh? Where's the guy with the wings?" },
            { 738243735, "He ventured further upward after summoning his friends." },
            { 738243736, "Y'know, I've been thinking..." },
            { 738243737, "What if dying here doesn't actually mean dying?" },
            { 738243743, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243744, "ぐぬ……" },
            { 738243745, "It's over, Aldacor." },
            { 738243746, "It is over. But not for me." },
            { 738243749, "In the name of Rheddah, I bid you, Demon! Rise!!!" },
            { 738243750, "Aaaahhh!" },
            { 738243751, "Thalia!" },
            { 738243752, "う……くっ……！" },
            { 738243754, "What are you doing!?" },
            { 738243755, "Whatever I can!" },
            { 738243756, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243757, "Aaaggghhhhhh!" },
            { 738243758, "It's no...use...!" },
            { 738243759, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243760, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243761, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243762, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243763, "Cinta..." },
            { 738243764, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738243765, "I thought the Gloaming failed... Did it not?" },
            { 738243766, "Thalia, forgive me... I thought I could save you..." },
            { 738243767, "It's okay... Cinta... Listen..." },
            { 738243768, "Something bad is gonna happen. I don't know when, but...soon..." },
            { 738243769, "When it does...promise me you won't lose hope." },
            { 738243770, "Thalia, it's alright. You don't have to—" },
            { 738243772, "...Alright. I promise." },
            { 738243773, "Okay... I'd say it's been a blast, but..." },
            { 738243774, "Am I...?" },
            { 738243775, "Back. In your own time." },
            { 738243776, "Did I... Did Thalia die?" },
            { 738243777, "Yes. Her final moments were the beginning of the end." },
            { 738243778, "You saw the bird. Thus was Susurrus called forth." },
            { 738243779, "But what does that mean? Did Thalia become Susurrus?" },
            { 738243780, "No. As Aldacor said, she was merely a vessel." },
            { 738243781, "And though Cinta tried her hardest, she was not able to prevent his return." },
            { 738243782, "His power grew over the years that followed...until Athia faced total destruction at his hand..." },
            { 738243783, "Stirring stuff. I'd shed a tear if I were able." },
            { 738243784, "But where did Susurrus even come from? Aldacor couldn't have made him." },
            { 738243785, "Indeed. No mortal could have created such an abomination." },
            { 738243786, "Susurrus owes his existence to a far more terrifying power." },
            { 738243787, "A \"more terrifying power\"?" },
            { 738243788, "Interesting..." },
            { 738243789, "Hold—I-I don't even know who I'm talking to! Who are you!?" },
            { 738243790, "I...am one of the Tantas of Rheddah." },
            { 738243791, "Say what?" },
            { 738243792, "The answers you seek lie beyond Athia's borders. Come to me. I will be waiting." },
            { 738243793, "Wait, no—wait, just hold on—can you just—" },
            { 738243794, "...Great. Well, Cuff, I hope you're ready for a trip to Rheddah." },
