            { 738244270, "Flotsam and Jetsam" },
            { 738244271, "A cloak that sometimes restores health when critical hits are inflicted on enemies." },
            { 738244272, "A cloak that reduces the duration of negative status effects." },
            { 738244273, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Taking \"photographs\" of Athia with your \"smartphone\"? I struggle to even comprehend what that might mean, but I'd imagine you have ..." },
            { 738244274, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Ahh, the sight of their smiling little faces... Priceless. Probably. You certainly looked pleased, anyway. Which is a surprise, giv..." },
            { 738244275, "<iconChapterSumVfx>You've really thrown yourself into this vista-capturing lark, haven't you? Well, the children seem very happy with your efforts. Wh..." },
