            { 738245053, "Aldacor Unbound" },
            { 738245074, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Some \"Tanta instinct\" you've got. Well, in case you were too stupefied to pay attention, I believe you've somehow taken over someon..." },
            { 738245075, "<iconChapterSumVfx>That was quite a nap you took. Must be nice to be so insouciant... Now, if we could put the ramblings of that insufferable voice as..." },
            { 738245076, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Ah, a family reunion. Quite the dysfunctional family, really, given you're not actually you and your mother doesn't know you exist...." },
            { 738245077, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Did that Aldacor fellow really make this beauty? I must say, not bad for a day's work, even if it's not a patch on my own true form..." },
            { 738245078, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Well, that was a little close for comfort. I don't really want to find out what happens to us if you get this Thalia person killed...." },
            { 738245079, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Sacrificing one's humanity for the sake of one's cause... Now that's what I call commitment. Still, this would be rather a dismal p..." },
            { 738245080, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Hmm... Is it just me, or did that rootlike thing react to your \"tattoo\"? Well, at least it's made you stronger. And it looks like w..." },
            { 738245081, "<iconChapterSumVfx>How have we still not seen any sunlight? Surely the surface must be close by now. I believe your new spells have put some pep in yo..." },
            { 738245082, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Splendid. Trapped in Visoria by a tree, of all things. Well, Cinta seems to think you should try hacking at its roots, so knock you..." },
            { 738245083, "<iconChapterSumVfx>My countrymen have certainly kept themselves busy sacrificing all these townsfolk. Can't blame them for trying to protect their han..." },
            { 738245084, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Only one root to go, I see. Someone must be pleased with themselves. That Aldacor doesn't seem particularly concerned, though. I do..." },
            { 738245085, "<iconChapterSumVfx>The energy from those roots has certainly made you stronger. I assume that's why your \"tattoo\" has gotten all the more...striking. ..." },
            { 738245086, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Ah, a familiar face. The creature seems to have taken a liking to you, wouldn't you say? I still think this is suicide, by the way...." },
            { 738245087, "<iconChapterSumVfx>\"Kill me\"!? I beg your pardon? How could you possibly know Thalia would have done the same thing? Now I know for sure you've really..." },
            { 738245088, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Are you quite done with your touching mother-daughter chat? I must be the only one with a sense of urgency in this place. Look, I d..." },
            { 738245089, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Hello, Frey. It's me. Your unwilling companion. Still here, still convinced you've utterly lost your mind. You don't know that dyin..." },
            { 738245090, "<iconChapterSumVfx>Aldacor's certainly got some tricks up his sleeve. Not that he's anywhere near as awe-inspiring as my magnificent self. Well, this ..." },
            { 738245092, "Press <buttonHealthDraught> to restore health." },
