            { 738245447, "Thalia's Grave" },
            { 738245448, "Here lies the unsung hero of Visoria, who freed her beloved home from the Rheddig's cruel occupation. Thalia was no ordinary soldier, but a member of ..." },
            { 738245449, "The Strange Tale of Susurrus" },
            { 738245450, "In a time long past, we found ourselves at war with our neighbors from Rheddah. We thought the war all but ended when we drove them from our shores, n..." },
            { 738245453, "You! Where do you think you're going?" },
            { 738245454, "Another one! Seize her!" },
            { 738245461, "Memo 1: The Island Explosion" },
            { 738245462, "We did exactly as the general asked, but it wasn't enough. The damned Tantas appeared out of nowhere... It was their fault the rite failed. The explos..." },
            { 738245517, "Cynognathus" },
            { 738245518, "Another earthquake! ...Huh?" },
            { 738245519, "Careful!" },
            { 738245520, "It's stopped..." },
            { 738245521, "I sense...trouble ahead..." },
            { 738245522, "Yeah. I'm not sure I want to know what kind..." },
            { 738245533, "What the hell am I looking at?" },
            { 738245534, "The root we destroyed must have belonged to the tree." },
            { 738245535, "Geez... Did not expect a magic beanstalk..." },
            { 738245536, "A what?" },
            { 738245537, "The vines have entirely enclosed the town. No one can get in or out." },
            { 738245600, "Oh... I thought I was a goner for sure..." },
            { 738245602, "Tanta Cinta! I knew you would come for us!" },
            { 738245603, "Whoa. It's on my left arm now, too." },
            { 738245604, "Could it be somehow connected to your powers improving?" },
            { 738245605, "Peculiar..." },
            { 738245611, "Fuck! What now!?" },
            { 738245612, "Bit smarter than your garden-variety Breakbeast, isn't it?" },
            { 738245613, "It's shielding itself!" },
            { 738245614, "You'll have to find another way to hurt it." },
            { 738245615, "I'm barely doing anything...!" },
            { 738245620, "Fuck! Not again!" },
            { 738245621, "We know what to do this time!" },
            { 738245622, "On second thought...I think I'm good." },
            { 738245623, "Oh. Very well." },
            { 738245624, "Are you ready?" },
            { 738245625, "I'm ready." },
            { 738245626, "Not just yet." },
            { 738245627, "I... I think I... I think I need a minute." },
            { 738245628, "I understand." },
            { 738245629, "You ready?" },
            { 738245639, "Look out!" },
            { 738245640, "Too good for us, huh? I'll show Mister High and Mighty..." },
            { 738245641, "Maybe it just means I get sent back to our time." },
            { 738245642, "Since when were you an optimist?" },
            { 738245643, "Listen, this is the past. So this has all already happened, right?" },
            { 738245644, "And if we can't fight it, we might as well just go along for the ride." },
            { 738245645, "I, for one, would very much like to get off the ride." },
            { 738245646, "Sorry, pal. We're in this together." },
            { 738245647, "Hey! It's them!" },
            { 738245648, "The flying dude still won't come down and face us?" },
            { 738245649, "I get the sense that they wish to test our mettle first..." },
            { 738245651, "Nice! Let's keep going!" },
            { 738245652, "I expect our winged friends will have more surprises in store." },
            { 738245653, "It'll take a lot of surprises to stop us." },
            { 738245654, "I believe it would." },
            { 738245656, "What if this was what the voice wanted all along...?" },
            { 738245657, "What could you possibly be babbling about now?" },
            { 738245658, "Maybe this is how we learn what we're supposed to do about the Break." },
            { 738245659, "Remember the good old days when you didn't trust anything you were told?" },
            { 738245660, "Two of them!?" },
            { 738245661, "We're almost there! Finish them!" },
            { 738245662, "On it!" },
            { 738245663, "More of them!" },
            { 738245664, "Not for long!" },
            { 738245665, "Guess we're finally worth their time." },
            { 738245666, "Steel yourself—these are truly formidable foes." },
            { 738245667, "Roger that." },
            { 738245668, "That's gotta be all of 'em. Now for Aldacor..." },
            { 738245669, "Why do I feel that we are being led by our noses...?" },
            { 738245670, "What do you mean?" },
            { 738245671, "...Nothing. Come." },
            { 738245682, "Home sweet home. I'm sure the horrors awaiting us won't be too life-threatening..." },
            { 738245683, "A great beast of war created by General Aldacor by experimenting on Athian creatures with Rheddig magical ore. It is far lighter on its feet than its ..." },
            { 738245686, "Winged Sentinel" },
            { 738245687, "Healing Draught" },
            { 738245722, "You can't save while using a belfry." },
            { 738245723, "Start the battle again from the beginning." },
            { 738245724, "End the current battle?" },
            { 738245725, "Start the current battle again from the beginning?" },
            { 738245726, "Defeat the enemy." },
            { 738245727, "GAME SYSTEMS" },
            { 738245728, "Prav's \"Glide\" Spell" },
            { 738245729, "This spell manipulates gravity, allowing you to skim across the surface of water, moving much more quickly than you would by simply swimming.\n\n\nPress ..." },
            { 738245730, "Press and Hold <buttonMovement> + <buttonParkour> to Try Using the Glide Spell" },
            { 738245731, "Check the Map" },
            { 738245732, "You can't perform a Cuff Scan without Cuff!" },
            { 738245733, "To Be a Tanta" },
            { 738245734, "Make your way to the surface." },
            { 738245735, "Destroy the roots of the Tree of Offering." },
            { 738245736, "Destroy the roots of the Tree of Offering (2 remaining)." },
            { 738245737, "Destroy the roots of the Tree of Offering (1 remaining)." },
            { 738245738, "Reach the top of the tree." },
            { 738245739, "Defeat the Rheddig monstrosity." },
            { 738245740, "Speak to Cinta." },
            { 738245741, "Leave the room when you're ready." },
            { 738245748, "Whatever power it possesses also seems to be suppressing my own..." },
            { 738245749, "Do you think there's something at the top? Maybe we should check it out." },
            { 738245750, "Let us find its remaining roots first. We might be able to weaken its power." },
            { 738245751, "Sounds like a plan." },
            { 738245752, "Mere floundering. Our victory will come soon enough." },
            { 738245753, "Indeed. We need only do as the general commands." },
            { 738245754, "And we shall—even should he command that we lay down our very lives." },
            { 738245755, "Now for the next two. How are you feeling?" },
            { 738245756, "Like I could kick more butt and then some." },
            { 738245757, "More bodies..." },
            { 738245758, "There will be time to mourn later. For now, we must destroy that root." },
            { 738245759, "...Those assholes are going to pay." },
            { 738245760, "Fuck. Just how many people have they killed...?" },
            { 738245761, "Careful. Guards." },
            { 738245762, "We must eliminate them." },
            { 738245763, "My pleasure." },
            { 738245764, "And now for the root itself." },
            { 738245765, "On it." },
            { 738245766, "I hate this. This is so fucked up..." },
            { 738245767, "Whatever they're up to, it certainly seems to require a lot of...honoring." },
            { 738245768, "They're not getting away with this." },
            { 738245770, "The Tree demands more offerings!" },
            { 738245771, "Round up every last Athian in Visoria!" },
            { 738245772, "All must be sacrificed for the cause!" },
            { 738245777, "Let us destroy this one and move on to the next." },
            { 738245780, "Just one more..." },
            { 738245781, "They will be expecting us. We must hurry." },
            { 738245788, "Are you hurt?" },
            { 738245789, "I'm alright... Thank you, thank you!" },
            { 738245790, "Tanta Cinta! You've come to save us!" },
            { 738245791, "...Find somewhere to hide until it is safe." },
            { 738245792, "Don't worry, okay? We're gonna get rid of all the bad guys." },
            { 738245793, "..." },
            { 738245794, "Tanta's blessings be upon you!" },
            { 738245795, "Thanks! You're our hero!" },
            { 738245796, "It's nothing. And I'm no hero." },
            { 738245797, "You doing okay?" },
            { 738245798, "Mm-hm! I knew one of the Tantas would come!" },
            { 738245803, "Come. Let us destroy the abominable thing." },
            { 738245805, "Let's clean 'em up!" },
            { 738245807, "This can be changed later via the SETTINGS menu." },
            { 738245808, "Standard setting that focuses on achieving a stable frame rate at 4k." },
            { 738245809, "Enables ray tracing, offering beautiful, graphically enhanced visuals." },
            { 738245810, "Lowers resolution in order to achieve a higher frame rate." },
            { 738245812, "The setting you choose won't affect how the story unfolds.\n\nYou'll also be able to change it any time you like (except for during events/battle) via t..." },
            { 738245813, "Focus on the Story" },
            { 738245814, "Recommended for players who just want to enjoy watching the game's narrative unfold." },
            { 738245815, "Explore the Open World" },
            { 738245816, "Recommended for players who want to visit every corner of the game world." },
            { 738245817, "Take Part in Challenging Battles" },
            { 738245818, "Recommended for players who are used to playing action games." },
            { 738245819, "Default" },
            { 738245820, "Recommended for players who want to enjoy a balance of all gameplay elements." },
            { 738245821, "All changes except those made to the difficulty level will be reflected in your saved data." },
            { 738245822, "DECREASED" },
            { 738245823, "SIGNIFICANTLY DECREASED" },
            { 738245824, "Highlight Nearby Characters" },
            { 738245828, "Set this to \"ON\" to make nearby characters and enemies more visible." },
            { 738245834, "Magic Parkour Sprinting" },
            { 738245838, "DEFAULT\nTrigger by holding <buttonMovement> + <buttonParkour>. Continues until effect wears off.\nTOGGLE\nTrigger by holding <buttonMovement> + <buttonP..." },
            { 738245839, "Leap/Soar Controls" },
            { 738245843, "DEFAULT\nMove toward a wall while in midair and press <buttonMovement> + <buttonParkour>.\nSEMI-AUTO\nMove toward a wall using <buttonMovement> while per..." },
            { 738245844, "Sprint Button" },
            { 738245848, "<buttonSprint>\nRun by using <buttonSprint>.\n<buttonSprint>/<buttonParkour>\nRun with <buttonParkour> when magic parkour is not available." },
            { 738245854, "Automatic Support Spell-Switching" },
            { 738245858, "When this is set to \"ON,\" you'll automatically switch to support spells that aren't currently subject to cooldown." },
            { 738245859, "Auto-Evasion" },
            { 738245863, "When this is set to \"ON,\" you'll automatically evade using magic parkour when attacked." },
            { 738245864, "Automatically Use Healing Items" },
            { 738245868, "When this is set to \"ON,\" you'll automatically use healing items when low on health." },
            { 738245869, "Enemy Knockdown Time" },
            { 738245873, "Adjust how long enemies will take to get back up when knocked to the ground." },
            { 738245877, "DEFAULT" },
            { 738245878, "TOGGLE" },
            { 738245879, "DEFAULT" },
            { 738245880, "SEMI-AUTO" },
            { 738245881, "DEFAULT" },
            { 738245882, "EXTENDED" },
            { 738245883, "Thalia—the Rheddig will be expecting us..." },
            { 738245884, "Let me guess: Don't be too hasty, don't rush in...right?" },
            { 738245885, "Not at all. I trust you will do the right thing. I merely wished to say that my strength is yours should you require it." },
            { 738245886, "...Is it just me, or has she softened up a little?" },
            { 738245887, "I cannot tell you how little your blossoming bond interests me." },
            { 738245888, "That Frey would never have chased a strange voice back through time in the first place..." },
            { 738245891, "Language/Subtitles" },
            { 738245892, "Haptics" },
            { 738245893, "Input" },
            { 738245894, "HUD" },
            { 738245895, "Use Skip (<buttonSkipButton1alt><buttonSkipButton2><buttonSkipButton1>) to evade attack." },
            { 738245896, "<Unknown67>/<Unknown71>" },
            { 738245899, "<varChapterNum>%" },
            { 738245900, "Press <buttonAttackMagic> to Try Out Prav's magic" },
            { 738245907, "This way." },
            { 738245908, "Follow me." },
            { 738245909, "Come now, quickly." },
            { 738245910, "I'm coming, I'm coming..." },
            { 738245911, "Not that way." },
            { 738245912, "Oh. Oops." },
            { 738245913, "Where are you going?" },
            { 738245914, "Sorry. Got turned around." },
            { 738245915, "Are you sure this leads to the surface?" },
            { 738245916, "Yes. I came this way myself mere hours ago." },
            { 738245917, "Although there were considerably fewer soldiers before, so we must be careful." },
            { 738245927, "Brave warriors of Rheddah!" },
            { 738245928, "Visoria Castle is fallen! The Tree of Offering overflows with the essence of those who have been honored!" },
            { 738245929, "All proceeds as ordained! The Gloaming approaches! You know what you must do—all sacrifice shall be rewarded." },
            { 738245930, "Their general is certainly quite the orator." },
            { 738245931, "Pfft. Talk it up while you can, asshole." },
            { 738245932, "DURING PARKOUR ONLY" },
            { 738245933, "ALWAYS" },
            { 738245934, "<buttonSprint>" },
            { 738245935, "<buttonSprint>/<buttonParkour>" },
            { 738245939, "Control layout has been customized." },
            { 738245941, "Choose a function to customize." },
            { 738245942, "Press the button you wish to assign." },
            { 738245943, "The spell you have selected must not currently be equipped. You also cannot convert spells back to mana while in the middle of performing an action." },
            { 738245944, "SEMI-TRANSPARENT" },
            { 738245945, "OPAQUE" },
            { 738245946, "PURGE OF THE RHEDDIG" },
            { 738245947, "BEFORE THE MARKING" },
            { 738245948, "UNDERGROUND CASTLETOWN PART2" },
            { 738245949, "WAKE IN UNDERGROUND DUNGEON" },
            { 738245950, "EXPLORE UNDERGROUND DUNEGON" },
            { 738245951, "BATTLE WITH RHEDDIGS" },
            { 738245952, "TOGETHER WITH CINTA" },
            { 738245953, "AFTER AQUEDUCT" },
            { 738245954, "FIRST BATTLE WITH CINTA" },
            { 738245955, "BEFORE CHIMERA" },
            { 738245956, "ENCOUNTER CHIMERA" },
            { 738245957, "CAVE AFTER CHIMERA" },
            { 738245958, "BEFORE PALADIN" },
            { 738245959, "AFTER ABSORB ROOT" },
            { 738245960, "DLC CHAPTER 01-1" },
            { 738245961, "DLC CHAPTER 01-2" },
            { 738245962, "Button" },
            { 738245963, "Investigate the unusual light." },
            { 738245965, "Frey was discovered by the enemy..." },
            { 738245978, "<buttonZip>: Use Swing" },
            { 738245981, "This \"vessel\"...that's me, isn't it?" },
            { 738245982, "I rather think it might be, yes." },
            { 738245983, "Well, I don't know about you, but I feel great about this." },
            { 738245984, "Nice work, Mom." },
            { 738245985, "Seems they thought their little barrier was Tanta-proof..." },
            { 738245986, "Guess we know who they're talking about here..." },
            { 738245987, "The creature's no...me, but I must admit to being something of an admirer." },
            { 738245988, "Guess that explains why Olas isn't home." },
            { 738245989, "And while she was away, that home was overrun. Hardly a strategic victory..." },
            { 738245990, "Weird machines that create illusions..." },
            { 738245991, "I think we might have come across one or two of those." },
            { 738245992, "Figuring that shit out musta been a real headache..." },
            { 738245993, "Well, they certainly seem to have had the leisure to do so. Alright for some..." },
            { 738245994, "Wow. She made them to teach people..." },
            { 738245995, "Isn't it wonderful how idealists always manage to do the most damage?" },
            { 738245996, "How come every new invention ever gets turned into a weapon sooner or later?" },
            { 738245997, "So that immaculate creations such as myself can come into being, of course." },
            { 738245998, "They still fought like hell even without Olas here to lead them." },
            { 738245999, "Yes, for...gosh, all of five minutes." },
            { 738246000, "Yeah, this Aldacor guy doesn't fuck around." },
            { 738246001, "He certainly seems formidable. Almost as formidable as yours truly..." },
            { 738246002, "Makes me sick..." },
            { 738246003, "The strong survive while the weak are trampled. A tale as old as time..." },
            { 738246004, "Sounds like they put up a hell of a fight..." },
            { 738246005, "Yes. Right up until they were slaughtered by the Rheddig. Every last one of them." },
            { 738246006, "He has a rather poetic turn of phrase, don't you find?" },
            { 738246007, "Sure, if you're into batshit fanaticism." },
            { 738246008, "Seriously, is anyone ever gonna tell me what the hell is up with this tree?" },
            { 738246009, "Whatever it does, it certainly seems important to our Rheddig friends..." },
            { 738246010, "Non-Tantas using magic? Is that a good idea?" },
            { 738246011, "It's a wonderful idea! Think of the chaos it will cause!" },
            { 738246012, "Sure, just \"sacrifice\" yourself for your \"noble cause.\" What's a life, anyway?" },
            { 738246013, "A small price to pay in exchange for ultimate power..." },
            { 738246014, "Look, I love a horror story as much as the next girl, but...this is a lot." },
            { 738246015, "It's fun imagining their terrified screams of agony though, isn't it?" },
            { 738246016, "These guys are members of Olas's personal guard too, right?" },
            { 738246017, "...Ex-members. Extremely \"ex.\"" },
            { 738246018, "None of them got away. Not a single one..." },
            { 738246019, "A plan that keeps people in as well as out. Ingenious..." },
            { 738246020, "Aw, more \"offerings.\" How quaint." },
