            { 738246671, "Oh, I do so wish I was able to help..." },
            { 738246672, "This could be tricky..." },
            { 738246673, "Not if we work together." },
            { 738246674, "We might be in for a rough ride here..." },
            { 738246675, "Try not to overextend yourself." },
            { 738246676, "I got a bad feeling about this..." },
            { 738246677, "Just don't go rushing in without a plan." },
            { 738246678, "She knows you so well already." },
            { 738246679, "Be very careful, Thalia." },
            { 738246680, "I'll try..." },
            { 738246681, "Better buckle up for this one..." },
            { 738246682, "Just try to remain calm." },
            { 738246683, "Oh, this one will definitely hurt." },
            { 738246684, "Alright. Cut it with the commentary." },
            { 738246685, "You know what to do, Thalia!" },
            { 738246686, "You bet!" },
            { 738246687, "What do you think?" },
            { 738246688, "I think we've already won!" },
            { 738246689, "We're in this to win this!" },
            { 738246690, "I suppose we do make quite a team." },
            { 738246691, "You seem like you're struggling..." },
            { 738246692, "Pfft. Struggling? Who's struggling...?" },
            { 738246693, "Ugh! Come on already!" },
            { 738246694, "Stay focused. Learn to observe your enemy." },
            { 738246695, "Is it just me, or are you huffing and puffing already?" },
            { 738246696, "It's just you, asshole." },
            { 738246697, "Please let this be over already..." },
            { 738246698, "A good soldier never complains." },
            { 738246699, "Shit, thought this would be over by now..." },
            { 738246700, "Endurance is just as important as strength." },
            { 738246701, "You're letting the enemy get the better of you." },
            { 738246702, "I'm trying! They're just...so...annoying!" },
            { 738246703, "And here I was thinking this would be a breeze..." },
            { 738246704, "And what have you contributed, exactly?" },
            { 738246705, "Stay strong, Thalia. We can do this." },
            { 738246706, "Yeah..." },
            { 738246707, "Thalia, are you alright?" },
            { 738246708, "Hanging in there somehow!" },
            { 738246709, "Think it's about time we wrapped this up!" },
            { 738246710, "Then let's show them what we're made of." },
            { 738246711, "How are there still more of them!?" },
            { 738246712, "Don't lose focus now!" },
            { 738246713, "Is this not over yet? Really?" },
            { 738246714, "Really. Now hurry up and finish them off." },
            { 738246715, "Geez, just give up already!" },
            { 738246716, "Less complaining!" },
            { 738246717, "Bring it on, bitches. I'll just keep slaying your ass!" },
            { 738246718, "You certainly sound...confident." },
            { 738246719, "It's not over yet!" },
            { 738246720, "I got this! We got this!" },
            { 738246721, "Fuuuck. Leave me alone already..." },
            { 738246722, "I certainly didn't expect there to be this many." },
            { 738246723, "And how are we doing? Feeling good? Feeling sprightly?" },
            { 738246724, "Shut up!" },
            { 738246725, "So many of them..." },
            { 738246726, "And still no match for us." },
            { 738246727, "Thalia? Are you still feeling alright?" },
            { 738246728, "Don't worry about me! Plenty of gas left in the tank!" },
            { 738246729, "If I have to kill one more of you, I'm gonna scream!" },
            { 738246730, "...Please don't." },
            { 738246731, "Does literally everybody want to kill us?" },
            { 738246732, "Luckily, we're far more capable than them." },
            { 738246733, "We can always run if you're tired of fighting." },
            { 738246734, "Me? Run? Oh, I'm just getting started!" },
            { 738246735, "Come on, admit it. You miss my help, don't you?" },
            { 738246736, "The only thing I miss is the silence when you're not talking." },
            { 738246737, "Remember: adapt your approach to the enemy at hand." },
            { 738246738, "Yes, Tanta Cinta." },
            { 738246739, "Ugh, fuck these guys for what they've done to Visoria!" },
            { 738246740, "Anger will only cloud your vision." },
            { 738246741, "Don't be too hasty, Thalia." },
            { 738246742, "I know, I know. I'll be careful." },
            { 738246743, "Ugh, I'm so mad. Why would the Rheddig hurt so many innocent people?" },
            { 738246744, "Civilians or soldiers, it doesn't matter to them. They've set out to kill every last Athian." },
            { 738246745, "At least you're getting better at fighting as Thalia." },
            { 738246746, "Still much rather be good old Frey, thanks." },
            { 738246747, "Are they seriously gonna chase us all the way up this tree?" },
            { 738246748, "Not if we knock them down to the ground." },
            { 738246749, "They appear to have rallied the troops." },
            { 738246750, "For all the good it's gonna do them..." },
            { 738246751, "Shit... How many more of these guys do we have to take out?" },
            { 738246752, "Stay with me, Thalia. We're nearly there." },
            { 738246753, "Now, Thalia!" },
            { 738246754, "Just tell me when!" },
            { 738246755, "Say the word, Thalia!" },
            { 738246756, "Let us combine our strength!" },
            { 738246757, "We must strike them! Now!" },
            { 738246758, "Now's our chance!" },
            { 738246759, "I'm ready, Thalia!" },
            { 738246760, "Might wanna duck!" },
            { 738246761, "Sucks to be you!" },
            { 738246762, "See ya!" },
