            { 738246841, "That looked like it hurt!" },
            { 738246842, "As it should have." },
            { 738246843, "Appreciate that!" },
            { 738246844, "I appreciate your gratitude." },
            { 738246845, "Well, that went nicely." },
            { 738246846, "More than just \"nicely.\"" },
            { 738246847, "Out of the way!" },
            { 738246848, "Someone's a badass." },
            { 738246849, "You deserve no mercy." },
            { 738246850, "You tell 'em, Tanta of Love!" },
            { 738246851, "Whoa! Nice one!" },
            { 738246852, "Why, thank you, Thalia." },
            { 738246853, "Yeah, just like that!" },
            { 738246854, "...Precisely." },
            { 738246855, "You can count on me." },
            { 738246856, "Did I mention you're awesome?" },
            { 738246857, "Don't just stand there!" },
            { 738246858, "I'm not! I swear!" },
            { 738246903, "Now's your chance, Thalia!" },
            { 738246904, "All yours!" },
            { 738246905, "Now, Thalia!" },
            { 738246906, "Quickly!" },
            { 738246907, "Thalia, if you please!" },
            { 738246908, "The rest is up to you!" },
            { 738246909, "Strike while you can!" },
            { 738246910, "Next!" },
            { 738246911, "Yes!" },
            { 738246912, "Nice!" },
            { 738246913, "Bye!" },
            { 738246914, "Yeah!" },
            { 738246915, "Bam!" },
            { 738246916, "Sorry!" },
            { 738246917, "はっ" },
            { 738246918, "Alright!" },
            { 738246919, "Keep 'em coming!" },
            { 738246920, "Now, Cinta!" },
            { 738246921, "Take it away!" },
            { 738246922, "Go get 'em!" },
            { 738246923, "Now!" },
            { 738246924, "Make 'em hurt!" },
            { 738246925, "Do it!" },
            { 738246926, "Hell yeah!" },
            { 738246927, "Not bad." },
            { 738246928, "Bye-bye now!" },
            { 738246929, "That should do it." },
            { 738246930, "See ya later!" },
            { 738246931, "I hope we don't." },
            { 738246932, "Nighty-night!" },
            { 738246933, "And may you never wake again." },
            { 738246934, "Some of my best work!" },
            { 738246935, "Glad to hear it." },
            { 738246936, "This'll be an easy win!" },
            { 738246937, "Do not get too carried away..." },
            { 738246938, "Might I offer some critique on your technique?" },
            { 738246939, "No." },
            { 738246940, "I think I just kicked some ass." },
            { 738246941, "...Quite possibly." },
            { 738246942, "We literally can't lose!" },
            { 738246943, "Thalia..." },
            { 738246944, "Good riddance!" },
            { 738246945, "My thoughts exactly!" },
            { 738246946, "Nice job, Cinta!" },
            { 738246947, "You didn't do so badly yourself." },
            { 738246948, "Admit it. That was pretty cool." },
            { 738246949, "Yes, if only you'd planned it that way..." },
            { 738246950, "Excellent work, Thalia." },
            { 738246951, "Uh, wow. Thanks." },
            { 738246952, "That was awesome!" },
            { 738246953, "I've certainly seen worse." },
            { 738246954, "How about that?" },
            { 738246955, "It was rather nice." },
            { 738246956, "Remarkable technique." },
            { 738246957, "Yeah, I thought so too." },
            { 738246958, "Someone got lucky." },
            { 738246959, "Then why am I stuck with you?" },
            { 738246960, "Thanks for backing me up!" },
            { 738246961, "Just returning the favor!" },
            { 738246962, "Way to get in there!" },
            { 738246963, "I could say the same to you!" },
            { 738246964, "Just like clockwork!" },
            { 738246965, "I'm proud of us both." },
            { 738246966, "That's a win!" },
            { 738246967, "And an easy one, at that." },
            { 738246968, "Well, that was quick." },
            { 738246969, "All the better." },
            { 738246970, "Good. Let's keep moving." },
            { 738246971, "Yeah. Let's do it." },
            { 738246972, "At least make me work for it!" },
            { 738246973, "Complacency is the real enemy." },
            { 738246974, "Kinda wanted a challenge..." },
            { 738246975, "Be careful what you wish for." },
            { 738246976, "Come. There is no time." },
            { 738246977, "Again with the rushing..." },
            { 738246978, "We had better be on our way. Ready?" },
            { 738246979, "As I'll ever be." },
            { 738246980, "Aaaand done." },
            { 738246981, "You're certainly getting stronger." },
            { 738246982, "Really? That's it?" },
            { 738246983, "Be thankful, Thalia." },
            { 738246984, "You're doing much better than I anticipated." },
            { 738246985, "Uh, thanks? ...I think." },
            { 738246986, "I can't...go on..." },
            { 738246987, "ううっ……！" },
            { 738246988, "Fuck... No..." },
            { 738246989, "This can't...be happening..." },
            { 738246990, "Not like this..." },
            { 738246991, "Sorry, Cinta..." },
            { 738246995, "ああっ……" },
            { 738246996, "I am...a disgrace..." },
            { 738246997, "I must...heal myself..." },
            { 738246998, "Can't... Ugh..." },
            { 738246999, "Forgive me..." },
            { 738247000, "This cannot be..." },
            { 738247004, "Wouldn't these battles go more smoothly if you actually worked together?" },
            { 738247005, "You know, my life would go more smoothly if you'd stay quiet once in a while." },
            { 738247006, "I suppose that was...unobjectionable." },
            { 738247007, "Then why do you keep objecting?" },
            { 738247008, "Shall we move on?" },
            { 738247009, "Fine by me." },
            { 738247012, "No match for us!" },
            { 738247013, "Pride ill becomes you." },
            { 738247014, "What she said." },
            { 738247015, "That was too easy!" },
            { 738247016, "Then you're ready for our next battle?" },
            { 738247017, "I could go all day!" },
            { 738247018, "Good. You might have to." },
            { 738247019, "All done." },
            { 738247020, "On to the next unlucky victim!" },
            { 738247021, "Gotta keep moving." },
            { 738247022, "You're right. Come on." },
            { 738247023, "Feel bad for anyone standing in our way." },
            { 738247024, "Not too bad, I hope." },
            { 738247025, "Are you hurt?" },
            { 738247026, "Not a scratch on me. Or you, I hope." },
            { 738247027, "Wow. That was close." },
            { 738247028, "A little. But one must never panic." },
            { 738247029, "That's her polite way of saying you were fighting like a headless chicken." },
            { 738247030, "Whew... Finally got 'em." },
            { 738247031, "Fighting is just slowing us down." },
            { 738247032, "Was that tough? Because that felt tough." },
            { 738247033, "Tend your wounds if need be, and let us continue on our way." },
            { 738247034, "Ugh, that was exhausting..." },
            { 738247035, "Perhaps if you approached the enemy more tactically?" },
            { 738247036, "Glad that's over..." },
            { 738247037, "Let's hope there's less trouble ahead..." },
            { 738247038, "A hard-won victory." },
            { 738247039, "Ugh, I can do better!" },
            { 738247040, "Look at you, working up a sweat." },
            { 738247041, "I know, right? I'm trying here...unlike some of us." },
            { 738247042, "Could really use a break..." },
            { 738247043, "I'm certainly with you there..." },
            { 738247044, "Couldn't have done that without you." },
            { 738247045, "We're a team, Thalia. Give yourself some credit." },
            { 738247046, "I didn't expect that much of a challenge." },
            { 738247047, "Lucky we've got each other then, huh?" },
            { 738247048, "Suddenly feeling better..." },
            { 738247049, "My wounds are healing!" },
            { 738247050, "That's the good stuff." },
            { 738247051, "Whew... Yeah. that feels good." },
            { 738247052, "Cinta, you're a literal lifesaver." },
            { 738247053, "Thanks, Cinta!" },
            { 738247090, "Heal your wounds, Thalia!" },
            { 738247091, "I'm trying already!" },
            { 738247092, "Owww..." },
            { 738247093, "Can you heal yourself?" },
            { 738247094, "How are you feeling?" },
            { 738247095, "Like I could use a healing draught or two..." },
            { 738247096, "You're hurt, Thalia." },
            { 738247097, "I know. Gotta heal up." },
            { 738247098, "I should really take care of these wounds..." },
            { 738247099, "That sounds like a good idea." },
            { 738247120, "I must find a way to heal." },
            { 738247121, "This is not ideal..." },
            { 738247122, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738247123, "How could I have been so careless?" },
            { 738247124, "Flagging...somewhat..." },
            { 738247125, "Must...move..." },
            { 738247126, "What's...wrong with me...?" },
            { 738247127, "Why...?" },
            { 738247148, "They built 'em big here, huh?" },
            { 738247149, "Indeed. The Cognoscents' Guilds were modeled on buildings such as these." },
            { 738247150, "What kind of people used to live here?" },
            { 738247151, "If the tales are to be believed, this was a place of learning. Much of what we know today was discovered here." },
            { 738247152, "So why was this place abandoned?" },
            { 738247153, "They say that as the buildings aged, it was no longer safe to live here." },
            { 738247154, "These crystal things have smothered everything..." },
            { 738247155, "And they will keep spreading if we do not destroy that tree." },
            { 738247156, "So how do we know that the tree won't just...topple over and crush us when we destroy the roots?" },
            { 738247157, "We don't. But there is no other way." },
            { 738247158, "You think any of the townspeople are still alive?" },
            { 738247159, "Most were evacuated in time. But I fear some may still remain..." },
            { 738247160, "Okay, this is one tall tree. Do not look down, do not look down..." },
            { 738247161, "But please do watch where you step." },
            { 738247162, "Man, this tree sprang up real quick. Like, what...in a matter of hours?" },
            { 738247163, "Indeed. It is possessed of a formidable power, there is no doubting that." },
            { 738247164, "Wish I knew why this tree was so important..." },
            { 738247165, "As do I. It must play an important role in their ceremony..." },
            { 738247166, "Let's go!" },
            { 738247167, "Let's." },
            { 738247168, "Time to fly!" },
            { 738247169, "Very well." },
            { 738247170, "Let's get moving!" },
            { 738247171, "Stay alert!" },
            { 738247172, "Here we go!" },
            { 738247173, "I'm right behind you." },
            { 738247174, "Alley-oop!" },
            { 738247175, "After you." },
            { 738247176, "Ngh! Dammit!" },
            { 738247177, "Are you alright?" },
            { 738247178, "Ugh! Aw, my ankle..." },
            { 738247179, "Must you be so reckless?" },
            { 738247180, "Oof! Whoa. Okay, that could have been a lot worse." },
            { 738247181, "Sometimes you worry me..." },
            { 738247182, "Are you hurt?" },
            { 738247183, "N-no...!" },
            { 738247184, "What happened?" },
            { 738247185, "Yeah, I kinda botched that landing..." },
            { 738247186, "Is something the matter?" },
            { 738247187, "Huh? Oh, sorry. No, I just...spaced out for a sec." },
            { 738247188, "We really must keep moving." },
            { 738247189, "Yeah, I know, so you keep saying..." },
            { 738247190, "You look troubled." },
            { 738247191, "Just, you know... Got a lot to think about." },
            { 738247192, "Hello? Hellooo? Wake up, Frey!" },
            { 738247193, "Huh? Oh no, I'm awake! I was just...thinking." },
            { 738247194, "Where are you going?" },
            { 738247195, "That's the wrong way." },
            { 738247196, "Are you going somewhere?" },
            { 738247197, "We don't have time for detours." },
            { 738247198, "Not that way." },
            { 738247199, "You're heading in the wrong direction." },
            { 738247208, "Hey, Cinta? Think we can take a quick break?" },
            { 738247209, "Of course, Thalia. We've certainly earned one." },
            { 738247210, "The Rheddig won't be coming back here anytime soon." },
            { 738247211, "Good. 'Cause I need a break before we keep going." },
