            { 738247267, "EPILOGUE" },
            { 738247272, "Name: Matilda Schram\nBirthplace: Bjarg, Visoria\nRank/Unit: Praetorian, Tanta Olas's Personal Guard\nNext of Kin: Asmi (Mother), William (Father)\nNote: ..." },
            { 738247273, "Name: Edith Somoza\nBirthplace: Visoria Castle Town\nRank/Unit: Praetorian, Tanta Olas's Personal Guard\nNext of Kin: Nicolette (Mother), Milo (Father)\nN..." },
            { 738247274, "Name: Gillian Strom\nBirthplace: Visoria Castle Town\nRank/Unit: Praetorian, Tanta Olas's Personal Guard\nNext of Kin: Bard (Father), Ava (Sister)\nNote: ..." },
            { 738247275, "Name: Mabely Duganur\nBirthplace: Graenn, Visoria\nRank/Unit: Praetorian, Tanta Olas's Personal Guard\nNext of Kin: Oriana (Mother), Finnian (Father), Tr..." },
            { 738247292, "(Hold) Restore All to Default" },
            { 738247293, "Are you sure you want to restore all the settings on this page to their defaults?" },
            { 738247294, "Enthalpy" },
            { 738247295, "Summons a deadly force field centered on a single enemy." },
            { 738247296, "Sliver" },
            { 738247297, "Fires magical energy at enemies." },
            { 738247298, "Slash" },
            { 738247299, "Slashes enemies with a magical sword." },
            { 738247300, "Am I going nuts, or did that thing just say my name?" },
            { 738247301, "Well, as with all ominous glowing objects, I'd advise you to steer well clear." },
            { 738247302, "I dunno... My Tanta instinct's telling me I should check it out." },
            { 738247303, "When this goes wrong, do remember that I told you so..." },
            { 738247310, "Frey..." },
            { 738247312, "Yes, I'd quite like to know that, too..." },
            { 738247313, "Okay, what is this place? Where are we?" },
            { 738247314, "It looks like we're in some kind of war zone..." },
            { 738247315, "Might I suggest we take the dead man's advice and leave before whoever tried to kill Thalia comes back?" },
            { 738247316, "Alright... I'll agree with you on that..." },
            { 738247317, "Let's find somewhere with a view, take a look around." },
            { 738247334, "Why do I feel like we've been here before?" },
            { 738247335, "Whoa. This is some new shit, too..." },
            { 738247336, "Perhaps it's thanks to your...\"tattoo,\" was it?" },
            { 738247337, "You! How did you get out of there!?" },
            { 738247338, "Sorry, but you're gonna have to step aside!" },
            { 738247345, "The vessel is escaping! Stop her!" },
            { 738247346, "Shit. Not again." },
            { 738247347, "Enjoy your fight!" },
            { 738247350, "Well, we won't be leaving by torana. We must find another way. Follow me." },
            { 738247351, "Stay still." },
            { 738247352, "We've had word of an intruder." },
            { 738247353, "Find them. Quickly. And do what you must. May the deaths of the sinners cleanse them." },
            { 738247354, "May the deaths of the sinners cleanse them!" },
            { 738247355, "It will be quicker to avoid them than to eliminate them. This way." },
            { 738247356, "Here we are." },
            { 738247357, "Huh? We're going through here?" },
            { 738247360, "So you can't torana all the way out of here...but you can still teleport? Then how come we're still walking everywhere?" },
            { 738247361, "To move both of us would require energy I cannot afford to spare." },
            { 738247362, "Gotcha. You're saving your energy...just in case." },
            { 738247372, "Stay close. More soldiers." },
            { 738247373, "And the Tree?" },
            { 738247374, "The general says more offerings are required." },
            { 738247376, "Then all proceeds according to plan. May the deaths of the sinners cleanse them!" },
            { 738247377, "May the deaths of the sinners cleanse them!" },
            { 738247388, "Oh, I was merely...dismayed at the prospect of losing such a capable soldier." },
            { 738247389, "But you... You're fine. We must be going." },
            { 738247390, "Right..." },
            { 738247394, "Please! Spare meee!!!" },
            { 738247395, "Cinta!?" },
            { 738247396, "Do not lose heart, brave warriors of Rheddah! What is one root? Nothing! The Tree of Offering stands tall!" },
            { 738247397, "Its veins course with the light of the lives we have offered! Our victory is all but assured!" },
            { 738247398, "The time draws nigh! Press on! We shall prevail!" },
            { 738247399, "Yeah, you keep telling them that. You're already done." },
            { 738247400, "Let us hope so..." },
            { 738247401, "Quite the opposition. Ready, Thalia?" },
            { 738247402, "Brave warriors of Rheddah! The Tree of Offering is near full-grown! This accursed land shall soon be cleansed!" },
            { 738247403, "One task, and one task alone, remains to us: we must protect the Tree, though it cost every last one of our lives!" },
            { 738247406, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738247408, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738247409, "Unlike Cinta, I haven't forgotten what it means to be a Tanta." },
            { 738247410, "I don't suppose you've got a plan...?" },
            { 738247411, "Wait for the right moment, then give me the sign to strike." },
            { 738247412, "Ngh! We're not doing enough!" },
            { 738247413, "Huh? Are those...traces of Cinta's magic?" },
            { 738247414, "Whoa! What was that?" },
            { 738247415, "Did our powers just...react with one another?" },
            { 738247416, "Hey, its shield is down!" },
            { 738247417, "Then we must act! Now!" },
            { 738247418, "Let's go!" },
            { 738247419, "Ignore him, Thalia. He seeks to sow discord, nothing more." },
            { 738247420, "...Perhaps we should investigate." },
            { 738247421, "Frey..." },
            { 738247422, "There it is again!" },
            { 738247423, "And again, I suggest you steer clear. It's clearly dangerous." },
            { 738247424, "Says the demon of Rheddah, vengeance personified." },
            { 738247426, "Is this...Visoria...?" },
            { 738247427, "Visoria before the Break. Rather different, isn't it?" },
            { 738247428, "Hang on, did we...time-travel!? No no no no, no way. That is not a thing." },
            { 738247429, "Stop." },
            { 738247430, "Hurry! The vessel has escaped!" },
            { 738247431, "It appears your absence has been noticed." },
            { 738247432, "There's gonna be more of them looking for me." },
            { 738247433, "Undoubtedly. We must keep moving." },
            { 738247434, "Faster. We cannot afford to dally." },
            { 738247440, "Hurry!" },
            { 738247441, "Stop right there! You're not getting away this time!" },
            { 738247442, "We have little choice but to fight." },
            { 738247443, "I'm right behind you!" },
            { 738247444, "Feel so heavy..." },
            { 738247449, "Careful now." },
            { 738247450, "Time to kick some major ass." },
            { 738247451, "Where exactly were you trained?" },
            { 738247452, "\"Enemies!\"" },
            { 738247453, "Ready, Thalia?" },
            { 738247454, "And raring to go!" },
            { 738247455, "I'll be working hard...just watching." },
            { 738247456, "What was that?" },
            { 738247457, "Of course they have! They're sworn enemies!" },
            { 738247458, "Hm. Next time, you might want to try—" },
            { 738247459, "Oh no. No backseat battling." },
            { 738247460, "Yes, please!" },
            { 738247461, "Use that wisely." },
            { 738247462, "Nice find." },
            { 738247463, "Put that to good use." },
            { 738247464, "Was just thinking I needed one of these!" },
            { 738247465, "A lucky find, then." },
            { 738247466, "Always useful." },
            { 738247467, "You got that right." },
            { 738247468, "Put it somewhere safe." },
            { 738247469, "Oh, I will!" },
            { 738247470, "What's that rubbish?" },
            { 738247471, "You know exactly what it is. Man, you are so annoying." },
            { 738247472, "Let's see..." },
            { 738247473, "Yes, let's..." },
            { 738247474, "Ooh, look..." },
            { 738247475, "What is it?" },
            { 738247476, "C'mon, chest! Gimme something good!" },
            { 738247477, "Come on, Thalia. We have places to be." },
            { 738247478, "Interesting..." },
            { 738247479, "I'm sure it is, but we must keep moving." },
            { 738247480, "What do we have here?" },
            { 738247481, "Well? What is it? Come on, do share!" },
            { 738247482, "Whoa, sweet." },
            { 738247483, "Something good?" },
            { 738247484, "Ngh..." },
            { 738247485, "Cinta!" },
            { 738247486, "No..." },
            { 738247487, "Hey! You okay!?" },
            { 738247488, "Huh? Cinta?" },
            { 738247489, "I just need...some time..." },
            { 738247490, "Cinta! You don't look so good..." },
            { 738247491, "Don't worry about me... Stay focused!" },
            { 738247492, "はあ……はあ……" },
            { 738247493, "Cinta! I'm coming!" },
            { 738247494, "Urgh..." },
            { 738247495, "Shit, she's in trouble!" },
            { 738247496, "Ah!" },
            { 738247497, "Cinta? What's going on?" },
            { 738247498, "Oh no..." },
            { 738247499, "Cinta doesn't look too good..." },
            { 738247500, "Ugh! No..." },
            { 738247501, "Hey! Hang in there!" },
            { 738247502, "Ngh..." },
            { 738247503, "Are you okay?" },
            { 738247504, "It seems the threat here has been neutralized." },
            { 738247505, "Some good news for once." },
            { 738247506, "Perhaps we should stop and catch our breath." },
            { 738247507, "Oh, please say I can take a nap..." },
            { 738247508, "Hooray. No more assholes." },
            { 738247509, "That's certainly worth celebrating." },
            { 738247510, "Think this place is safe now." },
            { 738247511, "We can take a few minutes if you need to rest." },
            { 738247512, "This should make our lives easier." },
            { 738247513, "Finally, a gift from the heavens." },
            { 738247514, "Splendid." },
            { 738247515, "Yeah. I'm sure not gonna complain." },
            { 738247516, "This should be useful." },
            { 738247517, "Tell me about it." },
            { 738247518, "Feel a bit safer." },
            { 738247519, "As do I." },
            { 738247520, "Now I've just gotta find more healing draughts..." },
            { 738247521, "And we must be sure not to waste them." },
            { 738247522, "Thank you very much!" },
            { 738247523, "Who are you thanking, exactly?" },
            { 738247524, "Feeling well rested?" },
            { 738247525, "Absolutely. Let's go!" },
            { 738247526, "Ahh, that felt good." },
            { 738247527, "Glad to hear it! Are you ready?" },
            { 738247528, "That helped, I hope?" },
            { 738247529, "Oh yeah. Successfully de-fatigueified." },
            { 738247530, "Alright! I am fully rested and fighting fit!" },
            { 738247531, "I'll take that to mean you're ready to leave." },
            { 738247532, "Ahhh. Charge level: one hundred percent." },
            { 738247533, "You have an odd way with words...but I take it you're feeling better." },
            { 738247534, "What would happen if you aimed your own magic at them, I wonder..." },
