            { 738247727, "<buttonAttackMagic>/<buttonSupportMagic> + <buttonMovement> + <buttonParkour> (Hold): Perform Dodge Roll" },
            { 738247728, "A match...? Excellent. We have ourselves a vessel." },
            { 738247729, "Take her to the dungeons!" },
            { 738247730, "And ready the Tree of Offering." },
            { 738247732, "This time, the Gloaming shall not fail." },
            { 738247733, "To kill you. And make my escape." },
            { 738247734, "And hurt a lot of people." },
            { 738247738, "Olas's personal guard? Thalia was one of them, right?" },
            { 738247739, "If I remember correctly, yes. Although I also seem to recall something about them having been mercilessly slaughtered..." },
            { 738247740, "An explosion on an island north of Junoon?" },
            { 738247741, "I expect the Tantas made some sort of monumental blunder." },
            { 738247743, "You are familiar with them?" },
            { 738247744, "Uh, maybe? I don't know why they'd be here, but I'm guessing the Rheddig have something to do with it." },
            { 738247745, "Whatever they are, I suspect they're the reason we can't leave Visoria by torana." },
            { 738247746, "I suggest we find the source of their power—and fast." },
            { 738247749, "If I..." },
            { 738247750, "You will bring death to the entire realm." },
            { 738247752, "Look out!" },
            { 738247753, "Thalia, move!" },
            { 738247754, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738247755, "Haa... Haa... Haa..." },
            { 738247756, "Is it gone? Are we good?" },
            { 738247757, "It's not over yet. We need to get to safety." },
            { 738247758, "<iconChapterSumVfx>What were you thinking, coming all the way out here because of some voice in your head? Don't get me wrong, I'm positively thrilled..." },
