            { 738247825, "Frey Holland. Daydreamer. Cat lover. New Yorker." },
            { 738247826, "On a fateful evening, her life changed drastically when she was mysteriously transported to the beautiful, treacherous land of Athia." },
            { 738247827, "Frey arrives with a magical, sentient bracelet inexplicably wrapped around her arm." },
            { 738247828, "Then discovers she can cast powerful spells, and use magic to swiftly traverse the sprawling landscapes." },
            { 738247829, "The last remnants of Athia's populace soon look to Frey as their only hope for confronting the Tantas—once-benevolent matriarchs who now rule as madde..." },
            { 738247830, "Reluctant to help, but desperate to find a way back home, Frey sets off on a journey through this strange and dangerous land." },
            { 738247831, "You can't change your current quest while in an illusory space." },
