            { 738247872, "Return to Title Screen" },
            { 738247873, "Controller Volume" },
            { 738247874, "Set the volume level of sound played through the controller." },
            { 738247875, "（攻撃アドリブ）" },
            { 738247876, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738247877, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738247878, "Hey, Cuff..." },
            { 738247879, "What do you want to talk to Cuff about?" },
            { 738247880, "Talk about Thalia." },
            { 738247881, "Talk about Cinta." },
            { 738247882, "Talk about the Rheddigs' masks." },
            { 738247883, "Never mind." },
            { 738247884, "Do you think things played out this way with Thalia? Like, was she captured too? Did she try to escape Visoria with Cinta?" },
            { 738247885, "It's possible, I suppose." },
            { 738247886, "Hmm. I wonder what they would've talked about..." },
            { 738247887, "One can only speculate...but let's not, eh? We have things to do." },
            { 738247888, "Does Cinta seem a little...strange to you?" },
            { 738247889, "Strange compared to what, exactly?" },
            { 738247890, "I dunno. I just thought she'd be...warmer and fuzzier. But she's all business." },
            { 738247891, "And how else would you expect her to be in the middle of a \"war zone,\" as you put it?" },
            { 738247892, "Yeah, I guess..." },
            { 738247893, "Those bird masks the Rheddig wear—they're pretty wild, huh?" },
            { 738247894, "I happen to think they're rather noble." },
            { 738247895, "I mean I guess you would, seeing as you're basically made of birds... Is that your people's thing or something?" },
            { 738247896, "And what if it is? A bird looks down on all creation from the freedom of the skies. A fitting symbol of superiority." },
            { 738247897, "Yeah, until it gets eaten by a cat..." },
            { 738247898, "What do you want to talk to Cuff about?" },
            { 738247899, "Talk about Olas's personal guard." },
            { 738247900, "Talk about the Tree of Offering." },
            { 738247901, "Talk about the crystals." },
            { 738247902, "Never mind." },
            { 738247903, "Thalia was part of Olas's personal guard, right? Wonder if any of them survived..." },
            { 738247904, "I rather doubt it, judging by the state of this place." },
            { 738247905, "She must have been pissed seeing what they did to her homeland. I know I would've been..." },
            { 738247906, "Are you actually getting upset? You didn't even know the woman." },
            { 738247907, "Maybe not, but...I dunno, I think I can...feel what she felt. Like, her emotions are...bleeding into mine or something." },
            { 738247908, "It's probably just your imagination." },
            { 738247909, "Giant trees, weird roots... You don't know anything about this stuff, do you?" },
            { 738247910, "Do you think I'd tell you if I did?" },
            { 738247911, "So you don't. Okay, gotcha. Probably above your pay grade anyway." },
            { 738247912, "Above my— I am the destroyer of Athia. Bane of the Tantas. *Nothing* is above my pay grade, thank you very much." },
            { 738247913, "I have far more important things to worry about than...shrubbery, that's all." },
            { 738247914, "Spoken like a true destroyer of worlds." },
            { 738247915, "The crystals we've been seeing around town—they're a lot like Breakshards, aren't they?" },
            { 738247916, "Hmm... Sort of. But also...not." },
            { 738247917, "Meaning?" },
            { 738247918, "Well, the Break was a result of the Rheddig's power—my power—fusing with that of the Tantas." },
            { 738247919, "The crystals here only represent the Rheddig part of the equation." },
            { 738247920, "So...Tanta magic plus these crystals...might equal the Break? Interesting..." },
            { 738247921, "Hey..." },
            { 738247922, "What do you want to talk to Cinta about?" },
            { 738247923, "Talk about Tanta Olas." },
            { 738247924, "Talk about Thalia." },
            { 738247925, "Talk about Robian." },
            { 738247926, "Talk about Susurrus." },
            { 738247927, "Never mind." },
            { 738247928, "You said you came here because Olas asked you to. Are the two of you close?" },
            { 738247929, "Of course. She is a Tanta. A sister. But...yes. Perhaps we are closer than the others." },
            { 738247930, "Prav and Sila do not always appreciate my way of thinking. Olas and I... We understand one another." },
            { 738247931, "Sounds like me and Auden..." },
            { 738247932, "Auden?" },
            { 738247933, "Oh, uh... Nothing." },
            { 738247934, "Did Olas tell you anything about Thali—I mean...me?" },
            { 738247935, "Only that you are the youngest of her personal guard. And the most dedicated." },
            { 738247936, "Huh... It's, uh...nice of her to say so..." },
            { 738247937, "...And that you can be somewhat reckless." },
            { 738247938, "Ha. Like possessor, like possessed." },
            { 738247939, "So, uh...how's Robian?" },
            { 738247940, "Robian Keen? You know him?" },
            { 738247941, "He, uh, helped me out once. I got stuck somewhere, and he, um...kinda showed me the way home." },
            { 738247942, "Is that so? He is well. The birth of his daughter has softened the sober scholar we once knew." },
            { 738247943, "Glad to hear it. She's a lucky kid, having such a nice guy for a dad." },
            { 738247944, "She is." },
            { 738247945, "Cinta... There's something I think I should tell you." },
            { 738247946, "Yes?" },
            { 738247947, "I don't know how to say this, but...Athia's in danger. This thing, Susur—" },
            { 738247948, "What? What is it?" },
            { 738247949, "I said, Susur—" },
            { 738247950, "Weren't you listening to your friend, the mysterious disembodied voice? No changing the past. That's cheating." },
            { 738247951, "You know what? Never mind." },
            { 738247952, "Odd child..." },
            { 738247953, "What do you want to talk to Cuff about?" },
            { 738247954, "Talk about Thalia." },
            { 738247955, "Talk about Aldacor." },
            { 738247956, "Talk about Susurrus." },
            { 738247957, "Never mind." },
            { 738247958, "Hey... Do you think Thalia's still alive in our time? I don't remember a Thalia back in Cipal..." },
            { 738247959, "I'd say the chances of her surviving the Rheddig *and* the Break are slim to none." },
            { 738247960, "Oh. Well, I wonder what goes through your head before you die..." },
            { 738247961, "Stick around long enough, and you might find out..." },
            { 738247962, "So why exactly does Aldacor need a gigantic tree?" },
            { 738247963, "I believe it channels the sacrifices somehow." },
            { 738247964, "Yeah, but why make the sacrifices in the first place?" },
            { 738247965, "Oh, you know—putting your enemies to the sword, basking in their cries and lamentations. Standard wartime behavior." },
            { 738247966, "Were Aldacor and the tree gone by the time you showed up in Athia?" },
            { 738247967, "Yes. Why do you ask?" },
            { 738247968, "Because that means Cinta and Thalia did it—they beat them! They destroyed the tree!" },
            { 738247969, "I suppose it does. As to whether they escaped in one piece or not—that's another matter." },
            { 738247970, "What do you want to talk to Cuff about?" },
            { 738247971, "Talk about what's at the top of the tree." },
            { 738247972, "Talk about Thalia's feelings." },
            { 738247973, "Talk about the Gloaming." },
            { 738247974, "Never mind." },
            { 738247975, "What makes you so sure Aldacor is at the top of the tree, anyway?" },
            { 738247976, "Well, I don't see him down here, do you? Which means he's probably off somewhere making more \"offerings.\"" },
            { 738247977, "And my gut tells me that \"somewhere\" is up." },
            { 738247978, "Ah. So a complete guess, then?" },
            { 738247979, "You know, I really think Thalia and I would have gotten along." },
            { 738247980, "And why is that, pray tell?" },
            { 738247981, "She was willing to put everything on the line for the people she cared about." },
            { 738247982, "Just like me. And Cinta." },
            { 738247983, "And you know this how, exactly? Your famous Tanta instinct, perhaps?" },
            { 738247984, "No, it's... I just...can feel it. I know this is what she would have wanted." },
            { 738247985, "So you know nothing about this \"ceremony\" we keep hearing about?" },
            { 738247986, "Not a sausage. Sorry. But I imagine it's suitably poignant and dramatic." },
            { 738247987, "And this theory is based on what, exactly?" },
            { 738247988, "Oh, I don't know. Call it a sort of...patriotic instinct." },
            { 738247990, "Enough of this!" },
            { 738247991, "Notgoodnotgoodnotgood!" },
            { 738247992, "Get in the air! Quickly!" },
            { 738247993, "Holy shit!" },
            { 738247994, "His is no ordinary power!" },
            { 738247995, "You're kidding me!" },
            { 738247996, "Jump! You'll know when!" },
            { 738247997, "Here it comes!" },
            { 738247998, "Got it!" },
            { 738248000, "What do you mean, \"what\"?" },
            { 738248001, "\"The truth lies in Visoria...\"?" },
            { 738248002, "What is this?" },
            { 738248003, "Their talisman, of course. You do not recognize it?" },
            { 738248004, "Yeah, uh, sorry. Memory's still hazy from whatever the Rheddig did to me..." },
            { 738248005, "It must be taken to the Mausoleum in Cipal." },
            { 738248006, "The dead must be honored, as is the custom." },
            { 738248007, "Riiight. Yeah... Course I remember..." },
            { 738248008, "But they cannot be honored if we do not make it out of here. Come..." },
            { 738248009, "We're not going over this again, Cuff. Don't tell me you're afraid." },
            { 738248010, "...We must climb it. It is time." },
            { 738248011, "Agreed. Let's make tracks." },
            { 738248012, "Boost" },
            { 738248013, "Climb even higher by using Vault several times in quick succession." },
            { 738248014, "Guess I'm fighting this thing...!" },
            { 738248015, "Fuck! Why is my magic not working!?" },
            { 738248016, "Nope, still not working!" },
            { 738248017, "Do not waste your energy! The beast is protected!" },
            { 738248018, "Oh yeah? Oh, I hadn't noticed!" },
            { 738248019, "Try to avoid it until I have recovered my strength!" },
            { 738248020, "Easier said than done!" },
            { 738248021, "Talk about the enormous beast." },
            { 738248022, "Do you think the Rheddig really can make Breakbeasts?" },
            { 738248023, "Well, they did make me. And I'd say that requires a lot more finesse." },
            { 738248024, "I guess. Just can't imagine anyone wanting to do something like that..." },
            { 738248025, "You sound almost scared. Surely not? The mighty Tanta Frey?" },
            { 738248026, "Wonder if this has something to do with what the voice was talking about..." },
            { 738248027, "Talk about the people being sacrificed." },
            { 738248028, "What do you think that guy meant? All that shit about \"honor\" and \"sin\"?" },
            { 738248029, "I got the sense those people were killed as some sort of sacrifice." },
            { 738248030, "Well that's not foreboding at all." },
            { 738248031, "Perhaps if you can find out why the Rheddig were sacrificing them, you might learn something useful." },
            { 738248032, "Yeah, maybe..." },
            { 738248033, "If I could learn how to control the Break like them...maybe it would help me save Athia." },
            { 738248034, "Yes. That, or it might consume you utterly..." },
            { 738248035, "Athian Soldier" },
            { 738248036, "They blocked the way ahead..." },
            { 738248037, "Well, you won't be vaulting nimbly over an obstacle like that in your current state." },
            { 738248038, "Wait—over there. I might be able to squeeze through." },
            { 738248039, "S-stay away!" },
            { 738248040, "There is nowhere to hide!" },
            { 738248041, "Who was that?" },
            { 738248042, "It looked to me like a bold Rheddig soldier chasing down a cowardly Athian dog." },
            { 738248043, "\"Rheddig\"? As in...your pals who invaded Athia, the Rheddig?" },
            { 738248044, "Anything?" },
            { 738248045, "Not yet. Keep looking!" },
            { 738248046, "Shit. We'd better keep moving." },
            { 738248047, "You know, I do believe we might've found ourselves in the midst of my people's glorious and entirely righteous invasion." },
            { 738248048, "Huh? Okay, I can barely process suddenly being someone else. You're gonna have to give me a sec." },
            { 738248049, "I'm not sure how much of a \"sec\" we can afford. May I suggest we find somewhere safe, and quickly?" },
            { 738248050, "There! Get him!" },
            { 738248051, "Aaaaaahhh!" },
            { 738248052, "Don't let him get away!" },
            { 738248053, "There'll be more! Find them!" },
            { 738248054, "Over there!" },
            { 738248055, "Not rushing to anyone's rescue?" },
            { 738248056, "In this shape? I've gotta get a handle on the situation first. Maybe see if I can get a view of the city..." },
            { 738248058, "Marked" },
            { 738248059, "Get past the barricade." },
            { 738248060, "Get past the barricade." },
            { 738248061, "What do you want to talk to Cuff about?" },
            { 738248062, "Never mind." },
            { 738248063, "Alright, time to give my new magic a whirl!" },
            { 738248064, "Why do I get the feeling you're about to badly hurt yourself?" },
            { 738248065, "Hey, if you've got any better ideas!" },
            { 738248066, "Congratulations. You didn't die." },
            { 738248067, "Whatever. Let's get out of here." },
            { 738248068, "Ugh! Really missing my moves right now!" },
            { 738248069, "Yes, you do seem rather ungainly." },
            { 738248070, "Wanna stop talking and start helping?" },
            { 738248071, "Trying as it may be, you'll have to fight without me for a change. My abilities don't seem to work here." },
            { 738248072, "So I get all your personality and none of your powers? Great. Talk about the worst of both worlds." },
            { 738248073, "Oh come on now, Frey. You were going to have to learn to stand on your own two feet one day." },
            { 738248074, "Okay... That was...a lot." },
            { 738248075, "Well, I hope you're ready for more." },
            { 738248076, "Fuck..." },
            { 738248077, "Wait." },
            { 738248078, "Stay there." },
            { 738248079, "Enemies!" },
            { 738248080, "Let them pass" },
            { 738248081, "Over here!" },
            { 738248082, "Hurry!" },
            { 738248083, "This way!" },
            { 738248084, "Quietly!" },
            { 738248085, "Stay low!" },
            { 738248086, "Stay close." },
            { 738248087, "We'll let them pass." },
            { 738248088, "Shh!" },
            { 738248089, "Quickly!" },
            { 738248090, "Got it." },
            { 738248091, "Okay." },
            { 738248092, "Hold on." },
            { 738248093, "Uh-huh." },
            { 738248094, "Sorry!" },
            { 738248095, "I know..." },
            { 738248096, "Here we go..." },
            { 738248097, "You there!" },
            { 738248098, "Get them!" },
            { 738248099, "Intruders!" },
            { 738248100, "It's the vessel!" },
            { 738248101, "Someone's there!" },
            { 738248102, "They say one of the Tantas might be here in Visoria..." },
            { 738248103, "Which one? Olas, I suppose." },
            { 738248104, "They're not sure. Anyway, be on your guard." },
            { 738248105, "How did the vessel even escape?" },
            { 738248106, "Broke the lock on her cell door, apparently." },
            { 738248107, "So she has the same powers as the other one?" },
            { 738248108, "That or the intruder we're looking for let her out." },
            { 738248109, "You're right. Seems more likely..." },
            { 738248110, "How go the preparations for the rite?" },
            { 738248111, "The roots have taken hold. We just need to keep the offerings coming." },
            { 738248112, "Glad to hear it. Keep thinking this place is about to fall down around our ears." },
            { 738248113, "It's old, that's for certain. Looks like no one's been down here in years." },
            { 738248114, "Wonder if there's anything valuable down here? Might be able to make some—" },
            { 738248115, "Don't even say it! What if the general heard you!?" },
            { 738248116, "Find them! They must not get away! For Rheddah!" },
            { 738248117, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738248118, "They're searching for us. Stay very close." },
            { 738248119, "They can't have gone far! Leave no stone unturned!" },
            { 738248120, "Find the vessel!" },
            { 738248121, "More word of the intruder! Find them and kill them!" },
            { 738248122, "Move! Move!!!" },
            { 738248123, "Get a move on! Find the vessel!" },
            { 738248124, "I met one of their generals earlier. At least I think he was." },
            { 738248125, "He stuck a...thing into my arm, and now I've got this weird tattoo—" },
            { 738248126, "Aldacor. One of their most formidable warriors." },
            { 738248127, "And if the rumors are to be believed, a man with a keen interest in human experimentation." },
            { 738248128, "Ooh. I think I'd like to get to know the good general a little better." },
            { 738248129, "Stop! Rheddig up ahead!" },
            { 738248130, "This way!" },
            { 738248131, "Don't make a sound." },
            { 738248132, "The vessel has escaped!" },
            { 738248133, "How is that possible!?" },
            { 738248134, "Find her, damn you!" },
            { 738248135, "We don't have long. Quickly." },
            { 738248136, "The only safe route lies ahead. Go. I will keep watch." },
            { 738248137, "Okay..." },
            { 738248138, "Well, this is...cozy. Was there really no other way?" },
            { 738248139, "That the Rheddig weren't aware of? No." },
            { 738248140, "Even Homer could barely squeeze through here..." },
            { 738248141, "Less chatter. We must keep moving." },
            { 738248142, "We can't find the vessel anywhere!" },
            { 738248143, "Can't have gone far!" },
            { 738248144, "Hmm... What about in here...?" },
            { 738248145, "Fool! Who'd fit in there!?" },
            { 738248146, "Oh, um... Of course! Heh..." },
            { 738248147, "Seems your mother's shrewder than she looks." },
            { 738248148, "Oh, man. That was way too close..." },
            { 738248149, "This way. Follow me." },
            { 738248150, "There are too many of them. Then we have little choice..." },
            { 738248152, "This way." },
            { 738248153, "Uh...this is a dead end." },
            { 738248154, "Is it?" },
            { 738248155, "Whoa. Was that one of Olas's illusions?" },
            { 738248156, "Not hers—one of her predecessor's. They were put in place for emergencies such as this." },
            { 738248157, "Over here!" },
            { 738248158, "Uh-oh." },
            { 738248159, "Through here." },
            { 738248160, "More tremors..." },
            { 738248161, "We need more offerings for the Tree." },
            { 738248162, "Then we shall find them." },
            { 738248163, "Now is our chance. We must strike while they are distracted." },
            { 738248164, "The exit isn't much farther. Come." },
            { 738248165, "Hey, what's that?" },
            { 738248166, "Who's there!?" },
            { 738248167, "Shit! Enemy alert!" },
            { 738248168, "Then we fight!" },
            { 738248169, "That appears to be the last of them." },
            { 738248170, "Maybe we should check out their camp. There could be some useful stuff, and...I'm kinda tired, not gonna lie." },
            { 738248171, "It might not be a bad idea to rest while we can..." },
            { 738248172, "Alright. We should be on our way." },
            { 738248176, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738248177, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738248178, "Cinta!" },
            { 738248179, "Not now!" },
            { 738248180, "Cin—! Aw, shit..." },
            { 738248181, "Maybe next time." },
            { 738248182, "You good, Cinta?" },
            { 738248183, "Give me a moment!" },
            { 738248184, "We are almost there. Come." },
            { 738248185, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738248186, "That will just lead us back where we came from. Come, to the exit." },
            { 738248187, "Just kidding! Coming..." },
            { 738248188, "What's that over there?" },
            { 738248189, "Wait, look..." },
            { 738248190, "...Hm?" },
            { 738248191, "Check it out." },
            { 738248192, "You see that?" },
            { 738248193, "Hey—over there." },
            { 738248194, "Hello there..." },
            { 738248195, "What do we have here?" },
            { 738248196, "Is that..." },
            { 738248197, "Look! You match!" },
            { 738248198, "One of your comrades, I presume. I am sorry..." },
            { 738248199, "May the deaths of the sinners cleanse them!" },
            { 738248200, "You are the ones who will die!" },
            { 738248201, "That takes care of them." },
            { 738248202, "Now for the root." },
            { 738248203, "So what exactly happens when the Tree reaches fruition?" },
            { 738248204, "The Athians pay the ultimate price. Need we know any more than that?" },
            { 738248205, "I suppose not. Let us win this war and return victorious." },
            { 738248206, "For Rheddah!" },
            { 738248207, "Are there even enough Athians here to bring the Tree to fruition?" },
            { 738248208, "It matters not. The general has a plan." },
            { 738248209, "And what might that be? Must we travel to other realms and bring back offerings from there?" },
            { 738248210, "That is not for us to know. Trust in the general. He will not fail us." },
            { 738248211, "The Tree...I have never seen its like. Who would have thought such a thing capable of keeping our enemies at bay?" },
            { 738248212, "Yes. The Tantas will not interfere while the barrier stands." },
            { 738248213, "But did one of them not \"interfere\" already?" },
            { 738248214, "Perhaps. But one Tanta alone is no match for the general." },
            { 738248215, "I do not doubt it. But things did not run smoothly last time. One cannot help but worry..." },
            { 738248216, "Why must the vessel be an Athian?" },
            { 738248217, "Your guess is as good as mine. But I am sure the general has his reasons." },
            { 738248218, "Bah. To have to rely on these filth..." },
            { 738248219, "Trawling these accursed lands to find the pieces we needed was bad enough." },
            { 738248220, "Aye, we sweated some to get what we needed for the Tree." },
            { 738248221, "At least now we have them, the rite can take place at last." },
            { 738248222, "<EmptyString>" },
            { 738248223, "What the fuck was that?" },
            { 738248224, "The beast we encountered before. Come on. Quickly." },
            { 738248225, "Let's finish this." },
            { 738248226, "We are currently beneath the castle." },
            { 738248227, "If we're going to face Aldacor, you'll need to be ready." },
            { 738248228, "All done here." },
            { 738248229, "Indeed. Up we go." },
            { 738248230, "More trouble. Why am I not surprised?" },
            { 738248231, "Out of our way! We will kill you if we must!" },
            { 738248232, "I expect the Rheddig will have more surprises in store." },
            { 738248233, "No no, you're kidding. There is no way that thing survived." },
            { 738248234, "It's not as strong as it used to be, but I wouldn't underestimate it." },
            { 738248235, "Yeah, I wasn't planning on it..." },
            { 738248236, "Together, Thalia! It's the only way to break through its defenses!" },
            { 738248237, "Alright, let's get him!" },
            { 738248238, "Need to find somewhere I can get a good look around..." },
            { 738248239, "Maybe getting out of here won't be so hard after all." },
            { 738248240, "We'll see..." },
            { 738248241, "Time to join forces with Cinta, perhaps?" },
            { 738248242, "Perhaps." },
            { 738248243, "Ready to hit 'em where it hurts?" },
            { 738248244, "But of course!" },
            { 738248245, "I'm ready when you are!" },
            { 738248246, "Ten-four!" },
            { 738248247, "What the—!?" },
            { 738248248, "Dear old magic to the rescue." },
