            { 738248618, "\"The truth lies in Visoria\"...? Um, the truth about what? Well, I'm here, so—huh? Did that light just say my name?" },
            { 738248619, "The Rheddig locked me in here... Who knows what kind of creepy shit they're planning to do to me? Let's put some distance between me and this cell, an..." },
            { 738248620, "What was that weird root thing? And what the hell is up with Cinta? Ugh, everything about this place feels wrong. I need to get out of here ASAP." },
            { 738248621, "The old me would probably have felt very differently, but I can see Cinta's just doing what she has to. And freaking out won't accomplish anything, so..." },
